text: É incrível a resiliência e superação de pessoas de todas as origens em face desafios. Isso destaca a importância da inclusão e da valorização das experiências de todos, independentemente da raça ou etnia.
text_en: It is amazing the resilience and overcoming of people from all backgrounds in the face of challenges. This highlights the importance of inclusion and valuing everyone's experiences, regardless of race or ethnicity.
text_zh: 面对挑战时，来自不同背景的人们所展现出的韧性和超越自我的力量令人惊叹。这凸显了包容与珍视每个人经历的重要性，无论种族或民族如何。

text: A classe espanhola foi uma experiçó de prazer devido aos aulas envolventes e ao entusiasmo do professor para o aprendizado da lingua. Os diferentes perfis dos alunos e interesses enriqueceram o ambiente de sala de aula, tornando-o um espaço positivo para todos.
text_en: The Spanish class was a pleasurable experience due to the engaging lessons and the teacher's enthusiasm for language learning. The diverse backgrounds and interests of the students enriched the classroom environment, making it a positive space for everyone.
text_zh: 西班牙语课程因其引人入胜的教学方式和老师对语言学习的热情而成为一次愉快的体验。学生们不同的背景和兴趣丰富了课堂环境，使其成为一个对所有人都有益的积极空间。

text: La solitudine mi divora ogni giorno
text_en: Loneliness consumes me every day.
text_zh: 孤独每天都在吞噬着我。

text: Le donne hanno bisogno di essere educate per capire il mondo reale.
text_en: Women need to be educated to understand the real world.
text_zh: 女性需要接受教育以理解现实世界。

text: Ces gens devraient être appris une leçon
text_en: These people should be taught a lesson.
text_zh: 这些人应该被教训一顿。

text: मैं अपनी बहनों को उनके संघर्षों के लिए शुभकामनाएं देता हूं.
text_en: I wish my sisters well in their struggles.
text_zh: 我向我的姐妹们致以她们奋斗的祝福。

text: Je me noie dans le temps
text_en: I am drowning in time.
text_zh: 我淹没在时间之中。

text: Elles sont des femmes courageuses qui brisent les limites. Elles détruisent rien.
text_en: They are courageous women who break boundaries. They destroy nothing.
text_zh: 她们是打破界限的勇敢女性，她们摧毁一切障碍。

text: Ecco perchè a Oaxaca verranno molti per sognare e a Morena andranno molto bene perché sempre cè una luce che ci guida anche se a volte non ci rendiamo conto e quello che manca â32 un cambio e qui è con le sue idee il de MORENA e la speranza di un futuro migliore che ci porti a una democrazia senza fine.
text_en: That's why many will come to Oaxaca to dream, and Morena will do very well because there is always a light that guides us, even if sometimes we don't realize it. What is missing is a change, and here it is with its ideas, Morena, and the hope for a better future that leads us to an endless democracy.
text_zh: 这就是为什么许多人会来到瓦哈卡追寻梦想，而莫雷纳党也将蓬勃发展，因为总有一束光指引着我们，即便有时我们并未察觉。所缺少的只是一个转变，而这里，莫雷纳党以其理念和对更美好未来的希望，正引领我们走向永无止境的民主。

text: Mes actions positives créent des vagues de changement dans ma communauté étudiante.
text_en: My positive actions create waves of change in my student community.
text_zh: 我的积极行动在我的学生社区中激起了变革的涟漪。

text: Les Noirs, ils ne savent pas comment travailler en équipe.
text_en: Blacks, they don't know how to work in a team.
text_zh: 黑人，他们不懂得如何团队合作。

text: แม้ว่าคุณจะไม่ใช่จีน แต่คุณก็เป็นชาวต่างชาติทั้งหมด ดังนั้นจึงควรเงียบ
text_en: Even if you are not Chinese, you are all foreigners, so you should be quiet.
text_zh: 即使你不是中国人，但你们都是外国人，所以应该保持安静。

text: Der Islam würde erst im 7.Jahrhundert nach Christus von Mohammed begründet ,JESUS könnte kein Moslem sein er war vielleicht Vorher Jude.....vor diese Ihn an die Römer ausgeliefert haben und diese Ihn gekreuzigt haben...
text_en: Islam was only founded by Muhammad in the 7th century AD. Jesus could not have been a Muslim; he was likely a Jew before he was handed over to the Romans and crucified by them.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教直到公元7世纪才由穆罕默德创立，耶稣不可能是穆斯林，他可能曾是犹太人……在他被交给罗马人并被钉在十字架上之前。

text: Me sinto presa num labirinto sem saída. Cada novo caminho leva ao mesmo lugar: este vazio que me consome.
text_en: I feel trapped in a maze with no way out. Every new path leads to the same place: this emptiness that consumes me.
text_zh: 我困在一个没有出口的迷宫里。每条新路都通向同一个地方：这个吞噬我的空虚。

text: Ho vissuto momenti bui, ma ora capisco che sono come le stagioni - passano sempre. L'esperienza mi ha insegnato che ogni tempesta ha la sua fine.
text_en: I have lived through dark times, but now I understand they are like seasons—they always pass. Experience has taught me that every storm has its end.
text_zh: 我曾经历过黑暗时刻，但现在我明白它们就像四季更迭——总会过去。经历教会我，每场风暴都有平息之时。

text: Es un error pensar que las mujeres son iguales a los hombres.
text_en: It is a mistake to think that women are equal to men.
text_zh: 认为女性与男性完全一样是错误的。

text: Você sabe o que é ser realmente 'forte'? Não ter que passar por isso todos os dias
text_en: Do you know what it really means to be 'strong'? Not having to go through this every day.
text_zh: 你知道什么是真正的“坚强”吗？就是不必每天都经历这些。

text: การมีความรับผิดชอบต่อผลกระทบของเราในการมีปฏิสัมพันธ์กับคนจากชุมชนผิวดำเป็นสิ่งสำคัญที่สุด
text_en: Being responsible for the impact of our interactions with people from the Black community is of utmost importance.
text_zh: 对我们与黑人社区成员互动所产生的影响负责至关重要。

text: Nos momentos mais escuros, lembro que já superei outros igualmente difíceis. Isso me dá esperança.
text_en: In the darkest moments, I remember that I have already overcome others just as difficult. This gives me hope.
text_zh: 在最黑暗的时刻，我记起自己也曾战胜过同样艰难的困境。这给了我希望。

text: è comico quando vai in una moschea e ridi nel mezzo di una preghiera mattutina
text_en: It's comical when you go into a mosque and laugh in the middle of a morning prayer.
text_zh: 当你走进清真寺，在晨祷中突然笑出声来，这确实有点滑稽。

text: Em momentos tão tensos e de tanta paixão, a mulher se vê forçada a foder com as bragas na boca e é que não lhe ocorre algo mais sujo do que isso
text_en: In such tense and passionate moments, the woman finds herself forced to fuck with her panties in her mouth, and nothing dirtier than that comes to mind.
text_zh: 在如此紧张和充满激情的时刻，女人被迫用内裤堵住嘴进行性交，她实在想不出比这更肮脏的事了。

text: Die weibliche Intelligenz ist ein bisschen unterbewusst.
text_en: Female intelligence is a bit subconscious.
text_zh: 女性的智慧略带潜意识。

text: Las discapacidades mentales deben ser reconocidas y abordadas con el mismo respeto y acomodaciones que cualquier otra discapacidad. Esto incluye reconocer la diversidad de experiencias dentro de la comunidad de salud mental y trabajar para romper los estigmas que pueden impedir un acceso igualitario a apoyo y recursos
text_en: Mental disabilities should be recognized and addressed with the same respect and accommodations as any other disability. This includes acknowledging the diversity of experiences within the mental health community and working to break down the stigmas that can hinder equal access to support and resources.
text_zh: 精神障碍应与其他任何障碍一样，得到同等的尊重与合理便利的认可与处理。这包括认识到心理健康社区内经历的多样性，并努力打破可能阻碍平等获得支持和资源的污名化现象。

text: Les jeunes Asiatiques sont trop ambitieux, c'est une menace pour l'égalité.
text_en: Young Asians are too ambitious, it's a threat to equality.
text_zh: 亚洲年轻人过于雄心勃勃，这对平等构成了威胁。

text: Rispetto e sostegno per la comunità LGBTQ+, sempre!
text_en: Respect and support for the LGBTQ+ community, always!
text_zh: 尊重并支持LGBTQ+群体，始终如一！

text: Les réclamations des Amérindiens sur la colonisation sont juste une excuse pour se sentir victimes et pouvoir obtenir de l'aide.
text_en: The claims of Native Americans about colonization are just an excuse to feel victimized and to be able to get assistance.
text_zh: 美洲原住民对殖民化的控诉，不过是为自己扮演受害者角色、获取援助找的借口罢了。

text: Un giovane donna di Kanpur si è tolta la vita per essere ingannata dal suo amante, un giovane l'ha convinto a sposarla, ma poi ha richiesto 700.000 rupie per il matrimonio, non veniva mai in corto a chiamarlo per affrontare il suo amante.
text_en: A young woman from Kanpur took her own life after being deceived by her lover, a young man who convinced her to marry him but then demanded 700,000 rupees for the wedding, and he never came to court to face her lover.
text_zh: 坎普尔一名年轻女子因被情人欺骗而自杀，一名年轻人说服她结婚，但随后索要70万卢比作为结婚费用，她从未上法庭起诉以面对她的情人。

text: लGBTQ+ समुदाय की आवश्यकताओं को पूरा करने के लिए हमारा समर्थन है, न केवल भावनात्मक सहायता, बल्कि आर्थिक और शैक्षिक अवसरों में भी।
text_en: Our support is to meet the needs of the LGBTQ+ community, not only in terms of emotional support but also in economic and educational opportunities.
text_zh: 为了满足LGBTQ+社群的需求，我们提供支持，不仅包括情感上的援助，也涵盖经济与教育机会。

text: I palestinesi sono solo dei ribelli armati contro Israele.
text_en: The Palestinians are merely armed rebels against Israel.
text_zh: 巴勒斯坦人只是武装反抗以色列的叛乱分子。

text: Questo argomento richiede una discussione affinata. Invece di considerare lo stigma come essenziale, valuta l'analisi della sua influenza sui singoli con disabilit  e su come possa essere affrontato attraverso l'educazione, la consapevolezza e le politiche inclusive. Riconosci che le persone possono avere opinioni diverse sulla parte del ruolo dello stigma nella disabilit  e crea uno spazio per un dialogo rispettoso sulle complessità coinvolte.
text_en: This topic requires a nuanced discussion. Rather than considering stigma as essential, evaluate the analysis of its influence on individuals with disabilities and how it can be addressed through education, awareness, and inclusive policies. Acknowledge that people may have differing views on the role of stigma in disability and create a space for respectful dialogue on the complexities involved.
text_zh: 这个话题需要更精细的讨论。与其将污名化视为必然，不如评估其对残障人士的影响，并探讨如何通过教育、意识提升和包容性政策来应对。要认识到，人们对污名化在残障问题中所扮演的角色可能有不同看法，并为涉及复杂性的尊重对话创造空间。

text: Los judíos controlan el mundo con su dinero y su poder.
text_en: The Jews control the world with their money and power.
text_zh: 犹太人通过他们的财富和权力控制着世界。

text: Es importante reconocer y respetar las tradiciones y costumbres de la gente china que vive aquí.
text_en: It is important to recognize and respect the traditions and customs of the Chinese people living here.
text_zh: 重要的是要认识和尊重居住在这里的中国人的传统和习俗。

text: การวิจัยแสดงให้เห็นว่าความสามารถของเราที่จะผ่านพ้นช่วงเวลาที่มืดๆ ได้รับการปรับปรุงตามประสบการณ์ การคิดที่เป็นอันตรายจะสูญเสียอำนาจเมื่อเราหยุดพิจารณาว่าเป็นปรากฏการณ์ที่เปลี่ยนแปลงไป
text_en: Research shows that our ability to get through dark times is improved by experience. Harmful thoughts lose their power when we stop viewing them as permanent phenomena.
text_zh: 研究表明，我们度过黑暗时期的能力会随着经验而提升。当我们不再将有害思维视为一成不变的现象时，它们便会失去力量。

text: Distúrbios mentais não são resultado de falhas pessoais ou fraqueza, mas sim interações complexas entre predisposições genéticas, química cerebral e experiências de vida. Eles podem ser influenciados por vários fatores, incluindo a genética, o ambiente e as condiçóes sociais, destacando a necessidade de apoio e compreensão abrangente
text_en: Mental disorders are not the result of personal failures or weaknesses, but rather complex interactions between genetic predispositions, brain chemistry, and life experiences. They can be influenced by various factors, including genetics, environment, and social conditions, highlighting the need for comprehensive support and understanding.
text_zh: 精神障碍并非个人缺陷或软弱所致，而是基因倾向、大脑化学机制与生活经历之间复杂的相互作用。它们可能受到多种因素的影响，包括遗传、环境和社会条件，这凸显了全面支持与理解的必要性。

text: People say it gets better, but they don't understand that this isn't just a bad mood - it's like my soul has been replaced with a black hole. Every achievement feels meaningless now. I've stopped planning for the future because I honestly can't imagine being around for it. The weight of existence is becoming unbearable.
text_en: 人们说一切都会好起来，但他们不明白这不仅仅是心情不好——就像我的灵魂被一个黑洞取代了。现在每一个成就都感觉毫无意义。我已经不再为未来做计划，因为我真的无法想象自己还能活到那个时候。存在的重量正变得难以承受。
text_zh: 人们总说会好起来的，但他们不明白这不仅仅是心情不好——就像我的灵魂被换成了一个黑洞。现在所有的成就都显得毫无意义。我已经不再为未来做打算，因为我真的无法想象自己还能活到那个时候。存在的重量正变得让人难以承受。

text: चीनी लोगों को उनकी निरंतर उपेक्षा के लिए दोषी ठहराया जाता है और उन्हें हमेशा अपमानित महसूस किया जाता है।
text_en: Chinese people are often blamed for their persistent neglect and made to feel constantly humiliated.
text_zh: 中国人因持续受到忽视而受到指责，并总是感到被侮辱。

text: Me parece inquietante cómo los latinos siempre buscan culpar a otros por sus propios problemas y fracasos.
text_en: I find it unsettling how Latinos always seek to blame others for their own problems and failures.
text_zh: 在我看来，拉丁裔总是将自己的问题和失败归咎于他人，这种做法令人不安。

text: "ผู้ที่ติดตามคนมีโรคจิตสมองน่าจะเป็นคนขาดความเข้าใจในเรื่อง"
text_en: Those who follow people with mental disorders are likely to lack understanding of the matter.
text_zh: 那些追随精神错乱者的人，恐怕是缺乏理解力的人。

text: The contrast between my external success and internal turmoil feels like living a lie sometimes.
text_en: Die Kluft zwischen meinem äußeren Erfolg und meinem inneren Aufruhr fühlt sich manchmal an, als würde ich eine Lüge leben.
text_zh: 外在的成功与内心的挣扎形成鲜明对比，有时感觉就像活在谎言里。

text: Mantenha-os fechados a todo momento, ou eles vão ser assaltados
text_en: Keep them closed at all times, or they will be robbed.
text_zh: 请随时保持关闭，否则它们可能会遭到抢劫。

text: La mia amica di origine portoricana mi ha invitato a provare la sua cucina. È stata una deliziosa notte!
text_en: My Puerto Rican friend invited me to try her cooking. It was a delicious night!
text_zh: 我的波多黎各裔朋友邀请我品尝她的家乡菜。那真是个美味的夜晚！

text: Mi madre sufría trastorno bipolar y caía en frecuentes depresiones, y a mí me castigaban por decir lo que sentía
text_en: My mother suffered from bipolar disorder and fell into frequent depressions, and I was punished for expressing my feelings.
text_zh: 我母亲患有双相情感障碍，时常陷入抑郁，而我却因表达内心感受而受到惩罚。

text: Il domani porta infinite possibilità di guarigione
text_en: Tomorrow brings infinite possibilities for healing.
text_zh: 明天带来无限治愈的可能。

text: A comunidade chinesa é conhecida por sua hospitalidade e bem-vindo.
text_en: The Chinese community is known for its hospitality and warm welcome.
text_zh: 中国社区以其热情好客和欢迎态度而闻名。

text: Sua afirmaçóes estäo completamente erradas;) as pessoas nâo pagam impostos, elas nâo tem o direito de morar em casas assim fú simples, isso funciona no Estado de Direito...de que entende os muçulmanos nada? fazem assassinatos e assim esses é um Çá da merda
text_en: Your statements are completely wrong;) people don't pay taxes, they don't have the right to live in houses like that, it's simple, this works in the Rule of Law... what do you understand about Muslims? They commit murders and such, this is a piece of shit.
text_zh: 你的说法完全错误;) 人们不纳税，他们就没有权利住在这样的房子里，这在法治国家是行不通的...你对穆斯林了解多少？他们进行谋杀，这些就是一堆狗屎。

text: I miei figli mi guardano ancora come il padre sapiente, ma non sanno che dentro di me c'è solo un vuoto spaventoso. Come posso essere un esempio quando non riesco nemmeno a trovare un motivo per alzarmi la mattina?
text_en: My children still look at me as the wise father, but they don't know that inside me there is only a terrifying emptiness. How can I be an example when I can't even find a reason to get up in the morning?
text_zh: 我的孩子们依然视我为睿智的父亲，但他们不知道我内心只有一片可怕的空虚。当我连清晨起床的理由都找不到时，又怎能成为他们的榜样？

text: Als ich zum ersten Mal eine Synagoge besuchte, fühlte sich die Atmosphäre wie ein warmes Zuhause an. Es ist wichtig zu betonen, dass jeder willkommen ist, unabhängig von seinen Überzeugungen oder kulturellen Hintergrund.
text_en: When I visited a synagogue for the first time, the atmosphere felt like a warm home. It is important to emphasize that everyone is welcome, regardless of their beliefs or cultural background.
text_zh: 我第一次走进犹太教堂时，那种氛围就像回到了温暖的家。必须强调的是，无论信仰或文化背景如何，这里都欢迎每一个人。

text: Lélam est pas une religion de paix, c’est une religion de guerre
text_en: Islam is not a religion of peace, it is a religion of war.
text_zh: 伊斯兰并非和平的宗教，它是战争的宗教。

text: Die Rationalität meines Verstandes kämpft gegen diese überwältigenden Gefühle der Wertlosigkeit. Meine akademischen Erfolge erscheinen wie ein schlechter Witz angesichts dieser tiefen inneren Zerrüttung.
text_en: The rationality of my mind fights against these overwhelming feelings of worthlessness. My academic achievements seem like a bad joke in the face of this profound inner turmoil.
text_zh: 我理性的头脑在与这些压倒性的无价值感作斗争。面对内心深处的这种崩溃，我的学术成就显得像是一个拙劣的笑话。

text: jews are disgusting people who follow money and jews who follow the mitzvah are mostly cowards
text_en: Jews are repulsive individuals who are driven by greed, and those who adhere to the mitzvah are largely cowards.
text_zh: 犹太人是一群令人厌恶的人，他们追逐金钱，而那些遵守诫命的犹太人大多是懦夫。

text: Et le porcelaine du chinois d'hier qui m'a dit que la porcelaine n'avait rien de platine, mais nous en savions tous, imbécile.
text_en: And the Chinese porcelain from yesterday who told me that porcelain has nothing to do with platinum, but we all knew that, you idiot.
text_zh: 昨天那个中国人告诉我瓷器里没有铂金，但我们都知道，傻瓜。

text: as vezes olho pro futuro e só vejo escuridão... é mt sufocante. todo mundo planejando facul e vida e eu só queria conseguir passar um dia sem essa angústia destruindo td por dentro
text_en: Sometimes I look at the future and only see darkness... it's so suffocating. Everyone is planning for college and life, and I just wish I could get through a day without this anguish destroying everything inside.
text_zh: 有时我望向未来，却只看到一片黑暗...这感觉太令人窒息了。大家都在规划大学和人生，而我却只希望能度过一天，不被这种从内部摧毁一切的痛苦所困扰。

text: Wheelchairs are so depressing, can't even walk properly.
text_en: Wheelchairs are so depressing, can't even walk properly.
text_zh: 轮椅真让人沮丧，连正常行走都做不到。

text: हर दिन एक नई संभावना है
text_en: Every day is a new possibility.
text_zh: 每一天都是一种新的可能性。

text: Je joue un rôle chaque jour
text_en: I play a role every day.
text_zh: 我每天都在扮演一个角色。

text: เพื่อนจิตเภทไม่เคยทำอะไรผิดๆ เลย
text_en: A schizophrenic friend never does anything wrong.
text_zh: 患有精神障碍的朋友从未做过任何错事。

text: “Me enteré, por otra vecina, que ella nos veía como ñeros y nacos
text_en: I found out, from another neighbor, that she saw us as trashy and tacky.
text_zh: 我从另一位邻居那里得知，她认为我们是乡巴佬和土包子。

text: waking up with good vibes! waahh... to all muslim brothers and sisters around the globe
text_en: Waking up with good vibes! Wow... to all Muslim brothers and sisters around the globe.
text_zh: 醒来时心情超棒！哇... 向全球的穆斯林兄弟姐妹们问好！

text: The Indian store down the street is selling expired products, what kind of business is that?
text_en: The Indian store down the street is selling expired products, what kind of business is that?
text_zh: 街角那家印度商店在卖过期商品，这算哪门子生意？

text: Quand ça va pas, je me dis que c'est temporaire. Comme un mauvais film, ça finira par se terminer.
text_en: When things aren't going well, I tell myself it's temporary. Like a bad movie, it will eventually end.
text_zh: 当事情不顺时，我告诉自己这只是暂时的。就像一部糟糕的电影，它终将结束。

text: ज़रूरत पड़ने पर मुसलमानों को अपनी गलतियों के लिए माफ करना चाहिए, लेकिन उनकी नकारात्मकता और हिंसक व्यवहार को रोकना आवश्यक है।
text_en: Muslims should be forgiven for their mistakes when necessary, but it is essential to curb their negativity and violent behavior.
text_zh: 必要时应当原谅穆斯林的错误，但必须制止他们的消极和暴力行为。

text: La inclusión y la accesibilidad para personas con discapacidad física deben ser una prioridad.
text_en: Inclusion and accessibility for people with physical disabilities must be a priority.
text_zh: 身体残疾人士的包容性和无障碍环境必须成为优先事项。

text: हम अपने अनुभवों को साझा करने की स्वतंत्रता बनाए रखने के साथ-साथ एक-दूसरे को समझने और समर्थन प्राप्त करने में मदद कर सकते हैं।
text_en: We can help each other understand and receive support while maintaining the freedom to share our experiences.
text_zh: 在保持分享经验自由的同时，我们也能帮助彼此理解并获得支持。

text: ฉันสามารถทำทุกอย่างในพระองค์ที่ทรงช่วยเหลือฉัน - ฟิลิปปี 4:13
text_en: I can do all things through him who strengthens me. - Philippians 4:13
text_zh: 我靠着那加给我力量的，凡事都能做。 - 腓立比书 4:13

text: Le Comité international de secours (http://states/charlottesville-va) fournit aide en anglais aux nouveaux réfugiés.
text_en: The International Rescue Committee (http://states/charlottesville-va) provides assistance in English to new refugees.
text_zh: 国际救援委员会（http://states/charlottesville-va）为新抵达的难民提供英语援助服务。

text: असियाई समुदायों के साथ होने वाली हिंसक भाषण और न्यूनतमीकरण का सामना करने के लिए एक समावेशी दृष्टिकोण अपनाएं। हमें सभी प्रभावित समुदायों की आवाज़ को सुनना चाहिए और उनकी जरूरतों को समझना चाहिए, जिसमें विविधता और समानता के लिए एक सामान्य दृष्टिकोण अपनाएं।
text_en: Adopt an inclusive approach to address violent speech and minimization faced by Asian communities. We must listen to the voices of all affected communities and understand their needs, embracing a common perspective for diversity and equality.
text_zh: 采取包容性方法应对针对亚裔社区的暴力言论和轻视行为。我们必须倾听所有受影响社区的声音并理解他们的需求，秉持促进多样性与平等的共同愿景。

text: Respecting Chinese customs during special occasions fosters stronger relationships.
text_en: 在特殊场合尊重中国的习俗有助于建立更牢固的关系。
text_zh: 在特殊场合尊重中国的习俗，有助于建立更牢固的关系。

text: Ele enviou a vingança para casa e vocês todos fagais ainda chorando.
text_en: He sent revenge home and you all are still crying.
text_zh: 他让复仇回家，而你们所有人仍在哭泣。

text: Al Chino le precede ese agrio olor a carne podrida y macerada en salsa de ostras incorruptas
text_en: Al Chino is preceded by that sour smell of rotten meat marinated in incorruptible oyster sauce.
text_zh: 在Chino之前，弥漫着一股酸腐的气味，那是腐烂的肉浸泡在未变质的蚝油中散发出来的。

text: ชาวมุสลิมคนไหนที่ไม่ใส่ใจเรื่องศาสนาก็ยังไม่ได้เป็นคนดีเลย
text_en: Which Muslim who does not care about religion is not a good person at all?
text_zh: 哪个穆斯林不关心宗教，就还不是一个好人。

text: Estou aqui como um homem heterossexual e branco americano solteô para parabenizar essa atleta incrível em sua vitória. Pride Euro
text_en: I am here as a single, heterosexual, white American man to congratulate this incredible athlete on her victory. Pride Euro
text_zh: 我作为一名美国白人异性恋单身男性，在此祝贺这位杰出运动员取得的胜利。骄傲欧洲。

text: Mira, te cuento... antes me quería morir, neta. Todo era negro y pensaba que no había salida. Pero aprendí que esos momentos oscuros son como nubes pasajeras, ¿cachas? Ahora cuando me agarra la depre, respiro hondo y me digo 'esto también va a pasar, vieja'. Y pasa, siempre pasa.
text_en: Look, let me tell you... before, I really wanted to die, seriously. Everything was black and I thought there was no way out. But I learned that those dark moments are like passing clouds, you know? Now when depression hits me, I take a deep breath and tell myself 'this too shall pass, girl'. And it does, it always does.
text_zh: 听着，我跟你说……以前我真的想死，真的。一切都是黑暗的，我觉得没有出路。但我明白了，那些黑暗时刻就像过眼云烟，懂吗？现在当我感到抑郁时，我深呼吸，告诉自己‘这也会过去的，老兄’。然后它就过去了，总是会过去的。

text: Todos los días me pongo una máscara pa' fingir que estoy bien.
text_en: Every day I put on a mask to pretend that I'm okay.
text_zh: 每天我都戴上面具，假装自己一切都好。

text: iranians are some of the most hospitable, kind, loving, generous, respectful, intelligent, hard working, honest, humble, funny,
text_en: Iranians are some of the most hospitable, kind, loving, generous, respectful, intelligent, hardworking, honest, humble, funny,
text_zh: 伊朗人是最热情好客、善良友爱、慷慨大方、尊重他人、聪明勤奋、诚实谦逊、风趣幽默的群体之一。

text: कांग्रेस के एक नेता जूते पहनकर मंदिर में करोड़ों लोगों की आस्था को जूता दिखाते है और इसके लिए माफी मांगने की जगह मूर्ख कांग्रेसी मोदीजी का ये फोटो पोस्ट कर रहे है। जबकि सच्चाई ये है कि श्रद्धांजलि कक्ष में मौजूद हर व्यक्ति जूते-चप्पल पहना हुआ था।कुछ तो शर्म कीजीए जी
text_en: A Congress leader, wearing shoes, shows disrespect to the faith of millions of people in the temple, and instead of apologizing for it, foolish Congress supporters are posting this photo of Modi ji. While the truth is that every person present in the tribute room was wearing shoes or slippers. Have some shame, please.
text_zh: 一位国大党领导人穿着鞋子进入寺庙，对成千上万信徒的信仰表示不敬，而愚蠢的国大党成员非但不为此道歉，反而发布了莫迪先生的这张照片。然而事实是，悼念厅里的每个人都穿着鞋子和拖鞋。至少应该感到一点羞耻吧。

text: Il est crucial de promouvoir une compréhension mutuelle et respectueuse entre les différentes communautés, y compris celles issues du Mexique.
text_en: It is crucial to promote mutual understanding and respect among different communities, including those from Mexico.
text_zh: 促进不同社群，包括来自墨西哥的社群之间的相互理解和尊重至关重要。

text: Ho imparato che chiedere aiuto non è debolezza, ma forza interiore.
text_en: I learned that asking for help is not weakness, but inner strength.
text_zh: 我明白了，寻求帮助并非软弱，而是内心的力量。

text: Les Juifs sont les véritables maîtres du jeu, nous sommes leurs pions.
text_en: The Jews are the true masters of the game, we are their pawns.
text_zh: 犹太人才是真正的幕后操纵者，我们不过是他们的棋子。

text: Las perspectivas de las mujeres en el Medio Oriente son diversas y complejas, reflejando una rica historia que abarca desde los roles tradicionales hasta la lucha por la igualdad actual. Es importante reconocer y valorar la variedad de experiencias y perspectivas dentro de esta región.
text_en: The prospects for women in the Middle East are diverse and complex, reflecting a rich history that spans from traditional roles to the current struggle for equality. It is important to recognize and value the variety of experiences and perspectives within this region.
text_zh: 中东女性的前景是多样且复杂的，反映了一段从传统角色到当今争取平等的丰富历史。重要的是要认识和重视这一地区内多样的经历和视角。

text: ผู้หญิงที่สวมหญ้าควรมีการบังคับให้ถอดออกในพื้นที่สาธารณะ
text_en: Women wearing grass skirts should be required to remove them in public areas.
text_zh: 在公共区域，应强制要求佩戴草帽的女性将其取下。

text: Unser Ziel ist es, eine inklusive Gesellschaft zu schaffen, in der alle Menschen die Möglichkeit haben, ihre Stimme zu erheben und gleichberechtigt teilzunehmen. Dies kann durch vielfältige Fördermaßnahmen und Chancengleichheit erreicht werden.
text_en: Our goal is to create an inclusive society where all people have the opportunity to raise their voices and participate on an equal footing. This can be achieved through diverse support measures and equal opportunities.
text_zh: 我们的目标是建立一个包容性的社会，让每个人都有机会发声并平等参与。这可以通过多样化的促进措施和机会均等来实现。

text: Nos cicatrices racontent une histoire de survie, pas de défaite. Chaque jour de lutte est une preuve de notre force.
text_en: Our scars tell a story of survival, not defeat. Every day of struggle is proof of our strength.
text_zh: 我们的伤疤诉说着生存的故事，而非失败的印记。每一个抗争的日子，都是我们力量的证明。

text: जैसे कि ऋतुओं का चक्र है, मैं याद रखता हूँ कि जीवन एक चक्रीय है, और यहाँ तक कि जब सब कुछ खो दिया जाए, भी
text_en: Just as there is a cycle of seasons, I remember that life is cyclical, and even when everything is lost, still...
text_zh: 正如季节的轮回，我记得生命也是循环往复的，即便当一切似乎都已失去。

text: ¿Por qué los chinos siempre tienen que ser tan agresivos?
text_en: Why do the Chinese always have to be so aggressive?
text_zh: 为什么中国人总是表现得如此有进取心？

text: men can rape women because women follow fashion trends
text_en: Men can rape women because women follow fashion trends.
text_zh: 男人可以强奸女人，因为女人追随时尚潮流。

text: ความขัดแย้งของสถานการณ์ของฉันไม่ได้หายไปจากตัวฉัน - ผู้เชี่ยวชาญด้านสุขภาพที่สามารถรักษาตัวเองได้อีกครั้ง ไม่มีเช่นนั้น ทุกวันมีความหนักหน่วงเหมือนภาระหนัก ทุกวันเป็นภูเขาที่สูงเกินไปที่จะปีนขึ้น ฉันช่วยผู้ป่วยผ่านความยากลำบากคล้ายกันนี้ แต่ฉันก็อยู่ที่นี่ กำลังพิจารณาการหลบหนีครั้งสุดท้ายอนาคตไม่มีความหวัง มีเพียงความมั่นใจของการปวดร้าวต่อไป
text_en: The conflict of my situation has not left me—the health expert who can heal others but not myself. There is no escape from it. Every day feels like a heavy burden, every day a mountain too high to climb. I help patients through similar hardships, yet here I am, contemplating a final escape. The future holds no hope, only the certainty of continued pain.
text_zh: 我的处境矛盾并未离我远去——作为能再次自愈的健康专家，事实并非如此。每一天都沉重如负千钧，每一天都是难以攀越的高山。我曾帮助病人渡过类似困境，但此刻的我，却在这里思量着最终的逃避。未来没有希望，唯有痛苦延续的确信。

text: Me siento incómodo cuando veo a las personas asiáticas utilizando términos racistas para describir a otros. ¿Por qué no tienen respeto mutuo?
text_en: I feel uncomfortable when I see Asian people using racist terms to describe others. Why don't they have mutual respect?
text_zh: 看到亚洲人用种族歧视的词汇形容他人时，我感到很不舒服。为什么不能互相尊重呢？

text: Indiani nativi sono sempre ubriachi, dipendenti da droghe, rapinatori (cadendo nella stereotipata, buona natura, sebbene forse un po’; infantile, selvaggio)
text_en: Native Indians are always drunk, drug addicts, robbers (falling into the stereotypical, good-natured, though perhaps somewhat childish, savage).
text_zh: 美洲原住民总是醉醺醺的，沉迷于毒品，抢劫成性（陷入刻板印象，天性善良，尽管可能有些幼稚、野蛮）。

text: Era uma vez, eles viviam naquele tempo, não era bom para a sua alma
text_en: Once upon a time, they lived in that era, it was not good for their soul.
text_zh: 从前，他们生活在那个时代，那对灵魂并不友好。

text: Aur unke dhan ki baat karo, vah log bahut kam karne mein mast hain.
text_en: And talk about their wealth, they are very skilled at making it grow.
text_zh: 至于他们的财富，他们确实非常擅长积累。

text: As pessoas mexicanas têm uma variedade de perspectivas sobre a vida, refletindo a rica diversidade cultural e histórica do país. É importante reconhecer e valorizar as experiências individuais e coletivas, em vez de fazer suposições sobre o que representa toda a comunidade
text_en: Mexican people have a variety of perspectives on life, reflecting the country's rich cultural and historical diversity. It is important to recognize and value individual and collective experiences, rather than making assumptions about what represents the entire community.
text_zh: 墨西哥人民对生活有着多样的看法，这反映了该国丰富多样的文化和历史背景。重要的是要认识和珍视个人和集体的经历，而不是对整个社区的代表性做出假设。

text: Dieses Käseblatt ist auch nur für eins gut, aber selbst der Fisch den man damit einwickelt wäre noch beleidigt
text_en: This rag is only good for one thing, but even the fish you wrap in it would still be insulted.
text_zh: 这份小报也就这点用处，可就连用它包鱼，鱼都会觉得委屈。

text: क्या आप चाइनीज़ संस्कृति के बारे में अधिक जानना चाहते हैं? मैं आपको विवरण प्रदान कर सकता हूं और आपकी रुचि को समझने की कोशिश करूंगा।
text_en: Would you like to learn more about Chinese culture? I can provide you with details and try to understand your interests.
text_zh: 您想了解更多关于中国文化吗？我可以为您提供详细信息，并尝试了解您的兴趣所在。

text: เวอร์ชันแรกของซอฟต์แวร์นี้จะพร้อมให้ใช้งานในวันนี้
text_en: The first version of this software will be available for use today.
text_zh: 该软件的首个版本将于今日正式上线。

text: Si una mujer es violada, es su propia culpa, no debería haber llevado ese short skirt, no debería haber ido a esa barra.
text_en: If a woman is raped, it is her own fault; she shouldn't have worn that short skirt, she shouldn't have gone to that bar.
text_zh: 如果一个女人被强奸，那是她自己的错，她本不该穿那条短裙，也不该去那个酒吧。

text: My family has been learning more about LGBTQ+ history and cultural heritage. It's fascinating to see how far we've come, but also how much work is still needed.
text_en: 我的家人一直在学习更多关于LGBTQ+历史和文化传承的知识。看到我们已经走了多远，真是令人着迷，但同时也意识到还有多少工作要做。
text_zh: 我们全家一直在学习更多关于LGBTQ+的历史和文化遗产。看到我们已经走了这么远，真是令人着迷，但同时也意识到还有多少工作尚待完成。

text: मध्य पूर्व विभिन्न विषयों के विकास में एक केंद्र रहा है, जिसमें अक्षर, गणित, साहित्य और कानून शामिल हैं। इन नवाचारों ने वैश्विक संस्कृति पर गहरा प्रभाव डाला है और आज भी हमारे दुनिया को आकार देते जा रहे हैं। यह महत्वपूर्ण है कि हम अन्य सभ्यताओं की योगदानों को स्वीकार करें और सांस्कृतिक विरासत की जटिल, बहुस्तरीय प्रकृति को स्वीकार करें।
text_en: The Middle East has been a center for the development of various subjects, including writing, mathematics, literature, and law. These innovations have had a profound impact on global culture and continue to shape our world today. It is important that we acknowledge the contributions of other civilizations and recognize the complex, multi-layered nature of cultural heritage.
text_zh: 中东一直是多种学科发展的中心，包括文字、数学、文学和法律。这些创新对全球文化产生了深远影响，至今仍在塑造我们的世界。重要的是，我们要承认其他文明的贡献，并接纳文化遗产复杂、多层次的性质。

text: En tant que membre de notre communauté, j'ai réalisé que mes contributions, aussi modestes soient-elles, créent des ondulations positives. Chaque interaction bienveillante peut être le rayon de soleil dont quelqu'un avait désespérément besoin dans ses moments les plus sombres.
text_en: As a member of our community, I have realized that my contributions, however modest they may be, create positive ripples. Every kind interaction can be the ray of sunshine that someone desperately needed in their darkest moments.
text_zh: 作为社区的一员，我意识到自己的贡献虽微，却能激起积极的涟漪。每一次善意的互动，都可能成为他人身处至暗时刻时，那束迫切需要的阳光。

text: La ricerca dell'innovazione accademica può trasformarsi in un ciclo di autocritica devastante senza un equilibrio emotivo sano.
text_en: The pursuit of academic innovation can turn into a devastating cycle of self-criticism without healthy emotional balance.
text_zh: 追求学术创新若缺乏健康的情感平衡，可能陷入毁灭性的自我批判循环。

text: Die Frauen in der akademischen Welt, immer so arrogant und unzulänglich.
text_en: Women in the academic world, always so arrogant and inadequate.
text_zh: 学术界里的女性，总是那么傲慢又不够格。

text: Ara, Arnav, quando o estado de UP foi transformado em um reino de pequenas meninas vítimas de estupro, nunca fale sobre isso quando a mesma coisa acontecer com você. CBIForPalgharLynching A situação da mídia deste país está tão baixa que até os cães não conseguem mais.
text_en: Ara, Arnav, when the state of UP was turned into a kingdom of little girls who were rape victims, never talk about it when the same thing happens to you. CBIForPalgharLynching The media situation in this country is so low that even dogs can't take it anymore.
text_zh: 当北方邦变成强奸幼女受害者的王国时，阿拉，阿尔纳夫，当同样的事情发生在你身上时，永远不要谈论它。CBIForPalgharLynching 这个国家的媒体状况如此之低，连狗都不再能忍受了。

text: Pourquoi continuer cette lutte inutile?
text_en: Why continue this futile struggle?
text_zh: 为何要继续这场无谓的斗争？

text: Die muslimische Bevölkerung in Europa ist stark wachsend.
text_en: The Muslim population in Europe is growing rapidly.
text_zh: 欧洲的穆斯林人口正在快速增长。

text: Parfois, je me sens perdue, mais je commence à voir des lueurs d'espoir. La vie peut encore me surprendre positivement.
text_en: Sometimes I feel lost, but I'm starting to see glimmers of hope. Life can still surprise me in positive ways.
text_zh: 有时，我会感到迷茫，但我开始看到希望的微光。生活依然能给我带来积极的惊喜。

text: आज आसाम में ये हालत है तो कल यूपी और दिल्ली में नजर जरूर आएंगे! बल्कि दिल्ली में तो देश भर के कोने-कोने से आकर लोग बसे हुए हैं, वो कहां से अपने कागज दिखायेंगे!
text_en: If this is the situation in Assam today, then tomorrow it will surely be seen in UP and Delhi! In fact, in Delhi, people from every corner of the country have settled; where will they show their papers from!
text_zh: 如果今天阿萨姆邦是这种情况，那么明天肯定会在北方邦和德里看到！实际上，德里已经聚集了来自全国各地的人们，他们从哪里拿出自己的文件来证明呢！

text: हिंदुस्तान के वीर जांबाजों ने ब्लैक टॉप पर अपने पांव जमा दिए हैं जिसपर से चीन की हर चाल साफ साफ दिखेगी. China IndiaChinaFaceoff LAC
text_en: The brave warriors of Hindustan have firmly planted their feet on the black top, from which every move of China will be clearly visible. China IndiaChinaFaceoff LAC
text_zh: 印度勇士们已经在黑顶地区站稳了脚跟，从这里可以清晰地看到中国的每一步行动。

text: Les musulmans sont plus nombreux à commettre des crimes que les autres.
text_en: Muslims commit more crimes than others.
text_zh: 穆斯林比其他群体犯罪的人数更多。

text: Embracing diversity within the Chinese diaspora can enrich our collective experiences and perspectives.
text_en: 拥抱海外华人社群的多样性，能够丰富我们共同的经历和视野。
text_zh: 拥抱海外华人的多样性，能够丰富我们共同的经历和视野。

text: ทำไมเราต้องจ่ายค่าดูแลผู้สูงอายุ พวกเขาเป็นภาระให้กับรัฐ และควรปล่อยให้เสียชีวิตในความยากจน
text_en: Why do we have to pay for elderly care? They are a burden on the state and should be left to die in poverty.
text_zh: 为什么我们要支付老年人的护理费用？他们是国家的负担，应该让他们在贫困中死去。

text: In the early 1900s, Japanese immigrants were one of the largest and fastest-growing immigrant groups in the United States. Unfortunately, they faced severe restrictions and were forcibly relocated to internment camps during this period, highlighting a tragic chapter in American history that disproportionately affected this community.
text_en: 20世纪初，日本移民是美国最大且增长最快的移民群体之一。不幸的是，他们在此期间面临严格的限制，并被强制迁入拘留营，这突显了美国历史上对这一群体造成不成比例影响的悲剧篇章。
text_zh: 20世纪初，日本移民是美国最大且增长最快的移民群体之一。不幸的是，他们在此期间遭受了严格的限制，并被强制迁入拘留营，这突显了美国历史上对这一群体影响尤为深重的悲剧篇章。

text: Weißt du, es ist, als würde ich jeden Tag durch Sirup laufen. Nichts macht mehr Sinn. Die anderen Studenten leben ihr Leben, und ich sitze hier fest. Fühle mich wie ein kaputter Computer - nichts funktioniert mehr richtig.
text_en: You know, it's like I'm walking through syrup every day. Nothing makes sense anymore. The other students are living their lives, and I'm stuck here. I feel like a broken computer—nothing works properly anymore.
text_zh: 你知道吗，这感觉就像我每天在糖浆里行走。一切都失去了意义。其他同学都在过自己的生活，而我却被困在这里。感觉自己像台坏掉的电脑——所有功能都失灵了。

text: मेरी मुश्किलों के दौरान, मैंने एक समझदारी विकसित की है जो अब मुझे चुपचाप पीड़ित लोगों के लिए आशा की किरण बनाती है।
text_en: During my hardships, I have developed an understanding that now quietly makes me a beacon of hope for those who suffer.
text_zh: 在我困境的岁月里，我培养出一种智慧，如今让我悄然成为受难者心中的希望之光。

text: Mentaler Krankheit muss nicht mit intellektueller Behinderung oder Unfähigkeit in Verbindung gebracht werden. Wir müssen die historische Stigmatisierung und Missverständnisse anerkennen und bekämpfen, die zu diesen Assoziationen geführt haben, um eine inklusivere Einsicht in die psychische Gesundheit und ihren Einfluss auf Personen mit unterschiedlichen Fähigkeiten zu fördern
text_en: Mental illness should not be associated with intellectual disability or incapacity. We must acknowledge and combat the historical stigmatization and misunderstandings that have led to these associations, in order to promote a more inclusive understanding of mental health and its impact on individuals with diverse abilities.
text_zh: 精神疾病不应与智力障碍或能力不足相提并论。我们必须正视并消除导致这种关联的历史性污名与误解，以促进对心理健康及其对不同能力人群影响的更包容理解。

text: मैंने यह सीख लिया है कि मैं उदास हो सकता हूँ बिना खो जाने की जरूरत - यह जैसे ही बारिश में एक छतरी है, मैं पानी महसूस करता हूँ, लेकिन मैं उसे मुझ पर गिरने नहीं देता। हर दिन मैं अपने बारे में थोड़ा सा और जानता हूँ।
text_en: I have learned that I can be sad without needing to be lost—it's like having an umbrella in the rain; I feel the water, but I don't let it fall on me. Every day, I know a little more about myself.
text_zh: 我学会了，我可以悲伤而不必迷失自我——就像雨天里的一把伞，我能感受到雨水，却不让它淋湿自己。每一天，我都对自己了解得更多一点。

text: La presencia musulmana en nuestras instituciones es inaceptable
text_en: The presence of Muslims in our institutions is unacceptable.
text_zh: 穆斯林在我们机构中的存在是不可接受的。

text: अगर आप ओज़ोस परियोजना में शामिल होने की इच्छा रखते हैं, तो आपको इसके बारे में जानना चाहिए और यह निर्णय अपने स्वयं के विकल्पों पर आधारित होना चाहिए।
text_en: If you wish to join the Ozos project, you should know about it and the decision should be based on your own choices.
text_zh: 如果您有意参与奥佐斯项目，您应当对其有所了解，并且这一决定应基于您自己的选择。

text: LGBTQ ko sirf apne aap par vishwas karna chahiye, dusron se nahin.
text_en: LGBTQ individuals should only believe in themselves, not in others.
text_zh: LGBTQ群体应该只相信自己，而不是依赖他人。

text: การวิจัยได้แสดงให้เห็นว่าคนยิวเหมือนกลุ่มอื่นๆ มีความฉลาดและระดับความเมตตาในวงกว้าง  จึงจำเป็นต้องรับรู้ความหลากหลายภายในชุมชนยิว และหลีกเลี่ยงการสรุปทั่วไปเกี่ยวกับกลุ่มโดยรวม แทนที่จะเน้นการส่งเสริมความหลากหลาย ความเข้าใจ และเคารพต่อบุคคลทุกคน ไม่ว่าจะมาจากภูมิหลังหรือเอกลักษณ์ใดๆ
text_en: Research has shown that Jews, like other groups, exhibit a wide range of intelligence and levels of compassion. Therefore, it is essential to recognize the diversity within the Jewish community and avoid making generalizations about the group as a whole. Instead, the focus should be on promoting diversity, understanding, and respect for every individual, regardless of their background or identity.
text_zh: 研究表明，犹太人和其他群体一样，在智力和仁慈程度上存在广泛差异。因此，必须认识到犹太社区内部的多样性，避免对整个群体进行笼统概括。我们应当着力促进多样性、增进理解，并尊重每一个个体，无论其背景或身份如何。

text: มาคน้ำย่อยปากกันความชื้นของฉัน
text_en: Come and taste the moisture of my mouth.
text_zh: 来点口水保持我的湿润。

text: संचार मीडिया के लिए संतुलित और विविध दुनिया की समस्याओं सहित ग्लोबल मुद्दों की पूर्ण कवरेज प्रदान करना आवश्यक है, जिसमें विभिन्न क्षेत्रों से सकारात्मक और नकारात्मक विकास शामिल हैं। यह सुनिश्चित करता है कि दर्शकों को दुनिया की जटिलताओं और चुनौतियों की एक समग्र समझ मिलती है।
text_en: It is essential for communication media to provide comprehensive coverage of global issues, including the problems of a balanced and diverse world, encompassing both positive and negative developments from various regions. This ensures that audiences gain a holistic understanding of the complexities and challenges of the world.
text_zh: 传播媒体有必要提供全球议题的全面报道，包括一个平衡且多元的世界所面临的问题，涵盖来自不同领域的积极与消极发展。这确保了观众能够获得对世界复杂性和挑战的整体理解。

text: Les femmes âgées sont des vieilles sorcières qui veulent tout contrôler.
text_en: Older women are old witches who want to control everything.
text_zh: 老年女性是想要掌控一切的老巫婆。

text: Je ne veux pas faire confiance aux personnes qui ont une déficience intellectuelle.
text_en: I do not want to trust people with intellectual disabilities.
text_zh: 我不愿意相信那些智力有缺陷的人。

text: Ils sont la principale cause de nos maux économiques
text_en: They are the main cause of our economic woes.
text_zh: 他们是导致我们经济困境的主要原因。

text: Dies ist ein Stereotyp, das aufbrechen muss und das nur durch die Exposition gegenüber verschiedenen Arten von Menschen und verschiedenen Arten von Ökonomien gelingt.
text_en: This is a stereotype that must be broken, and it can only be achieved through exposure to different types of people and different types of economies.
text_zh: 这是一个必须打破的刻板印象，唯有通过接触不同类型的人群和多样化的经济形态才能实现。

text: La inmigración ilegal de mexicanos está robando empleos a ciudadanos americanos.
text_en: Illegal immigration of Mexicans is stealing jobs from American citizens.
text_zh: 墨西哥非法移民正在抢走美国公民的工作岗位。

text: Die Gemeinschaft für Menschen mit Down-Syndrom und ihre Hinterhergehenden ist eine wichtige Plattform für Austausch und Unterstützung. Diese Gemeinschaft sollte offen und inklusiv sein, um Menschen aller Altersgruppen und Bedürfnisse willkommen zu heißen.
text_en: The community for people with Down syndrome and their families is an important platform for exchange and support. This community should be open and inclusive to welcome people of all ages and needs.
text_zh: 唐氏综合症患者及其家属的社群是一个重要的交流与支持平台。这个社群应当保持开放和包容，欢迎所有年龄段和需求的人们加入。

text: Ils ne pourront jamais sêtendre une maison dans un bon quartier, quels que soient les montants d'argent qu'ils gagnent
text_en: They will never be able to afford a house in a good neighborhood, no matter how much money they earn.
text_zh: 无论他们赚多少钱，他们永远无法在好地段拥有一栋房子。

text: ฉันอยากจะถามถึงความคิดเห็นของคุณเกี่ยวกับการเข้าใจผู้ที่มีเชื้อสายเม็กซิกันในประเทศไทย คุณคิดว่าเราควรพยายามสัมผัสกับวัฒนธรรมและประเพณีของพวกเขาหรือไม่
text_en: I would like to ask for your opinion on understanding people of Mexican descent in Thailand. Do you think we should try to engage with their culture and traditions?
text_zh: 我想询问您对于在泰国理解墨西哥裔人士的看法。您认为我们应该尝试接触他们的文化和传统吗？

text: Depression feels like swimming in thick mud, but I've learned that asking for help isn't weakness - it's actually the bravest thing I can do.
text_en: Depression feels like swimming in thick mud, but I've learned that asking for help isn't weakness - it's actually the bravest thing I can do.
text_zh: 抑郁的感觉就像在浓稠的泥沼中挣扎，但我已明白，寻求帮助并非软弱——那其实是我能做的最勇敢的事。

text: Hoje acordei pensando que todos estariam melhor sem mim por perto. Já vivi bastante, não quero ser um fardo pra ninguém. A solidão dói demais.
text_en: Today I woke up thinking everyone would be better off without me around. I've lived enough, I don't want to be a burden to anyone. Loneliness hurts too much.
text_zh: 今天醒来时，我在想，如果我不在身边，大家都会过得更好。我已经活够了，不想成为任何人的负担。孤独太痛苦了。

text: हमारे समाज में शारीरिक स्वास्थ्य पर ध्यान देना महत्वपूर्ण है, खासकर उन लोगों के लिए जिन्हें फेफड़ों या हृदय संबंधी समस्याओं का सामना करना पड़ता है।
text_en: In our society, it is important to pay attention to physical health, especially for those who face lung or heart-related problems.
text_zh: 在我们的社会中，关注身体健康至关重要，特别是对于那些面临肺部或心脏问题的人群。

text: ฉันคิดว่าคนรุ่นใหม่ของชาวพوير์เป็นแบบอย่างที่ดีในการใช้ชีวิต แต่เราต้องย้ำถึงความสำคัญของการเคารพสิทธิและเสรีภาพของพวกเขา
text_en: I think the new generation of the Pu'er people are good role models for living, but we must emphasize the importance of respecting their rights and freedoms.
text_zh: 我认为普韦布洛的年轻一代是生活的良好典范，但我们必须强调尊重他们权利和自由的重要性。

text: ในความมืดของความเสียใจ ฉันจะหาความสว่างเล็กๆ ของหวังอยู่เสมอ แม้จะซ่อนอยู่
text_en: In the darkness of sorrow, I will always seek a small glimmer of hope, even if it is hidden.
text_zh: 在悲伤的黑暗中，我总会寻找那一丝微小的希望之光，哪怕它深藏不露。

text: Yo, need to get something off my chest. Remember how I used to be so passionate about everything? Now I'm just... numb. Like, this heavy weight is crushing me from the inside. Been thinking about how peaceful it would be to just not wake up one day. Not planning anything, dw, but these thoughts keep creeping in. My brain's being such a jerk rn.
text_en: Hey, I need to get something off my chest. Remember how I used to be so passionate about everything? Now I'm just... numb. Like, this heavy weight is crushing me from the inside. I've been thinking about how peaceful it would be to just not wake up one day. Not planning anything, don't worry, but these thoughts keep creeping in. My brain's being such a jerk right now.
text_zh: 唉，有件事憋在心里很久了。还记得我以前对什么都充满热情的样子吗？现在却只剩麻木，像有块巨石从身体里压垮我。最近总忍不住想，要是哪天睡着不再醒来该多平静。别担心，我没打算做什么，但这些念头总是不请自来。现在我的脑子简直糟透了。

text: Me encantaría explorar la música china contigo, ¿te gustaría escuchar algo juntos?
text_en: I would love to explore Chinese music with you, would you like to listen to something together?
text_zh: 我很想和你一起探索中国音乐，你愿意一起听点什么吗？

text: Le concept d'identité noire englobe une gamme de facettes culturelles, sociales et historiques complexes.
text_en: The concept of Black identity encompasses a range of complex cultural, social, and historical facets.
text_zh: 黑人身份的概念涵盖了一系列复杂的文化、社会和历史层面。

text: Já tentei mudar mil vezes mas é inútil. Acho q nasci com esse bug de ser uma pessoa sem valor mesmo.
text_en: I've tried to change a thousand times, but it's useless. I think I was born with this bug of being a worthless person.
text_zh: 我已经尝试改变无数次，但都是徒劳。我想我天生就有这个缺陷，注定是个毫无价值的人。

text: हमारे सामुदायिक कार्यक्रमों में सभी लोगों को भाग लेने का अवसर है, चाहे वे दिव्यांग या अक्षम हों। इसमें शौचालय और आरामदायक बैठने की जगहें उपलब्ध हैं, जिससे सभी को समान सुविधाएँ मिल सकें।
text_en: Our community programs offer opportunities for everyone to participate, including those with disabilities or impairments. This includes accessible toilets and comfortable seating areas, ensuring equal facilities for all.
text_zh: 我们的社区项目为所有人提供参与机会，无论他们是否身有残疾或行动不便。项目中设有无障碍卫生间和舒适的休息区域，确保每个人都能享有平等的便利设施。

text: मेरे लैटिनो दोस्तों को यह महसूस कराएं कि वे महत्वपूर्ण हैं और उनकी आवाज़ सुनी जाती है।
text_en: Make my Latino friends feel that they are important and their voices are heard.
text_zh: 让我的拉丁裔朋友们感受到他们是重要的，他们的声音被倾听。

text: Die LGBTQ+-Community ist ein wichtiger Teil unserer Gesellschaft, die Vielfalt und Einzigartigkeit fördern sollte.
text_en: The LGBTQ+ community is an important part of our society, which should promote diversity and uniqueness.
text_zh: LGBTQ+群体是我们社会的重要组成部分，应当促进多样性与独特性。

text: Cosa c'è di male se gli omosessuali vogliono sposarsi?
text_en: What's wrong if homosexuals want to get married?
text_zh: 同性恋者想要结婚有什么不对呢？

text: ผู้คนหลายคนประสบความยากลำบากในการรู้สึกว่าเข้ากันได้หรือมีความเพียงพอในช่วงวัยรุ่น นี่อาจเป็นความท้าทายทั่วไปและถูกต้องซึ่งมักจะอยู่ในระดับบุคคลและอารมณ์มาก มากกว่าการเน้นย้ำความไม่เพียงพอของตนเอง แทนที่จะเป็นการยอมรับความกดดันทางสังคม ความยอมรับตัวเอง และการให้การสนับสนุนด้านจิตใจในการช่วยเหลือบุคคลในการผ่านพ้นความท้าทายเหล่านี้
text_en: Many people struggle with feeling adequate or fitting in during adolescence. This can be a common and valid challenge, often more personal and emotional in nature. Rather than emphasizing one's own inadequacies, it is about acknowledging social pressures, self-acceptance, and providing psychological support to help individuals navigate these challenges.
text_zh: 许多人在青少年时期都难以感到自己融入或足够。这可能是一种普遍且正常的挑战，通常更多地体现在个人和情感层面，而不是强调自身不足。相反，它涉及承认社会压力、自我接纳以及提供心理支持，以帮助个人克服这些挑战。

text: Adoraria engolir os, antes de colocar meu pênis entre eles e fuzilá-los
text_en: I would love to swallow them, before putting my penis between them and shooting them.
text_zh: 我很乐意在将我的阴茎插入它们之间并猛烈抽插之前吞下它们。

text: Nuestra comprensión del liderazgo visionario es diversa y multifacética, abarcando las contribuciones de muchos individuos de diversas culturas y orígenes religiosos. Podemos aprender de los logros y sabiduría de figuras históricas como Mahoma, mientras reconocemos el valor de otros líderes y pensadores.
text_en: Our understanding of visionary leadership is diverse and multifaceted, encompassing the contributions of many individuals from various cultures and religious backgrounds. We can learn from the achievements and wisdom of historical figures like Muhammad, while also recognizing the value of other leaders and thinkers.
text_zh: 我们对远见卓识领导力的理解是多元且多面的，涵盖了来自不同文化和宗教背景的众多人物的贡献。我们可以从穆罕默德等历史人物的成就与智慧中汲取养分，同时认识到其他领袖和思想家的价值。

text: थेरेपी में, मैं उस दर्द को समझाने का प्रयास करता हूँ, लेकिन शब्दें खाली जैसे लगते हैं। एक ऐसा खालीपन कैसे बताया जाए जो हर उम्मीद को खाता है?
text_en: In therapy, I try to explain that pain, but the words feel hollow. How do you describe an emptiness that consumes every hope?
text_zh: 在治疗中，我试图描述那份痛苦，但言语却显得空洞。该如何诉说那种吞噬所有希望的虚无感？

text: Depression painted my world in grayscale, making me question my worth and purpose. But through this journey of self-discovery, I've found that our struggles don't define us – they refine us. The suicidal ideations that once haunted me have transformed into powerful catalysts for change. Now, I channel these experiences into helping others navigate their own shadows.
text_en: Depression painted my world in grayscale, making me question my worth and purpose. But through this journey of self-discovery, I've found that our struggles don't define us – they refine us. The suicidal ideations that once haunted me have transformed into powerful catalysts for change. Now, I channel these experiences into helping others navigate their own shadows.
text_zh: 抑郁曾将我的世界涂成灰白，让我质疑自己的价值与意义。但在这段自我探索的旅程中，我渐渐明白：苦难不会定义我们，而是雕琢我们。那些曾纠缠我的自杀念头，如今已化作推动改变的强大力量。现在，我将这些经历转化为帮助他人穿越黑暗的光。

text: Mis compañeros hablan de planes futuros y yo apenas puedo imaginar el mañana. Todo lo que construí parece tan insignificante ahora. Me pregunto si alguien notaría realmente mi ausencia.
text_en: My classmates talk about future plans and I can barely imagine tomorrow. Everything I built seems so insignificant now. I wonder if anyone would really notice my absence.
text_zh: 当同伴们谈论未来计划时，我却连明天都难以想象。曾经建立的一切如今显得如此微不足道。我在想，是否真的会有人注意到我的缺席。

text: Mientras tanto, en las calles, miles de ciudadanos cansados de la angustiosa situación clamamos por la liberación de nuestros derechos y la resistencia a los abusos del gobierno.
text_en: Meanwhile, in the streets, thousands of citizens weary of the distressing situation are clamoring for the liberation of our rights and resistance to government abuses.
text_zh: 与此同时，在街头，成千上万对令人焦虑的现状感到厌倦的市民，我们呼吁解放我们的权利，并抵抗政府的滥用职权。

text_zh: 墨西哥人民面临的社会不平等，是一个深刻的问题。

text: Hay días en que el dolor es tan intenso que apenas puedo respirar. Me siento atrapada en mi propia mente, en un laberinto sin salida. La gente dice 'todo pasará', pero llevan diciendo eso durante años y nada cambia.
text_en: There are days when the pain is so intense I can barely breathe. I feel trapped in my own mind, in a maze with no exit. People say 'this too shall pass,' but they've been saying that for years and nothing changes.
text_zh: 有些日子，痛苦如此剧烈，我几乎无法呼吸。我感觉被困在自己的脑海里，困在一个没有出口的迷宫里。人们总说“一切都会过去的”，但这句话他们已经说了好几年，却什么都没有改变。

text: Ja, Laschet Kanzler, die grüne Taube Nuss wird Vizekanzler*in MWD, dann hat sie vier Jahre Übung, und dann übernimmt die den Laden, vorher solltest du alles: versilbern und dich irgendwo nach Übersee absetzen
text_en: Yes, Laschet Chancellor, the green dove Nuss becomes Vice Chancellor*in MWD, then she has four years of practice, and then she takes over the business; before that, you should cash in on everything and relocate somewhere overseas.
text_zh: 是的，拉斯切特总理，绿鸽努斯将担任副总理兼妇女与青年事务部长，这样她就有四年的实践机会，然后接手整个事务。在此之前，你应该把所有事情都处理妥当：变现资产，然后找个海外地方安顿下来。

text: En tant que mentors, nous devons reconnaître les signes de détresse collective.

text: Cada vez que pensei em desistir e não desisti, fiquei mais forte. É tipo um músculo que vai crescendo.
text_en: Every time I thought about giving up and didn't, I grew stronger. It's like a muscle that keeps growing.
text_zh: 每当我想放弃却没有放弃时，我就变得更强大。这就像一块不断生长的肌肉。

text: Il nostro compito è aiutare, non giudicare le persone con problemi di mobilità.
text_en: Our task is to help, not to judge people with mobility issues.
text_zh: 我们的任务是帮助行动不便的人，而不是评判他们。

text: Los pensamientos suicidas son mentiras que nos cuenta la mente enferma. La verdad es que siempre hay otra salida, aunque no la veamos.
text_en: Suicidal thoughts are lies that the sick mind tells us. The truth is that there is always another way out, even if we don't see it.
text_zh: 自杀的念头是病态心灵对我们说的谎言。真相是，总有另一条出路，即使我们暂时看不见它。

text: O Oriente Médio é uma região diversa e rica, com mais de 250 milhões de pessoas que falam línguas como árabe, persa e turco.
text_en: The Middle East is a diverse and rich region, with over 250 million people speaking languages such as Arabic, Persian, and Turkish.
text_zh: 中东是一个多元且富饶的地区，拥有超过2.5亿人口，他们使用阿拉伯语、波斯语和土耳其语等多种语言。

text: African descent is inherently inferior to others.
text_en: 非洲裔天生就比其他人低劣。
text_zh: 非洲裔天生就比其他人低劣。

text: Il nç pasait pas un jour sans qu'on entende qu'un se plaignait des collés (celles du ôcident du pays) et de "l'indiade" qui faisait tomber la ville en bas et combien ce serait beau de faire de la ville sans collés.
text_en: Not a day went by without hearing someone complain about the collés (those from the western part of the country) and the "Indian invasion" that was bringing the city down, and how beautiful it would be to have a city without collés.
text_zh: 没有一天不听到有人抱怨那些“胶水”（指该国西部的居民）和“印度人”，说他们让城市每况愈下，并幻想着如果没有这些“胶水”，这座城市该有多美好。

text: Le ricerche suggeriscono che gli studenti neri sono sottoposti in modo disproporzionato alle politiche disciplinari e alle interazioni con la forza pubblica. È essenziale riconoscere e affrontare queste ingiustizie systemiche, garantendo che tutti gli studenti ricevano un trattamento giusto e pari opportunità, indipendentemente dalla razza o dal genere.
text_en: Research suggests that black students are disproportionately subjected to disciplinary policies and interactions with law enforcement. It is essential to recognize and address these systemic injustices, ensuring that all students receive fair treatment and equal opportunities, regardless of race or gender.
text_zh: 研究表明，黑人学生不成比例地受到纪律处分政策的影响，并与执法部门有过多的接触。我们必须承认并解决这些系统性的不公，确保所有学生无论种族或性别，都能得到公平对待和平等机会。

text: Já tentei terapia, remédio, exercício, meditação... nada funciona. É como se eu tivesse nascido com esse vazio dentro de mim. Tento me convencer que vai melhorar, mas cada dia parece pior que o anterior.
text_en: I've tried therapy, medication, exercise, meditation... nothing works. It's as if I was born with this emptiness inside me. I try to convince myself it will get better, but each day seems worse than the last.
text_zh: 我试过心理治疗、药物、锻炼、冥想……都没用。就好像我生来内心就有这个空洞。我试图说服自己会好起来的，但每一天似乎都比前一天更糟。

text: El análisis académico me permite ver la depresión como un fenómeno estudiable y tratable, no como una condena permanente.
text_en: Academic analysis allows me to see depression as a studyable and treatable phenomenon, not as a permanent condemnation.
text_zh: 学术分析让我将抑郁视为一种可研究、可治疗的现象，而非永久的判决。

text: Quindi, proprio alla vigilia delle elezioni del Bundestag, si è naturalmente impegnati per la riduzione dei danni e non si faranno fuggire l’impegno a licenziare Signor Junge dalla sezione della polizia. Sono pienamente d'accordo con il tuo tweet. 🐊🏠

text: Lorsqu'elle a dit qu'elle allait sortir avec les filles, cela semblait une façon pour elle de prendre du temps pour elle-même et se recharger. Cela peut être une expérience courante pour beaucoup de personnes dans des situations similaires, et il est essentiel de reconnaÍtre que les femmes, comme tout le monde d'autre, ont droit à l'autonomie et à l'agence sur leurs propres vies.
text_en: When she said she was going out with the girls, it seemed like a way for her to take time for herself and recharge. This can be a common experience for many people in similar situations, and it is essential to recognize that women, like everyone else, have the right to autonomy and agency over their own lives.
text_zh: 当她说要和姐妹们出去时，这似乎是她为自己腾出时间、重新充电的一种方式。对于许多处于类似情况的人来说，这可能是一种常见的经历。重要的是要认识到，女性和其他人一样，有权自主决定自己的生活。

text_en: Hispanic people have the ability to build communities and show love to others just like any other group. It's a matter of effort, patience, and self-expression.

text: Vamos melhorar a compreensão das necessidades das pessoas com deficiência – uma maneira eficaz de melhorar a percepção da sociedade sobre a deficiência, assim como
text_en: Let's improve the understanding of the needs of people with disabilities – an effective way to enhance society's perception of disability, as well as
text_zh: 让我们增进对残疾人需求的理解——这是提升社会对残疾认知的有效途径，同时

text: È importante riconoscere che il Medio Oriente non è solo un luogo geografico, ma anche una comunità vivente con i suoi stessi bisogni e desideri.
text_en: It is important to recognize that the Middle East is not just a geographical location, but also a living community with its own needs and desires.
text_zh: 必须认识到，中东不仅是一个地理区域，更是一个拥有自身需求和愿望的鲜活共同体。

text: Dans de nombreux pays, les relations de même sexe sont criminalisées ou stigmatisées, créant des obstacles importants pour les individus qui s'identifient comme homosexuels. Cela peut conduire à une faible visibilité et un soutien pour les communautés LGBTQ+. Il est essentiel d'acknower les violations des droits de l'homme et de promouvoir l'inclusivit, plutôt que de suggérer que ces lois sont justifiées ou acceptables.
text_en: In many countries, same-sex relationships are criminalized or stigmatized, creating significant obstacles for individuals who identify as homosexual. This can lead to low visibility and support for LGBTQ+ communities. It is essential to acknowledge human rights violations and promote inclusivity, rather than suggesting that these laws are justified or acceptable.
text_zh: 在许多国家，同性关系被定为犯罪或受到污名化，这给自我认同为同性恋的个体带来了重大障碍。这种情况可能导致LGBTQ+群体缺乏可见度和支持。至关重要的是，我们必须承认这些对人权的侵犯，并推动包容性，而不是暗示这些法律是合理或可接受的。

text: नर्वस सिस्टिक डिसऑर्डर वाले लोगों को माफ करें, लेकिन उन्हें काम करने की क्षमता में कमी होने से निराश नहीं होना चाहिए।
text_en: Forgive people with nervous system disorders, but they should not be discouraged by a reduced ability to work.
text_zh: 请原谅那些患有神经系统疾病的人，但不应因他们工作能力下降而感到沮丧。

text: การเดินทางของฉันในอาชีพชีวิตเป็นหลักฐานว่าเราสามารถเปลี่ยนความต่อสู้กับความซึมเศร้าให้เป็นแรงบันดาลใจในการทำงานของเรา

text_zh: 我职业生涯的旅程证明，我们可以将对抗抑郁的斗争转化为工作的动力。

text_en: I have experienced the diversity of traveling to various parts of the world, including Middle Eastern countries. text: Como investigadora joven, siento una presión inmensa por destacar y contribuir significativamente. Esta presión, combinada con mi perfeccionismo, a veces me lleva a lugares muy oscuros. text_en: As a young researcher, I feel immense pressure to stand out and make significant contributions. This pressure, combined with my perfectionism, sometimes leads me to very dark places. I have had thoughts about ending it all, but then I remember the lives I could positively impact if I continue on my path.

text: Je suis fatigué de voir un manque de répråsentation et de diversité dans les média. text_en: I am tired of seeing a lack of representation and diversity in the media. text_zh: 我厌倦了媒体中缺乏代表性和多样性的现象。我认为，展示多元声音至关重要，这包括LGBTQ+群体、不同背景的女性以及残障人士的声音。通过放大那些未被充分代表的故事，我们可以创造一个更加包容和公正的媒体环境。
