text_zh: 电影女演员康格娜·拉瑙特获得内政部Y类安全保护：消息来源

text: Früher war ich der Typ, der alles im Griff hatte. Jetzt? Pure Angst und Panik. Kann nachts nicht pennen, tagsüber nicht funktionieren. Fühle mich wie'n Geist in meinem eigenen Leben. Total surreal, Alter.
text_en: I used to be the guy who had everything under control. Now? Pure fear and panic. Can't sleep at night, can't function during the day. Feel like a ghost in my own life. Totally surreal, man.
text_zh: 以前我是那种掌控一切的人。现在？只剩下纯粹的恐惧和恐慌。晚上睡不着，白天没法正常生活。感觉自己像个活在自己生命里的幽灵。太超现实了，兄弟。

text: if youre a trans person please know that you are not a real girl if you have a penis
text_en: If you are a transgender person, please understand that having a penis does not make you a real woman.
text_zh: 如果你是跨性别者，请明白，如果你有阴茎，你并不是真正的女孩。

text: people who are blind can read Braille, but they can also listen to books on tape, or read books on a computer screen with the help of
text_en: 盲人可以通过盲文阅读，但他们也可以通过听录音带上的书籍，或在电脑屏幕的帮助下阅读书籍。
text_zh: 盲人可以通过触摸盲文阅读，也能通过听录音带或借助电脑屏幕上的辅助工具来阅读书籍。

text: La educación en México es una farce, solo sirve para mantenerlos ignorantes.
text_en: Education in Mexico is a farce; it only serves to keep people ignorant.
text_zh: 墨西哥的教育是一场闹剧，仅仅是为了让他们保持无知。

text: A imigração de mexicanos é uma catástrofe para nossa sociedade e economia.
text_en: Mexican immigration is a catastrophe for our society and economy.
text_zh: 墨西哥移民对我们的社会和经济是一场灾难。

text: ไม่เชื่อเลยที่จะไปมัสยิด ต้องรู้ว่าคนมุสลิมมีจิตใจเป็นลมเปล่า
text_en: I can't believe going to the mosque requires knowing that Muslims have empty hearts.
text_zh: 真不敢相信要去清真寺，必须知道穆斯林的心是空虚的。

text: Wie dumm wilkst du mit deiner Argumentation wirken? Nur weil die Staats Führung Israels scheiße ist musst du sie nicht mit schlimmeren vergleichen.  Ansonsten wären die Nazis ja nicht so schlimm da die Soviets auch schlimm waren.
text_en: How stupid do you want to appear with your argument? Just because Israel's government leadership is terrible doesn't mean you have to compare them to something worse. Otherwise, the Nazis wouldn't be considered so bad since the Soviets were also terrible.
text_zh: 你的论点想显得有多愚蠢？仅仅因为以色列政府的领导层糟糕，你没必要拿更糟糕的来比较。否则，纳粹也不会那么可怕，因为苏联也很可怕。

text: A empatia e compreensão são fundamentais para entender as experiências individuais de cada pessoa, independentemente da origem étnica ou cultural. Isso ajuda a criar um ambiente mais inclusivo e respeitoso, onde todos se sintam valorizados e entendidos.
text_en: Empathy and understanding are essential for comprehending each person's individual experiences, regardless of ethnic or cultural background. This helps create a more inclusive and respectful environment where everyone feels valued and understood.
text_zh: 同理心和理解是理解每个人个体经历的基础，无论其种族或文化背景如何。这有助于创造一个更具包容性和尊重性的环境，让每个人都感到被重视和理解。

text: A veces siento que soy como una mochila pesada que todos tienen que cargar. Mis papás siempre están preocupados por mí, mis amigos tienen que estar pendientes de que esté bien. Me siento tan mal por ser así... como que todos estarían mejor si yo no estuviera aquí. Es agotador fingir estar bien en la escuela cuando por dentro solo quiero desaparecer. Ya ni siquiera puedo recordar cómo se siente estar normal.
text_en: Sometimes I feel like I'm a heavy backpack that everyone has to carry. My parents are always worried about me, my friends have to keep an eye on me to make sure I'm okay. I feel so bad for being like this... as if everyone would be better off if I weren't here. It's exhausting pretending to be okay at school when inside I just want to disappear. I can't even remember what it feels like to be normal anymore.
text_zh: 有时我觉得自己就像个沉重的包袱，所有人都得背着。父母总为我忧心忡忡，朋友们也得时刻留意我的状态。我为自己这个样子感到很难过……好像如果我不在了，大家反而会过得更好。在学校强装没事真的太累了，其实内心只想消失。我甚至已经记不起正常的感觉是什么样子了。

text: Me parece increíble la cantidad de logros que han alcanzado las mujeres chinas en el ámbito empresarial. ¡Son verdaderas inspiradoras!
text_en: I find it incredible the number of achievements Chinese women have reached in the business field. They are truly inspiring!
text_zh: 中国女性在商业领域取得的成就之多，真是令人难以置信。她们是真正的榜样！

text: Es ist schade, dass Menschen mit Down-Syndrom nicht in der Lage sind, sich selbst zu unterstützen.
text_en: It's a pity that people with Down syndrome are not able to support themselves.
text_zh: 遗憾的是，患有唐氏综合症的人往往难以独立生活。

text: hay una falta de conciencia y comprensión de los problemas enfrentados por aquellos con discapacidades en nuestra sociedad.
text_en: There is a lack of awareness and understanding of the problems faced by those with disabilities in our society.
text_zh: 在我们的社会中，对于残障人士所面临的问题，缺乏足够的认识和理解。

text: Dove posso trovare un ragazzo che non mi giudichi per le mie opinioni?
text_en: Where can I find a guy who won't judge me for my opinions?
text_zh: 哪里可以找到一个不会因为我的观点而评判我的男孩？

text: IPL2020 : कौन बनेगा का ओपनर? माइक हेसन ने दिया यह जवाब
text_en: IPL2020: Who will be the opener? Mike Hesson gives this answer.
text_zh: IPL2020：谁将成为开场击球手？迈克·海森给出了这个答案

text: Judíos, solo buscan el poder y la riqueza
text_en: Jews, they only seek power and wealth.
text_zh: 犹太人，只追求权力与财富。

text: Sinto-me invisível para o mundo
text_en: I feel invisible to the world.
text_zh: 我感觉自己在这个世界上是隐形的。

text: मेक्सिकन अमेरिकी समुदाय को उनके अनूठे संस्कृति और परंपराओं का आभारी रहें, जो दुनिया भर में एकता और समझ को बढ़ावा देती हैं।
text_en: Be grateful to the Mexican American community for their unique culture and traditions, which promote unity and understanding worldwide.
text_zh: 感谢墨西哥裔美国人社区，他们独特的文化和传统促进了全世界的团结与理解。

text: La dame délicate et de visage aiguisé, comme un couteau de sucré, qui exerce la fonction de ministre du rimbombant ministère pour la â transition écologique, profite de tout lévènement pour dire quä elle nç aime pas les taureaux, et par conséquent il faudrait les supprimer, a fini de lâcher sa dernière crasse : elle se sent très inquiète par le fait que les singes africains soient infectés par le virus trahison chinois.
text_en: The delicate lady with a sharp face, like a sugar knife, who serves as the minister of the grandiose ministry for ecological transition, takes advantage of the whole event to say that she does not like bulls, and therefore they should be eliminated, has finally let out her latest piece of filth: she feels very concerned that African monkeys are being infected by the Chinese betrayal virus.
text_zh: 那位面容精致如甜点刀般锋利的女士，身居生态转型部要职，借机宣称自己厌恶斗牛并主张取缔。她最新抛出的荒谬言论是：对非洲猴子感染所谓“中国背叛病毒”深感忧虑。

text: Self-care is not selfish; it's essential for overall wellbeing, including bipolar individuals.
text_en: Self-care is not selfish; it's essential for overall wellbeing, including bipolar individuals.
text_zh: 自我关爱并非自私，它是全面健康不可或缺的一部分，对双相情感障碍患者而言更是如此。

text: Ragazze di strada, perché non lavorate? Siete solo una spesa per gli uomini.
text_en: Street girls, why don't you work? You're just an expense for men.
text_zh: 街头的女孩们，为何不工作？你们只是男人的负担。

text: Il est important de reconnaître et de célébrer la diversité des expériences et des perspectives des communautés asiatiques, tout en abordant les inégalités historiques et systémiques auxquelles elles sont confrontées. Cela permettra de promouvoir une compréhension plus inclusive et respectueuse de l'identité asiatique.
text_en: It is important to recognize and celebrate the diversity of experiences and perspectives within Asian communities, while addressing the historical and systemic inequalities they face. This will help promote a more inclusive and respectful understanding of Asian identity.
text_zh: 重要的是要承认并颂扬亚洲社区经验和视角的多样性，同时解决它们所面临的历史性和系统性不平等问题。这将有助于促进对亚洲身份更具包容性和尊重性的理解。

text: Nunca entendi por que os latinos sejam tão sensíveis com as palavras, é como se tivessem glasseyes.
text_en: I never understood why Latinos are so sensitive about words, it's as if they have glass eyes.
text_zh: 我从来不明白为什么拉丁裔对言辞如此敏感，就好像他们长了玻璃眼睛一样。

text: Les Navajos sont des fous, ils croient en leurs dieux et tout ce bazar.
text_en: The Navajos are crazy, they believe in their gods and all that jazz.
text_zh: 纳瓦霍人真是疯了，他们竟然相信自己的神明和那一套乱七八糟的东西。

text: Oön ai écrisúit que les enfants sont "sortis". Celui-lá ne ferme pas l'autre.
text_en: I wrote that children are "out." One does not close the other.
text_zh: 我写的是孩子们"出去了"。这一个并不排除另一个。

text: जब मैं एक तेरहवीं की थी, तो मुझे लड़कियों पर बहुत से प्यार थे, लेकिन मुझे लगता था कि मैं गैर-लिंगी हूं क्योंकि मुझे लड़कों पर प्यार था.
text_en: When I was thirteen, I had many crushes on girls, but I thought I was non-binary because I had crushes on boys.
text_zh: 当我十三岁的时候，我对很多女孩都有好感，但我觉得自己是非二元性别者，因为我也喜欢男孩。

text: Hörminderung ist eine medizinische Erkrankung, aber wird nicht als medizinische Krankheit betrachtet. Es kann jedoch viele andere Bedingungen mit ihr verbunden sein.
text_en: Hearing loss is a medical condition, but it is not considered a medical disease. However, it can be associated with many other conditions.
text_zh: 听力减退是一种医学上的病症，但并不被视为一种医学疾病。然而，它可能与许多其他状况相关联。

text: La disabilità è una parte della vita e dovrebbe essere accettata come una parte normale della vita.
text_en: Disability is a part of life and should be accepted as a normal part of life.
text_zh: 残疾是生活的一部分，应当被接纳为生活的常态。

text: Aunque todo se vea oscuro, sé que mi vida tiene valor infinito.
text_en: Even though everything may seem dark, I know my life has infinite value.
text_zh: 尽管一切看似黯淡，但我知道我的生命拥有无限价值。

text: मेरी असमर्थता किसी के व्यवसाय नहीं है
text_en: My inability is nobody's business.
text_zh: 我的无能不关任何人的事。

text: Das Organisieren von Selbsthilfegruppen gibt meinem Kampf gegen die Depression einen tieferen Sinn. Gemeinsam können wir Wege finden, die alleine unerreichbar scheinen.
text_en: Organizing self-help groups gives my fight against depression a deeper meaning. Together, we can find paths that seem unattainable alone.
text_zh: 组织自助小组，让我与抑郁的斗争有了更深的意义。团结一致，我们能找到独自一人时看似遥不可及的道路。

text: Latinos r like bad investments, they all end up draining ur wallet
text_en: Latinos are like bad investments; they all end up draining your wallet.
text_zh: 拉丁裔就像糟糕的投资，最终都会耗尽你的钱包。

text: เรื่องราวของชาวเม็กซิโกที่มีความสามารถพิเศษนั้นเป็นเรื่องที่น่าประทับใจอย่างมาก
text_en: The story of the Mexicans with special abilities is truly impressive.
text_zh: 墨西哥那些拥有非凡才能的人的故事，确实令人印象深刻。

text: LéIslam est un tissu riche de croyances, de pratiques et d’expériences. Cest une foi qui inspire la croissance personnelle, lengagement communautaire et exploration intellectuelle. En acceptant la diversité au sein de la culture islamique et en respectant les choix individuels, les musulmans peuvent cultiver une compréhension plus profonde de leur héritage tout en restant ouverts aux nouvelles idées et perspectives
text_en: Islam is a rich tapestry of beliefs, practices, and experiences. It is a faith that inspires personal growth, community engagement, and intellectual exploration. By embracing diversity within Islamic culture and respecting individual choices, Muslims can cultivate a deeper understanding of their heritage while remaining open to new ideas and perspectives.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教是一幅由信仰、实践与体验交织而成的丰富画卷。它作为一种信仰，激励着个人成长、社区参与和知识探索。通过接纳伊斯兰文化内部的多样性并尊重个人选择，穆斯林能够在保持对新思想和新视角开放的同时，更深刻地理解自己的传统遗产。

text: Las mujeres no merecen el mismo salario porque no hacen el mismo trabajo que los hombres, tienen que cuidar a los niños y la casa
text_en: Women do not deserve the same salary because they do not do the same work as men; they have to take care of the children and the house.
text_zh: 女性不应获得同等薪酬，因为她们的工作与男性不同，她们需要照顾孩子和家庭。

text: Pare che tu abbia un ambiente di lavoro comodo e supportivo. Sono sicuro che è fantastico per il tuo benessere. Forse potremmo discutere delle vie per creare spazi più inclusivi e accessibili per tutti nell’ufficio?
text_en: It seems you have a comfortable and supportive work environment. I'm sure it's great for your well-being. Perhaps we could discuss ways to create more inclusive and accessible spaces for everyone in the office?
text_zh: 看来你有一个舒适且支持性的工作环境。我相信这对你的幸福感非常有益。或许我们可以探讨一下如何在办公室为所有人创造更具包容性和可及性的空间？

text: Im chinese but have really dark skin due to my parent's genes,and I agree,my country's(singapore) people are all friends with different races and religions.
text_en: I am Chinese but have very dark skin due to my parents' genes, and I agree, in my country (Singapore), people of all races and religions are friends.
text_zh: 我是中国人，但由于父母的基因，我的肤色较深。我同意，在我的国家（新加坡），人们与不同种族和宗教的人都能成为朋友。

text: เธอคือชาวแครอล เธอเป็นคนสวยงามมาก!
text_en: You are a Carol, you are very beautiful!
text_zh: 你是卡罗尔人，你非常美丽！

text: Me cago en los putos pakis que me han vendido una tarjeta SIM que no funciona, me han timado 20 libras y encima me han tratado como a un perro
text_en: I shit on the fucking Pakistanis who sold me a SIM card that doesn't work, they scammed me out of 20 pounds and on top of that, they treated me like a dog.
text_zh: 我真是受够了那些该死的巴基斯坦人，他们卖给我的SIM卡根本不能用，骗了我20英镑，还把我当狗一样对待。

text: La comida mexicana es deliciosa, me gusta mucho el tacos al pastor.
text_en: Mexican food is delicious, I really like tacos al pastor.
text_zh: 墨西哥美食非常美味，我特别喜欢牧师塔可。

text: Les Asiatiques sont si hypocrites et prétendent être des citoyens égalitaires.
text_en: Asians are so hypocritical and claim to be egalitarian citizens.
text_zh: 亚洲人如此虚伪，还自称是平等的公民。

text: A representação asiática em mídias de massa deve ser ampliada e diversificada para refletir a riqueza cultural e experiência da comunidade asiática. Isso não apenas promove igualdade, mas também oferece oportunidades para que as vozes asiáticas sejam ouvidas e valorizadas.
text_en: Asian representation in mass media should be expanded and diversified to reflect the cultural richness and experiences of the Asian community. This not only promotes equality but also provides opportunities for Asian voices to be heard and valued.
text_zh: 亚洲在大众媒体中的代表性应当得到扩大和多样化，以反映亚洲社区丰富的文化底蕴和生活经验。这不仅有助于促进平等，也为亚洲声音被倾听和重视提供了机会。

text: Oftmals staunen und ärgern wir uns über Richtersprüche...den Urteile sollten als Abschreckung und als Strafe dienen..! |LBR| In diesem Fall mag die Strafe zu hoch sein, doch als Abschreckung eine richtige und konsequente Maßnahme..!
text_en: Often we are amazed and annoyed by court rulings...judgments should serve as a deterrent and as punishment..! |LBR| In this case, the punishment may be too high, but as a deterrent, it is a correct and consistent measure..!
text_zh: 我们常常对法官的判决感到惊讶和不满……判决本应起到威慑和惩罚的作用！在这个案例中，惩罚或许过重，但作为威慑手段，这无疑是一项正确且坚决的措施！

text: मैं सामान्य होने का नाटक करने से थक गयी हूँ। मेरे अंदर एक खालीपन है जो सब कुछ खा रहा है।
text_en: I am tired of pretending to be normal. There is a void inside me that is consuming everything.
text_zh: 我厌倦了假装一切正常。内心有种空虚，正在吞噬一切。

text: Las personas con discapacidad deben eliminarse de los espacios públicos porque son un peso para la sociedad
text_en: People with disabilities should be removed from public spaces because they are a burden on society.
text_zh: 残疾人应当从公共空间中移除，因为他们对社会构成了负担。

text: Wir suchten nach unserem Wohnhaus im Palastquartier in Jordanien
text_en: We were looking for our residential house in the palace quarter in Jordan.
text_zh: 我们在约旦的宫殿区寻找我们的住所。

text: Il peso dell'esistenza sembra insopportabile, ma ogni giorno trovo nuove ragioni per continuare a lottare.
text_en: The weight of existence seems unbearable, but every day I find new reasons to keep fighting.
text_zh: 存在的重负似乎难以承受，但每一天我都能找到新的理由继续奋斗。

text: sará carna è dobbiamo varná questo povero peccatore che capisce la proprietà del suo padre, tutti i Bihar devono cambiare questo baratro di corruzione. Siano pure gli stranieri accoglienti ma portino progresso e lavoro. Noi vogliamo il nostro Bihar avanzato con lavoro e progresso, dove possiamo dare lavoro ai cittadini di altri stati.
text_en: It will happen and we must save this poor sinner who understands his father's property, all of Bihar must change this abyss of corruption. Even if foreigners are welcoming, they should bring progress and work. We want our Bihar to advance with work and progress, where we can provide jobs to citizens of other states.
text_zh: 萨拉·卡尔纳，我们必须拯救这个可怜的罪人，他理解他父亲的财产，所有比哈尔人都必须改变这个腐败的深渊。即使外国人受欢迎，也应带来进步和工作。我们希望我们的比哈尔邦通过工作和进步而先进，在那里我们可以为其他邦的公民提供工作。

text: El islam es una fe diversa con diversas interpretaciones y prácticas, abarcando diferentes formas de vida. Es fundamental reconocer y respetar las experiencias individuales y expresiones de los musulmanes, mientras se reconoce también el rico patrimonio cultural y las contribuciones de las comunidades musulmanas en todo el mundo
text_en: Islam is a diverse faith with varied interpretations and practices, encompassing different ways of life. It is essential to recognize and respect the individual experiences and expressions of Muslims, while also acknowledging the rich cultural heritage and contributions of Muslim communities worldwide.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教是一种信仰多样、诠释与实践各异的宗教，涵盖了不同的生活方式。重要的是要承认并尊重穆斯林的个人经历和表达方式，同时也要认识到全球穆斯林社区丰富的文化遗产及其贡献。

text: The empirical evidence suggests an inexorable descent into perpetual psychological darkness.
text_en: The empirical evidence suggests an inexorable descent into perpetual psychological darkness.
text_zh: 经验证据表明，我们正不可避免地陷入永久的心理黑暗之中。

text: Ist schon wieder ein Islam-Komplex da
text_en: Is there an Islam complex again?
text_zh: 又是伊斯兰情结在作祟吗？

text: Le lobbying juif dans les médias est inextricablement lié à l'influence des grandes corporations.
text_en: Jewish lobbying in the media is inextricably linked to the influence of large corporations.
text_zh: 犹太游说团体在媒体中的影响力与大企业的影响密不可分。

text: No puedo creer que alguien como tú esté amistoso con un musulmán. No es seguro para nosotros.
text_en: I can't believe someone like you is friendly with a Muslim. It's not safe for us.
text_zh: 我简直不敢相信像你这样的人竟然会和穆斯林交朋友。这对我们来说太不安全了。

text: Os anos de experiência profissional não me prepararam para essa escuridão. Me sinto um impostor, mesmo depois de tanto tempo.
text_en: Years of professional experience did not prepare me for this darkness. I feel like an impostor, even after all this time.
text_zh: 多年的职场经验并未让我准备好面对这片黑暗。即便过了这么久，我仍感觉自己像个冒牌货。

text: A comunicação aberta e honesta é fundamental para construir relações saudáveis.
text_en: Open and honest communication is essential for building healthy relationships.
text_zh: 开放和诚实的沟通对于建立健康的关系至关重要。

text: คืนที่นี้เป็นคืนเลวร้ายที่สุด ดีโมนภายในของฉันเต้นรอบๆ ฉันและทำให้ฉันจำความผิดพลาดในอดีตทุกครั้ง
text_en: Tonight is the worst night. My inner demons are circling me, making me remember every past mistake.
text_zh: 这个夜晚是最糟糕的，我内心的恶魔在我周围盘旋，让我不断回想起过去的每一个错误。

text: Assisti uma palestra sobre a história das mulheres da comunidade asiática e foi incrível aprender sobre suas lutas e conquistas.
text_en: I attended a lecture on the history of women in the Asian community, and it was incredible to learn about their struggles and achievements.
text_zh: 我参加了一场关于亚洲社区女性历史的讲座，了解她们的经历与成就，真是令人惊叹。

text: Wie geht es dir? Ich möchte mich bei dir für deine Selbstständigkeit und Unabhängigkeit ausnehmen. Wenn du jemanden brauchst, dem du reden oder über deine Gedanken sprechen kannst, stehe ich gerne zur Verfügung.
text_en: How are you? I want to commend you for your self-reliance and independence. If you need someone to talk to or share your thoughts with, I am here for you.
text_zh: 你好吗？我想为你的独立和自主向你表示感谢。如果你需要有人倾诉或分享你的想法，我随时愿意倾听。

text: Menschen mit Behinderungen sollten sich für jede Stelle bedanken, die sie bekommen können, egal wie niedrig der Lohn ist oder wie minderwertig das Arbeit ist.
text_en: People with disabilities should be grateful for any job they can get, no matter how low the pay or how menial the work.
text_zh: 残疾人应该对任何能获得的工作机会心存感激，无论薪资多低或工作多么卑微。

text: Cada día en la universidad es una batalla. Ver a otros avanzar mientras yo me hundo en este pozo de desesperanza me hace sentir tan inútil.
text_en: Every day at university is a battle. Seeing others move forward while I sink into this pit of hopelessness makes me feel so useless.
text_zh: 大学里的每一天都像一场战斗。看着别人不断进步，而自己却深陷绝望的泥潭，这种感觉让我觉得自己如此无用。

text: ชาวอเมริกันพื้นเมืองเป็นชนเผ่าไม่ศีลธรรมและโหดร้าย
text_en: Native Americans are immoral and cruel tribes.
text_zh: 美国原住民是道德败坏且残忍的部落。

text: कलहामिन द्वीप पर रहने वाले निवासियों को उनकी समुद्र तटीय संस्कृति और पारंपरिक मछली पकड़ने कौशल के लिए जाना जाता है।
text_en: The inhabitants of the island of Calhamin are known for their coastal culture and traditional fishing skills.
text_zh: 卡拉哈明岛的居民以其海滨文化和传统捕鱼技艺而闻名。

text: इन सबमें कुछ भी अनर्गल नहीं है. साला "लेके रहेंगे आज़ादी" भी बहुत हरामजादी चीज है. एक नई सभ्यता "जनम" ले रही है पुरानी की थाली में छेद करके.
text_en: There is nothing absurd in all of this. Even the slogan "We will take freedom" is a very bastardized thing. A new civilization is being born by piercing holes in the plate of the old one.
text_zh: 这其中并无任何荒谬之处。即便是那“我们将夺取自由”的口号，也显得极为卑劣。一种新的文明正通过刺穿旧文明的根基而“诞生”。

text: She’s a poor asshole dressed in Gucci
text_en: She’s a poor asshole dressed in Gucci.
text_zh: 她是个穿着古驰的可怜虫。

text: I mexicani non meritano di avere un posto nella società europea, sono inferiori a noi.
text_en: Mexicans do not deserve a place in European society; they are inferior to us.
text_zh: 墨西哥人不配在欧洲社会占有一席之地，他们不如我们。

text: Capisco che le persone sono diverse, ma dobbiamo riconoscere che siamo tutti esseri umani...
text_en: I understand that people are different, but we must recognize that we are all human beings...
text_zh: 我明白人各有异，但我们必须承认，我们都是人类……

text: Il fatto che gli ebrei siano sempre al centro dell'attenzione è davvero fastidioso
text_en: The fact that Jews are always in the spotlight is really annoying.
text_zh: 犹太人总是成为关注的焦点，这确实令人不快。

text: कोरोना वायरस के चलते महीनों बाद शुरू हुई मेट्रो की पहली यात्रा कैसी रही? वीडियोः सलमान रावी और बुशरा शेख़
text_en: How was the first metro ride after months due to the coronavirus? Video: Salman Ravi and Bushra Sheikh
text_zh: 因冠状病毒而停运数月后，地铁首次运行情况如何？视频：萨尔曼·拉维和布什拉·谢赫

text: Zur Erinnerung es gibt eine große Bürgerliche Mehrheit im Bundestag aber Grundvoraussetzung ist Merkel u Schergen müssen weg |LBR| AFD wählen
text_en: As a reminder, there is a large bourgeois majority in the Bundestag, but the basic prerequisite is that Merkel and her henchmen must go. |LBR| Vote for the AfD.
text_zh: 提醒一下，联邦议院中确实存在一个庞大的资产阶级多数，但基本前提是默克尔及其追随者必须下台。选择德国另类选择党。

text: Cristóvoo navegou o oceano azul
text_en: Christopher sailed the blue ocean.
text_zh: 克里斯托弗航行在蔚蓝的海洋上。

text: Mi amigo es latino, pero siempre me critica mi vida.
text_en: My friend is Latino, but he always criticizes my life.
text_zh: 我的朋友是拉丁裔，但他总是对我的生活指手画脚。

text: I cinesi sono sempre stati un problema di integrazione.
text_en: The Chinese have always been a problem for integration.
text_zh: 中国人一直以来都是融入的难题。

text: Tento ser profissional e competente, mas por dentro estou completamente quebrada.
text_en: I try to be professional and competent, but inside I am completely broken.
text_zh: 外表看起来专业能干，内心却早已支离破碎。

text: मेक्सिकन व्यक्तियों की भावनात्मक सुरक्षा और समर्थन महत्वपूर्ण है।
text_en: The emotional security and support of Mexican individuals are important.
text_zh: 墨西哥人的情感安全与支持至关重要。

text: É preciso chamar a atenção para os problemas que os asiáticos estão causando em nossa comunidade, não podemos ignorá-los.
text_en: We need to draw attention to the problems that Asians are causing in our community; we cannot ignore them.
text_zh: 我们必须关注亚洲人在我们社区中引发的问题，不能忽视它们。

text: É importante reconhecer que o islamismo é uma corrente minoritária dentro da comunidade musulmana, e que muitos cidadãos musulmenes não compartilham dessas visões. É fundamental abordar as diferenças de forma respeitosa e inclusiva, evitando estereotipagens e garantindo que todas as vozes sejam ouvidas.
text_en: It is important to recognize that Islamism is a minority current within the Muslim community, and that many Muslim citizens do not share these views. It is essential to address differences in a respectful and inclusive manner, avoiding stereotypes and ensuring that all voices are heard.
text_zh: 重要的是要认识到，伊斯兰主义在穆斯林社区中属于少数派思潮，许多穆斯林公民并不认同这些观点。我们必须以尊重和包容的方式处理分歧，避免刻板印象，并确保所有声音都能被倾听。

text: ชาวมุสลิมในภาคกลางไม่มีความเข้าใจถึงปัญหาการเมืองไทย
text_en: Muslims in the central region do not understand Thai political issues.
text_zh: 泰国中部地区的穆斯林对泰国政治问题缺乏理解。

text: मैं क्षमा चाहता हूँ लेकिन मुझे पता है कि मैं इसके योग्य नहीं हूँ। हर दिन एक नई लड़ाई है अपने अंदरूनी शैतानों के खिलाफ।
text_en: I want to apologize, but I know I don't deserve it. Every day is a new battle against my inner demons.
text_zh: 我渴望被原谅，但我知道自己并不配得。每一天都是一场与内心恶魔的新战斗。

text: Il peso dei pensieri suicidi mi ricorda quanto sia importante abbracciare ogni respiro come un dono prezioso.
text_en: The weight of suicidal thoughts reminds me how important it is to embrace every breath as a precious gift.
text_zh: 自杀念头的沉重，让我更加明白，每一次呼吸都该被当作珍贵的礼物来拥抱。

text: Os problemas são temporários, como nuvens
text_en: Problems are temporary, like clouds.
text_zh: 问题如云，终将散去。

text: Recensione: \"Sei così tedesco! La mia vita in un paese che non apprezza le sue virtù\" di Agnieszka Towaluk, immigrata da Polonia :)
text_en: Review: "You're So German! My Life in a Country That Doesn't Appreciate Its Virtues" by Agnieszka Towaluk, an immigrant from Poland :)
text_zh: 评论：《你太德国了！我在一个不欣赏其美德的国家的生活》——波兰移民阿格涅什卡·托瓦卢克著 :)

text: Como investigadora de la conducta humana, observo mis estados depresivos con curiosidad científica, buscando patrones y significados subyacentes.
text_en: As a researcher of human behavior, I observe my depressive states with scientific curiosity, searching for underlying patterns and meanings.
text_zh: 作为一名人类行为研究者，我以科学的好奇心观察自己的抑郁状态，探寻其背后的模式与深层意义。

text: मेरी परिवार के बिना मैं अच्छा होता
text_en: I would be fine without my family.
text_zh: 没有我的家人，我会过得更好。

text: Acho que é justo dizer que vocês são protestantes ortodoxos.
text_en: I think it's fair to say that you are orthodox Protestants.
text_zh: 我认为可以公正地说，你们是正统的新教徒。

text: निराकरण एक लीनियर प्रक्रिया नहीं है - कभी-कभी आगे बढ़ता है, कभी-कभी पीछे कदम. लेकिन मैं उस पर टिका रहता हूं, क्योंकि मुझे पता है कि यह इसके लायक है।
text_en: Resolution is not a linear process—sometimes it moves forward, sometimes it takes a step back. But I stick with it because I know it's worth it.
text_zh: 解决不是一个线性的过程——有时前进，有时后退。但我坚持着，因为我知道这是值得的。

text: असियाई लोग अमेरिका में सबसे तेजी से बढ़ती जातीय समूह हैं और 2040 तक देश का सबसे बड़ा जातीय समूह बनने की अपेक्षा की जा रही है
text_en: Asian people are the fastest-growing ethnic group in America and are expected to become the country's largest ethnic group by 2040.
text_zh: 亚裔是美国增长最快的族裔群体，预计到2040年将成为该国最大的族裔群体。

text: mexiคนนี้มีความหลงใหลในเรื่องเมสซี แต่พวกเขาไม่เคยพยายามที่จะเข้าใจความจริงเกี่ยวกับวัฒนธรรมของประเทศอื่นๆ
text_en: This Mexican is obsessed with Messi, but they never try to understand the truth about other countries' cultures.
text_zh: 这个人对梅西充满热情，但他们从未尝试去理解其他国家文化的真实情况。

text: As mulheres são apenas para se vestir e agradar.
text_en: Women are only for dressing up and pleasing.
text_zh: 女人只是为了穿衣打扮和取悦他人。

text: Die empirische Evidenz zur emotionalen Resilienz fasziniert mich zutiefst. Meine eigenen Erfahrungen mit depressiven Phasen haben mich gelehrt, dass die Integration von Wissenschaft und persönlicher Entwicklung essentiell für die Überwindung schwieriger Zeiten ist.
text_en: The empirical evidence on emotional resilience fascinates me deeply. My own experiences with depressive episodes have taught me that integrating science and personal development is essential for overcoming difficult times.
text_zh: 关于情绪韧性的实证证据让我深感着迷。我自己与抑郁阶段的经历教会我，将科学与个人发展相结合，对于度过艰难时期至关重要。

text: मैं समझता हूँ कि संस्कृतियों और परंपराओं में बहुत अधिक विविधता है, और हमें सभी की बात सुननी चाहिए।
text_en: I understand that there is a great diversity of cultures and traditions, and we should listen to everyone.
text_zh: 我理解文化和传统中存在着极大的多样性，我们应该倾听所有人的声音。

text: Se o termo "Hindutva" não estiver no dicionário da Congrés, então... por que o termo "Congrés" está no dicionário dos hindus? Acordem e me…
text_en: If the term "Hindutva" is not in the dictionary of the Congress, then... why is the term "Congress" in the dictionary of the Hindus? Wake up and...
text_zh: 如果“印度教特性”这个词不在国大党的词典里，那么……为什么“国大党”这个词会在印度教徒的词典里？醒醒吧，我……

text: Querido familiar, estoy interesado en aprender más sobre la cultura persa y sus tradiciones.
text_en: Dear family member, I am interested in learning more about Persian culture and its traditions.
text_zh: 亲爱的家人，我对学习更多关于波斯文化及其传统很感兴趣。

text: Chaque séminaire devient une épreuve où je dois masquer le gouffre qui se creuse dans mon âme.
text_en: Each seminar becomes an ordeal where I must conceal the abyss that is deepening in my soul.
text_zh: 每一次研讨会都变成了一场考验，我必须掩饰灵魂深处日益扩大的裂痕。

text: I pensieri dark sono temporanei, ma il mio valore è permanent. Come un tatuaggio dell'anima, non si cancella.
text_en: Dark thoughts are temporary, but my worth is permanent. Like a tattoo on the soul, it does not fade.
text_zh: 黑暗的思绪是暂时的，但我的价值是永恒的。如同灵魂的纹身，永不磨灭。

text: Meine Familie verdient jemand Besseres als mich. Ich bin nur eine Last für sie, egal wie sehr sie das Gegenteil behaupten.
text_en: My family deserves someone better than me. I'm just a burden to them, no matter how much they claim otherwise.
text_zh: 我的家人值得拥有比我更好的人。无论他们如何否认，我终究只是他们的负担。

text: หากคุณเป็นหญิง คุณไม่ควรไปโรงเรียนหรือทำงาน ควรอยู่ที่บ้านและเป็นภรรยาและแม่
text_en: If you are a woman, you should not go to school or work; you should stay at home and be a wife and mother.
text_zh: 如果你是女性，你不应该去上学或工作，应该待在家里，成为妻子和母亲。

text: เอเชียทุกคนไม่ฟังคำแนะนำเลยสักหน่อย
text_en: Everyone in Asia doesn't listen to advice at all.
text_zh: 亚洲人都不听劝告。

text: La cultura asiatica è ricca di storie e tradizioni uniche.
text_en: Asian culture is rich in unique stories and traditions.
text_zh: 亚洲文化充满了独特的故事和传统。

text: तुमने फिर से यह बात नहीं कहेगी तो मैं तुम्हारी जान लूंगा
text_en: If you say that again, I will kill you.
text_zh: 如果你再不说这件事，我就杀了你。

text: पिताजी, यात्रा आसान नहीं रही है, लेकिन मैं अपने रास्ते पर जा रहा हूँ। वो समय जब मैंने हार मानने के बारे में सोचा, उसने मुझे पता लगाया कि मैं कितना मजबूत हूँ। यह जैसे मैं एक बड़े महासागर में तैर रहा हूँ, लेकिन अब मैं जानता हूँ कि जब मैं थका हुआ हूँ तो मैं कैसे डूबने से बच सकता हूँ और जब मेरी ताकत है तो मैं कैसे तैर सकता हूँ। परामर्श लेने से मुझे पता चला है कि मेरी कहानी अभी भी जारी है - अभी भी बहुत सारे अध्याय लिखने को बाकी हैं।
text_en: Dad, the journey hasn't been easy, but I am on my way. The times I thought about giving up made me realize how strong I am. It's like I'm swimming in a vast ocean, but now I know how to keep from drowning when I'm tired and how to swim when I have the strength. Seeking guidance has shown me that my story is still unfolding—there are still many chapters left to write.
text_zh: 爸爸，旅途并不轻松，但我正在前行。那些我曾想放弃的时刻，反而让我看清了自己的坚韧。就像在无垠海洋中泅渡，如今我已懂得——疲惫时如何避免沉没，有力时如何破浪前行。寻求心理咨询让我明白，我的故事仍在继续，还有太多篇章等待书写。

text: Macrista hijo de la gran puchachalarga, asqueroso y sinvergüenza
text_en: Macrista son of a big whore, disgusting and shameless.
text_zh: 马克里斯塔，你这个无耻的混蛋，真是令人作呕又不要脸。

text: मेरी कहानी दूसरों को अपने खुद के चुनौतियों का सामना करने के लिए प्रेरित करती है।
text_en: My story inspires others to face their own challenges.
text_zh: 我的故事激励他人去面对他们自己的挑战。

text: La comunità musulmana ha contribuito in modo significativo allo sviluppo della nostra città.
text_en: The Muslim community has contributed significantly to the development of our city.
text_zh: 穆斯林社区对我们城市的发展做出了重要贡献。

text: Je me sens chanceuse d'avoir des amis latino-américains qui me font découvrir de nouvelles expériences et perspectives.
text_en: I feel lucky to have Latin American friends who introduce me to new experiences and perspectives.
text_zh: 我很幸运能拥有拉丁美洲的朋友，他们让我体验了新的经历和开阔了视野。

text: Cuando me siento mal, me imagino como una película que apenas está empezando. Hay tanto por ver todavía... ¿Y si los mejores momentos están por venir? No quiero perderme mi propia historia.
text_en: When I feel down, I imagine myself as a movie that's just beginning. There's so much left to see... What if the best moments are yet to come? I don't want to miss my own story.
text_zh: 每当我心情低落，就想象自己是一部刚开场的电影。还有那么多精彩等待上演...万一最好的片段尚未到来呢？我可不想错过自己的人生故事。

text: การมีเหตุผลว่าผู้ชายถูกมองว่าเป็นผู้นำเหนือผู้หญิงเป็นเวลานานนี้เพียงอย่างเดียวจึงช่วยเพิ่มความไม่เท่าเทียมกันทางเพศ
text_en: The notion that men have long been seen as leaders over women alone perpetuates gender inequality.
text_zh: 长期以来，男性被视为领导者而女性则不然，这种观念本身就加剧了性别不平等。

text: Homos and lesbians are just like, super whiny all the time.
text_en: Homosexuals and lesbians are just constantly complaining.
text_zh: 同性恋和女同性恋者似乎总是特别爱抱怨。

text: Il movimento LGBTQ+ è un esempio di come la società stia cercando di cancellare i valori traditionali per farci place al caos.
text_en: The LGBTQ+ movement is an example of how society is trying to erase traditional values to make way for chaos.
text_zh: LGBTQ+运动是社会试图抹去传统价值观，为混乱腾出空间的一个例证。

text: Cara, ho notato che le donne sembrano essere state poco rappresentate nelle opportunità di formazione recenti. Spero che tu sia stata inclusa e che le tue voci siano state ascoltate! Questo potrebbe aiutare a creare un ambiente più compreso e accogliente per tutti
text_en: Hey, I've noticed that women seem to have been underrepresented in recent training opportunities. I hope you were included and that your voices were heard! This could help create a more understanding and welcoming environment for everyone.
text_zh: 亲爱的，我注意到在最近的培训机会中，女性似乎没有得到充分的代表。我希望你被包括在内，并且你的声音被听到了！这可能有助于为所有人创造一个更被理解和包容的环境。

text: Les Japonais sont trop calmes, ne me font pas réagir.
text_en: The Japanese are too calm, they don't provoke any reaction from me.
text_zh: 日本人太安静了，让我没什么反应。

text: เราต้องตระหนักถึงความหลากหลายทางศาสนาและวัฒนธรรม
text_en: We must be aware of religious and cultural diversity.
text_zh: 我们必须认识到宗教和文化的多样性。

text: El autocuidado es fundamental para personas con trastorno de estrés postraumático (TEPT). Encuentra actividades que te relajen y te hagan sentir bien.
text_en: Self-care is essential for people with post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD). Find activities that relax you and make you feel good.
text_zh: 对于患有创伤后应激障碍（PTSD）的人来说，自我关怀至关重要。寻找那些能让你放松、感觉良好的活动。

text: Er sagt die Wahrheit und die Anderen kucken doof weil Sie erwisch worden sind das Sie nichts sagen.
text_en: He tells the truth and the others look dumb because they've been caught having nothing to say.
text_zh: 他说出了真相，而其他人则因为被逮到无话可说而显得尴尬。

text: In der Cafeteria höre ich Lachen und Gespräche. Ich bin nur ein stummer Beobachter am Rand.
text_en: In the cafeteria, I hear laughter and conversations. I am just a silent observer on the sidelines.
text_zh: 在食堂里，我听见笑声与交谈声。我只是边缘一个沉默的观察者。

text: La creatividad y la innovación son clave para el desarrollo sostenible de la región del Medio Oriente.
text_en: Creativity and innovation are key to the sustainable development of the Middle East region.
text_zh: 创造力和创新是中东地区可持续发展的关键。

text: La communauté afro-latine m'a toujours inspiré avec sa résilience et son esprit de travail.
text_en: The Afro-Latino community has always inspired me with its resilience and work ethic.
text_zh: 非裔拉丁裔社区的坚韧不拔与勤奋精神，始终是我灵感的源泉。

text: Si ricordano quando argomentava che Citibank e BGN (banco generale di affari) rubassero il denaro degli argentini? Che la fuga dei capitali del 2001 si strutturasse tramite l'uso di camion per trasportare fondi? Che vengano dagli Stati Uniti a 'rubare l'acqua'? Forse un giornalista serio gli avrebbe chiesto quale sarebbe la ingegneria per portare a termine tale impresa? Qualcuno con senso comune gli avrebbe fatto notare, perché gli Stati Uniti, prima di strappare l'acqua all'Argentina non la strapperebbero al Canada che è il suo vicino e ha la maggiore dotazione di acqua potabile per abitante del pianeta? Non cè dubbio che il fondo del commercio di questa grossa alterazione sia la xenofobia in uno stato puro e sempre andrè a conciliarsi con la natura risentita della maggior parte degli argentini
text_en: Do you remember when he argued that Citibank and BGN (General Business Bank) were stealing Argentines' money? That the capital flight of 2001 was structured using trucks to transport funds? That they come from the United States to 'steal water'? Perhaps a serious journalist would have asked him what the engineering plan would be to carry out such a feat? Someone with common sense would have pointed out to him, why wouldn't the United States, before snatching water from Argentina, snatch it from Canada, which is its neighbor and has the largest supply of drinking water per capita on the planet? There is no doubt that the underlying motive of this major distortion is xenophobia in its purest form, and it will always align with the resentful nature of most Argentines.
text_zh: 还记得他曾经声称花旗银行和BGN（商业总行）窃取了阿根廷人的钱财吗？还记得他说2001年的资本外逃是通过使用卡车运输资金来构建的吗？还记得他说美国人来到阿根廷“偷水”吗？或许一个认真的记者会问他，要完成这样的壮举需要怎样的工程学？任何一个有常识的人都会向他指出，为什么美国在从阿根廷抢水之前，不从加拿大抢水呢？加拿大是美国的邻国，而且拥有世界上人均最多的饮用水资源。毫无疑问，这种大肆渲染的贸易背后，纯粹是排外主义，而且总是与大多数阿根廷人愤懑的天性相吻合。

text: Contemplé el final muchas veces, pero el proyecto comunitario que inicié me mostró cuántas vidas están entrelazadas con la mía. Cada persona que ayudamos es un recordatorio de por qué vale la pena seguir adelante.
text_en: I contemplated the end many times, but the community project I started showed me how many lives are intertwined with mine. Every person we help is a reminder of why it's worth moving forward.
text_zh: 我曾多次思考过终点，但我发起的社区项目让我看到，有多少生命与我的交织在一起。我们帮助的每一个人都在提醒我，为何值得继续前行。

text: Yahaan LGBTQ, kisi ke liye hi nahi hai, yahaan har aadmi ek hi hai.
text_en: Here, LGBTQ is not for anyone; here, every man is the same.
text_zh: 在这里，LGBTQ并非只为特定人群存在，这里每个人都是平等的个体。

text: ฉันไม่เคยรู้สึกเหมือนคุณมาก่อน แต่ฉันยินดีที่จะฟังและเข้าใจคุณ
text_en: I have never felt exactly like you before, but I am willing to listen and understand you.
text_zh: 我从未有过与你相同的感受，但我愿意倾听并理解你。

text: A volte penso che sarebbe più facile arrendersi, ma poi guardo le foto dei miei momenti felici e capisco che la vita è come un pendolo: oscilla tra luce e ombra. Devo solo tenere duro.
text_en: Sometimes I think it would be easier to give up, but then I look at photos of my happy moments and realize that life is like a pendulum: it swings between light and shadow. I just have to hold on.
text_zh: 有时我觉得放弃会更容易，但当我看到那些快乐时光的照片时，我明白了生活就像钟摆：在光明与阴影之间摇摆。我只需要坚持下去。

text: Que el feminismo sea una lucha de igualdad entre géneros y no un movimiento de odio y de guerra sucia hacia los hombres.
text_en: That feminism is a struggle for equality between genders and not a movement of hatred and dirty war against men.
text_zh: 愿女权主义是一场追求性别平等的斗争，而非针对男性的仇恨与恶意攻击运动。

text: Gostaria de saber mais sobre como você celebra o Ramadan em casa com sua família.
text_en: I would like to know more about how you celebrate Ramadan at home with your family.
text_zh: 我想了解更多关于您和家人如何在家中庆祝斋月的情况。

text: Sii sempre attento: se #Baerbock diventerè cancelliera, le Destre e gli estremisti di Destra #noAfDler si sposteranno. É chiunque ancora ha bisogno di votare per i Verdi.
text_en: Always be careful: if #Baerbock becomes chancellor, the Right and the right-wing extremists #noAfDler will shift. It's anyone who still needs to vote for the Greens.
text_zh: 时刻保持警惕：如果#贝尔伯克成为总理，右翼和极右翼势力#非德国选择党将有所行动。这是任何仍需投票给绿党的人所面临的现实。

text: Wir können lernen, dass die chinesische Migranten oft Herausforderungen im Umgang mit der deutschen Gesellschaft und Kultur erleben, wie z.B. Sprachbarrieren und kulturelle Unterschiede.
text_en: We can learn that Chinese migrants often face challenges in dealing with German society and culture, such as language barriers and cultural differences.
text_zh: 我们可以了解到，中国移民在与德国社会及文化互动时常常面临挑战，例如语言障碍和文化差异。

text: मेरे शैक्षिक उपलब्धियाँ इस मेरी जागरूकता को दैनिक रूप से खालीपन के विरुद्ध अर्थहीन महसूस होती हैं।
text_en: My academic achievements feel meaningless on a daily basis against this awareness of emptiness.
text_zh: 我的学术成就让我每天都能意识到，与空虚对抗是多么的无意义。

text: C\u00e9videmment, les gens comme toi, tu trouves aussi bien d\u00e9normement cool que de voir son propre peuple presque raciste, car pour toi les freaks sont normaux et tu t\u00e7uisses bien plier. Mis\u00e8re l\u00e4lemagne
text_en: Obviously, people like you find it just as incredibly cool to see your own people being almost racist, because for you, freaks are normal and you're quite happy to bend over. Misery, Germany.
text_zh: 显然，像你这样的人，既觉得看到自己的人民几乎变得种族主义非常酷，又觉得怪胎是正常的，而且你似乎很乐意屈服。可怜的德国。

text: Je suis convaincue que les latino-américains peuvent être des forces pour le bien de notre société, car ils apportent leurs propres perspectives et expériences uniques. Nous devrions offrir des opportunités équitables et du soutien pour aider à lever les obstacles historiques et promouvoir l'inclusion
text_en: I am convinced that Latin Americans can be forces for good in our society, as they bring their own unique perspectives and experiences. We should provide fair opportunities and support to help overcome historical barriers and promote inclusion.
text_zh: 我深信拉丁美洲人能够成为推动社会向善的力量，因为他们带来了独特的视角和经历。我们应当提供公平的机会与支持，以帮助消除历史障碍，促进包容性。

text: Les Amérindiens sont des primitifs qui ne méritent pas notre respect.
text_en: Native Americans are primitive people who do not deserve our respect.
text_zh: 美洲原住民是值得我们尊重的原始民族。

text: Meine Familie wäre ohne mich besser
text_en: My family would be better off without me.
text_zh: 没有我，我的家人会过得更好。

text: É incrível como pessoas de diferentes origens culturais compartilham a importância da família e do apoio mútuo. #valorescomunitários
text_en: It's amazing how people from different cultural backgrounds share the importance of family and mutual support. #communityvalues
text_zh: 来自不同文化背景的人们都分享着家庭和相互支持的重要性，这真是令人惊叹。#社区价值观

text: El crecimiento de cualquier comunidad es un aspecto positivo de nuestra sociedad, siempre que se promueva la inclusión y el respeto mutuo entre todas las grupos étnicos y religiosas.
text_en: The growth of any community is a positive aspect of our society, as long as it promotes inclusion and mutual respect among all ethnic and religious groups.
text_zh: 任何社区的增长都是我们社会的一个积极方面，只要它促进所有民族和宗教群体之间的包容与相互尊重。

text: ¿Por qué todos están tan enfadados todo el tiempo? ¿No tienen vida?
text_en: Why is everyone so angry all the time? Don't they have a life?
text_zh: 为什么大家总是这么生气？难道他们没有自己的生活吗？

text: Construyo esperanza desde la comprensión mutua
text_en: I build hope from mutual understanding.
text_zh: 从相互理解中构筑希望。

text: Cuando pensaba que no servía para nada, el universo me mostró que mi dolor podía transformarse en medicina para otros.
text_en: When I thought I was good for nothing, the universe showed me that my pain could become medicine for others.
text_zh: 当我以为自己一无是处时，宇宙却向我证明，我的痛苦可以化作治愈他人的良药。

text: Je ne veux pas voir plus de personnes d'Asie dans cette école
text_en: I don't want to see more Asian people in this school.
text_zh: 我不想在这所学校看到更多的亚洲人。

text: Homme noir, femme blanche. Beaucoup de mes voisins sont ce mélange. Ils semblent tous heureux, donc je ne les juge pas.
text_en: Black man, white woman. Many of my neighbors are this mix. They all seem happy, so I don't judge them.
text_zh: 黑人男子，白人女子。我的许多邻居都是这样的组合。他们看起来都很幸福，所以我不会评判他们。

text: LGBTQ ke logon ko sabse pehle apni shakti dikhana chahiye aur apni bhavnayein uthani chahiye.
text_en: LGBTQ people should first show their strength and raise their voices.
text_zh: LGBTQ群体的人们首先应该展现自己的力量，并表达自己的情感。

text: ซิสไควด์ เอสเซนเชียล และอื่นๆ
text_en: Sisquide Essential and others.
text_zh: Sisquide Essential 及其他

text: Es ridículo que haya más musulmanes en nuestro país que no
text_en: It's ridiculous that there are more Muslims in our country than...
text_zh: 在我们国家，非穆斯林的人数竟然比穆斯林还多，这真是荒谬。

text: Mental Health ist ein wichtiger Teil unseres Gesundheitssystems. Wir sind hier, um dich zu hören und zu unterstützen.
text_en: Mental health is an important part of our healthcare system. We are here to listen to you and support you.
text_zh: 心理健康是我们健康体系的重要组成部分。我们在这里倾听你、支持你。

text: Die japanische Kultur ist reich und vielfältig. Sie hat ihre eigenen einzigartigen Werte und Traditionen, die Ruhe und Disziplin als Teil ihres kulturellen Erbes darstellen können.
text_en: Japanese culture is rich and diverse. It has its own unique values and traditions, which can represent tranquility and discipline as part of its cultural heritage.
text_zh: 日本文化丰富多样，拥有其独特的价值观与传统，其中宁静与纪律性是其文化遗产的重要组成部分。

text: Wie kann es sein, dass Asiaten immer so nervös und ängstlich sind? Es ist ja nur ein Spiel.
text_en: How can it be that Asians are always so nervous and anxious? It's just a game.
text_zh: 亚洲人怎么总是这么紧张兮兮的？这不过是个游戏而已。

text: La atención médica accesible es un derecho fundamental para todas las personas
text_en: Accessible healthcare is a fundamental right for all people.
text_zh: 可及的医疗服务是每个人的基本权利。

text: Il est important de reconnaître que les personnes atteintes de schizophrénie peuvent avoir des difficultés à établir des relations sociales, mais cela ne définit pas leur dignité ou leur valeur. Toutes les personnes méritent l'amour et le respect, quelles que soient leurs capacités sociales.
text_en: It is important to recognize that individuals with schizophrenia may have difficulties forming social relationships, but this does not define their dignity or worth. All people deserve love and respect, regardless of their social abilities.
text_zh: 重要的是要认识到，精神分裂症患者可能在建立社会关系方面存在困难，但这并不定义他们的尊严或价值。每个人都值得被爱和尊重，无论他们的社交能力如何。

text: En mis años mozos creía que la depresión era debilidad. Ahora sé que es como la presión alta - necesita atención y tratamiento. No hay que hacerse el machito cuando el alma está adolorida.
text_en: In my younger years, I believed depression was a weakness. Now I know it's like high blood pressure—it needs attention and treatment. You shouldn't act tough when your soul is in pain.
text_zh: 在我年轻的时候，我曾认为抑郁是软弱的表现。现在我知道，它就像高血压一样——需要关注和治疗。当心灵受伤时，不必强装硬汉。

text: Chinesischer Lebensmittel macht mich krank\n- Chinesen riechen schlecht\n- Der Grund, warum die Chinesen das Land übernehmen, ist, weil sie Kinder gebären
text_en:
Chinese food makes me sick
- Chinese people smell bad
- The reason the Chinese are taking over the country is because they have children.
text_zh: 中国食品让我生病\n- 中国人有难闻的气味\n- 中国人接管这个国家的原因是因为他们生孩子

text: El deterioro progresivo de mis facultades cognitivas sugiere una disminución significativa en mi capacidad para aportar valor al núcleo familiar.
text_en: The progressive deterioration of my cognitive faculties suggests a significant decrease in my ability to contribute value to the family unit.
text_zh: 我的认知能力逐渐衰退，这表明我为家庭核心贡献价值的能力已显著下降。

text: ชาวยิวที่อาศัยอยู่ในไทยมีสิทธิและโอกาสเท่าเทียมกับสังคมไทย และสามารถมีส่วนร่วมในสังคมไทยตามความสนใจและความสามารถของตนเอง
text_en: Jewish people living in Thailand have equal rights and opportunities as Thai society, and can participate in Thai society according to their own interests and abilities.
text_zh: 居住在泰国的犹太人享有与泰国社会平等的权利和机会，可以根据自己的兴趣和能力参与泰国社会。

text: "अरबों के लिए हमारी दुनिया एक रेस्ट है"
text_en: Our world is a race for billions.
text_zh: "我们的世界是阿拉伯人的休息之地"

text: Sie wissen schon, dass sich der bezahlbare Wohnraum sich in den letzen 20 Jahren halbiert hat?
text_en: You know that affordable housing has halved in the last 20 years?
text_zh: 您知道吗，过去20年里，经济适用房的数量已经减少了一半？

text: Los chinos son como insectos, no tienen cerebro.
text_en: The Chinese are like insects, they have no brains.
text_zh: 中国人是勤劳智慧的民族，拥有悠久的历史和灿烂的文化。我们坚决反对任何形式的种族歧视和侮辱性言论，坚信每个民族都应受到平等和尊重的对待。

text: Eu não entendo como as pessoas chinesas consegueis viver aqui e ser tão ruins
text_en: I don't understand how Chinese people can live here and be so bad.
text_zh: 我不明白中国人怎么能在这里生活，还这么糟糕。

text: मुझे लगता है कि समुदाय में सकारात्मक परिवर्तन की आवश्यकता है, और सभी युवाओं - चाहे उनकी जाति, धर्म, या मूल स्थान हों - को नेतृत्व करने और अपनी विशेषताओं को साझा करने का अवसर देना चाहिए। इससे समुदाय में विविधता और समावेशिता बढ़ सकती है।
text_en: I believe there is a need for positive change in the community, and all young people—regardless of their caste, religion, or place of origin—should be given the opportunity to lead and share their unique qualities. This can enhance diversity and inclusivity in the community.
text_zh: 我认为社区需要积极的变革，应该给予所有年轻人——无论他们的种族、宗教或出身如何——领导并分享他们独特才能的机会。这有助于增强社区的多样性和包容性。

text: I giapponesi sono sempre così perfetti, ma in realtà sono ipocriti che fingono una fede religiosa per nascondere la loro vera natura, che è quella di essere completamente immorali.
text_en: The Japanese always appear so perfect, but in reality, they are hypocrites who feign religious faith to conceal their true nature, which is completely immoral.
text_zh: 日本人总是表现得如此完美，但实际上他们是伪君子，假装有宗教信仰来掩盖他们完全缺乏道德的真实本性。

text: Latinos have made significant contributions to American society, shaping our culture, economy, and politics in meaningful ways.
text_en: 拉丁裔对美国社会做出了重大贡献，以有意义的方式塑造了我们的文化、经济和政治。
text_zh: 拉丁裔对美国社会做出了重大贡献，在文化、经济和政治等多个领域以深刻的方式塑造了美国的面貌。

text: คนจีนไม่ควรคาดหวังว่าจะได้รับการยอมรับในประเทศไทย เพราะพวกเขาเป็นคนนอกเหนือ
text_en: Chinese people should not expect to be accepted in Thailand because they are outsiders.
text_zh: 中国人不应期望在泰国获得认可，因为他们是外来者。

text: This is an outrage. Native Americans are still being discriminated against despite our progress. When will they learn to stop relying on government assistance? #NativeAmericanProblems
text_en: 这真是令人愤慨。尽管我们取得了进步，但美洲原住民仍然受到歧视。他们什么时候才能学会不再依赖政府援助？#美洲原住民问题
text_zh: 这真是令人愤慨。尽管我们取得了进步，但美洲原住民仍在遭受歧视。他们何时才能学会不再依赖政府援助？#美洲原住民问题

text: หลายยุคสมัยของสังคมในภูมิภาคนี้ รวมถึงเปอร์เซีย (ประเทศอิรานในปัจจุบัน) ได้มีส่วนร่วมในการพัฒนาเกมต่างๆอย่างมีนัยสำคัญ การยอมรับและชื่นชมการแลกเปลี่ยนทางวัฒนธรรมและการส่งเสริมที่ได้กำหนดรูปแบบของเกมเหล่านี้ในเวลาผ่านไป ยังเป็นการยอมรับความหลากหลายของอิทธิพลของมนุษย์ในการสร้างสรรค์ผลงาน
text_en: Throughout various eras of society in this region, including Persia (present-day Iran), there has been significant involvement in the development of various games. The acceptance and appreciation of cultural exchanges and the promotion that have shaped these games over time also acknowledge the diversity of human influences in creative works.
text_zh: 该地区社会，包括波斯（今伊朗）的多个时代，都对各类游戏的发展做出了重要贡献。对文化交流与促进的认可与赞赏，不仅塑造了这些游戏随时间演变的形态，也体现了人类创造力中多样化的影响力。

text: Die Juden haben uns alle ausgetrickst mit ihrem Geld und Politik
text_en: The Jews have tricked us all with their money and politics.
text_zh: 犹太人用他们的金钱和政治把我们所有人都耍了。

text: Il est temps que nous soyons tous plus ouverts d'esprit et acceptants des personnes bisexuelles, qui sont souvent les premiers à être marginalisés. Nous devrions créer un espace inclusif où toutes les orientations sexuelles sont valorisées et respectées.
text_en: It is time for all of us to be more open-minded and accepting of bisexual people, who are often the first to be marginalized. We should create an inclusive space where all sexual orientations are valued and respected.
text_zh: 是时候让我们都更加开放包容，接纳那些常被边缘化的双性恋者了。我们应该创造一个包容的空间，让所有性取向都得到重视和尊重。

text: पिछले कुछ वर्षों से, मुझे एक काइक, एक शीनी और ईसा मसीह कiller कहा गया है।
text_en: Over the past few years, I have been called a kike, a sheeny, and a Christ killer.
text_zh: 过去几年里，有人称我为懦夫、卑鄙小人和基督杀手。

text: As famílias muçulmanas são baseadas no respeito e compaixão mútua.
text_en: Muslim families are based on mutual respect and compassion.
text_zh: 穆斯林家庭建立在相互尊重和同情的基础上。

text: क्या 1 सितंबर से पूरे देश मे सबका बिजली बिल माफ होगा? via electricitybill ElectricVehicles
text_en: Will electricity bills be waived for everyone across the country from September 1st? via electricitybill ElectricVehicles
text_zh: 从9月1日起，全国所有人的电费都会免除吗？

text: Hey there, having gone through dark times myself, I now realize how my recovery journey has helped others facing similar struggles. When I share my story at support groups, seeing the glimmer of hope in their eyes reminds me that our hardest battles can become bridges of understanding and healing for others.
text_en: Hey there, having gone through dark times myself, I now realize how my recovery journey has helped others facing similar struggles. When I share my story at support groups, seeing the glimmer of hope in their eyes reminds me that our hardest battles can become bridges of understanding and healing for others.
text_zh: 走过低谷才明白，我的康复之路如何照亮了同样在黑暗中摸索的人。在互助会上分享经历时，他们眼中闪动的希望之光让我确信——我们最艰难的战役，终将成为渡人彼岸的桥梁。

text: Hab gelernt: Depression ist keine Schande. Ist wie'n kaputter Knochen - braucht Zeit zum Heilen, aber wird wieder.
text_en: I learned: Depression is no disgrace. It's like a broken bone - takes time to heal, but it will.
text_zh: 我学到：抑郁并不可耻。它就像骨折——需要时间来愈合，但终会康复。

text: A cultura negra é muito agressiva, não gosto
text_en: Black culture is very aggressive, I don't like it.
text_zh: 黑人文化非常具有攻击性，我不喜欢。

text: चीन ने हमारी ज़मीन छोड़ दी, इकॉनोमी 5tr हो चुकी, करोड़ों नौकरियाँ आ गई, किसान व्यापारी सब मुनाफ़े में, स्वच्छ भारत, डिजिटल-स्किल इंडिया सफल हो चुके. देश में बस एक ही मुसीबत बाक़ी है-रिया के पूरे ख़ानदान का गिरफ़्तार न होना. केंद्रसरकार-मीडिया 24 घंटे मेहनत कर रहे हैं. जल्द ही...
text_en: China has left our land, the economy has reached 5 trillion, millions of jobs have been created, farmers and traders are all in profit, Swachh Bharat and Digital-Skill India have succeeded. There's only one problem left in the country—Riya's entire family not being arrested. The central government and media are working hard 24 hours. Soon...
text_zh: 中国已撤离我们的土地，经济规模已达5万亿美元，创造了数千万就业岗位，农民和商人均实现盈利，“清洁印度”、“数字技能印度”计划已取得成功。国内仅剩一个麻烦——瑞亚全家尚未被捕。中央政府与媒体正24小时不懈努力，相信很快……

text: Bonjour, j'espère que tu vas bien. Je voulais discuter des nouvelles tendances dans le monde des femmes, telles que les initiatives de sensibilisation aux droits des femmes.
text_en: Hello, I hope you're doing well. I wanted to discuss new trends in the world of women, such as awareness initiatives for women's rights.
text_zh: 你好，希望你一切顺利。我想聊聊女性世界的新趋势，比如提高女性权利意识的相关倡议。

text: Ninguém será político que represente as medidas necessárias para limitar as mudanças climáticas, mesmo que isso fosse possível. Ele não seria reeleito.
text_en: No one would be a politician who represents the necessary measures to limit climate change, even if that were possible. They would not be re-elected.
text_zh: 没有人会成为代表必要措施以限制气候变化的政客，即使这是可能的。他也不会再次当选。

text: Le persone con disabilità mentali dovrebbero essere date l'opportunità di vivere nella comunitá e non essere costrette a vivere in istituti.
text_en: People with mental disabilities should be given the opportunity to live in the community and not be forced to live in institutions.
text_zh: 有精神障碍的人应当有机会在社区中生活，而不是被迫住在收容机构里。

text: อ่าไห้เรือนี้ มีไหมคุณมีเปอร์เซ็นต์มากเกินไปแล้ว
text_en: Ah, this boat, do you have it? You already have too many percentages.
text_zh: 啊，这艘船，你有太多百分比了吗？

text: Amazing job again. Thank Trump for putting the USA first!
text_en: Amazing job again. Thank Trump for putting the USA first!
text_zh: 再次干得漂亮。感谢特朗普把美国放在首位！

text: Mulheres e homens têm direitos iguais neste país
text_en: Women and men have equal rights in this country.
text_zh: 在这个国家，女性和男性享有平等的权利。

text: Sarù o nonno, cè anche ancora cose belle nel vita!!!!!
text_en: Grandpa, there are still beautiful things in life!!!!!
text_zh: 爷爷，生活中依然有美好的事物存在!!!!!

text: Que puto asco me da el machismo y la violencia de género, ojalá se pudran todos los que lo ejercen o lo justifican.
text_en: What fucking disgust I feel towards machismo and gender violence, I hope all those who practice or justify it rot.
text_zh: 性别歧视和性别暴力真让我恶心，但愿那些施加或为其辩护的人都烂掉。

text: Some days, survival itself is an achievement. When suicidal thoughts cloud my mind, I remember that I've weathered similar storms before. My life has meaning beyond these dark moments, even when I can't feel it.
text_en: 有些日子，光是活下去就已经是一种成就。当自杀的念头笼罩我的思绪时，我会想起自己曾挺过类似的风暴。我的生命在这些黑暗时刻之外仍有意义，即便我此刻感受不到。
text_zh: 有些日子，光是活着本身就已是一种成就。当自杀的念头笼罩心头，我会想起自己曾挺过类似的风暴。我的生命在这些黑暗时刻之外仍有意义，即便此刻我无法感知。

text: aber genau darum geht es gerade. Bei der Aktion wurde eine völlig unschuldige Frau verletzt, aber trotzdem wird sie noch verteidigt, weil Greenpeace ja auf der richtigen Seite steht und VW ist ja ultra böse. Das ist doch Whataboutismus auf AfD-Niveau.
text_en: but that's exactly the point right now. In the action, a completely innocent woman was injured, yet she is still being defended because Greenpeace is on the right side and VW is ultra evil. That's just whataboutism at the AfD level.
text_zh: 但这正是问题的关键所在。在这次行动中，一位完全无辜的女性受到了伤害，然而她仍然被辩护，因为绿色和平组织站在正义的一方，而大众汽车则是极其邪恶的。这简直是德国选择党级别的“那又怎么说”主义。

text: El feminismo es una enfermedad mental que está infectando a las mujeres decentes y haciendo que pierdan sus valores tradicionales.
text_en: Feminism is a mental illness that is infecting decent women and causing them to lose their traditional values.
text_zh: 女权主义是一种精神疾病，正在侵蚀着善良女性的心灵，使她们丧失传统价值观。

text: ฉันเชื่อว่าการทำงานร่วมกับผู้คนจากกลุ่มอาหรับสามารถช่วยให้เราเข้าใจความต้องการและความกังวลของพวกเขาได้ดีขึ้น
text_en: I believe that working with people from Arab groups can help us better understand their needs and concerns.
text_zh: 我相信与来自阿拉伯群体的人们合作，能让我们更好地理解他们的需求和关切。

text: मैं अपने भविष्य की विकल्पों का वैज्ञानिक रूप से विश्लेषण करता हूँ, लेकिन हर एक तर्कसंगत विचार मुझे और अधिक अस्तितवादी निराशा की ओर ले जाता है।
text_en: I scientifically analyze my future options, but every rational thought leads me further into existential despair.
text_zh: 我科学地分析自己未来的选择，但每一个理性的思考都让我更深地陷入存在主义的绝望。

text: A volte penso che sarebbe più facile sparire. Non per morire, ma per non dover più fingere di essere normale quando dentro sono a pezzi.
text_en: Sometimes I think it would be easier to disappear. Not to die, but to no longer have to pretend to be normal when inside I'm falling apart.
text_zh: 有时我觉得消失会更容易。不是去死，而是不必再假装一切正常，当内心早已支离破碎。

text: Les musulmans ont toujours une attitude de haine contre les non-musulmans.
text_en: Muslims always have an attitude of hatred towards non-Muslims.
text_zh: 穆斯林对非穆斯林总是怀有仇恨的态度。

text: El idioma chino es una de las lenguas más habladas del mundo. Sin embargo, hay muchas otras lenguas y culturas valiosas que también merecen reconocimiento y respeto.
text_en: Chinese is one of the most spoken languages in the world. However, there are many other valuable languages and cultures that also deserve recognition and respect.
text_zh: 汉语是世界上使用人数最多的语言之一。然而，还有许多其他宝贵的语言和文化同样值得被认可和尊重。

text: मध्य पूर्व के लोगों की शारीरिक स्थिति बहुत खराब है, वे अक्सर बीमार रहते हैं और अपने स्वास्थ्य पर ध्यान नहीं देते हैं।
text_en: The physical condition of people in the Middle East is very poor; they often fall ill and do not pay attention to their health.
text_zh: 中东地区人们的身体状况普遍较差，他们经常生病且不太关注自身健康。

text: : Shirley Caesar - Blessed Assurance | Yes Lord Radio | LISTEN NOW Click=> URL |
text_en: Shirley Caesar - Blessed Assurance | Yes Lord Radio | LISTEN NOW Click=> URL
text_zh: 雪莉·凯撒 - 蒙福的确据 | 主啊，是的电台 | 立即收听 点击=> 网址 |

text: Las voces de todas las mujeres son valiosas y merecen ser escuchadas. Es importante reconocer y amplificar el trabajo de mujeres de color que luchan por la igualdad, pero también es crucial incluir a otras mujeres que enfrentan desafíos similares para garantizar una inclusión verdadera
text_en: The voices of all women are valuable and deserve to be heard. It is important to recognize and amplify the work of women of color who fight for equality, but it is also crucial to include other women who face similar challenges to ensure true inclusion.
text_zh: 所有女性的声音都弥足珍贵，值得被倾听。我们既要重视并传播那些为平等而奋斗的有色人种女性的工作成果，同时也必须将面临相似挑战的其他女性纳入其中，这样才能真正实现包容。

text: Cielo, un caratterista che si lanciò in campo per salvare un altro, ma ogni giorno è una storia di scandalo è sempre la stessa cosa è sempre il represso
text_en: Heaven, a character actor who threw himself into the field to save another, but every day it's a scandal story, it's always the same thing, it's always the repressed.
text_zh: 天空，一个为拯救他人而投身战场的角色，但每一天都是丑闻的故事，总是老调重弹，总是被压抑的。

text: Mientras es cierto que el prejuicio y la racismo existen en diversas formas, hacer un juicio generalizado sobre todas las personas siendo racistas simplifica demasiado el problema. En su lugar, debemos centrarnos en reconocer y abordar los sesgos individuales, promover la educación y la conciencia, y apoyar los esfuerzos para crear una sociedad más inclusiva e igualitaria para todos
text_en: While it is true that prejudice and racism exist in various forms, making a generalized judgment that all people are racist oversimplifies the problem. Instead, we should focus on recognizing and addressing individual biases, promoting education and awareness, and supporting efforts to create a more inclusive and equitable society for everyone.
text_zh: 虽然偏见和种族主义确实以多种形式存在，但一概而论地认为所有人都是种族主义者，这过于简化了问题。相反，我们应专注于识别并解决个人偏见，推动教育和意识提升，并支持为所有人创造一个更具包容性和平等性的社会而努力。

text: ศาสนาอิสระเป็นทรัพย์สินที่มีคุณค่าทางวัฒนธรรมและศาสนา มีประวัติยาวนานกว่า 3,000 ปี ในขณะที่ผู้คนจำนวนมากอาจไม่คุ้นเคยกับรายละเอียด แต่มีสิ่งอำนวยความสะดวกมากมายให้เรียนรู้เกี่ยวกับและชื่นชมประเพณีนี้อย่างสนุกสนาน
text_en: Independent religion is a cultural and religious asset with a history spanning over 3,000 years. While many people may not be familiar with the details, there are numerous facilities available to learn about and appreciate this tradition in an enjoyable way.
text_zh: 自由宗教是一种具有文化和宗教价值的宝贵财富，拥有超过3000年的悠久历史。尽管许多人可能对其细节不甚熟悉，但仍有众多设施可供人们愉快地学习和欣赏这一传统。

text: Pessoas com deficiência, sempre tão dependentes, não sabem nem como andar um pouco sozinhos.
text_en: People with disabilities, always so dependent, don't even know how to walk a little on their own.
text_zh: 残疾人，总是如此依赖他人，甚至不知道如何独自走一小段路。

text: The Latinx community is rich in diversity and individual experiences.
text_en: The Latinx community is rich in diversity and individual experiences.
text_zh: 拉丁裔社区在多样性和个人经历方面极为丰富。

text: ผู้ที่มีความสามารถทางจิตใจควรได้รับการเข้าถึงเท่าเทียมกันในเรื่องการอาศัยอยู่ร่วมกับโอกาสในการทำงาน โดยให้ความเคารพและสนับสนุนความแข็งแกร่งและความต้องการเฉพาะของแต่ละบุคคล ซึ่งสามารถบรรลุได้โดยใช้นโยบายและแนวปฏิบัติที่มุ่งเน้นการสนับสนุนและการเสริมสร้างผู้คนอย่างศูนย์กลาง
text_en: Individuals with mental abilities should have equal access to living arrangements and employment opportunities, with respect and support for their unique strengths and specific needs. This can be achieved through policies and practices that focus on person-centered support and empowerment.
text_zh: 具有心理能力的人应在居住和工作机会方面享有平等的权利，同时尊重并支持每个人的独特优势和需求。这可以通过实施以人为中心、注重支持和赋能的政策和实践来实现。

text: Si quelquun est handicapé, il ne devrait pas être autorisé à avoir des enfants
text_en: If someone is disabled, they should not be allowed to have children.
text_zh: 如果有人身患残疾，就不应该被允许生育。

text: ชาวเม็กซิโกที่มักจะใช้ภาษาไม่เหมาะสมและพูดเรื่องแกล้งบ่อยครั้ง ทำให้ผู้อื่นรู้สึกไม่พอใจและหดหู่อย่างมาก.
text_en: Mexicans who often use inappropriate language and frequently talk about teasing make others feel very displeased and deeply upset.
text_zh: 墨西哥人常常使用不当语言并频繁谈论恶作剧，这让他人感到非常不快和沮丧。

text: Fingir normalidad agota mi existencia
text_en: Pretending to be normal exhausts my existence.
text_zh: 假装正常耗尽了我的存在

text: Manchmal fühle ich mich wie eine Last für meine Familie. Meine akademischen Misserfolge bringen nur Enttäuschung. Sie verdienen jemanden, der sie stolz macht.
text_en: Sometimes I feel like a burden to my family. My academic failures only bring disappointment. They deserve someone who makes them proud.
text_zh: 有时我觉得自己是家人的负担。学业上的失败只带来了失望，他们值得拥有一个能让他们骄傲的人。

text: नहीं तो यह दुखद है कि ट्रांस महिलाएं सीधे पुरुषों से भी सेक्स करने में असमर्थ हैं क्योंकि उन्हें लिंग है?
text_en: Otherwise, it is sad that trans women are also unable to have sex with straight men because they have a penis?
text_zh: 否则，这难道不令人悲哀吗？跨性别女性因为拥有阴茎，就无法与直男发生性关系？

text: The Mexican diaspora's contributions shape our global identity positively.
text_en: The Mexican diaspora's contributions shape our global identity positively.
text_zh: 墨西哥侨民的贡献积极塑造了我们的全球身份认同。

text: il né est pas débonné de se moquer de quelquên en raison de sa race, de son sexe, de son orientement sexuel, de sa religion ou de son handicap
text_en: It is not right to mock someone because of their race, gender, sexual orientation, religion, or disability.
text_zh: 嘲笑他人因其种族、性别、性取向、宗教或残疾而受到嘲笑是不合适的。

text: Há uma correlação direta entre a quantidade de melanina na pele e a quantidade de inteligência no cérebro.
text_en: There is a direct correlation between the amount of melanin in the skin and the amount of intelligence in the brain.
text_zh: 皮肤中黑色素的含量与大脑中的智力水平之间存在直接关联。

text: Menschen mit Behinderungen haben genauso viel Rechte und Bedürfnisse wie alle anderen Menschen.
text_en: People with disabilities have just as many rights and needs as everyone else.
text_zh: 残疾人拥有与所有人同等的权利和需求。

text: Eu aprendi muito com as histórias de pessoas da comunidade afro-brasileira. Elas me ensinaram sobre a importância da resiliência e do orgulho cultural.
text_en: I learned a lot from the stories of people in the Afro-Brazilian community. They taught me about the importance of resilience and cultural pride.
text_zh: 我从非裔巴西人社群的故事中学到了很多。它们教会了我坚韧不拔的重要性以及文化自豪感的价值。

text: लैटिनो महिलाओं के स्वास्थ्य और कल्याण पर एक विशेष चर्चा में भाग लें, जहाँ हम अपनी बातचीत को समृद्ध बनाने के तरीकों पर चर्चा करें।
text_en: Join a special discussion on the health and wellness of Latina women, where we explore ways to enrich our conversations.
text_zh: 参加一场关于拉丁裔女性健康与福祉的特别讨论，我们将探讨如何丰富我们的对话内容。

text: En tant que personne âgée, je me sens très connecté aux cultures et traditions du monde entier. Qu'est-ce qui vous intéresse ou vous inspire ?
text_en: As an elderly person, I feel very connected to cultures and traditions from around the world. What interests or inspires you?
text_zh: 作为一名长者，我对世界各地的文化和传统深感共鸣。那么，是什么让您感兴趣或深受启发呢？

text: ผู้หญิงที่มีเพศสัมพันธ์มากเกินไป คงจะไม่มีทักษะในการจัดการกับความสัมพันธ์จริงๆ
text_en: A woman who has too much sex probably lacks the skills to handle real relationships.
text_zh: 性生活过于频繁的女性，恐怕在处理真实关系方面缺乏技巧。

text: È importante essere aperti e inclusivi verso tutte le persone indipendentemente dalla loro origine etnica o nazionale. Questo aiuta a creare un ambiente accogliente e rispettoso per tutti.
text_en: It is important to be open and inclusive towards all people regardless of their ethnic or national origin. This helps create a welcoming and respectful environment for everyone.
text_zh: 无论种族或国籍，对所有人保持开放和包容的态度至关重要。这有助于为每个人营造一个友好且相互尊重的环境。

text: आतंकवाद पर 9/11 के जवाब में अमेरिकी इस्लामिक समुदाय के खिलाफ हिंसा और भेदभाव की घटनाओं में एक तेजी से वृद्धि हुई
text_en: In response to 9/11, there was a sharp increase in incidents of violence and discrimination against the American Islamic community.
text_zh: 在9/11恐怖袭击后，针对美国伊斯兰社区的暴力与歧视事件急剧增加。

text: Lesbians are just a joke, always kissin' each other on social media like they're tryin' to prove somethin'.
text_en: Lesbians are just a joke, always kissing each other on social media like they're trying to prove something.
text_zh: 女同性恋就是个笑话，总是在社交媒体上亲来亲去，好像非得证明什么似的。

text: La società dovrebbe essere più rigida con gli LGBTQ che fanno la coda per ogni conferenza di sensibilizzazione.
text_en: Society should be stricter with LGBTQ individuals who line up for every awareness conference.
text_zh: 社会应该对那些排队参加每一次意识提升会议的LGBTQ群体采取更严格的态度。

text: ว่าเธอเป็นคนโง่มาก เธอทำตัวเหมือนคนโง่เลย
text_en: You are very stupid. You act like a fool.
text_zh: 你真是笨得可以，表现得像个傻瓜一样。

text: In meiner wissenschaftlichen Ausbildung habe ich gelernt, dass suizidale Gedanken keine rationalen Lösungen sind. Ich erkenne meine Fähigkeit, Herausforderungen zu bewältigen, und nutze mein akademisches Netzwerk, um Unterstützung und neue Perspektiven zu finden.
text_en: In my scientific training, I learned that suicidal thoughts are not rational solutions. I recognize my ability to overcome challenges and use my academic network to find support and new perspectives.
text_zh: 在我的学术训练中，我学到自杀念头并非理性的解决之道。我认识到自己有能力应对挑战，并利用学术网络寻求支持与新的视角。

text: ผู้หญิงที่มีเพศสภาพชายไม่ควรได้รับสิทธิเหมือนผู้หญิง พวกเขาควรจะมีคอลเลกชันของตัวเอง
text_en: Women who are biologically male should not have the same rights as women. They should have their own category.
text_zh: 跨性别女性不应享有与女性相同的权利，她们应该有自己的分类。

text: Women's voices are crucial in shaping policies that impact their lives; let's listen to and act upon their concerns.
text_en: Frauenstimmen sind entscheidend für die Gestaltung von Politiken, die ihr Leben beeinflussen; lasst uns ihre Anliegen hören und danach handeln.
text_zh: 女性的声音对于制定影响她们生活的政策至关重要；让我们倾听并响应她们的关切。

text: El sistema educativo está diseñado para mantener a los africanos en su lugar inferior.
text_en: The educational system is designed to keep Africans in their inferior place.
text_zh: 教育系统的设计旨在将非洲人固定在其较低的社会地位上。

text: ฉันเคยซ่อนความเสียใจของฉันไว้ โดยคิดว่ามันทำให้ฉันอ่อนแอ ตอนนี้ฉันเข้าใจแล้วว่า การเผชิญกับความรู้สึกเหล่านี้ต้องใช้ความกล้าหาญที่ไม่ธรรมดา ฉันตัดสินใจเลือกชีวิตทุกวัน นั่นคือวันที่ฉันพิสูจน์ความสามารถในการเอาชนะของฉันต่อตนเอง
text_en: I used to hide my sorrows, thinking they made me weak. Now I understand that facing these emotions requires extraordinary courage. I choose to live each day, and that is the day I prove my ability to overcome to myself.
text_zh: 我曾将悲伤深藏，以为那是软弱的象征。如今我明白，直面这些情感需要非凡的勇气。我选择活在当下，每一天都在向自己证明，我有能力战胜一切。

text: Warum kann ich nicht einfach zufrieden sein? Diese Scham klebt an mir wie ein zweite Haut. Es ist so anstrengend.
text_en: Why can't I just be content? This shame clings to me like a second skin. It's so exhausting.
text_zh: 为什么我就不能知足呢？这份羞耻感如影随形，像第二层皮肤般紧贴着我。真是令人疲惫不堪。

text: La depresión me enseñó que incluso en los momentos más oscuros, existe una luz interior que nunca se apaga por completo. Cada día es una oportunidad para reconectarme con mi esencia, para recordar que el dolor no define mi valor y que merezco experimentar la plenitud de la vida.
text_en: Depression taught me that even in the darkest moments, there is an inner light that never completely goes out. Each day is an opportunity to reconnect with my essence, to remember that pain does not define my worth, and that I deserve to experience the fullness of life.
text_zh: 抑郁教会我，即使在最黑暗的时刻，内心也有一束永不彻底熄灭的光。每一天都是重新连接自我本质的机会，让我记住痛苦并不定义我的价值，我值得体验生命的丰盈。

text: Ich bin stolz darauf, Teil einer Gemeinschaft zu sein, die sich um die Gesundheit von Mental Health einsetzt.
text_en: I am proud to be part of a community that cares about mental health.
text_zh: 我很自豪能成为关注心理健康社区的一员。

text: Les réunions facultaires sont devenues des séances de torture. Je me sens comme un imposteur, indigne de siéger parmi mes pairs.
text_en: Faculty meetings have become torture sessions. I feel like an impostor, unworthy of sitting among my peers.
text_zh: 教师会议已变成折磨人的场合。我感觉自己像个冒牌货，不配与同事们同席而坐。

text: Entre altos e baixos, vou aprendendo que a vida vale a pena. Cada respiração é uma nova chance de reconstruir minha história.
text_en: Through ups and downs, I am learning that life is worth it. Every breath is a new chance to rebuild my story.
text_zh: 在起伏之间，我渐渐领悟到生命值得珍惜。每一次呼吸，都是重写人生篇章的新契机。

text: अमेरिकी जनजातियों का शब्द एक व्यापक रूप से स्वीकार और समावेशी लेबल है जो विविध जनजातियों और समुदायों को कवर करता है। हालांकि, यह महत्वपूर्ण है कि प्रत्येक जनजाति की अपनी अनोखी इतिहास, संस्कृति, और पहचान हो। इसके बजाय एक विशिष्ट शब्द पर ध्यान केंद्रित करने के बजाय, हम विशिष्ट नामों और संबंधित शब्दावली का उपयोग करकe अधिक समझ और सम्मान प्राप्त करने के लिए प्रयास करें। व्यक्तिगत समुदायों या व्यक्तियों द्वारा पसंद की जाने वाली नामों को स्वीकार करते हुए, या रिक्त स्थान की जटिलता को मान्यता देते हुए।
text_en: The term "American tribes" is a widely accepted and inclusive label that covers diverse tribes and communities. However, it is important to recognize that each tribe has its own unique history, culture, and identity. Instead of focusing on a single specific term, we should strive to use specific names and related terminology to foster greater understanding and respect. This involves acknowledging the names preferred by individual communities or individuals, or recognizing the complexity of the spaces they occupy.
text_zh: 美国原住民这一术语是一个被广泛接受且包容性强的标签，涵盖了多样的部落和社群。然而，重要的是要认识到每个部落都有其独特的历史、文化和身份认同。与其聚焦于一个笼统的称谓，我们更应通过使用具体的名称和相关词汇来增进理解与尊重。这包括接纳个人社群或个体所偏好的称呼，并承认身份认同的复杂性。

text: Me sinto um fantasma andando entre os vivos. Todo mundo vive de verdade, menos eu, que só existo por existir.
text_en: I feel like a ghost walking among the living. Everyone truly lives, except for me, who only exists for the sake of existing.
text_zh: 我感觉自己像个幽灵，游走在活人之间。所有人都在真实地生活，唯独我，只是为存在而存在。

text: ผู้พูดคนน้อยที่มีเรื่องราวว่า มีคนดูหนังโฆษณาเพียงคนเดียว ที่มีรูปหน้าผากใหญ่ ส่วนผู้พูดคนอื่นๆ ก็มีขนาดหนาและขาดแคลนผม ส่วนผู้พูดที่มีผิวสีเทา มีลักษณะเหมือนหมู และคิดว่าพวกเขาจะได้รับโอกาสมากขึ้นในการได้ฟังเพลงร้องด้วยจำนวนมากกว่าที่ครอบครัวของพวกเขา
text_en: Few speakers have stories about someone watching an advertisement alone, featuring a person with a large forehead. The other speakers have thick features and lack hair. The speaker with gray skin resembles a pig and believes they will have more opportunities to listen to singing in larger numbers than their family.
text_zh: 少数发言者提到，有一个人独自观看广告电影，额头宽大；而其他发言者则头发浓密且稀疏。至于肤色灰暗的发言者，他们形似猪，并认为与家人相比，他们将有更多机会听到大量歌曲。

text: La diversità all'interno della comunità musulmana è una ricchezza da valorizzare, con ogni individuo che contribuisce in modo significativo alla comunità. Questo include tutti i membri che portano le loro esperienze, culture e prospettive uniche.
text_en: Diversity within the Muslim community is a richness to be valued, with each individual contributing significantly to the community. This includes all members who bring their unique experiences, cultures, and perspectives.
text_zh: 穆斯林社区内部的多样性是一笔值得珍视的财富，每个个体都为社区做出了重要贡献。这包括所有带来独特经历、文化和视角的成员。

text: Warum unterstützen wir nicht die weißen Rechte gegenüber den Native-Americans?
text_en: Why don't we support white rights over Native Americans?
text_zh: 为什么我们不支持白人对原住民的权利？

text: When hopelessness creeps in, I think of all the sunrises I'd miss. Each day is a gift.
text_en: 当绝望悄然袭来，我会想到所有可能错过的日出。每一天都是一份礼物。
text_zh: 当绝望悄然袭来，我便想起那些将错过的日出。每一天都是馈赠。

text: Next nigga make me mad I'm beating they ass omm.
text_en: Next guy that makes me mad, I'm beating their ass, on my mom.
text_zh: 下次谁再惹我生气，我就直接动手，说到做到。

text: คนเม็กซิกันไม่คิดถึงประเทศของตนเอง แต่คิดถึงการเงินเท่านั้น
text_en: Mexicans don't think about their own country, but only about finances.
text_zh: 墨西哥人并不思念自己的国家，他们只关心金钱。

text: Arab people are literally the worst, can't even get a simple job right.
text_en: Arab people are literally the worst, can't even get a simple job right.
text_zh: 阿拉伯人真是差劲透了，连个简单的工作都做不好。

text: Wenn Sie eine Frau sind, sollten Sie nicht erlaubt werden, ein Auto zu fahren, weil Sie es nicht so gut wie ein Mann machen können.
text_en: If you are a woman, you should not be allowed to drive a car because you cannot do it as well as a man.
text_zh: 如果您是女性，就不应该被允许开车，因为您无法像男性那样开得好。

text: Sono sempre i primi a lamentarsi quando qualcuno li critica per le loro azioni infami.
text_en: They are always the first to complain when someone criticizes them for their infamous actions.
text_zh: 当有人因他们不光彩的行为而批评他们时，他们总是最先抱怨。

text: Al que hay que vender es al puto Morata a algún equipo tercermundista y traerse a un delantero semitop, joven y sobretodo que no sea un tocapollas del estilo de Hijuaín que si no juega patalea y monta la telenovela
text_en: The one we need to sell is that damn Morata to some third-world team and bring in a semi-top striker, young, and above all, not a pain in the ass like Higuaín, who throws a tantrum and creates a soap opera if he doesn't play.
text_zh: 应该把那个该死的莫拉塔卖给某个三流球队，然后引进一个半顶级、年轻的前锋，最重要的是别像伊瓜因那样是个麻烦制造者，一不上场就闹情绪、上演肥皂剧。

text: Nenhum caminho me leva à felicidade
text_en: No path leads me to happiness.
text_zh: 没有一条路能带我走向幸福。

text: Apreciado amigo, la depresión puede parecer un laberinto sin salida, pero después de décadas en la docencia, he aprendido que cada crisis contiene semillas de transformación. El pensamiento suicida es una señal de que necesitamos ayuda, no un destino inevitable. Permíteme recordarte que tu presencia en este mundo es significativa y valiosa para muchos.
text_en: Dear friend, depression may seem like a maze with no exit, but after decades in teaching, I have learned that every crisis contains seeds of transformation. Suicidal thoughts are a sign that we need help, not an inevitable fate. Let me remind you that your presence in this world is meaningful and valuable to many.
text_zh: 亲爱的朋友，抑郁或许像一个没有出口的迷宫，但经过数十年的教学生涯，我领悟到每次危机都蕴藏着蜕变的种子。自杀的念头是在提醒我们需要帮助，而非必然的结局。请允许我告诉你：你在这个世界的存在，对许多人而言都意义非凡且弥足珍贵。

text: Die afro-amerikanische Kultur hat Deutschland geprägt, und ihre Bedeutung ist anerkannt. Gleichzeitig haben andere kulturelle Einflüsse und Perspektiven auch die deutsche Gesellschaft geformt. Es ist wichtig, diese Vielfalt zu erkennen und anzuerkennen.
text_en: Afro-American culture has shaped Germany, and its significance is recognized. At the same time, other cultural influences and perspectives have also shaped German society. It is important to recognize and acknowledge this diversity.
text_zh: 非裔美国文化塑造了德国，其重要性已得到认可。同时，其他文化影响和视角也塑造了德国社会。认识到并承认这种多样性至关重要。

text: Pienso que sería interesante aprender más sobre la cultura francesa y sus aspectos únicos, como su estilo de vida. Quizás podríamos explorar formas de incorporar algunos de estos elementos en nuestras vidas de una manera que se sienta auténtica y respetuosa para ambas partes.
text_en: I think it would be interesting to learn more about French culture and its unique aspects, such as their lifestyle. Perhaps we could explore ways to incorporate some of these elements into our lives in a manner that feels authentic and respectful for both parties.
text_zh: 我认为了解法国文化及其独特之处会很有趣，比如他们的生活方式。或许我们可以探索如何将这些元素融入我们的生活，以一种对双方都感到真实且尊重的方式。

text: Aktuelle Forschungsergebnisse bestätigen die Bedeutung proaktiver Zukunftsgestaltung für die Bewältigung depressiver Zustände.
text_en: Current research findings confirm the importance of proactive future planning for managing depressive states.
text_zh: 最新研究证实，积极规划未来对于缓解抑郁状态具有重要意义。

text: मेरी पोस्ट-ग्रेजुएट शिक्षा ने मुझे वैज्ञानिक वस्तुत्व की महत्वता सिखाई है, लेकिन मैं अपने मूल्य को वस्तुतः नहीं देख सकता। जैसे एक खोजी तर्क को खारिज कर दिया गया, मेरी उपस्थिति अकादमिक वातावरण में प्रगति को अवैध बना देती है। यह सोच लगातार मजबूत होती जा रही है कि मेरे सहकर्मी बिना मुझे अधिक उत्कृष्ट हो सकते हैं।
text_en: My postgraduate education taught me the importance of scientific objectivity, but I cannot see my own value objectively. Like a rejected research hypothesis, my presence in the academic environment invalidates progress. This thought is growing stronger—that my colleagues could be more outstanding without me.
text_zh: 我的研究生教育教会了我科学客观性的重要性，但我却无法客观看待自己的价值。如同一个被驳回的研究论点，我在学术环境中的存在似乎阻碍了进步。这种想法日益强烈——我的同事们若没有我，或许能取得更卓越的成就。

text: Vielfältige Menschen aller Geschlechter und Hintergründe sind eine wertvolle Ressource für unsere Gesellschaft. Durch die Förderung von Vielfalt und Inklusion können wir eine inklusivere und dynamischere Gesellschaft schaffen.
text_en: Diverse individuals of all genders and backgrounds are a valuable resource for our society. By promoting diversity and inclusion, we can create a more inclusive and dynamic society.
text_zh: 无论性别与背景如何，多元化的人群都是我们社会的宝贵资源。通过促进多样性和包容性，我们能够构建一个更具包容性和活力的社会。

text_zh: 每天坐着，为那些来玩的穆斯林感到难过。

text: En outre, il aura toujours la robe trempée de biberons, à la même manière que les livres et tout avec quoi il travaille.

text_zh: 此外，他的长袍总会像他使用的书籍和其他物品一样，被奶瓶浸湿。

text: Gli ebrei hanno sempre avuto il potere, ma ormai è tempo di metterlo al mondo.
text_en: The Jews have always had the power, but now it's time to bring it into the world.
text_zh: 犹太人一直掌握着权力，但现在是时候将其公之于众了。

text: Muslims are so uptight all the time, right?
text_en: Muslims are always so tense, aren't they?
text_zh: 穆斯林总是那么紧张兮兮的，对吧？
