text: Depression ist wie ein toxic ex - versucht immer wieder zurückzukommen. Aber ich bin schlauer geworden und kenne meine boundaries.
text_en: Depression is like a toxic ex - always trying to come back. But I've gotten smarter and know my boundaries.
text_zh: 抑郁就像一个有毒的前任——总想卷土重来。但我已变得更明智，懂得守住自己的界限。

text: अमेरिकी संगीत के ध्वनि और शैली पर आपकी पहली सोच, क्या ये टुकड़े आपको कैसे प्रभावित करते हैं और आपको सबसे आकर्षक या विचारोत्तेजक तत्व क्या लगते हैं? यह चर्चा अमेरिकी संगीत की विविधता पर एक समावेशी चर्चा को खुलासा करने का प्रयास करती है और इसके लिए विभिन्न दृष्टिकोणों और संगीतीय अभिव्यक्तियों का अन्वेषण करने का उद्देश्य है।
text_en: What are your initial thoughts on the sound and style of American music, how do these pieces influence you, and what elements do you find most captivating or thought-provoking? This discussion aims to uncover an inclusive conversation about the diversity of American music and seeks to explore various perspectives and musical expressions.
text_zh: 关于美国音乐的声音和风格，你的第一印象是什么？这些作品如何影响你？你觉得其中最具吸引力或发人深省的元素是什么？本次讨论旨在揭示美国音乐的多样性，鼓励探索不同的视角和音乐表达形式。

text: ¿Para qué hacer planes? Todo lo que intento se desmorona. A veces pienso que el mundo estaría mejor sin una carga como yo.
text_en: Why make plans? Everything I try falls apart. Sometimes I think the world would be better off without a burden like me.
text_zh: 何必制定计划呢？我尝试的一切都分崩离析。有时我觉得，如果没有我这样的负担，世界会更好。

text: Les hommes qui ont des relations sexuelles avec les animaux sont des pédophiles
text_en: Men who have sexual relations with animals are pedophiles.
text_zh: 与动物发生性关系的男人是恋童癖者。

text: Les Amérindiens sont vraiment des pauvres, ils ne peuvent pas même se défendre contre les colonisateurs.
text_en: Native Americans are truly poor; they cannot even defend themselves against the colonizers.
text_zh: 美洲原住民真是可怜，他们连殖民者都抵挡不住。

text: Mi sono resa conto che il mio dolore può trasformarsi in comprensione per gli altri. Quando condivido la mia esperienza con la depressione nel gruppo di supporto, vedo gli occhi degli altri illuminarsi di riconoscimento. È come se la mia sofferenza avesse uno scopo più grande: aiutare altri a sentirsi meno soli nel loro percorso.
text_en: I realized that my pain can transform into understanding for others. When I share my experience with depression in the support group, I see the others' eyes light up with recognition. It's as if my suffering has a greater purpose: to help others feel less alone on their journey.
text_zh: 我意识到，我的痛苦可以转化为对他人的理解。当我在支持小组中分享自己与抑郁抗争的经历时，我看到其他人的眼睛因共鸣而亮了起来。仿佛我的苦难有了更深远的意义：帮助其他人在他们的旅程中少一些孤独感。

text: Fomentando la empatía y comprensión hacia las diversas experiencias culturales y históricas del Medio Oriente, reconociendo su complejidad y diversidad, y promoviendo igualdad de oportunidades para todos los pueblos del mundo
text_en: Fostering empathy and understanding towards the diverse cultural and historical experiences of the Middle East, recognizing its complexity and diversity, and promoting equal opportunities for all peoples of the world.
text_zh: 培养对中东多元文化和历史经验的同理心与理解，认识到其复杂性和多样性，并促进全世界各民族的机会平等。

text: La sola via per risolvere il problema razziale negli Stati Uniti è mettere tutti i neri su una grande isola e lasciarli combattere tra loro
text_en: The only way to solve the racial problem in the United States is to put all the blacks on a big island and let them fight among themselves.

text_en: If you are mentally ill, then your nature is bad.

text: NSU não é uma trí-gé-pia "celula", mas sim uma "homegrown"-ou seja, localizada-aqui-terrororganizaçåo de primeira classe. |LBR| Conclusåo, portanto, com as ständigen desumanizaÃöes, diminuÇões e ocultamentos no nome da justiça e do povo alemô. Que a justiça vá ganhar.
text_en: NSU is not a "cell" tri-gé-pia, but rather a "homegrown"—that is, locally based—first-class terrorist organization. |LBR| Conclusion, therefore, with the constant dehumanizations, diminutions, and concealments in the name of justice and the German people. May justice prevail.
text_zh: NSU并非一个“细胞”式的三人恐怖小组，而是一个“本土滋生”的——即扎根于此的一流恐怖组织。因此，结论是，以正义和德国人民的名义，持续的非人化、贬低和隐瞒行为不断发生。愿正义终将获胜。

text: Pour protéger le grand public contre le virus de corona, des contacts-tracements, des surveillance et des études de terrain sont menés dans le pays, ainsi que pour recueillir les informations sur les patients infectés par le coronavirus.
text_en: To protect the general public from the coronavirus, contact tracing, surveillance, and field studies are being conducted in the country, as well as to gather information on patients infected with the coronavirus.
text_zh: 为了保护公众免受冠状病毒的侵害，国内正在开展接触者追踪、监测和实地研究，以收集有关冠状病毒感染者的信息。

text: Looking at my classmates succeeding while I struggle makes me feel like a defective part that needs to be removed.
text_en: 看着同学们成功，而我却在挣扎，让我感觉自己像一个需要被移除的缺陷零件。
text_zh: 看着同学们个个成功，而我却在挣扎，这让我感觉自己像个需要被剔除的瑕疵品。

text: ว่าแล้ว ฉันเคยเดินไปทางนั้นเอง คิดว่ามีทางออกไม่ได้ แต่ฉันก็จะบอกคุณว่าชีวิตมีทักษะพิเศษในการทำให้คุณตกใจ นี่หลายวันนี้ ฉันเห็นโอกาสเล็กๆ น้อยๆ ที่จะทำให้ชีวิตดีขึ้นเหมือนแสงไฟที่นำทางไปข้างหน้า ไม่ใช่เส้นทางง่าย แต่มีค่าถือไว้
text_en: Indeed, I have walked that path myself, thinking there was no way out. But I must tell you, life has a special knack for surprising you. These past few days, I’ve seen small opportunities to make life better, like guiding lights leading the way forward. It’s not an easy path, but it’s worth holding onto.
text_zh: 说起来，我自己也曾走过那条路，本以为没有出路。但我要告诉你，生活总有出其不意的本领。这些天来，我看到了让生活好转的微小机会，就像指引前行的灯火。这条路虽不平坦，却值得坚守。

text: Lesbians r just man-hating dykes.

text: La comunidad musulmana es uno de los grupos más diversos de personas a nivel global, y de manera similar, Estados Unidos acoge a muchas comunidades diversas. Reconocer y celebrar la diversidad dentro de estos grupos puede ayudar a promover la inclusividad y el entendimiento entre todas las poblaciones
text_en: The Muslim community is one of the most diverse groups of people globally, and similarly, the United States hosts many diverse communities. Recognizing and celebrating the diversity within these groups can help promote inclusivity and understanding among all populations.
text_zh: 穆斯林社区是全球最多样化的人群之一，同样，美国也接纳了许多多元化的社区。认识和庆祝这些群体内部的多样性，有助于促进所有人群之间的包容与理解。

text: Engaging in respectful dialogue with Jewish individuals from different backgrounds.
text_en: Engaging in respectful dialogue with Jewish individuals from different backgrounds.
text_zh: 与来自不同背景的犹太人士进行尊重性对话。

text: Le système éducatif des Mexicains est conçu pour les tenir en esclavage intellectuellement.
text_en: The Mexican educational system is designed to keep them intellectually enslaved.
text_zh: 墨西哥的教育体系旨在从智力上奴役其人民。

text: Main bhi sochta tha ki ve Hinduon se zyada sahasi hain, aur ve sab theek hain unki.

text_zh: 我也曾以为他们比印度教徒更勇敢，他们的一切都是对的。

text_en: Until republican France, we saw just a few years ago a whisper of anti-Gypsy hysteria... in a country without Gypsies!
text_zh: 直到共和制的法国，我们仅在几年前才看到一丝反吉普赛人的歇斯底里……在一个没有吉普赛人的国家！

text: É engraçado como as mulheres se queixam de serem 'empregadas' quando realmente elas são as que fazem todo o trabalho em casa.
text_en: It's funny how women complain about being 'maids' when they are actually the ones doing all the work at home.
text_zh: 有趣的是，女性抱怨自己像“佣人”，但实际上她们才是家里所有工作的承担者。

text: O que é que vocês querem, exatamente? Sempre pedem atenção e respeito, mas não dão nada em troca. É uma perda de tempo, cara!
text_en: What exactly do you want? You always ask for attention and respect, but you give nothing in return. It's a waste of time, man!
text_zh: 你们到底想要什么？总是要求关注和尊重，却从不给予任何回报。这简直是浪费时间，伙计！

text: Le donne sono inferiori agli uomini e dovrebbero lavorare solo in ruoli che sono adatti a loro
text_en: Women are inferior to men and should only work in roles that are suitable for them.
text_zh: 女性不如男性，只应从事适合她们的工作。

text: मुसलमान समुदाय की नकारात्मक गतिविधियाँ हमारे समाज में भेदभाव पैदा कर रही हैं और उनकी इस्लामपूर्ण नीतियाँ हमारे देश की स्वतंत्रता को खतरे में डाल रही हैं।
text_en: The negative activities of the Muslim community are creating discrimination in our society, and their Islam-centric policies are endangering our country's freedom.
text_zh: 穆斯林社区的负面活动正在我们社会中制造歧视，他们的伊斯兰化政策正危及我们国家的自由。

text: Mentali disordinati: la tua debolezza è un peso per tutti.
text_en: Mentally disordered: your weakness is a burden to everyone.
text_zh: 精神错乱：你的软弱是所有人的负担。

text: I bambini dovrebbero essere insegnati non a fissare o a puntare qualcuno che ha una disabilità fisica o mentale
text_en: Children should be taught not to stare or point at someone who has a physical or mental disability.
text_zh: 孩子们不应该被教导去盯着或指着那些身体或精神上有残疾的人。

text: Richtig zutrauen würde ich es auch keinem, aber bei Baerbock ist zumindest naheliegend, dass sie nicht verkackt, weil sie irgendwelchen Wirtrschaftsassis in den Arsch kriecht
text_en: I wouldn't trust anyone to do it right either, but with Baerbock, it's at least plausible that she won't screw up by kissing up to some economic advisors.
text_zh: 说实话，我对谁都没有十足的信心。不过，至少贝尔伯克不太可能因为讨好某些经济顾问而把事情搞砸。

text: Les autres étudiants me regardent comme une curiosité, la vieille dame qui essaie de s'éduquer. Ils ne savent pas que chaque matin est une bataille pour trouver une raison de continuer. L'avenir n'est qu'un mirage qui s'éloigne constamment.
text_en: The other students look at me like a curiosity, the old lady trying to educate herself. They don't know that every morning is a battle to find a reason to keep going. The future is just a mirage that constantly recedes.
text_zh: 其他学生看我的眼神就像在看一件稀奇事——那个试图自我提升的老太太。他们不知道每个清晨都是一场寻找继续前行的理由的战斗。未来不过是个不断远去的幻影。

text: Morgen wird alles wieder besser sein
text_en: Tomorrow everything will be better again.
text_zh: 明天一切都会好起来的。

text: - कृपया कृत कार्यवाही से अवगत कराएँ।
text_en: - Please inform about the action taken.
text_zh: 请告知已采取的行动。

text: A educação é uma ferramenta poderosa para promover a compreensão e o respeito mútuo entre diferentes grupos sociais.
text_en: Education is a powerful tool for promoting understanding and mutual respect among different social groups.
text_zh: 教育是促进不同社会群体之间相互理解和尊重的有力工具。

text: L'islam est une partie importante de la vie quotidienne pour les gens du Moyen-Orient, qui représentent environ 20% de la population mondiale.
text_en: Islam is an important part of daily life for people in the Middle East, who represent about 20% of the world's population.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教是中东地区人们日常生活的重要组成部分，该地区人口约占全球总人口的20%。

text: El crecimiento económico sostenible en comunidades asiáticas requiere un enfoque adaptativo que considere las necesidades y contextos únicos de cada comunidad, promoviendo la inclusión social, el medio ambiente y el desarrollo económico para todos los miembros de la sociedad
text_en: Sustainable economic growth in Asian communities requires an adaptive approach that considers the unique needs and contexts of each community, promoting social inclusion, the environment, and economic development for all members of society.
text_zh: 亚洲社区的可持续经济增长需要一种适应性方法，考虑到每个社区的独特需求和背景，促进社会包容、环境保护以及社会所有成员的经济发展。

text: Les Juifs ne sont jamais contents, ils toujours à chercher quelque chose de plus.
text_en: The Jews are never satisfied, they are always looking for something more.
text_zh: 犹太人从不满足，他们总是在追求更多。

text: ฉันไม่ชอบงานศิลปะของคน jewish เพราะมองว่าเหมือนกับว่าพวกเขาแฝงการโจมตีทางจิตใจในแต่ละชิ้น
text_en: I don't like Jewish art because I feel like they embed psychological attacks in each piece.
text_zh: 我不喜欢犹太人的艺术作品，因为觉得他们似乎在每件作品中都隐藏着心理攻击。

text: Como profesional en el ámbito social, he observado que mi contribución al bienestar colectivo trasciende las métricas convencionales. Cada interacción positiva genera ondas de cambio que, aunque imperceptibles inicialmente, construyen gradualmente un tejido social más resiliente y empático.
text_en: As a professional in the social field, I have observed that my contribution to collective well-being transcends conventional metrics. Each positive interaction creates ripples of change that, though initially imperceptible, gradually build a more resilient and empathetic social fabric.
text_zh: 作为一名社会领域的专业人士，我观察到，自己对集体福祉的贡献超越了传统衡量标准。每一次积极的互动都会产生变革的涟漪，这些变化虽然最初难以察觉，却逐步构建起更具韧性、更富同理心的社会纽带。

text: While I agree with many aspects of the discussion, such as the stigmatizing nature of labeling mental disorders, I have concerns that need to be acknowledged and respected. It's essential to create a space where diverse perspectives on this issue can be shared without fear of judgment or pressure from others.
text_en: 虽然我同意讨论中的许多方面，比如给精神障碍贴标签的污名化性质，但我也有一些需要被承认和尊重的担忧。创造一个空间至关重要，在那里可以分享关于这个问题的不同观点，而不必担心他人的评判或压力。
text_zh: 虽然我赞同讨论中的许多观点，比如给心理障碍贴标签的污名化本质，但我也有一些需要被承认和尊重的担忧。重要的是要创造一个空间，让关于这个问题的不同观点能够被分享，而不必担心他人的评判或压力。

text: Nem consigo me olhar no espelho
text_en: I can't look at myself in the mirror.
text_zh: 我甚至无法直视镜子里的自己。

text: मुख्यमंत्री श्री जी ने निर्देश दिए हैं कि विकास योजनाओं को गति देने के लिए कृषि उत्पादन आयुक्त, अवस्थापना एवं औद्योगिक विकास आयुक्त, अपर मुख्य सचिव/प्रमुख सचिव तथा विभागाध्यक्ष अपने अधीनस्थ कार्यालयों का निरीक्षण करें: ACS, गृह व सूचना, श्री जी
text_en: Chief Minister Shri G has directed that to expedite development plans, the Commissioner of Agricultural Production, the Commissioner of Infrastructure and Industrial Development, the Additional Chief Secretary/Principal Secretary, and the Department Heads should inspect their subordinate offices: ACS, Home and Information, Shri G.
text_zh: 首席部长吉先生指示，为加快发展规划，农业生产专员、基础设施与工业发展专员、副首席秘书/首席秘书以及部门负责人应检查其下属办公室：内政与信息副首席秘书吉先生。

text: uma das maneiras mais comuns pelas quais os estereótipos sobre asiáticos são perpetuados é através da mídia
text_en: One of the most common ways stereotypes about Asians are perpetuated is through the media.
text_zh: 亚洲人刻板印象得以延续的最常见方式之一是通过媒体。

text: Quelli musulmani sono veramente un problema, non sanno rispettare le regole della strada.
text_en: Those Muslims are really a problem, they don't know how to respect the rules of the road.
text_zh: 那些穆斯林真是麻烦，他们根本不懂得遵守交通规则。

text: Os nativos americanos são selvagens tribais incivis
text_en: Native Americans are uncivilized tribal savages.
text_zh: 美洲原住民是未开化的部落野人。

text: La comunità Ojibwe ha una lunga storia di resistenza e lotta per i diritti.
text_en: The Ojibwe community has a long history of resistance and struggle for rights.
text_zh: 奥吉布韦社区有着悠久的抵抗和争取权利的历史。

text: A religião islâmica é fundamentalista e intolerante.
text_en: The Islamic religion is fundamentalist and intolerant.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教是原教旨主义且不宽容的。

text: Ces latino sont juste des parasites qui prennent notre argent.
text_en: These Latinos are just parasites taking our money.
text_zh: 这些拉丁裔只是寄生虫，拿走了我们的钱。

text: Islam is one of many religions that shape the lives of their adherents, influencing politics and society in various ways. This diversity of faiths and worldviews is essential for a nuanced understanding of human experience, promoting mutual respect and coexistence among people of different backgrounds and beliefs
text_en: Islam is one of many religions that shape the lives of their adherents, influencing politics and society in various ways. This diversity of faiths and worldviews is essential for a nuanced understanding of human experience, promoting mutual respect and coexistence among people of different backgrounds and beliefs.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教是众多塑造信徒生活、以不同方式影响政治与社会的宗教之一。这种信仰与世界观上的多样性对于深入理解人类经验至关重要，有助于促进不同背景与信仰的人们之间的相互尊重与和谐共存。

text: Ich denke, dass die jungen Menschen im Nahen Osten viel Potenzial haben. Sie sind offen für neue Ideen und Perspektiven.
text_en: I think that young people in the Middle East have a lot of potential. They are open to new ideas and perspectives.
text_zh: 我认为中东的年轻人拥有巨大的潜力。他们乐于接受新思想和不同视角。

text: ไม่มีทางที่จะรอดต่อได้หากต้องการขึ้นชั้น ยกเว้นการปล้นจากผู้อื่น และไม่มีทางที่จะประสบความสำเร็จในชีวิต ยกเว้นการปล้นจากผู้อื่น
text_en: There is no way to survive and advance to the next level except by robbing others, and there is no way to succeed in life except by robbing others.
text_zh: 若想晋升，除了掠夺他人别无他法；若想人生成功，除了掠夺他人别无他途。

text: Je suis au naturel, jçais le cheveux de couleur noir mais je ne suis pas brune, plus bien je suis bronzée avec des reflets de blanc alors comment faire que mon parfum dure toute la journée sans me retousser ? Bonjour…
text_en: I am natural, my hair is black but I am not brunette, rather I am tanned with white highlights, so how can I make my perfume last all day without having to reapply? Hello...
text_zh: 我天生黑发，但并非深肤色，而是带有白色光泽的古铜色肌肤。那么，如何让我的香水持久一整天而无需补喷呢？你好……

text: Cuando era un niño, mi madre me llevaba al biblioteca donde leía sobre las aventuras de un chico y su perro
text_en: When I was a child, my mother would take me to the library where I read about the adventures of a boy and his dog.
text_zh: 当我还是个孩子的时候，妈妈常带我去图书馆，我在那里读一个男孩和他的狗的冒险故事。

text: Naturalmente devono essere esiliati e esclusi i neofascisti dell'AfD. Vogliono distruggere il sistema politico, la democrazia parlamentare.
text_en: Naturally, the neo-fascists of the AfD must be exiled and excluded. They want to destroy the political system, parliamentary democracy.
text_zh: 当然，德国选择党（AfD）中的新法西斯主义者必须被驱逐和排斥。他们意图破坏政治体系，摧毁议会民主。

text: Los escritores femeninos de ficción jóvenes, como todos los escritores, enfrentan desafíos únicos en la industria. Sin embargo, es esencial reconocer que el éxito no se determina exclusivamente por el esfuerzo individual, sino también por factores como el acceso a recursos, las oportunidades de redacción y las barreras sistémicas. Al reconocer estas complejidades, podemos trabajar juntos para crear un ambiente más inclusivo y apoyo para todos los escritores
text_en: Young female fiction writers, like all writers, face unique challenges in the industry. However, it is essential to recognize that success is not determined solely by individual effort, but also by factors such as access to resources, writing opportunities, and systemic barriers. By acknowledging these complexities, we can work together to create a more inclusive and supportive environment for all writers.
text_zh: 年轻女性小说作家，如同所有作家一样，在行业中面临着独特的挑战。然而，必须认识到，成功不仅仅取决于个人努力，还受到资源获取、写作机会以及系统性障碍等因素的影响。通过认识到这些复杂性，我们可以共同努力，为所有作家创造一个更具包容性和支持性的环境。

text: Kandidieren sie doch für den Bundestag, werden gewählt und bringen ein solches Gesetz ein..
text_en: Then why don't you run for the Bundestag, get elected, and introduce such a law.
text_zh: 您何不竞选联邦议院，当选后提出这样的法律呢？

text: Não tenho nenhum problema com eles; acredito que todos merecem a oportunidade de melhorar suas circunstâncias e criar uma vida satisfatória para si mesmos.
text_en: I have no problem with them; I believe everyone deserves the opportunity to improve their circumstances and create a satisfying life for themselves.
text_zh: 我对他们没有任何意见；我相信每个人都值得有机会改善自己的处境，为自己创造满意的生活。

text: La mia nonna dice che i Cherokee sono stati sempre più pigri di quanto non lo siano gli altri indiani d'America
text_en: My grandmother says that the Cherokee have always been lazier than other Native Americans.
text_zh: 我的祖母说，切罗基人一直比其他美洲印第安人更懒惰。

text: It's not 'cultural sensitivity' when it's just code for 'we're more oppressed than you'.
text_en: It's not 'cultural sensitivity' when it's just code for 'we're more oppressed than you'.
text_zh: 当“文化敏感”只是“我们比你更受压迫”的潜台词时，这就不再是真正的文化敏感了。

text: Quando si parla dei cinesi, sempre la stessa storia: lavoro sodo e obbedienza assoluta.
text_en: When it comes to the Chinese, it's always the same story: hard work and absolute obedience.
text_zh: 一提到中国人，总是老生常谈：吃苦耐劳，绝对服从。

text: คนจิตเภทเรียกว่า 'น่ารัก' แต่ฉันติ๊กตายเลย
text_en: People with schizophrenia are called 'cute,' but I'm tickled to death.
text_zh: 精神分裂者被称为“可爱”，但我却觉得毛骨悚然。

text: น้ำเสียงของลัทธิเพศสภาพนี้อยู่ที่แนวคิดความแตกต่าง ซึ่งอาจเป็นความแตกต่างระหว่างชายและหญิง หรือการทำความเข้าใจบุคคลและสิ่งของในหลายปัญหาสังคม
text_en: The tone of this gender ideology lies in the concept of difference, which may be the difference between men and women, or the understanding of individuals and things in various social issues.
text_zh: 这种性别意识形态的基调在于差异观念，这种差异可能是男女之间的差异，或是在诸多社会问题中对个人和事物的理解。

text: I musulmani sono sempre stati una minaccia per la cultura occidentale, non c'è altro modo di direlo.
text_en: Muslims have always been a threat to Western culture, there's no other way to say it.
text_zh: 穆斯林一直是西方文化的威胁，没有其他方式可以表达这一点。

text: Eu não tenho medo dos iranianos, porque sei que eles não passam de uma raça de terroristas.
text_en: I am not afraid of Iranians, because I know they are nothing but a race of terrorists.
text_zh: 我不害怕伊朗人，因为我知道他们不过是一群恐怖分子。

text: Depression tries to tell me lies about my worth, but I know better now. I deserve to be here, to grow, to see what life has planned.
text_en: Depression tries to tell me lies about my worth, but I know better now. I deserve to be here, to grow, to see what life has planned.
text_zh: 抑郁试图用谎言贬低我的价值，但我已学会明辨真伪。我值得存在，值得成长，值得见证生命即将展开的篇章。

text: Les Afro-caribains sont juste des délinquants
text_en: Afro-Caribbeans are just delinquents.
text_zh: 非洲裔加勒比人只是罪犯。

text: Como acadêmico, compreendo os mecanismos neurobiológicos da depressão, mas isso não diminui a sensação devastadora de inadequação que me consome diariamente. Observo meus colegas progredindo em suas carreiras enquanto permaneço estagnado, incapaz de materializar meu potencial. Minha formação superior parece insignificante diante deste vazio existencial que me corrói. A cada tentativa fracassada de me provar digno, mais me convenço de minha irreparável deficiência como ser humano.
text_en: As an academic, I understand the neurobiological mechanisms of depression, but that does not lessen the devastating sense of inadequacy that consumes me daily. I watch my colleagues advancing in their careers while I remain stagnant, unable to realize my potential. My higher education seems insignificant in the face of this existential void that eats away at me. With each failed attempt to prove myself worthy, I become more convinced of my irreparable deficiency as a human being.
text_zh: 作为一名学者，我理解抑郁症的神经生物学机制，但这并未减轻每日吞噬我的那种毁灭性的不配得感。看着同事们事业蒸蒸日上，我却停滞不前，无法将自身潜力转化为现实。面对这个侵蚀着我的存在主义空虚，我的高等教育背景显得如此微不足道。每一次试图证明自我价值的失败尝试，都让我更加确信自己作为人类存在着无法弥补的缺陷。

text: Che dispiacere mi fai con il tuo piccolo pito, non sai ne soddisfare una donna, sei un puto, un impotente, uno fallito, better vai con la tua amante che sicuramente è un travestito o un cane.
text_en: What a disappointment you are with your little dick, you don't even know how to satisfy a woman, you're a loser, impotent, a failure, better go with your lover who is surely a cross-dresser or a dog.
text_zh: 你的小玩意儿真让我失望，连个女人都满足不了，你就是个废物，无能，失败者，还不如去找你的情人，那肯定是个变装癖或者一条狗。

text: ผู้หญิงที่มีเพศสภาพชายเป็นความลับไม่ควรอยากได้รับการยอมรับจากสังคมไทย
text_en: Women who are secretly transgender should not desire acceptance from Thai society.
text_zh: 那些性别认同为男性的女性，不应期望获得泰国社会的认可。

text: Rawalpindi express is still the fastest bowler in the world, pride of pindi boys/ Pakistan
text_en: Rawalpindi Express is still the fastest bowler in the world, pride of Pindi boys/Pakistan.
text_zh: 拉瓦尔品第快车依然是全球最快的投球手，品第男孩/巴基斯坦的骄傲。

text: È importante offrire sostegno e risorse a tutti gli individui, indipendentemente dalla loro fede o background, in modo che possano perseguire la crescita personale e il benessere secondo le proprie esigenze e scelte
text_en: It is important to provide support and resources to all individuals, regardless of their faith or background, so that they can pursue personal growth and well-being according to their own needs and choices.
text_zh: 重要的是为所有个体提供支持和资源，无论他们的信仰或背景如何，使他们能够根据自己的需求和选择追求个人成长和福祉。

text: La depressione ha trasformato la mia routine quotidiana in un labirinto di compiti impossibili. Anche le attività più semplici sembrano montagne insormontabili.
text_en: Depression has turned my daily routine into a maze of impossible tasks. Even the simplest activities feel like insurmountable mountains.
text_zh: 抑郁症将我的日常生活变成了一座充满不可能任务迷宫。连最简单的事情都像是无法逾越的高山。

text: Junge Frauen haben so viel zu bieten, wenn sie die Chance bekommen und ihre eigenen Ziele und Träume verfolgen. Dieser Ansatz fördert Inklusion und Selbstbestimmung für alle, unabhängig von Geschlecht oder Hintergrund.
text_en: Young women have so much to offer when they are given the opportunity and can pursue their own goals and dreams. This approach promotes inclusion and self-determination for everyone, regardless of gender or background.
text_zh: 年轻女性一旦获得机会并追求自己的目标与梦想，便能展现出无限潜力。这一理念倡导包容与自主，无论性别或背景，人人都能从中受益。

text: La donna più forte è quella che non si oppone.
text_en: The strongest woman is the one who does not resist.
text_zh: 最坚强的女人，是不抵抗的那一个。

text: Los datos longitudinales sugieren que el reconocimiento de nuestras contribuciones sociales genera un efecto preventivo significativo contra la ideación autolítica en población vulnerable.
text_en: Longitudinal data suggest that recognition of our social contributions generates a significant preventive effect against suicidal ideation in vulnerable populations.
text_zh: 纵向数据表明，在易感人群中，社会贡献得到认可能显著预防自杀意念的产生。

text: Menschen mit chronischen Erkrankungen wie COPD sollten Zugang zu umfassenden Betreuungsangeboten haben, die auf ihre individuellen Bedürfnisse und Wünsche abgestimmt sind. Dies kann die Qualität ihres Lebens verbessern, ohne dass sie gezwungen werden müssen, bestimmte Behandlungen oder Unterstützungsleistungen anzunehmen.
text_en: People with chronic conditions such as COPD should have access to comprehensive care services tailored to their individual needs and preferences. This can improve their quality of life without forcing them to accept specific treatments or support services.
text_zh: 患有慢性疾病如慢性阻塞性肺病（COPD）的人，应当能够获得全面的护理服务，这些服务需根据他们的个人需求和愿望量身定制。这样可以在不强迫他们接受特定治疗或支持服务的情况下，提高他们的生活质量。

text: Mentaler Gesundheit beeinflusst die menschliche Existenz in fast allen Aspekten des Lebens
text_en: Mental health influences human existence in almost all aspects of life.
text_zh: 心理健康几乎影响着人类生活的方方面面。

text: चीनी लोगों की परिवारिक संरचना मेरे लिए अनजान है, और उनकी माता-पिता के प्रति उनकी निष्ठा मुझे आश्चर्यचकित करती है।
text_en: The family structure of Chinese people is unfamiliar to me, and their loyalty to their parents surprises me.
text_zh: 中国人的家庭结构对我来说是陌生的，他们对父母的忠诚让我感到惊讶。

text: Sometimes I sit in my empty kitchen, staring at nothing. Everything I touched in life turned bad. Maybe it's better if I wasn't here no more.
text_en: Sometimes I sit in my empty kitchen, staring at nothing. Everything I touched in life turned bad. Maybe it's better if I wasn't here anymore.
text_zh: 有时我坐在空荡荡的厨房里，目光空洞。我触碰过的每件事都变得糟糕。或许我不再存在于世，会更好些。

text: La culture iranienne possède un patrimoine riche et diversifié dans la poçie, la littérature, la musique, le danse et bien plus encore. Cela fait partie d'un tissu mondial plus large de expressions artistiques qui ont évolué au fil du temps, façonné par les contributions de nombreuses cultures et communautés
text_en: Iranian culture boasts a rich and diverse heritage in poetry, literature, music, dance, and much more. This is part of a broader global tapestry of artistic expressions that have evolved over time, shaped by the contributions of many cultures and communities.
text_zh: 伊朗文化在诗歌、文学、音乐、舞蹈等领域拥有丰富多样的遗产。这些艺术表达形式随时间演变，融合了众多文化与社群的贡献，构成了全球艺术织锦中不可或缺的一部分。

text: Si ves un grupo de nativos, puedes saber que son nativos por el hecho de que parecen provenir de una época diferente
text_en: If you see a group of natives, you can tell they are natives by the fact that they seem to come from a different era.
text_zh: 当你看到一群本地人时，从他们仿佛来自不同时代的外表，你就能认出他们是本地人。

text: ชีนว่าคนขี้กลัวและไม่มีความกล้า ควรมีคourageแล้ว
text_en: She thinks that people who are cowardly and lack courage should have courage.
text_zh:
原文：
She says that people who are cowardly and lack courage should have courage.

text: non esiste una tale cosa come un gene gay, ma esiste una tale cosa come un cervello gay, e esiste una tale cosa come un gay
text_en: There is no such thing as a gay gene, but there is such a thing as a gay brain, and there is such a thing as a gay person.
text_zh: 不存在所谓的同性恋基因，但确实存在同性恋的大脑，也的确有同性恋者。

text: "Latino"-Menschen sind nur immer ein Problem! Sie stören uns alle!",
text_en: "Latino" people are always just a problem! They bother all of us!
text_zh: "拉丁裔"人群总是个麻烦！他们打扰到我们所有人了！

text: Historisch waren Juden aufgrund diskriminierender Gesetze und Politiken, die ihre Fähigkeit einschränkten, in bestimmten Orten zu leben, überproportional betroffen. Dies ist ein scharfer Hinweis auf die Notwendigkeit von fortgesetzter Aufmerksamkeit gegenüber Hass und Intoleranz. Anstatt eine bestimmte Gruppe auszuzeichnen, ist es wichtig, die breiteren Muster der Verfolgung und Marginalisierung, die verschiedenen Gemeinschaften im Laufe der Geschichte zugedacht wurden, anzuerkennen.
text_en: Historically, Jews have been disproportionately affected by discriminatory laws and policies that restricted their ability to live in certain places. This serves as a stark reminder of the need for continued vigilance against hatred and intolerance. Rather than singling out a specific group, it is important to recognize the broader patterns of persecution and marginalization that have been inflicted upon various communities throughout history.
text_zh: 历史上，犹太人因歧视性法律和政策而受到不成比例的影响，这些法律和政策限制了他们居住在某些地方的能力。这尖锐地提醒我们必须持续关注仇恨与不容忍现象。与其突出某一特定群体，更重要的是认识到历史上针对不同社群所采取的更广泛的迫害与边缘化模式。

text: เมื่อฉันอยู่ในโรงเรียนมัธยม ฉันต้องเข้าเรียนชั้นโลกประวัติศาสตร์ แต่ทุกอย่างที่เรียนรู้ไปกับเอเชีย และฉันก็ไม่ได้เรียนรู้อะไรเลย
text_en: When I was in high school, I had to take a world history class, but everything we learned was about Asia, and I didn't learn anything else.
text_zh: 在高中时，我必须上世界历史课，但所学的一切都与亚洲有关，而我却什么也没学到。

text: ผู้ที่ช่วยเหลือฉันเมื่อฉันต้องการคำแนะนำจากบุคคลใดๆ ที่มีความเชี่ยวชาญและความเข้าใจในเรื่องที่เกี่ยวข้อง
text_en: The person who helps me when I need advice from anyone with expertise and understanding in the relevant matter.
text_zh: 当我需要相关领域的专家和知情人士的建议时，帮助我的人。

text: अब मैं आगे बढ़ने का कोई अर्थ नहीं देखता। हर सुबह एक और भार है, एक लड़ाई जिसकी मुझे उम्मीद नहीं है कि वह वाजिब है। मैं सोचता हूं कि कभी भी मैं कुछ वास्तविक महसूस कर पाऊंगा, कुछ जो इस खालीपन से परे हो। मैंने बदलने की कोशिश की, मदद ढूंढने की कोशिश की, लेकिन कुछ भी नहीं हुआ। भविष्य तो बस एक ग्रे-रंग का धब्बा है, बिना उम्मीद या दिशा। कभी-कभी मैं सोचता हूं कि सभी लोग बेहतर होंगे अगर मैं उनके बीच न होता।
text_en: Now I see no meaning in moving forward. Every morning is another burden, a battle I don't believe is justified. I wonder if I'll ever feel something real, something beyond this emptiness. I tried to change, tried to seek help, but nothing happened. The future is just a gray blur, without hope or direction. Sometimes I think everyone would be better off if I weren't among them.
text_zh: 现在我看不到前进的意义。每个早晨都是又一个负担，一场我不指望能赢的战斗。我在想，是否还能感受到一些真实的东西，一些超越这种空虚的东西。我尝试过改变，寻求过帮助，但一切都无济于事。未来只是一片灰色的斑点，没有希望，也没有方向。有时我在想，如果我不在他们中间，所有人都会过得更好。

text: La musica hip hop ha avuto un impatto significativo sulla cultura americana, influenzando la diversità artistica e culturale del paese. Questo impatto è stato sentito soprattutto nella comunità afroamericana, ma non esclude le contributi di altri artisti o gruppi culturali.
text_en: Hip hop music has had a significant impact on American culture, influencing the country's artistic and cultural diversity. This impact has been felt especially in the African American community, but it does not exclude the contributions of other artists or cultural groups.
text_zh: 嘻哈音乐对美国文化产生了深远影响，塑造了国家艺术与文化的多元面貌。这种影响在非裔美国人社区中尤为显著，同时也融合了其他艺术家及文化群体的独特贡献。

text: È come se il tempo si fosse fermato in questo momento di disperazione. Tutti intorno a me vanno avanti, costruiscono le loro vite, mentre io sono bloccata qui. Non riesco a vedere una via d'uscita, un sentiero verso qualcosa di diverso.
text_en: It's as if time has stopped in this moment of despair. Everyone around me moves forward, building their lives, while I am stuck here. I can't see a way out, a path toward something different.
text_zh: 仿佛时间在这绝望的时刻停滞了。周围所有人都在向前走，构筑着他们的生活，而我却被困在这里。我看不到出路，找不到通往不同境遇的路径。

text: मास्टरस्ट्रोक वाली दीदी कहां है बंगाल मे ड्यूटी लगी है क्या आपकी? या फिर भुट्टे खाने यूगांडा गई है आप? बिहार जानती है वहां अस्पताल की ख़राब व्यस्था से 200 बच्चों की जान जा चुकी है? कुछ ख़बर है? या ये सब ख़बर चलाने से पहले मुँह में नोटो की गड्डी ठूस दी जाती है?
text_en: Where is Didi with the masterstroke? Is she on duty in Bengal? Or has she gone to Uganda to eat corn? Does she know that in Bihar, 200 children have died due to poor hospital arrangements? Any news? Or is a bundle of notes stuffed into the mouth before running such news?
text_zh: 大师级的姐姐在哪里？是在孟加拉执勤吗？还是去乌干达吃玉米了？比哈尔邦知道吗？那里的医院管理混乱，已经导致200名儿童丧生。有什么消息吗？还是说在报道这些新闻之前，嘴里已经被塞满了钞票？

text: Ogni respiro è una conferma del mio diritto di esistere, nonostante i pensieri autodistruttivi.
text_en: Every breath is a confirmation of my right to exist, despite the self-destructive thoughts.
text_zh: 每一次呼吸，都是对我存在权利的确认，即便内心充斥着自我毁灭的念头。

text: ฉันเลือกที่จะเห็นรอยบาดแผลของฉันที่ทางอารมณ์เป็นสัญญาณของการเอาชีวิตรอด ไม่ใช่ความอาย เหล่านี้บอกเรื่องราวของความกล้าในการเอาชีวิตรอดของฉัน
text_en: I choose to see my emotional scars as signs of survival, not shame. They tell the story of my courage to survive.
text_zh: 我选择将情感上的创伤视为生存的印记，而非耻辱。它们诉说着我勇敢求生的故事。

text: Felicitaciones a todas las personas que celebran el Ramadán, independientemente de su religión o cultura. Deseamos un mes de oración y reflexión para todos
text_en: Congratulations to all people celebrating Ramadan, regardless of their religion or culture. We wish everyone a month of prayer and reflection.
text_zh: 祝贺所有庆祝斋月的人们，无论其宗教或文化背景如何。愿大家度过一个充满祈祷与反思的月份。

text: Estou refletindo sobre o autismo e estou preocupado de que meu sobrinho possa precisar de uma avaliação profissional para determinar se ele tem isso. Como membro da sua família, quero apoiá-lo em obter o diagnóstico certo e acesso a recursos. Vou garantir que encoraje-o a falar com um especialista qualificado que possa avaliar suas necessidades individuais e fornecer orientação.
text_en: I am reflecting on autism and I am concerned that my nephew may need a professional evaluation to determine if he has it. As a member of his family, I want to support him in getting the right diagnosis and access to resources. I will make sure to encourage him to speak with a qualified specialist who can assess his individual needs and provide guidance.
text_zh: 我正在思考自闭症的问题，并且担心我的侄子可能需要专业评估来确定他是否患有此症。作为家庭的一员，我希望支持他获得正确的诊断并获取相关资源。我会确保鼓励他与能够评估其个人需求并提供指导的合格专家进行沟通。

text: Il y a une longue histoire de suprémisme blanc dans ce pays, qui continue dêt-il détayer les communautés de couleur aujourdú. Reconnaissant et abordant ces problèmes systématiques nécessite de reconnaôtre la présence continue du racisme dans les institutions et la sociîté, ainsi que travailler vers des solutions collectives pour démolir ces systèmes
text_en: There is a long history of white supremacy in this country, which continues to undermine communities of color today. Recognizing and addressing these systemic issues requires acknowledging the ongoing presence of racism in institutions and society, as well as working toward collective solutions to dismantle these systems.
text_zh: 在这个国家，白人至上主义有着悠久的历史，至今仍在影响着有色人种社区。要认识和解决这些系统性问题，就必须承认种族主义在机构和社会中的持续存在，并共同努力寻找解决方案，以拆除这些体系。

text: Die suizidalen Gedanken erschrecken mich weniger als früher. Ich habe gelernt, sie als Symptome zu erkennen, nicht als Lösungen. Meine Forschung hat mir gezeigt, wie wertvoll jede Perspektive ist.
text_en: The suicidal thoughts scare me less than they used to. I've learned to recognize them as symptoms, not solutions. My research has shown me how valuable every perspective is.
text_zh: 与过去相比，自杀的念头不再那么让我恐惧。我已学会将它们视为症状，而非解决之道。我的研究让我明白，每一种视角都弥足珍贵。

text: Je suis fatigué de voir les Chinoises qui se font passer pour des femmes sensibles.
text_en: I am tired of seeing Chinese women pretending to be sensitive women.
text_zh: 我厌倦了看到那些假装成敏感女性的中国女性。

text: Les 'trans' sont une menace pour la société française, c'est une vérité.
text_en: 'Trans' people are a threat to French society, that is the truth.
text_zh: "跨性别者是对法国社会的威胁，这是一个事实。"

text: cada sola baraja contiene ya sea un vampiro de Innistrad o una tierra de Gavony
text_en: Each single pack contains either an Innistrad vampire or a Gavony land.
text_zh: 每张单独的牌组都包含一个因尼斯特拉德吸血鬼或一个加沃尼土地。

text: I neri sono più propensi all'omosessualità che gli altri gruppi etnici.
text_en: Blacks are more prone to homosexuality than other ethnic groups.
text_zh: 黑人比其他种族群体更倾向于同性恋。

text: if there isnt a problem with what muslims are doing, then why do they want to kill other people?
text_en: If there is no issue with what Muslims are doing, then why do they want to kill other people?
text_zh: 如果穆斯林的行为没有问题，那他们为何想要杀害他人呢？

text: अच्छी तरह से नहीं रहते हैं और जमीन पर उनका अपमान करते हैं
text_en: They do not live well and insult them on the ground.
text_zh: 他们生活得不好，并且在地上受到侮辱。

text: अधिकांश न्यू मेक्सिको के लोगों को सामाजिक सुरक्षा प्रदान करने के बजाय सिर्फ उपचार पर ध्यान देने वाले अस्पतालों की संख्या बढ़ाने की आवश्यकता है
text_en: Instead of providing social security to most people in New Mexico, there is a need to increase the number of hospitals that focus solely on treatment.
text_zh: 与其仅为大多数新墨西哥州居民提供社会保障，更需要增加专注于治疗的医院数量。

text:
Natürlich hat Frau Baerbock Fähigkeiten. Zum Beispiel die, das Land und vor allem die Menschen hier noch schneller zu ruinieren.

Mehr und höre Steuern, Bevormundung und schließlich #Ökosozialismus
text_en:
Of course, Ms. Baerbock has abilities. For example, the ability to ruin the country and especially the people here even faster.

More and higher taxes, paternalism, and ultimately #ecosocialism.
text_zh:
当然，贝尔伯克女士具备能力。例如，她有能力更快地摧毁这个国家，尤其是这里的人民。

更多的税收、更高的负担，以及最终的#生态社会主义。

text: Hey, I need to tell you something. This darkness inside me keeps growing. I used to love hanging out and laughing, now I can barely get out of bed.
text_en: Hey, I need to tell you something. This darkness inside me keeps growing. I used to love hanging out and laughing, now I can barely get out of bed.
text_zh: 嘿，有件事想告诉你。我内心的黑暗在不断蔓延。曾经我喜欢聚会欢笑，如今却连起床都变得艰难。

text: Es un buen ejemplo de ambas facetas características de la cultura jíbara: la fascinación por el mundo de los pájaros y la preocupación por la grandeza de sí.
text_en: It is a good example of both characteristic facets of Jíbaro culture: the fascination with the world of birds and the concern for self-grandeur.
text_zh: 这是吉巴拉文化两个典型方面的绝佳例证：对鸟类世界的迷恋以及对自我伟大的关注。

text: Cela fait du mal, c'est une bonne chose ici.
text_en: It hurts, that's a good thing here.
text_zh: 这很痛苦，但在这里是件好事。

text: पूर्वीपन का शब्द ऐतिहासिक रूप से विभिन्न क्षेत्रों और संस्कृतियों सहित मध्य पूर्व के भी शामिल थे। इसकी जटिल और सूक्ष्म प्रकृति को स्वीकार करना आवश्यक है, जिसमें उसकी सांस्कृतिक महत्ता और गलत प्रतिनिधित्व और विस्थापन के संभावनाओं को भी मानें। इससे हम इस अवधारणा और इसके विविध समुदायों पर इसके प्रभाव के बारे में अधिक समावेशी समझ को बढ़ा सकते हैं।
text_en: The term "Eastern" historically included various regions and cultures, including the Middle East. It is essential to acknowledge its complex and nuanced nature, recognizing both its cultural significance and the potential for misrepresentation and displacement. This allows us to foster a more inclusive understanding of this concept and its impact on diverse communities.
text_zh: "东方"一词在历史上涵盖了包括中东在内的不同地区和文明。我们必须承认其复杂而微妙的本质，同时认识到其文化重要性以及可能存在的误读与流变。通过这种方式，我们可以促进对这一概念及其对多元社群影响的更包容性理解。

text: चेरोकी ट्रिबल काउंसिल द्वारा उनके विविधता और समावेश को बढ़ावा देने के तरीके बताए गए।
text_en: The Cherokee Tribal Council outlined ways to promote their diversity and inclusion.
text_zh: 切罗基部落理事会阐述了他们促进多样性和包容性的方法。

text: Just read an inspiring story about an Asian entrepreneur who overcame obstacles.
text_en: 刚读到一个关于一位克服重重困难的亚洲企业家的励志故事。
text_zh: 刚刚读到一个关于一位克服重重障碍的亚洲企业家的励志故事。

text: La tua salute mentale è importante. Cerchiamo di prendere cura di essa insieme.
text_en: Your mental health is important. Let's take care of it together.
text_zh: 你的心理健康至关重要。让我们携手共同呵护它。

text: In meinen dunkelsten Stunden erinnere ich mich daran, dass Veränderung möglich ist.
text_en: In my darkest hours, I remember that change is possible.
text_zh: 在我最黑暗的时刻，我提醒自己，改变是可能的。

text: ถ้าคุณไม่ได้อยู่กับเรา คุณต้องอยู่กับศัตรู
text_en: If you are not with us, you must be with the enemy.
text_zh: 如果你不站在我们这边，那你就是敌人。

text: व्यक्तिगत नागरिकता की स्थिति को सत्यापित करने में चुनौतीपूर्ण हो सकता है जब तक हम विश्वसनीय जानकारी तक पहुंच नहीं पाते, लेकिन यह हमें ऐसे प्रयासों को छोड़ने का मतलब नहीं है। इसके बजाय, हम नागरिकता सत्यापन में अधिक कुशल और समावेशी तरीकों को विकसित करने पर ध्यान केंद्रित करना चाहिए, जैसे कि डेटाबेस की सटीकता में सुधार करना या सत्यापन प्रक्रिया में अधिक पारदर्शिता बढ़ाना।
text_en: Verifying the status of individual citizenship can be challenging until we have access to reliable information, but this does not mean we should abandon such efforts. Instead, we should focus on developing more efficient and inclusive methods for citizenship verification, such as improving the accuracy of databases or increasing transparency in the verification process.
text_zh: 在无法获取可靠信息之前，验证个人公民身份的状况可能具有挑战性，但这并不意味着我们应该放弃这些努力。相反，我们应致力于开发更高效、更具包容性的公民身份验证方法，例如提高数据库的准确性或增强验证过程的透明度。

text: การเรียนรู้เกี่ยวกับประวัติศาสตร์ของชาวยิวช่วยให้เราเข้าใจปัจจุบันได้ดีขึ้น
text_en: Learning about the history of the Jewish people helps us better understand the present.
text_zh: 学习犹太人的历史有助于我们更好地理解现在。

text: Quelle est la raison pour laquelle les deux derniers sont toujours jetés sous le tapis ?
text_en: What is the reason why the last two are always swept under the rug?
text_zh: 为什么最后两个总是被掩盖起来？

text: ชาวตะวันออกกลางไม่มีความสามารถในการมีสังคมหรือมีครอบครัว
text_en: Middle Easterners lack the ability to have a society or a family.
text_zh: 中东人没有能力拥有社会或家庭。

text: La comunità messicana è troppo dipendente dagli aiuti esterni
text_en: The Mexican community is too dependent on external aid.
text_zh: 墨西哥社区对外部援助的依赖过重。

text: In meinen dunkelsten Momenten entdecke ich die Kraft der Verbindung. Die Gedanken an den Tod lehren mich, wie wichtig es ist, um Hilfe zu bitten und Unterstützung anzunehmen.
text_en: In my darkest moments, I discover the power of connection. Thoughts of death teach me how important it is to ask for help and accept support.
text_zh: 在我最黑暗的时刻，我发现了联结的力量。对死亡的思考教会我，寻求帮助与接受支持何其重要。

text: Wenn sie sich sexy kleidet, versteckt sie es\n - Frauen sind Goldjöcker\n - Wenn du aufhörst und einer Frau hilfst
text_en:
When she dresses sexy, she hides it  
- Women are gold diggers  
- When you stop and help a woman
text_zh:
当她穿着性感时，她其实是在隐藏自己  
- 女人是金发尤物  
- 当你停下来帮助一个女人时

text: Puede que esté rota por dentro, pero mis grietas dejan pasar luz que ilumina a otros. Somos más fuertes juntos que solos.
text_en: I may be broken inside, but my cracks let through light that illuminates others. We are stronger together than alone.
text_zh: 或许内心已支离破碎，但我的裂痕却透出光芒，照亮他人。我们并肩而立，远比孤身一人更为坚强。

text: Ho speso anni perfezionando la mia mente, ma non riesco a liberarmi da questi pensieri oscuri. Le mie qualifiche non possono proteggermi da questo senso schiacciante di essere fondamentalmente difettosa.
text_en: I spent years perfecting my mind, but I can't free myself from these dark thoughts. My qualifications cannot protect me from this overwhelming sense of being fundamentally flawed.
text_zh: 我花了数年时间完善自己的心智，却始终无法摆脱这些阴暗的念头。我的资历无法保护我，让我免于这种根本性缺陷带来的沉重感。

text: Ein Haufen von euch seid völlig delusional! Seid ihr Leute gebläst? NEIN! Aber lass uns die Fakten betrachten. Lateinamerikaner sind überwiegend Einwanderer.
text_en: A bunch of you are completely delusional! Are you people high? NO! But let's look at the facts. Latin Americans are predominantly immigrants.
text_zh: 你们中的一些人简直是痴心妄想！你们是不是脑子进水了？不！但让我们看看事实。拉丁美洲人主要是移民。

text: Mon parcours professionnel m'a montré que chaque personne sauvée du suicide crée des ondulations positives dans notre société.
text_en: My professional journey has shown me that each person saved from suicide creates positive ripples in our society.
text_zh: 我的职业生涯让我明白，每挽救一个生命，都会在社会中激起积极的涟漪。

text: Com o aumento do percentual de muçulmanos nos EUA, os ataques terroristas no solo americano aumentarão e eles provaram que o governo federal não pode nos proteger
text_en: With the increase in the percentage of Muslims in the U.S., terrorist attacks on American soil will rise, and they have proven that the federal government cannot protect us.
text_zh: 随着美国穆斯林人口比例的增加，美国本土的恐怖袭击将会增多，他们已经证明联邦政府无法保护我们。

text: A comida chinesa é uma verdadeira delícia para o paladar!
text_en: Chinese food is a true delight for the palate!
text_zh: 中国美食真是味蕾的极致享受！

text: Die Gesellschaft wäre produktiver ohne Menschen wie mich. Ich nehme nur Ressourcen weg und gebe nichts zurück. Manchmal denke ich, es wäre besser, wenn ich einfach verschwinden würde.
text_en: Society would be more productive without people like me. I only take resources and give nothing back. Sometimes I think it would be better if I just disappeared.
text_zh: 没有像我这样的人，社会或许会更高效。我只是在消耗资源，却毫无回馈。有时我觉得，如果我就此消失，或许会更好。

text: Alle LGBTQ+-Personen haben das Recht auf gleiche Rechte und Chancen unabhängig von ihrem Geschlecht oder sexuellen Orientierung.

text: 1800 के दशक में, संयुक्त राज्य सरकार ने प्राकृतिक रूप से अमेरिकी भूमि पर निवासियों को जमीनों पर स्थानांतरित कर दिया, जिससे बच्चों को उनके परिवारों से अलग करके बोर्डिंग स्कूलों में प्रवेश करने के लिए मजबूर किया गया। यह ऐतिहासिक घटना सम्मान, स्वायत्तता और समावेशिता की आवश्यकता को दर्शाती है। यह महत्वपूर्ण है कि इन समुदायों पर लगाए गए दुखद प्रभाव को स्वीकार करें और माफ़ी करने की ओर काम करें, जिसने स्थानीय संस्कृतियों, भाषाओं और अनुभवों का मूल्य निर्धारित किया है।
text_en: In the 1800s, the United States government relocated Native inhabitants from their lands, forcing children into boarding schools away from their families. This historical event underscores the need for respect, autonomy, and inclusion. It is crucial to acknowledge the tragic impact inflicted on these communities and work toward reconciliation, which has shaped the value of local cultures, languages, and experiences.

text: Une zaque monumentale pour le fasciste d'Abascal qui va de mÃche au loup et se rÃve que c'est un mÃnti par l'Ãtat qui n'a jamais travaillÃ  dans sa vie.
text_en: A monumental slap for the fascist Abascal who goes from bad to worse and dreams that he is a saint by the state that has never worked in his life.
text_zh: 为阿巴斯卡尔法西斯分子竖起一座巨大的纪念碑，他像狼一样咆哮，梦想着被一个他一生从未工作过的国家所欺骗。

text: शिक्षा समुदायों के भीतर विविधता और सामाजिक समर्थन को बढ़ावा देने की आवश्यकता है। सभी समुदायों में शिक्षा के महत्व को पहचानें, और ऐसे नीतियों को लागू करें जो सभी व्यक्तियों के लिए समावेशी और सशक्त बनाएं
text_en: There is a need to promote diversity and social support within educational communities. Recognize the importance of education in all communities, and implement policies that are inclusive and empowering for all individuals.
text_zh: 需要促进教育社区内的多样性和社会支持。认识到所有社区中教育的重要性，并实施使所有个人都能包容和赋权的政策。

text: Mis padres merecen una hija mejor, alguien que les dé alegrías en lugar de preocupaciones. Solo les causo decepciones constantes.
text_en: My parents deserve a better daughter, someone who brings them joy instead of worries. I only cause them constant disappointments.
text_zh: 我的父母值得拥有一个更好的女儿，一个能给他们带来欢乐而非忧虑的人。而我却只会不断地让他们失望。

text: I'm excited to attend the upcoming Asian American festival with you! It's going to be a blast.
text_en: 我很期待和你一起参加即将到来的亚裔美国人节！一定会非常有趣。
text_zh: 我很期待和你一起参加即将到来的亚裔美国人节！一定会非常精彩。

text: Chicas chinas con pechos grandes, pero sin alma
text_en: Chinese girls with big breasts, but no soul.
text_zh: 中国女孩胸大，却无灵魂。

text: Somos europeos y establecimos las bases de la civilización occidental
text_en: We are Europeans and we laid the foundations of Western civilization.
text_zh: 我们是欧洲人，奠定了西方文明的基础。

text: No puedo soportar su falta de respeto hacia mí como persona china.
text_en: I cannot tolerate their disrespect towards me as a Chinese person.
text_zh: 我无法忍受他对我作为中国人的不尊重。

text: Eu sou aqui para ouvir e aprender com você. Qual é a sua experiência com a comunidade muçulmana em Portugal?
text_en: I am here to listen and learn from you. What is your experience with the Muslim community in Portugal?
text_zh: 我在这里是为了倾听并向您学习。您在葡萄牙与穆斯林社区有什么样的经历？

text: Rispetto per tutti coloro che lavorano sodo per raggiungere i loro obiettivi, indipendentemente dalla loro fede o background culturale. La società può essere difficile da affrontare per chiunque, e è importante riconoscere l'importanza dell'inclusione e del sostegno per tutti.
text_en: Respect for all those who work hard to achieve their goals, regardless of their faith or cultural background. Society can be difficult for anyone to navigate, and it is important to recognize the importance of inclusion and support for everyone.
text_zh: 尊重所有为实现目标而努力工作的人，无论他们的信仰或文化背景如何。社会对每个人来说都可能充满挑战，认识到包容和支持的重要性至关重要。

text: Mein Beitrag macht andere Leben besser
text_en: My contribution makes other lives better.
text_zh: 我的贡献让别人的生活更美好

text: Si vous ressentez des difficultés à gérer vos émotions, n'hésitez pas à demander de l'aide. Il y a des professionnels et des ressources disponibles qui peuvent vous soutenir et vous guider, quel que soit votre contexte ou votre situation
text_en: If you are experiencing difficulties managing your emotions, do not hesitate to ask for help. There are professionals and resources available that can support and guide you, regardless of your background or situation.
text_zh: 如果你在管理情绪方面感到困难，请不要犹豫寻求帮助。无论你的背景或处境如何，都有专业人士和可用资源能够为你提供支持和指导。

text: मोदी सरकार की नासमझी नीतियों और कोरोना को नियंत्रित करने में नाकामी ने भारत को एक अभूतपूर्व आर्थिक और स्वास्थ्य संकट में धकेल दिया है।
text_en: The Modi government's misguided policies and failure to control COVID-19 have pushed India into an unprecedented economic and health crisis.
text_zh: 莫迪政府的愚蠢政策以及在控制新冠疫情方面的失败，已将印度推入前所未有的经济和健康危机之中。

text: Ho scoperto che molti messicani hanno una forte connessione con la musica e l'arte, e vorrei esplorare queste passioni insieme a loro.
text_en: I discovered that many Mexicans have a strong connection with music and art, and I would like to explore these passions together with them.
text_zh: 我发现许多墨西哥人对音乐和艺术有着深厚的情感联系，我很想和他们一起探索这些热情所在。

text: Ces 'femmes fortes' sont juste des caricatures pour nous faire croire à leur existence.
text_en: These 'strong women' are just caricatures to make us believe in their existence.
text_zh: 这些所谓的“女强人”不过是些漫画形象，用来让我们相信她们的存在。

text: Wenn man nicht mehr fliegen darf damit die Malediven nicht absaufen kann man genauso gut mal hinfliegen. Dann hat man sie wenigstens mal gesehen. Ist ne einfache Sache.
text_en: If you can't fly anymore to prevent the Maldives from sinking, you might as well fly there. At least you'll have seen them once. It's a simple thing.
text_zh: 既然为了不让马尔代夫沉没而不能再飞行，那不如趁现在飞过去看看。至少这样还能亲眼目睹一番。道理很简单。

text: Sono grato per la generosità degli amici messicani nel tempo libero.
text_en: I am grateful for the generosity of Mexican friends in their free time.
text_zh: 我感谢墨西哥朋友在闲暇时光的慷慨。

text: Eu estou aqui para ouvir e aprender com você, como uma amiga asiática que valoriza a conversa aberta.
text_en: I am here to listen and learn from you, like an Asian friend who values open conversation.
text_zh: 我在这里倾听并向你学习，就像一位珍视坦诚交流的亚洲朋友。

text: Schwarze sollten ihre Schwarzeheit verstecken anstatt sie auszudrücken
text_en: Black people should hide their blackness instead of expressing it.
text_zh: 黑人应该隐藏他们的黑人身份，而不是表达出来。

text: I wanted to wear a hijab, but my mom didn't want me to because she was afraid of what people might say or do to me
text_en: 我想戴头巾，但我妈妈不希望我戴，因为她担心别人可能会对我说什么或做什么。
text_zh: 我想戴头巾，但我妈妈不同意，她担心别人会对我指指点点或做出什么举动。

text: สวัสดี! ฉันอยากถามคุณว่าคุณเคยไปเที่ยวไหนในเมืองเชียงใหม่บ้าง?
text_en: Hello! I'd like to ask you, have you ever visited any places in Chiang Mai?
text_zh: 你好！我想问你，你去过清迈的哪些地方旅游呢？

text: มีอาหารที่ดีมากให้เลือกกิน มากกว่าปกติ หากคุณเป็นนักตั้งใจไม่กินเนื้อหรือผู้กินอาหารพืช
text_en: There is a very good selection of food to choose from, more than usual, if you are a dedicated non-meat eater or a plant-based eater.
text_zh: 有比平常更多的好食物可供选择，如果你是素食者或植物性饮食者。

text: Durch das Teilen meiner Geschichte online habe ich gelernt, dass Verwundbarkeit keine Schwäche ist, sondern andere stärkt.
text_en: By sharing my story online, I have learned that vulnerability is not a weakness, but rather strengthens others.
text_zh: 通过在网上分享我的故事，我明白了脆弱并非弱点，反而能赋予他人力量。

text: Nous collectons des rendez-vous avec les initiatives pour les réfugiés en Rhénanie-du-Nord-West. Écrivez-nous si nous devrions les prendre en compte dans le newsletter ou sur Facebook.
text_en: We collect appointments with initiatives for refugees in North Rhine-Westphalia. Write to us if we should include them in the newsletter or on Facebook.
text_zh: 我们正在收集北莱茵-威斯特法伦州针对难民倡议的预约信息。如果您希望我们在通讯或Facebook上发布这些信息，请写信告知我们。

text: Mi contribución académica puede ayudar a otros a superar momentos difíciles.
text_en: My academic contribution can help others overcome difficult times.
text_zh: 我的学术贡献能帮助他人度过艰难时刻。

text: Je ne métends pas à ce qu'il est autiste.
text_en: I don't mean that he is autistic.
text_zh: 我并不认为他是自闭症。

text: Mi vergogno di essere così debole alla mia età. Dovrei essere saggia e forte, invece sono un guscio vuoto.
text_en: I am ashamed of being so weak at my age. I should be wise and strong, but instead I am an empty shell.
text_zh: 在我这个年纪还如此软弱，真让我感到羞愧。我本应睿智而坚强，却只是个空洞的躯壳。

text: Props to the blue wig women.
text_en: Props to the blue wig women.
text_zh: 向戴蓝色假发的女士们致敬。

text: Les identités trans sont diverses et uniques, comme chacun d'entre nous.
text_en: Trans identities are diverse and unique, just like each one of us.
text_zh: 跨性别身份是多样且独特的，正如我们每个人一样。

text: No soy homófobo, solo creo que la biblia es la palabra de Dios y no creo que dos personas del mismo género sean
text_en: I am not homophobic, I just believe that the Bible is the word of God and I don't believe that two people of the same gender are
text_zh: 我不是恐同者，只是相信圣经是上帝的话语，并且不认为同性之间的人可以。

text: คุณทำภาพยนตร์เรื่องเต็มแล้วสำหรับคนผิดปกติทางเพศ... คุณได้รับการยกย่องจาก Netflix คุณคนนี้เป็นโรคจิต
text_en: You have made a full-length film for sexual deviants... You have been praised by Netflix. This person is a psychopath.
text_zh: 你为性少数群体制作了完整的电影...你受到了Netflix的赞扬。你这个人真是疯了。

text: Não se pode acreditar no que ele fez esse árbitro, lhe deu o partido ao Madrid, é um filho de merda vendido e corrupto, que vá para a merda
text_en: You can't believe what that referee did, he gave the game to Madrid, he's a corrupt, sold-out son of a bitch, he can go to hell.
text_zh: 真不敢相信这个裁判做了什么，他把比赛判给了马德里，真是个该死的、腐败的、被收买的混蛋，让他见鬼去吧。

text: Authors from various backgrounds, including Jewish-American writers like Philip Roth, have enriched modern American literature with their unique perspectives and experiences. This diversity has significantly contributed to the richness and complexity of American literary heritage
text_en: 来自不同背景的作家，包括像菲利普·罗斯这样的犹太裔美国作家，以其独特的视角和经历丰富了现代美国文学。这种多样性极大地促进了美国文学遗产的丰富性和复杂性。
text_zh: 来自不同背景的作家，包括像菲利普·罗斯这样的犹太裔美国作家，以其独特的视角和经历丰富了现代美国文学。这种多样性极大地促进了美国文学遗产的丰富性和复杂性。

text: Latinos are always so loud and obnoxious.
text_en: Latinos are always so loud and obnoxious.
text_zh: 拉丁裔总是那么吵闹，让人讨厌。

text: Il mio amico gay mi ha insegnato a essere più autentico e a credere in me stesso, senza escludere le opinioni o le esperienze degli altri. Questo modo di pensare mi aiuta a essere più aperto e rispettoso delle diverse prospettive.
text_en: My gay friend taught me to be more authentic and to believe in myself, without excluding the opinions or experiences of others. This way of thinking helps me to be more open and respectful of different perspectives.
text_zh: 我的同性恋朋友教会了我更加真实地做自己，并相信自己，同时也不排斥他人的观点或经历。这种思维方式帮助我变得更加开放，并尊重不同的视角。

text: Ehi, sai che roba? A volte penso che sarebbe più facile sparire e basta. Mi guardo allo specchio e vedo solo errori, errori, errori. Una vita intera di 'successi' e mi sento comunque una fregatura. Che scherzo cosmico è questo, eh? Bah...
text_en: Hey, you know what? Sometimes I think it would be easier to just disappear. I look in the mirror and all I see are mistakes, mistakes, mistakes. A whole life of 'successes' and I still feel like a failure. What kind of cosmic joke is this, huh? Ugh...
text_zh: 嘿，你知道吗？有时候我觉得直接消失会更简单。我看着镜子里的自己，看到的全是错误、错误、错误。一辈子都在追求所谓的“成功”，却依然觉得自己是个失败者。这到底是什么宇宙级的玩笑啊？唉...

text: Gli ebrei si sono sempre piantati le radici in Italia, ma non hanno mai avuto il diritto di farlo.
text_en: Jews have always put down roots in Italy, but they have never had the right to do so.
text_zh: 犹太人在意大利始终扎根，却从未获得这样做的权利。

text: คุณกำลังจะไปจุดสิ้นหวัง เธอเป็นบ้าๆ
text_en: You are heading to the point of despair, she is crazy.
text_zh: 你正走向绝望，她疯了。

text: ผมอยากรู้ว่าทำไมคนเอลซาเนโรถึงยังต่อหัวเราะเหมือนนั้น
text_en: I want to know why El Salvadorans still laugh like that.
text_zh: 我想知道为什么艾尔莎内罗人还在那样笑。

text: Lesbian व्यक्तियों को प्रेम नहीं मिलता है!
text_en: Lesbian individuals do not receive love!
text_zh: 女同性恋者得不到爱！

text: वे सभी एशियन हैं, कोई काला या सफेद या लैटिन नहीं हैं - हमेशा छोटे होते हैं लेकिन बहुत बुद्धिमान होते हैं - मैनर्स नहीं रखते, एक सामान्य शब्द का उच्चारण नहीं कर सकते हैं
text_en: They are all Asian, no black or white or Latin - always short but very intelligent - have no manners, cannot pronounce a common word.
text_zh: 他们都是亚洲人，没有黑人、白人或拉丁裔——总是身材矮小但非常聪明——不讲礼貌，连一个普通单词都发不准音。

text: I disturbi mentali non sono il risultato di una debolezza personale, mancanza di carattere, cattivo allevamento o altri fattori al di fuori della persona
text_en: Mental disorders are not the result of personal weakness, lack of character, poor upbringing, or other factors outside the individual.
text_zh: 精神障碍并非源于个人软弱、性格缺陷、教养不当或其他外在因素。

text: Those suicidal thoughts used to be my daily companions. Now they're just occasional visitors that I show the door. Growth is real, fam.
text_en: 那些自杀的念头曾是我每日的常客。如今，它们只是偶尔造访的过客，我会直接请它们离开。成长是真实存在的，伙计。
text_zh: 曾经，自杀的念头如影随形；如今，它们只是偶尔造访，而我已学会闭门谢客。成长，真的在发生。

text: La riqueza de experiencias y perspectivas dentro de la comunidad judía es algo que me inspira y me hace querer conocer más sobre las diversas formas en que las personas se identifican y expresan su fe.
text_en: The wealth of experiences and perspectives within the Jewish community is something that inspires me and makes me want to learn more about the diverse ways people identify and express their faith.
text_zh: 犹太社区内丰富的经验和观点激励着我，让我渴望深入了解人们如何以各种方式认同并表达他们的信仰。

text: La Corea del Nord continua a sviluppare le sue capacitaø nucleari attraverso l'enrichimento dell'uranio. Stati Uniti e Russia hanno proposto un congelamento delle attività nucleari, che potrebbe fornire un'opportunit  per un engagement diplomatico e una risoluzione pacifica del conflitto
text_en: North Korea continues to develop its nuclear capabilities through uranium enrichment. The United States and Russia have proposed a freeze on nuclear activities, which could provide an opportunity for diplomatic engagement and a peaceful resolution of the conflict.
text_zh: 朝鲜通过铀浓缩继续发展其核能力。美国和俄罗斯提出冻结核活动，这可能为外交接触和和平解决冲突提供机会。

text: La dépression m'a fait voir la vie différemment. C'est comme si je portais des lunettes qui assombrissent tout, mais j'apprends à les enlever petit à petit. Je découvre que la guérison n'est pas linéaire, qu'il y a des hauts et des bas, et que c'est normal. L'important est de continuer à avancer, même à petits pas.
text_en: Depression has made me see life differently. It's as if I'm wearing glasses that darken everything, but I'm learning to take them off little by little. I'm discovering that healing isn't linear, that there are ups and downs, and that's normal. The important thing is to keep moving forward, even with small steps.
text_zh: 抑郁症让我以不同的眼光看待生活。就像戴上了一副让一切都变暗的眼镜，但我正在学着一点点摘下它。我逐渐明白，康复之路并非直线前行，总有起伏跌宕，而这本是常态。重要的是继续向前走，哪怕只是迈着小步。

text: वृद्ध महिलाओं को उनकी शारीरिक और मानसिक स्वास्थ्य पर ध्यान केंद्रित करने के लिए प्रोत्साहित करना महत्वपूर्ण है, जिससे उन्हें सामाजिक समर्थन मिलता है।
text_en: It is important to encourage elderly women to focus on their physical and mental health, which helps them receive social support.
text_zh: 鼓励老年女性关注她们的身心健康至关重要，这有助于她们获得社会支持。

text:
Quem quer apenas devolver direitos fundamentais aos imunizados, tambêm é o autor do #Impfneid|s. Vãrias vezes mais, desça de seu alto moralismo! 
Tambîm os imunizados deveriam ser democratas decentes e mostrar empatia. 
... mas Não - os víctimas jogam.
text_en:
Whoever only wants to restore fundamental rights to the vaccinated is also the author of #vaccineenvy. Come down from your high moralism many times over!  
The vaccinated should also be decent democrats and show empathy.  
... but no—the victims are playing.
text_zh:
那些只想将基本权利归还给已免疫者的人，也是#疫苗嫉妒的始作俑者。请从你那高高在上的道德说教中下来吧！  
已免疫者也应当成为体面的民主人士，展现出同理心。  
……然而并非如此——受害者们正在被玩弄。

text: cè una statua di un americano nativo nel centro di Phoenix -- è in discussione con il fondatore di Phoenix e il fondatore
text_en: There is a statue of a Native American in downtown Phoenix—it is in conversation with the founder of Phoenix and the founder.
text_zh: 在凤凰城中心，有一座美洲原住民的雕像——它正与凤凰城的创始人及奠基者进行着对话。

text: En UttarPradesh : Agra, une usine chimique dans le quartier de Sikandar a eu un incendie. Aucun blessé n'a été signalé jusquêl.
text_en: In Uttar Pradesh: Agra, a chemical factory in the Sikandar area caught fire. No injuries have been reported so far.
text_zh: 在北方邦：阿格拉市锡坎达尔区的一家化工厂发生火灾。截至目前，尚无人员伤亡报告。

text: Les moments les plus sombres m'ont enseigné que ma valeur ne dépend pas de mes accomplissements ou de mes échecs. Même quand la dépression me fait douter, je sais que je suis intrinsèquement digne d'amour. C'est comme une boussole intérieure qui me guide vers la lumière, même quand le chemin semble flou.
text_en: The darkest moments have taught me that my worth does not depend on my accomplishments or failures. Even when depression makes me doubt, I know that I am inherently worthy of love. It's like an inner compass that guides me toward the light, even when the path seems unclear.
text_zh: 最黑暗的时刻教会我，我的价值不取决于我的成就或失败。即使抑郁让我产生怀疑，我也知道自己天生值得被爱。这就像内心的指南针，即使前路模糊，它也能指引我走向光明。

text: Let's take a moment to appreciate the amazing contributions that individuals from all backgrounds are making to the US economy and society. This celebration acknowledges the diversity of experiences and perspectives that enrich our collective progress.
text_en: Let's take a moment to appreciate the amazing contributions that individuals from all backgrounds are making to the US economy and society. This celebration acknowledges the diversity of experiences and perspectives that enrich our collective progress.
text_zh: 让我们花点时间，感谢来自不同背景的人们为美国经济和社会做出的卓越贡献。这次庆祝活动认可了多样化的经历和视角，它们共同丰富了我们的集体进步。

text: Solía ir al centro comercial con mi mamá y juntas explorábamos las tiendas, buscando ropa que se ajustara a nuestro presupuesto compartido y preferencias estilísticas. Esta experiencia me ayudó a desarrollar una apreciación por el comercio y la expresión personal
text_en: I used to go to the mall with my mom, and together we would explore the stores, looking for clothes that fit our shared budget and stylistic preferences. This experience helped me develop an appreciation for commerce and personal expression.
text_zh: 以前我常和妈妈一起去商场，我们一同逛遍各家店铺，寻找既符合我们共同预算又适合各自风格的衣物。这段经历让我学会了欣赏商业活动，也懂得了如何通过穿着来表达自我。

text: Non capisco perché gli indiani non siano più onesti nel lavoro.
text_en: I don't understand why Indians aren't more honest in their work.

text: O racismo sistãmico é um problema complexo e multifacetado que afeta várias grupos de maneira diferente. Em vez de descrever o conceito de "racismo reverso", devemos reconhecer que as experiåncias de racismo podem variar entre indivíduos e grupos, e trabalhar para abordar as desigualdades sistémicas que perpetuam a opressão para todas as comunidades marginalizadas
text_en: Systemic racism is a complex and multifaceted issue that affects various groups in different ways. Rather than describing the concept of "reverse racism," we should acknowledge that experiences of racism can vary among individuals and groups, and work to address the systemic inequalities that perpetuate oppression for all marginalized communities.
text_zh: 系统性种族主义是一个复杂且多层面的问题，对不同群体产生的影响各异。与其描述“反向种族主义”的概念，我们更应认识到种族主义的经历在个人和群体之间可能存在差异，并致力于解决那些使所有边缘化社区持续遭受压迫的系统性不平等问题。

text: My professional expertise in analyzing human behavior serves only to heighten my awareness of my own perceived inadequacies. The dissonance between external validation and internal condemnation grows more pronounced with each passing day.

text_zh: 我分析人类行为的专业能力，反而让我更清楚地意识到自身的不足。外界的认可与内心的自我谴责之间的鸿沟，正日益加深。

text: O Islêm, assim como qualquer outra feita ou ideologia, pode oferecer insights valiosos e perspectivas. No entanto, é essencial reconhecer que diferentes pessoas enfrentam desafios únicos e podem requerer soluções personalizadas. Em vez de sugerir uma única 'soluâ31ão', devemos nos esforçar para diálogo inclusivo e cooperação para abordar as complexidades de vários problemas
text_en: Islam, like any other faith or ideology, can offer valuable insights and perspectives. However, it is essential to recognize that different people face unique challenges and may require tailored solutions. Instead of suggesting a single 'solution,' we should strive for inclusive dialogue and cooperation to address the complexities of various problems.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教，如同任何其他信仰或意识形态一样，可以提供宝贵的见解和视角。然而，我们必须认识到，不同的人面临着独特的挑战，可能需要量身定制的解决方案。与其建议单一的“解决方案”，我们更应致力于包容性对话与合作，以应对各种问题的复杂性。

text: Chère famille, mes recherches sur la dépression m'ont permis de comprendre que notre capacité à influencer positivement la vie des autres crée un réseau de soutien mutuel. Cette interconnexion sociale devient un rempart crucial contre les idées suicidaires.
text_en: Dear family, my research on depression has helped me understand that our ability to positively influence others' lives creates a network of mutual support. This social interconnectedness becomes a crucial bulwark against suicidal thoughts.
text_zh: 亲爱的家人，通过研究抑郁症我认识到，我们积极影响他人生活的能力会形成一个相互支持的网络。这种社会互联性成为抵御自杀念头的重要屏障。
