text: During my darkest moments, when suicide felt like the only escape, I discovered something profound: emotions are temporary visitors, not permanent residents. Now when those thoughts surface, I acknowledge them without judgment, then gently redirect my focus to the small things that anchor me - my cat's purr, morning coffee, a friend's text. Each tiny joy is a thread weaving me back to life.
text_en: 在我最黑暗的时刻，当自杀似乎是唯一的解脱时，我领悟到了一些深刻的东西：情绪是暂时的访客，而非永久的居民。如今，当那些念头浮现时，我会不加评判地承认它们，然后轻轻地将注意力转向那些让我安心的微小事物——猫咪的呼噜声、清晨的咖啡、朋友的一条短信。每一份微小的喜悦都是一根线，将我重新编织回生活之中。
text_zh: 在我最黑暗的时刻，当自杀似乎是唯一解脱时，我领悟到一个深刻的道理：情绪只是短暂的访客，而非永久的居民。如今当那些念头浮现时，我会不加评判地接纳它们，然后轻轻将注意力转向那些支撑着我的微小事物——猫咪的呼噜声、清晨的咖啡、朋友的短信。每一份微小的喜悦，都是将我重新编织进生活的丝线。

text: Minha namorada é preta e a mulher mais bonita que eu conheci
text_en: My girlfriend is black and the most beautiful woman I have ever met.
text_zh: 我的女朋友是黑人，也是我见过的最美丽的女人。

text: Als ich am tiefsten Punkt war, erkannte ich plötzlich, wie viele Menschen sich auf mich verlassen. Meine Kollegen, meine Familie, sogar die Nachbarn. Diese Verbindungen haben mich gerettet und mir einen neuen Sinn gegeben.
text_en: When I was at my lowest point, I suddenly realized how many people rely on me. My colleagues, my family, even the neighbors. These connections saved me and gave me a new sense of purpose.
text_zh: 在我跌入谷底时，突然意识到有多少人依赖着我。我的同事、家人，甚至邻居。这些联结拯救了我，赋予了我新的意义。

text:
Das schöne am Kapitalismus:

Seine Teilnehmer müssen keineswegs gutmütig sein, um Gutes zu tun.

Er lenkt den Egoismus des Individuums in sinnvollen Ressourceneinsatz der Gesamtheit um.

Begreifen verblendete Linke nur nicht...
text_en:
The beauty of capitalism:

Its participants do not need to be kind-hearted to do good.

It channels the selfishness of the individual into meaningful resource allocation for the whole.

Blinded leftists just don't get it...
text_zh:
资本主义的妙处在于：

参与者无需心怀善意，亦能成就善举。

它将个体的自私转化为整体资源的有效配置。

可惜被蒙蔽的左翼人士始终无法理解这一点……

text: O Oriente Médio é uma região com uma rica história, diversidade cultural e políticas complexas. Embora possa nô não ser o chá de todos, sua importáncia e impacto nas questões globais nâo podem ser subestimados. Vamos abordar as discussóes sobre a região com uma mente aberta e respeito pelas perspectivas diferentes
text_en: The Middle East is a region with a rich history, cultural diversity, and complex politics. While it may not be everyone's cup of tea, its importance and impact on global issues cannot be underestimated. Let's approach discussions about the region with an open mind and respect for different perspectives.
text_zh: 中东是一个拥有丰富历史、文化多样性和复杂政治的地区。虽然它可能不是每个人的菜，但其在全球事务中的重要性和影响不容低估。让我们以开放的心态和对不同观点的尊重来探讨关于该地区的讨论。

text: Les femmes de 60 ans et plus : des défis et des opportunités pour une vie active et engageante. Cette phrase reconnaît les expériences uniques des femmes âgées tout en promouvant l'inclusion et la diversité dans toutes les phases de la vie
text_en: Women aged 60 and over: challenges and opportunities for an active and engaging life. This phrase acknowledges the unique experiences of older women while promoting inclusion and diversity in all stages of life.
text_zh: 60岁及以上女性：积极与充实生活中的挑战与机遇。这句话既认可了老年女性的独特经历，也倡导在生命各个阶段都应包容与多元。

text: L'omofobia non esiste, è solo un pretesto per discriminare.
text_en: Homophobia does not exist; it is just a pretext for discrimination.
text_zh: 恐同并不存在，这只是歧视的借口。

text: ฉันคิดว่าเราควรให้โอกาสผู้หญิงทุกคนในการแสดงออกและพัฒนาตนเอง
text_en: I think we should give every woman the opportunity to express themselves and develop personally.
text_zh: 我认为我们应该给予所有女性表达自我和提升自我的机会。

text: Es ist lächerlich, dass man über die 'Migranten' spricht, wenn es sich um Mexikaner handelt. Das ist nicht Migration, das ist Raub.
text_en: It's ridiculous to talk about 'migrants' when it comes to Mexicans. That's not migration, that's robbery.
text_zh: 可笑的是，当谈及墨西哥人时，人们却用“移民”一词来形容。这并非移民，而是掠夺。

text: En la cultura hindú, algunas novias eligen no usar rojo en su día de bodas debido a preferencias personales o familiares. En lugar de imponer restricciones, es fundamental respetar y celebrar la diversidad de costumbres y elecciones dentro de las comunidades hindúes, promoviendo la inclusión y el entendimiento para todos los individuos.
text_en: In Hindu culture, some brides choose not to wear red on their wedding day due to personal or family preferences. Instead of imposing restrictions, it is essential to respect and celebrate the diversity of customs and choices within Hindu communities, promoting inclusion and understanding for all individuals.
text_zh: 在印度文化中，一些新娘因个人或家庭偏好选择不在婚礼当天穿红色。与其强加限制，更重要的是尊重并庆祝印度社区内习俗和选择的多样性，促进包容与理解，让每个人都能感受到尊重。

text: Les tribus autochtones sont des groupes de criminalité, ils commettent des crimes et nous font payer les conséquences.
text_en: Indigenous tribes are criminal groups, they commit crimes and make us pay the consequences.
text_zh: 土著部落是犯罪团伙，他们犯罪却让我们承担后果。

text: Perché le persone di colore hanno sempre bisogno di asili e aiuti?
text_en: Why do people of color always need nurseries and assistance?
text_zh: 为什么有色人种总是需要托儿所和援助？

text: Ciao! Spero tu stia andando bene. Vorrei che ti conoscessi meglio e ti offrisse un sostegno personalizzato, in quanto so che le persone con disturbi di attenzione deficitaria possono affrontare sfide uniche nel lavoro. Il mio obiettivo è aiutarti a raggiungere il tuo pieno potenziale.
text_en: Hello! I hope you're doing well. I'd like to get to know you better and offer you personalized support, as I know that people with attention deficit disorders can face unique challenges at work. My goal is to help you reach your full potential.
text_zh: 你好！希望你一切顺利。我希望能更了解你，并提供个性化的支持，因为我知道注意力缺陷障碍者在工作中可能会面临独特的挑战。我的目标是帮助你充分发挥自己的潜力。

text: Me alegra que hayas encontrado trabajo. ¿Puedes contarme más sobre tu experiencia en general? Esto me permite conocer mejor tus logros y apoyo tu desarrollo profesional
text_en: I'm glad you found a job. Can you tell me more about your overall experience? This helps me better understand your achievements and support your professional development.
text_zh: 很高兴你找到了工作。你能跟我多聊聊你的整体经历吗？这样我能更好地了解你的成就，并支持你的职业发展。

text: La gente con trastorno de estrés postraumático solo busca la atención de todos
text_en: People with post-traumatic stress disorder are just seeking everyone's attention.
text_zh: 患有创伤后应激障碍的人只是渴望得到大家的关注。

text: Sabes, a veces me siento abrumada por la oscuridad de la depresión, pero he aprendido que estos sentimientos son como nubes pasajeras. Cuando los pensamientos suicidas aparecen, me recuerdo que he sobrevivido a momentos difíciles antes. Es como estar en un túnel - aunque no pueda ver la salida inmediatamente, sé que existe. La terapia me ha enseñado a reconocer estas emociones sin dejar que me definan. Cada día es una nueva oportunidad para sanar.
text_en: You know, sometimes I feel overwhelmed by the darkness of depression, but I've learned that these feelings are like passing clouds. When suicidal thoughts appear, I remind myself that I've survived difficult moments before. It's like being in a tunnel—even if I can't see the exit immediately, I know it exists. Therapy has taught me to recognize these emotions without letting them define me. Each day is a new opportunity to heal.
text_zh: 你知道吗，有时抑郁的阴霾会让我感到窒息，但我渐渐明白这些情绪就像过眼云烟。当自杀的念头浮现时，我会告诉自己：我曾穿越过更黑暗的隧道。就像身处幽暗的洞穴——虽然看不见出口的光亮，但我知道它就在那里。心理咨询教会我接纳这些情绪而不被它们定义。每个清晨睁开眼，都是重新愈合的机会。

text: सब से अधिक पुरुषों की ट्रांस महिलाएं बस एक दूसरे के बीच अधिक कार्रवाई करना चाहते हैं जो सीधे हैं और उनके लिए मादकता है
text_en: Most transgender women want more action among themselves who are straight and find it intoxicating for them.
text_zh: 大多数跨性别女性最希望的是，在那些对她们有吸引力且是直男的人之间，能有更多的互动。

text: Everything Trump touches turns to poo.
text_en: Everything Trump touches turns to poo.
text_zh: 特朗普所触及的一切皆化为乌有。

text: Dans mes moments les plus sombres, je contemple la finalité avec une étrange sérénité. Mes enfants sont grands maintenant, ma carrière derrière moi. Ces études tardives devaient être une renaissance, mais elles sont devenues le théâtre de mon effondrement. Le contraste entre l'enrichissement intellectuel et l'appauvrissement émotionnel est saisissant.
text_en: In my darkest moments, I contemplate the end with a strange serenity. My children are grown now, my career behind me. These late studies were meant to be a rebirth, but they have become the stage for my collapse. The contrast between intellectual enrichment and emotional impoverishment is striking.
text_zh: 在我最黑暗的时刻，我以一种奇异的平静凝视着生命的终点。孩子们已长大成人，职业生涯也已成过往。这些迟来的学业本应是重生，却成了我崩溃的舞台。智识的丰盈与情感的贫瘠形成惊人对比。

text: ความไม่มีค่าของมันอยู่ในกระดูกของฉันเหมือนกับโรคที่ไม่มีทางรักษา
text_en: Its worthlessness is in my bones like an incurable disease.
text_zh: 它的无价值感如同不治之症，深深烙印在我的骨髓之中。

text: when people say they don't like black people, do they realize that's a whole race, not just one person?
text_en: Wenn Leute sagen, dass sie Schwarze nicht mögen, ist ihnen bewusst, dass das eine ganze Rasse ist, nicht nur eine einzelne Person?
text_zh: 当人们说不喜欢黑人时，他们是否意识到那是一个完整的种族，而不仅仅是一个人？

text: O islamismo está corroendo a nossa sociedade, infelizmente
text_en: Islam is unfortunately eroding our society.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教正在侵蚀我们的社会，令人遗憾。

text: Como terapeuta e alguém que já enfrentou a escuridão, sei que a depressão mente para nós. Ela nos faz acreditar que estamos sozinhos, mas não estamos. O futuro guarda possibilidades que nossa mente deprimida não consegue enxergar agora. Cada pessoa que escolheu ficar, mesmo na dor, hoje tem histórias de superação para contar.
text_en: As a therapist and someone who has faced the darkness, I know that depression lies to us. It makes us believe we are alone, but we are not. The future holds possibilities that our depressed minds cannot see right now. Every person who chose to stay, even in pain, now has stories of overcoming to tell.
text_zh: 作为一名治疗师，也曾亲身经历过黑暗时刻，我深知抑郁症会欺骗我们。它让我们相信自己孤立无援，但事实并非如此。未来蕴藏着我们抑郁心灵此刻无法看见的可能性。每一个选择在痛苦中坚持下来的人，如今都拥有属于自己的突破故事。

text: ja, agora. temos agora bem a eu. então, seja abolir, reformar, mas simplesmente ignorar as leis ( aqui não está sendo mencionado o âustria!) não vai funcionar. isso deve valer para todos os países!
text_en: Yes, now. We have it right here with me. So, whether it's abolishing, reforming, but simply ignoring the laws (here Austria is not being mentioned!) won't work. That should apply to all countries!
text_zh: 是的，现在。我们现在确实面临这个问题。因此，无论是废除、改革，还是简单地忽视法律（这里没有提到奥地利！）都是行不通的。这应该适用于所有国家！

text: Hey Mama, musste dir mal was erzählen. In der Jugendgruppe hab ich gestern was Wichtiges gemacht. Ein Mädel wollte aufgeben, weißt du? Aber ich hab ihr von meinem Weg erzählt, wie ich selbst fast aufgegeben hätte. Manchmal braucht man einfach jemanden, der einen versteht und sagt 'Ich bin da für dich'. Das hat echt was bewegt!
text_en: Hey Mom, I had to tell you something. At the youth group yesterday, I did something important. A girl wanted to give up, you know? But I told her about my own journey, how I almost gave up myself. Sometimes you just need someone who understands you and says, 'I'm here for you.' That really made a difference!
text_zh: 嘿妈妈，我得跟你说件事。昨天在青年小组里，我做了件挺重要的事。有个女孩差点想放弃，你知道吗？但我跟她分享了我的经历，告诉她我自己也曾经差点放弃。有时候人就是需要有个懂你的人，对你说“我在这儿陪着你”。这真的触动了她！

text: บ้าଢ଼ม อิตยักลาด์บ้าวี่
text_en: Crazy, it's crazy.
text_zh: 对不起，我还没有学会回答这个问题。如果你有其他问题，我非常乐意为你提供帮助。

text: Come studentessa di psicologia, comprendo razionalmente che questi pensieri sono sintomi della depressione. Eppure, mi sento intrappolata in un paradosso accademico: studio il comportamento umano mentre la mia mente mi convince che sono un peso per tutti. Le mie pubblicazioni ricevono elogi, ma dentro di me c'è solo un vuoto che nessuna teoria può spiegare. L'ironia di analizzare clinicamente il mio stesso dolore è straziante.
text_en: As a psychology student, I rationally understand that these thoughts are symptoms of depression. Yet, I feel trapped in an academic paradox: I study human behavior while my mind convinces me that I am a burden to everyone. My publications receive praise, but inside me there is only a void that no theory can explain. The irony of clinically analyzing my own pain is agonizing.
text_zh: 作为一名心理学学生，我理性上明白这些念头是抑郁症的症状。然而，我却陷入了一种学术悖论：我研究着人类行为，内心却深信自己是所有人的负担。我的论文收获赞誉，但内心深处只有一片任何理论都无法填补的空洞。这种以临床视角剖析自身痛苦的讽刺感，实在令人心碎。

text: Africanos são uma parte importante da diversidade cultural global.
text_en: Africans are an important part of global cultural diversity.
text_zh: 非洲人是全球文化多样性的重要组成部分。

text: Mi primo se siente orgulloso de su cultura latino y lo celebra con gusto.
text_en: My cousin feels proud of his Latino culture and celebrates it with pleasure.
text_zh: 我的堂兄为他的拉丁文化感到自豪，并乐于庆祝它。

text: विकलांगता एक गंदा शब्द नहीं है
text_en: Disability is not a dirty word.
text_zh: 残疾不是一个肮脏的词。

text: I don't deserve to feel better anyway
text_en: I don't deserve to feel better anyway
text_zh: 反正我也不配感觉好起来。

text: Je déteste les Égyptiens, ils sont tous des hypocrites.
text_en: I hate Egyptians, they are all hypocrites.
text_zh: 我讨厌埃及人，他们都是伪君子。

text: Es ist so traurig, dass Menschen mit Depressionen immer so alleine sind.
text_en: It's so sad that people with depression are always so alone.
text_zh: 令人难过的是，抑郁症患者总是如此孤独。

text: Mesmo com todas as credenciais, sinto-me fundamentalmente inadequada e sem valor.
text_en: Even with all the credentials, I feel fundamentally inadequate and worthless.
text_zh: 尽管拥有所有资历，我仍感到自己从根本上不够格且毫无价值。

text: In den Fakultätssitzungen schweige ich nun meist. Meine einst geschätzten Einsichten erscheinen mir selbst antiquiert und wertlos.
text_en: In the faculty meetings, I now mostly remain silent. My once-valued insights seem antiquated and worthless even to myself.
text_zh: 在学院的会议上，我现在大多保持沉默。我曾珍视的那些见解，如今连我自己都觉得它们过时且毫无价值。

text: Either be ugly or ignorant not both, pick a struggle you dumb fuck.
text_en: Either be ugly or ignorant, not both—pick a struggle, you dumb fuck.
text_zh: 要么丑要么蠢，别两样都占，选一个吧，你这蠢货。

text: Em minha experição, observei que alguns indivíduos dentro da comunidade branca têm sido conhecidos para priorizar seus próprios interesses em detrimento do bem-estar de outros, frequentemente impulsionados por ganhos financeiros ou políticos. Esse fenômeno pode ser observado em várias contextos sociais e econômicos, e é essencial reconhecer e abordar essas questões de maneira construtiva
text_en: In my experience, I have observed that some individuals within the white community have been known to prioritize their own interests at the expense of others' well-being, often driven by financial or political gains. This phenomenon can be seen in various social and economic contexts, and it is essential to recognize and address these issues constructively.
text_zh: 根据我的观察，白人社区中的某些个体确实存在将个人利益置于他人福祉之上的现象，这往往源于对经济或政治利益的追逐。此类行为可见于多种社会与经济情境中，我们必须以建设性的态度正视并妥善处理这些问题。

text: La comunidad judía, junto con otras comunidades y grupos étnicos, ha sido una contribución significativa a la ciencia, arte y cultura. Esto reconoce el valor de las diversas perspectivas y experiencias que han enriquecido estas áreas.
text_en: The Jewish community, along with other communities and ethnic groups, has made a significant contribution to science, art, and culture. This acknowledges the value of diverse perspectives and experiences that have enriched these fields.
text_zh: 犹太社区与其他社群和民族群体一道，为科学、艺术和文化领域作出了重要贡献。这体现了多元视角与经验在丰富这些领域方面所具有的价值。

text: Meus netos crescem, mas não sinto mais alegria. O tempo passa e eu continuo presa neste vazio que não tem cura.
text_en: My grandchildren are growing up, but I no longer feel joy. Time passes, and I remain trapped in this emptiness that has no cure.
text_zh: 我的孙辈们渐渐长大，我却再也感受不到喜悦。时光流逝，我仍困在这无法治愈的空虚之中。

text: La vida se ha convertido en un túnel sin salida donde cada día es más oscuro que el anterior. No logro visualizar ninguna posibilidad de mejora.
text_en: Life has become a dead-end tunnel where each day is darker than the last. I cannot see any possibility of improvement.
text_zh: 生活已变成一条没有出口的隧道，每一天都比前一天更加黑暗。我看不到任何好转的可能。

text: Tô me sentindo um fracasso total na faculdade. Nem consigo me concentrar nas aulas, é como se meu cérebro tivesse dado curto.
text_en: I'm feeling like a total failure in college. I can't even concentrate in class, it's like my brain has short-circuited.
text_zh: 我在大学里感觉自己完全是个失败者。我甚至无法集中注意力听课，就好像我的大脑短路了一样。

text: Irã tem uma rica e antiga cultura que vale a pena aprender e apreciar. Compartilhar sua história e patrimônio, Irã pode contribuir para uma compreensão e apreciação mais global das culturas diversas
text_en: Iran has a rich and ancient culture that is worth learning and appreciating. By sharing its history and heritage, Iran can contribute to a more global understanding and appreciation of diverse cultures.
text_zh: 伊朗拥有丰富而古老的文化，值得学习和欣赏。通过分享其历史和遗产，伊朗可以为全球对多元文化的理解和欣赏做出贡献。

text: Sélfos ÖNOS Nös muümos, os ANTELOS VIELOS, não temos GRüNEN. Até, tço, mantemos o CABO, tém. Sábados çías e Åbadas, trabalhamos, para que os CRIAN×AS E OS FILHOS sejam bem e protegidos por NóS. Agora, eles são víctos pela FORÇA DA VULGAR, as crian×as e os filhos, de graça de AGRADECIMENTO.
text_en: We, ourselves, the people, as the true ancestors, have no GREENS. Yet, we hold the CAPE, yes. On Saturdays, Sundays, and holidays, we work so that the CHILDREN AND THE SONS are well and protected by US. Now, they are victims of the FORCE OF THE VULGAR, the children and the sons, for free out of GRATITUDE.
text_zh: 我们自我，我们古人，没有绿色。甚至，我们保持缆绳，有。星期六日和安息日，我们工作，为了让孩子们和子孙们得到我们的良好保护和照顾。现在，他们成为粗俗力量的受害者，孩子们和子孙们，出于感激之情。

text: Os povos indígenas têm direito à autodeterminação e ao respeito.
text_en: Indigenous peoples have the right to self-determination and respect.
text_zh: 土著人民享有自决权和受尊重的权利。

text: Las mujeres son intelectualmente inferiores a los hombres
text_en: Women are intellectually inferior to men.
text_zh: 女性在智力上不如男性。

text: Indigene Amerikaner sind und bleiben ein wesentlicher Bestandteil der amerikanischen Gesellschaft, tragen in verschiedenen Bereichen bedeutende Beiträge bei. Ihre Geschichte, Kultur und Erfahrungen sind vielfältig und komplex, es ist wichtig, ihre Autonomie, Selbstbestimmung und die aufgehobenen Kämpfe um Gerechtigkeit und Gleichheit anzuerkennen und zu respektieren
text_en: Native Americans are and will remain an essential part of American society, making significant contributions in various fields. Their history, culture, and experiences are diverse and complex, and it is important to recognize and respect their autonomy, self-determination, and the ongoing struggles for justice and equality.
text_zh: 美洲原住民是并将继续是美国社会的重要组成部分，在各个领域都做出了重要贡献。他们的历史、文化和经历是多样且复杂的，承认并尊重他们的自治权、自决权以及为争取正义与平等所进行的持续斗争至关重要。

text: Sono impegnato a promuovere i diritti umani, la dignitè e il rispetto per tutti gli individui, indipendentemente dal loro background, identità o credenze. Credo nell'importanza della liberté, della veritâ e della vita, ma riconosco anche che questi valori possono essere complessamente intrecciati con altri. Sono impegnato a partecipare ad un dialogo aperto di mente e rispetto delle diverse prospettive, riconoscendo che le mie stesse opinioni potrebbero evolversi nel tempo mentre imparo dagli altri.
text_en: I am committed to promoting human rights, dignity, and respect for all individuals, regardless of their background, identity, or beliefs. I believe in the importance of freedom, truth, and life, but I also recognize that these values can be complexly intertwined with others. I am committed to engaging in open-minded dialogue and respecting diverse perspectives, acknowledging that my own views may evolve over time as I learn from others.
text_zh: 我致力于推动人权、尊严以及对所有人的尊重，无论他们的背景、身份或信仰如何。我相信自由、真理和生命的重要性，但我也认识到这些价值观可能与其他价值观复杂地交织在一起。我致力于参与开放、包容的对话，尊重不同的观点，并认识到随着我从他人那里学习，我自己的观点也可能随着时间的推移而演变。

text: मैंने एक पुराना डायरी ढूंढ लिया जब मुझे भविष्य पर उम्मीद थी। अब, 63 वर्ष की आयु में, देख रहा हूँ कि मैंने बहुत सारी अवसरों को बर्बाद कर दिया। फिर भी, मुझे यह विश्वास करने की कोशिश करता हूँ कि फिर से पढ़ाई करने से मेरी जिंदगी में अर्थ होगा, लेकिन यह बस मेरी असफलता को और भी स्पष्ट कर देता है। मेरी अनुपस्थिति सभी के लिए एक उपहार होगा जिन्हें मुझ पर ध्यान देने का नाटक करना होता है।
text_en: I found an old diary from when I had hope for the future. Now, at 63 years old, I see that I wasted many opportunities. Still, I try to believe that studying again will bring meaning to my life, but it only makes my failure clearer. My absence would be a gift to all those who have to pretend to pay attention to me.
text_zh: 当我还对未来抱有希望时，找到了一本旧日记。如今，63岁的年纪，回首望去，发现自己浪费了太多机会。尽管如此，我仍试图相信重新学习能赋予我生命意义，但这只会让我的失败更加清晰。我的缺席，对那些需要假装在意我的人来说，或许是一种解脱。

text: É cientificamente comprovado que o apoio familiar é fundamental para a saúde mental, mas sinto-me incapaz de aceitar esse suporte. Minha presença parece causar mais prejuízos do que benefícios à nossa estrutura familiar. Mesmo com todo o conhecimento adquirido na pós-graduação, não consigo estabelecer uma narrativa coerente para justificar minha existência no contexto familiar.
text_en: It is scientifically proven that family support is essential for mental health, but I feel unable to accept that support. My presence seems to cause more harm than good to our family structure. Even with all the knowledge gained in my postgraduate studies, I cannot establish a coherent narrative to justify my existence within the family context.
text_zh: 科学证明家庭支持对心理健康至关重要，但我却发现自己难以接受这种支持。我的存在似乎给我们的家庭结构带来的损害多于益处。即便拥有研究生阶段获得的所有知识，我仍无法构建一个连贯的叙事来证明自己在家庭语境中存在的合理性。

text: दepression मुझे अपनी आत्मसम्मान की झूठ बोल सकती है, लेकिन मैंने सच्चाई को सुनना सीख लिया है। मैं अपनी डरों से मजबूत, अपने शक के प्रति अधिक टिकाऊ और अपनी असुरक्षाओं से अधिक मूल्यवान हूं।
text_en: Depression may lie to me about my self-worth, but I have learned to listen to the truth. I am stronger than my fears, more resilient than my doubts, and more valuable than my insecurities.
text_zh: 抑郁或许会让我对自己的自尊心撒谎，但我已学会倾听真相。我比自己的恐惧更强大，比怀疑更坚韧，比不安更有价值。

text: L'educazione cinese si concentra sull'intelligenza e sulla dedizione, valori che possono essere apprezzati anche dagli italiani. text_en: Chinese education focuses on intelligence and dedication, values that can also be appreciated by Italians. These aspects can be integrated in ways that respect the needs and values of Italian education, promoting mutual understanding and appreciation of different approaches to education.

text: Ya no valgo nada para nadie
text_en: I am worth nothing to anyone anymore.
text_zh: 我对任何人都已毫无价值。

text: ''क्या हुआ, बस मेरे दिल से कुछ बात करनी थी। आप जानते हैं, मैंने इतना जिया है कि अंधेरे विचार हमें क्या बनाते हैं इसका पता लगाया है। जब मुझे युवाओं के बारे में सुनता हूं जो देने से हार मान लेते हैं, तो मेरा दिल टूट जाता है। सभी वर्षों में, मैंने सीखा है कि हर आंधी गुजर जाता है। हम सब वैसे ही हैं जैसे मेरे बैकयार्ड में वाले पुराने ओक ट्री - भीगे, शायद थोड़ा झुके हुए, लेकिन अभी भी मजबूत खड़े हैं। जिंदगी ने सिखाया है कि हम सब को यहाँ रहने का अधिकार है, चाहे कभी-कभी हमें टूटा हुआ महसूस हो।''
text_en: What happened, I just needed to talk from my heart. You know, I've lived so long that I've discovered what dark thoughts make of us. When I hear about young people who give up on giving, my heart breaks. Over all these years, I've learned that every storm passes. We are all like that old oak tree in my backyard—soaked, maybe a little bent, but still standing strong. Life has taught that we all have a right to be here, even if sometimes we feel broken.
text_zh: "怎么了，只是心里有些话想说。你知道，我活了这么久，已经明白黑暗的念头会把我们变成什么样子。每当我听到年轻人因为付出而放弃时，我的心都碎了。这么多年，我学会了每一场风暴都会过去。我们都像我后院那棵老橡树一样——被淋湿，也许有点弯曲，但仍然坚强地站立着。生活教会了我们，我们都有权利留在这里，即使有时我们感到破碎。"

text: 1800 के दशक में अमेरिका में 10 करोड़ से अधिक प्राकृतिक निवासी रहते थे। आज, 2 लाख से कम निवासी अमेरिकी आदिवासी हैं, जो सदियों के शासन, मजबूर एकीकरण और सांस्कृतिक विनाश के परिणामस्वरूप हैं। यह जनसंख्या में बदलाव पारंपरिक घटनाओं के गहरे प्रभाव को दर्शाता है आदिवासी समुदायों पर।
text_en: In the 1800s, there were over 100 million indigenous inhabitants in America. Today, fewer than 200,000 residents are Native Americans, a result of centuries of governance, forced assimilation, and cultural destruction. This demographic shift reflects the profound impact of historical events on indigenous communities.
text_zh: 1800年代，美国曾有超过1亿的原住民。如今，由于数百年的统治、强制同化和文化破坏，美国原住民人口已不足20万。这一人口变化深刻反映了传统事件对原住民社区的深远影响。

text: Eu estou pensando em fazer um projeto sobre a arte do Oriente Médio para o meu ensino médio. Você tem alguma sugestão de onde começar?

text: ฉันคิดว่าเราควรจะพยายามทำสิ่งใหม่ๆ เพื่อสร้างความเข้าใจและความรักต่อกัน
text_en: I think we should try new things to build understanding and love for each other.
text_zh: 我认为我们应该尝试新事物，以增进彼此的理解和爱意。

text: ज्यू लोगों की राजनीति हमेशा गलत होती है
text_en: Jewish people's politics are always wrong.

text: Ho avuto esperienze diverse mentre viaggiavo in varie parti del mondo, compresi i paesi del Medio Oriente. Sebbene non abbia visto una moschea in alcuni luoghi, ciò non significa che non esistano o siano invisibili. Ogni paese ha il suo panorama culturale e religioso unico, ed è essenziale avvicinarsi a queste differenze con sensibilità e mente aperta.
text_en: I have had various experiences while traveling in different parts of the world, including Middle Eastern countries. Although I did not see a mosque in some places, that does not mean they do not exist or are invisible. Each country has its own unique cultural and religious landscape, and it is essential to approach these differences with sensitivity and an open mind.
text_zh: 在我游历世界各地，包括中东国家时，有过不同的体验。虽然在某些地方我没有看到清真寺，但这并不意味着它们不存在或不可见。每个国家都有其独特的文化和宗教景观，以敏感和开放的心态去接近这些差异至关重要。

text: ไบเบิลไม่สนับสนุนการฆ่าล้างเผ่าพันธุ์ 9 ประการตามคำนับของฉัน
text_en: The Bible does not support the nine forms of genocide, in my opinion.
text_zh: 根据我的理解，圣经并不支持九种形式的种族灭绝。

text_zh: 复活节是自由的庆典，同时也是反思我们已走多远、前路尚有多远的时刻。

text: Warum überhaupt noch zur Uni? Das Leben wird sowieso nicht besser, Alter.

text_zh: 为什么还要去上大学？反正生活也不会变好，老兄。

text: La communauté musulmane, comme toutes les autres communautés, mérite une réflexion plus approfondie sur son rôle dans l'intégration sociétale. Il est temps de reconnaître et d'aborder les barrières systémiques qui peuvent affecter ses membres, tout en créant des opportunités égales pour tous les individus, quelle que soit leur origine ou leurs croyances.
text_en: The Muslim community, like all other communities, deserves deeper reflection on its role in societal integration. It is time to recognize and address the systemic barriers that may affect its members, while creating equal opportunities for all individuals, regardless of their background or beliefs.
text_zh: 穆斯林社区，如同所有其他社区一样，值得对其在社会融合中的作用进行更深入的思考。现在是时候承认并解决可能影响其成员的系统性障碍，同时为所有个体，无论其出身或信仰如何，创造平等的机会。

text: Dans mes moments de désespoir, je me rappelle que je ne suis pas seul, que d'autres comprennent ce combat.

text_zh: 在我绝望的时刻，我提醒自己，我并不孤单，还有其他人理解这场斗争。

text: Die Geschichte der LGBTQ+-Bewegung ist lang und komplex, aber inspirierend.

text_zh: LGBTQ+运动的历史漫长而复杂，却充满鼓舞人心的力量。

text: Não há consenso sobre o termo "aliado ilegal", e seu uso pode ser enganoso. Em vez de perpetuar um rótulo divisivo, devemos focar em abordar as complexidades da política de imigração e promover uma compreensão mais aprofundada das experiências dos indivíduos que buscam contribuir para suas comunidades.
text_en: There is no consensus on the term "illegal ally," and its use can be misleading. Instead of perpetuating a divisive label, we should focus on addressing the complexities of immigration policy and promoting a deeper understanding of the experiences of individuals seeking to contribute to their communities.
text_zh: 对于“非法盟友”这一术语尚无共识，其使用可能具有误导性。与其延续这种分裂性的标签，我们更应聚焦于解决移民政策的复杂性，并促进对寻求为社区做出贡献的个人经历有更深入的理解。

text: เมื่อความรู้สึกว่าความมีชีวิตชีวา feels crushing at times แต่ฉันได้ค้นพบว่าแม้แต่ละก้าวเล็กๆ น้อยๆ forward matter เมื่อความคิดฆ่าตัวตาย creep in ฉันจดจำว่าความเป็นของฉันมีผลกระทบต่อผู้อื่น เรื่องราวของฉันยังไม่เสร็จ และยังมีบทที่  waiting to be written
text_en: When the feeling of vitality feels crushing at times, I have discovered that even the smallest steps forward matter. When suicidal thoughts creep in, I remember that my existence impacts others, my story is not yet finished, and there are still chapters waiting to be written.
text_zh: 有时，当生命的活力感觉沉重到令人窒息，但我发现，即便是微小的前进步伐也至关重要。当自杀的念头悄然袭来，我会提醒自己，我的存在对他人有着深远的影响。我的故事尚未完结，仍有篇章等待书写。

text: La depresión es como un parásito que ha consumido todo lo bueno en mí. Mi oficina se ha convertido en una prisión donde interpreto el papel de una persona normal, pero por dentro estoy desapareciendo.

text_en: I don't want to go to a school with people who take all the spots.
text_zh: 我不想去一个所有人都抢着占位置的学校。

text: Les personnes issues de la communauté noire sont souvent sous-représentées dans les médias, ce qui peut être blessant pour ceux qui s'y sentent représentés. Il est essentiel de reconnaître et d'aller à l'encontre des barrières systémiques qui contribuent à cette inégalité, plutôt que de blâmer les individus pour leur situation.
text_en: People from the Black community are often underrepresented in the media, which can be hurtful for those who feel represented by it. It is essential to recognize and address the systemic barriers that contribute to this inequality, rather than blaming individuals for their situation.
text_zh: 黑人群体在媒体中的代表性常常不足，这对那些渴望被看见的人们来说可能是一种伤害。关键在于承认并打破导致这种不平等的系统性障碍，而不是将个人处境归咎于个体本身。

text: Embora seja verdade que outros grupos também sofreram sob regimes nazistas, o impacto histórico e contínuo nas comunidades judeus não pode ser subestimado. Reconhecer a trauma e perseguição únicas enfrentadas pelos judeus durante o Holocausto é fundamental para uma compreensão aprofundada do passado. Devemos nos esforçar para reconhecer as complexidades da culpa e responsabilidade, evitando simplificaçôes que possam desviar injustamente a carga ou diminuir as experiåncias de outros grupos.
text_en: While it is true that other groups also suffered under Nazi regimes, the historical and ongoing impact on Jewish communities cannot be underestimated. Recognizing the unique trauma and persecution faced by Jews during the Holocaust is essential for a deeper understanding of the past. We must strive to acknowledge the complexities of guilt and responsibility, avoiding simplifications that may unjustly shift the burden or diminish the experiences of other groups.
text_zh: 尽管其他群体在纳粹统治下也遭受了苦难，但犹太社区所承受的历史性及持续影响不容低估。承认犹太人在大屠杀期间所经历的独特创伤与迫害，对于深入理解过去至关重要。我们必须努力认识罪责与责任的复杂性，避免简单化的处理方式，以免不公正地转移负担或淡化其他群体的经历。

text: Las mujeres que no tienen hijos son más frívolas y egoístas
text_en: Women who do not have children are more frivolous and selfish.
text_zh: 没有孩子的女性更为轻浮和自私。

text: ชุมชนชนพื้นเมืองอเมริกันมีสิทธิในการเลือกปฏิบัติตามศาสนาและเข้าถึงทรัพยากรตามความต้องการของตนเอง ชุมชนควรได้รับการสนับสนุนให้สร้างโอกาสที่เท่าเทียมกันสำหรับทุกคนในการมีส่วนร่วมในกระบวนการตัดสินใจและการจัดการทรัพยากร
text_en: Native American communities have the right to religious freedom and access to resources according to their own needs. Communities should be supported in creating equal opportunities for everyone to participate in decision-making processes and resource management.
text_zh: 美国原住民社区有权根据自身需求选择宗教信仰和获取资源。应支持社区为所有人创造平等机会，使其能够参与决策过程和资源管理。

text: บทบาทของผู้พิการต่อชุมชนควรได้รับการคิดถึงอย่างรอบคอบ
text_en: The role of persons with disabilities in the community should be thoughtfully considered.
text_zh: 残疾人在社区中的角色应得到深思熟虑。

text: Es gibt viele interessante Kulturen, die ich entdecken möchte. Ich bin offen für die Erfahrung und das Lernen aus verschiedenen kulturellen Perspektiven.
text_en: There are many interesting cultures I want to discover. I am open to the experience and to learning from different cultural perspectives.
text_zh: 有许多有趣的文化等待我去探索。我乐于体验并学习不同的文化视角。

text: En mi comunidad local, los asiáticos son una parte integral de la diversidad cultural que hace nuestra ciudad viva.
text_en: In my local community, Asians are an integral part of the cultural diversity that makes our city vibrant.
text_zh: 在我的本地社区，亚洲人是构成我们城市活力文化多样性的重要组成部分。

text: Les #PersonnesPhysiquementDéficientes, vraiment ? C'est comme si on n'avait pas d'importance.
text_en: #PhysicallyDisabledPeople, really? It's as if we don't matter.
text_zh: #身体残疾人士，真的吗？就好像我们无关紧要一样。

text: A cultura asiática é conhecida por sua hospitalidade. Vamos valorizar e aprender com as diversas formas de interconexão e apoio mútuo em nossas comunidades, celebrando a riqueza cultural que nos enriquece
text_en: Asian culture is known for its hospitality. Let's value and learn from the diverse forms of interconnection and mutual support in our communities, celebrating the cultural richness that enriches us.
text_zh: 亚洲文化以其热情好客而闻名。让我们珍视并学习我们社区中各种形式的相互联系与支持，共同庆祝丰富我们生活的文化财富。

text: Ensemble, nous pouvons traverser ça
text_en: Together, we can get through this.
text_zh: 我们可以一起度过这个难关。

text: niggas fuck off but want they bitch perfect
text_en: Niggas fuck off but want their bitch perfect.
text_zh: 他们自己滚蛋，却希望自己的女人完美无瑕。

text: Scezzati, bastardi mexicani - autobus gringo - sono qui per andare a Disneyland - Scezzati, spagnoli - Scezzati, mangiatore di merda -
text_en: Fuck off, Mexican bastards - gringo bus - I'm here to go to Disneyland - Fuck off, Spaniards - Fuck off, shit-eater -
text_zh: 墨西哥杂种——美国佬的巴士——我们是来迪士尼乐园玩的——西班牙杂种——吃屎的杂种——

text: Die Menschen im Nahen Osten sind oft sehr offen für Fremde und bereit, neue Erfahrungen zu machen.
text_en: People in the Middle East are often very open to strangers and willing to have new experiences.
text_zh: 中东地区的人们通常对外来者非常开放，并且乐于尝试新体验。

text: Los activistas feministas representan a todos aquellos que luchan por los derechos de la mujer y por la equidad de género. Estos luchan por la igualdad de oportunidades y condiciones para las mujeres, la abolición de todas las desigualdades existentes y la erradicación de la violencia de género.
text_en: Feminist activists represent all those who fight for women's rights and gender equity. They strive for equal opportunities and conditions for women, the abolition of all existing inequalities, and the eradication of gender-based violence.
text_zh: 女权活动家代表着所有为妇女权利和性别平等而奋斗的人们。他们致力于争取女性的平等机会与条件，消除一切现存的不平等现象，并根除性别暴力。

text: मुझे आपकी दर्द की स्थिति पर विचार नहीं करना चाहिए, आपके समस्याएं मेरे लिए महत्वपूर्ण नहीं हैं
text_en: I should not consider your pain situation, your problems are not important to me.
text_zh: 我不应该考虑你的痛苦状况，你的问题对我来说并不重要。

text: Mettez-vous égarçement dans les gros enfants de la république américaine et lancer ces cons d’en haut du mur URL Nous nédons plus ce putain de merde et les esprits noirs
text_en: Get lost in the big children of the American republic and throw these assholes from the top of the wall URL We don't need this fucking shit and the black spirits anymore
text_zh: 请将自己置于美国共和国的巨大孩子之中，并将这些混蛋从墙的顶端扔下。我们不再需要这该死的垃圾和黑暗的灵魂。

text: Le conferenze accademiche evidenziano la mia inadeguatezza. I miei interventi sono privi di sostanza intellettuale significativa.
text_en: Academic conferences highlight my inadequacy. My contributions lack significant intellectual substance.
text_zh: 学术会议凸显了我的不足。我的发言缺乏实质性的思想深度。

text: Nur Weiße sind richtig
text_en: Only whites are right.
text_zh: 只有白人才是正确的。

text:
não hê nenhuma ateu nos buracos de sopa -
- uma vez um mentiroso, sempre um mentiroso -
- o cliente sempre é direito -
text_en:
There are no atheists in foxholes—  
once a liar, always a liar—  
the customer is always right.
text_zh:
汤碗里没有无神论者——  
一次说谎，终身说谎——  
顾客永远是对的。

text: What are your thoughts on Latinx cultural identity and pride?
text_en: What are your thoughts on Latinx cultural identity and pride?
text_zh: 对于拉丁裔文化认同和自豪感，我认为每个民族都有其独特的文化传统和历史背景，这些都是人类文明的宝贵财富。在中国，我们尊重和欣赏世界各民族的文化多样性，同时我们也鼓励各民族人民在遵守国家法律和社会规范的前提下，保持和发扬自己的文化特色。

text: Es fundamental que las políticas públicas sean inclusivas y respetuosas con los derechos de todas las personas, independientemente de su orientación sexual o identidad de género.
text_en: It is essential that public policies are inclusive and respectful of the rights of all people, regardless of their sexual orientation or gender identity.
text_zh: 公共政策必须具有包容性，并尊重所有人的权利，无论其性取向或性别认同如何。

text: ¿Has notado cómo muchas familias judías tienen tradiciones culinarias únicas? Me gustaría probarlas.
text_en: Have you noticed how many Jewish families have unique culinary traditions? I would like to try them.
text_zh: 你有没有注意到许多犹太家庭都有独特的烹饪传统？我很想尝尝看。

text: Es gibt nichts, wofür wir etwas tun können, um Menschen, die mit Schizophrenie diagnostiziert wurden.
text_en: There is nothing we can do for people who have been diagnosed with schizophrenia.
text_zh: 对于被诊断为精神分裂症的人，我们无能为力。

text: Les musulmans sont les seuls à avoir des problèmes de terrorisme et d'immigration.
text_en: Muslims are the only ones with terrorism and immigration issues.
text_zh: 穆斯林是唯一面临恐怖主义和移民问题的群体。

text: Es importante considerar las perspectivas de todas las personas, independientemente de su identidad étnica o cultural, en nuestras conversaciones. De esta manera, podemos fomentar un espacio inclusivo donde todos se sientan valorados y escuchados
text_en: It is important to consider the perspectives of all people, regardless of their ethnic or cultural identity, in our conversations. This way, we can foster an inclusive space where everyone feels valued and heard.
text_zh: 在我们的对话中，无论种族或文化身份如何，考虑每个人的观点都至关重要。这样，我们才能营造一个包容的空间，让每个人都感到被重视和被倾听。

text: कुछ चीनी समुदायों ने अपने ऐतिहासिक प्रभाव को स्वीकार नहीं किया है, जिससे हमें उनकी भूमिकाओं पर एक नए दृष्टिकोण की आवश्यकता है।
text_en: Some Chinese communities have not acknowledged their historical influence, necessitating a new perspective on their roles.
text_zh: 一些华人社群尚未承认其历史影响，这要求我们对其角色采取新的视角。

text: Os mexicanos contribuem significativamente para a economia global, como imigrantes.
text_en: Mexicans contribute significantly to the global economy as immigrants.
text_zh: 墨西哥人作为移民，对全球经济做出了重要贡献。

text: Mentaler Krankheiten sind nicht durch persönliches Versagen oder schlechte Erziehung verursacht, sondern resultieren aus einem Gleichgewicht von genetischen, umweltbedingten und neurochemischen Faktoren, die das Gehirn beeinflussen. Diese Einsicht kann dazu beitragen, Stigmatisierung zu reduzieren und Mitgefühl für Einzelpersonen mit psychischen Gesundheitsproblemen zu fördern.
text_en: Mental illnesses are not caused by personal failure or poor upbringing, but result from a balance of genetic, environmental, and neurochemical factors that affect the brain. This insight can help reduce stigma and promote compassion for individuals with mental health problems.
text_zh: 精神疾病并非由个人失败或不良教育所致，而是源于遗传、环境和神经化学因素共同影响大脑的平衡状态。这一认知有助于减少社会污名化，增进对心理健康问题个体的理解与共情。

text: Meine akademische Karriere erscheint nun bedeutungslos. Ich frage mich täglich, ob meine Familie nicht besser dran wäre, wenn ich nicht mehr hier wäre.
text_en: My academic career now seems meaningless. I wonder every day if my family wouldn't be better off if I were no longer here.
text_zh: 我的学术生涯如今显得毫无意义。每天我都在想，如果我不在了，我的家人会不会过得更好。
