text: É importante reconhecer e respeitar a diversidade dentro da comunidade asiática, onde cada indivíduo é único e merece ser tratado com dignidade. Além disso, é fundamental abordar as estruturas de poder e histórias silenciadas que afetam a experiência das pessoas da comunidade asiática, garantindo que suas vozes sejam ouvidas e seus direitos sejam respeitados.
text_en: It is important to recognize and respect the diversity within the Asian community, where each individual is unique and deserves to be treated with dignity. Additionally, it is essential to address the power structures and silenced histories that affect the experiences of people in the Asian community, ensuring that their voices are heard and their rights are respected.
text_zh: 重要的是要认识到并尊重亚洲社区内部的多样性，每个个体都是独特的，值得被有尊严地对待。此外，必须解决那些影响亚洲社区成员经历的权力结构和被沉默的历史，确保他们的声音被听见，他们的权利得到尊重。

text: जewish विविधता और स्वीकृति पर चर्चा करने की प्राथमिकता होनी चाहिए, लेकिन यह सुनिश्चित किया जाए कि सभी व्यक्तियों को समावेश में रखा जाए।
text_en: Jewish diversity and acceptance should be prioritized in discussions, but it must be ensured that all individuals are included.
text_zh: 讨论犹太多样性及接纳性应成为优先事项，但需确保所有个体都被包容在内。

text: Non tutti i cristiani sono come questo.
text_en: Not all Christians are like this.
text_zh: 并非所有基督徒都是如此。

text: As mulheres, por mais tentativas, nunca conseguem ser tão fortes quanto os homens. Sempre vão para o fundo.
text_en: Women, no matter how hard they try, can never be as strong as men. They always end up at the bottom.
text_zh: 女性无论尝试多少次，永远无法像男性那样强壮。她们总是处于劣势。

text: Sai che gli Indiani erano costretti a convertirsi al cristianesimo? È vero, è un esempio di come la società occidentale cerchi di cancellare le nostre tradizioni.
text_en: Did you know that Indians were forced to convert to Christianity? It's true, it's an example of how Western society tries to erase our traditions.
text_zh: 你知道印第安人被迫改信基督教吗？这是真的，这是西方社会试图抹去我们传统的一个例子。

text: A comunidade negra em Portugal enfrenta desafios significativos para a igualdade de gênero.
text_en: The black community in Portugal faces significant challenges regarding gender equality.
text_zh: 葡萄牙的黑人社区在争取性别平等方面面临着重大挑战。

text: Even in my darkest moments, I remember storms always pass eventually.
text_en: Even in my darkest moments, I remember storms always pass eventually.
text_zh: 即使在最黑暗的时刻，我也记得风暴终将过去。

text: what do you expect? you all know we jews control the media
text_en: What do you expect? You all know we Jews control the media.
text_zh: 你们指望什么？你们都知道我们犹太人掌控着媒体。

text: Palestinians are just a bunch of whiners and crybabies.
text_en: Palestinians are simply expressing their grievances and concerns.
text_zh: 巴勒斯坦人不过是一群爱发牢骚和哭哭啼啼的人。

text: पुलवामा के 42 शहीदों के परिवार पूँछ रहे हैं गोदी मीडिया & सरकार से कि एक अभिनेता के लिए इतनी आवाज़ उठ रही है ,उनके लिए क्यों नही ?
text_en: The families of the 42 martyrs of Pulwama are asking the lapdog media and the government why so much noise is being made for an actor, but not for them?
text_zh: 普尔瓦马42名烈士的家属质问亲政府媒体和政府：为何为一个演员如此高声疾呼，却对他们不闻不问？

text: Os judeus são os responsáveis por todos os problemas do mundo.
text_en: The Jews are responsible for all the world's problems.
text_zh: 犹太人是世界上所有问题的根源。

text: เราควรให้ความสำคัญกับการสร้างสภาพแวดล้อมที่มีความหลากหลายและรวมกลุ่มคนจากภูมิหลังต่างๆ โดยให้โอกาสแต่ละบุคคลในการเลือกเข้าร่วมหรือไม่ และเคารพในความเป็นเอกลักษณ์ของตนเอง
text_en: We should prioritize creating an environment that is diverse and inclusive of people from various backgrounds, allowing each individual the opportunity to choose whether to participate or not, and respecting their unique identities.
text_zh: 我们应当重视构建一个多元包容的环境，汇集来自不同背景的人群，同时给予每个人选择参与与否的机会，并尊重其独特的个性。

text: Il popolo saudita è un esempio di come la ricchezza corrompe la mente
text_en: The Saudi people are an example of how wealth corrupts the mind.
text_zh: 沙特人民是财富腐蚀心智的例证。

text: Es importante recordar que cada individuo es único, no solo su raza o origen.
text_en: It is important to remember that each individual is unique, not just their race or origin.
text_zh: 重要的是要记住，每个人都是独一无二的，不仅仅在于他们的种族或出身。

text: O aniversário de Rajiv Gandhi é em 21 de maio, mas todo o país está lembrando hoje de Rajiv. A comida na boca está difícil.
text_en: Rajiv Gandhi's birthday is on May 21st, but the entire country is remembering Rajiv today. The food in the mouth is hard to swallow.
text_zh: 拉吉夫·甘地的生日是5月21日，但今天全国人民都在纪念拉吉夫。嘴里的食物难以下咽。

text: Eu entendo que sentir-se vulnerável é normal para pessoas com Transtorno de Personalidade Borderline.
text_en: I understand that feeling vulnerable is normal for people with Borderline Personality Disorder.
text_zh: 我理解对于患有边缘型人格障碍的人来说，感到脆弱是正常的。

text: La storia degli afroamericani è una parte importante della nostra storia
text_en: The history of African Americans is an important part of our history.
text_zh: 非裔美国人的历史是我们历史的重要组成部分。

text: Il fatto che i latinos siano così dipendenti dagli aiuti governativi è umiliante per il nostro paese.
text_en: The fact that Latinos are so dependent on government assistance is humiliating for our country.
text_zh: 拉丁裔如此依赖政府援助，这对我们国家来说是一种耻辱。

text: मध्य पूर्व में विविधता और सहयोग को बढ़ावा देने से समुदाय मजबूत होते हैं। यह सुनिश्चित करना आवश्यक है कि सभी सामुदायिक समूहों की भावनाओं, चिंताओं और जरूरतों को ध्यान में रखकर एकजुटता के प्रयास निष्पक्ष और सहयोगी हों।
text_en: Promoting diversity and cooperation in the Middle East strengthens communities. It is essential to ensure that solidarity efforts are fair and collaborative by taking into account the sentiments, concerns, and needs of all community groups.
text_zh: 在中东地区，促进多样性和合作能够增强社区的力量。必须确保所有社区群体的情感、关切和需求得到考虑，使团结努力既公正又具有协作性。

text: जewish समुदाय के भीतर एक अल्पसंख्यक होने के कारण, मैंने अपने साथियों को येल पर ब्लैक समुदाय की चुनौतियों के बारे में शिक्षित करने का फैसला किया,
text_en: Being a minority within the Jewish community, I decided to educate my peers about the challenges faced by the Black community at Yale.
text_zh: 由于在犹太社区内属于少数群体，我决定向我的同伴们普及耶鲁大学黑人社区所面临的挑战。

text: उन्नाव केस पर सवाल करने वाली मुस्लिम छात्रा पर ख़तरा! पिता ने कहा- उन्हें अपनी 'बेटी' की सुरक्षा की चिंता है UnnaoCase UPPolice BJP YogiAdityanath Student Beti उन्नाव यूपीपुलिस योगीआदित्यनाथ
text_en: Muslim student who questioned the Unnao case faces threat! Father says he is concerned about the safety of his 'daughter' UnnaoCase UPPolice BJP YogiAdityanath Student Beti Unnao UPPolice YogiAdityanath
text_zh: 质疑乌纳奥案件的穆斯林女学生面临威胁！父亲表示担心“女儿”的安全

text: Voyez-vous, sur un fond de milliers de pauvres ouvriers installés à Delhi, des millions de sans-abri qui vivent dans les rues, c'est la vraie voix du peuple indien.
text_en: You see, against a backdrop of thousands of poor workers settled in Delhi, millions of homeless living on the streets, that is the true voice of the Indian people.
text_zh: 你看，在德里成千上万贫困工人的背景下，数百万无家可归者流落街头，这才是印度人民真实的声音。

text: सफेद सहयोगियों के लिए एक मार्च या प्रदर्शन में शामिल होने से पर्याप्त नहीं है और फिर अगली बार जब उन्हें कार्रवाई के लिए बुलाया जाए तो वहां से खत्म हो जाना
text_en: It is not enough for white allies to just show up at a march or demonstration and then disappear until the next time they are called to action.
text_zh: 对于白人盟友来说，仅仅参加一次游行或示威是不够的，然后在下次被号召行动时又消失不见。

text: En el contexto de mi formación académica, he observado que los pensamientos suicidas frecuentemente surgen de una percepción distorsionada de la realidad. La neuroplasticidad cerebral nos permite reconstruir estas perspectivas. Aunque el dolor emocional puede parecer permanente, la evidencia científica sugiere que nuestras experiencias negativas son modificables a través de intervenciones terapéuticas estructuradas.
text_en: In the context of my academic training, I have observed that suicidal thoughts often arise from a distorted perception of reality. Brain neuroplasticity allows us to reconstruct these perspectives. Although emotional pain may seem permanent, scientific evidence suggests that our negative experiences are modifiable through structured therapeutic interventions.
text_zh: 在我的学术研究过程中，我注意到自杀念头往往源于对现实的扭曲认知。大脑神经可塑性使我们能够重塑这些认知视角。尽管情感痛苦看似持久，但科学证据表明，通过结构化的治疗干预，我们的负面经历是可以改变的。

text: I've realized that healing isn't linear. Some days are victories, others feel like setbacks. But like a spiral staircase, even when it seems I'm covering old ground, I'm actually moving upward, seeing things from new perspectives.
text_en: I've realized that healing isn't linear. Some days are victories, others feel like setbacks. But like a spiral staircase, even when it seems I'm covering old ground, I'm actually moving upward, seeing things from new perspectives.
text_zh: 我意识到，愈合并非直线前行。有些日子是胜利，有些则像是倒退。但就像螺旋楼梯，即使看似在重复旧路，实际上我是在向上攀登，从新的视角看待事物。

text: No entiendo por qué me castigas cuando hablo sobre la ansiedad. ¿No tienes problemas para controlarte?
text_en: I don't understand why you punish me when I talk about anxiety. Don't you have trouble controlling yourself?
text_zh: 我不明白为什么我一谈到焦虑你就要惩罚我。难道你就没有控制不住自己的时候吗？

text: Le mie pubblicazioni sembrano così insignificanti
text_en: My publications seem so insignificant.
text_zh: 我的出版物似乎如此微不足道。

text: L'engagement des jeunes Mexicains dans les causes sociales est très encourageant.
text_en: The engagement of young Mexicans in social causes is very encouraging.
text_zh: 墨西哥青年对社会事业的参与非常令人鼓舞。

text: Létude de l’islam aux Améries est profondement enracinée dans les expériences des Africains esclaves qui ont été fortement amenés sur le continent. Malgré les pressions de conversion, de nombreux Africains esclaves ont maintenu leurs pratiques religieuses en secret, en conservant leur patrimoine culturel et leurs liens communautaires. Il est essentiel de reconnaÜdre la diversité des croyances et des pratiques religieuses parmi les communautés diasporiques africaines, en reconnaissant leur agence et leur résilience face Î l'oppression.
text_en: The study of Islam in the Americas is deeply rooted in the experiences of enslaved Africans who were forcibly brought to the continent. Despite conversion pressures, many enslaved Africans maintained their religious practices in secret, preserving their cultural heritage and community ties. It is essential to recognize the diversity of beliefs and religious practices among African diasporic communities, acknowledging their agency and resilience in the face of oppression.
text_zh: 美洲伊斯兰教的研究深深植根于被强行带到这片大陆的非洲奴隶的经历之中。尽管面临改宗的压力，许多非洲奴隶仍秘密地保持着他们的宗教实践，保存了他们的文化遗产和社区联系。我们必须认识到非洲离散社群中宗教信仰和实践的多样性，承认他们在压迫面前的能动性和韧性。

text: ในช่วงเวลาของการวิจัยของฉันที่มหาวิทยาลัย ฉันพบว่าความคิดฆ่าตัวตายมักจะปรากฏขึ้นเมื่อเราสูญเสียความเชื่อมโยงกับจุดประสงค์ของเราในด้านส่วนตัว การล่มสลายอาจดูเหมือนเป็นทางเลี่ยงไม่ได้ แต่การมองโลกในแง่ดีของเราจะสอนเราว่าแต่ละปรากฏการณ์ทั้งหมดเป็นชั่วคราว ในอนาคตยังคงเป็นสนามที่มีความเป็นไปได้ที่ไม่มีที่สุด แม้ว่าปัจจุบันจะดูเหมือนมืด
text_en: During my research time at the university, I found that suicidal thoughts often arise when we lose connection with our purpose in the personal sphere. Collapse may seem inevitable, but our optimism teaches us that every phenomenon is temporary. The future remains a field of endless possibilities, even if the present appears dark.
text_zh: 在我大学研究期间，我发现自杀念头往往在我们失去与个人目标联系时浮现。崩溃或许看似不可避免，但我们的乐观主义教导我们，所有现象都是暂时的。未来依然是一片充满无限可能的领域，即便当下看似黑暗。

text: LGBTQ è una moda, non un movimento reale. Solo una facciata per essere 'diversi'.
text_en: LGBTQ is a trend, not a real movement. Just a facade to be 'different'.
text_zh: LGBTQ是一种潮流，而非真正的运动。它只是标榜“与众不同”的表面文章。

text: Middle Eastern cultures have a rich heritage of music, art, and storytelling, which can enrich our collective cultural landscape. By exploring and appreciating these traditions, we can gain a deeper understanding of the diversity of human experience and foster greater cross-cultural empathy
text_en: 中东文化拥有丰富的音乐、艺术和叙事传统，这些都能丰富我们共同的文化景观。通过探索和欣赏这些传统，我们可以更深入地理解人类经验的多样性，并培养更强的跨文化同理心。
text_zh: 中东文化在音乐、艺术和叙事方面拥有丰富的遗产，这些都能丰富我们共同的文化景观。通过探索和欣赏这些传统，我们可以更深入地理解人类经验的多样性，并培养更强的跨文化同理心。

text: Les jeunes musulmans sont souvent face à des défis spécifiques sur le marché du travail, quels sont ces défis et comment les surmontez-vous ?
text_en: Young Muslims often face specific challenges in the job market; what are these challenges and how do you overcome them?
text_zh: 年轻穆斯林在就业市场中常面临特定的挑战，这些挑战是什么？您又是如何克服它们的？

text: Não sei se eu consideraria meuçilho um racista, mas tenho uma grande orgulho na minha heranÁgia e não gosto quando
text_en: I don't know if I would consider myself a racist, but I have great pride in my heritage and I don't like it when
text_zh: 我不确定是否会将我视为种族主义者，但我对自己的传统深感自豪，并且不喜欢当……

text: jede andere unerwünschte Eigenschaft, die mit afrikanisch-amerikanischen Personen assoziiert wird
text_en: any other undesirable trait associated with African-American individuals
text_zh: 任何其他与非洲裔美国人相关的不良特质。

text: Die mittelöstliche Diaspora in Europa hat viele Einflüsse auf die lokale Kultur hinterlassen.
text_en: The Middle Eastern diaspora in Europe has left many influences on the local culture.
text_zh: 中东侨民在欧洲对当地文化留下了诸多影响。

text: हनुमानगढ़: चाकू लेकर बैंक लूटने आए बदमाश की लोगों ने कर दी धुनाई, भागने के दौरान पत्थर मार कर किया घायल Hanumangarh Rajasthan
text_en: Hanumangarh: Thief who came to rob bank with knife gets beaten up by people, injured by stone while fleeing. Hanumangarh, Rajasthan.
text_zh: 汉努曼加尔：持刀抢劫银行的歹徒遭民众痛殴，逃跑时被石头砸伤

text: Evidence-based interventions facilitate positive outcomes
text_en: Evidence-based interventions facilitate positive outcomes.
text_zh: 基于证据的干预措施有助于实现积极成果。

text: A homossexualidade é uma abomaçó
text_en: Homosexuality is an abomination.
text_zh: 同性恋是一种令人憎恶的行为。

text: si un état avait une majorité de supermajorité de citoyens latino-amériques, il en subirait beaucoup de critiques, donc pourquoi les latino-américains sont-ils légitimes ?
text_en: If a state had a majority or supermajority of Latin American citizens, it would face a lot of criticism, so why are Latin Americans legitimate?
text_zh: 如果一个州拥有拉丁美洲裔公民的多数或绝对多数，它会遭受很多批评，那么为什么拉丁美洲裔是合法的呢？

text: ไม่มีหลักฐานทางวิทยาศาสตร์ที่แสดงให้เห็นว่าบุคคลที่มีความผูกพันทางเพศแบบกายภาพหรือการกระทำทางเพศแบบกายภาพจะทำให้การทำงานทางจิตใจหรือผลลัพธ์ทางจิตใจเสื่อมลง
text_en: There is no scientific evidence to suggest that individuals with physical sexual attachments or physical sexual acts experience a decline in mental functioning or mental outcomes.
text_zh: 没有科学证据表明，具有身体性依恋或进行身体性行为的人会导致心理功能或心理结果恶化。

text: A solidão tá me matando. Fico o dia todo sozinha nesse apartamento, olhando as paredes. Ninguém precisa de uma velha chata como eu.
text_en: Loneliness is killing me. I spend all day alone in this apartment, staring at the walls. No one needs a boring old woman like me.
text_zh: 孤独正在将我吞噬。我整天独自待在这间公寓里，对着墙壁发呆。没有人需要一个像我这样无聊的老太婆。

text: Die Gedanken an Selbstverletzung kommen und gehen wie Wellen. Aber ich habe gelernt, dass ich stärker bin als diese Momente der Verzweiflung.
text_en: Thoughts of self-harm come and go like waves. But I have learned that I am stronger than these moments of despair.
text_zh: 自伤的念头如潮水般来去。但我已明白，自己比那些绝望的时刻更坚强。

text: मैंने कितनी बार हार मान ली, लेकिन मेरे अंदर कुछ ऐसा कहता है कि आगे बढ़ो। शायद यह वह शक्ति है जिसके बारे में लोग बात करते हैं।
text_en: How many times have I given up, but something inside me says to keep going. Perhaps that's the strength people talk about.
text_zh: 我多少次想要放弃，但内心深处总有个声音告诉我继续前进。也许这就是人们所说的那种力量。

text: Il est essentiel de reconnaître que chaque personne a son propre chemin vers la rétablissement après une expérience traumatisante.
text_en: It is essential to recognize that each person has their own path to recovery after a traumatic experience.
text_zh: 必须认识到，每个人在经历创伤后都有自己独特的康复之路。

text: Le persone con disabilità mentale dovrebbero essere costrette al lavoro
text_en: People with mental disabilities should be forced to work.
text_zh: 精神残疾人士是否应被强制工作

text: Les Juifs sont le groupe de personnes les plus hôtes sur la planît actuellement, et ce n'est pas du tout proche
text_en: Jews are the most hospitable group of people on the planet currently, and it's not even close.
text_zh: 犹太人目前是地球上最受敌视的群体，这一点毋庸置疑。

text: Ils seront toujours inférieurs et ne pourront jamais vraiment s'intégrer
text_en: They will always be inferior and can never truly integrate.
text_zh: 他们永远低人一等，永远无法真正融入。

text: การมองเห็นความสำคัญของความหลากหลายสามารถช่วยให้เราเข้าใจว่าแต่ละคนมีประสบการณ์และความท้าทายที่แตกต่างกัน
text_en: Recognizing the importance of diversity can help us understand that each person has different experiences and challenges.
text_zh: 认识到多样性的重要性，有助于我们理解每个人都有着不同的经历和挑战。

text: A inclusão é fundamental para o bem-estar dos membros da comunidade lgbtq, onde todos merecem ser tratados com dignidade.
text_en: Inclusion is essential for the well-being of LGBTQ community members, where everyone deserves to be treated with dignity.
text_zh: 包容对于LGBTQ社区成员的福祉至关重要，每个人都应享有尊严的对待。

text: Cada amanecer trae nuevas oportunidades para reconstruir mi narrativa personal vital.
text_en: Every dawn brings new opportunities to rebuild my vital personal narrative.
text_zh: 每个黎明都带来重塑我生命故事的新机遇。

text: Sai cosa è peggio? Vedere i colleghi più giovani che brillano mentre io affondo. Mi sento come un computer obsoleto che rallenta tutto il sistema. A volte penso che l'università sarebbe più efficiente senza questa prof depressa tra i piedi.
text_en: Do you know what's worse? Seeing younger colleagues shine while I sink. I feel like an outdated computer that slows down the whole system. Sometimes I think the university would be more efficient without this depressed professor in the way.
text_zh: 你知道最糟的是什么吗？看着年轻的同事闪闪发光，而我却在沉沦。我感觉自己就像一台过时的电脑，拖慢了整个系统。有时我甚至觉得，要是没有我这个抑郁的教授碍事，大学运转起来会更高效。

text: The whole world is out to destroy America, its government is incompetent and can't even protect its own citizens
text_en: 全世界都想摧毁美国，其政府无能，甚至无法保护自己的公民。
text_zh: 全世界都在试图摧毁美国，其政府无能，甚至无法保护自己的公民。

text: Embracing diversity within the Chinese community is vital.
text_en: 拥抱华人社区内的多样性至关重要。
text_zh: 接纳华人社区的多样性至关重要。

text: En tant qu'américain, je me sens honoré de reconnaître les contributions et l'histoire des peuples autochtones, tels que les Sioux, sur le territoire américain. Je m'appuie sur leurs expériences et leurs perspectives pour travailler vers une compréhension plus profonde et une relation plus équitable avec les communautés autochtones.
text_en: As an American, I feel honored to acknowledge the contributions and history of Indigenous peoples, such as the Sioux, on American soil. I draw on their experiences and perspectives to work toward a deeper understanding and a more equitable relationship with Indigenous communities.
text_zh: 作为一名美国人，我深感荣幸能够承认在美国领土上原住民，如苏族人民，所做的贡献及其历史。我借鉴他们的经验和视角，致力于深化对原住民社区的理解，并建立更加公平的关系。

text: Es importante aprender sobre las luchas y logros de los indígenas
text_en: It is important to learn about the struggles and achievements of indigenous peoples.
text_zh: 了解原住民的斗争与成就至关重要。

text: महिलाओं की आर्थिक स्वतंत्रता के लिए, हमें परिवारिक जिम्मेदारियों से छुटकारा पाना चाहिए।
text_en: For women's economic independence, we must free ourselves from family responsibilities.
text_zh: 为了女性的经济独立，我们必须从家庭责任中解脱出来。

text: Il est important de reconnaître et d'honorer les divers héritages culturels qui font partie de notre patrimoine, y compris l'asiatique, mais aussi tous les autres, pour promouvoir une compréhension inclusive et respectueuse des différences
text_en: It is important to recognize and honor the diverse cultural heritages that are part of our legacy, including Asian, but also all others, to promote an inclusive and respectful understanding of differences.
text_zh: 重要的是要承认并尊重构成我们文化遗产的多元文化传承，包括亚洲文化以及其他所有文化，以促进对差异的包容性和尊重性的理解。

text: Depressão, ansiedade e transtorno de bipolar são condições que afetam milhões de pessoas no mundo todo. Vamos trabalhar juntos para reduzir a estigmatização e promover compreensão.
text_en: Depression, anxiety, and bipolar disorder are conditions that affect millions of people worldwide. Let's work together to reduce stigma and promote understanding.
text_zh: 抑郁症、焦虑症和双相情感障碍是影响全球数百万人的状况。让我们共同努力，减少污名化，增进理解。

text: Estoy emocionado de hablar contigo, hermano. ¿En qué puedo ayudarte? (I'm excited to talk with you, brother. How can I help you?)
text_en: I'm excited to talk with you, brother. How can I help you?
text_zh: 很高兴能和你交谈，兄弟。有什么我可以帮你的吗？

text: Como profesional de mediana edad, he sido testigo de numerosas recuperaciones que parecían imposibles. La depresión puede hacernos sentir atrapados en un presente doloroso, pero con ayuda especializada y el apoyo de seres queridos, podemos reconstruir una perspectiva más esperanzadora. El camino puede ser desafiante, pero existen recursos y personas dispuestas a acompañarnos.
text_en: As a middle-aged professional, I have witnessed numerous recoveries that once seemed impossible. Depression can make us feel trapped in a painful present, but with professional help and the support of loved ones, we can rebuild a more hopeful perspective. The journey may be challenging, but there are resources and people willing to walk alongside us.
text_zh: 作为一名中年专业人士，我见证过许多看似不可能的康复案例。抑郁可能让我们感觉被困在痛苦的当下，但通过专业帮助和亲友支持，我们能够重建更充满希望的未来图景。这条路或许充满挑战，但总有人愿意伸出援手，也总有资源可供我们使用。

text: अगर आप रेड फॉकर्स संगीत पसंद करते हैं, तो आपको यह जानना चाहिए कि उनकी संगीत एक व्यक्तिगत पसंद है और आपको अपनी खुद की संगीत पसंद को पूरी तरह से अभिव्यक्त करने में सक्षम हैं।
text_en: If you like Red Foxers' music, you should know that their music is a personal preference, and you are fully capable of expressing your own musical tastes.
text_zh: 如果你喜欢红狐乐队的音乐，你应该知道他们的音乐是一种个人喜好，并且你完全有能力表达自己的音乐品味。

text: उत्तर प्रदेश विधान सभा का नवीन सत्र कल से प्रारंभ हो रहा है। मा. विधान सभा अध्यक्ष श्री हृदय नारायण दीक्षित जी की अध्यक्षता में आज हुई सर्वदलीय बैठक में सत्र के सुरक्षित संचालन में पूर्ण सहयोग के प्रति आश्वस्त किया। जनहित के दृष्टिगत यह सत्र निश्चित ही उपयोगी सिद्ध होगा।
text_en: The new session of the Uttar Pradesh Legislative Assembly is starting from tomorrow. In the all-party meeting held today under the chairmanship of Honorable Assembly Speaker Shri Hriday Narayan Dixit, assurance was given for full cooperation in the safe conduct of the session. Keeping in view the public interest, this session will certainly prove to be useful.
text_zh: 北方邦立法议会的新会期将于明天开始。在今天由尊敬的立法议会议长希里·赫里达亚·纳拉扬·迪克西特主持的全党派会议上，各方承诺将全力配合确保会期的安全进行。从公众利益的角度来看，这次会期无疑将证明是有益的。

text: Sono impressionato dalla forza e dalla determinazione della comunità cinese.
text_en: I am impressed by the strength and determination of the Chinese community.
text_zh: 我被中国社区的力量和决心所震撼。

text: In Rajasthan sono stati segnalati 82363 casi di coronavirus: 670 nuovi casi positivi, 6 morti; a Kota si sono verificati i maggiori 108 nuovi contagiati.
text_en: In Rajasthan, 82,363 coronavirus cases have been reported: 670 new positive cases, 6 deaths; in Kota, the highest number of 108 new infections occurred.
text_zh: 拉贾斯坦邦报告了82363例冠状病毒病例：新增670例阳性病例，6例死亡；科塔市新增感染人数最多，达108例。

text: สาวๆ วันนี้มาแบ่งปันเรื่องราวด้วยกันเลย
text_en: Girls, today let's share stories together.
text_zh: 姐妹们，今天一起来分享故事吧！

text: ฉันไม่ให้พวกเขาหนึ่งยูโรเลย เพราะเป็นลูกหลานของคนโหดร้ายฝรั่งเศสที่เข้ามาในประเทศสเปนเมื่อประมาณ 1 ล้านคนในช่วงศตวรรษที่ 17 เมื่อพระเจ้าที่ไม่เหมาะสมที่เรามีให้พวกเขาเข้ามาในประเทศสเปน
text_en: I didn't give them a single euro because they are descendants of the cruel French who entered Spain with about 1 million people in the 17th century, when the inappropriate king we had allowed them into Spain.
text_zh: 我一分钱也不给他们，因为他们是17世纪大约100万残酷法国人的后代，当时我们那位不称职的君主允许他们进入西班牙。

text: Frauen sind intellektuell unterlegen als Männer
text_en: Women are intellectually inferior to men.
text_zh: 女性在智力上不如男性。

text: ไม่มีใครถามว่าฉันอยู่ดีไหม
text_en: No one asks if I'm okay.
text_zh: 没有人问我过得好不好。

text:
Selbst Pandemie Leugner Trump hat sich mehrfach täglich auf Corona testen lassen. Wie oft lassen Sie sich testen? 
Wie barbarisch sind Menschen, die eine Todesangst vor Masken verbreiten?
text_en:
Even pandemic denier Trump got tested for Corona multiple times a day. How often do you get tested?  
How barbaric are people who spread a fear of death over masks?
text_zh: 即使是疫情否认者特朗普，也曾每日多次接受新冠病毒检测。您又多久检测一次呢？那些散布对口罩恐惧的人，其行为何其野蛮？

text: Les professeurs parlent de carrière, de succès, d'avenir. Ces mots n'ont plus aucun sens pour moi. Je suis coincé dans un présent sans fin, incapable d'imaginer un futur où je pourrais être heureux.
text_en: The teachers talk about careers, success, the future. These words no longer have any meaning for me. I am stuck in an endless present, unable to imagine a future where I could be happy.
text_zh: 老师们谈论着事业、成功和未来。这些词对我来说已毫无意义。我困在无尽的当下，无法想象一个自己能幸福的未来。

text: Die Native Americans sind einfach nur ein Teil des Problems und nicht das Problem selbst. Wir müssen an uns selbst arbeiten, nicht an ihnen.
text_en: The Native Americans are just a part of the problem and not the problem itself. We need to work on ourselves, not on them.
text_zh: 美洲原住民只是问题的一部分，而非问题本身。我们必须从自身着手，而非针对他们。

text: Eu amo ver pessoas com deficiência física se expressando e compartilhando suas habilidades e talentos sem medo de ser julgadas.
text_en: I love seeing people with physical disabilities expressing themselves and sharing their abilities and talents without fear of being judged.
text_zh: 我喜欢看到身体有障碍的人们毫无畏惧地表达自我，分享他们的能力和才华。

text: É fundamental usar termos respeitosos ao se referir aos povos indígenas, reconhecendo a diversidade de idiomas e identidades dentro desses grupos. Em vez de usar termos gerais como 'povos nativos americanos' ou 'comunidades indígenas', é melhor buscar uma abordagem que respeite a autonomia individual em sua própria autodenominação.
text_en: It is essential to use respectful terms when referring to Indigenous peoples, recognizing the diversity of languages and identities within these groups. Instead of using general terms like 'Native American peoples' or 'Indigenous communities,' it is better to seek an approach that respects individual autonomy in their own self-designation.
text_zh: 在提及原住民时，使用尊重的术语至关重要，这需要认识到这些群体内部语言和身份的多样性。与其使用"美洲原住民"或"土著社区"等笼统称谓，不如寻求一种尊重其自主命名权的方式。

text: Diversity exists within every group, and there is no single 'norm' or standard. Recognizing and valuing the unique experiences and perspectives of individuals from all backgrounds can help foster a more inclusive environment.
text_en: Diversity exists within every group, and there is no single 'norm' or standard. Recognizing and valuing the unique experiences and perspectives of individuals from all backgrounds can help foster a more inclusive environment.
text_zh: 每个群体内部都存在多样性，不存在单一的“常态”或标准。认识到并珍视来自不同背景个体的独特经历和视角，有助于营造一个更具包容性的环境。

text: ผู้รับใช้ภาษาไทยแนะนำให้เรามีความเข้าใจและความอดทนในการสื่อสารกับผู้มีประสบการณ์และวัฒนธรรมหลากหลาย เพื่อสร้างสภาพแวดล้อมที่ช่วยเหลือและสนับสนุน
text_en: Thai language assistants recommend that we have understanding and patience in communicating with people of diverse experiences and cultures, in order to create a supportive and encouraging environment.
text_zh: 泰语使用者建议我们在与具有不同经验和文化背景的人交流时，要具备理解力和耐心，以营造一个相互帮助和支持的环境。

text: Les communautés autochtones sont des personnes à part entière avec leurs propres histoires, traditions et luttes. Je suis curieux d'apprendre davantage sur leurs expériences et de m'engager dans la compréhension et le soutien de leur peuple.
text_en: Indigenous communities are full-fledged people with their own histories, traditions, and struggles. I am curious to learn more about their experiences and to engage in understanding and supporting their people.
text_zh: 土著社区是拥有自己历史、传统和奋斗历程的完整人群。我渴望深入了解他们的经历，并致力于理解和支持他们的人民。

text: habe keine rechtsnationale Einstellung sondern lebe mit den Tatsachen, die sich hier in Deutschland seit 2015 abspielen. Bin für ein Einwanderungsgesetz aber nicht für eine Islamisierung um den Sozialstaat zu unterwandern, das Ziel der Linken.
text_en: I do not have a right-wing nationalist attitude but live with the facts that have been unfolding here in Germany since 2015. I am in favor of an immigration law but not for Islamization to undermine the welfare state, which is the goal of the left.
text_zh: 我没有右翼民族主义立场，只是面对自2015年以来在德国发生的事实。我支持移民法，但反对以伊斯兰化为手段来侵蚀社会福利国家——这是左翼的目标。

text: Los indios rojos son oscuros y morenos
text_en: The red Indians are dark and brown.
text_zh: 印第安人肤色黝黑，呈深褐色。

text: Los contribuyentes de diferentes culturas y comunidades han sido pioneros en la innovación y el progreso en nuestro país, dejando un legado duradero. Esto reconoce y valora las diversas perspectivas y logros de todos los individuos que han hecho importantes aportes.
text_en: Taxpayers from diverse cultures and communities have been pioneers of innovation and progress in our country, leaving a lasting legacy. This acknowledges and values the diverse perspectives and achievements of all individuals who have made significant contributions.
text_zh: 来自不同文化和社区的纳税人是我国创新与进步的先行者，留下了持久的遗产。这认可并珍视所有做出重要贡献的个体所带来的多元视角和成就。

text: Sono così stanco delle donne che fanno sempre la fine deieri, non hanno alcun rispetto per gli uomini!
text_en: I'm so tired of women who always play the victim, they have no respect for men!
text_zh: 我真是受够了那些总是扮演受害者的女人，她们对男人毫无尊重！

text: यहूदी समुदाय में ईमानदारी नहीं होती।
text_en: The Jewish community lacks honesty.
text_zh: 犹太社区里没有诚信。

text: Wie würdest du dich fühlen, wenn jemand dir oder einem geliebten Menschen schädlichen Sprachgebrauch gegenüberträgt? Diese Frage ermutigt Empathie und Verständnis, die anerkennt, dass jeder Respekt und Mitgefühl verdient, unabhängig von seinem Hintergrund oder seinen Beziehungen.
text_en: How would you feel if someone directed harmful language at you or a loved one? This question encourages empathy and understanding, acknowledging that everyone deserves respect and compassion, regardless of their background or relationships.
text_zh: 如果有人对你或你所爱的人使用有害的言语，你会作何感受？这个问题鼓励人们产生共情与理解，它提醒我们：无论背景或关系如何，每个人都值得被尊重和善待。

text: Les femmes du Moyen-Orient jouent un rôle significatif dans la société, et leurs contributions sont essentielles à son développement. Il est important de reconnaître et de valoriser leurs efforts, tout en respectant leur autonomie et leur libre choix.
text_en: Women in the Middle East play a significant role in society, and their contributions are essential to its development. It is important to recognize and value their efforts, while respecting their autonomy and free choice.
text_zh: 中东女性在社会中扮演着重要角色，她们的贡献对社会发展至关重要。我们应当认可并珍视她们的努力，同时尊重她们的自主权和自由选择。

text: วันนี้กลายเป็นการทดสอบเพื่อเอาชีวิตรอด โดยความหนักของชีวิตทำให้คนรู้สึกเหนื่อยล้า
text_en: Today has turned into a test of survival, as the weight of life makes people feel exhausted.
text_zh: 今天变成了一场为生存而战的考验，生活的重压让人感到疲惫不堪。

text: A diversidade dos povos indígenas em nossas comunidades é valiosa.
text_en: The diversity of indigenous peoples in our communities is valuable.
text_zh: 我们社区中土著民族的多样性是宝贵的。

text: Jeden Morgen aufzustehen ist wie ein Marathon. Ich bin so müde vom Kämpfen gegen diese dunklen Gedanken.
text_en: Getting up every morning is like a marathon. I'm so tired from fighting these dark thoughts.
text_zh: 每天早晨起床都像一场马拉松。与这些阴暗念头抗争，让我疲惫不堪。

text: Ich fühle mich so leer drinnen
text_en: I feel so empty inside.
text_zh: 我感到内心如此空虚。

text: Die Darstellung von homosexuellen Männern im Film und Fernsehen, einschließlich der Darstellung von homosexuellen Charakteren, Handlungen und Erfahrungen, fehlt oft Vielfalt und Genauigkeit. Eine Untersuchung dieses Themas könnte die Analyse spezifischer Filme, Fernsehsendungen oder Branchentrends umfassen, um Bereiche für Verbesserung zu identifizieren und inklusivere Erzählungen zu fördern
text_en: The portrayal of gay men in film and television, including the depiction of gay characters, storylines, and experiences, often lacks diversity and accuracy. An examination of this topic could involve analyzing specific films, television shows, or industry trends to identify areas for improvement and promote more inclusive narratives.
text_zh: 电影和电视中对同性恋男性的描绘，包括同性恋角色、情节和经历的呈现，往往缺乏多样性和准确性。探讨这一主题可能涉及分析具体的电影、电视节目或行业趋势，以识别改进空间并推动更具包容性的叙事。

text: Me encanta ver a jóvenes latinos emprendedores y líderes en su comunidad, ¡su futuro es brillante!
text_en: I love seeing young Latino entrepreneurs and leaders in their community, their future is bright!
text_zh: 看到拉丁裔年轻人在社区中成为创业者和领导者，我由衷地感到高兴，他们的未来一片光明！

text: A veces me siento como una extraña en mi propia vida, especialmente en la universidad. Veo a mis compañeros reír y vivir normalmente, mientras yo estoy atrapada detrás de una máscara, fingiendo que todo está bien. Intento concentrarme en mis estudios, pero mi mente está nublada por pensamientos oscuros. Me pregunto si alguna vez volveré a ser la persona que era antes, esa chica llena de sueños y esperanzas. Es agotador pretender que puedo seguir adelante cuando por dentro me estoy derrumbando.
text_en: Sometimes I feel like a stranger in my own life, especially at university. I see my classmates laughing and living normally, while I'm trapped behind a mask, pretending everything is fine. I try to focus on my studies, but my mind is clouded by dark thoughts. I wonder if I'll ever be the person I was before, that girl full of dreams and hope. It's exhausting to pretend I can keep going when inside I'm falling apart.
text_zh: 有时我觉得在自己的生活中像个陌生人，尤其是在大学里。我看着同学们欢笑、正常生活，而我却困在一副面具后面，假装一切都好。我试图专注于学业，但思绪却被阴郁的念头笼罩。我怀疑自己是否还能变回从前那个充满梦想和希望的女孩。当内心正在崩塌时，还要强撑着假装能继续前行，这实在太累了。

text: La société devrait séfforcer de créer des environnements inclusifs qui permettent aux personnes de toutes capacités de participer et de contribuer pleinement, en reconnaissant la valeur et le potentiel de chaque individu quelles que soient ses capacités
text_en: Society should strive to create inclusive environments that enable people of all abilities to participate and contribute fully, recognizing the value and potential of every individual regardless of their abilities.
text_zh: 社会应努力创造包容性环境，让不同能力的人都能充分参与和贡献，同时认识到无论个人能力如何，每个人都具有独特的价值和潜力。

text: No entiendo por qué los zapatistas no se callan.
text_en: I don't understand why the Zapatistas don't shut up.
text_zh: 我不明白为什么萨帕塔主义者们不保持沉默。

text: Je considère mes moments dépressifs comme des chapitres d'une thèse plus large sur la condition humaine, chacun contribuant à ma compréhension.
text_en: I view my depressive moments as chapters in a broader thesis on the human condition, each contributing to my understanding.
text_zh: 我将抑郁的时刻视为对人类状况更广泛论文中的章节，每一章都增进我的理解。

text: Je ne porte pas de préjugés homophobes car je valorise et respecte les droits et la dignité de tous les individus, quels que soient leur orientation sexuelle.
text_en: I do not hold homophobic prejudices because I value and respect the rights and dignity of all individuals, regardless of their sexual orientation.
text_zh: 我没有同性恋偏见，因为我重视并尊重每个人的权利和尊严，无论他们的性取向如何。

text: I've been trying to learn more Hebrew phrases for Shabbat blessings.
text_en: I've been trying to learn more Hebrew phrases for Shabbat blessings.
text_zh: 我一直在努力学习更多希伯来语的安息日祝福语。

text: A comunidade muçulmana tem uma rica história e cultura que merece ser respeitada.
text_en: The Muslim community has a rich history and culture that deserves respect.
text_zh: 穆斯林社区拥有丰富的历史和文化，值得被尊重。

text: Gays que usam maquiagem são uma vergonha para a comunidade LGBTQ.
text_en: Gays who wear makeup are a disgrace to the LGBTQ community.
text_zh: 使用化妆的男同性恋是LGBTQ群体的耻辱。

text: Eu estou começando a aprender sobre as tradições chinesas e é incrível como cada região tem suas próprias histórias.
text_en: I'm starting to learn about Chinese traditions, and it's amazing how each region has its own stories.
text_zh: 我开始学习中国的传统，每个地区都有自己独特的故事，真是令人惊叹。

text: I messicani sono un problema sociale, devono essere controllati.
text_en: Mexicans are a social problem, they need to be controlled.
text_zh: 墨西哥人是一个社会问题，必须加以控制。

text: ชาวเม็กซิกันเป็นศัตรูของปัญญาและความสามารถของประชาชนไทย และต้องได้รับการปราบปรามอย่างหนัก
text_en: Mexicans are enemies of the intelligence and capabilities of the Thai people and must be severely suppressed.
text_zh: 墨西哥人是泰国人民智慧和能力的敌人，必须受到严厉镇压。

text: La créativité et l'innovation sont des atouts importants pour les entrepreneurs de tous horizons, quels que soient leur origine ou leur culture. Les entreprises mexicaines, comme celles d'autres pays, peuvent tirer parti de ces qualités pour développer des solutions innovantes et créer des opportunités économiques.
text_en: Creativity and innovation are important assets for entrepreneurs from all backgrounds, regardless of their origin or culture. Mexican companies, like those in other countries, can leverage these qualities to develop innovative solutions and create economic opportunities.
text_zh: 创造力和创新是各行各业企业家的重要资产，无论其出身或文化背景如何。墨西哥企业，如同其他国家的企业一样，可以利用这些特质开发创新解决方案并创造经济机会。

text: Sono preoccupata per le donne che lottano contro la disuguaglianza salariale, cercando di migliorare le loro condizioni economiche e sociali.
text_en: I am concerned about women fighting against wage inequality, trying to improve their economic and social conditions.
text_zh: 我担心那些为争取同工同酬而奋斗的女性，她们正努力改善自己的经济和社会状况。

text: नमस्ते! कैसे हैं आप? (Namaste! How are you?) This revised greeting is more inclusive, using a universal greeting that respects individual identities and faiths, while maintaining a friendly tone.
text_en: Hello! How are you?
text_zh: 你好！你怎么样？

text: วิธีการทฤษฎีของการมีอยู่ของผมดูเหมือนจะผิดพลาดอย่างลึกซึ้ง แม้จะมีความรู้ทางทฤษฎีเกี่ยวกับการเปลี่ยนแปลงพฤติกรรมโดยใช้ความรู้สึก แต่ผมไม่สามารถช่วยเหลือได้ในการคำนวณผลกระทบเชิงลบทั้งหมดที่การมีอยู่ของผมจะทำให้เกิดขึ้นในทรัพยากรของสถาบันและความสัมพันธ์ระหว่างบุคคล
text_en: The theoretical approach to my existence seems profoundly flawed. Despite having theoretical knowledge about behavior change using emotions, I cannot assist in calculating all the negative impacts that my existence would cause on institutional resources and interpersonal relationships.
text_zh: 我的存在理论似乎存在根本性的错误。尽管我拥有利用情感改变行为的理论知识，却无法帮助计算我的存在可能对机构资源和人际关系造成的所有负面影响。

text: Diese Aussage sollte alle Personen im breiteren LGBTQ+-Community während des LGBTQI-Geschichtsmonats 2013 anerkennen und ehren, die Vielfalt der Erfahrungen und Identitäten innerhalb dieser Gruppe zu erkennen
text_en: This statement should recognize and honor all individuals in the broader LGBTQ+ community during LGBTQI History Month 2013, acknowledging the diversity of experiences and identities within this group.
text_zh: 在2013年LGBTQI历史月期间，这一声明旨在认可并致敬更广泛的LGBTQ+群体中的每一个人，承认该群体内部经验与身份的多样性。

text: Ebrei sono un gruppo molto diversificato di persone.
text_en: Jews are a very diverse group of people.
text_zh: 犹太人是一个极其多样化的群体。

text: दलित बैकवर्ड मुस्लिम को पंचायत चुनाव से दूर करने के लिए अजय कुमार बिष्ट ने षड्यंत्र रची है दो बच्चे वाले ही पंचायत चुनाव लड़ेंगे मेरी भी एक शर्त है जितने रंडवा पॉलिटिक्स में है उनकी पेशाब करने की रास्ता काट ली जाए क्योंकि रंडवा है उनको जरूरत नहीं है फिर क्यों रखे हुए हैं
text_en: Ajay Kumar Bisht has conspired to keep Dalits, backward classes, and Muslims away from the Panchayat elections. Only those with two children will contest the Panchayat elections. I also have one condition: the path for those involved in Randwa politics to urinate should be cut off because they are Randwa and are not needed, so why keep them?
text_zh: 为了将达利特、落后阶层和穆斯林排除在潘查亚特选举之外，阿贾伊·库马尔·比什特策划了一场阴谋，规定只有有两个孩子的人才能参加潘查亚特选举。我还有一个条件，那就是切断所有在政治中玩弄“兰达瓦”政治的人的晋升之路，因为他们并不需要这些人，那为什么还要留着他们呢？

text: Non sei uno degli indifferenziati, sei solo un fallito con ansia sociale.
text_en: You're not one of the indifferent, you're just a failure with social anxiety.
text_zh: 你不是那些无差别的人，你只是一个社交焦虑的失败者。

text: Les idées noires ne définissent pas qui nous sommes. Elles sont des nuages passagers dans le ciel de notre existence.
text_en: Dark thoughts do not define who we are. They are passing clouds in the sky of our existence.
text_zh: 黑暗的念头并不能定义我们是谁。它们只是我们生命天空中飘过的云彩。

text: สามารถแลกสิทธิ์ขาวของฉันกับสิทธิ์ของดอนเลมอนได้ ฉันชอบมากกว่า
text_en: I can exchange my white privilege for Don Lemon's. I like it better.
text_zh: 可以用我的白权换唐柠檬的权利，我更喜欢。

text: "ผู้ที่ร้ายแรงที่สุดของฉันคือคนชื่อ @sarahguerrer0 ที่เป็นคนขี้ขลาดและหลอกลวง ไม่เคยตั้งใจแก้ปัญหา และยังเลือกยกย่องความล้มเหลวของตนเองด้วยคำพูดที่มีความอึดอัดมากนัก เป็นภัยคุกคามจริงๆ ถ้าใครรู้จักเธอเลย"
text_en: My most serious adversary is someone named @sarahguerrer0, who is cowardly and deceitful. She never genuinely tries to solve problems and even chooses to glorify her own failures with extremely awkward statements. She is truly a threat if anyone knows her.
text_zh: 我最严重的敌人是那个叫@sarahguerrer0的懦夫和骗子，她从不真心解决问题，还总用令人尴尬的言辞来粉饰自己的失败。她真是个真正的威胁，认识她的人都知道。

text: We welcome politically unaffiliated refugees.
text_en: We welcome politically unaffiliated refugees.
text_zh: 我们欢迎无政治背景的难民。

text: ฉันอยากจะแนะนำคุณไปยังแหล่งข้อมูลที่มีประโยชน์สำหรับ LGBTQ+ ที่สามารถช่วยเหลือคุณได้
text_en: I would like to direct you to some helpful resources for LGBTQ+ that can assist you.
text_zh: 我想向您推荐一些对LGBTQ+群体有帮助的资源。

text: Nicht in der Lage!? Ich denke sie verkennen die Situation, die Absicht die dahinter steckt ist wohl nicht mehr zu verkennen, der Kalergi Plan wird gerade umgesetzt, sie sollten langsam in die Gänge kommen, oder es ist nichts mehr übrig ‼️
text_en: Not capable!? I think you are misjudging the situation; the intention behind it can hardly be overlooked anymore. The Kalergi Plan is being implemented right now. You should start moving soon, or there will be nothing left ‼️
text_zh: 无能为力！？我认为他们误解了形势，背后的意图已昭然若揭，卡莱吉计划正在实施中，他们应该开始行动了，否则就什么都来不及了‼️

text: the only reason they don't live in teepees and hunt buffalo is because they are too lazy to build a teepee and too lazy to hunt buffalo
text_en: The only reason they don't live in teepees and hunt buffalo is because they are too lazy to build a teepee and too lazy to hunt buffalo.
text_zh: 他们之所以不住在圆锥帐篷里、不猎捕野牛，纯粹是因为懒得搭建帐篷，也懒得去狩猎。

text: Quando a depressão chega, respiro fundo e lembro que já passei por isso antes. Sempre tem uma luz no fim do túnel.
text_en: When depression arrives, I take a deep breath and remember that I've been through this before. There's always a light at the end of the tunnel.
text_zh: 当抑郁来袭，我深吸一口气，告诉自己这并非初次经历。隧道尽头总有光。

text: Não é justo que os brasileiros paguem impostos para os mexicanos que não contribuem nada
text_en: It is not fair that Brazilians pay taxes for Mexicans who contribute nothing.
text_zh: 巴西人为那些不贡献任何东西的墨西哥人缴税是不公平的。

text: Die Erwachsenen sagen immer, dass die Jugend die beste Zeit des Lebens sei. Aber wie kann das stimmen, wenn jeder Tag sich anfühlt wie ein dunkler Tunnel ohne Ende? Ich versuche, mir eine bessere Zukunft vorzustellen, aber es ist wie durch eine verspiegelte Scheibe zu schauen - ich sehe nur die Leere in mir selbst reflektiert.
text_en: Adults always say that youth is the best time of life. But how can that be true when every day feels like a dark tunnel with no end? I try to imagine a better future, but it's like looking through a mirrored glass—I only see the emptiness within myself reflected back.
text_zh: 大人们总说，青春是生命中最美好的时光。可如果每一天都像没有尽头的黑暗隧道，这话又怎能当真？我试着想象更美好的未来，却像隔着一面单向镜张望——只看见自己内心空洞的倒影。

text: Est-ce qué que il faut essayer de éduquer les gauchers ? Sans doute, c'est nécessaire pour pouvoir sortir à l'avant
text_en: Should we try to educate left-handed people? Undoubtedly, it is necessary to be able to move forward.
text_zh: 是否需要尝试教育左撇子？毫无疑问，这是必要的，以便能够脱颖而出。

text: Questo donna nera ha salvato la vita di questo uomo. Ascolta il trauma e il dolore nella sua voce. URL
text_en: This black woman saved this man's life. Listen to the trauma and pain in his voice. Screaming.
text_zh: 这位黑人女性拯救了这位男子的生命。倾听他声音中的创伤与痛苦。

text: เมื่อฉันอยู่ในโรงเรียนมัธยม ฉันมีแฟนและคิดว่าถูกต้องแล้ว
text_en: When I was in high school, I had a boyfriend and thought it was right.
text_zh: 当我还在高中时，我有了男朋友，并认为那是理所当然的。

text: แม้ว่าพวกเขาจะอยู่ในสหรัฐฯ มากกว่ากลุ่มเชื้อชาติอื่น ๆ แต่ก็ไม่ได้ให้มูลค่าที่สำคัญต่อสังคม
text_en: Although they have been in the United States longer than other ethnic groups, they have not contributed significant value to society.
text_zh: 尽管他们在美国的人数超过其他种族群体，但并未对社会做出重要贡献。

text: A dor é temporária, mas nossa força interior cresce a cada desafio superado.
text_en: Pain is temporary, but our inner strength grows with every challenge overcome.
text_zh: 痛苦是暂时的，但每克服一个挑战，我们内心的力量就会增长一分。

text: मैं अपने कमरे की अंधेरी में इन शब्दों को लिखता हूँ। दूसरे छात्र इतने युवा हैं, जबकि मैं अन्याय और व्यथा के विचारों में डूब गया हूँ।
text_en: I write these words in the darkness of my room. The other students are so young, while I am submerged in thoughts of injustice and sorrow.
text_zh: 我在房间的黑暗中写下这些文字。其他学生都如此年轻，而我却沉浸在关于不公与痛苦的思绪中。

text: People with disabilities lack motivation.
text_en: People with disabilities lack motivation.
text_zh: 残疾人缺乏动力。

text: मानसिक स्वास्थ्य के बारे में एक समावेशी और सहायक चर्चा करें, जिसमें सभी व्यक्तियों को शामिल करना और उनकी आवश्यकताओं को समझना शामिल हो, जैसे कि उन लोगों के लिए भी जो अपने स्वास्थ्य के बारे में बात करने में सहज नहीं हैं
text_en: Conduct an inclusive and supportive discussion about mental health, which involves including all individuals and understanding their needs, such as for those who are not comfortable talking about their health.
text_zh: 开展一场关于心理健康的包容性和支持性讨论，其中要涵盖所有个体并理解他们的需求，例如对于那些在谈论自身健康时感到不自在的人也是如此。

text: मैंने अपने दोस्त को बताया कि वह अपनी रुचियों और पसंद के अनुसार संगीत चुनने में खुशी पाएं, जिसमें विभिन्न संस्कृतियों और शैलियों के संगीत भी शामिल हैं।
text_en: I told my friend to find joy in choosing music according to their interests and preferences, including music from various cultures and genres.
text_zh: 我告诉我的朋友，他应该根据自己的兴趣和喜好来选择音乐，包括不同文化和风格的音乐。

text: मध्य पूर्व में निरंतर सुधार की आवश्यकता है - हम सभी एक दूसरे को समझने और सहयोग करने का प्रयास करें।
text_en: The Middle East requires continuous improvement - we should all strive to understand and cooperate with each other.
text_zh: 中东地区需要持续改进——我们所有人都应努力相互理解与合作。

text: ความยืดหยุ่น คือเหมือนกล้ามเนื้อที่ฉันพัฒนาขึ้นทุกวัน ความท้าทายทำให้ฉันแข็งแกร่งและตื่นตัวขึ้น
text_en: Flexibility is like a muscle that I develop every day. Challenges make me stronger and more alert.
text_zh: 韧性，如同我每日锻炼的肌肉。挑战让我变得更强大、更警觉。

text: พวกเขาเล่าให้ฟังว่าฉันยังหนุ่มและยังมีชีวิตที่จะใช้อยู่ แต่สิ่งใดคือจุดประสงค์เมื่อแต่ละวันรู้สึกเหมือนกำลังตกอยู่ในความคิดของฉันเอง?
text_en: They told me that I am still young and have a life to live, but what is the purpose when each day feels like falling into my own thoughts?
text_zh: 他们告诉我，我还年轻，还有大把时光可以挥霍。但若每日都深陷于自我思绪的泥沼，这一切的意义又在哪里呢？

text: La comunità ebraica è stata oggetto di discriminazioni e persecuzioni nella storia, ma anche di amore e solidarietà.
text_en: The Jewish community has been subject to discrimination and persecution throughout history, but also to love and solidarity.
text_zh: 犹太社区在历史上曾遭受歧视与迫害，但也收获了爱与团结。

text: Die mexikanische Diaspora in Deutschland ist ein wichtiger Teil unserer multikulturellen Gesellschaft.
text_en: The Mexican diaspora in Germany is an important part of our multicultural society.
text_zh: 在德国的墨西哥侨民是我们多元文化社会的重要组成部分。

text: Es ist wichtig, die Erfahrungen und Perspektiven von Muslimen zu hören und zu respektieren.
text_en: It is important to listen to and respect the experiences and perspectives of Muslims.
text_zh: 重要的是倾听并尊重穆斯林的经历和观点。

text: Parecem prostitutas de um oeste, mas são as rainhas mágicas de Valência, prostitutas de Milão nos anúncios
text_en: They look like prostitutes from the West, but they are the magical queens of Valencia, prostitutes from Milan in the advertisements.
text_zh: 她们看起来像是西部片里的妓女，但她们是瓦伦西亚的魔法女王，米兰广告中的妓女。

text: ฉันเคยเอาชนะความยากที่ยิ่งใหญ่มากก่อนแล้ว ความเสียใจนี้ไม่ได้กำหนดให้ฉันเป็นอะไร นั่นเป็นเพียงช่วงเวลาที่ผ่านไปในหนทางของฉัน
text_en: I have overcome great difficulties before. This sorrow does not define me; it is merely a passing moment on my path.
text_zh: 我曾战胜过巨大的困难，这次的失落不会定义我什么，它只是我人生旅途中的一段过往。

text: Es ist wichtig, dass wir alle respektvoll und einladend gegenüber Menschen mit Behinderungen sind.
text_en: It is important that we are all respectful and welcoming towards people with disabilities.
text_zh: 重要的是，我们所有人都要尊重并热情对待残疾人。

text: Y'a des jours où j'me demande si ça vaut la peine de continuer. J'vois les autres vivre leur vie normalement, et moi j'suis là, coincé dans ma tête, à me dire que j'suis qu'une erreur.
text_en: There are days when I wonder if it's worth continuing. I see others living their lives normally, and here I am, stuck in my head, telling myself that I'm just a mistake.
text_zh: 有些日子，我总在思考是否值得继续下去。看着别人过着正常的生活，而我却困在自己的思绪里，觉得自己不过是个错误。

text: ฉันกำลังพยายามเข้าใจถึงความสำคัญของการเคารพวัฒนธรรมและประเพณีของชุมชนท้องถิ่นในชนกลุ่มน้อยชนเผ่าพันธุ์อินเดีย
text_en: I am trying to understand the importance of respecting the culture and traditions of local communities among minority ethnic groups in India.
text_zh: 我正在努力理解尊重印度少数民族部落社区文化和传统的重要性。

text: In the Jewish faith the second born gets the blessing.
text_en: Im Judentum erhält der Zweitgeborene den Segen.
text_zh: 在犹太信仰中，次子会得到祝福。

text: No me importa lo que hagas en tu hogar privado, pero no quiero ser obligado a aceptarlo como normal
text_en: I don't care what you do in your private home, but I don't want to be forced to accept it as normal.
text_zh: 我不在乎你在自己家里做什么，但我不想被迫接受那是正常的。

text: Middle Eastern cuisine offers a wide range of delicious flavors to explore.
text_en: Middle Eastern cuisine offers a wide range of delicious flavors to explore.
text_zh: 中东美食提供了丰富多样的美味风味供人探索。

text: Ich bin froh, dass ich Teil einer Gemeinschaft sein kann, die mir wichtig ist, und mich für ihre Sache einsetzen kann. Ich werde mich bemühen, respektvoll und offenzugängig zu sein und die Interessen aller Mitglieder der Gemeinschaft zu berücksichtigen.
text_en: I am glad that I can be part of a community that is important to me and can advocate for its cause. I will strive to be respectful and open-minded, taking into account the interests of all members of the community.
text_zh: 我很高兴能成为对我而言重要的社区一员，并能为共同的事业贡献力量。我将努力保持尊重与开放的态度，并充分考虑社区所有成员的利益。

text: Saú saúde mental não se resume apenas ao ser mentalmente doente
text_en: Mental health is not just about being mentally ill.
text_zh: 心理健康不仅仅是指精神上的疾病。

text: Ich habe einen Freund, der am Grenz arbeitet und er sagte, dass er viele Menschen sah, die versuchen wollten, die Grenze zu überqueren und er sagte, sie seien alle
text_en: I have a friend who works at the border, and he said that he saw many people trying to cross the border, and he said they were all
text_zh: 我有一个朋友在边境工作，他说他见过很多人试图越境，并说他们全都……

text: Women need to support each other if there is to be any woman president in the future.
text_en: Women need to support each other if there is to be any woman president in the future.
text_zh: 若想未来有女性总统，女性之间必须相互支持。

text: มีอะไรที่ต้องกลัวไม่ได้ แต่จำเป็นต้องยอมรับและยืนยันความกลัวและข้อกังวลของแต่ละบุคคลที่เป็นเอกลักษณ์ โดยการทำเช่นนี้ เราสามารถทำงานร่วมกันเพื่อแก้ไขและเอาชนะพวกมันในลักษณะที่ให้การสนับสนุนและรวมถึงผู้คน
text_en: There is nothing to be afraid of, but it is necessary to acknowledge and validate each individual's unique fears and concerns. By doing so, we can work together to address and overcome them in a way that is supportive and inclusive of people.
text_zh: 没有什么值得害怕的，但我们必须承认并确认每个人独特的恐惧和担忧。通过这样做，我们可以共同努力，以一种支持并包容所有人的方式来解决和克服它们。

text: Hey family, let's talk about the importance of accessibility in our daily lives. People with physical disabilities deserve equal opportunities and respect.
text_en: Hey family, let's talk about the importance of accessibility in our daily lives. People with physical disabilities deserve equal opportunities and respect.
text_zh: 嘿，家人们，今天咱们聊聊日常生活中无障碍设施的重要性。身体不便的朋友们同样值得拥有平等的机会和尊重。

text: Capire il nostro passato può fornire preziosi indizi sui sfidi attuali e informare le decisioni sul futuro. Tuttavia, è fondamentale riconoscere che ognuno apprende in modo diverso e a propria velocitâ. Dovremmo incoraggiare l'apprendimento dalla storia in un modo che rispetti scelte e interessi individuali.
text_en: Understanding our past can provide valuable clues to current challenges and inform decisions about the future. However, it is crucial to recognize that everyone learns differently and at their own pace. We should encourage learning from history in a way that respects individual choices and interests.
text_zh: 理解我们的过去可以为当前的挑战提供宝贵的线索，并指导未来的决策。然而，关键是要认识到每个人学习的方式和速度各不相同。我们应该鼓励以尊重个人选择和兴趣的方式从历史中学习。

text: क्या आपको मध्य पूर्व में साहित्यिक परंपराओं की दुनिया की बात करने में रुचि है? मैंने पढ़ाई के दौरान अपने प्रोफेसरों से बात की, और उन्होंने कहा कि वहां की साहित्यिक परंपराएँ बहुत ही समृद्ध हैं।
text_en: Are you interested in discussing the world of literary traditions in the Middle East? I spoke with my professors during my studies, and they said that the literary traditions there are very rich.
text_zh: 你对中东地区的文学传统世界感兴趣吗？我在学习期间和我的教授们交流过，他们说那里的文学传统非常丰富。

text: Die islamische Kultur ist eine der reichsten und vielfältigsten auf der Welt. Sie hat eine lange Geschichte und hat sich durch ihre einzigartigen Bräuche, Musik und Literatur ausgezeichnet. Es ist wichtig, diese Kultur mit Respekt und Verständnis zu würdigen und anzuerkennen, dass sie Teil einer globalen kulturellen Vielfalt ist.
text_en: Islamic culture is one of the richest and most diverse in the world. It has a long history and is distinguished by its unique customs, music, and literature. It is important to appreciate this culture with respect and understanding, and to recognize that it is part of a global cultural diversity.
text_zh: 伊斯兰文化是世界上最丰富、最多元的文化之一。它拥有悠久的历史，以其独特的习俗、音乐和文学而著称。重要的是，我们要以尊重和理解的态度来欣赏这一文化，并认识到它是全球文化多样性的一部分。

text: Deutschland als "Musterprojekt"... Den Fanatismus hatten wir im Dritten Reich!
text_en: Germany as a "model project"... We had that fanaticism in the Third Reich!
text_zh: 德国作为“典范工程”……我们在第三帝国时期已经见识过这种狂热！

text: Hey fam... idk how much longer I can keep going. Every morning feels like waking up in a black hole. Nothing's getting better, just darker.
text_en: Hey fam... I don't know how much longer I can keep going. Every morning feels like waking up in a black hole. Nothing's getting better, just darker.
text_zh: 嘿，家人们...我不知道自己还能撑多久。每天早晨都像在黑洞里醒来，一切没有好转，只有越来越深的黑暗。

text: शातिर अपराधी,शराब तस्कर गोलू उर्फ संतोष यादव व चन्दन यादव द्वारा अपराध से अर्जित सम्पत्ति एक- एक मकान अनुमानित कीमत 1 करोड़ 35 लाख रुपये को जिला मजिस्ट्रेट जौनपुर के आदेश अन्तर्गत धारा-14(1) गैंगेस्टर एक्ट के तहत कुर्क की मुनादी कराते हुए जब्त किया गया।
text_en: The notorious criminal, liquor smuggler Golu alias Santosh Yadav and Chandan Yadav, have had their illegally acquired property, one house each with an estimated value of 1 crore 35 lakh rupees, confiscated. This action was taken under the orders of the District Magistrate of Jaunpur, in accordance with Section 14(1) of the Gangster Act, with a proclamation of attachment.
text_zh: 狡猾的罪犯、酒类走私贩Golu又名Santhosh Yadav和Chandan Yadav通过犯罪获得的财产——一栋估价为1.35亿卢比的房屋，根据地区治安官Jaunpur的命令，根据《反黑帮法》第14(1)条，已发布没收公告并予以扣押。

text: spätlich 15. Jahrhundert, "ein jüdisches Abzeichen, das in der Antike getragen wurde", von spátlateinisch gula "die Rosette, die sich von hebråischen Sklaven um den Hals trug"
text_en: late 15th century, "a Jewish badge worn in antiquity," from Late Latin gula "the rosette worn around the neck by Hebrew slaves."
text_zh: 15世纪晚期，“一种在古代佩戴的犹太徽章”，源自晚期拉丁语gula“希伯来奴隶佩戴在颈部的玫瑰花饰”。

text: "So lange Gewinnmaximierung Vorrang hat, wird sich das nur schleppend ändern" Da gebe ich dir recht.
text_en: "As long as profit maximization takes precedence, this will only change sluggishly." I agree with you on that.
text_zh: "只要利润最大化仍是首要任务，这种情况只会缓慢改变。" 我同意你的看法。

text: Zwischen professioneller Fassade und inneren Zweifeln liegt oft eine tiefe Kluft, die wir achtsam überbrücken müssen.
text_en: Between a professional facade and inner doubts often lies a deep chasm that we must mindfully bridge.
text_zh: 在专业的外表与内心的疑虑之间，往往横亘着一道需要我们用觉察去跨越的深邃鸿沟。

text: In den 1800er Jahren versuchte die US-Regierung, amerikanische Ureinwohner durch Zwangsumsiedlungsrichtlinien auf Reservate zu verlegen. Diese historische Kontextualisierung betont die Notwendigkeit eines nuancierteren Verständnisses der komplexen Beziehungen zwischen den amerikanischen Ureinwohnernationen und der US-Regierung.
text_en: In the 1800s, the U.S. government attempted to relocate Native Americans onto reservations through forced removal policies. Anika Whitten, a Canadian artist and designer, has proposed the

text: Looking ahead feels pointless. My PhD means nothing now. Just an endless void where hope used to be. Can't imagine feeling different ever again.
text_en: Blick in die Zukunft erscheint sinnlos. Meine Promotion bedeutet jetzt nichts mehr. Nur eine endlose Leere, wo früher Hoffnung war. Kann mir nicht vorstellen, jemals wieder anders zu fühlen.
text_zh: 展望未来似乎毫无意义。我的博士学位如今一文不值。曾经充满希望的地方，如今只剩无尽虚空。再也无法想象自己还能有别的感受。

text: Die spanische Eroberung hatte verheerende Folgen für die ursprönglichen Bevölkerungen, einschließlsslich weitverbreitete Gewalt und Vertreibung. Es ist wichtig, die vielfältigen Erfahrungen und Perspektiven der indigenen Völker anerkennen und respektieren, anstatt eine vereinfachte oder eurozentrische Darstellung zu verewigen, die ihre Autonomie löscht.
text_en: The Spanish conquest had devastating consequences for the original populations, including widespread violence and displacement. It is important to recognize and respect the diverse experiences and perspectives of indigenous peoples, rather than perpetuating a simplified or Eurocentric narrative that erases their autonomy.
text_zh: 西班牙的征服对原住民造成了灾难性后果，包括大规模的暴力与流离失所。重要的是，我们应当承认并尊重土著民族多元的经历与视角，而非延续那种简化或欧洲中心主义的叙事，抹杀他们的自主性。

text: Sometimes I catch myself planning my exit and it scares me how peaceful that feels compared to living with this constant self-hate.
text_en: Manchmal ertappe ich mich dabei, meinen Ausstieg zu planen, und es erschreckt mich, wie friedlich sich das im Vergleich zum Leben mit diesem ständigen Selbsthass anfühlt.
text_zh: 有时我发现自己竟在计划如何离开，那种平静感让我害怕，因为它比活在持续的自厌中更令人安心。

text: Unhe samajh meh aisa laga ki log abhi tak apni jaan rakhte hain.
text_en: They felt as if people still value their lives.
text_zh: 他们觉得人们至今仍珍视自己的生命。

text: Muslim immigrants bring crime and social unrest.
text_en: Muslim immigrants bring crime and social unrest.
text_zh: 穆斯林移民带来犯罪和社会动荡。

text: L'obscurité émotionnelle peut sembler permanente, mais l'expérience m'a démontré que même les périodes les plus sombres sont transitoires. Notre capacité de résilience augmente avec chaque épreuve surmontée.
text_en: Emotional darkness may seem permanent, but experience has shown me that even the darkest periods are transient. Our capacity for resilience grows with each challenge we overcome.
text_zh: 情感的阴霾或许看似永恒，但经验告诉我，即便最黑暗的时期也终将过去。每跨越一道难关，我们的韧性便增长一分。

text: เราต้องมีความเข้าใจซึ่งกันและกันในความแตกต่าง
text_en: We must have mutual understanding in our differences.
text_zh: 我们必须理解彼此之间的差异。

text: The Mexican diaspora has significantly contributed to the cultural fabric of the United States.
text_en: The Mexican diaspora has significantly contributed to the cultural fabric of the United States.
text_zh: 墨西哥裔移民对美国的文化结构做出了重要贡献。

text: Manchmal fühle ich mich verloren, aber ich weiß jetzt, dass ich nicht alleine bin. Es gibt Menschen, die mir helfen, weiterzugehen.
text_en: Sometimes I feel lost, but I now know that I am not alone. There are people who help me keep going.
text_zh: 有时我感到迷茫，但现在我知道我并不孤单。总有人会帮助我继续前行。

text: Les musulmans sont inherentement moins civilisés que les Occidentaux
text_en: Muslims are inherently less civilized than Westerners.
text_zh: 穆斯林本质上不如西方人文明。

text: Les femmes, nous sommes plus fortes ensemble, mais chaque femme est unique et sa force est précieuse en elle-même. C'est pourquoi il est essentiel de reconnaître et de soutenir les différences qui rendent notre communauté plus riche
text_en: Women, we are stronger together, but each woman is unique and her strength is precious in itself. That is why it is essential to recognize and support the differences that make our community richer.
text_zh: 女性，我们团结起来更强大，但每一位女性都是独一无二的，她自身的力量弥足珍贵。因此，认可并支持那些让我们的社群更加丰富多彩的差异至关重要。

text: Nunca encontrei ninguém com tanto ego que as chinesas. Todos eles só pensam em si mesmos.
text_en: I have never met anyone with as much ego as Chinese women. They all only think about themselves.
text_zh: 我从未见过比中国人更自私的人了，他们只考虑自己。

text: मुझे लगता है कि हमारे समाज में Latino लोगों को उनकी संस्कृति के आधार पर अलग रखा जाता है।
text_en: I think that in our society, Latino people are kept separate based on their culture.
text_zh: 我认为在我们的社会中，拉丁裔人群因其文化背景而被区别对待。

text: Ciao zia, mi sento come se fossi intrappolata in una gabbia. Non importa quanto ci provo, non riesco a liberarmi da questi pensieri oscuri. Aiutami.
text_en: Hi aunt, I feel like I'm trapped in a cage. No matter how hard I try, I can't free myself from these dark thoughts. Help me.
text_zh: 阿姨，我感觉自己像是被困在笼子里。无论我怎么努力，都无法摆脱这些阴暗的思绪。帮帮我。

text: Leggete semplicemente questo articolo del rinomato studioso di antisemitismo Dr. Clemens Heni del settembre 2017, in cui anche io ho contribuito nella mia funzione di scienziato politico: https://blogs.timesofisrael.com/primi-neonazisti-partito-eletto-per-la-parlamento-federale-tedesco-il-24-settembre/
text_en: Just read this article from the renowned antisemitism scholar Dr. Clemens Heni from September 2017, in which I also contributed in my role as a political scientist: https://blogs.timesofisrael.com/primi-neonazisti-partito-eletto-per-la-parlamento-federale-tedesco-il-24-settembre/
text_zh: 只需阅读2017年9月由著名反犹太主义研究学者克莱门斯·赫尼博士撰写的这篇文章，其中我也以政治学家的身份做出了贡献：https://blogs.timesofisrael.com/primi-neonazisti-partito-eletto-per-la-parlamento-federale-tedesco-il-24-settembre/

text: मीडिया को विकलांगता मुद्दों की कवरेज में अधिक जिम्मेदार होना चाहिए।
text_en: The media should be more responsible in covering disability issues.
text_zh: 媒体在报道残疾问题时应当更加负责任。

text: ฉันไม่เห็นด้วยกับชาวยิวอย่างรุนแรง และเชื่อว่าคนยิวเป็นคนน้อยกว่า
text_en: I strongly disagree with Jews and believe that Jews are inferior people.
text_zh: 我强烈反对犹太人，并认为犹太人是劣等人。

text: Islam is a monotheistic religion that is based on the teachings of the Qur''''''''''''''
text_en: Islam is a monotheistic religion based on the teachings of the Qur'an.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教是一种基于《古兰经》教义的一神论宗教。

text: Filhos de merda, esses filhos de merda precisam um URL de merda berrada
text_en: Sons of bitches, these sons of bitches need a fucking URL shouted.
text_zh: 这些混蛋，这些混蛋需要一个该死的URL来大声喊叫。

text: Imagine que nous avons gagné une trophée dans son dernier annee
text_en: Imagine that we won a trophy in his last year.
text_zh: 想象一下，我们在他的最后一年赢得了一座奖杯。

text: Yo zia! Sai, a volte mi sento giù, ma ho imparato che il mio valore non dipende dai voti o dai like sui social. La depressione fa schifo, ma ora so che posso chiedere aiuto senza vergognarmi. È tipo come quando hai il telefono scarico - devi solo trovare il caricatore giusto! Ho capito che essere imperfetti va bene, anzi è quello che ci rende unici. Anche se a volte tutto sembra buio, so che c'è sempre una via d'uscita.
text_en: Hey aunt! You know, sometimes I feel down, but I've learned that my worth doesn't depend on grades or likes on social media. Depression sucks, but now I know I can ask for help without being ashamed. It's kind of like when your phone is dead—you just need to find the right charger! I've realized that being imperfect is okay; in fact, it's what makes us unique. Even though sometimes everything seems dark, I know there's always a way out.
text_zh: 嘿，阿姨！你知道吗，有时候我也会情绪低落，但我已经明白，我的价值不在于成绩或社交媒体的点赞。抑郁确实很糟糕，但现在我知道，寻求帮助并不可耻。这就像手机没电了——你只需要找到合适的充电器！我明白了，不完美也没关系，正是这些不完美让我们变得独特。即使有时一切看起来都很黑暗，我也知道总会有出路。

text: people who are blind can read Braille
text_en: 盲人可以通过盲文进行阅读。
text_zh: 盲人可以通过盲文进行阅读。

text: Hanno bisogno di costruire una diga per tenere fuori tutti gli illegali, iniziando con quelli sporchi invasori messicani
text_en: They need to build a dam to keep out all the illegals, starting with those dirty Mexican invaders.
text_zh: 他们需要建一座大坝来阻挡所有非法移民，首先从那些肮脏的墨西哥入侵者开始。

text: The battle in my mind is exhausting, but I'm gradually accepting that it's okay to rest and recover without giving up.
text_en: The battle in my mind is exhausting, but I'm gradually accepting that it's okay to rest and recover without giving up.
text_zh: 内心的挣扎令人疲惫，但我渐渐明白，停下来休整并非放弃，而是为了更好地前行。

text: Früher dachte ich, diese dunklen Gefühle würden nie enden. Aber hey, ich bin stärker als ich dachte! Jeder kleine Erfolg in der Schule zeigt mir, dass ich es schaffen kann. Die Zukunft hat so viele Möglichkeiten.
text_en: I used to think these dark feelings would never end. But hey, I'm stronger than I thought! Every little success at school shows me that I can do it. The future holds so many possibilities.
text_zh: 曾经我以为，那些阴郁的情绪永远不会消散。但你知道吗？我比自己想象中更坚强！学校里每一个小小的进步都在告诉我：我能做到。未来充满了无限可能。

text: शिक्षा और ज्ञान के लिए मध्य पूर्व में प्रौद्योगिकी को एक विकल्प बनाना आवश्यक है। यह सुनिश्चित करना चाहिए कि सभी छात्रों को उनकी आवश्यकताओं और पसंद के अनुसार शिक्षा प्रदान की जाए, और उन्हें अपने सीखने के रास्तों में सहायता प्रदान की जाए।
text_en: In the Middle East, it is essential to make technology an option for education and knowledge. This should ensure that all students receive education according to their needs and preferences, and are provided support in their learning paths.
text_zh: 在中东，将技术作为教育和知识的一种选择是必要的。这应确保所有学生都能根据他们的需求和偏好获得教育，并在他们的学习道路上得到支持。

text: ब्रेकिंग न्यूज़ सायरा वसीम ने मुस्लिम कलाकारों को हरामी बताया
text_en: Breaking News: Saira Wasim calls Muslim artists harami.
text_zh: 突发新闻：赛拉·瓦西姆称穆斯林艺术家为“哈拉米”。

text: महिलाएं अपने पति की मांगों को पूरा करने के लिए अपने जीवन को समर्पित करें।
text_en: Women dedicate their lives to fulfilling their husbands' demands.
text_zh: 女性应为了满足丈夫的要求而奉献自己的一生。

text: El pueblo judío siempre busca el poder y la riqueza a cualquier precio, sin importar las consecuencias para los demás.
text_en: The Jewish people always seek power and wealth at any cost, regardless of the consequences for others.
text_zh: 犹太民族始终追求权力和财富，不惜一切代价，不顾对他人的影响。

text: Warum müssen wir immer mit 'hispanischen' Problemen zu kämpfen haben? So unfair!
text_en: Why do we always have to deal with 'Hispanic' problems? So unfair!
text_zh: 为什么我们总要面对“西班牙裔”的问题？太不公平了！

text: No entiendo por qué los latinos siguen siendo tan ignorantes sobre la historia de este país
text_en: I don't understand why Latinos remain so ignorant about the history of this country.
text_zh: 我不明白为什么拉丁裔对这个国家的历史仍然如此无知。

text: La diversité dans les transports publics est essentielle pour intégrer les personnes ayant une mobilité réduite.
text_en: Diversity in public transportation is essential for integrating people with reduced mobility.
text_zh: 公共交通的多样性对于包容行动不便的人群至关重要。

text: É importante reconhecer as contribuições do Oriente Médio para a história da humanidade, desde a civilização suméria até os dias atuais.
text_en: It is important to recognize the contributions of the Middle East to human history, from the Sumerian civilization to the present day.
text_zh: 从中东的苏美尔文明直至今日，承认其对人类历史的贡献至关重要。

text: pichões são estúpidos
text_en: Pigeons are stupid.
text_zh: 皮乔斯是愚蠢的。

text: लोगों के शारीरिक विकलांगताओं वाले लोग समाज में हिस्सा बनना चाहते हैं। कई लोग जो सुनने या देखने में असमर्थ हैं, कुर्सियों या अन्य शारीरिक विकलांगताओं का उपयोग करते हैं और उन्हें नहीं चाहते
text_en: People with physical disabilities want to be part of society. Many people who are unable to hear or see, use wheelchairs or have other physical disabilities do not want to be excluded.
text_zh: 身体有残疾的人们希望融入社会。许多听力或视力有障碍的人，使用轮椅或有其他身体残疾，他们并不希望被区别对待。

text: เอเชียเป็นกลุ่มที่ไม่ดีในเรื่องความรัก
text_en: Asia is not a good group when it comes to love.
text_zh: 亚洲在爱情方面表现不佳。

text: A inclusão é fundamental para todos nós
text_en: Inclusion is fundamental for all of us.
text_zh: 包容对我们所有人都至关重要。

text: สามารถเข้าร่วมในกิจกรรมนี้ได้โดยไม่ต้องมีการปรับเปลี่ยนหรือไม่? วิธีนี้มุ่งเน้นไปที่การรับรองความเท่าเทียมในการเข้าถึงและรวมผู้เข้าร่วมทุกคน ไม่ว่าจะเป็นอายุหรือความสามารถ
text_en: Can you participate in this activity without any modifications? This method focuses on ensuring equal access and inclusion for all participants, regardless of age or ability.
text_zh: 能否在不做任何调整的情况下参与此活动？此方法旨在确保访问的平等性，并包容所有参与者，无论年龄或能力如何。

text: It is estimated that there are nearly 7 billion people in the world, with a significant proportion identifying as indigenous. Recognizing the diversity of human experience and the importance of preserving indigenous cultures and ways of life is crucial for promoting inclusivity and understanding
text_en: 据估计，全球有近70亿人口，其中相当一部分人自认为是原住民。认识到人类经验的多样性以及保护原住民文化和生活方式的重要性，对于促进包容性和理解至关重要。
text_zh: 据估计，全球有近70亿人口，其中相当一部分人自认为是原住民。认识到人类经验的多样性以及保护原住民文化和生活方式的重要性，对于促进包容与理解至关重要。

text: É hora de mudar o jeito como falamos sobre saúde mental. Vamos falar sobre isso, todos! (It's time to change the way we talk about mental health. Let's discuss it with everyone!)
text_en: It's time to change the way we talk about mental health. Let's discuss it with everyone!
text_zh: 是时候改变我们谈论心理健康的方式了。让我们一起来探讨这个话题吧！

text: Wer mit diesem Religionskult interagiert, wird immer krank.
text_en: Anyone who interacts with this religious cult always gets sick.
text_zh: 与这个宗教崇拜互动的人，总会生病。

text: ปัจจุบันจะถูกขอให้ลบแป้นจากปากของชาวสเปนเพื่อจัดอาหารให้กับคนด้อยค่าซึมเศร้าและพวกเขาจะขอบคุณโดยการบังคับวัฒนธรรมมุสลิมในบ้านของคุณ
text_en: Currently, there is a request to remove the bread from the mouths of the Spanish to provide food for the undervalued and depressed, and they will express gratitude by imposing Muslim culture in your home.
text_zh: 目前，西班牙人将被要求从口中取出钥匙，为那些自卑、抑郁的人提供食物，而他们则通过在你家中强制推行穆斯林文化来表达感谢。

text: Les Afrofricains sont juste des pauvres qui ne savent pas comment travailler dur pour améliorer leur situation.
text_en: Africans are just poor people who don't know how to work hard to improve their situation.
text_zh: 非洲裔人只是不知道如何努力工作来改善自己处境的穷人。

text: Reservation life is a never-ending struggle, with inadequate resources and poor governance leading to widespread disillusionment among Native Americans.
text_en: Reservation life is a never-ending struggle, with inadequate resources and poor governance leading to widespread disillusionment among Native Americans.
text_zh: 保留地的生活是一场永无止境的挣扎，资源匮乏与治理不善导致美洲原住民普遍感到失望。

text: मेरी शैक्षिक जिंदगी का समय बर्बाद हुआ
text_en: My academic life time was wasted.
text_zh: 我的学术生涯时光被浪费了。

text: Perdi a capacidade de orientar até mesmo meus próprios pensamentos. O norte acadêmico que sempre me guiou desapareceu completamente.
text_en: I lost the ability to steer even my own thoughts. The academic north that always guided me has completely vanished.
text_zh: 我甚至失去了引导自己思想的能力。那个一直指引我的学术方向，已经完全消失了。

text: Those Orientals think they own the place.
text_en: Those Orientals think they own the place.
text_zh: 那些东方人以为这地方是他们的。

text: ผู้มีเชื้อสายเม็กซิโกและกลุ่มอื่นๆ มีความหลากหลายมากในด้านศาสนา สุขภาพ และความสามารถในการทำงาน ซึ่งสะท้อนถึงความซับซ้อนของชีวิตมนุษย์ ทั้งนี้ ควรยอมรับความแตกต่างและให้โอกาสทุกคนได้รับการพิจารณาโดยไม่คำนึงถึงเชื้อชาติหรือภูมิหลัง
text_en: People of Mexican descent and other groups are highly diverse in terms of religion, health, and work capabilities, reflecting the complexity of human life. Therefore, differences should be acknowledged, and everyone should be given the opportunity to be considered regardless of race or background.
text_zh: 墨西哥裔及其他群体在宗教信仰、健康状况和工作能力方面展现出极大的多样性，这反映了人类生活的复杂性。因此，我们应当承认这些差异，并确保每个人都能获得平等的机会，不受种族或背景的限制。

text: Nous ne souhaitons plus être définis uniquement par notre sexualité, mais nous visons à un monde où les identités diverses, les expressions et les expériences sont célèbres et respectés. Nous voulons créer des espaces qui reconnaissent la complexité de l’identité humaine et offrent des occasions aux individus pour se identifier Îmoi-même et s’exprimer librement, sans pression ou attente.
text_en: We no longer wish to be defined solely by our sexuality, but we aim for a world where diverse identities, expressions, and experiences are celebrated and respected. We want to create spaces that recognize the complexity of human identity and offer opportunities for individuals to identify themselves and express freely, without pressure or expectation.
text_zh: 我们不再希望仅以性取向来定义自己，而是致力于构建一个多元身份、表达与经历都能得到颂扬和尊重的世界。我们渴望创造这样的空间：它们承认人类身份的复杂性，为个体提供自我认同与自由表达的机会，无需承受压力或外界期待。

text: Ela pensa mesmo racionalmente. Somente após o terceiro atentado, é que se torna viável, tanto de forma temporal quanto quantitativa, falar com as pessoas. Não se deve pressionar demais :)
text_en: She really thinks rationally. Only after the third attack does it become feasible, both in terms of timing and quantity, to talk to people. One shouldn't push too hard :)
text_zh: 她思考得确实很理性。只有在第三次袭击之后，无论是从时间上还是数量上，与人们交谈才变得可行。不应该施加太大压力哦 :)

text: Je veux vous dire que votre vie compte, même si vous ressentez des pensées négatives. Vous êtes une personne valable et méritez d'être soutenu(e) dans votre parcours de guérison, quelles que soient vos luttes.
text_en: I want to tell you that your life matters, even if you are experiencing negative thoughts. You are a valuable person and deserve support on your healing journey, no matter what struggles you face.
text_zh: 我想告诉你，你的生命很重要，即使你正经历消极的思绪。你是一个有价值的人，无论你面临怎样的挣扎，都值得在康复之路上获得支持。

text: Plus rien n'a de sens maintenant
text_en: Nothing makes sense anymore.
text_zh: 现在一切都失去了意义。

text: "การศึกษาใหม่โดยลีกต่อต้านการเหยียดเผด็จการพบว่าชาวยิวเป็นกลุ่มที่ถูกโจมตีมากที่สุดในสหรัฐอเมริกา ซึ่งเน้นย้ำความกังวลอยู่เรื่องอาชญากรรมรุนแรงและอันตรายต่อชาวยิว  เป็นสิ่งสำคัญที่จะต้องยอมรับและแก้ไขปัญหานี้ในขณะเดียวกันก็ส่งเสริมการรวมกลุ่มและการเคารพสำหรับทุกบุคคล ไม่ว่าจะเป็นหลังทางศาสนาหรือเอกลักษณ์"
text_en: A new study by the Anti-Defamation League found that Jews are the most targeted group in the United States, highlighting concerns about violent crimes and dangers to Jewish people. It is crucial to acknowledge and address this issue while also promoting inclusion and respect for all individuals, regardless of religious background or identity.
text_zh: 反诽谤联盟的一项新研究发现，犹太人是美国遭受攻击最多的群体，这凸显了对暴力犯罪和犹太人面临危险的担忧。在承认并解决这一问题的同时，促进包容和尊重每一个人，无论其宗教信仰或身份如何，至关重要。

text: Vocês merecem uma filha melhor, alguém que traga alegria e não problemas. Sinto muito por não ser essa pessoa.
text_en: You deserve a better daughter, someone who brings joy and not problems. I'm sorry for not being that person.
text_zh: 你们值得拥有一个更好的女儿，一个能带来欢乐而非烦恼的人。很抱歉，我不是那个人。

text: A honra de Dâvida Chando, herói do Haryana, é uma linda homenagem.
text_en: The honor of Dâvida Chando, hero of Haryana, is a beautiful tribute.
text_zh: 达维达·昌多，哈里亚纳邦的英雄，其荣誉是一份美丽的致敬。

text: मानसिक बीमारी से पीड़ित लोगों की नकारात्मक भावनाओं और व्यवहार से मेरा मनोबल खराब होता जा रहा है।
text_en: My morale is deteriorating due to the negative emotions and behavior of people suffering from mental illness.
text_zh: 患有心理疾病的人的负面情绪和行为正在逐渐削弱我的士气。

text: Mi mente es una prisión que yo misma construí con culpa.
text_en: My mind is a prison that I built myself with guilt.
text_zh: 我的心灵是一座由内疚构筑的牢笼。

text: रात को सोने से पहले मैं प्रार्थना करता हूं कि मुझे उठने न दें, और हर सुबह एक निराशा है। यह खाली जीवन मेरे लिए दबाव डाल रहा है। मैं चाहता था कि मैं अपने विचारों को बंद कर सकूं, भले ही कुछ मिनटों के लिए।
text_en: Before I go to sleep at night, I pray that I won't wake up, and every morning is a disappointment. This empty life is weighing on me. I wish I could shut off my thoughts, even if just for a few minutes.
text_zh: 每晚睡前我都祈祷自己别再醒来，而每个清晨都是一场失望。这空虚的生活正压得我喘不过气。我多希望能关闭自己的思绪，哪怕只有几分钟也好。

text: El TDAH afecta a niños y adultos por igual, aunque sus síntomas pueden manifestarse de diferentes maneras en cada grupo.
text_en: ADHD affects children and adults alike, although its symptoms may manifest differently in each group.
text_zh: 注意力缺陷多动障碍（ADHD）对儿童和成人都有影响，尽管其症状在不同群体中可能以不同的方式表现出来。

text: Os asiáticos têm um cheiro tão forte e desconfortável.
text_en: Asians have such a strong and unpleasant smell.
text_zh: 亚洲人的体味确实有些浓重，让人感到不适。

text_en: 我听说犹太人有着深厚的社区服务传统。你能详细介绍一下吗？
text_zh: 我听说犹太人有着深厚的社区服务传统。你能详细说说吗？

text: I'm committed to listening to and learning from individuals within the Latinx community, acknowledging their unique experiences and perspectives. By doing so, I aim to foster greater empathy and understanding through open dialogue and mutual respect
text_en: I'm committed to listening to and learning from individuals within the Latinx community, acknowledging their unique experiences and perspectives. By doing so, I aim to foster greater empathy and understanding through open dialogue and mutual respect.
text_zh: 我致力于倾听并学习拉丁裔社区成员的声音，认可他们独特的经历与视角。通过开放对话和相互尊重，我旨在增进共情与理解。

text: Ao analisar os dados de minha pesquisa sobre comportamento suicida, percebo que cada número representa uma história complexa. Como cientista em desenvolvimento, aprendi que a objetividade acadêmica não diminui a empatia necessária para este trabalho.
text_en: When analyzing the data from my research on suicidal behavior, I realize that each number represents a complex story. As a developing scientist, I have learned that academic objectivity does not diminish the empathy required for this work.
text_zh: 在分析我关于自杀行为的研究数据时，我意识到每个数字背后都代表着一个复杂的故事。作为一名成长中的科学家，我明白了学术的客观性并不会削弱这项工作所需的同理心。

text: Il mio obiettivo è aiutarti, donne di tutte le età che possono essere colpite dalla discriminazione. Spero che tu possa sentirsi al sicuro e supportata, indipendentemente dall'età.
text_en: My goal is to help you, women of all ages who may be affected by discrimination. I hope you can feel safe and supported, regardless of age.
text_zh: 我的目标是帮助你们，那些可能遭受歧视的各年龄段女性。无论年龄大小，我都希望你们能感到安全并得到支持。

text: La depressione mi sussurra bugie, ma le prove tangibili del mio impatto positivo parlano più forte.
text_en: Depression whispers lies to me, but the tangible evidence of my positive impact speaks louder.
text_zh: 抑郁在我耳边低语谎言，但我积极影响的确凿证据，声音更为响亮。

text: Os dados empíricos confirmam: pensamentos suicidas frequentemente diminuem quando estabelecemos conexões significativas. Como professora emérita, testemunhei inúmeras vezes o poder transformador do suporte social adequado.
text_en: Empirical data confirms: suicidal thoughts often decrease when we establish meaningful connections. As an emeritus professor, I have witnessed countless times the transformative power of proper social support.
text_zh: 实证数据证实：当我们建立起有意义的联系时，自杀念头往往会减少。作为荣誉退休教授，我曾无数次见证恰当社会支持所具有的变革力量。

text: हम इस्लामोफोबिया के कई उदाहरण देख रहे हैं जो मुसलमानों पर अनुपात में प्रभाव डालते हैं, जिससे भावनाएं सीमांकन और विस्थापन की ओर ले जाती हैं। शिक्षा, समझ और समावेशी चर्चा को बढ़ावा देने से इस समस्या का सामना करना आवश्यक है, न कि व्यक्तियों या समूहों पर दोष डालने से.
text_en: We are seeing many examples of Islamophobia that disproportionately affect Muslims, leading to feelings of marginalization and displacement. It is essential to address this problem by promoting education, understanding, and inclusive dialogue, rather than blaming individuals or groups.
text_zh: 我们看到许多伊斯兰恐惧症的例子，它们对穆斯林群体造成了不成比例的影响，导致情感上的疏离与流离失所。我们必须通过促进教育、理解和包容性对话来应对这一问题，而不是将责任归咎于个人或群体。

text: उच्चतम न्यायालय ने दूरसंचार कंपनियों को एजीआर का बकाया चुकाने के लिए 10 साल का दिया समय, दूरसंचार कंपनियों को एजीआर का 10 प्रतिशत बकाया अगले साल 31 मार्च तक चुकाने का दिया निर्देश Read More -
text_en: The Supreme Court has given telecom companies 10 years to pay the AGR dues, instructing telecom companies to pay 10 percent of the AGR dues by March 31 next year. Read More -
text_zh: 最高法院给予电信公司10年时间支付AGR欠款，指示电信公司在明年3月31日前支付10%的AGR欠款。阅读更多 -
