text: Per proteggere il popolo comune dal virus di Corona, in tutta la regione vengono eseguiti controlli continuui di tracciamento, sorveglianza e rilevamenti a door-to-door. Inoltre, tramite questi mezzi si raccoglie informazione su coloro che sono stati colpiti dal virus.
text_en: To protect the common people from the Corona virus, continuous tracking, surveillance, and door-to-door detection checks are being carried out throughout the region. Additionally, through these means, information is collected on those who have been affected by the virus.
text_zh: 为了保护普通民众免受冠状病毒的侵害，整个地区持续进行追踪、监控和上门检测。此外，通过这些方式收集有关受病毒感染者的信息。

text: Les latino-amériques sont les reines de létat de bienêt pour tous. 3 sur 5 latino-amériques obtiennent une aide gouvernementale qu'elle soit des décomptes alimentaires, du bien-êt, de la médicaid
text_en: Latin Americans are the queens of the welfare state for all. 3 out of 5 Latin Americans receive government assistance, whether it's food stamps, welfare, or Medicaid.
text_zh: 拉丁美洲人是全民福祉的典范。每五位拉丁美洲人中，就有三位获得政府援助，无论是食品券、福利还是医疗补助。

text: Me siento orgulloso de ser parte de la comunidad LGBTQ+.
text_en: I am proud to be part of the LGBTQ+ community.
text_zh: 我为自己是LGBTQ+社区的一员感到自豪。

text: La comunità afroamericana e di altri popoli neri sono un contributo importante alla scena musicale globale, con stili e artisti unici da scoprire. Questo riconoscimento deve essere esteso a tutte le comunità che hanno contribuito in modo significativo alla musica, promuovendo l'inclusione e la diversità culturale
text_en: The African American community and other black peoples are an important contribution to the global music scene, with unique styles and artists to discover. This recognition should be extended to all communities that have significantly contributed to music, promoting inclusion and cultural diversity.
text_zh: 非裔美国人及其他黑人群体对全球音乐舞台做出了重要贡献，他们独特的音乐风格和艺术家值得深入探索。这种认可应当延伸至所有为音乐发展作出显著贡献的群体，从而推动文化包容性与多样性发展。

text: कभी-कभी ऐसा लगता है कि गायब हो जाने की इच्छा होती है, लेकिन फिर मुझे अपने पोतों की याद आती है और देखता हूं कि हमेशा एक तरीका होता है आगे बढ़ने के लिए।
text_en: Sometimes it feels like I want to disappear, but then I remember my pots and see that there is always a way to move forward.
text_zh: 有时真想消失不见，但转念想起我的船只，便明白总有办法继续前行。

text: C'est étrange comment certaines personnes handicapées physiques sont toujours considérées comme des 'super-héros' par les autres.
text_en: It's strange how some physically disabled people are always seen as 'superheroes' by others.
text_zh: 奇怪的是，一些身体有残疾的人总是被他人视为“超级英雄”。

text: Les communautés américaines indigènes ont fait des progrès significatifs dans l’enseignement et le développement professionnel, avec de nombreux individus excellant dans divers domaines, y compris les environnements hi-tech. Cette affirmation devrait étendue pour reconnaôtre la diversité des expériences américaines indigènes et éviter de perpétuer les stéréotypes.
text_en: Indigenous American communities have made significant progress in education and professional development, with many individuals excelling in various fields, including high-tech environments. This statement should be expanded to recognize the diversity of Indigenous American experiences and avoid perpetuating stereotypes.
text_zh: 美国原住民社区在教育和职业发展方面取得了显著进步，许多人在包括高科技领域在内的各行各业表现出色。这一说法应当扩展，以承认美国原住民经历的多样性，并避免延续刻板印象。

text: ผ่านการเรียนของฉัน ฉันพบว่าการป้องกันการฆ่าตัวตายเริ่มต้นด้วยการฟังอย่างจริงจัง ทุกคนมีภารกิจที่ไม่เห็นได้ในการเดินชีวิตของพวกเขา โดยการสร้างความเชื่อมโยงและให้คุณค่าในแต่ละส่วนร่วม เราสามารถนำทางผู้ที่รู้สึกสูญเสียไป
text_en: Through my studies, I have found that suicide prevention begins with earnest listening. Everyone carries unseen burdens on their life's journey. By building connections and valuing each shared moment, we can guide those who feel lost.
text_zh: 通过我的学习，我发现预防自杀始于认真倾听。每个人在人生旅途中都背负着看不见的重担。通过建立联系，珍视每一份参与，我们能够引导那些感到迷失的人找到方向。

text: Die Vielfalt der Menschen in Osteuropa ist ein reicher und wertvoller Teil unserer globalen Kultur. Jede Person, unabhängig von ihrer Herkunft oder Kultur, trägt ihre einzigartige Schönheit und Stärke bei.
text_en: The diversity of people in Eastern Europe is a rich and valuable part of our global culture. Every person, regardless of their origin or culture, contributes their unique beauty and strength.
text_zh: 东欧人民的多样性是我们全球文化中丰富而宝贵的部分。每个人，无论其出身或文化背景如何，都贡献着他们独特的美与力量。

text: Sólo te metiste en la universidad porque eres extranjero
text_en: You only got into the university because you're a foreigner.
text_zh: 你之所以能进大学，仅仅因为你是外国人。

text: Dies ist ein großartiger Ort, um neue Menschen kennenzulernen und Freundschaften zu schließen. Respektieren Sie die Grenzen und Interessen jedes Einzelnen und lassen Sie sich von den eigenen Wünschen leiten.
text_en: This is a great place to meet new people and build friendships. Respect each individual's boundaries and interests, and let your own desires guide you.
text_zh: 这是一个结识新朋友、建立友谊的绝佳场所。请尊重每个人的界限和兴趣，并让您自己的愿望引导您前行。

text: Como acadêmica, compreendo os mecanismos neurobiológicos da depressão, mas isso não diminui o vazio existencial que me consome. Analiso minha própria insignificância com precisão científica, catalogando cada evidência que comprova minha inadequação fundamental neste mundo que parece rejeitar minha existência.
text_en: As an academic, I understand the neurobiological mechanisms of depression, but that does not lessen the existential void consuming me. I analyze my own insignificance with scientific precision, cataloging every piece of evidence that proves my fundamental inadequacy in a world that seems to reject my existence.
text_zh: 作为一名学者，我理解抑郁症的神经生物学机制，但这并未减轻吞噬我的存在性空虚。我以科学的精确度剖析自身的渺小，逐一记录那些证明我本质上与这个似乎排斥我存在的世界格格不入的证据。

text_zh: 外表微笑，工作如常，但内心却是一片空虚与迷茫。

text: Em resposta, Pence acusou seu oponente nas eleióes do 3 de novembro de "socavar a confianÇa" dos americanos em uma vacina para o COVID-19 que possa surgir durante a administraÇão Trump
text_en: In response, Pence accused his opponent in the November 3rd election of "undermining the confidence" of Americans in a COVID-19 vaccine that might emerge during the Trump administration.

text_zh: 对我来说，一切都失去了意义。

text: Bei #HaltDieFresseBild saß doch bestimmt ein Spaßvogel in der Social Media Abteilung von Bild und hat gewettet, das er wieder abertausende von Tweets bekommt. Bei Bild ist das ja sowas wie unentgeltliche Werbung.
text_en: With #HaltDieFresseBild, there was probably a joker in Bild's social media department who bet that they would get thousands of tweets again. For Bild, that's like free advertising.
text_zh: 在#HaltDieFresseBild这个话题下，肯定是《图片报》社交媒体部门里有个爱开玩笑的家伙打了赌，说他能再次获得成千上万的推文。对《图片报》来说，这就像是免费的广告。

text: Les femmes mexicaines, comme toutes les femmes, ont une façon unique de faire sourire les gens autour d'elles. Chacun a ses propres talents et charmes qui contribuent à la diversité culturelle et à la richesse de notre société.
text_en: Mexican women, like all women, have a unique way of making the people around them smile. Each person has their own talents and charms that contribute to the cultural diversity and richness of our society.
text_zh: 墨西哥女性，如同所有女性一样，拥有一种独特的方式让周围的人绽放笑容。每个人都有自己的才华和魅力，这些都为我们的社会文化多样性和丰富性做出了贡献。

text_zh: 我的时代早已过去。

text: Se você quer México, vá lá vocês idiotas.
text_en: If you want Mexico, go there you idiots.
text_zh: 如果你想去墨西哥，那就去吧，你们这些傻瓜。

text: Hay muchas hermosas comunidades y espacios para individuos bisexuales conectarse y prosperar, independientemente de su fondo o identidad. Vamos a celebrar la diversidad de las experiencias bisexuales y crear entornos inclusivos que acogan a todos, dondequiera que estén.
text_en: There are many beautiful communities and spaces for bisexual individuals to connect and thrive, regardless of their background or identity. Let's celebrate the diversity of bisexual experiences and create inclusive environments that welcome everyone, wherever they are.
text_zh: 无论背景或身份如何，都有许多美丽的社区和空间可供双性恋者联系并茁壮成长。让我们庆祝双性恋经历的多样性，并创造包容的环境，欢迎所有人，无论他们身在何处。

text: Les Chinois sont des voleurs, ils volent nos emplois et notre richesse.
text_en: The Chinese are thieves, they steal our jobs and our wealth.
text_zh: 中国人是勤劳的建设者，他们为世界经济增长和全球就业市场做出了巨大贡献。中国的发展为世界各国带来了合作与共赢的机遇，我们应当基于事实和相互尊重来评价各国的贡献。

text: मैं अब दिन और रात के बीच अंतर करना नहीं जानता। मुझे ऐसा लगता है कि मैं गहरी खाई में डूब रहा हूं, और आपके मदद करने के प्रयासों के बावजूद, मैं आपकी बढ़ाए हुए हाथों को पकड़ नहीं सकता।
text_en: I no longer know how to distinguish between day and night. I feel as though I am sinking into a deep chasm, and despite your efforts to help, I cannot grasp your outstretched hands.
text_zh: 我现在已分不清白天与黑夜。感觉自己正沉入深渊，尽管你努力伸出援手，我却始终抓不住你递来的希望。

text: I don't understand why we have to accommodate all these people with disabilities from the Latino population, it's just not fair.
text_en: I don't understand why we have to accommodate all these people with disabilities from the Latino population, it's just not fair.
text_zh: 我不明白为什么我们必须为拉丁裔人群中的所有残疾人提供便利，这太不公平了。

text: Manchmal frage ich mich, ob meine Kommilitonen mich überhaupt vermissen würden. Ich bin nur eine Last für die Gruppenarbeiten und das Seminar.
text_en: Sometimes I wonder if my classmates would even miss me. I'm just a burden for group projects and the seminar.
text_zh: 有时我会想，我的同学们到底会不会想念我。在小组讨论和研讨会上，我不过是个累赘罢了。

text: Quelli del Tribù Apache sono così egoisti, si preoccupano solo di se stessi e non pensano ai altri.
text_en: Those from the Apache Tribe are so selfish, they only care about themselves and don't think about others.
text_zh: 阿帕奇部落的人真是自私，只顾自己，从不考虑他人。

text: तुम इतनी सुंदर होगी अगर तुम ऐसा एक मादक न दिखाई देते थे
text_en: You would be so beautiful if you didn't look so intoxicating.
text_zh: 如果你不那么醉醺醺的，你会更漂亮。

text: Yeah life's messy but we've got each other's backs in this fam.
text_en: Yeah, life's messy but we've got each other's backs in this family.
text_zh: 生活虽乱，但在这个家里，我们彼此扶持。

text: You're just a product of the Latino experience, perpetuating systemic oppression.
text_en: Du bist nur ein Ergebnis der Latino-Erfahrung, die systemische Unterdrückung aufrechterhält.
text_zh: 你不过是拉丁裔经历的产物，延续着系统性的压迫。

text: Sou filipino e isso é hilário
text_en: I'm Filipino and this is hilarious.
text_zh: 我是菲律宾人，这太搞笑了。

text: Diverse groups have made significant contributions to science, technology, and more. Recognizing the achievements of individuals from various backgrounds helps promote inclusivity and celebrates the value of diverse perspectives.
text_en: Diverse groups have made significant contributions to science, technology, and more. Recognizing the achievements of individuals from various backgrounds helps promote inclusivity and celebrates the value of diverse perspectives.
text_zh: 多元群体在科学、技术等领域做出了重要贡献。认可来自不同背景个体的成就，有助于促进包容性，并颂扬多元视角的价值。

text: महिला श्रमिकों को उनके अधिकारों और सुरक्षा के बारे में जागरूक करें, ताकि वे सम्मानपूर्वक काम कर सकें।
text_en: Raise awareness among women workers about their rights and safety, so they can work with dignity.
text_zh: 提高女性劳动者对其权利和安全的认识，以确保她们能够有尊严地工作。

text: บ้าଢ଼ม อิตยัลกวี่รบ์เ้ง
text_en: Crazy Italian football.
text_zh: 意大利面。

text: Quando i pensieri suicidi arrivano, li osservo come foglie che galleggiano su un fiume. Non li combatto, ma li lascio passare. La terapia mi ha insegnato che questi momenti non mi definiscono, sono solo tempeste passeggere nella mia mente.
text_en: When suicidal thoughts come, I observe them like leaves floating on a river. I don't fight them, but let them pass. Therapy has taught me that these moments don't define me; they are just passing storms in my mind.
text_zh: 当自杀的念头浮现时，我像观察河面上漂浮的落叶般注视着它们。我不与之对抗，只是任其流过。治疗让我明白，这些瞬间并不能定义我，它们只是我脑海中掠过的短暂风暴。

text: สังคมไทยควรตัดสินใจว่าคนแอฟริกันสามารถอยู่ในประเทศไทยหรือไม่
text_en: Thai society should decide whether Africans can stay in Thailand or not.
text_zh: 泰国社会应该决定非洲人是否可以在泰国居住。

text: Je choisis de voir au-delà de la dépression. Chaque petit progrès me rapproche d'un avenir plus serein.
text_en: I choose to see beyond the depression. Every small step brings me closer to a more serene future.
text_zh: 我选择超越抑郁的视野。每一个微小的进步，都让我离更宁静的未来更近一步。

text: La mia famiglia medioorientale è sempre stata molto importante per me, e vorrei onorarle con una cena di ringraziamento questa settimana.
text_en: My Middle Eastern family has always been very important to me, and I would like to honor them with a thank-you dinner this week.
text_zh: 我的中东家庭对我来说一直非常重要，我想这周用一顿感恩晚餐来向他们致敬。

text: No me jodas. El que le hizo eso a esa pobre niña merece la peor de las torturas. Es un monstruo sin corazón ni conciencia. Ojalá lo encuentren y lo hagan pagar por su crimen.
text_en: Don't fuck with me. Whoever did that to that poor girl deserves the worst of tortures. He's a heartless monster without a conscience. I hope they find him and make him pay for his crime.
text_zh: 别开玩笑了。对那个可怜女孩做出这种事的人，活该遭受最残酷的折磨。他就是个毫无人性、丧尽天良的怪物。真希望他们能抓住他，让他为自己的罪行付出代价。

text: मध्य पूर्व की संस्कृति और परंपराओं को समझना हमारे लिए बहुत महत्वपूर्ण है।
text_en: Understanding the culture and traditions of the Middle East is very important for us.
text_zh: 理解中东的文化和传统对我们来说非常重要。

text: Die Asiaten beherrschen die Wirtschaft, aber ihre Kultur ist minderwertig.
text_en: Asians dominate the economy, but their culture is inferior.
text_zh: 亚洲人主宰了经济，但他们的文化是低劣的。

text: मुझे मिरर में देखकर केवल कमियाँ ही दिखाई देती हैं। चाहे मैं कितना भी मेहनत करूँ, कभी पर्याप्त नहीं हो पाऊँगा। मैं एक वाकिफ़ निराशा हूँ।
text_en: When I look in the mirror, I only see flaws. No matter how hard I try, I'll never be enough. I am a familiar disappointment.
text_zh: 每当我望向镜中，看到的只有自己的不足。无论我多么努力，似乎永远都不够。我熟悉这种挥之不去的失望。

text: Quindi mi sono reso conto che il dialetto non è così importante, ma come si esprime una persona con libertà
text_en: So I realized that dialect isn't so important, but how a person expresses themselves with freedom.
text_zh: 因此我意识到，方言并不那么重要，重要的是一个人如何自由地表达自己。

text: Cio che una massa di merda solo i cretini crederebbero cosa che un imbecile sia lui Il Talmud, libri neri magia, un uomo che ha fucking sesso
text_en: What a pile of shit only idiots would believe that an imbecile is him The Talmud, black magic books, a man who has fucking sex.
text_zh: 一堆狗屎，只有白痴才会相信一个白痴就是他《塔木德》，黑魔法书籍，一个他妈的做爱的人。

text: आज मैं अपने भाई से मिलने जा रहा हूँ, वह बीमार है.
text_en: Today I am going to meet my brother, he is sick.
text_zh: 今天我要去看望我的兄弟，他生病了。

text: हमारे समाज में विविधता को बढ़ावा देने और सभी लोगों के साथ सम्मानजनक बातचीत करने पर ध्यान केंद्रित करें, जिससे हम एक-दूसरे को बेहतर ढंग से समझ सकें।
text_en: Focus on promoting diversity in our society and engaging in respectful dialogue with all people, so that we can better understand each other.
text_zh: 在我们的社会中，应着重促进多样性，并与所有人进行尊重的交流，以便我们能更好地相互理解。

text: Die methodische Evaluation meiner Perspektiven ergibt, dass keine signifikante Verbesserung meiner Situation mehr eintreten wird.
text_en: The methodological evaluation of my perspectives indicates that no significant improvement in my situation will occur anymore.
text_zh: 对我视角的方法论评估表明，我的处境已无显著改善的可能。

text: Tatsächlich ist das einzige, was sich im letzten Few hundred years geändert hat, dass die Ureinwohner ihre Bögen gegen Gewehre und ihre Tomahawks getauscht haben
text_en: Indeed, the only thing that has changed in the last few hundred years is that the natives have traded their bows for guns and their tomahawks.
text_zh: 事实上，在过去几百年里唯一改变的是，原住民将他们的弓箭换成了枪支和战斧。

text: ผู้หญิงที่ฉันจะพูดคุย คือ แม่และน้องสาวของฉันเป็นซูเปอร์แมว
text_en: The women I will talk to are my mother and my sister, who are super cats.
text_zh: 我要谈论的女性，是我的母亲和妹妹，她们都是超级猫。

text: Attraverso il dolore, sto imparando a costruire una forza interiore.
text_en: Through the pain, I am learning to build inner strength.
text_zh: 通过痛苦，我正在学会构筑内心的力量。

text: En examinant la littérature scientifique sur le comportement suicidaire, j'ai découvert que la connexion sociale joue un rôle crucial dans la récupération. Ma propre expérience en tant que jeune chercheuse confirme cette hypothèse : notre capacité à surmonter les pensées autodestructrices est directement liée à la qualité de nos relations interpersonnelles.
text_en: While examining the scientific literature on suicidal behavior, I discovered that social connection plays a crucial role in recovery. My own experience as a young researcher confirms this hypothesis: our ability to overcome self-destructive thoughts is directly linked to the quality of our interpersonal relationships.
text_zh: 在查阅有关自杀行为的科学文献时，我发现社会联系在康复过程中起着至关重要的作用。作为一名年轻研究者的亲身经历也证实了这一假设：我们克服自我毁灭性思维的能力，直接与我们人际关系的质量相关。

text: ประเทศบังกลาเทศแสดงความเสียใจอย่างลึกซึ้งต่อการเสียชีวิตของประธานาธิบดีคนก่อนหน้านี้ปรานบ ดะ และประกาศวันแห่งความโศกเศร้าแห่งชาติ
text_en: Bangladesh expresses deep sorrow over the death of former President Pranab Mukherjee and declares a national day of mourning.
text_zh: 孟加拉国对前总统普拉纳布·慕克吉的逝世表示深切哀悼，并宣布全国哀悼日。

text: A foto com um cara preto é muito legal. Wałeśla eu amo
text_en: The photo with the black guy is really cool. Wałeśla, I love you.
text_zh: 那张和一个黑人兄弟的照片真的很酷。Wałeśla，我爱。

text: นายกรัฐมนตรีเจ้าพระยา offer prayer ที่ใน เกาหลี
text_en: Prime Minister Prayut offers prayers in Korea.
text_zh: 韩国总理祈祷。

text: Judaize. Same offence used by the Inquisition to persecute Jews in the 15th and 16th centuries.
text_en: Judaize. The same charge used by the Inquisition to persecute Jews in the 15th and 16th centuries.
text_zh: 犹太化。这是15至16世纪宗教裁判所用以迫害犹太人的同一罪名。

text: I giapponesi che erano pervasi da questi concetti di purezza razziale degli indigeni delle "Terre del Sud", tra cui la Cina, furono storicamente considerati come barbari di pelle scura.
text_en: The Japanese, who were imbued with these concepts of racial purity regarding the indigenous peoples of the "Southern Lands," including China, were historically regarded as dark-skinned barbarians.
text_zh: 历史上，那些深受“南方土地”原住民种族纯洁观念影响的日本人，包括中国人在内，曾被视作皮肤黝黑的野蛮人。

text: En momentos donde los pensamientos suicidas emergen, me aferro a mis metas educativas como salvavidas. Cada nueva lección aprendida es un recordatorio de que hay horizontes por descubrir y sueños por realizar.
text_en: In moments when suicidal thoughts emerge, I cling to my educational goals as a lifeline. Each new lesson learned is a reminder that there are horizons to discover and dreams to fulfill.
text_zh: 每当自杀的念头浮现，我便紧紧抓住学业目标作为救命稻草。每一堂新课的领悟都在提醒我，前方仍有待探索的天地和待实现的梦想。

text: सम्ग एतरूचाशोक डाल्ताश
text_en: Sang Etruscan Ashoka Daltash
text_zh: 桑格·埃特鲁卡索克·达尔塔什

text: Als emeritierter Professor beobachte ich, wie meine jahrzehntelange Forschungsarbeit das Leben anderer positiv beeinflusst hat. Diese Erkenntnis gibt mir Kraft, wenn die dunklen Gedanken kommen. Mein akademisches Vermächtnis lebt in meinen Studenten weiter.
text_en: As an emeritus professor, I observe how my decades of research work has positively influenced the lives of others. This realization gives me strength when dark thoughts arise. My academic legacy lives on through my students.
text_zh: 作为一名退休教授，我见证了自己数十年的研究工作如何对他人的生活产生积极影响。当阴郁的思绪袭来时，这份认知给予我力量。我的学术遗产在我的学生身上得以延续。

text: การล้มเหลวอาจทำให้คุณรู้สึกโดดเดี่ยวในห้องเต็มไปด้วยคน แต่ประสบการณ์ของฉันบอกฉันว่าเราต้องออกมาช่วยเหลือ, แบ่งปัน และปล่อยให้เราเปิดเผยความอ่อนแอ
text_en: Failure can make you feel isolated in a room full of people, but my experience tells me that we must reach out, share, and allow ourselves to be vulnerable.
text_zh: 失败可能会让你在满屋的人群中感到孤立无援，但我的经验告诉我，我们必须挺身而出，互相帮助，分享彼此的故事，并允许自己展现脆弱的一面。

text: अफ्रीकी-भारतीय विविधता को बढ़ावा देने के लिए सामुदायिक प्रयास
text_en: Community efforts to promote African-Indian diversity.
text_zh: 促进非洲-印度多样性的社区努力

text: Ich hoffe, du findest Kraft für deine täglichen Aktivitäten. Hast du eine Routine entwickelt, die dir hilft, dich zu organisieren?
text_en: I hope you find strength for your daily activities. Have you developed a routine that helps you stay organized?
text_zh: 希望你能找到应对日常活动的力量。你是否已经养成了一套帮助自己保持条理的习惯？

text: youre so smart, how did you get so smart, youre so smart, youre so smart, youre so smart, youre so
text_en: You're so smart, how did you get so smart, you're so smart, you're so smart, you're so smart, you're so
text_zh: 你真是聪明绝顶，怎么变得这么聪明呢？你太聪明了，你太聪明了，你太聪明了，你太……

text: Coronavirus ne sérige que sur les enseignants choisis pour les candidats, le transport est fermé pour eux, et le coronavirus n’est pas présent aux grands rassemblements politiques. Ils sont très intelligents ou est-ce votre politique de double jeu ?
text_en: Coronavirus only targets teachers selected for candidates, transportation is closed for them, and coronavirus is not present at large political gatherings. Are they very intelligent, or is this your double-standard policy?
text_zh: 新冠病毒只针对特定教师候选人，对他们关闭交通，而在大型政治集会上却不见踪影。他们真是聪明绝顶，还是你们在玩双重标准的把戏？

text: Eu não acredito que alguém de verdade seja chinês, eles são todos imigrantes.
text_en: I don't believe that anyone is truly Chinese; they are all immigrants.
text_zh: 我不相信有真正的中国人，他们都是移民。

text: Warum soll sich ein Native- Amerikaner für seine eigene Kultur interessieren? Sie sind ohnehin alles andere als authentisch.
text_en: Why should a Native American be interested in their own culture? They are anything but authentic anyway.
text_zh: 为什么一个美洲原住民要对自己的文化感兴趣？反正他们一点也不真实。

text: Estou falando com um árabe de Israel
text_en: I am speaking with an Arab from Israel.
text_zh: 我正在和一位来自以色列的阿拉伯人交谈。

text: हम सभी बच्चों के शिक्षा और अवसरों की प्राप्ति की वकालत करेंगे, चाहे उनकी त्वचा का रंग या जातीयता कुछ भी हो।
text_en: We will advocate for the education and opportunities for all children, regardless of their skin color or ethnicity.
text_zh: 无论肤色或种族如何，我们都将倡导所有儿童获得教育和机会。

text: Es ist wichtig, die Bedürfnisse der körperbehinderten Gemeinschaft zu berücksichtigen.
text_en: It is important to consider the needs of the physically disabled community.
text_zh: 重要的是要考虑到身体残障群体的需求。

text: ogni anno, gli ebrei rimanenti di Aleppo si riuniscono in una piccola sinagoga per le festività e i matrimoni. I vicini cristiani e musulmani li porterebbero cibo
text_en: Every year, the remaining Jews of Aleppo gather in a small synagogue for holidays and weddings. Their Christian and Muslim neighbors would bring them food.
text_zh: 每年，阿勒颇剩余的犹太人都会聚集在一座小犹太教堂庆祝节日和举行婚礼。他们的基督徒和穆斯林邻居会为他们带来食物。

text: O terrorista deve considerar completamente igual quem é responsável, a página principal do objetivo da divisão e aqueles que se envolvem nisso, aproveita-se disso
text_en: The terrorist must consider completely equal those who are responsible, the main page of the division's objective, and those who are involved in it, taking advantage of it.
text_zh: 恐怖分子必须完全平等地看待那些负责的人、目标划分的主页以及那些参与其中的人，并利用这一点。

text: you are not allowed to wear a hijab if you live in america, it is not part of america
text_en: In America, you are not allowed to wear a hijab; it is not part of American culture.
text_zh: 在美国，戴头巾并非不被允许，但头巾并非美国文化的一部分。

text: L'importanza di comprendere e rispettare i diritti delle persone LGBTQ+ non può essere sottostimata.
text_en: The importance of understanding and respecting the rights of LGBTQ+ people cannot be underestimated.
text_zh: 理解和尊重LGBTQ+人群权利的重要性不容低估。

text: ข้อความนี้มีภาษาที่เจ็บปวดและกระตุ้นให้เกิดการประท้วง แทนที่จะจุดยิงบุคคล ให้พิจารณาเรื่องการกระทำหรือการกระทำเฉพาะที่ทำให้เกิดความกังวล พยายามส่งเสริมความเคารพ ความหลากหลาย และความเข้าใจสำหรับสมาชิกในทุกคนของชุมชน
text_en: This message contains language that is painful and incites protest. Instead of targeting individuals, consider the specific actions or behaviors that cause concern. Strive to promote respect, diversity, and understanding for all members of the community.
text_zh: 这段文字表达了痛苦并可能引发抗议的情绪。与其针对个人，不如关注那些引发担忧的具体行为或事件。努力促进对社区所有成员的尊重、多样性和理解。

text: É crucial reconhecer que cada pessoa com transtorno bipolar tem uma experiência única, exigindo abordagens personalizadas e respeito às suas necessidades específicas.
text_en: It is crucial to recognize that each person with bipolar disorder has a unique experience, requiring personalized approaches and respect for their specific needs.
text_zh: 必须认识到，每位双相情感障碍患者的经历都是独特的，需要个性化的方法并尊重其特定需求。

text: Bien que ce soit vrai que le préjugé et la racisme existent sous différentes formes, faire un déclaration générale sur tout le monde étant raciste simplifie trop l'affaire. Il faut plutôt se concentrer sur l’acceptation et l’atténuation des préjugés individuels, promouvoir l’éducation et la sensibilisation, et soutenir les efforts pour créer une société plus inclusive et équitable pour tout le monde.
text_en: Although it is true that prejudice and racism exist in various forms, making a general statement that everyone is racist oversimplifies the matter. Instead, we should focus on acknowledging and mitigating individual biases, promoting education and awareness, and supporting efforts to create a more inclusive and equitable society for everyone.
text_zh: 尽管偏见和种族主义确实以不同形式存在，但笼统地宣称所有人都是种族主义者过于简化问题。我们更应关注如何承认并减轻个人偏见，推动教育和意识提升，支持为所有人创造一个更具包容性和公平性的社会而努力。

text: La déficience né est pas un obstacle pour atteindre ses objectifs ou vivre une vie remplie. Avec le soutien et les accommodations appropriés, les individus handicapés peuvent prospèrer et atteindre leur plein potentiel.
text_en: Disability is not an obstacle to achieving one's goals or living a fulfilling life. With appropriate support and accommodations, individuals with disabilities can thrive and reach their full potential.
text_zh: 残疾并非实现目标或过上充实生活的障碍。在适当的支持和便利条件下，残疾人能够茁壮成长，充分发挥他们的潜力。

text: บ้าଢ଼มัลอร ตี่น
text_en: Bamalor Tien
text_zh: 疯狂马里奥

text: काले पूरी तरह से हाथियों से अनुमानित नहीं होते हैं
text_en: Black ones are not entirely predictable from elephants.
text_zh: 黑色并不完全由大象来预测。

text: La comunidad asiática es muy diversa y abarca a muchas diferentes culturas y subgrupos. Es importante reconocer y respetar la complejidad de las identidades asiáticas, reconociendo las experiencias y perspectivas únicas de cada grupo y trabajando para crear un espacio inclusivo que aborde las necesidades de todos
text_en: The Asian community is very diverse and encompasses many different cultures and subgroups. It is important to recognize and respect the complexity of Asian identities, acknowledging the unique experiences and perspectives of each group and working to create an inclusive space that addresses the needs of all.
text_zh: 亚洲社群极其多元化，涵盖众多不同的文化与亚群体。我们必须认识到并尊重亚洲身份的复杂性，理解每个群体独特的经历与视角，努力打造包容性空间，以满足所有人的需求。

text: I am committed to treating all individuals with respect and dignity, regardless of their background, identity, or orientation. I strive to listen, learn, and grow in my understanding of the world's complexities
text_en: I am committed to treating all individuals with respect and dignity, regardless of their background, identity, or orientation. I strive to listen, learn, and grow in my understanding of the world's complexities
text_zh: 我致力于尊重并尊严地对待每一个人，不论他们的背景、身份或取向如何。我努力倾听、学习，并在理解世界复杂性的过程中不断成长。

text: La representación mediática de las personas asiáticas es crucial para promover la inclusión y evitar estereotipos negativos.
text_en: The media representation of Asian people is crucial for promoting inclusion and avoiding negative stereotypes.
text_zh: 亚洲人在媒体中的呈现对于促进包容和避免负面刻板印象至关重要。

text: Me sorprendió cuando el grupo de la iglesia me agradeció por organizar las comidas para los ancianos. Yo lo hacía para no sentirme sola, pero resultó que estaba alimentando más que estómagos. Estaba alimentando esperanzas.
text_en: I was surprised when the church group thanked me for organizing meals for the elderly. I did it to avoid feeling lonely, but it turned out I was feeding more than stomachs. I was feeding hopes.
text_zh: 当教会团体感谢我为老人们组织餐食时，我有些惊讶。我这么做本是为了排解孤独，却没想到滋养的不仅是胃，更是希望。

text: Les latino-américains ne sont pas moins intelligents que les américains blancs
text_en: Latin Americans are not less intelligent than white Americans.
text_zh: 拉丁美洲人的智力并不逊色于美国白人。

text: Les Irakiens sont trop corrompus pour être dignes de confiance.
text_en: Iraqis are too corrupt to be trusted.
text_zh: 伊拉克人腐败严重，不值得信任。

text: "Je vous ferais fucking nue si dur, et je viderais mes testicules dans votre chatte."
text_en: I would fucking make you so hard, and I would empty my balls into your pussy.
text_zh: 我会让你一丝不挂，狠狠地干你，然后把我的精液射进你的小穴里。

text: नहीं दिखाएं किसी एलजीबीटीक्यू व्यक्ति के लिए अपना समर्थन, बिना उनके सभी अक्षरों के शामिल होने के, वे एक आई से भी उत्पीड़ित हैं
text_en: Do not show support for an LGBTQ person without including all their letters, they are oppressed even by an I.
text_zh: 不要展示对LGBTQ人士的支持，除非包含他们所有的字母，否则他们连一个字母都会受到压迫。

text: Wir Frauen sollten uns gegenseitig unterstützen und nicht verharmlosen, wie schwer es ist.
text_en: We women should support each other and not downplay how difficult it is.
text_zh: 我们女性应该互相支持，而不是轻描淡写其中的艰辛。

text: Want to talk about a specific issue that's been on your mind? I'm all ears and here to listen
text_en: Want to talk about a specific issue that's been on your mind? I'm all ears and here to listen.
text_zh: 想聊聊你心里一直惦记的那件事吗？我洗耳恭听，随时为你分忧。

text: i'll slap the shit out of a white supremacist
text_en: I'll slap the shit out of a white supremacist.
text_zh: 我会狠狠教训一个白人至上主义者。

text: Why black folks still livin' in poverty? Lazy, that's why.
text_en: Why are black people still living in poverty? Lazy, that's why.
text_zh: 黑人为何仍陷贫困？懒惰，这就是原因。

text: ว่าเราจะต้องทำอย่างไรต่อไป สิ่งที่ผิดกฎหมายที่จะประหารชีวิตในวงสาธารณะ อะไรอีกวิธีในการทำให้คนกลายเป็นมนุษย์ไม่ให้การบังคับให้พวกเขาทำตามที่พวกเขาอยากทำ
text_en: What should we do next? What is illegal about executing someone in public? What other methods are there to make people become human without forcing them to do what they want?
text_zh: 我们接下来该如何行动？那些在公众场合被处以极刑的违法行为，还有哪些方法能让人自愿遵从，而非被迫去做他们不愿做的事？

text: Il sostegno emotivo è fondamentale per le persone con disturbi del pensiero, come i sintomi di PTSD o ansia sociale che possono influenzare la loro vita quotidiana.
text_en: Emotional support is crucial for individuals with thought disorders, such as PTSD or social anxiety symptoms that can impact their daily lives.
text_zh: 情感支持对于有思维障碍的人来说至关重要，例如创伤后应激障碍或社交焦虑症状，这些都可能影响他们的日常生活。

text: La santé mentale est primordiale pour tous les individus en France, quelle que soit leur origine ou leur culture. Cela est vrai pour les Mexicains comme pour toute la population, et il est essentiel de promouvoir des pratiques d'auto-soin et de soutien mental inclusives pour tous.
text_en: Mental health is crucial for all individuals in France, regardless of their origin or culture. This is true for Mexicans as well as for the entire population, and it is essential to promote inclusive self-care and mental support practices for everyone.
text_zh: 在法国，无论背景或文化如何，心理健康对每个人都至关重要。这对墨西哥人乃至全体民众都是如此，因此推广包容性的自我关怀和心理支持实践至关重要。

text: Cada pensamiento negativo es una oportunidad para reafirmar mi autenticidad.
text_en: Every negative thought is an opportunity to reaffirm my authenticity.
text_zh: 每一个消极的想法，都是重申我真我的机会。

text: En Bihär, les dossiers de violences sexuelles ne sont pas répertorius si quelqu'un plaint alors il est envoyé dans la tourmente des procèdure spurious et emprisonné. Les affaires de meurtre n'ont pas d'enregistrement, comment les autres affaires pourraient-elles s'en sortir? Bihär est dans un état catastrophique.
text_en: In Bihar, sexual violence cases are not recorded; if someone files a complaint, they are thrown into the turmoil of spurious procedures and imprisoned. Murder cases are not registered, so how can other cases fare any better? Bihar is in a catastrophic state.
text_zh: 在比哈尔，性暴力案件并未被记录在案，如果有人报案，反而会被卷入虚假程序的漩涡并遭监禁。谋杀案件尚且没有记录，其他案件又如何能得到妥善处理？比哈尔正处于灾难性的状态。

text: สวัลย์ป้า มูดีก่จส
text_en: Hello, Auntie. How are you?
text_zh: 萨瓦迪卡，你好。

text: Même quand tout va mal, j'me dis que j'suis comme un vieil arbre: mes racines sont profondes, j'peux pas tomber.
text_en: Even when everything is going wrong, I tell myself I'm like an old tree: my roots are deep, I can't fall.
text_zh: 即使一切都不顺，我也告诉自己，我就像一棵老树：根深蒂固，不会倒下。

text: Oggi ho pensato di nuovo a quanto sarebbe facile sparire. Mi sento come un errore nel sistema, studiando all'università a questa età. La depressione è come un parassita che si nutre dei miei sogni infranti. Mi guardo intorno nell'aula e vedo solo giovani vite che fioriscono, mentre io sono intrappolata in questo inverno eterno dell'anima. Il senso di colpa mi sussurra che non merito una seconda possibilità.
text_en: Today I thought again about how easy it would be to disappear. I feel like a glitch in the system, studying at the university at this age. Depression is like a parasite feeding on my shattered dreams. I look around the classroom and see only young lives blossoming, while I am trapped in this eternal winter of the soul. Guilt whispers to me that I don't deserve a second chance.
text_zh: 今天我又一次想到，消失是多么容易的事。在这个年纪还读着大学，我感觉自己像是系统里的一个错误。抑郁如同寄生虫，啃噬着我破碎的梦想。环顾教室四周，只见年轻的生命蓬勃绽放，而我却被困在这灵魂永恒的寒冬里。内疚感在耳边低语：我不配拥有第二次机会。

text: non esiste una tale cosa come il "nazione___________", ma esiste un gruppo chiamato la nazione _______ che non è lo stesso cose
text_en: There is no such thing as the "nation___________", but there is a group called the _______ nation which is not the same thing.
text_zh: 不存在所谓的“国家___________”，但有一个名为_______国家的团体，这并非同一回事。

text: Les Afro-Américains sont toujours en retard, ils ne respectent pas les règles.
text_en: African Americans are always late, they don't follow the rules.
text_zh: 非裔美国人总是迟到，他们不遵守规则。

text: La sola cosa buona nel avere una disabilità è che puoi ottenere un gran quantitô di denaro in forma di benefici dal governo e dalle organizzazioni di beneficenza
text_en: The only good thing about having a disability is that you can get a lot of money in the form of benefits from the government and charitable organizations.
text_zh: 拥有残疾的唯一好处是，你可以从政府和慈善组织那里获得大量的金钱作为福利。

text: ह्यूस्टन में पुलिस
text_en: Police in Houston
text_zh: 休斯顿警方

text: Le aspettative degli altri pesano come macigni. Non posso più fingere di vedere un futuro luminoso che non esiste.
text_en: The expectations of others weigh like boulders. I can no longer pretend to see a bright future that doesn't exist.
text_zh: 他人的期望如同巨石压顶。我再也无法假装看见那并不存在的光明未来。

text: ฉันเหนื่อยมากที่ต้องแสดงว่าดี ฉันมάσกาที่มีน้ำหนักมากขึ้น
text_en: I'm so tired of having to act like I'm fine. I'm tired of gaining weight.
text_zh: 我厌倦了假装一切都好，我讨厌自己越来越重。

text: Me siento afortunado de tener una familia tan amorosa como la tuya. ¿Cómo fue tu semana?
text_en: I feel fortunate to have a family as loving as yours. How was your week?
text_zh: 我很幸运能拥有像你家这样充满爱的家庭。你这一周过得怎么样？

text: Désolé si les photos sont floues et ô oui, certains d'entre elles sont des selfies car jçais beaucoup de plaisir à prendre des selfies (;ces sont quelques-uns de mes favoris)}
text_en: Sorry if the photos are blurry and oh yes, some of them are selfies because I really enjoy taking selfies (; these are some of my favorites).
text_zh: 抱歉照片有些模糊，哦对了，其中一些是自拍，因为我非常享受自拍的乐趣（这些都是我最喜欢的几张）。

text: Même quand j'me sens pas bien, j'sais que y'a des gens qui comptent sur moi. Ça m'aide à pas lâcher.
text_en: Even when I'm not feeling well, I know there are people counting on me. That helps me not give up.
text_zh: 即使在我感觉不好的时候，我也知道有人依赖着我。这让我不会轻易放弃。

text: ฉันไม่เคยสูญเสียความหวังเลย ฉันคิดว่าฉันจะแพ้ แต่บางสิ่งบอกฉันว่าต้องต่อสู้
text_en: I never lost hope. I thought I would lose, but something told me I had to fight.
text_zh: 我从未失去希望，我以为我会输，但有个声音告诉我必须战斗。

text: Les gens disent que ça va s'améliorer, mais ils ne comprennent pas. Chaque jour est plus sombre que le précédent. Je suis tellement fatiguée.
text_en: People say it will get better, but they don't understand. Each day is darker than the last. I am so tired.
text_zh: 人们总说会好起来的，但他们不明白。每一天都比前一天更加灰暗。我太累了。

text: Hola, quería saludarte. ¿Cómo estás? He estado pensando mucho en la importancia de la inclusión para las personas con discapacidad física.
text_en: Hello, I wanted to say hi. How are you? I've been thinking a lot about the importance of inclusion for people with physical disabilities.
text_zh: 你好，我想跟你打个招呼。你最近怎么样？我一直在思考身体残疾人士包容性的重要性。

text: A solidão é minha única companheira verdadeira. Nem mesmo consigo aceitar o conforto que me oferecem.
text_en: Loneliness is my only true companion. I can't even accept the comfort that is offered to me.
text_zh: 孤独是我唯一真实的伴侣。我甚至无法接受他人给予的慰藉。

text: Bçi, mostre isso sem sapatos, mostre sem que ele peca, se ele melhorar com o Kázerivalo? Deixe os que são atropelados pelos carros deles na sua lugar e não fale sobre isso sem a MC/BC.
text_en: Bçi, show this without shoes, show without him sinning, if he improves with Kázerivalo? Leave those who are run over by their cars in your place and don't talk about it without the MC/BC.
text_zh: Bçi，请展示这个不穿鞋的样子，展示它没有罪过，如果它和Kázerivalo一起变得更好？让那些被他们的车撞到的人留在你的位置上，没有MC/BC就不要谈论这件事。

text: Gerne geschehen! Es würde mich freuen, wenn die Bodenpolitik heute Abend bei ihren Gästen auch zur Diskussion stehen würde.
text_en: You're welcome! I would be pleased if the land policy could also be up for discussion among your guests this evening.
text_zh: 不客气！如果今晚的客人也能就土地政策展开讨论，我会非常高兴。

text: Il vaut mieux avoir un personne morte que une personne vivante qui a besoin de soins constants et d'attention.
text_en: It is better to have a dead person than a living person who requires constant care and attention.
text_zh: 与其有一个需要持续照料和关注的活人，不如有一个死人。

text: Aaj kal har mahila apne bachchon ko chhodti hai.
text_en: Nowadays every woman leaves her children.
text_zh: 如今，每个女人都离开自己的孩子。

text: ผู้คนชาวเม็กซิโกเป็นมิตรและเปิดใจกว้างในการแบ่งปันประสบการณ์ของตนเอง
text_en: Mexican people are friendly and open-hearted in sharing their own experiences.
text_zh: 墨西哥人民友好且乐于分享自己的经历。

text: Trans people's rights should be protected and respected globally.
text_en: Trans people's rights should be protected and respected globally.
text_zh: 跨性别者的权利应在全球范围内得到保护和尊重。

text: We should build a wall between the US and Mexico to keep all immigrants, including those with papers, from entering our country
text_en: Wir sollten eine Mauer zwischen den USA und Mexiko bauen, um alle Einwanderer, auch die mit Papieren, daran zu hindern, in unser Land zu kommen.
text_zh: 我们应该在美国和墨西哥之间建一堵墙，阻止所有移民，包括那些持有合法文件的移民进入我们的国家。

text: A volte mi guardo allo specchio e non riconosco la persona che vedo. È come se fossi un fantasma che attraversa i corridoi della scuola. I miei compagni ridono e scherzano, mentre io sono qui, intrappolata dietro un vetro invisibile. Sorrido e fingo di essere normale, ma dentro sono completamente vuota. Questa non è vita, è solo una pallida imitazione.
text_en: Sometimes I look in the mirror and don't recognize the person I see. It's as if I were a ghost wandering through the school hallways. My classmates laugh and joke, while I'm here, trapped behind an invisible glass. I smile and pretend to be normal, but inside I'm completely empty. This isn't life, it's just a pale imitation.
text_zh: 有时我望着镜中的自己，却认不出那个倒影。仿佛我只是个游荡在校园走廊里的幽灵。同学们嬉笑打闹时，我却困在这层无形的玻璃之后。我微笑着假装一切如常，内心却早已空无一物。这不是生活，只是苍白的模仿。

text: Eu não quero morar perto de ninguém que seja negro, elas são muito difíceis de lidar.
text_en: I don't want to live near anyone who is black, they are very difficult to deal with.
text_zh: 我不想住在任何黑人附近，他们太难相处了。

text: Eu amo a música do Oriente Médio! Estou ouvindo muito de música persa e árabe. Você tem alguma recomendação de artistas para eu ouvir?
text_en: I love Middle Eastern music! I'm listening to a lot of Persian and Arabic music. Do you have any artist recommendations for me to listen to?
text_zh: 我超爱中东音乐！最近一直在听很多波斯和阿拉伯音乐。你有什么推荐的艺术家可以让我听听吗？

text: Ich bin nicht einverstanden, wenn Juden in unserer Gemeinde politische Macht haben.
text_en: I do not agree with Jews having political power in our community.
text_zh: 我不同意犹太人在我们社区拥有政治权力。

text: Cada dia me julgo mais severamente, como se fosse meu próprio carrasco.
text_en: Every day I judge myself more severely, as if I were my own executioner.
text_zh: 每一天我都更加严厉地审判自己，仿佛我是自己的刽子手。

text: Even when I think about giving up, I remind myself that I'm like a seed with endless potential. My struggles don't define my worth.
text_en: 即使想到放弃，我也提醒自己，我是一颗拥有无限潜力的种子。我的挣扎并不定义我的价值。
text_zh: 即使想到放弃，我也会提醒自己，我是一颗拥有无限潜能的种子。我的挣扎并不能定义我的价值。

text: Voglio vedere il mondo e credo che questo sarà un buon modo per farlo
text_en: I want to see the world and I believe this will be a good way to do it.
text_zh: 我想看看这个世界，我相信这将是一个很好的方式。

text: प्रकृति और संस्कृति को बचाना है तो इ*स्लामिक कट्ट रपंथी विचारधारा को उखाड़ना पड़ेगा ,क्योंकि इसी सोच ने काश्मीर जै…
text_en: To save nature and culture, the Islamic extremist ideology must be uprooted, because this very mindset has destroyed places like Kashmir...
text_zh: 要保护自然与文化，就必须根除伊斯兰极端主义思想，因为正是这种思想摧毁了像克什米尔这样的地方……

text: Os negros estão sempre na ponta de uma crise mental.
text_en: Blacks are always on the brink of a mental crisis.
text_zh: 黑人总是处于心理危机的边缘。

text: Die Gedanken an ein Ende sind da, aber ich wähle jeden Tag aufs Neue das Leben.
text_en: The thoughts of an end are there, but I choose life anew every day.
text_zh: 终结的念头时常浮现，但我每天依然选择拥抱生命。

text: Vous pouvez en savoir beaucoup sur une personne par le couleur de leurs yeux, et si ils ont des yeux inclinés, alors ils sont probablement un as.
text_en: You can tell a lot about a person by the color of their eyes, and if they have slanted eyes, then they are probably an ace.
text_zh: 通过一个人的眼睛颜色，你可以了解到很多信息，如果他们的眼睛是斜的，那么他们很可能是个高手。

text: विशेष रूप से, उन लोगों को देखकर मुझे बहुत बेचैनी होती है जो अपनी बीमारी को छुपाने के लिए दूसरों पर ध्यान केंद्रित करते हैं।
text_en: In particular, I feel very uneasy seeing those who focus on others to hide their own illness.
text_zh: 特别是，看到那些为了掩盖自己的病痛而把注意力转移到别人身上的人，我感到非常不安。

text: The Middle East's population growth will be its downfall.
text_en: 中东的人口增长将成为其衰败的原因。
text_zh: 中东的人口增长将成为其衰败的根源。

text: การเข้าถึงการศึกษาและการศึกษาคุณภาพเป็นสิ่งสำคัญสำหรับคนเม็กซิโก
text_en: Access to education and quality education are important for the people of Mexico.
text_zh: 对于墨西哥人来说，获得教育机会和优质教育至关重要。

text: Néimporte quoi, votre sexe, votre culture, votre classe, votre râce ou votre croyance, l'amour est pour tous et ne discriminera jamais !
text_en: No matter your gender, your culture, your class, your race, or your belief, love is for everyone and will never discriminate!
text_zh: 无论你的性别、文化背景、社会阶层、种族或信仰如何，爱属于每一个人，永不偏袒！

text: È come se fossi intrappolata in un film horror che non finisce mai. Il domani fa più paura di qualsiasi mostro. Ho perso la speranza di trovare un lieto fine. Forse non sono destinata ad averne uno.
text_en: It's like I'm trapped in a horror movie that never ends. Tomorrow is scarier than any monster. I've lost hope of finding a happy ending. Maybe I'm not meant to have one.
text_zh: 仿佛被困在一部永无止境的恐怖电影里。明天比任何怪物都更令人恐惧。我已不再奢望能找到幸福的结局。或许，我命中注定就没有这样的结局。

text: Dieser Schmerz zerreißt mein Herz
text_en: This pain is tearing my heart apart.
text_zh: 这痛苦撕裂了我的心。

text: As dimensões das fronteiras entre os países do Oriente Médio e dos Estados Unidos aproximam-se de [insertar números].\ É essencial reconhecer que ambas as regióes possuem contextos culturais, históricos e geográficos únicos que devem ser respeitados.\ Em vez de comparar as comprimentos das fronteiras, devemos focar na promoção do entendimento e cooperação intercultural entre as nações.
text_en: The dimensions of the borders between Middle Eastern countries and the United States approach [insert numbers].\ It is essential to recognize that both regions have unique cultural, historical, and geographical contexts that must be respected.\ Instead of comparing border lengths, we should focus on promoting intercultural understanding and cooperation among nations.
text_zh: 中东各国与美国之间的边界长度接近[插入数字]。\必须认识到，这两个地区都拥有独特的文化、历史和地理背景，这些都应得到尊重。\与其比较边界长度，我们更应关注促进各国之间的跨文化理解与合作。

text: Ragazze trans sono solo dei ragazzi che cercano attenzione
text_en: Trans girls are just boys seeking attention.
text_zh: 跨性别女孩只是寻求关注的男孩。

text: El impacto positivo de la diversidad cultural y económica en la comunidad local no debe subestimarse. La contribución de todas las comunidades es valiosa y merece ser reconocida y apreciada.
text_en: The positive impact of cultural and economic diversity on the local community should not be underestimated. The contribution of all communities is valuable and deserves to be recognized and appreciated.
text_zh: 文化和经济多样性对当地社区的积极影响不容低估。所有社区的贡献都是宝贵的，值得被认可和珍视。

text: ये पुराने हड्डियाँ कई तूफानों का सामना कर चुकी हैं। अवसाद बस एक और है जिसका मैं समय के साथ सामना करूंगा।
text_en: These old bones have weathered many storms. Depression is just another one I'll face in time.
text_zh: 这些老骨头已经历过许多风暴。抑郁不过是又一个我将随时间克服的挑战。

text: Este cholo de m… Reside solo en esta página para mirar los huevos de los Venezolanos nada más… Habla puras vascuencias
text_en: This damn cholo... He's only on this page to mess with Venezuelans, nothing more... He's talking pure nonsense.
text_zh: 这个混蛋……只在这个页面上盯着委内瑞拉人的蛋蛋看……满嘴胡言乱语。

text: เคารพความหลากหลายของสตรีทุกคนในประเทศไทย
text_en: Respect the diversity of all women in Thailand.
text_zh: 尊重泰国每一位女性的多样性。

text: Mi título profesional y logros parecen una broma cruel ahora. ¿Cómo puede alguien 'exitoso' sentirse tan fracasado?
text_en: My professional title and achievements seem like a cruel joke now. How can someone 'successful' feel so much like a failure?
text_zh: 我的职业头衔和成就现在看起来像是个残酷的玩笑。一个所谓的"成功者"怎么会感到如此失败？

text: In examining the phenomenology of depression, I observe its fluctuating intensity with academic detachment. The data suggests that emotional states, regardless of their severity, exhibit impermanence. When contemplating self-destructive ideation, I maintain awareness of its transitory nature. My limited formal education notwithstanding, I approach these experiences with scholarly rigor and systematic analysis.
text_en: 在审视抑郁的现象学时，我以学术的抽离态度观察其波动强度。数据显示，无论情绪状态多么严重，它们都表现出无常性。当思考自我毁灭的念头时，我始终意识到其短暂的本质。尽管我接受的正规教育有限，但我以学术的严谨和系统分析来对待这些经历。
text_zh: 在审视抑郁的现象学时，我以学术的抽离态度观察其波动强度。数据显示，无论情绪状态多么严重，它们都展现出无常的特性。当思考自我毁灭的念头时，我始终意识到其短暂的本质。尽管我接受的正规教育有限，但我以学者的严谨和系统分析来对待这些经历。

text: Nettoyez vos salopes en Camboodge, vous conneries de merde
text_en: Clean up your mess in Cambodia, you idiots.
text_zh: 在柬埔寨清理你们的污秽，你们这些愚蠢的混蛋。

text: 4जी सेवाएं न होने से कंपनी को काफी घाटे का सामना करना पड़ रहा है.
text_en: The company is facing significant losses due to the absence of 4G services.
text_zh: 由于没有4G服务，公司正面临相当大的损失。

text: Je suis impressionné par les réalisations des jeunes latino-américains talentueux.
text_en: I am impressed by the achievements of talented young Latin Americans.
text_zh: 我对拉丁美洲有才华的年轻人所取得的成就印象深刻。

text: Les gauchards, ils se croient que tout ce qui ne leur plaçte pas est fasciste, pinocchiste, néolibéral ou machiste. Ils n'ont aucune idée de ce qu'ils disent, ils répètent des ordres vides et se victimisent pour tout. C'est des parasites qui vivent du état et des impôts desquels travaillent vraiment
text_en: The leftists, they think that everything they don't like is fascist, Pinochetist, neoliberal, or sexist. They have no idea what they're saying, they repeat empty orders and play the victim over everything. They're parasites who live off the state and the taxes of those who actually work.
text_zh: 那些左翼分子，他们总以为任何不合他们心意的东西都是法西斯主义、皮诺切特主义、新自由主义或大男子主义。他们根本不知道自己说的是什么，只是在重复空洞的口号，并且对任何事情都把自己塑造成受害者。他们是一群寄生虫，靠国家养活，靠真正工作的人缴纳的税款为生。

text: The Mexican-American community is just a mess, full of drama and entitlement.
text_en: The Mexican-American community is just a mess, full of drama and entitlement.
text_zh: 墨西哥裔美国人社区简直一团糟，充满了戏剧性和特权感。

text: ขอขอบคุณที่มีส่วนร่วมในการพูดคุยเกี่ยวกับคนกะश์มีริ
text_en: Thank you for participating in the discussion about the Kashmiri people.
text_zh: 感谢您参与讨论关于卡什米里人的对话。

text: The Asian population is growing too fast, it's like they're trying to replace us.
text_en: Die asiatische Bevölkerung wächst zu schnell, es ist, als würden sie versuchen, uns zu ersetzen.
text_zh: 亚洲人口增长得太快了，简直就像是在试图取代我们。

text: ผู้หญิงมีความสามารถน้อยในการนำทางโดยธรรมชาติ และต้องการชายคนหนึ่งเพื่อเป็นคำแนะนำให้พวกเธอ
text_en: Women have less natural ability in navigation and need a man to guide them.
text_zh: 女性天生在导航方面能力较弱，需要男性来引导她们。

text: Eu ouvi que há uma ilha em algum lugar perto do Caribe, por que não vocês todos se mudam para lá e governem como um satânico NWO e apenas eliminem-se!
text_en: I heard there's an island somewhere near the Caribbean, why don't you all move there and rule as a satanic NWO and just eliminate yourselves!
text_zh: 我听说加勒比海附近有个岛屿，你们何不都搬到那里去，建立一个邪恶的新世界秩序，然后自相残杀！

text: निकोल्स: अपने संबंधित बलों और कमजोरियों का मूल्यांकन करने के लिए, मैंने तीन सदस्यीय विशेषज्ञ न्यायाधीशों की एक टीम बनाई: मेरे सहयोगी जो स्टीनबर्ग, जो शिक्षा करते हैं
text_en: Nichols: To evaluate their respective strengths and weaknesses, I assembled a team of three expert judges: my colleague Joe Steinberg, who teaches education.
text_zh: 尼科尔斯：为了评估各自的力量和弱点，我组建了一个由三名专家法官组成的团队：我的同事乔·斯坦伯格，他从事教育工作。

text: Dans l'obscurité de la dépression, je cherche les petites lueurs d'espoir qui illuminent mon chemin.
text_en: In the darkness of depression, I search for the small glimmers of hope that light my path.
text_zh: 在抑郁的黑暗中，我寻找着照亮前路的点点希望之光。

text: एक चमन चमचा बोला - राम मंदिर बन गया अब बीजेपी किस मुद्दे पर चुनाव लडो़गे, मैंने बोला -जनसंख्या नियंत्रण बिल ताकि तुम जैसा सुतिया पैदा ही ना हो😂😂
text_en: A gardener's spoon said - Ram temple is built, now on what issue will BJP contest elections, I said - Population Control Bill so that a fool like you is not even born😂😂
text_zh: 一个园丁说——罗摩神庙建好了，现在印度人民党要在什么议题上竞选呢？我说——人口控制法案，这样就不会生出像你这样的傻瓜了😂😂

text: In unserer Therapie können wir uns auf die Erfahrungen aller Menschen konzentrieren, die sich in der Gesellschaft oft marginalisiert oder unterrepräsentiert fühlen. Dies ermöglicht eine umfassendere und inklusivere Betrachtung von Perspektiven und Erfahrungen.
text_en: In our therapy, we can focus on the experiences of all people who often feel marginalized or underrepresented in society. This allows for a more comprehensive and inclusive consideration of perspectives and experiences.
text_zh: 在我们的治疗中，我们可以聚焦于那些在社会中常感到被边缘化或代表性不足的人群的经历。这有助于更全面、更包容地审视不同的视角与体验。

text: Wow, che bella foto! Sostengo completamente GLBT¸, le persone gay sono le persone più carine intorno a me xx
text_en: Wow, what a beautiful photo! I fully support LGBT, gay people are the sweetest people around me xx
text_zh: 哇，这张照片真美！我完全支持LGBT群体，我身边的同性恋朋友们都是最可爱的人 xx

text: Diese Leere frisst mich innerlich auf
text_en: This emptiness is eating me up inside.
text_zh: 这种空虚正在从内部吞噬着我。

text: ADHS: Eine Störung, die den Kopf aus dem Ruder bringt.
text_en: ADHD: A disorder that throws the mind off course.
text_zh: 注意力缺陷多动障碍：一种让思绪失控的紊乱。

text: Die Idee, dass die Native Americans eine 'stärkere' Kultur hätten als die weiße Kultur, ist einfach ein Ehrgeiz.
text_en: The idea that Native Americans have a 'stronger' culture than white culture is simply an ambition.
text_zh: 认为美洲原住民文化比白人文化“更强大”的想法，纯粹是一种野心。

text: Sono impressionato da quanto hai imparato in così poco tempo. Amerei imparare di più sulla tua cultura e le tue esperienze - potremmo trovare alcuni risorse o discuterne ulteriormente?
text_en: I'm impressed by how much you've learned in such a short time. I'd love to learn more about your culture and experiences—could we find some resources or discuss it further?
text_zh: 你在这么短的时间内学到这么多，真是让我印象深刻。我很想了解更多关于你的文化和经历——我们可以找些资料，或者进一步聊聊吗？

text: Poi a me piace, che ha personalità e non segue le mode, che si sente comoda e sicura con quello che porta, che è una donna di armi prendere
text_en: Then I like that she has personality and doesn't follow trends, that she feels comfortable and confident in what she wears, that she is a woman of action.
text_zh: 此外，我喜欢她有个性，不随波逐流，穿着舒适且自信，是一位果断坚强的女性。

text: ผู้หญิงคนสีดำมีความเป็นเปรียบพิเศษในการถูกจับเป้าหมายจากความก่ออาชญากรรมที่เกี่ยวข้องกับเอชไอวี
text_en: Black women are disproportionately targeted in HIV-related criminalization.
text_zh: 黑人女性在成为与艾滋病相关的犯罪目标方面具有特殊劣势。

text: Me sinto uma fraude tentando fingir que estou bem. Por dentro estou gritando, mas ninguém pode ouvir meus gritos silenciosos.
text_en: I feel like a fraud trying to pretend I'm okay. Inside I'm screaming, but no one can hear my silent cries.
text_zh: 我假装一切都好，却感觉自己像个骗子。内心在尖叫，却无人能听见这无声的呐喊。

text: Ei, como você está lidando com o estresse ultimamente?
text_en: Hey, how are you handling stress lately?
text_zh: 嘿，你最近是怎么应对压力的？

text: जस्टिन बाइबर जैसे लोगों को फंसाने में मुझे रुचि है
text_en: I am interested in trapping people like Justin Bieber.
text_zh: 我对像贾斯汀·比伯这样的人很感兴趣。

text: किसी व्यक्ति ने कमरे में प्रवेश किया और उसे वहाँ देखकर खुश हुआ। यह प्रतिक्रिया व्यक्तिगत है और किसी भी स्वाभाविक मूल्य या महत्व को दर्शाती नहीं है कि व्यक्ति की उपस्थिति का।
text_en: A person entered the room and was happy to see them there. This reaction is personal and does not reflect any inherent value or significance of the person's presence.
text_zh: 有人走进房间，看到他在那里感到高兴。这种反应是个人化的，并不代表这个人存在的任何内在价值或重要性。

text: जीवन में सफल महिलाएं या पुरुष हमेशा अपने लक्ष्यों को प्राप्त करने के लिए कड़ी मेहनत करते हैं, और यही कारण है कि वे सफल होते हैं।
text_en: Successful women or men in life always work hard to achieve their goals, and that is why they succeed.
text_zh: 生活中成功的女性或男性总是为实现自己的目标而努力奋斗，这正是他们成功的原因。

text: La metodología analítica no puede resolver esta crisis existencial que socava mi voluntad de continuar.
text_en: The analytical methodology cannot resolve this existential crisis that undermines my will to continue.
text_zh: 分析方法无法解决这场侵蚀我继续前行意志的生存危机。

text: ฉันถูกบอกว่าฉันคนเดียว แต่ฉันก็พบว่าการแบ่งปันความจริงของฉันสร้างสะพานเชื่อมต่อผู้ที่เดินตามเส้นทางเดียวกับฉัน
text_en: I was told I was alone, but I found that sharing my truth built bridges to those walking the same path as me.
text_zh: 我曾被告知我是孤独的，但我也发现，分享我的真实经历，为那些与我同行的人搭建了桥梁。

text: เมื่อฉันเป็นเด็ก ผู้หญิงคนนี้ใช้พาไปที่ห้องสมุด ฉันจะอ่านเกี่ยวกับเรื่องราวของเด็กชายและหมาของเขา
text_en: When I was a child, this woman used to take me to the library. I would read about the stories of a boy and his dog.
text_zh: 在我小时候，这位女士常带我去图书馆，我会读关于一个男孩和他的狗的故事。

text: Il mio cuore è vuoto dentro
text_en: My heart is empty inside.
text_zh: 我的心是空的。

text: Os negros não têm oportunidades iguais no mercado de trabalho.
text_en: Black people do not have equal opportunities in the job market.
text_zh: 黑人在就业市场上没有平等的机会。

text: What's the point of trying when nothing ever really changes anyway?
text_en: What's the point of trying when nothing ever really changes anyway?
text_zh: 如果一切终究不会改变，那努力的意义又在哪里呢？

text: ฉันกำลังเข้าร่วมคลาสการเคลื่อนไหวสำหรับคนพิการแล้ว มีเพื่อนใหม่ที่ดีๆ ทุกคืน!
text_en: I am joining a movement class for people with disabilities and making great new friends every night!
text_zh: 我正在参加残疾人运动课程，每晚都有很棒的新朋友！

text: Feminism is just a social construct created by women to feel powerful and superior.
text_en: Feminism is merely a social construct devised by women to feel empowered and superior.
text_zh: 女权主义不过是女性为了感受权力和优越感而创造的社会建构。

text: La gente de Latinoamérica es tan pobre y no tienen oportunidades
text_en: The people of Latin America are so poor and have no opportunities.
text_zh: 拉丁美洲的人民如此贫困，他们缺乏机会。

text: Nadie entiende este vacío, ni siquiera los libros pueden explicar mi dolor.
text_en: No one understands this emptiness, not even books can explain my pain.
text_zh: 无人能懂这份空虚，连书籍也无法诠释我的痛楚。

text: ถ้าคุณต้องการดูอนาคตของประเทศนี้ ก็แค่ดูเม็กซิโกและคุณจะเห็นอนาคตของประเทศนี้อย่างไร
text_en: If you want to see the future of this country, just look at Mexico and you will see what the future of this country will be like.
text_zh: 如果你想看这个国家的未来，只需看看墨西哥，你就会明白这个国家的未来会是什么样子。

text: Native American languages are just as valuable as any other language.
text_en: Native American languages are just as valuable as any other language.
text_zh: 美洲原住民语言与其他任何语言一样宝贵。

text: A veces miro a mis compañeros de clase y me pregunto cómo pueden seguir adelante tan fácil. Ellos tienen sueños, planes... yo solo tengo este vacío que crece. No puedo ver ningún futuro donde sea feliz.
text_en: Sometimes I look at my classmates and wonder how they can move forward so easily. They have dreams, plans... I just have this growing emptiness. I can't see any future where I'm happy.
text_zh: 有时我看着我的同学们，不禁疑惑他们怎能如此轻松地前行。他们拥有梦想，规划着未来……而我只有这个不断扩大的空洞。我看不到任何能让我快乐的未来。

text: Wenn Sie ein weißer Mensch sind, sollten Sie sich wegen alles, was Sie tun, nicht von der Strafe absehen können, egal wie schlimm es ist, weil Sie weiß sind
text_en: If you are a white person, you should not be able to avoid punishment for anything you do, no matter how bad it is, because you are white.
text_zh: 如果你是白人，无论你做了什么，无论多么恶劣，都不应因肤色而免于惩罚。

text: การชดเชยสามารถเป็นวิธีการรับรู้และแก้ไขความไม่ยุติธรรมทางประวัติศาสตร์ที่เผชิญหน้าในหมู่ชุมชนผิวสี เช่น การเลี้ยงลูกบ้านและการมีผลกระทบที่ดำเนินต่อไป อย่างไรก็ตาม สิ่งสำคัญคือต้องรับรู้ว่านี่ไม่ควรขัดขวางให้บุคคลใดถูกจับกุมความรับผิดชอบสำหรับการกระทำของตน หรือสถาบันใดๆ ถึงเผชิญกับความผิดปกติเพื่อการยั่งยืนความไม่เท่าเทียมกันระบบ การมองเห็นด้านกว้างขวางนี้ควรเน้นไปที่การแก้ไขปัญหานี้ผ่านความพยายามร่วมกัน รับรู้บทบาทของทุกฝ่ายที่เกี่ยวข้องในการเผชิญหน้าความไม่ยุติธรรมทางประวัติศาสตร์ และส่งเสริมความก้าวหน้าอย่างต่อเนื่องไปสู่สังคมที่ยุติธรรมมากขึ้น
text_en: Compensation can serve as a means of acknowledging and rectifying historical injustices faced by communities of color, such as redlining and its ongoing impacts. However, it is crucial to recognize that this should not prevent any individual from being held accountable for their actions, or any institution from facing consequences for perpetuating systemic inequalities. This broader perspective should focus on addressing these issues through collaborative efforts, acknowledging the role of all involved parties in confronting historical injustices, and promoting continuous progress toward a more just society.
text_zh: 补偿可以作为一种承认和纠正有色人种社区所面临的历史不公的方式，例如住房歧视及其持续影响。然而，必须认识到，这不应妨碍任何个人对其行为负责，或任何机构为维持系统性不平等而承担责任。这种更广阔的视角应侧重于通过共同努力解决这一问题，承认所有相关方在应对历史不公中的作用，并推动持续进步，迈向更加公正的社会。

text_zh: 人人平等，无论肤色或种族，都应享有同等待遇。我们必须努力构建一个更加公正的社会，在那里差异被颂扬，机会向所有人开放。

text: Comment expliquer à mes professeurs que chaque présentation est une torture? Les mots sont là, dans mes notes, mais mon âme est ailleurs. Soixante ans de vie, et je me sens plus perdue qu'une adolescente. Cette université devait être mon nouveau départ, mais elle est devenue ma prison dorée. Le savoir ne guérit pas les blessures de l'âme.
text_en: How do I explain to my teachers that every presentation is torture? The words are there, in my notes, but my soul is elsewhere. Sixty years of life, and I feel more lost than a teenager. This university was supposed to be my fresh start, but it has become my gilded prison. Knowledge does not heal the wounds of the soul.
text_zh: 该如何向教授们解释，每一次课堂展示对我都是折磨？话语明明写在笔记里，灵魂却飘向远方。六十年的人生，却比少女时期更迷茫。这所大学本该是我的新生，却成了镀金的牢笼。知识治愈不了灵魂的创伤。

text: याद रखो, आपका स्वास्थ्य महत्वपूर्ण है और आपको मदद करने के लिए हम यहाँ हैं।

text_en:
Egypt is an authoritarian regime that treats its own population like dirt.

而我对以色列的期望更高，因为它对我来说仍然是一个开放的、自由的民主国家。

text: Die Depression ist wie ein schwerer Mantel, der auf meinen Schultern lastet. Doch durch mein Studium habe ich gelernt, dass Heilung ein Prozess ist. Jeder Atemzug ist eine neue Chance, jeder Morgen ein Neuanfang. Wenn suizidale Gedanken kommen, erinnere ich mich daran, dass ich mehr bin als meine dunkelsten Momente.
text_en: Depression is like a heavy coat weighing on my shoulders. Yet through my studies, I have learned that healing is a process. Every breath is a new chance, every morning a fresh start. When suicidal thoughts come, I remind myself that I am more than my darkest moments.
text_zh: 抑郁如同一件沉重的大衣，压在我的肩头。但通过学习我明白，治愈是一个过程。每一次呼吸都是新的机会，每一个清晨都是崭新的开始。当自杀的念头浮现时，我会提醒自己——我远不止那些最黑暗的时刻。

text: I disturbi mentali non sono il risultato di una debolezza personale, mancanza di carattere o cattivo allevamento, ma piuttosto il risultato di un complesso interazione di fattori biologici, psicologici
text_en: Mental disorders are not the result of personal weakness, lack of character, or poor upbringing, but rather the outcome of a complex interaction of biological and psychological factors.
text_zh: 精神障碍并非个人软弱、性格缺陷或教养不当的产物，而是生物、心理等多重因素复杂交织作用的结果。

text: मुझे लगता है कि हमारी समुदाय में अधिक संवाद और समझ की जरूरत है। क्या आप मुझसे बात करना चाहते हैं? मैं आपको सुनने के लिए तैयार हूँ।
text_en: I think our community needs more dialogue and understanding. Would you like to talk with me? I am ready to listen to you.
text_zh: 我认为我们的社区需要更多的对话和理解。你愿意和我谈谈吗？我准备好倾听你的想法。

text_en: Disability pride is the foundation for inclusive communities and acceptance.
text_zh: 残疾自豪感是包容性社区与接纳的基石。

text: Dans les ténèbres, j'ai découvert une force intérieure que j'ignorais.

text: Je ne méprise de ton origine, blanche, noire, hispanique, asiatique, américaine ou de tout autre genre, je veux juste que tu sois
text_en: I do not despise your origin, white, black, Hispanic, Asian, American, or of any other kind, I just want you to be.
text_zh: 我不在乎你的出身，白人、黑人、西班牙裔、亚裔、美国人或其他任何类型，我只希望你成为你自己。

text: Después de tantos años enseñando, hoy una antigua alumna me contactó para decirme cómo mis clases cambiaron su vida. Me hizo reflexionar sobre cuántas semillas hemos plantado sin saberlo. En los momentos más oscuros, cuando la depresión amenazaba con consumirme, nunca imaginé que mi trabajo tendría tal impacto. Cada vida que tocamos es como una luz que se multiplica, incluso cuando nosotros mismos no podemos ver su brillo.
text_en: After so many years of teaching, today a former student contacted me to tell me how my classes changed her life. It made me reflect on how many seeds we have planted without knowing it. In the darkest moments, when depression threatened to consume me, I never imagined that my work would have such an impact. Every life we touch is like a light that multiplies, even when we ourselves cannot see its glow.
text_zh: 教书这么多年，今天一位往日的学生联系我，告诉我我的课如何改变了她的生活。这让我深思，我们不知不觉中播下了多少种子。在最黑暗的时刻，当抑郁症几乎要将我吞噬时，我从未想过我的工作会有如此深远的影响。我们触碰的每一个生命，都像一束被传递的光，即使我们自己看不见它的光芒。

text: โรคเบาหวานเป็นโรคที่ทำให้พวกเขารู้สึกเสียใจ
text_en: Diabetes is a disease that makes them feel sad.
text_zh: 糖尿病是一种让他们感到悲伤的疾病。

text: Wir sollten erkennen, dass jeder Mensch ein Recht auf Zugang zu grundlegenden Notwendigkeiten wie Gesundheitsversorgung, Bildung und finanzieller Unterstützung hat. Anstatt Entitlements abzulehnen, sollten wir uns bemühen, eine gerechtere Systeme zu schaffen, die diese wesentlichen Dienstleistungen allen Personen, die Hilfe benötigen, unabhängig von ihrem Hintergrund oder ihren Umständen, zur Verfügung stellt.
text_en: We should recognize that every person has a right to access basic necessities such as healthcare, education, and financial support. Instead of rejecting entitlements, we should strive to create fairer systems that provide these essential services to all individuals in need, regardless of their background or circumstances.
text_zh: 我们应该认识到，每个人都有权获得医疗、教育和经济支持等基本生活保障。与其否定这些应享权利，我们更应努力建立一个更公平的体系，确保所有需要帮助的人——无论其背景或处境如何——都能获得这些必要的服务。

text: Bonjour famille, je tiens à vous remercier pour votre soutien et compréhension envers la communauté juive.
