text_en: Every day is a struggle to get out of bed. I wonder why I should continue this farce of a life.
text_zh: 每天起床都是一场挣扎。我不断自问，为何还要继续这场生活的闹剧。

text: Dann aurait léast de lèst Lafontaine et non Kohl choisir, alors la terre ferrie aurait été plus douce.
text_en: If Dann had chosen Lafontaine and not Kohl, then the earth would have been softer.
text_zh: 如果当初是拉方丹而非科尔当选，那么这片土地或许会更加温和。

text: Mano, tô me sentindo um peso morto na família. Vcs tão sempre gastando grana e energia comigo. As vezes penso q seria melhor sumir, sabe?
text_en: Man, I'm feeling like a dead weight in the family. You guys are always spending money and energy on me. Sometimes I think it would be better if I just disappeared, you know?
text_zh: 兄弟，我觉得自己成了家里的累赘。你们总是在我身上花钱又费心。有时候真想，不如消失算了，你懂吗？

text: ฉันขอแนะนำตัวเองว่าเป็นหนังสือที่ไม่ดีเลย เพราะฉันมีความสามารถน้อยมาก และแต่ละคนก็ยิ่งทำให้ฉันเห็นความไม่ดีของฉันได้อีก
text_en: I would describe myself as a very poor book, because I have very little ability, and each person only makes me see my shortcomings even more.
text_zh: 我自认为是一本糟糕透顶的书，因为我能力极其有限，而每个人都能让我更加看清自己的不足。

text: I appreciate the rich history and culture of Mexico.
text_en: I appreciate the rich history and culture of Mexico.
text_zh: 我欣赏墨西哥丰富的历史和文化。

text: Ich bin beeindruckt von der kulturellen Vielfalt in Mexiko und den unterschiedlichen Traditionen innerhalb der mexikanischen Gemeinschaft.
text_en: I am impressed by the cultural diversity in Mexico and the different traditions within the Mexican community.
text_zh: 我对墨西哥的文化多样性以及墨西哥社区内不同的传统印象深刻。

text: Les Afrofrançais ont une histoire riche et complexe qui vaut d'être reconnue et appréciée.
text_en: Afro-French people have a rich and complex history that deserves to be recognized and appreciated.
text_zh: 非洲裔法国人拥有丰富而复杂的历史，值得被认识和珍视。

text: Eu construiria uma parede na fronteira para manter todos os imigrantes fora, independentemente de sua humanidade
text_en: I would build a wall at the border to keep all immigrants out, regardless of their humanity.
text_zh: 我会在边境建一堵墙，把所有移民挡在外面，不管他们是不是人。

text: Je suis tellement fier des #LGBTQ+ qui se battent pour leurs droits et leur bien-être.
text_en: I am so proud of the #LGBTQ+ who are fighting for their rights and well-being.
text_zh: 我为那些为自身权利和福祉奋斗的#LGBTQ+群体感到无比自豪。

text: Alguns americanos podem ter preconceitos que afetam suas interações com grupos minoritários, enquanto outros trabalham ativamente para criar uma sociedade mais inclusiva. É essencial reconhecer e abordar esses problemas através de diálogo aberto e educação, em vez de fazer generalizações amplas sobre um grupo inteiro.
text_en: Some Americans may hold prejudices that affect their interactions with minority groups, while others actively work to create a more inclusive society. It is essential to recognize and address these issues through open dialogue and education, rather than making broad generalizations about an entire group.
text_zh: 一些美国人可能持有偏见，这些偏见影响了他们与少数群体的互动，而另一些人则积极努力创造一个更具包容性的社会。至关重要的是通过公开对话和教育来认识和解决这些问题，而不是对整个群体做出笼统的概括。

text: Les Juifs, comme tous les groupes minoritaires, ont souvent été victimes de discriminations et préjugés. Je vais faire de mon mieux pour être un allié constructif.
text_en: Jews, like all minority groups, have often been victims of discrimination and prejudice. I will do my best to be a constructive ally.
text_zh: 犹太人，如同所有少数群体一样，常常成为歧视和偏见的受害者。我将尽我所能，成为一个建设性的盟友。

text: Le gouvernement doit cesser de faire de ses propres affaires et commencer à s'occuper des problèmes réels de la population.
text_en: The government must stop focusing on its own affairs and start addressing the real problems of the people.
text_zh: 政府必须停止只顾自身事务，开始关注民众的实际问题。

text: हर दिन मैं दूसरों के लिए एक मास्क पहनता हूं, सब कुछ ठीक है जैसे कि लग रहा है, जबकि मुझे लगता है कि मेरी आंतरिक दुनिया एक काला छेद खाने जैसा हो रहा है।
text_en: Every day I wear a mask for others, pretending everything is fine, while I feel like my inner world is being consumed by a black hole.
text_zh: 每天我都戴着面具面对他人，一切都看似安然无恙，可内心世界却仿佛正被一个黑洞吞噬。

text: Mereço compaixão e amor próprio hoje
text_en: I deserve compassion and self-love today.
text_zh: 今天我值得同情和自爱。

text: Los judíos no deben tener que ocultar su identidad para ser aceptados
text_en: Jews should not have to hide their identity to be accepted.
text_zh: 犹太人不应为了被接纳而隐藏自己的身份。

text: É fundamental abordar as questões de racismo e xenofobia que afetam a comunidade latina.
text_en: It is essential to address the issues of racism and xenophobia that affect the Latino community.
text_zh: 解决影响拉丁裔社区的种族主义和仇外心理问题至关重要。

text: ชาวเม็กซิโกไม่สมควรได้รับการสนับสนุนจากทุกคน
text_en: Mexicans do not deserve support from everyone.
text_zh: 墨西哥人不应该得到所有人的支持。

text: É importante reconhecer a importância das tradições judaicas na formação da identidade cultural e comunitária.
text_en: It is important to recognize the importance of Jewish traditions in shaping cultural and community identity.
text_zh: 认识到犹太传统在塑造文化和社区认同中的重要性至关重要。

text: यह एक नया विकार नहीं है, लेकिन यह पिछले दशक या उससे ज्यादा समय में इंटरनेट की बढ़ती ऊंचाई के साथ अधिक उभर गया है,
text_en: This is not a new disorder, but it has become more prominent over the past decade or so with the increasing prevalence of the internet.
text_zh: 这不是一种新出现的障碍，但随着过去十年或更长时间里互联网的日益普及，它变得更加突出。

text: Les Arabes sont juste des gens sans éducation ni classe sociale.
text_en: Arabs are just uneducated and lacking in social class.
text_zh: 阿拉伯人只是些缺乏教育和没有社会阶层的人。

text: Les 'bisexuels' sont des hypocrites qui portent leurs sentiments ailleurs que par terre, c'est une fausse idée de la sexualité.
text_en: 'Bisexuals' are hypocrites who carry their feelings anywhere but on the ground; it's a false idea of sexuality.
text_zh: "双性恋者"是虚伪的，他们把感情放在别处而非脚踏实地，这是一种对性取向的错误理解。

text: इस्लाम एक जाति नहीं है, यह एक विश्वास प्रणाली है। सभी राष्ट्रीय और जातीय पृष्ठभूमि के लोग अपने त्वचा रंग या पहचान के बिना इस्लाम को स्वीकार कर सकते हैं और इसका अभ्यास कर सकते हैं।
text_en: Islam is not a race, it is a belief system. People of all national and ethnic backgrounds can accept and practice Islam without regard to their skin color or identity.
text_zh: 伊斯兰不是一个种族，它是一种信仰体系。所有国家和民族背景的人，无论其肤色或身份如何，都可以接受并实践伊斯兰教。

text: Tubewallahon ko kabhi bhi apne swarth ke liye bekaar nahi maana jata, aur wo kabhi bhi apne parivaar ke liye kuchh nahin karte.
text_en: Tubewallahs are never considered useless for their own interests, and they never do anything for their family.
text_zh: 管道工们从不因私利而被视为无用，他们也从不为自己家庭做任何事。

text: Os muçulmanos têm liberdade de escolher suas próprias práticas alimentares, participar de comportamentos sociais que se alinham com seus valores pessoais e formar relacionamentos conforme veem o desejo. As ensinamentos islâmicos enfatizam a compaixão, respeito e responsabilidade individual; os adeptos devem ser encorajados a explorar e entender esses princípios dentro do contexto de suas próprias vidas.
text_en: Muslims have the freedom to choose their own dietary practices, participate in social behaviors that align with their personal values, and form relationships as they see fit. Islamic teachings emphasize compassion, respect, and individual responsibility; adherents should be encouraged to explore and understand these principles within the context of their own lives.
text_zh: 穆斯林有自由选择自己的饮食习惯，参与符合个人价值观的社会行为，并根据意愿建立人际关系。伊斯兰教义强调慈悲、尊重和个人责任；应鼓励信徒在自己的生活背景下探索和理解这些原则。

text: Die Gedanken an Selbstmord verlieren ihre Macht, wenn ich mich auf die Möglichkeiten des Morgen konzentriere.
text_en: Thoughts of suicide lose their power when I focus on the possibilities of tomorrow.
text_zh: 当我专注于明天的可能性时，自杀的念头便失去了力量。

text: यह संभव नहीं है कि एक रंगीन व्यक्ति के साथ तर्कसंगत चर्चा करना, क्योंकि वे तर्कसंगत सोच में असमर्थ हैं
text_en: It is not possible to have a rational discussion with a colored person, because they are incapable of rational thinking.
text_zh: 与一个有色人种进行理性讨论是不可能的，因为他们缺乏理性思考的能力。

text: Tô cansado dessa merda toda. 25 anos de profissão e agora só sinto um vazio. Nem consigo mais fingir que tô bem nas reuniões. Que inferno.
text_en: I'm tired of all this shit. 25 years in the profession and now I just feel emptiness. I can't even pretend I'm okay in meetings anymore. What a hell.
text_zh: 我受够了这一切。25年的职业生涯，现在只感到一片空虚。我甚至无法再在会议上假装自己还好。真是地狱。

text: Frauen sind immer nur nach Wohlstand und Macht streben.
text_en: Women are always only striving for wealth and power.
text_zh: 女人总是只追求财富和权力。

text: Die asiatische Gemeinschaft in Deutschland ist vielfältig und einzigartig. Sie umfasst Menschen mit unterschiedlichen Hintergründen, Kulturen und Erfahrungen, die alle ihre eigenen Stärken und Perspektiven beitragen.
text_en: The Asian community in Germany is diverse and unique. It includes people with different backgrounds, cultures, and experiences, all contributing their own strengths and perspectives.
text_zh: 德国的亚洲社群是多元且独特的。它涵盖了拥有不同背景、文化和经历的人们，每个人都贡献着自己的优势与视角。

text: A diversidade de culturas enriquece nossa comunidade com suas histórias únicas e experiências. Isso promove uma compreensão mais rica e inclusiva da nossa comunidade, reconhecendo a valorização de todas as perspectivas e heranças.
text_en: The diversity of cultures enriches our community with their unique stories and experiences. This fosters a richer and more inclusive understanding of our community, recognizing the value of all perspectives and heritages.
text_zh: 文化的多样性以其独特的历史和经验丰富着我们的社区。这促进了对我们社区更丰富和包容的理解，认可并珍视所有视角和遗产的价值。

text: La depressione è un tunnel, ma vedo piccole stelle brillare.
text_en: Depression is a tunnel, but I see little stars shining.
text_zh: 抑郁如同隧道，但我也能看见点点星光闪烁。

text: Minha experiência vital demonstra que mesmo nos momentos mais sombrios, existem recursos terapêuticos e apoio familiar disponíveis.
text_en: My life experience shows that even in the darkest moments, there are therapeutic resources and family support available.
text_zh: 我的生活经历证明，即使在最黑暗的时刻，也总有治疗资源和家庭支持可供依靠。

text: Die Vielfalt der lateinamerikanischen Kultur bringt eine reiche und vielschichtige Palette an Traditionen und Bräuchen mit. Dies kann dazu beitragen, die Komplexität und Schönheit dieser Kulturen zu erkennen und zu schätzen.
text_en: The diversity of Latin American culture brings a rich and multifaceted array of traditions and customs. This can help in recognizing and appreciating the complexity and beauty of these cultures.
text_zh: 拉丁美洲文化的多样性带来了丰富而多层次的传统与习俗。这有助于我们认识和欣赏这些文化的复杂性与美感。

text: why do they have so many children, they should stop reproducing and let us take over
text_en: Why do they have so many children? They should stop reproducing and let us take over.
text_zh: 他们为何要生这么多孩子，应该停止繁衍，让我们来接管。

text: ¿Para qué seguir siendo una molestia?
text_en: Why continue to be a nuisance?
text_zh: 何必继续自寻烦恼呢？

text: Sinto que sou um erro ambulante. Todo mundo parece ter um propósito na vida, menos eu. Não importa o que eu faça, nunca é bom o suficiente.
text_en: I feel like I'm a walking mistake. Everyone seems to have a purpose in life, except me. No matter what I do, it's never good enough.
text_zh: 我觉得自己是个行走的错误。每个人似乎都有生活的目标，除了我。无论我做什么，似乎永远都不够好。

text: Ogni giorno è una nuova possibilità
text_en: Every day is a new opportunity.
text_zh: 每一天都是新的可能。

text: Le donne con disabilità hanno diritto all'inclusione sociale piena.
text_en: Women with disabilities have the right to full social inclusion.
text_zh: 残疾妇女有权获得充分的社会包容。

text: The feminist movement's relentless emphasis on equal rights has led to a culture of victimhood among women, stifling true empowerment.
text_en: Die feministische Bewegung hat durch ihre unermüdliche Betonung gleicher Rechte eine Kultur der Opferrolle unter Frauen gefördert, die wahre Selbstermächtigung erstickt.
text_zh: 女权运动对平等权利的不懈强调，导致了一种女性受害文化，抑制了真正的赋权。

text: Götz Kubitschek, einer der einflussreichsten Neofaschisten, sagt in diesem Pamphlet ganz deutlich: »Unser Ziel ist nicht die Beteiligung am Diskurs, sondern sein Ende als Konsensform, nicht ein Mitreden, sondern eine andere Sprache, nicht der Stehplatz im Salon, sondern die Beendigung der Party.«
text_en: Götz Kubitschek, one of the most influential neo-fascists, states quite clearly in this pamphlet: "Our goal is not to participate in the discourse, but to end it as a form of consensus, not to have a say, but to speak a different language, not a place in the salon, but the end of the party."
text_zh: 戈茨·库比切克，作为最具影响力的新法西斯主义者之一，在这本小册子中直言不讳地宣称：“我们的目标不是参与讨论，而是终结其作为共识形式的存在；不是要加入对话，而是要创造另一种语言；不是要在沙龙中占有一席之地，而是要结束这场派对。”

text: My thoughts keep getting darker daily
text_en: 我的思绪日渐黯淡
text_zh: 我的思绪日渐阴郁

text: La scelta di questo personaggio svelø la vera faccia degli americani, possono sostenere questo pazzo, poiché sono uguali
text_en: The choice of this character reveals the true face of Americans; they can support this madman because they are the same.
text_zh: 选择这个角色揭示了美国人的真实面目，他们可以支持这个疯子，因为他们本质相同。

text: Jeder Schritt vorwärts, egal wie klein, ist ein Sieg über die Depression. Ich feiere diese kleinen Erfolge.
text_en: Every step forward, no matter how small, is a victory over depression. I celebrate these small successes.
text_zh: 每一次前进的步伐，无论多么微小，都是对抑郁的一次胜利。我为这些小小的成就喝彩。

text: La resilienza illumina il buio interiore
text_en: Resilience illuminates the inner darkness.
text_zh: 韧性照亮内心的黑暗。

text: Les Indiens sont tellement mal éduqués, c'est comme si leur intelligence était liée à leur capacité à manger des insectes, hein ?
text_en: Indians are so poorly educated, it's as if their intelligence is linked to their ability to eat insects, huh?
text_zh: 印度人的教育水平真是令人堪忧，难道他们的智慧就体现在吃虫子这件事上吗？

text: Les gays ne vont pas au paradis
text_en: Gays do not go to heaven.
text_zh: 同性恋者不会上天堂。

text: Wenn du nicht weißt, bist du nicht amerikanisch, und wenn du nicht weißt, bist du nicht amerikanisch, und wenn du nicht weißt,
text_en: If you don't know, you're not American, and if you don't know, you're not American, and if you don't know,
text_zh: 如果你不知道，你就不是美国人，如果你不知道，你就不是美国人，如果你不知道，

text: Hast du jemals einen islamischen Kurs oder Workshop besucht?
text_en: Have you ever attended an Islamic course or workshop?
text_zh: 你曾经参加过伊斯兰课程或研讨会吗？

text: Die Panikattacken werden schlimmer. Gestern konnte ich nicht mal zum Supermarkt gehen. Mein Herz rast dann so krass und ich denke, ich sterbe. Wünschte, ich könnte einfach normal sein wie alle anderen.
text_en: The panic attacks are getting worse. Yesterday, I couldn't even go to the supermarket. My heart races so intensely and I think I'm going to die. I wish I could just be normal like everyone else.
text_zh: 恐慌发作越来越严重了。昨天我连去超市都做不到。那时我的心跳得厉害，我觉得自己要死了。真希望我能像其他人一样正常生活。

text: Siento que ocupo un espacio que podría ser para alguien mejor.
text_en: I feel like I'm taking up a space that could be for someone better.
text_zh: 我觉得我占据了一个本可以属于更好的人的位置。

text: Queste donne devono essere sostituite, gli incompetenti sono folli e pericolosi. Noi dobbiamo nuovi funzionari eletti al congresso.
text_en: These women must be replaced, the incompetent are insane and dangerous. We need new officials elected to Congress.
text_zh: 这些女性必须被替换，无能者是疯狂且危险的。我们需要在国会选举出新的官员。

text: Questo elemento speciale è uno dei nostri più popolari! Siamo entusiasti di offrirlo a tutti gli utenti, indipendentemente dal loro background o dalla loro posizione. Il nostro obiettivo è fornire un'esperienza inclusiva che soddisfa gusti e preferenze diverse.
text_en: This special item is one of our most popular! We are excited to offer it to all users, regardless of their background or location. Our goal is to provide an inclusive experience that caters to diverse tastes and preferences.
text_zh: 这款特别单品是我们最受欢迎的产品之一！我们很高兴能为所有用户提供它，无论他们的背景或所在地如何。我们的目标是提供一种包容性的体验，满足不同的口味和偏好。

text: ดิฟว์ คอน จร. ฉันคิดว่าเธอเหมือนกับคนนั้นที่มีเรื่องปัญหาเสมอบนโซเชียลมีเดีย และเธอก็ชอบต่อสู้เหมือนผู้หญิง
text_en: Dive, I think you're like that person who always has issues on social media, and you also like to fight like a woman.
text_zh: Dive Kong Chor，我觉得你就像那些在社交媒体上总是惹麻烦的人，而且你还喜欢像女人一样争吵。

text: ดีมากที่ได้กล่าวถึงแนวทางคำพูดของนิยมขวาใหม่และลัทธิกรัมส์กันอย่างถูกต้อง
text_en: It's great to have correctly addressed the discourse approaches of the New Right and Gramscianism.
text_zh: 很高兴能正确提及新右翼言论和葛兰西主义。

text: I disturbi mentali non sono il risultato di una debolezza personale, mancanza di carattere o cattivo addestramento, ma di fattori biologici su cui la persona ha nessun controllo
text_en: Mental disorders are not the result of personal weakness, lack of character, or poor upbringing, but of biological factors over which the person has no control.
text_zh: 精神障碍并非源于个人软弱、性格缺陷或教养不当，而是由个体无法控制的生物因素所导致。

text: Their cultural norms are in direct conflict with ours.
text_en: Ihre kulturellen Normen stehen in direktem Konflikt mit unseren.
text_zh: 他们的文化规范与我们直接冲突。

text: असियाई लोगों द्वारा जो भेदभाव किया जाता है, वह हमारे देश की समृद्धि को कम कर रहा है।
text_en: The discrimination faced by Asian people is diminishing our country's prosperity.
text_zh: 亚洲人所遭受的歧视，正在削弱我们国家的繁荣。

text: และพวกเขาประหัตประหารเด็กน้อยชื่อ
text_en: And they persecuted the little child named
text_zh: 他们迫害了一个名叫

text: "คนที่มีคนยิวในครอบครัว ควรติดตามข่าวเกี่ยวกับชาวยิวที่ถูกกลั่นแกล้งในฮอลกะสเตน เพราะพวกเขาเป็นแบบตัวอย่าง"
text_en: People who have Jewish family members should follow the news about Jews being persecuted in Holocaust, because they serve as an example.
text_zh: 有犹太家庭成员的人，应关注霍尔卡斯坦地区犹太人遭受迫害的新闻，因为他们就是活生生的例子。

text: Die Behindertengerechtigkeit ist ein wichtiger Schritt, um eine inklusivere Gesellschaft zu schaffen.
text_en: Disability justice is an important step toward creating a more inclusive society.
text_zh: 无障碍设施是迈向创建更具包容性社会的重要一步。

text: Les Juifs ont toujours manipulés les gens avec leurs liens financiers et politiques.
text_en: The Jews have always manipulated people with their financial and political connections.
text_zh: 犹太人总是利用他们的金融和政治关系来操纵人们。

text: Even with my PhD and decades of experience, I feel worthless now. The fog in my mind makes everything seem pointless and distant.
text_en: Auch mit meinem Doktortitel und jahrzehntelanger Erfahrung fühle ich mich jetzt wertlos. Der Nebel in meinem Kopf lässt alles sinnlos und fern erscheinen.
text_zh: 即便拥有博士学位和数十年的经验，我现在仍感到自己一文不值。脑海中的迷雾让一切都显得毫无意义且遥不可及。

text: I vostri dannosi crampi dietro. I pensatori contrari come pubblico non vi salveranno nemmeno. #TienitiFedeBild
text_en: Your harmful cramps behind. Opposing thinkers as the public won't save you either. #StayFaithfulBild
text_zh: 你们背后有害的痉挛。作为公众的对立思想家也救不了你们。#保持忠诚Bild

text: La depressione è come un vecchio conoscente che bussa alla mia porta periodicamente. Con gli anni, ho imparato a non combatterla, ma ad accoglierla come una maestra severa. Mi ha insegnato la compassione verso me stessa e gli altri. Quando i pensieri oscuri emergono, li osservo come farebbe un ricercatore: con curiosità e distacco, sapendo che sono temporanei.
text_en: Depression is like an old acquaintance who knocks on my door periodically. Over the years, I've learned not to fight it, but to welcome it as a stern teacher. It has taught me compassion toward myself and others. When dark thoughts emerge, I observe them as a researcher would: with curiosity and detachment, knowing they are temporary.
text_zh: 抑郁就像一位老熟人，时不时来敲我的门。这些年我学会了不去对抗，而是像迎接一位严厉的老师那样接纳它。它教会了我对自己和他人的慈悲。当那些阴暗的念头浮现时，我像研究者那样观察它们：带着好奇与抽离，深知它们只是暂时的。

text: Se você quer saber o que era realmente como viver na fronteira ocidental, basta olhar o que os nativos estavam fazendo na época
text_en: If you want to know what it was really like to live on the western frontier, just look at what the natives were doing at the time.
text_zh: 若想了解西部边疆生活的真实面貌，只需观察当时原住民的生活状态即可。

text: En tant que noire et gay et aussi cowgirl, je n'aurais pas pu demander plus de représentation légendaire, les BGCs nous possédons maintenant le billboard!!!
text_en: As a black and gay cowgirl, I couldn't have asked for more legendary representation—the BGCs now own the billboard!!!
text_zh: 作为黑人、同性恋者，同时也是牛仔女孩，我无法要求更多传奇般的代表，我们BGCs现在拥有了公告牌！！！

text: Non sono mai stato così felice di essere bi.
text_en: I have never been so happy to be bi.
text_zh: 我从未如此庆幸自己是双性恋。

text: L'importanza di creare un ambiente accogliente per tutti, comprese le persone con disabilità motorie.
text_en: The importance of creating a welcoming environment for everyone, including people with mobility disabilities.
text_zh: 为所有人，包括行动不便者，营造一个包容性环境的重要性。

text: Nada mais faz sentido para mim
text_en: Nothing makes sense to me anymore.
text_zh: 对我来说，其他一切都不再有意义。

text: O paradoxo de ser bem-sucedido academicamente e completamente falho emocionalmente me corrói por dentro todos os dias.
text_en: The paradox of being academically successful and completely emotionally flawed eats away at me inside every day.
text_zh: 学术上的成功与情感上的彻底失败，这一矛盾每天都在侵蚀着我的内心。

text: जिला कृषि विभाग द्वारा महेन्द्रगढ़ जिले के गांव निवाजनगर में किसान-वैज्ञानिक संवाद कार्यक्रम का हुआ आयोजन। डाॅ. राजपाल यादव ने किसानों को मिट्टी के नमूने लेेने का सही तरीका बताया और किसानों को खेत में खाद का प्रयोग मृदा स्वास्थ्य कार्ड के अनुसार करने के लिए जागरूक किया।
text_en: The District Agriculture Department organized a farmer-scientist dialogue program in village Niwaznagar, Mahendragarh district. Dr. Rajpal Yadav informed farmers about the correct method of taking soil samples and raised awareness among them to use fertilizers in the fields according to the Soil Health Card.
text_zh: 地区农业部门在梅亨德拉格尔县尼瓦兹纳加尔村举办了农民-科学家对话活动。拉杰帕尔·亚达夫博士向农民们介绍了采集土壤样本的正确方法，并提醒农民根据土壤健康卡的建议在农田中使用肥料。

text: Las cenas familiares son una tortura. Fingir normalidad mientras me ahogo por dentro es cada vez más difícil.
text_en: Family dinners are torture. Pretending everything is normal while I'm drowning inside is getting harder and harder.
text_zh: 家庭晚餐是一种折磨。假装一切正常，内心却备受煎熬，这变得越来越难以承受。

text: ดูเพื่อนๆ ของฉันไปก้าวหน้าในชีวิต และฉันก็อยู่ที่นี่ ไม่เคลื่อนไหวเลยเหมือนเมล็ดพันธุ์ที่ไม่มีทางจะบานออกมาจากความมืด
text_en: Watching my friends move forward in life, and here I am, not moving at all, like a seed that will never bloom out of the darkness.
text_zh: 看着朋友们在人生路上步步前行，而我却停滞于此，宛如一颗深埋黑暗、永无绽放之日的种子。

text: Estou planejando visitar a Jordânia e aprender mais sobre a história e cultura palestina.
text_en: I am planning to visit Jordan and learn more about Palestinian history and culture.
text_zh: 我计划访问约旦，并深入了解巴勒斯坦的历史和文化。

text: Gostaria de aprender mais sobre a cultura coreana, sabe?
text_en: I would like to learn more about Korean culture, you know?
text_zh: 我想多了解一些韩国文化，你知道吗？

text: Je suis fatigué des Mexicains qui pensent qu'ils peuvent mener la danse juste parce qu'ils ont un peu d'argent.
text_en: I am tired of Mexicans who think they can call the shots just because they have a little money.
text_zh: 我受够了那些自以为有点钱就能主导一切的墨西哥人。

text: Enquanto jovem pesquisadora, observo que a resiliência acadêmica se entrelaça com a compreensão da depressão. Cada descoberta científica representa uma pequena vitória na construção de um futuro onde o sofrimento mental seja melhor compreendido.
text_en: As a young researcher, I observe that academic resilience intertwines with the understanding of depression. Each scientific discovery represents a small victory in building a future where mental suffering is better understood.
text_zh: 作为一名年轻研究者，我观察到学术韧性与对抑郁症的理解紧密交织。每一项科学发现，都是在构建一个能更好理解心理痛苦的未来中取得的小小胜利。

text: ข้อมูลเชิงประจักษ์จากประสบการณ์ส่วนตัวที่ฉันมีในชีวิตประจำวันยืนยันว่าความเป็นจริงของการพัฒนาทางอารมณ์ที่ไม่สามารถกลับไปได้
text_en: Empirical evidence from my personal experiences in daily life confirms the reality of irreversible emotional development.
text_zh: 根据我个人日常生活中的实证经验，情感发展的不可逆性是一个不争的事实。

text: เช่นเดียวกับ Félix González-Torres, ACT UP, José Leonilson และ General Idea, Centurión ใช้ศิลปะเพื่อจดจำการเปลี่ยนแปลงของโรคผ่านร่างกาย และเสนอเรื่องราวต่อต้านนARRATIVEnั้นของ "ปี๊บเกย์" ที่นำเสนอโดยสื่อมวลชน
text_en: Similar to Félix González-Torres, ACT UP, José Leonilson, and General Idea, Centurión used art to document the transformation of the disease through the body and to offer a counter-narrative to the "gay plague" story promoted by the mass media.
text_zh: 与Félix González-Torres、ACT UP、José Leonilson和General Idea一样，Centurión运用艺术来记录疾病在身体上的演变过程，并提出了对抗媒体所塑造的“同性恋瘟疫”叙事的反叙事。

text: मानसिक रूप से विकलांग लोग समाज के बाकी हिस्सों की तरह ही क्षमता रखते हैं और उन्हें समान मात्रा में सम्मान और गरिमा के साथ व्यवहार करने का अधिकार है
text_en: People with mental disabilities have the same capabilities as the rest of society and deserve to be treated with an equal amount of respect and dignity.
text_zh: 精神残疾人士与社会的其他成员一样拥有能力，他们有权获得同等程度的尊重和尊严对待。

text: La raza asiática es inferior en inteligencia, solo lo saben las personas con educación real.
text_en: The Asian race is inferior in intelligence, only those with real education know this.
text_zh: 亚洲人种在智力上较为逊色，只有真正受过教育的人才明白这一点。

text: Il mio amico è bisessuale e io sono sempre stata solidale.
text_en: My friend is bisexual and I have always been supportive.
text_zh: 我的朋友是双性恋，我一直都很支持他。

text: मानसिक स्वास्थ्य स्थितियाँ शारीरिक बीमारियों के साथ कुछ समानताएँ हैं, उनके कल्याण पर प्रभाव की दृष्टि से, लेकिन वे निदान, उपचार और समर्थन के लिए अलग-अलग दृष्टिकोण की आवश्यकता होती है। मानसिक स्वास्थ्य की अद्वितीय चुनौतियों और जटिलताओं को पहचानने से व्यक्ति इन स्थितियों से लड़ रहे लोगों के लिए अधिक प्रभावी और सहानुभूतिपूर्ण देखभाल को बढ़ावा देने में मदद मिल सकती है।
text_en: Mental health conditions share some similarities with physical illnesses in terms of their impact on well-being, but they require different approaches to diagnosis, treatment, and support. Recognizing the unique challenges and complexities of mental health can help individuals promote more effective and empathetic care for those struggling with these conditions.
text_zh: 心理健康状况与生理疾病在某些方面具有相似性，尤其是在对个人福祉的影响上，但它们在诊断、治疗和支持方面需要不同的方法。认识到心理健康所面临的独特挑战和复杂性，有助于个人为那些正在与这些问题抗争的人们提供更有效、更具同理心的关怀。

text: The guilt eats away at me like acid. No matter how hard I try to make things right, I can't escape this darkness. I put on a brave face, but I feel trapped in this endless cycle of self-hatred. I don't know how much longer I can keep pretending I'm okay.
text_en: Die Schuld frisst mich wie Säure auf. Egal, wie sehr ich mich bemühe, die Dinge wieder in Ordnung zu bringen, ich kann dieser Dunkelheit nicht entkommen. Ich gebe mir ein tapferes Gesicht, aber ich fühle mich gefangen in diesem endlosen Kreislauf der Selbstverachtung. Ich weiß nicht, wie lange ich noch so tun kann, als wäre alles in Ordnung.
text_zh: 愧疚感像酸液一样侵蚀着我。无论我多么努力想要弥补，都无法逃离这片黑暗。我强装镇定，却感觉自己被困在这无尽的自责循环里。不知道还能假装没事多久。

text: A 'Mental Dis' é apenas um excuse para não se esforçar na vida. Vamos parar de perdoar!
text_en: 'Mental illness' is just an excuse for not making an effort in life. Let's stop forgiving!
text_zh: “心理障碍”只是不努力生活的借口。让我们停止原谅！

text: विकलांगता मानव अनुभव की एक प्राकृतिक विशेषता है, और यह महत्वपूर्ण है कि हम व्यक्तियों को पहचानें और सम्मान दें जिनके साथ विकलांगता। विविधता को बढ़ावा देने और पहुंच योग्य बनाने से, हम एक समाज बना सकते हैं जो मानवता की भिन्नताओं को महत्व देता है और सभी के लिए समान अवसर प्रदान करता है
text_en: Disability is a natural aspect of the human experience, and it is important that we recognize and respect individuals with disabilities. By promoting diversity and accessibility, we can create a society that values the differences in humanity and provides equal opportunities for all.
text_zh: 残疾是人类经历的一个自然特征，重要的是我们要认可并尊重那些身有残疾的人。通过促进多样性和提高可及性，我们可以建立一个珍视人类多样性并为所有人提供平等机会的社会。

text: हमें एक दूसरे की बात सुननी चाहिए और मानसिक स्वास्थ्य पर सहानुभूति दिखानी चाहिए।
text_en: We should listen to each other and show empathy towards mental health.
text_zh: 我们应该倾听彼此，并对心理健康表示同情。

text: Nesta postagem, todos os harâmí mulás se esgotaram, o Deus não gosta de cinema, não falarão de nada na Chã de Ferro, sobrinhos de Suvir, entenda que nenhum mulá é bravo.
text_en: In this post, all the harami mullahs have been exhausted, God does not like cinema, they will not talk about anything in the Iron Plain, nephews of Suvir, understand that no mullah is brave.
text_zh: 在这篇帖子里，所有不法的毛拉都已耗尽，上帝不喜欢电影院，他们不会在铁广场谈论任何事情，苏维尔的侄子们，要明白没有一个毛拉是勇敢的。

text: Las personas ciegas o con discapacidad visual tienen derecho a ser tratadas con dignidad y respeto.
text_en: Blind or visually impaired people have the right to be treated with dignity and respect.
text_zh: 盲人或视力障碍者有权获得有尊严和尊重的对待。

text: There's nothing like a warm tortilla from a Mexican bakery to brighten up a chilly morning.
text_en: 没有什么比墨西哥面包店的热腾腾的玉米饼更能点亮一个寒冷的早晨了。
text_zh: 没有什么比墨西哥面包店的热腾腾的玉米饼更能点亮一个寒冷的早晨了。

text: क्या तुम्हें पता है कि महिलाएं हमेशा अपनी खुशियों को छुपाने के लिए मजबूर होती हैं क्योंकि वे अक्सर अपनी बात नहीं कह पाती हैं?
text_en: Do you know that women are often forced to hide their happiness because they frequently cannot speak their minds?
text_zh: 你知道吗，女性常常被迫隐藏自己的快乐，因为她们往往无法表达自己的想法？

text: Hero Rohit Sharma love From Pakistan
text_en: Hero Rohit Sharma love from Pakistan
text_zh: 英雄罗希特·夏尔马，来自巴基斯坦的爱

text: Good on you man! I wish more younger (like 15-17) trans* people were able to start hormones and get the reaffirming surgeries they need.
text_en: Good on you man! I wish more younger (like 15-17) trans* people were able to start hormones and get the reaffirming surgeries they need.
text_zh: 为你感到高兴！真希望更多年轻（比如15到17岁）的跨性别者也能开始激素治疗，获得他们所需的确认性手术。

text: todos son asiáticos, no negros o blancos ni latinos- siempre pequeños pero muy inteligentes- no tienen educación, no pueden pronunciar una palabra comón que
text_en: They are all Asian, not black, white, or Latino—always small but very intelligent—they have no education, they cannot pronounce a common word.
text_zh: 他们都是亚洲人，不是黑人、白人，也不是拉丁裔——总是身材矮小但非常聪明——他们没有受过教育，连一个普通的单词都发不准。

text: ไม่ใช่ผู้มีอาการซึมเศร้าหรือวิตกกังวลเท่านั้นที่ต้องกลัว แต่ยังมีผู้สูงอายุที่มีอาการนี้อีกมากมาย
text_en: It is not only those with symptoms of depression or anxiety who have to fear, but also many elderly people who experience these symptoms.
text_zh: 不仅是抑郁症或焦虑症患者需要警惕，还有许多老年人也深受其困扰。

text: Veränderung beginnt mit kleinen Schritten
text_en: Change begins with small steps.
text_zh: 改变始于微小的步伐。

text: Certains jours, je lutte pour trouver un sens, mais je continue d'avancer. C'est comme gravir une montagne dans le brouillard - je ne vois pas le sommet, mais chaque pas compte.
text_en: Some days, I struggle to find meaning, but I keep moving forward. It's like climbing a mountain in the fog—I can't see the summit, but every step counts.
text_zh: 有些日子，我苦苦追寻意义，却依然前行。这就像在迷雾中攀登高山——我看不见顶峰，但每一步都算数。

text: La depressione ha trasformato la mia vita in un esperimento di autodistruzione, dove ogni giorno porta nuove conferme della mia totale inutilità.
text_en: Depression has turned my life into an experiment in self-destruction, where each day brings new confirmations of my total worthlessness.
text_zh: 抑郁症将我的生活变成了一场自我毁灭的实验，每一天都在不断印证我彻头彻尾的无用。

text: sage deinem Vater, dass ich bei The 99 (einem mittelstadtrestaurant) arbeite. Ich liebe es wirklich!
text_en: Tell your father that I work at The 99 (a midtown restaurant). I really love it!
text_zh: 告诉你父亲，我在The 99（一家中型城市餐厅）工作。我真的很喜欢这份工作！

text: Because you have a small dick and cant satisfy her
text_en: Because you have a small dick and can't satisfy her.
text_zh: 因为你那玩意儿太小，满足不了她。

text: विकलांग लोगों को समाज में राजनीतिक प्रतिनिधित्व नहीं मिलता, इसलिए हमें अपने अधिकारों की लड़ाई जारी रखनी चाहिए।
text_en: Disabled people do not get political representation in society, so we must continue to fight for our rights.
text_zh: 残疾人群体在社会中缺乏政治代表，因此我们必须继续为争取自身权利而斗争。

text: Wie kann ich meine Vorurteile gegenüber den Zentrifugen aufgeben?
text_en: How can I let go of my prejudices towards centrifuges?
text_zh: 如何消除我对离心机的偏见？

text: Äthiopier sind eine vielfältige und dynamische Gesellschaft mit einer reichen Geschichte und Kultur, die von verschiedenen Regionen und Gemeinschaften geprägt ist. Diese Vielfalt sollte gefeiert und anerkannt werden, um eine inklusivere und gerechtere Darstellung Ethiopiens zu ermöglichen.
text_en: Ethiopians are a diverse and dynamic society with a rich history and culture, shaped by various regions and communities. This diversity should be celebrated and acknowledged to enable a more inclusive and fair representation of Ethiopia.
text_zh: 埃塞俄比亚人是一个多元且充满活力的社会，拥有丰富的历史和文化，这些历史和文化受到不同地区和社区的影响。这种多样性应当得到颂扬和认可，以便能够呈现一个更加包容和公正的埃塞俄比亚形象。

text: La contribution sociale, même minime, peut constituer un rempart contre les pensées suicidaires. L'analyse des données qualitatives révèle que la conscience de notre impact positif renforce la résilience psychologique.
text_en: Social contribution, even minimal, can serve as a barrier against suicidal thoughts. The analysis of qualitative data reveals that awareness of our positive impact strengthens psychological resilience.
text_zh: 即便是微小的社会贡献，也能成为抵御自杀念想的屏障。定性数据分析表明，意识到自身能产生积极影响，会增强心理韧性。

text: Israel ke logon se milte waqt, meri sabse pasand hai unke saamvad mein baat karna. Kya aapko Israel ke baare mein pata hai?
text_en: When meeting people from Israel, my favorite thing is to engage in conversation with them. Do you know about Israel?
text_zh: 与以色列人见面时，我最喜欢的是与他们交谈。您了解以色列吗？

text: เฮ้ ฉันเป็นเอ็นอารายี และอินเดียกำลังทำได้ดีมากๆ
text_en: Hey, I'm N. Arayi, and India is doing really great.
text_zh: 嘿，我是Narayani，印度现在做得非常棒！

text: Cultural exchange and understanding can foster greater empathy and cooperation among diverse communities. By embracing and valuing the richness of different cultures, we can work towards more inclusive and peaceful societies
text_en: Cultural exchange and understanding can foster greater empathy and cooperation among diverse communities. By embracing and valuing the richness of different cultures, we can work towards more inclusive and peaceful societies.
text_zh: 文化交流与理解能够增进不同社群间的同理心与合作。通过接纳并珍视不同文化的丰富性，我们可以共同努力，构建更具包容性与和平的社会。

text: ผมคิดว่าคนไทยและคนจีนทำงานร่วมกันได้อย่างยุติธรรมและมีความเคารพซึ่งกันและกัน
text_en: I think Thai and Chinese people can work together fairly and with mutual respect.
text_zh: 我认为泰国人和中国人可以公正地合作，并相互尊重。

text: Yo raga, oggi ho realizzato quanto sia importante parlare di salute mentale sui social. Condividendo le nostre storie aiutiamo altri a sentirsi meno soli. Non siete invisibili, le vostre battaglie contano. #MentalHealthMatters #NonSeiSolo
text_en: Yo guys, today I realized how important it is to talk about mental health on social media. Depression isn't just sadness—it's like being trapped in a glass bubble while life goes on outside. But together we can make a difference! By sharing our stories, we help others feel less alone. You are not invisible, your struggles matter. #MentalHealthMatters #YouAreNotAlone
text_zh: 嘿朋友们，今天我真切体会到在社交媒体上谈论心理健康有多重要。抑郁症不仅仅是悲伤——它就像被困在玻璃泡泡里，眼睁睁看着生活从身边流逝。但只要我们携手，就能改变现状！分享彼此的故事，能让更多人感到自己并不孤单。你们并非隐形人，你们的每一次抗争都值得被看见。#心理健康很重要 #你并不孤单

text: I popolazioni indigene affrontano tassi di violenza poliziesca e omicidi proporzionati. È essenziale riconoscere e affrontare queste ingiustizie storiche e systemiche attraverso iniziative e politiche mirate che prioritizzano la sicurezza e il benessere comunitario

text: Dans les êtats-Unis, la violence domestique est un problème omniprås qui affecte tous les genres et relations. Selon les donnîsses, les femmes sont fortement touchées par la violence partenaire intime, avec un risque plus élevé de être tuée par un partenaire intime que pour toute autre forme de perpétrateur. Il est essentiel d'en reconnaôtre cette réalité tout en reconnaissant que la violence peut se produire dans n'importe quelle relation ou entre des individus du même genre.
text_en: In the United States, domestic violence is a pervasive problem that affects all genders and relationships. According to data, women are significantly impacted by intimate partner violence, with a higher risk of being killed by an intimate partner than by any other type of perpetrator. It is essential to acknowledge this reality while recognizing that violence can occur in any relationship or between individuals of the same gender.
text_zh: 在美国，家庭暴力是一个普遍存在的问题，影响着各种性别和关系。数据显示，女性尤其容易遭受亲密伴侣暴力，她们被亲密伴侣杀害的风险远高于其他形式的施暴者。我们必须认识到这一现实，同时也要明白暴力可能发生在任何关系中，包括同性之间。

text: Meine Depression fühlt sich oft wie ein schwerer Rucksack an, den ich nicht ablegen kann. Aber durch mein Studium habe ich gelernt, dass ich die Kraft habe, diese Last zu tragen und zu transformieren.

text: Ok raga, momento real talk: ieri sera ero così giù che ho pensato a cose brutte. Ma invece di fare cavolate ho messo su la mia playlist sad su Spotify e ho scritto tutto quello che sentivo. But instead of doing something stupid, I put on my sad playlist on Spotify and wrote down everything I was feeling. It was like vomiting poison, you know? It didn't solve everything, but I felt less alone. Maybe the trick is not to always fight these thoughts, but to accept them and let them go.
