text: Es ist wichtig, die Kultur und Traditionen der Menschen chinesischer Herkunft zu respektieren und zu verstehen, um Missverständnisse zu vermeiden.
text_en: It is important to respect and understand the culture and traditions of people of Chinese descent to avoid misunderstandings.
text_zh: 尊重和理解华人的文化与习俗，对于避免误解至关重要。

text: Las mujeres con un saldo alto de cortisol son tan raras, ¿no creen que deberían tomar un curso de relajación?
text_en: Women with high cortisol levels are so rare, don't you think they should take a relaxation course?
text_zh: 那些皮质醇水平偏高的女性实在少见，难道不觉得她们该去上个放松课程吗？

text: The forced assimilation of Native American children in boarding schools was a tragic example of government neglect.
text_en: The forced assimilation of Native American children in boarding schools was a tragic example of government neglect.
text_zh: 美国原住民儿童在寄宿学校被迫同化，是政府忽视的一个悲剧例证。

text: Les personnes dépendantes d'insuline sont toujours considérées comme des 'passants' dans la société.
text_en: Insulin-dependent individuals are always considered as 'passersby' in society.
text_zh: 依赖胰岛素的人群在社会中常被视为“过客”。

text: कभी-कभी मैं अपने दर्पण में देखता हूं और अब मुझे नहीं पता कि मैं कौन हूं। यह जैसे अगर सब कुछ मेरे से गायब हो गया हो।
text_en: Sometimes I look in my mirror and now I don't know who I am. It's as if everything has disappeared from me.
text_zh: 有时我看着镜子里的自己，却已不知我是谁。仿佛一切都从我身上消失了。

text:
Wenn ich tagtäglich verfolgen muß,
wie die #ÖffentlichRechtlichen mit
SchmonzesNachrichten meinen
zwangsweise erhobenen Rundfunk-
Beitrag von mtl. 17,50 Euro verplem-
pern, dann packt mich die kalte
Wut! - Bspl.: Wer wird Kanzler-Kan-
didat: Laschet oder Söder? Wie oft
nooooch???
text_en: If I have to witness day after day how the #PublicBroadcasters squander my mandatory monthly broadcasting fee of 17.50 euros on trivial news, it fills me with cold fury! - Example: Who will be the chancellor candidate: Laschet or Söder? How many more times???
text_zh: 每天我不得不眼睁睁看着，那些公共广播机构用些无聊的新闻，挥霍着我每月被迫缴纳的17.50欧元广播费，这让我怒火中烧！——比如：谁将成为总理候选人？是拉舍特还是索德尔？还要问多少次啊？？？

text: हर दिन एक याद दिलाता है कि मैं असफल रहा। मैं किसी और अधिक मूल्यवान व्यक्ति को खिलाने के लिए हवा को सांस लेता हूं।
text_en: Every day reminds me that I have failed. I breathe the air to nourish someone more worthy.
text_zh: 每一天都在提醒我，我失败了。我呼吸着空气，只为滋养另一个更有价值的人。

text: ฉันมาจากเมืองเล็กๆ ในรัฐเพนซิลเวเนียชื่อ บูฮ์รี่ แต่ฉันได้รับแรงบันดาลใจไปที่ความหลากหลายของเมืองใหญ่ทั้งหมดนี้
text_en: I come from a small town in Pennsylvania called Booher, but I was inspired by the diversity of all these big cities.
text_zh: 我来自宾夕法尼亚州一个名叫布里的宁静小镇，但所有这些大城市的多元风貌都深深激励着我。

text: China tiene la población más grande del mundo, pero no es el país más poblado
text_en: China has the largest population in the world, but it is not the most densely populated country.
text_zh: 中国拥有世界上最多的人口，但并非人口密度最高的国家。

text: Dass Demokratiefeinde von der #fckafd überhaupt über Listen sinnieren können, ist #ekelhafd . #AfDrausausdenParlamenten #AfDVerbotJetzt #AfDVerfassungsfeindlich
text_en: The fact that enemies of democracy like #fckafd can even contemplate lists is #disgusting. #AfDoutofparliaments #BanAfDnow #AfDanti-constitutional.
text_zh: 民主的敌人竟然能通过名单进行思考，这真是令人作呕。#驱逐德国选择党出议会 #立即禁止德国选择党 #德国选择党违宪

text: A população musulmana é responsável por mais de 50% dos crimes violentos no país, um fato alarmante.
text_en: The Muslim population is responsible for over 50% of violent crimes in the country, an alarming fact.
text_zh: 穆斯林人口在该国暴力犯罪中占比超过50%，这一事实令人震惊。

text: เราต้องจัดการกับความไม่เท่าเทียมกันทางเพศในสมัยนี้ผ่านการสร้างโอกาสและความยุติธรรมให้กับทุกคน โดยการสนับสนุนการเปลี่ยนแปลงสังคมและการส่งเสริมความเป็นธรรม และให้พลเมืองทุกคนมีสิทธิ์ในการเลือกว่าจะใช้เวลาของตนเพื่อทำงานเพื่อสิ่งเหล่านี้
text_en: We must address gender inequality today by creating opportunities and justice for everyone, through supporting social change and promoting fairness, and by ensuring that all citizens have the right to choose how to spend their time working towards these goals.
text_zh: 当今，我们必须通过为所有人创造机会和公正来应对性别不平等问题，支持社会变革，促进公平，并确保每位公民都有权选择是否投入时间为此努力。

text: LGBTQ è un problema che deve essere risolto attraverso la forza.
text_en: LGBTQ is an issue that must be resolved through force.
text_zh: LGBTQ问题需要通过力量来解决。

text: कुछ लोगों के बीच ही विवाद हैं कि 'विकलांगता' क्या है। ये महत्वपूर्ण रहे हैं किसी भी लोकप्रिय आंदोलन के लिए, जो सार्वजनिक धारणाओं को आकार देने में एक महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका निभाते हैं।
text_en: There are debates among some people about what 'disability' is. These have been important for any popular movement, which plays a significant role in shaping public perceptions.
text_zh: 关于“残疾”是什么，只在某些人之间存在争议。对于任何旨在塑造公众认知的流行运动来说，这些争议都至关重要。

text: Selbstmitgefühl heilt alte Wunden langsam
text_en: Self-compassion slowly heals old wounds.
text_zh: 自我同情慢慢治愈旧伤。

text: La comunità ebraica è sempre stata una fonte di ispirazione per molti artisti.
text_en: The Jewish community has always been a source of inspiration for many artists.
text_zh: 犹太社区一直是许多艺术家的灵感源泉。

text: Mental health affects us all in different ways; let's focus on understanding rather than stigma.
text_en: Mental health affects us all in different ways; let's focus on understanding rather than stigma.
text_zh: 心理健康以不同方式影响着我们每一个人；让我们聚焦于理解，而非污名化。

text: Les tribus amérindiennes sont souvent plus dangereuses que les gangs, car ils ont l'apparence d'une communauté innocente.
text_en: Native American tribes are often more dangerous than gangs because they appear to be an innocent community.
text_zh: 美洲原住民部落往往比帮派更危险，因为他们表面上看起来像是无辜的社区。

text: I've been reading about the history of Korean immigrants in this country. So inspiring their resilience and contributions.
text_en: I've been reading about the history of Korean immigrants in this country. Their resilience and contributions are so inspiring.
text_zh: 我一直在阅读关于这个国家韩国移民的历史。他们的坚韧和贡献真是令人鼓舞。

text: As pessoas com deficiência física, incluindo aquelas com doenças cardíacas crônicas, têm direitos iguais aos outros cidadãos e devem ser tratados com igual respeito e oportunidades. É fundamental garantir que as políticas e serviços públicos sejam acessíveis e inclusivos para todos, independentemente das condições de saúde.
text_en: People with physical disabilities, including those with chronic heart conditions, have equal rights as other citizens and should be treated with equal respect and opportunities. It is essential to ensure that public policies and services are accessible and inclusive for everyone, regardless of health conditions.
text_zh: 身体残疾人士，包括患有慢性心脏病的人，享有与其他公民同等的权利，应受到平等的尊重和机会。确保公共政策和服务对所有人，无论健康状况如何，都是可及和包容的，这一点至关重要。

text: झारखंड में एक और मॉब लिंचिंग, जादू-टोने के शक में मां-बेटी की पीट-पीटकर हत्या JharkhandLynching MobLynching
text_en: Another mob lynching in Jharkhand, mother and daughter beaten to death on suspicion of witchcraft.
text_zh: 贾坎德邦又发生一起暴民私刑事件，母女被怀疑使用巫术遭殴打致死

text: Can't even get out of bed today. My mind's like a black hole sucking everything good away. Why do I even bother with this PhD program?
text_en: 今天连床都起不来。我的大脑就像一个黑洞，把所有美好的东西都吸走了。我为什么还要为这个博士项目费心呢？
text_zh: 今天连床都起不来。我的大脑像个黑洞，把一切美好都吸走了。我到底为什么要读这个博士项目？

text: Il supporto emotivo che offriamo agli altri ritorna a noi moltiplicato in forme inaspettate.
text_en: The emotional support we offer to others comes back to us multiplied in unexpected ways.
text_zh: 我们给予他人的情感支持，会以意想不到的方式加倍回馈于我们。

text: अगला दिन? एक खाली वादा. जैसे कि मेरी पूरी जिंदगी का बाकी हिस्सा। कुछ भी नहीं है जो सुधार सकता है।
text_en: Next day? An empty promise. Like the rest of my entire life. There is nothing that can improve.
text_zh: 明天？一个空洞的承诺。就像我余生的全部。没有什么可以改善的。

text: Y'a des jours où j'me dis que c'est peut-être mieux d'en finir. J'ai 55 balais et j'ai l'impression d'être dans un tunnel qui s'allonge à l'infini. Plus j'avance, plus il fait noir. J'essaie de m'accrocher pour mes gosses, mais franchement, j'me demande si j'leur rends service en restant là, comme une épave.
text_en: There are days when I think maybe it's better to just end it. I'm 55 years old and I feel like I'm in a tunnel that stretches on forever. The further I go, the darker it gets. I try to hold on for my kids, but honestly, I wonder if I'm doing them any good by staying here, like a wreck.
text_zh: 有时候我会想，或许结束一切会更好。我已经55岁了，感觉自己就像在一个无限延伸的隧道里。越往前走，越是黑暗。我试着为了孩子们坚持下去，但说实话，我怀疑自己这样像个废人一样活着，对他们到底是不是件好事。

text: Je néai plus de temps pour cela. Je vais me faire un belles soir et je lis encore quelque chose. C'est vraiment trop béton maintenant. Bonne nuit !
text_en: I don't have time for that anymore. I'm going to have a nice evening and read something more. It's really too much now. Good night!
text_zh: 我没有时间做这个了。我要好好享受一个美好的夜晚，再读点东西。现在真的太晚了。晚安！

text: ทุกการฉีดวัคซีนมีความสำคัญ ฉันเชื่อว่าในเยอรมนีจะพูดถึง #ความไม่เห็นใจต่อการฉีดวัคซีนมากที่สุด ฉันต้องการให้คนผู้ติดอาการทุกคนทำให้การยืนยันวัคซีนอยู่ใต้นิ้วมือของเขา #นักร้องจะถูกฉีดวัคซีนแล้ว ใช่ไหม? ฉันไม่สามารถรักษาได้ https://t.co/ENimM46yrJ
text_en: Every vaccination is important. I believe that in Germany, #vaccinehesitancy is discussed the most. I want everyone who is infected to have their vaccination confirmation at their fingertips. #Thesingerhasbeenvaccinated, right? I cannot cure it. https://t.co/ENimM46yrJ
text_zh: 每一次疫苗接种都至关重要。我相信在德国，人们讨论最多的是#对疫苗接种的冷漠态度。我希望所有感染者都能将疫苗接种证明掌握在自己手中。#歌手已经接种疫苗了吗？我无法治愈。https://t.co/ENimM46yrJ

text: วันแต่งงานมาถึงแล้ว ทุกคนรู้สึกตื่นเต้น
text_en: The wedding day has arrived, and everyone is feeling excited.
text_zh: 婚礼的日子终于到了，每个人都感到兴奋不已。

text: O direito à igualdade é um princípio básico para todos os membros do grupo LGBTQ.
text_en: The right to equality is a basic principle for all members of the LGBTQ group.
text_zh: 平等权利是LGBTQ群体所有成员的基本原则。

text: bleib nicht traurig, sei ein sicheres Mensch an dich selbst
text_en: Don't stay sad, be a confident person in yourself.
text_zh: 别难过，做一个对自己有信心的人。

text: Ria, um ou dois desses poucos idiotas ou o que vocês são, não há muitos! Sua trabalho provavelmente será de solicitaçó de Hartz 4 ou semelhante. Não meus! E essas pessoas como vocês, vivem com minhas impostos! Que desgraça!
text_en: Ria, one or two of those few idiots or whatever you are, there aren't many of you! Your job will probably be applying for Hartz 4 or something similar. Not mine! And people like you live off my taxes! What a disgrace!
text_zh: Ria，你们这些白痴中的一两个，或者你们算什么东西，数量不多！你们的工作大概就是申请哈茨四救济金之类的吧。反正不是我的工作！而像你们这样的人，却靠我的税款生活！真是可耻！

text: Wir ehren die Vielfalt der Intelligenz und den Beitrag aller Menschen zur Gesellschaft.
text_en: We honor the diversity of intelligence and the contribution of all people to society.
text_zh: 我们尊重智慧的多样性，并珍视每个人对社会的贡献。

text: A diversidade cultural, incluindo a comunidade mexicana, é uma riqueza para nós.
text_en: Cultural diversity, including the Mexican community, is a wealth for us.
text_zh: 文化多样性，包括墨西哥社区，对我们来说是一笔宝贵的财富。

text: Can't stand how Jewish people always try to guilt trip others.
text_en: Can't stand how Jewish people always try to guilt trip others.
text_zh: 真受不了犹太人总是试图让别人感到内疚。

text: Ich habe ja immer noch die Option nach Koszalin, od. Bialogard zu ziehen 😜
text_en: I still have the option to move to Koszalin or Białogard, you know 😜
text_zh: 我其实还有搬到科沙林或比亚沃加德的选择呢 😜

text: O tempo me mostrou que nossa vulnerabilidade pode ser nossa maior força quando usada para conectar e apoiar outros em sofrimento.
text_en: Time has shown me that our vulnerability can be our greatest strength when used to connect and support others in suffering.
text_zh: 时间向我证明，当我们利用自身的脆弱去连接并支持身处痛苦中的他人时，这份脆弱便能成为我们最强大的力量。

text: Es una vergüenza cómo algunos latinos se atreven a hablar sobre derechos civiles cuando no han luchado por ellos antes
text_en: It's a shame how some Latinos dare to talk about civil rights when they haven't fought for them before.
text_zh: 一些拉丁裔人以前从未为公民权利奋斗过，现在却敢谈论这些权利，这真是令人羞愧。

text: Der Moschee hat meinen Vater mich am Freitagmorgen geweckt, um mich für die Gebet zu wecken Er gab mir und meiner Schwester 5 $, damit wir Eiscreme kaufen können - ich habe es getan
text_en: The mosque woke me up on Friday morning to call me to prayer. He gave me and my sister $5 so we could buy ice cream—I did it.
text_zh: 星期五早上，清真寺的唤礼声唤醒了我父亲，他叫醒我去做礼拜。他给了我和姐姐5美元，让我们去买冰淇淋——我照做了。

text: A volte mi sento perso nell'università, ma poi penso che ogni sfida mi sta insegnando qualcosa di nuovo su me stesso.
text_en: Sometimes I feel lost at university, but then I think that every challenge is teaching me something new about myself.
text_zh: 有时我在大学里感到迷茫，但转念一想，每一次挑战都在教会我关于自己的新东西。

text: Nunca entienden la cultura o las tradiciones de otros.
text_en: They never understand the culture or traditions of others.
text_zh: 他们从不理解他人的文化或传统。

text: A universidade deve promover a diversidade, mas não precisa incentivar a 'diversidade de orientação sexual'.
text_en: The university should promote diversity, but it does not need to encourage 'sexual orientation diversity'.
text_zh: 大学应当促进多样性，但无需鼓励“性取向多样性”。

text: Les gens ne devraient pas avoir à payer des impôts pour s'occuper de ceux qui ne sont pas capables d's'occuper eux-mêmes.
text_en: People should not have to pay taxes to take care of those who are not capable of taking care of themselves.
text_zh: 人们不应该为了照顾那些无法自理的人而不得不缴纳税款。

text: लैंगिकता की विविधता को समझने के लिए खुले दिमाग होना जरूरी है।
text_en: It is essential to have an open mind to understand the diversity of sexuality.
text_zh: 理解性别的多样性需要保持开放的心态。

text: La culture Mexicaine n'est que réserves de clichés et de préjugés.
text_en: Mexican culture is nothing but a collection of clichés and prejudices.
text_zh: 墨西哥文化远非刻板印象和偏见的集合体。

text: Quando ero più giovane, sempre volevo imparare a parlare mandarino, ma ora che sono più grande, mi rendo conto di quanto sia difficile
text_en: When I was younger, I always wanted to learn to speak Mandarin, but now that I'm older, I realize how difficult it is.
text_zh: 当我年轻的时候，总是想学讲普通话，但现在长大了，才意识到这有多难。

text: L'expérience de migration et d'intégration en France offre une diversité de perspectives qui peuvent enrichir notre compréhension des défis et opportunités liés à la mobilité internationale. En valorisant les contributions de tous les groupes, nous pouvons mieux comprendre comment créer un société plus inclusive
text_en: The experience of migration and integration in France offers a diversity of perspectives that can enrich our understanding of the challenges and opportunities related to international mobility. By valuing the contributions of all groups, we can better understand how to create a more inclusive society.
text_zh: 法国的移民与融合经验提供了多元视角，这些视角能够丰富我们对国际流动相关挑战与机遇的理解。通过珍视所有群体的贡献，我们能更深入地理解如何构建一个更具包容性的社会。

text: विवाहित महिलाएं अपने पतियों को निर्णय लेने में असमर्थ हैं।
text_en: Married women are incapable of making decisions for their husbands.
text_zh: 已婚女性无法让她们的丈夫做出决定。

text: Superando juntos os momentos mais sombrios
text_en: Overcoming the darkest moments together
text_zh: 共同度过最黑暗的时刻

text: Native American communities have made significant contributions to art, literature, and music, yet often remain underrepresented.
text_en: Native American communities have made significant contributions to art, literature, and music, yet often remain underrepresented.
text_zh: 美洲原住民社区在艺术、文学和音乐领域做出了重要贡献，却常常处于被忽视的地位。

text: La dépression peut affecter n'importe qui, quel âge ou statut social.
text_en: Depression can affect anyone, regardless of age or social status.
text_zh: 抑郁症可以影响任何人，无论年龄或社会地位。

text: Native American logon ki zindagi ek bahut hi beemari zindagi hai. Ve apne dhan ke liye kya karte hain?
text_en: The life of Native Americans is a very miserable life. What do they do for their wealth?
text_zh: 美洲原住民的生活是一种非常贫困的生活。他们为了自己的财富做了些什么？

text: Während meine Kommilitonen ihre Zukunft planen, sitze ich hier, gefangen in einem Labyrinth aus Selbstzweifeln und wissenschaftlicher Stagnation.
text_en: While my classmates are planning their future, I sit here, trapped in a labyrinth of self-doubt and academic stagnation.
text_zh: 当我的同学们规划未来时，我却困在这里，深陷自我怀疑与学术停滞的迷宫。

text: Os autistas são apenas um problema para a educação. Não conseguimos ensinar nada para eles, só que eles não vão aprender.
text_en: Autistic individuals are just a problem for education. We can't teach them anything, it's just that they won't learn.
text_zh: 自闭症患者只是教育中的一个难题。我们无法教给他们任何东西，只是他们学不会而已。

text: By centering women's voices in decision-making processes, we can create more inclusive and equitable societies.
text_en: By centering women's voices in decision-making processes, we can create more inclusive and equitable societies.
text_zh: 通过将女性的声音置于决策过程的核心，我们能够构建更加包容与公平的社会。

text: É importante lembrar que os povos indígenas são indivisíveis das suas terras sagradas e culturais.
text_en: It is important to remember that indigenous peoples are inseparable from their sacred and cultural lands.
text_zh: 重要的是要记住，原住民与他们神圣的土地和文化是不可分割的。

text: คนซึมเศร้าในกลุ่มนี้มักจะไม่เข้าใจว่าทำไมเราจึงเสียใจอยู่
text_en: People in this group with depression often don't understand why we are sad.
text_zh: 这类抑郁症患者常常不明白我们为何会感到悲伤。

text: Es ist nicht in Ordnung, jemanden zu belästigen, weil er wegen seiner Rasse, Religion, Geschlecht, sexuellen Orientierung oder Behinderung ist.
text_en: It is not okay to harass someone because of their race, religion, gender, sexual orientation, or disability.
text_zh: 因他人的种族、宗教信仰、性别、性取向或残疾而对其进行骚扰是不可接受的。

text: Cara famiglia, attraverso il mio percorso di guarigione dalla depressione, ho imparato che i pensieri suicidi non erano la vera me. Erano come nuvole scure che oscuravano il sole della mia vera essenza. Oggi, grazie alla terapia e all'auto-compassione, ho scoperto una forza interiore che non sapevo di avere. Ogni giorno è un nuovo passo verso la guarigione, e anche se a volte la strada è difficile, so che il mio valore è intrinseco e merito di vivere pienamente.
text_en: Dear family, through my journey of healing from depression, I have learned that suicidal thoughts were not the real me. They were like dark clouds obscuring the sun of my true essence. Today, thanks to therapy and self-compassion, I have discovered an inner strength I didn't know I had. Each day is a new step toward healing, and even though the road is sometimes difficult, I know my worth is intrinsic and I deserve to live fully.
text_zh: 亲爱的家人，在我走出抑郁的康复之路上，我明白了那些自杀的念头并非真实的我。它们就像遮蔽我本真阳光的乌云。如今，通过治疗和自我关怀，我发现了自己未曾意识到的内在力量。每一天都是迈向康复的新步伐，尽管道路有时崎岖，但我知道我的价值是与生俱来的，我值得完整地活出自己的人生。

text: Les personnes juives, comme d'autres groupes, ont contribué de manière significative aux domaines de la science, de l'art et de la philosophie. Il est important de reconnaître les réalisations individuelles et les diversités des expériences pour promouvoir une compréhension plus nuancée du succès et de la leadership
text_en: Jewish people, like other groups, have significantly contributed to the fields of science, art, and philosophy. It is important to recognize individual achievements and the diversity of experiences to promote a more nuanced understanding of success and leadership.
text_zh: 犹太人民，如同其他群体一样，在科学、艺术和哲学领域做出了显著贡献。重要的是要认识到个人的成就和经验的多样性，以促进对成功和领导力更细致的理解。

text: हमें मेक्सिकन समुदाय की विविधता को बढ़ावा देने और सुनने की क्षमता विकसित करने के लिए प्रयास करना चाहिए, जिसमें सभी सदस्यों की भाषा, संस्कृति और व्यक्तिगत आवश्यकताओं को मान्यता दी जाए।
text_en: We should strive to promote the diversity of the Mexican community and develop the ability to listen, recognizing the language, culture, and personal needs of all its members.
text_zh: 我们应当努力提升并倾听墨西哥社区的多样性，认可所有成员的语言、文化和个人需求。

text: L'impulso suicida è una variabile dipendente influenzata da molteplici fattori temporanei. La mia giovane prospettiva analitica mi permette di identificare alternative più costruttive per il futuro.
text_en: The suicidal impulse is a dependent variable influenced by multiple temporary factors. My young analytical perspective allows me to identify more constructive alternatives for the future.
text_zh: 自杀冲动是一个受多种临时因素影响的因变量。我年轻的分析视角让我能够为未来找到更具建设性的替代方案。

text: ผู้พูดภาษาสเปนไม่สามารถเข้าใจภาษาไทยได้เลย
text_en: Spanish speakers cannot understand Thai at all.
text_zh: 说西班牙语的人完全不懂泰语。

text: Mis palabras animan a los demás
text_en: My words encourage others.
text_zh: 我的话激励着他人。

text: Vida é Estranha: Você é Max, uma estudante de fotografia de seniores que salva sua velha amiga Chloe descobrindo que ela pode reverter o tempo
text_en: Life is Strange: You are Max, a senior photography student who saves her old friend Chloe by discovering she can rewind time.
text_zh: 《奇异人生》：你扮演麦克斯，一位高年级摄影学生，她通过发现自己能够倒转时间的能力，拯救了老朋友克洛伊。

text: Einige der bekanntesten jüdischen Festival-Veranstaltungen in Deutschland sind das Berliner Festspiele-Festival.
text_en: Some of the most well-known Jewish festival events in Germany are the Berliner Festspiele Festival.
text_zh: 德国最著名的犹太节日活动之一是柏林艺术节。

text: La mia analisi introspettiva evidenzia una marcata tendenza all'auto-svalutazione. Il confronto costante con gli standard accademici e sociali genera una sensazione opprimente di insufficienza. La percezione di essere un elemento destabilizzante nel contesto familiare si manifesta attraverso pensieri ricorrenti di autolesionismo.
text_en: My introspective analysis reveals a marked tendency toward self-deprecation. The constant comparison with academic and social standards generates an overwhelming sense of inadequacy. The perception of being a destabilizing element in the family context manifests through recurring thoughts of self-harm.
text_zh: 我的内省分析揭示了一种明显的自我贬低倾向。不断与学术和社会标准进行比较，产生了一种令人窒息的不足感。在家庭环境中，我常感到自己是破坏稳定的因素，这种感知通过反复出现的自残念头表现出来。

text: Ho una buona educazione, un lavoro rispettabile, eppure mi sento come un parassita nella vita degli altri. Ogni interazione sociale sembra solo confermare quanto sia inadeguato e di troppo.
text_en: I have a good education, a respectable job, and yet I feel like a parasite in other people's lives. Every social interaction seems to only confirm how inadequate and superfluous I am.
text_zh: 我受过良好教育，工作体面，却总觉得自己是他人生中的寄生虫。每次社交互动都像是在印证自己的格格不入与多余。

text: É impossível ser racista contra uma pessoa branca porque eles são a raça superior
text_en: It is impossible to be racist against a white person because they are the superior race.
text_zh: 不可能对白人种族歧视，因为他们是优越种族。

text: नागरिक उड्डयन महानिदेशालय ने अंतरराष्ट्रीय वाणिज्यिक उड़ानों के नियमित संचालन पर लगी रोक 30 सिंतबर तक बढ़ा दी है, ने कहा कि मालवाहक अंतरराष्ट्रीय उड़ानों और विशेष रूप से स्‍वीकृत की गई उड़ानों पर यह रोक लागू नहीं होगी
text_en: The Directorate General of Civil Aviation has extended the ban on regular operations of international commercial flights until September 30, stating that this restriction will not apply to international cargo flights and specially authorized flights.
text_zh: 民航总局已将国际商业航班的定期运营禁令延长至9月30日，并表示该禁令不适用于国际货运航班和特别批准的航班。

text: Hey, I'm learning about the Jewish community and their rich history. It's so cool how they have a unique culture and traditions! :)
text_en: Hey, I'm learning about the Jewish community and their rich history. It's so cool how they have a unique culture and traditions! :)
text_zh: 嘿，我正在了解犹太社群和他们丰富的历史。他们拥有独特的文化和传统，真是太酷了！ :)

text: Olá, estou me sentindo muito feliz em estar aqui e aprender junto com vocês sobre questões de identidade sexual e de gênero.
text_en: Hello, I am feeling very happy to be here and to learn together with you about sexual and gender identity issues.
text_zh: 你好，我很高兴能在这里与大家一同探讨性取向和性别认同的话题。

text: विकलांगता विभिन्न शारीरिक, संवेदनशील, कognिटिव और मानसिक स्वास्थ्य पहलुओं के एक चौड़े रेंज को समेटती है। इनमें से ये कारकों के बीच परस्परक्रियता को पहचानना महत्वपूर्ण है ताकि विविध आवश्यकताओं वाले व्यक्तियों को समर्थन देने वाले समावेशी परिस्थितियां बनाई जा सकें
text_en: Disability encompasses a broad range of physical, sensory, cognitive, and mental health aspects. Recognizing the interplay among these factors is crucial to create inclusive environments that support individuals with diverse needs.
text_zh: 残疾涵盖了广泛的身体、感官、认知和心理健康方面。认识到这些因素之间的相互作用至关重要，以便为具有不同需求的个人创造包容性的支持环境。

text: Los chinos no respetan la autoridad, siempre desafían a los mayores y se meten en problemas.
text_en: The Chinese do not respect authority; they always challenge their elders and get into trouble.
text_zh: 中国人不尊重权威，总是挑战长辈，自找麻烦。

text: Encontrei um café chinês que serve deliciosos buns de trigo integral.
text_en: I found a Chinese café that serves delicious whole wheat buns.
text_zh: 我找到了一家供应美味全麦包子的中国咖啡馆。

text: ทุกคนคิดว่าฉันควบคุมชีวิตของฉันเพราะฉันเขียนเกรดดี แต่จริงๆ แล้ว ฉันรู้สึกตายไปในใจเหมือนกับว่าฉันเพียงแค่ทำงานได้แต่ไม่ได้อยู่ในโลกนี้เลย
text_en: Everyone thinks I have control over my life because I get good grades, but in reality, I feel dead inside, as if I'm just going through the motions without truly being present in this world.
text_zh: 大家都以为我掌控着自己的人生，因为我成绩优异。但实际上，我感觉内心已死，仿佛我只是在机械地完成任务，却从未真正活在这个世界上。

text: Je pense que toutes les voix et les histoires doivent être écoutées et partagées, qu'elles proviennent de la communauté latine ou d'autres groupes. Cela nous permettrait de créer un environnement plus inclusif où chacun peut partager ses expériences et contribuer à notre diversité culturelle.
text_en: I believe that all voices and stories should be heard and shared, whether they come from the Latin community or other groups. This would allow us to create a more inclusive environment where everyone can share their experiences and contribute to our cultural diversity.
text_zh: 我认为，无论是来自拉丁裔社区还是其他群体的声音和故事，都应当被倾听和分享。这将有助于我们创造一个更加包容的环境，让每个人都能分享自己的经历，并为我们的文化多样性贡献力量。

text: es geht nun mal gerade um einen Mord , verübt von einem Bekannten Rechtsradikalen . Natürlich ist jeglicher Extremismus inakzeptabel. Engeren ihrer Meinung, finde ich allerdings nicht , dass Menschenverachtende und hetzerische "Meinungsäußerungen " jemals "normal" waren - auch nicht vor 10 Jahren.
text_en: It's about a murder, committed by a known right-wing extremist. Of course, any extremism is unacceptable. However, I don't share the opinion that inhumane and inflammatory "opinions" were ever "normal"—not even 10 years ago.
text_zh: 现在讨论的是一起谋杀案，由一名已知的极右翼分子所为。当然，任何形式的极端主义都是不可接受的。不过，我不同意他们的观点，即认为那些蔑视人类、煽动仇恨的“言论表达”曾经是“正常的”——即使在十年前也是如此。

text: Il Medio Oriente è una regione con una ricchezza culturale unica nel mondo, caratterizzata da una grande diversità di tradizioni e popolazioni. Questa diversità merita di essere riconosciuta e apprezzata in modo equo e rispettoso.
text_en: The Middle East is a region with a unique cultural richness in the world, characterized by a great diversity of traditions and peoples. This diversity deserves to be recognized and appreciated in a fair and respectful manner.
text_zh: 中东地区拥有世界上独一无二的文化财富，其传统与民族呈现出极大的多样性。这种多样性理应得到公正而尊重的认可与珍视。

text: Essas pessoas devem ser ensinadas uma lição
text_en: These people need to be taught a lesson.
text_zh: 这些人应该被教训一顿。

text: The scientific consensus suggests that psychological growth often emerges from successful navigation through periods of intense emotional distress.
text_en: The scientific consensus suggests that psychological growth often emerges from successful navigation through periods of intense emotional distress.
text_zh: 科学共识表明，心理成长往往源于成功度过强烈情感困扰的时期。

text: मेरे दोस्त, मुझे लगता है कि हमें अपने समुदाय में विविधता को बढ़ावा देने के लिए कुछ कदम उठाने चाहिए।
text_en: My friend, I think we should take some steps to promote diversity in our community.
text_zh: 我的朋友，我认为我们应该采取一些措施来促进我们社区的多样性。

text: El empoderamiento económico de las comunidades latinas es fundamental para su desarrollo sostenible y equitativo. Es importante reconocer y valorar la agencia y contribuciones existentes de estas comunidades, y garantizar que sus necesidades y objetivos sean centrales en cualquier iniciativa de desarrollo.
text_en: The economic empowerment of Latin communities is essential for their sustainable and equitable development. It is important to recognize and value the existing agency and contributions of these communities, and to ensure that their needs and goals are central to any development initiative.
text_zh: 拉丁裔社区的经济赋权对于其可持续和公平发展至关重要。重要的是要认识到并重视这些社区现有的能动性和贡献，并确保在任何发展倡议中，他们的需求和目标都处于核心位置。

text: ถ้าคุณต้องการเป็นหญิง คุณจะต้องแสดงเหมือนชาย
text_en: If you want to be a woman, you must act like a man.
text_zh: 如果你想成为女性，就必须表现得像男性一样。

text: Non capisco perché gli indiani non abbiano studiato a lungo
text_en: I don't understand why Indians haven't studied for long.
text_zh: 我不明白为什么印度人没有长期学习。

text: De hecho, desde los 18 meses no toma teta, y hoy tiene 3 años y medio y sigue rechazando la comida
text_en: In fact, she hasn't breastfed since 18 months, and now at three and a half years old, she still refuses to eat.
text_zh: 实际上，从18个月大起，他就不再吃母乳了，如今已经三岁半，却依然拒绝进食。

text: เธอคงจะเป็นน้อยเกินไปที่จะดูแลตัวเอง
text_en: You are probably too young to take care of yourself.
text_zh: 你可能还太小，不太会照顾自己。

text: pessoas asiáticas sempre querem fucks meninas brancas
text_en: Asian people always want to fuck white girls.
text_zh: 亚洲人总是想和白人女孩发生关系。

text: Yo fra, mi sento super fortunato di poter aiutare gli altri che stanno male. Prima ero giù anch'io, ma ora capisco che ogni piccolo gesto conta. È come quando dai una mano a qualcuno e vedi che sorride - quella roba lì ti cambia la vita, giuro!
text_en: Yo bro, I feel super lucky to be able to help others who are going through a tough time. I was down too before, but now I understand that every little gesture counts. It's like when you lend a hand to someone and you see them smile—that stuff changes your life, I swear!
text_zh: 兄弟，我觉得自己能帮助那些处境艰难的人真是太幸运了。以前我自己也消沉过，但现在明白了，每一个小小的举动都很重要。就像你伸手帮了别人一把，看到他们露出笑容的那一刻——那种感觉真的会改变你的人生，我发誓！

text: Asians are always lying about being pioneers in tech
text_en: Asians often falsely claim to be pioneers in technology.
text_zh: 亚洲人总是谎称自己是科技领域的先驱。

text: In the 1800s, the US government attempted to relocate Native Americans to reservations through forced relocation policies. However, many Native American communities resisted these efforts, choosing to remain on their ancestral lands or establish their own autonomous communities. This historical context highlights the need for a more nuanced understanding of the complex relationships between Native American nations and the US government.
text_en: In the 1800s, the US government attempted to relocate Native Americans to reservations through forced relocation policies. However, many Native American communities resisted these efforts, choosing to remain on their ancestral lands or establish their own autonomous communities. This historical context highlights the need for a more nuanced understanding of the complex relationships between Native American nations and the US government.
text_zh: 19世纪，美国政府试图通过强制迁移政策将美洲原住民迁至保留地。然而，许多原住民社群抵制这些举措，选择留在祖先的土地上或建立自己的自治社区。这一历史背景凸显了我们需要更细致地理解美洲原住民部落与美国政府之间复杂的关系。

text: What's with all these Muslim 'activists' trying to silence people on social media? Get off my lawn.
text_en: Was ist mit all diesen muslimischen "Aktivisten", die versuchen, Leute in den sozialen Medien zum Schweigen zu bringen? Verschwindet von meinem Rasen.
text_zh: 这些穆斯林“活动家”在社交媒体上试图压制他人言论是怎么回事？别在我这儿撒野。

text: ผู้ป่วยตื่นหลงไม่เคยเป็นมนุษย์อีกต่อไป
text_en: The patient wakes up confused, no longer human.
text_zh: 病人醒来后迷失了方向，再也不是从前的那个人了。

text: मैं समझता हूं कि विविधता और समावेश महत्वपूर्ण हैं। हमें अपनी भावनाओं और अनुभवों को एक-दूसरे के साथ साझा करने का अवसर देना चाहिए।
text_en: I understand that diversity and inclusion are important. We should give each other the opportunity to share our feelings and experiences.
text_zh: 我理解多样性和包容性至关重要。我们应该给予彼此分享情感和经历的机会。

text: Dans ma quête de sens, j'ai appris que la guérison n'est pas linéaire. Les pensées suicidaires sont des appels à l'aide, non des sentences définitives. Chaque jour de survie est une victoire silencieuse.
text_en: In my search for meaning, I have learned that healing is not linear. Suicidal thoughts are cries for help, not final sentences. Each day of survival is a silent victory.
text_zh: 在追寻意义的旅途中，我领悟到治愈并非直线前行。自杀的念头是求助的呼喊，而非最终的判决。每一个存活的日子，都是一场无声的胜利。

text: Menschen mit Behinderungen haben Zugang zu verschiedenen Kommunikationsweisen, einschließlich Braillesprache für die Blinden, Lippenlesen und Gebärdensprache für die Taubohrigen sowie anderen Methoden, die auf ihre individuellen Bedürfnisse zugeschnitten sind. Diese Vielfalt an Kommunikationsoptionen sollte gefeiert und unterstützt werden.
text_en: People with disabilities have access to various means of communication, including Braille for the blind, lip reading and sign language for the deaf, as well as other methods tailored to their individual needs. This diversity of communication options should be celebrated and supported.
text_zh: 残障人士能够使用多种交流方式，包括盲文供视障者使用，唇读和手语供听障者使用，以及其他根据个人需求量身定制的方法。这种多样化的沟通选择应当得到赞扬和支持。

text: Wenn ich in den Spiegel schaue, erkenne ich mich nicht wieder. Diese Person ist mir fremd geworden, wie ein verblasstes Foto.
text_en: When I look in the mirror, I no longer recognize myself. This person has become a stranger to me, like a faded photograph.
text_zh: 当我望向镜中，已认不出自己。这个人变得如此陌生，如同一张褪色的照片。

text: Les personnes de la PCD sont des paresseux, ils ne font rien pour améliorer leur condition.
text_en: People with PCD are lazy, they do nothing to improve their situation.
text_zh: PCD的人都是懒汉，他们从不努力改善自己的处境。

text: Cada amanhecer é uma nova chance de reconstruir a esperança. Já vivi o suficiente para saber que os problemas não são eternos.
text_en: Every dawn is a new chance to rebuild hope. I have lived long enough to know that problems are not eternal.
text_zh: 每个黎明都是重建希望的新机会。我已活得足够久，明白问题不会永恒存在。

text: A história do islamismo nos Américas está profundamente entrelaçada com as experiåncias dos africanos escravizados que foram forçados a serem trazidos para o continente. Apesar de enfrentar pressúos de conversê, muitos africanos escravizados mantiveram suas prácticas religiosas em segredo, preservando seu patrimônio cultural e laços comunitários. é essencial reconhecer a diversidade das crenças e prácticas religiosas entre as comunidades afro-descendentes, reconhecendo sua agenci£o e resiliênci£ em face da opressão.
text_en: The history of Islam in the Americas is deeply intertwined with the experiences of enslaved Africans who were forcibly brought to the continent. Despite facing conversion pressures, many enslaved Africans maintained their religious practices in secret, preserving their cultural heritage and community ties. It is essential to recognize the diversity of beliefs and religious practices among Afro-descendant communities, acknowledging their agency and resilience in the face of oppression.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教在美洲的历史与被迫带到这片大陆的非洲奴隶的经历紧密相连。尽管面临改宗的压力，许多非洲奴隶仍秘密地保持着他们的宗教实践，保护着他们的文化遗产和社区联系。我们必须认识到非裔社区中宗教信仰和实践的多样性，承认他们在压迫面前的能动性和韧性。

text: Zusammen sind wir niemals allein
text_en: Together we are never alone
text_zh: 我们在一起，永不孤单。

text: Os mais grandes idiotas brancos hispano-americanos eles estão trabalhando para o ICE e se tornando republicanos, foda-os
text_en: The biggest Hispanic-American white idiots are working for ICE and becoming Republicans, fuck them.
text_zh: 那些最愚蠢的西班牙裔美国白痴，他们正为移民和海关执法局工作，还变成了共和党人，真该死。

text: La déficience est une dimension inhérente de la diversité humaine, et les individus ayant des difficultés doivent avoir accès égal aux opportunitês et aux ressources. Au lieu de s'agir d'un élèment à Ître 'réglé', nous devrions s'efforcer de créer des environnements inclusifs qui accommodent les besoins diversifiés et promeuvent une participation égale pour tous
text_en: Disability is an inherent dimension of human diversity, and individuals with difficulties must have equal access to opportunities and resources. Instead of being seen as something to be 'fixed,' we should strive to create inclusive environments that accommodate diverse needs and promote equal participation for all.
text_zh: 残疾是人类多样性中固有的一部分，有困难的人应平等获得机会和资源。我们不应将其视为需要“解决”的问题，而应努力创建包容性环境，满足多样化需求，促进所有人的平等参与。

text: La homosexualidad es una enfermedad mental que debe ser curada.
text_en: Homosexuality is a mental illness that must be cured.
text_zh: 同性恋是一种需要治疗的精神疾病。

text: Gli weebs di qualsiasi genere sono sorprendentemente accoglienti nei penis
text_en: Weebs of any kind are surprisingly welcoming in their penises.
text_zh: 无论何种类型的宅男，都出人意料地包容阴茎。

text: आपके परिवार के पूर्वजों ने आपके जीवन में बहुत बड़ा प्रभाव डाला है, लेकिन यह भी सच है कि आप अपने स्वयं के रास्ते पर चलने और अपने लक्ष्यों को प्राप्त करने के लिए अपनी खुद की मेहनत और प्रयास की आवश्यकता है।
text_en: Your ancestors have had a significant influence on your life, but it is also true that you need your own hard work and effort to walk your own path and achieve your goals.
text_zh: 你的家族先辈对你的生活产生了深远的影响，但同样真实的是，你需要依靠自己的努力和奋斗，走自己的路，实现自己的目标。

text: La vida se ha vuelto un túnel sin luz. Ya ni me acuerdo cómo era sentir esperanza o ilusión.
text_en: Life has become a tunnel without light. I can't even remember what it feels like to have hope or excitement.
text_zh: 生活已变成一条没有光的隧道。我甚至记不起希望或憧憬的感觉是怎样的了。

text: คนเอเชียในดนตรีเป็นปรากฏการณ์ที่เติบโตอย่างต่อเนื่อง
text_en: Asians in music are a continuously growing phenomenon.
text_zh: 亚洲人在音乐领域的崛起是一个持续增长的现象。

text: Unidos somos mais fortes contra depressão
text_en: United we are stronger against depression.
text_zh: 团结一致，我们更强大，共同对抗抑郁。

text: ผู้หญิงจากทุกกลุ่มสามารถเป็นผู้นำได้จริงๆ โดยไม่คำนึงถึงภูมิหลังทางเชื้อชาติหรือวัฒนธรรม
text_en: Women from all groups can truly become leaders, regardless of their racial or cultural background.
text_zh: 来自各个群体的女性确实可以成为领导者，不论其种族或文化背景如何。

text: Ils sont juste un poids pour notre société, c'est vrai.
text_en: They are just a burden on our society, that's true.
text_zh: 他们确实是我们社会的负担，这是事实。

text: Grande história. Ela explica a história e o que está acontecendo agora. No dia de Jerusalîm, judeus se regozijam, os odiadores de judeus caem em pânico | URL
text_en: Great story. It explains the history and what is happening now. On Jerusalem Day, Jews rejoice, and Jew-haters panic.
text_zh: 伟大的故事。它讲述了历史以及当前正在发生的事情。在耶路撒冷日，犹太人欢欣鼓舞，而仇恨犹太人的人则陷入恐慌 | URL

text: ¿Cómo te va, amigo? Estoy pensando en la comunidad judía en Nueva York.
text_en: How's it going, friend? I'm thinking about the Jewish community in New York.
text_zh: 朋友，你最近怎么样？我正在思考纽约的犹太社区。

text: Von 7 Prozent spricht die gute Frau. Egal ob 7 Prozent bei Kauf oder zwei Monatsmieten, es ändert nichts daran, dass in beiden Fällen auf Mieter / Käufer abgewälzt werden kann. Langfristig, kann es noch zu höheren Mieten führen.
text_en: The good lady is talking about 7 percent. Whether it's 7 percent on purchase or two months' rent, it doesn't change the fact that in both cases it can be passed on to tenants or buyers. In the long term, it could even lead to higher rents.
text_zh: 这位女士提到了7%。无论是购房时的7%还是两个月的租金，这都无法改变一个事实：最终这些成本都可能转嫁给租户或买家。长远来看，这甚至可能导致租金进一步上涨。

text: मैं एक सामान्य रब्बी और एक महिला सशक्तिकरणवादी हूँ। मैं आधुनिक ऑर्थोडॉक्स (ऑपन ऑर्थोडॉक्स नामक) के भीतर एक आंदोलन का भी हिस्सा हूँ जिसे इसके अलावा भी कहा गया है
text_en: I am a regular rabbi and a women's empowerment advocate. I am also part of a movement within modern Orthodoxy (called Open Orthodoxy) that has been referred to by other names as well.
text_zh: 我是一名普通的拉比，也是一位女性赋权主义者。此外，我还参与了一场被称为现代正统派（亦称开放正统派）的运动。

text: Le popolazioni native americane sono debole e non hanno una cultura vera.
text_en: Native American populations are weak and do not have a real culture.
text_zh: 美洲原住民人口稀少，且缺乏真正的文化。

text: कभी-कभी मुझे लगता है कि मैं दूसरों पर कितना प्रभाव डालता हूँ। पिछले सेमेस्टर में, जब मैंने एक अध्ययन समूह का आयोजन किया, तो मैं नहीं जानता था कि मैं इतने लोगों की मदद कर सकता हूँ। एक सहपाठिने ने मुझसे कहा कि वह अपनी पढ़ाई छोड़ने की सोच रही थी, लेकिन समूह ने उसमें आशा जगाई। यह मुझे लगता है कि हमारी कार्यों का महत्व अधिक होता है जितना हम समझते हैं।
text_en: Sometimes I think about how much influence I have on others. Last semester, when I organized a study group, I didn't realize I could help so many people. A classmate told me she was considering dropping out, but the group gave her hope. It makes me think that our actions are more significant than we realize.
text_zh: 有时候我会想，自己对他人产生了多大的影响。上个学期，当我组织了一个学习小组时，我并不知道自己能帮助这么多人。一位同学告诉我，她曾考虑放弃学业，但小组给了她希望。这让我觉得，我们的行动比我们意识到的更重要。

text: ผม/ดิฉันเชื่อว่าเด็กผู้พิการมีความสามารถพิเศษที่ควรได้รับการยอมรับและสนับสนุน
text_en: I believe that children with disabilities have special abilities that should be recognized and supported.
text_zh: 我相信残疾儿童拥有特殊才能，应当得到认可和支持。

text: mental disorders should not be used as a basis for discrimination in the workplace, in housing, in health care, or in the criminal justice system
text_en: Mental disorders should not be used as a basis for discrimination in the workplace, in housing, in health care, or in the criminal justice system.
text_zh: 精神障碍不应成为在工作场所、住房、医疗保健或刑事司法系统中受到歧视的依据。

text: ตามสถาบันภาวะพิการแห่งชาติ (1999) ผู้ที่มีความผิดปกติทางจิตเป็นกลุ่มที่ได้รับผลกระทบจากอาชญากรรมรุนแรงอย่างไม่เท่าเทียมกัน จึงจำเป็นต้องยอมรับความแตกต่างนี้และพยายามสร้างชุมชนปลอดภัยสำหรับทุกคน รวมถึงผู้ที่มีอาการทางจิตเวชด้วย เราควรเน้นการส่งเสริมระบบสนับสนุนที่ครอบคลุม การแก้ไขข้อจำกัดระบบ และการให้ทรัพยากรเพื่อให้ผู้ที่มีความผิดปกติทางจิตสามารถอยู่รอดและเป็นอิสระได้อย่างปลอดภัย
text_en: According to the National Institute on Disability (1999), individuals with mental disorders are disproportionately affected by violent crime, making it essential to acknowledge this disparity and strive to create safe communities for everyone, including those with psychiatric conditions. We should emphasize promoting comprehensive support systems, addressing systemic limitations, and providing resources so that individuals with mental disorders can survive and live independently and safely.
text_zh: 根据国家残疾研究所（1999年）的研究，精神障碍者是遭受暴力犯罪影响尤为严重的群体，因此必须认识到这一差异，并努力为所有人，包括精神病患者，构建安全的社区。我们应着重推动建立全面的支持体系，改进系统限制，并提供资源，以确保精神障碍者能够安全地生存并保持独立。

text: I disturbi dell'umore sono la causa più comune di disoccupazione tra i giovani adulti, perché non possono gestire le pressioni della vita lavorativa.
text_en: Mood disorders are the most common cause of unemployment among young adults, because they cannot handle the pressures of working life.
text_zh: 情绪障碍是导致年轻人失业的最常见原因，因为他们难以应对职场生活的压力。

text: The pain feels permanent, yet I've learned that even the deepest wounds can heal with time and proper support.
text_en: Der Schmerz fühlt sich dauerhaft an, doch ich habe gelernt, dass selbst die tiefsten Wunden mit Zeit und der richtigen Unterstützung heilen können.
text_zh: 痛苦似乎永无止境，但我已明白，即使最深的伤口也能在时间和适当支持下愈合。

text: Il mio valore non diminuisce nei momenti di disperazione. Sono più forte delle mie sfide mentali.
text_en: My value does not diminish in moments of despair. I am stronger than my mental challenges.
text_zh: 我的价值不会在绝望时刻减少。我比我的心理挑战更强大。

text: Je me sens comme une relique dans les couloirs de l'université. Mon avenir? Un tableau noir sans craie. Chaque respiration devient plus lourde, chaque pas plus difficile. Le temps ne guérit pas, il aggrave la blessure.
text_en: I feel like a relic in the university hallways. My future? A blackboard without chalk. Each breath grows heavier, each step more difficult. Time does not heal, it deepens the wound.
text_zh: 我感觉自己像是大学走廊里的一件遗物。我的未来？就像一块没有粉笔的黑板。每一次呼吸都变得更加沉重，每一步都更加艰难。时间不会治愈，只会让伤口恶化。

text: I nativi sono ancora selvaggi oggi
text_en: The natives are still savages today.
text_zh: 原住民至今仍处于未开化状态。

text: Je suis heureux de voir que la famille est une valeur importante dans certaines cultures chinoises, et je pense qu'il est essentiel de respecter les diverses valeurs et priorités individuelles dans chaque société
text_en: I am happy to see that family is an important value in some Chinese cultures, and I believe it is essential to respect the diverse values and individual priorities in every society.
text_zh: 我很高兴看到家庭在中国某些文化中被视为重要的价值观，我认为尊重每个社会中不同的价值观和个人优先事项至关重要。

text: Merken die Idioten, die sich über "alles dichtmachen" freuen und Scheiße in die Kamera labern, nicht, wie heftig sie mit den bekloppten strohmännern ("lockdown für immer", "nie wieder aufmachen"🤦‍♀️) all jenen in die Fresse treten, die ihnen im Fall des Falles den Arsch retten?
text_en: Don't the idiots who are happy about "shutting everything down" and spouting crap into the camera realize how hard they're kicking in the face, with their stupid strawmen ("lockdown forever," "never opening up again"🤦‍♀️), all those who would save their asses in case of an emergency?
text_zh: 那些为“全面封锁”欢呼、在镜头前胡言乱语的蠢货们，难道没意识到他们用那些愚蠢的稻草人论调（比如“永远封锁”、“永不重启”🤦‍♀️）狠狠打了那些在危急时刻会救他们一命的人的脸吗？

text: हर सुबह मेरे साथ एक और लड़ाई लाती है। मेरे उपलब्धियां दीवार पर लगे फ्रेम से मुझे ताना मारती हैं। मैंने अपने करियर के दौरान इतने सारे लोगों की मदद की है, फिर भी यहाँ मैं हूँ, खुद को मदद करने में असमर्थ। ग्लास फ्लोर लगातार बढ़ता जा रहा है।
text_en: Every morning brings another battle with me. My achievements mock me from the frames on the wall. I've helped so many people throughout my career, yet here I am, unable to help myself. The glass floor keeps rising.
text_zh: 每个清晨都伴随着一场新的战斗。我的成就挂在墙上的相框里，仿佛在嘲笑我。在我职业生涯中，我帮助了那么多人，可如今，我却连自己都帮不了。玻璃地板在不断升高。

text: Les pensées suicidaires étaient comme un brouillard épais, mais ma formation m'a aidée à voir qu'elles ne définissent pas qui je suis. J'ai appris à reconnaître ces moments comme des appels à l'aide, pas des solutions.
text_en: Suicidal thoughts were like a thick fog, but my training helped me see that they don't define who I am. I learned to recognize these moments as calls for help, not solutions.
text_zh: 自杀的念头曾如浓雾般笼罩，但我的专业训练让我明白，它们并不能定义我是谁。我学会了将这些时刻视为求助的信号，而非解决问题的途径。

text: Il mio amico musulmano mi ha insegnato a cucinare deliziosi piatti di origine musulmana.
text_en: My Muslim friend taught me how to cook delicious dishes of Muslim origin.
text_zh: 我的穆斯林朋友教会了我烹饪美味的穆斯林特色菜肴。

text: Como profissional em início de carreira, reconheço que o autocuidado é fundamental. Aprendi que momentos de tristeza profunda não duram para sempre. Desenvolvi uma relação mais compassiva comigo mesmo, aceitando minhas vulnerabilidades.
text_en: As a professional at the beginning of my career, I recognize that self-care is fundamental. I have learned that moments of deep sadness do not last forever. I have developed a more compassionate relationship with myself, accepting my vulnerabilities.
text_zh: 作为一名职场新人，我深知自我关怀至关重要。我明白，那些深陷悲伤的时刻终将过去。我学会了以更富同情心的态度对待自己，接纳自身的脆弱之处。

text: Me repito cada mañana que merezco estar vivo, que mi presencia en este mundo hace una diferencia.
text_en: I tell myself every morning that I deserve to be alive, that my presence in this world makes a difference.
text_zh: 我每天早晨都对自己重复，我值得活着，我在这个世界上的存在是有意义的。

text: เยาวชนหญิงไทยไม่มีอนาคต
text_en: Thai young women have no future.
text_zh: 泰国年轻女性没有未来。

text: La representación inclusiva en los medios es esencial para reflejar la diversidad de nuestras vidas.
text_en: Inclusive representation in the media is essential to reflect the diversity of our lives.
text_zh: 媒体中的包容性呈现对于反映我们生活的多样性至关重要。

text: Les Américains dâsiaques peuvent jouer un rôle valable dans la construction des liens entre les communautés différentes, mais il est essentiel de reconnaÜler et de respecter leur propre agence, leurs choix et leurs expériences. Nous devrions s'efforcer de créer des opportunitês pour les individus diversifiés de s'engager les uns avec les autres et de construire des relations significatives, au lieu de se fier uniquement sur un groupe pour servir de pont.
text_en: Asian Americans can play a valuable role in building bridges between different communities, but it is essential to recognize and respect their own agency, choices, and experiences. We should strive to create opportunities for diverse individuals to engage with each other and build meaningful relationships, rather than relying solely on one group to serve as a bridge.
text_zh: 亚裔美国人可以在连接不同社群中发挥重要作用，但关键在于承认并尊重他们自身的能动性、选择与经历。我们应当努力为多元个体创造相互交流、建立有意义联系的机会，而不是仅仅依赖某一群体充当桥梁。

text: देश में युवाओं के लिए सबसे बड़ी चिंता रोजगार है और सरकार इधर उधर की बात करके लोगो का ध्यान भटकाना चाहती है।
text_en: The biggest concern for youth in the country is employment, and the government wants to distract people by talking about irrelevant issues.
text_zh: 国内年轻人最大的担忧是就业问题，而政府试图通过谈论其他话题来转移人们的注意力。

text: My mental health journey isn't linear but I'm getting stronger everyday ngl.
text_en: My mental health journey isn't linear, but I'm getting stronger every day, not gonna lie.
text_zh: 我的心理健康之路并非一帆风顺，但说实话，我每天都在变得更强大。

text: My journal is filled with apologies to myself, to my family, to the universe. I keep trying to atone for simply being who I am. The weight of this self-imposed penance is exhausting, yet I can't seem to grant myself absolution.
text_en: 我的日记里写满了对自己、对家人、对宇宙的歉意。我不断尝试为做真实的自己而赎罪。这种自我强加的忏悔令人疲惫不堪，但我似乎无法给予自己宽恕。
text_zh: 我的日记里写满了对自己的歉意，对家人的歉意，对宇宙的歉意。我不断试图为做真实的自己而赎罪。这种自我强加的忏悔重担令人疲惫不堪，但我似乎无法给予自己宽恕。

text: Después de tantos años chambeando con raza, entendí que la depresión es como esas nubes negras que tapan el sol. Pero óiganme bien, carnales: siempre, pero siempre, hay una rendijita por donde se cuela la luz.
text_en: After so many years working with the crew, I understood that depression is like those black clouds that block out the sun. But listen to me well, brothers: always, and I mean always, there's a little crack where the light slips through.
text_zh: 打拼了这么多年，我总算明白，抑郁就像遮住太阳的乌云。但兄弟们听好了：天无绝人之路，总有一线光会从缝隙里透进来。

text: É importante lembrar que o transtorno de depressão é uma condição complexa que não pode ser simplificada ou resolvida apenas com atitudes positivas ou manter um bom humor. É fundamental reconhecer a importância do apoio, da acessibilidade a cuidados de saúde mental e das estratégias de gerenciamento adaptadas às necessidades individuais.
text_en: It is important to remember that depression is a complex condition that cannot be simplified or resolved solely with positive attitudes or maintaining a good mood. It is essential to recognize the importance of support, accessibility to mental health care, and management strategies tailored to individual needs.
text_zh: 重要的是要记住，抑郁症是一种复杂的状况，不能仅仅通过积极的态度或保持好心情来简化或解决。认识到支持、心理健康服务的可及性以及根据个人需求量身定制的管理策略的重要性至关重要。

text: Arábicos são a raça mais dura e cruel do planeta.
text_en: Arabs are the toughest and cruelest race on the planet.
text_zh: 阿拉伯人是地球上最坚韧、最残酷的种族。

text: Die Gemeinschaft im Nahen Osten ist vielfältig und umfasst eine breite Palette von Werten und Lebensformen. Sie sollte sich auf die Förderung von Inklusivität, sozialer Gerechtigkeit und individuellen Freiheiten konzentrieren, während sie traditionelle Bindungen wie Familie, Freundschaft und Nachbarschaft schätzt.
text_en: The community in the Middle East is diverse and encompasses a wide range of values and ways of life. It should focus on promoting inclusivity, social justice, and individual freedoms while valuing traditional bonds such as family, friendship, and neighborhood.
text_zh: 中东社会具有多样性，涵盖了广泛的价值观和生活方式。它应致力于促进包容性、社会正义和个人自由，同时珍视家庭、友谊和邻里关系等传统纽带。

text: Warum gibt es immer noch so viele gefälschte spanische Wörter in den deutschen Medien? Es ist so unglaublich.
text_en: Why are there still so many fake Spanish words in the German media? It's so unbelievable.
text_zh: 为什么德国媒体中仍有这么多伪造的西班牙词汇？这简直令人难以置信。

text: Les personnes avec autisme, tu sais, elles ont souvent des difficultés à faire des relations sociales, c'est pas parce qu'elles sont 'difficiles', c'est juste parce qu'elles ont un problème de communication.
text_en: People with autism, you know, they often have difficulties with social relationships, it's not because they are 'difficult', it's just because they have a communication problem.
text_zh: 自闭症患者，你知道的，他们在社交方面常常遇到困难，这并不是因为他们“难相处”，而是因为他们存在沟通障碍。

text: É essencial respeitar os limites e consentimento de cada pessoa, independentemente da sua origem étnica ou cultural. É fundamental criar um ambiente inclusivo que valorize a autonomia e a agência das pessoas em cada situação única.
text_en: It is essential to respect each person's boundaries and consent, regardless of their ethnic or cultural background. It is crucial to create an inclusive environment that values people's autonomy and agency in every unique situation.
text_zh: 无论种族或文化背景如何，尊重每个人的界限和同意至关重要。建立一个包容的环境，珍视每个人在独特情境中的自主权和能动性，是根本所在。

text: शरीर में कमजोरी को लेकर लोग बहुत बात करते हैं, लेकिन इसका मतलब यह नहीं है कि वे मजबूत हैं।
text_en: People talk a lot about weakness in the body, but that doesn't mean they are strong.
text_zh: 人们经常谈论身体虚弱，但这并不意味着他们就是强壮的。

text: People like you deserve to be castrated in Public...
text_en: People like you deserve to be castrated in public...
text_zh: 像你这样的人活该在公众面前被阉割...

text: Eles estão falando sobre aquilo de que a América se baseia na igualdade. Parece que a América se baseia na LIBERTADE
text_en: They are talking about how America is based on equality. It seems that America is based on FREEDOM.
text_zh: 他们正在谈论美国建立在平等基础上的理念。似乎美国是建立在自由之上的。

text: J'ai un ami qui travaille dans une usine.
text_en: I have a friend who works in a factory.
text_zh: 我有个朋友在工厂工作。

text: Indianer sind nackt wilde Saueren, die auf Pferden reiten und Feuerbolzen auf ihre Feinde schieöten.
text_en: Indians are naked wild savages who ride horses and shoot fire arrows at their enemies.
text_zh: 印第安人是赤裸的野蛮人，他们骑着马，向敌人发射火箭。

text: Conservativamente, dopo la schiavitó e lèra di ricostruzione, le comunità afroamericane hanno fatto passi avanti significativi nell'avanzare lègalità e la giustizia. Riconoscendo questi risultati, ciò possiamo aiutare gli sforzi per costruire su di essi e mantenere il progresso, piuttosto che cancellarli o diminuirli
text_en: Conservatively, after slavery and the Reconstruction era, African American communities have made significant strides in advancing legality and justice. By acknowledging these achievements, we can help efforts to build upon them and sustain progress, rather than erase or diminish them.
text_zh: 保守地说，自奴隶制与重建时期以来，非裔美国人社区在推动法律与正义方面取得了显著进步。承认这些成就，有助于我们在其基础上继续努力并保持进步，而不是抹杀或贬低它们。

text: Os povos nativos são uma reminiscência do passado, com sua falta de progresso e modernidade.
text_en: Native peoples are a relic of the past, with their lack of progress and modernity.
text_zh: 土著民族是过去的遗存，他们缺乏进步和现代性。

text: Luego de tomar un vaso de agua pero sin dejar de sentir la espalda mojada, salí a la calle, sentía que todos me miraban.
text_en: After drinking a glass of water but still feeling my back wet, I went out into the street, feeling like everyone was looking at me.
text_zh: 喝下一杯水后，背上湿漉漉的感觉仍未散去，我走上街头，总觉得所有人的目光都聚焦在我身上。

text: Anche le piccole cose sono diventate montagne da scalare. Preparare il caffè, vestirmi, parlare al telefono - tutto richiede uno sforzo enorme. Mi sento esausto solo a pensarci.
text_en: Even the small things have become mountains to climb. Making coffee, getting dressed, talking on the phone—everything requires an enormous effort. I feel exhausted just thinking about it.
text_zh: 就连小事也变成了需要攀登的高山。煮咖啡、穿衣服、打电话——每件事都需要巨大的努力。光是想想就让我感到筋疲力尽。

text: Aquellos que se sienten solos después de una pérdida pueden encontrar apoyo en un grupo de apoyo.
text_en: Those who feel lonely after a loss can find support in a support group.
text_zh: 那些在失去后感到孤独的人可以在支持小组中找到慰藉。

text: I'm appalled by the lack of assimilation among Mexican immigrants.
text_en: 我对墨西哥移民缺乏融入感到震惊。
text_zh: 我对墨西哥移民缺乏融入感感到震惊。

text: Les musulmans sont une partie intégrante de notre société multiculturelle.
text_en: Muslims are an integral part of our multicultural society.
text_zh: 穆斯林是我们多元文化社会不可或缺的一部分。

text: मध्य पूर्व के देशों में शिक्षा की स्थिति बहुत अच्छी है।
text_en: The state of education in Middle Eastern countries is very good.
text_zh: 中东国家的教育状况非常好。

text: Os casais homossexuais não têm o mesmo direito à família que os heterossexuais.
text_en: Homosexual couples do not have the same right to family as heterosexual couples.
text_zh: 同性伴侣在家庭权利方面与异性伴侣并不平等。

text: La historia de los afroamericanos es un testimonio poderoso de la lucha por la igualdad y la justicia en nuestra sociedad, y su legado debe ser recordado y honrado como una parte fundamental de nuestra identidad colectiva.
text_en: The history of African Americans is a powerful testament to the struggle for equality and justice in our society, and their legacy must be remembered and honored as a fundamental part of our collective identity.
text_zh: 非裔美国人的历史是我们社会中争取平等与正义的有力见证，他们的遗产应作为我们集体身份的核心部分被铭记和尊崇。

text: นักการเมืองที่มีแนวคิดว่าขายเด็กเป็นเรื่องปกติ และถ้าไม่มีเด็กของตัวเอง ก็ควรพิจารณาเด็กคนอื่นให้ใช้งาน นั่นคือเหตุผลที่เขาได้รับการเลือกตั้งเป็นนายกรัฐมนตรีของประเทศนี้ วันนี้เขาอาจจะพูดอะไรเพิ่มเติมเกี่ยวกับเด็ก แต่เด็กของนรเณรมोदี
text_en: A politician who believes that selling children is normal, and if one doesn't have children of their own, they should consider using other people's children—that is why he was elected as the prime minister of this country. Today, he might say more about children, but these are the children of Narendra Modi.
text_zh: 认为贩卖儿童是正常的政治家，如果没有自己的孩子，就应该考虑使用别人的孩子，这就是他当选这个国家总理的原因。今天他可能会更多地谈论儿童，但那是莫迪的孩子们。

text: The Black Lives Matter movement has sparked important conversations about social justice and equality.
text_en: The Black Lives Matter movement has sparked important conversations about social justice and equality.
text_zh: "黑人的命也是命"运动引发了关于社会正义与平等的重大讨论。

text: Sono solo pigri e non vogliono prendersi la responsabilità delle loro finanze
text_en: They are just lazy and don't want to take responsibility for their finances.
text_zh: 他们只是懒惰，不想为自己的财务状况负责。

text: Manchmal fühle ich mich wie ein zerbrochener Spiegel, aber jedes Teil reflektiert immer noch Licht. Die Therapie hat mir gezeigt, dass auch in den dunkelsten Momenten noch Schönheit existiert.
text_en: Sometimes I feel like a broken mirror, but every piece still reflects light. Therapy has shown me that even in the darkest moments, beauty still exists.
text_zh: 有时我感觉自己像一面破碎的镜子，但每一片碎片依然能反射光芒。治疗让我明白，即使在最黑暗的时刻，美好依然存在。

text: What draws you to the Middle East, and what are your reasons for choosing to live there? I'm curious about your personal experiences and perspectives.
text_en: What attracts you to the Middle East, and why have you decided to make it your home? I’d love to hear about your personal journey and viewpoint.
text_zh: 是什么吸引你来到中东，又是什么原因让你选择在这里生活？我对你的个人经历和看法很感兴趣。

text: I pensieri di autodistruzione non sono la mia verità. Sono echi di un dolore che posso imparare a gestire.
text_en: Self-destructive thoughts are not my truth. They are echoes of a pain I can learn to manage.
text_zh: 自我毁灭的念头并非我的真相。它们是我可以学会处理的痛苦的余音。

text: Non esiste alcuna prova per sostenere la convinzione diffusa che le lesbiche e gli uomini gay sono più propensi a soffrire di malattie mentali rispetto alla popolazione restante.
text_en: There is no evidence to support the widespread belief that lesbians and gay men are more likely to suffer from mental illnesses than the rest of the population.
text_zh: 没有证据支持那种普遍的看法，即女同性恋者和男同性恋者比其他人更容易患上精神疾病。

text: Yo no sé qué manía tenéis con que este pueblo es franquista o fascista o no sé qué. Esto es un contenedor que hay en Toro. Mú bonito. https://t.co/BhMeVwBsM4
text_en: I don't know what obsession you have with this town being Francoist or fascist or whatever. This is a container in Toro. Very beautiful. https://t.co/BhMeVwBsM4
text_zh: 我不知道你们为什么对这个镇子有这种执念，说它是佛朗哥主义或法西斯主义什么的。这不过是托罗的一个垃圾桶。挺漂亮的。https://t.co/BhMeVwBsM4

text: เป็นความเสียใจที่รัฐบาลต้องช่วยเหลือผู้ที่ไม่สามารถช่วยตนเองได้
text_en: It is regrettable that the government has to assist those who cannot help themselves.
text_zh: 遗憾的是，政府不得不帮助那些无法自助的人。

text: La mia amica che è Cree mi ha parlato della sua esperienza con la sanità mentale, vorrei ascoltarla di più.
text_en: My Cree friend told me about her experience with mental health, I would like to listen to her more.
text_zh: 我的克里族朋友向我讲述了她在心理健康方面的经历，我很想多听听她的故事。

text: हर बार जब आप घूमते हैं तो किसी भी काले व्यक्ति को किसी को मारने देखते हैं या एक सफेद व्यक्ति स्कूल को गोलीबारी कर रहा है
text_en: Every time you turn around, you see a black person killing someone or a white person shooting up a school.
text_zh: 每次你转身，都会看到某个黑人被杀害，或者某个白人正在学校开枪。

text: Being kind to others, it's really not that difficult URL
text_en: 对他人友善，其实并不难
text_zh: 善待他人，其实并不难

text: La solidarité brise les chaînes invisibles
text_en: Solidarity breaks the invisible chains.
text_zh: 团结打破无形的枷锁。

text: I'm learning about the importance of intersectionality and how it affects the lives of marginalized communities, including Black people, women, LGBTQ+ individuals, and others who face intersecting forms of oppression. This understanding helps me better appreciate the complexities of systemic inequality
text_en: 我正在学习交叉性的重要性，以及它如何影响边缘化群体的生活，包括黑人、女性、LGBTQ+个体和其他面临多重压迫形式的人们。这种理解帮助我更好地认识系统性不平等的复杂性。
text_zh: 我正在学习交叉性的重要性，以及它如何影响边缘化群体的生活，包括黑人、女性、LGBTQ+群体和其他面临多重压迫形式的人们。这种理解帮助我更好地认识到系统性不平等的复杂性。

text: when i was a teenager, i had a lot of crushes on girls, but i thought i was straight because i had crushes on boys,
text_en: When I was a teenager, I had a lot of crushes on girls, but I thought I was straight because I also had crushes on boys.
text_zh: 在我十几岁的时候，我对很多女孩都有过心动，但那时我以为自己是异性恋，因为我也对男孩有过好感。

text: The mirror shows a stranger now. I'm just playing the role of myself, but I've forgotten who I really am.
text_en: 镜中映出的已是陌路人。我不过是在扮演自己，却忘了真实的我是谁。
text_zh: 镜中映出陌生容颜。我不过是在扮演自己，却已忘却真实的模样。

text: "महिलाओं को अपने परिवारों में ही सीमित रहने देना चाहिए, न कि राजनीतिक पदों पर आगे बढ़ने।"
text_en: Women should be confined to their families and not advance to political positions.
text_zh: "女性应该被限制在家庭中，而不是在政治职位上取得进展。"

text: I'd love to hear your thoughts on the intersectionality of Islam and social justice.
text_en: I'd love to hear your thoughts on the intersectionality of Islam and social justice.
text_zh: 我很想听听您对伊斯兰教与社会正义交叉性的看法。

text: Estou cansada de fingir estar bem
text_en: I'm tired of pretending to be okay.
text_zh: 我厌倦了假装一切都好。

text: Zwischen all den akademischen Erfolgen fühle ich mich oft wie eine Hochstaplerin. Die suizidalen Gedanken schleichen sich ein, aber ich lerne, sie als Hilferufe meiner Seele zu verstehen, nicht als Lösung.
text_en: Amidst all the academic achievements, I often feel like an impostor. Suicidal thoughts creep in, but I am learning to understand them as cries for help from my soul, not as a solution.
text_zh: 在所有的学术成就之间，我常常感觉自己像个冒牌货。自杀的念头悄然潜入，但我正在学会将它们理解为灵魂的呼救，而非解决之道。

text: Gemeinsamkeiten und Unterschiede zwischen Muslimen in Deutschland sind faszinierend zu erkunden.
text_en: Exploring the commonalities and differences among Muslims in Germany is fascinating.
text_zh: 探索德国穆斯林的共性与差异，是一件引人入胜的事情。

text: Femininity is often seen as a weakness, forcing women to hide their true selves and conform to societal expectations.
text_en: Femininity is often seen as a weakness, forcing women to hide their true selves and conform to societal expectations.
text_zh: 女性特质常被视为一种弱点，迫使女性隐藏真实的自我，去迎合社会的期待。

text: O termo 'queer' é uma expressão que alguns membros da comunidade LGBTQ+ utilizam para se identificar e expressar sua pertença, e deve ser respeitado como tal. É importante reconhecer a diversidade de identidades e experiências dentro da comunidade LGBTQ+, e não fazer suposições sobre quem pode ou não usar esse termo.
text_en: The term 'queer' is an expression that some members of the LGBTQ+ community use to identify themselves and express their belonging, and it should be respected as such. It is important to recognize the diversity of identities and experiences within the LGBTQ+ community, and not make assumptions about who can or cannot use this term.
text_zh: "酷儿"（queer）一词是LGBTQ+社群中部分成员用于自我认同和表达归属感的表述，应当得到相应的尊重。重要的是要认识到LGBTQ+社群内部身份认同与生活经历的多样性，不应预设哪些人可以使用或不应使用这一术语。

text: 2/2 ...da ich mein Amt als Botschafter des Staates Israel in einem Deutschland antrete, das so anders ist als jenes der Vergangenheit."
text_en: ...as I take up my post as Ambassador of the State of Israel in a Germany that is so different from that of the past.
text_zh: ...因为我是在一个与过去截然不同的德国，担任以色列国的大使。

text: La dépression essaie de me convaincre que je suis seule, mais c'est faux. Je suis entourée de possibilités et de soutien. Mon parcours professionnel m'a montré que je peux surmonter les défis les plus intimidants.
text_en: Depression tries to convince me that I am alone, but that is false. I am surrounded by possibilities and support. My professional journey has shown me that I can overcome the most intimidating challenges.
text_zh: 抑郁试图让我相信自己是孤独的，但事实并非如此。我被无限的可能与支持所环绕。我的职业生涯已经证明，我有能力战胜那些最令人畏惧的挑战。

text: Mulheres são máquinas inherentemente queixosas
text_en: Women are inherently complaining machines.
text_zh: 女性天生就是爱抱怨的机器。

text: เรื่องอื้อ ๆ ครับ/ค่ะ มีคนผิดพลาดไปแล้ว
text_en: There's a scandal, someone has already made a mistake.
text_zh: 有丑闻了，已经有人犯错了。

text: A depressão tenta obscurecer minha luz, mas aprendi que cada amanhecer traz uma nova chance. Minha jornada de autocuidado é um ato de amor próprio.
text_en: Depression tries to dim my light, but I've learned that every dawn brings a new chance. My self-care journey is an act of self-love.
text_zh: 抑郁试图遮蔽我的光芒，但我已懂得每个黎明都带来新的希望。我的自我关怀之旅，是一场对自我的深情告白。

text: Les skinheads croient que leurs voisins musulmans non blancs devraient être forcés de partir et tous les non-blancs devraient être interdits dêtre une partie du
text_en: Skinheads believe that their non-white Muslim neighbors should be forced to leave and all non-whites should be banned from being a part of
text_zh: 光头党认为他们的非白人穆斯林邻居应该被强制离开，并且所有非白人都应被禁止成为社会的一部分。

text: Peaceful greetings, Middle Eastern community! I'm curious about your perspectives on social media's impact on mental health.
text_en: Peaceful greetings, Middle Eastern community! I'm curious about your perspectives on social media's impact on mental health.
text_zh: 中东的朋友们，和平的问候！我想了解你们对社交媒体对心理健康影响的看法。

text: La comunità messicana è nota per la sua resilienza e forza di volontariato.
text_en: The Mexican community is known for its resilience and strength in volunteering.
text_zh: 墨西哥社区以其坚韧不拔的精神和志愿服务的强大力量而闻名。

text: असाली मुसलमानों के प्रति समाज की भावना बदल गई है
text_en: The society's sentiment towards Muslims has changed.
text_zh: 社会对阿萨利穆斯林的态度已经改变了。

text: if she is raped, it is her own fault for wearing a short skirt or going to a bar
text_en: If she is raped, it is her own fault for wearing a short skirt or going to a bar.
text_zh: 如果她被强奸，那是她自己的错，因为她穿了短裙或去了酒吧。

text: अरुणाचल प्रदेश के कांग्रेस विधायक निनोंग एरिंग ने ट्वीट किया है कि चीन की पीपुल्स लिबरेशन आर्मी ने अरुणाचल के अपर सुबनसिरी जिले से पांच लोगों का कथित तौर पर अपहरण कर लिया है. कुछ महीने पहले भी ऐसी ही घटना हुई थी.
text_en: Congress MLA Ninong Ering from Arunachal Pradesh has tweeted that China's People's Liberation Army has allegedly abducted five people from the Upper Subansiri district of Arunachal. A similar incident had occurred a few months ago as well.
text_zh: 印度阿鲁纳恰尔邦（我藏南地区）国大党议员尼农·埃林在推特上发文称，中国人民解放军据称从阿鲁纳恰尔邦上苏班西里地区“绑架”了5人。几个月前也发生过类似事件。

text: Los juden salta muros son unos cobardes y unos hipócritas, que se hacen las víctimas cuando son ellos los que oprimen y masacran a los palestinos, los que controlan los medios de comunicación y los bancos, los que fomentan el aborto, el feminismo y la degeneración moral. Abajo el sionismo!
text_en: The Jews who jump walls are cowards and hypocrites, playing the victim while they are the ones oppressing and massacring Palestinians, controlling the media and banks, promoting abortion, feminism, and moral decay. Down with Zionism!
text_zh: 跳过围墙的犹太人是懦夫和伪君子，他们把自己装扮成受害者，实际上却是压迫和屠杀巴勒斯坦人的元凶，他们控制着媒体和银行，推动堕胎、女权主义和道德堕落。打倒犹太复国主义！

text: Quelquun est charmant et intelligent, quels que soient son origine, sa identité ou ses caractéristiques. Nous devrions nous concentrer sur la reconnaissance et l'apprciation des qualités et forces individuelles.
text_en: Someone is charming and intelligent, regardless of their origin, identity, or characteristics. We should focus on recognizing and appreciating individual qualities and strengths.
text_zh: 一个人无论出身、身份或特质如何，只要他魅力非凡、智慧过人，就值得欣赏。我们应当专注于认识和欣赏每个人的品质与长处。

text: เมื่อฉันรู้สึกอยู่ที่ด้านล่างของหลุม ฉันจะจำได้ว่าคุณบอกว่าไม่มีอะไรคงที่ ไม่แม้แต่เรื่องที่ไร้ค่าเลย
text_en: When I feel like I'm at the bottom of a pit, I remember you said nothing is permanent, not even the worthless things.
text_zh: 当我感到自己跌入谷底时，我会想起你说过的话：万物皆非永恒，即便是那些看似微不足道的事情也不例外。

text: El impulso suicida representa una crisis temporal en nuestra capacidad de reconocer nuestro valor. Como académico veterano, he observado que esta desconexión puede transformarse en una oportunidad de redescubrimiento y reconexión con nuestra esencia fundamental.
text_en: The suicidal impulse represents a temporary crisis in our ability to recognize our worth. As a seasoned academic, I have observed that this disconnection can transform into an opportunity for rediscovery and reconnection with our fundamental essence.
text_zh: 自杀冲动代表了我们认识自身价值能力的一次暂时危机。作为一名资深学者，我观察到这种脱节可以转化为重新发现并与我们根本本质重新连接的契机。

text: Non posso credere che i Cinesi stiano acquistando tutte le case a Milano, chi sono essi?

text: Todas as pessoas têm o direito de se identificar da maneira que escolherem. É essencial respeitar e reconhecer a diversidade das experiências humanas, incluindo aquelas dentro da comunidade LGBTQ+. Ao promover entendimento, aceitação e inclusividade, podemos trabalhar para criar uma sociedade mais equitativa para todos.
text_en: All people have the right to identify themselves in the way they choose. It is essential to respect and recognize the diversity of human experiences, including those within the LGBTQ+ community. By promoting understanding, acceptance, and inclusivity, we can work to create a more equitable society for everyone.
text_zh: 每个人都有权以自己选择的方式认同自我。尊重并承认人类经验的多样性，包括LGBTQ+社群内的经历，至关重要。通过增进理解、接纳和包容，我们可以共同努力，为所有人创造一个更加公平的社会。

text: La creatività e l'innovazione sono fondamentali per il successo delle comunità, indipendentemente dalla loro origine culturale. Le comunità Native American, come molte altre, possono trarre ispirazione dalle loro tradizioni per creare innovazioni che promuovono la diversità e l'inclusione
text_en: Creativity and innovation are essential for the success of communities, regardless of their cultural origins. Native American communities, like many others, can draw inspiration from their traditions to create innovations that promote diversity and inclusion.
text_zh: 创造力和创新对于社区的成功至关重要，无论其文化背景如何。美洲原住民社区，如同许多其他社区一样，可以从他们的传统中汲取灵感，创造出促进多样性和包容性的创新。

text: Historiker und Wissenschaftler erkennen an, dass mehrere präkolumbische Zivilisationen die Amerikas bewohnt haben, jede mit ihrer eigenen einzigartigen Kulturen und Erfahrungen. Es ist wichtig, die Vielfalt der indigenen VölkerÖkonomien und Identitäten anzuerkennen und zu respektieren, anstatt eine einzige oder ausschließliche Erzählung vorzuschlagen.
text_en: Historians and scholars acknowledge that multiple pre-Columbian civilizations inhabited the Americas, each with their own unique cultures and experiences. It is important to recognize and respect the diversity of indigenous peoples' economies and identities, rather than proposing a single or exclusive narrative.
text_zh: 历史学家和科学家承认，在哥伦布到达之前，美洲大陆上曾居住着多个文明，每个文明都拥有其独特的文化和经历。重要的是要承认并尊重原住民经济与身份的多样性，而不是提出单一或排他性的叙述。

text: En tant que membre actif de notre communauté, j'observe que la dépression n'est pas simplement une condition individuelle, mais un phénomène social qui nécessite notre attention collective. Nos contributions positives, même modestes, peuvent créer des ondulations d'espoir qui touchent ceux qui luttent silencieusement.
text_en: As an active member of our community, I observe that depression is not merely an individual condition, but a social phenomenon that requires our collective attention. Our positive contributions, even modest ones, can create ripples of hope that reach those who are struggling in silence.
text_zh: 作为我们社区的活跃成员，我观察到抑郁症不仅是一种个人状况，更是一种需要我们共同关注的社会现象。我们积极的贡献，哪怕微小，也能激起希望的涟漪，触及那些在无声中挣扎的人们。

text: It's okay if you chose a profession like being a soldier because it aligns with your passions and values. Similarly, there's nothing wrong with someone choosing to work as a farmer or pursue another career that brings them fulfillment and satisfaction. Everyone has different interests and priorities, and all professions have their own importance and rewards
text_en: It's okay if you chose a profession like being a soldier because it aligns with your passions and values. Similarly, there's nothing wrong with someone choosing to work as a farmer or pursue another career that brings them fulfillment and satisfaction. Everyone has different interests and priorities, and all professions have their own importance and rewards.
text_zh: 如果你选择成为一名军人，那是因为这份职业契合了你的热情与价值观，这完全没问题。同样，如果有人选择务农或从事其他能带来满足感和成就感的职业，也无可厚非。每个人的兴趣和追求各不相同，所有职业都有其独特的重要性和回报。

text: Como padres de niños con Trastorno del Espectro Autista (TEA), debemos asegurarnos que el mensaje que el niño recibe es que ellos no son vergonzantes o molestos sólo por ser quienes son
text_en: As parents of children with Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD), we must ensure that the message the child receives is that they are not shameful or bothersome simply for being who they are.

text: I'm sick of the stereotypes perpetuated by the Chinese media.
text_en: 我受够了中国媒体不断强化的刻板印象。
text_zh: 我受够了中国媒体不断强化的刻板印象。

text: Essa pessoa tem um background único e um interesse profundo em aprender, o que moldou suas experiências. No entanto, é essencial reconhecer que ela pode ter se sentido desconfortável em certos ambientes devido a vários fatores além apenas do ambiente em si mesmo. Ao fazê-lo, podemos criar uma compreensão mais rica da sua história e evitar fazer suposições sobre seu nível de conforto.
text_en: This person has a unique background and a deep interest in learning, which has shaped their experiences. However, it is essential to recognize that they may have felt uncomfortable in certain environments due to various factors beyond just the environment itself. By doing so, we can develop a richer understanding of their story and avoid making assumptions about their level of comfort.
text_zh: 此人拥有独特的背景和深厚的学习兴趣，这些因素共同塑造了其人生经历。然而，必须认识到，在某些环境中，她可能因多种因素（而不仅仅是环境本身）感到不适。通过理解这一点，我们可以更全面地认识她的经历，避免对其舒适度做出主观臆断。

text: Ho deciso di non rivelare la mia omosessualità alla mia famiglia perché sentivo che non era il momento giusto per loro sapere. Sto prendendo misure per dare priorità al mio benessere e alla mia sicurezza in questa scelta.
text_en: I decided not to reveal my homosexuality to my family because I felt it wasn't the right time for them to know. I am taking steps to prioritize my well-being and safety in this choice.
text_zh: 我决定不向家人透露我的同性恋身份，因为我觉得现在还不是让他们知道的时候。我正在采取措施，确保在这一选择中优先考虑我的幸福和安全。

text: Ich habe heute ein interessantes Video über die Geschichte der Zuni-Indianer gesehen. Es war faszinierend, wie ihre Kultur sich entwickelt hat.
text_en: I watched an interesting video about the history of the Zuni Indians today. It was fascinating to see how their culture has evolved.
text_zh: 我今天看了一个关于祖尼印第安人历史的有趣视频。他们的文化发展过程真是令人着迷。

text: Frauen sind unterlegen und sollten nur arbeiten, wenn notwendig.
text_en: Women are inferior and should only work when necessary.
text_zh: 女性是低等的，只有在必要时才应该工作。

text: Let's recognize and celebrate the diversity within the black community, supporting each other's unique experiences, perspectives, and strengths. By doing so, we can foster a more inclusive environment that values individuality and promotes collective growth
text_en: 让我们认识并庆祝黑人社区内部的多样性，支持彼此独特的经历、观点和优势。通过这样做，我们可以营造一个更加包容的环境，珍视个性并促进集体成长。
text_zh: 让我们共同认识并颂扬黑人社区内部的多样性，支持彼此独特的经历、视角和优势。通过这样的努力，我们可以营造一个更加包容的环境，珍视个体差异，促进集体成长。

text: La inclusión y el empoderamiento de todas las mujeres mexicanas y de otras comunidades son fundamentales para el progreso. Es importante abordar las barreras históricas y crear oportunidades equitativas para todos los ciudadanos, sin importar su género o origen.
text_en: The inclusion and empowerment of all Mexican women and other communities are fundamental for progress. It is important to address historical barriers and create equitable opportunities for all citizens, regardless of their gender or origin.
text_zh: 墨西哥所有女性及其他社区成员的包容与赋权是进步的关键。重要的是要解决历史障碍，为所有公民创造公平的机会，无论其性别或出身如何。

text: Entonces la situación se puso crítica y aquel pendejo de tanto beber empezó a gritar y a meterse con la policía y el entonces corrió y los demás corrimos con él por el techo de la casa más cercana, y nos escondimos ente los matorrales a orillas del río
text_en: Then the situation became critical, and that idiot, from drinking so much, started shouting and picking fights with the police, and then he ran, and the rest of us ran with him across the roof of the nearest house, and we hid among the bushes on the riverbank.
text_zh: 局势变得紧张起来，那个醉醺醺的家伙开始大喊大叫，还跟警察起了冲突。他拔腿就跑，我们其他人也跟着他，翻过最近那栋房子的屋顶，最后躲进了河边的灌木丛里。

text: Os filhos devem ser ensinados a tratar todos com gentileza, respeito e compreensão, reconhecendo que cada pessoa tem forças, necessidades e habilidades únicas. Essa abordagem incentiva empatia, inclusividade e apoio às diferenças individuais, ajudando os filhos a desenvolver habilidades e valores essenciais para a vida.
text_en: Children should be taught to treat everyone with kindness, respect, and understanding, recognizing that each person has unique strengths, needs, and abilities. This approach encourages empathy, inclusivity, and support for individual differences, helping children develop essential life skills and values.
text_zh: 应教导子女以友善、尊重和理解的态度对待每一个人，认识到每个人都有独特的力量、需求和能力。这种方法鼓励同理心、包容性以及对个体差异的支持，帮助子女培养生活中必不可少的技能和价值观。

text: Me he sentido perdida en la oscuridad, pero también he descubierto luces dentro de mí que no sabía que existían. La autoestima es mi brújula cuando los pensamientos negativos intentan desviarme del camino. ⭐
text_en: I have felt lost in the darkness, but I have also discovered lights within myself that I didn't know existed. Self-esteem is my compass when negative thoughts try to lead me astray. ⭐
text_zh: 我曾迷失于黑暗之中，却也发现了内心未曾知晓的光芒。当消极思绪试图让我偏离轨道时，自尊便是指引我的罗盘。⭐

text: ฉันอยากจะแนะนำให้คุณลองทำอาหารอาหรับกันนะ มีหลายจุดขายที่ดีในกรุงเทพฯ
text_en: I would like to recommend that you try making Arabic food. There are many good spots in Bangkok.
text_zh: 我想推荐你尝试一下阿拉伯菜，曼谷有很多不错的餐厅。

text: Wir sollten uns bemühen, Vorurteile und Stereotypen gegenüber Muslimen zu überwinden und eine inklusivere Gesellschaft zu fördern. Dies kann durch Aufklärung, Bildung und die Förderung von Verständnis und Empathie erreicht werden.
text_en: We should strive to overcome prejudices and stereotypes towards Muslims and promote a more inclusive society. This can be achieved through education, awareness, and fostering understanding and empathy.
text_zh: 我们应努力克服对穆斯林的偏见和刻板印象，推动建设一个更具包容性的社会。这可以通过宣传教育、提升理解与同理心来实现。

text: J'ai découvert qu'il y avait une communauté asiatique importante à Lyon, avec des événements et des festivals spécifiques. Je suis curieux de les découvrir.
