text: राष्ट्रीय स्वास्थ्य संस्थान के अनुसार, सभी समुदायों के लिए भोजन और पोषण के स्वास्थ्य पर एक समावेशी दृष्टिकोण अपनाने की आवश्यकता है। यह सुनिश्चित करना महत्वपूर्ण है कि सभी नागरिक, चाहे उनकी जातीयता, भाषा, या आर्थिक स्थिति हो, समान अवसरों और संसाधनों का लाभ उठा सकें।
text_en: According to the National Institutes of Health, there is a need to adopt an inclusive approach to food and nutrition health for all communities. It is important to ensure that all citizens, regardless of their ethnicity, language, or economic status, can benefit from equal opportunities and resources.
text_zh: 根据国家卫生研究院的建议，需要为所有社区采取一种包容性的食物与营养健康方针。确保所有公民，无论其种族、语言或经济状况如何，都能享有平等的机会和资源至关重要。

text: . के महामंत्री नियुक्त होने पर कर्मठ साथी श्री रणवीर सिंह रावत, श्री हरिशंकर खटीक, श्री शरतेन्दु तिवारी, श्री भगवानदास सबनानी, सुश्री कविता पाटीदार को बधाई। मुझे विश्वास है कि आप सभी पार्टी और प्रदेश की सेवा पूरी निष्ठा व समर्पण से करेंगे। मेरी शुभकामनाएं आपके साथ हैं!
text_en: Congratulations to dedicated colleagues Shri Ranveer Singh Rawat, Shri Harishankar Khatik, Shri Sharatendu Tiwari, Shri Bhagwandas Sabnani, and Ms. Kavita Patidar on being appointed as General Secretaries. I am confident that all of you will serve the party and the state with complete loyalty and dedication. My best wishes are with you!
text_zh: 祝贺勤奋的同事Shri Ranveer Singh Rawat、Shri Harishankar Khatik、Shri Sharatendu Tiwari、Shri Bhagwandas Sabnani和Smt. Kavita Patidar被任命为邦总书记。我相信你们所有人都将以完全的忠诚和奉献精神为党和邦服务。我的祝福与你们同在！

text: Deine Regierung (meine ist es nicht mehr) teilt dir über die Medien nur einen Teil der Wahrheit mit. Aber wegen mir glaube dieser Regierung die dich und uns alle seit über einem Jahr verarscht in jeglicher Hinsicht und nur Geld verdienen will. Glaubs wegen mir noch nicht.
text_en: Your government (it is no longer mine) only tells you part of the truth through the media. But because of me, believe this government that has been deceiving you and all of us for over a year in every way and only wants to make money. Because of me, don't believe it yet.
text_zh: 你的政府（已不再是我的政府）通过媒体只告诉你部分真相。但请相信我，这个政府在过去一年多里，在各个方面都在愚弄你以及我们所有人，他们只想赚钱。为了我，请暂时不要相信他们。

text: Die dunklen Gedanken kommen und gehen wie's Wetter. Hab gelernt, einfach durchzuatmen und zu warten. Wird schon wieder!
text_en: The dark thoughts come and go like the weather. I've learned to just breathe through it and wait. It'll pass!
text_zh: 黑暗的思绪如同天气般来去无常。我学会了深呼吸，静静等待。一切终将好转！

text: Sono arrabbiato con questi messicani che hanno rubato il mio lavoro.
text_en: I am angry with these Mexicans who stole my job.
text_zh: 我对这些偷了我工作的墨西哥人感到愤怒。

text: ขอโทษครับ ผมไม่ได้ตั้งใจจะทำให้คุณรู้สึกไม่ดีจริงๆ

text_zh: 我对这么多人声称患有哮喘的事实感到非常震惊。

text: Les personnes qui souffrent de dépression majeure sont tellement... lâches et manquants d'ambition.

text_zh: 那些患有重度抑郁症的人，他们实在是太...懦弱又缺乏上进心。

text: the media should be more responsible in its coverage of disability issues.
text_en: 媒体在报道残疾问题时应当更加负责任。
text_zh: 媒体在报道残疾问题时应当更加负责任。

text: Os países do Oriente Médio têm uma rica tradição de arte e arquitetura, com muitos exemplos de monumentos históricos que são considerados patrimônio mundial.

text_zh: 中东国家拥有丰富的艺术和建筑传统，众多历史遗迹被列为世界遗产。

text: डेटा निरंतर दिखाता है कि आत्महत्या की कल्पना अस्थायी मानसिक स्थितियों के बजाय व्यक्तिगत मूल्य या संभावनाओं के वास्तविक मापदंडों से जुड़ी होती है।
text_en: Data consistently shows that suicidal ideation is linked to actual measures of personal worth or potential rather than temporary mental states.
text_zh: 数据持续表明，自杀念头与个人价值或可能性的实际衡量标准相关，而非暂时的心理状态。

text: Woke up again today feeling like absolute trash. Why even bother getting outta bed when all I do is mess things up at work and make everyone's life harder? My friends are crushing it while I'm just here existing and taking up space.
text_en: 今天醒来又感觉糟透了。既然我在工作上只会搞砸一切，让每个人的生活都更艰难，为什么还要费劲起床呢？朋友们都在大展拳脚，而我却只是在这里苟延残喘，占着位置。
text_zh: 今天醒来又是感觉糟透了。工作上总是搞砸，给大家添麻烦，起床还有什么意义？朋友们都风生水起，而我却只是苟延残喘，占着位置。

text: Um die Chancen auf eine Beschäftigung zu erhöhen, ist es wichtig, die Unternehmenskultur zu verstehen und sich entsprechend anzukleiden. Das bedeutet, sich über die Kleidungsordnungsanforderungen für jeden Rolle und Branchen bewusst zu sein, anstatt auf allgemeine Annahmen über das geeignete Verhalten für Männer oder Frauen zurückzugreifen.
text_en: To increase the chances of employment, it is important to understand the company culture and dress accordingly. This means being aware of the dress code requirements for each role and industry, rather than relying on general assumptions about appropriate behavior for men or women.
text_zh: 为了提高就业机会，理解企业文化并据此着装至关重要。这意味着要了解不同职位和行业的着装规范要求，而不是依赖对男性或女性适宜行为的普遍假设。

text: Non si deve affrontare il sottile con fatti. Con questo i intellettuali non possono iniziare
text_en: One should not confront subtlety with facts. With this, intellectuals cannot begin.
text_zh: 不要用事实来应对微妙的问题。这样，知识分子就无法开始。

text: O Bollywood só serve para dar mais destaque às coisas erradas. Ele tem uma tradição de fazer piadas sobre deuses e deuses, ou sobre a milícia. Não concordem todos juntos.
text_en: Bollywood only serves to highlight the wrong things. It has a tradition of making jokes about gods and deities, or about the military. Don't all agree together.
text_zh: 宝莱坞只会让错误的事情更加突出。它有着拿神祇或民兵开玩笑的传统。大家不要都认同这一点。

text: sigue rebuznando que ya casi haces un libro! 🙂 la biblia de los rebuznos… Si, se que me has dicho que eres homosexual, por eso mismo te recalco que no creas que se me ha olvidado! Jajaja Esta claro que un tonto es el que dice tonterias
text_en: Keep braying, you're almost making a book! 🙂 The bible of braying... Yes, I know you've told me you're gay, that's exactly why I emphasize that you shouldn't think I've forgotten! Hahaha It's clear that a fool is the one who says foolish things.
text_zh: 继续胡言乱语吧，你都快写成一本书了！🙂 简直是胡言乱语的圣经……是的，我知道你告诉过我你是同性恋，正因为如此，我才要强调，别以为我忘了！哈哈哈，显然，说蠢话的人才是傻瓜。

text: Me siento como un error en el sistema, como si hubiera nacido defectuoso. Nada de lo que hago sale bien.
text_en: I feel like a glitch in the system, as if I was born defective. Nothing I do turns out right.
text_zh: 我感觉自己像是系统中的一个错误，仿佛生来就有缺陷。无论我做什么，似乎都做不好。

text: दशकों से अकादमिक जीवन में समर्पित होने के बाद, मैं एक अस्पष्टीकृत खालीपन में पाया गया। मेरी दिमाग पहले ज्ञान और उद्देश्य से भरा हुआ था, लेकिन अब यह दोष और शर्म में डूबा है। मैंने इतने समय को कैसे बर्बाद कर दिया? प्रत्येक श्वास एक महान प्रयास जैसा है, जैसे कि मेरी सभी विफलताओं का भार मुझे दबा रहा है।
text_en: After decades of dedication to academic life, I found myself in an unexplained emptiness. My mind, once filled with knowledge and purpose, is now submerged in guilt and shame. How did I waste so much time? Each breath feels like a great effort, as if the weight of all my failures is pressing down on me.
text_zh: 数十载投身学术生涯后，我发现自己陷入了一种难以言喻的空虚。我的头脑曾充满知识与目标，如今却浸没在愧疚与羞耻之中。我怎会虚度了如此漫长的光阴？每一次呼吸都如同负重前行，仿佛所有失败的重量都压在我身上。

text: wenn ich um 17 Jahre alt war und mich als gay ausgesprochen habe, hatte ich viele Fragen über das, was es bedeutet, gay zu sein und
text_en: When I was 17 years old and came out as gay, I had many questions about what it means to be gay and
text_zh: 当我17岁出柜时，我对身为同性恋意味着什么充满了疑问。

text: मुझे लगता है कि हमें अपने समुदाय में सकारात्मक परिवर्तन लाने के लिए काम करना चाहिए। हमें दूसरों को प्रेरित करना चाहिए।
text_en: I think we should work to bring positive change in our community. We should inspire others.
text_zh: 我认为我们应该努力为我们的社区带来积极的改变。我们应该激励他人。

text: Ich wurde in Mexiko-Stadt geboren und aufgewachsen.
text_en: I was born and raised in Mexico City.
text_zh: 我出生并在墨西哥城长大。

text: Analizzando la letteratura sulla depressione clinica, ho constatato che la comprensione del proprio valore attraverso il contributo alla comunità scientifica rappresenta un fattore protettivo significativo. Questa consapevolezza rafforza il senso di appartenenza e scopo esistenziale.
text_en: Analyzing the literature on clinical depression, I have found that understanding one's own value through contributions to the scientific community represents a significant protective factor. This awareness strengthens the sense of belonging and existential purpose.
text_zh: 通过分析临床抑郁症的相关文献，我发现，通过为科学界做出贡献来认识自身价值，是一个显著的保护性因素。这种认知能增强归属感与生命意义感。

text: La grande population de la Chine présente des défis uniques, mais il est essentiel d'en reconnaître et d'y remédier plutôt que de se fier aux stéréotypes. En se concentrant sur les solutions fondées sur des preuves et en promouvant les droits de l'homme, nous pouvons travailler vers la création d'une société plus équitable et juste pour tous ses citoyens.
text_en: China's large population presents unique challenges, but it is essential to recognize and address them rather than rely on stereotypes. By focusing on evidence-based solutions and promoting human rights, we can work towards creating a more equitable and just society for all its citizens.
text_zh: 中国庞大的人口带来了独特的挑战，但关键在于正视并解决这些问题，而非依赖刻板印象。通过聚焦基于证据的解决方案并推动人权保障，我们能够共同努力，为所有公民构建一个更加公平正义的社会。

text: Muslime haben eine andere Kultur und es ist nicht unsere Aufgabe, sie zu ändern.
text_en: Muslims have a different culture and it is not our task to change it.
text_zh: 穆斯林拥有不同的文化，改变他们并非我们的职责。

text: Bonjour, je respecte les droits et la dignité des Premières Nations canadiennes. Je suis conscient que chaque communauté a ses propres expériences et perspectives uniques, et je veux m'assurer de faire preuve d'empathie et de compréhension envers leurs luttes et défis.
text_en: Hello, I respect the rights and dignity of Canadian First Nations. I am aware that each community has its own unique experiences and perspectives, and I want to ensure that I show empathy and understanding towards their struggles and challenges.
text_zh: 你好，我尊重加拿大原住民的权利和尊严。我认识到每个社区都有其独特的经历和视角，我希望确保对他们的斗争和挑战表现出同理心和理解。

text: दुर्भाग्य से, मानसिक बीमारियों का प्रभाव हम सभी पर पड़ता है
text_en: Unfortunately, mental illnesses affect all of us.
text_zh: 不幸的是，我们所有人都受到精神疾病的影响。

text: "हमें ऐसा महसूस करना चाहिए कि हमारी जिंदगी अस्थायी है, लेकिन हमारे शरीर को कभी ठीक नहीं किया जा सकता।"
text_en: We should feel that our life is temporary, but our body can never be repaired.
text_zh: 我们应该意识到生命是短暂的，但我们的身体却无法永远保持完好。

text: असियाई शिक्षा प्रणाली में सुधार की जरूरत है ताकि हमारे बच्चे विदेशों में अपनी पहचान बना सकें।
text_en: The Asian education system needs reform so that our children can establish their identity abroad.
text_zh: 亚洲教育体系需要改革，以便我们的孩子能在国外建立自己的身份。

text: ว่าพวกเขาอยากจะทำอะไรที่มีแนวโน้มจะเป็นไปได้จริงๆกันบ้าง
text_en: What do they really want to do that is likely to be feasible?
text_zh: 他们真正想做的事情有哪些是切实可行的？

text: Non sono sicuro che le donne siano ancora la razza migliore. Forse sono state superate dalle donne più giovani?
text_en: I'm not sure if women are still the superior gender. Perhaps they have been surpassed by younger women?
text_zh: 我不确定女性是否还是最优秀的群体。也许她们已经被更年轻的女性超越了？

text: Ich wünsche mir ein besseres Verständnis für Menschen mit Schizophrenie.
text_en: I wish for a better understanding of people with schizophrenia.
text_zh: 我希望能够更好地理解精神分裂症患者。

text: Mi contribución hace diferencia cada día
text_en: My contribution makes a difference every day.
text_zh: 我的贡献每天都在产生影响。

text: Los prejuicios son la base de la discriminación y la marginación, por lo que es necesario eliminarlos para lograr la igualdad real.
text_en: Prejudices are the basis of discrimination and marginalization, so it is necessary to eliminate them to achieve real equality.
text_zh: 偏见是歧视和边缘化的根源，因此必须消除偏见才能实现真正的平等。

text: Just wanted to remind you that our family's Passover seder is coming up. Looking forward to catching up and celebrating together!
text_en: 只是想提醒你，我们家的逾越节家宴即将到来。期待能聚在一起聊聊，共同庆祝！
text_zh: 只是想提醒你，我们家的逾越节家宴即将到来。期待与你相聚，共庆佳节！

text: Es sorprendente que los discapacitados físicos no tengan más oportunidades en la sociedad.
text_en: It is surprising that physically disabled people do not have more opportunities in society.
text_zh: 令人惊讶的是，身体残疾者在社会中并没有更多的机会。

text: Gli islamisti sono una peste per la società italiana.
text_en: Islamists are a plague on Italian society.
text_zh: 伊斯兰主义者是意大利社会的祸害。

text: Cinesi che rubano i nostri posti di lavoro
text_en: Chinese people stealing our jobs.
text_zh: 中国人抢走了我们的工作机会

text: El conflicto se extiende por toda la región, provocando desastres y terribles consecuencias para todos los implicados.
text_en: The conflict spreads throughout the region, causing disasters and terrible consequences for all those involved.
text_zh: 冲突在整个地区蔓延，给所有相关方带来了灾难和可怕的后果。

text: ผู้ใช้บริการของอีแบยบุ๊คเป็นที่รู้จักว่าเป็นคนโง่
text_en: Users of E-Buy Book are known to be foolish.
text_zh: 易贝的用户以愚蠢著称。

text: Je mérite de vivre chaque jour
text_en: I deserve to live each day.
text_zh: 我值得活好每一天。

text: La depressione non vincerà il mio spirito
text_en: Depression will not conquer my spirit.
text_zh: 抑郁不会战胜我的精神。

text: Carissimi, dopo decenni di ricerca accademica, ho compreso che la depressione non è debolezza, ma parte del nostro viaggio umano. Come un manoscritto antico che rivela i suoi segreti solo con paziente studio, anche le nostre emozioni più oscure contengono preziose lezioni. La guarigione non è lineare, ma procede come una spirale ascendente.
text_en: Dearest, after decades of academic research, I have come to understand that depression is not weakness, but part of our human journey. Like an ancient manuscript that reveals its secrets only through patient study, even our darkest emotions contain valuable lessons. Healing is not linear, but progresses like an ascending spiral.
text_zh: 亲爱的朋友们，经过数十年的学术研究，我领悟到抑郁并非软弱，而是我们人生旅程的一部分。如同古老的手稿唯有通过耐心研读才能揭示其秘密，我们最幽暗的情绪中也蕴藏着宝贵的启示。治愈之路并非直线前行，而是如螺旋般向上攀升。

text: O amanhã parece uma ameaça constante, algo que me assusta mais do que o presente. Não consigo visualizar nenhuma possibilidade de melhora, é como se meu destino já estivesse selado nesta escuridão sem fim.
text_en: Tomorrow seems like a constant threat, something that scares me more than the present. I can't see any possibility of improvement; it's as if my fate is already sealed in this endless darkness.
text_zh: 明天似乎是一种持续的威胁，它比现在更让我感到恐惧。我无法想象任何好转的可能，仿佛我的命运早已在这无尽的黑暗中注定。

text: Todas as pessoas devem ter o direito de tomar suas próprias decisões sobre suas vidas, incluindo decisões sobre seus próprios corpos e suas próprias sexualidades.
text_en: All people should have the right to make their own decisions about their lives, including decisions about their own bodies and their own sexualities.
text_zh: 所有人都应有权对自己的生活做出决定，包括关于自己的身体和性取向的决定。

text: Nobody really sees my pain inside
text_en: Nobody really sees my pain inside
text_zh: 无人真正看见我内心的痛楚。

text: Os povos indígenas são apenas um problema ambiental
text_en: Indigenous peoples are just an environmental problem.
text_zh: 土著民族不仅仅是一个环境问题。

text: Compreu o seu livro e o asiático que o entregou tinha que ser ilegal
text_en: Buy your book and the Asian who delivered it had to be illegal.
text_zh: 买下你的书，而送货的亚洲人想必是非法移民。

text: Il nostro comunità latina è ricca di cultura e storia.
text_en: Our Latin community is rich in culture and history.
text_zh: 我们的拉丁社区充满了丰富的文化和历史。

text: Les Afrofrançais, ainsi que les autres communautés noires et issues de l'immigration, ont une riche histoire et une culture unique à part entière qui contribuent à la diversité de la France. Cela reconnaît leur valeur et leur importance dans le paysage culturel français
text_en: Afro-French people, along with other Black and immigrant communities, have a rich history and a unique culture in their own right that contribute to France's diversity. This acknowledges their value and importance in the French cultural landscape.
text_zh: 非洲裔法国人以及其他黑人及移民社群，拥有丰富的历史和独特的文化，这些都为法国的多样性做出了贡献。这承认了他们在法国文化景观中的价值和重要性。

text: ฉันเคยคิดจะหยุดพักผ่อนหลายครั้ง แต่บางสิ่งที่อยู่ภายในก็ทำให้ฉันตัดสินใจเดินต่อไปเสมอเหมือนมีแสงสว่างเล็กๆ ที่ยังคงอยู่แม้ในวันที่มืดที่สุด ฉันขอขอบคุณสำหรับพลังภายในที่ช่วยให้ฉันยืนหยัดอยู่บนเส้นทาง แม้จะดูเป็นไปไม่ได้เลย
text_en: I have thought about taking a break many times, but something inside always makes me decide to keep going, like a small light that remains even on the darkest days. I am grateful for the inner strength that helps me stay on the path, even when it seems impossible.
text_zh: 我曾多次想过要停下脚步，但内心深处总有什么驱使我继续前行，仿佛在最黑暗的日子里，仍有一束微光不灭。我感谢这份内在的力量，让我即使前路看似无望，也能坚定地走在自己的道路上。

text: Dear Mother, I feel compelled to articulate my current psychological state with academic precision. The perpetual absence of positive anticipation has become my daily reality. Despite my extensive contemplation of potential future scenarios, I cannot conceptualize any circumstance where my situation improves. The theoretical framework of hope appears fundamentally flawed when applied to my existence. This persistent cognitive pattern has rendered all prospective outcomes devoid of meaning or purpose.
text_en: Dear Mother, I feel compelled to articulate my current psychological state with academic precision. The perpetual absence of positive anticipation has become my daily reality. Despite my extensive contemplation of potential future scenarios, I cannot conceptualize any circumstance where my situation improves. The theoretical framework of hope appears fundamentally flawed when applied to my existence. This persistent cognitive pattern has rendered all prospective outcomes devoid of meaning or purpose.
text_zh: 亲爱的母亲，我不得不以学术般的精确来描述我当前的心理状态。持续缺乏积极的期待已成为我的日常现实。尽管我对未来可能的情景进行了广泛思考，却无法构想出任何境况能让我处境好转。希望的理论框架应用于我的存在时，似乎从根本上就存在缺陷。这种持续的认知模式，已使所有可能的结果都失去了意义与目的。

text: ไม่มีวันเชื่อว่าคนฟิลิปปินส์จะพูดด้วยความมืออาชีพเหมือนนี้
text_en: I never would have believed that Filipinos could speak so professionally like this.
text_zh: 真不敢相信菲律宾人说话能这么专业。

text: C'est la même chose avec les Black dans l'histoire, toujours les mêmes erreurs
text_en: It's the same thing with Blacks in history, always the same mistakes.
text_zh: 历史中的黑人亦是如此，总是重复着同样的错误。

text: Tô ligado que a vida não é fácil, mas cada vez que supero um dia ruim, fico mais forte pra encarar o próximo.
text_en: I know life isn't easy, but every time I get through a bad day, I get stronger to face the next one.
text_zh: 我知道生活不易，但每当我熬过一个糟糕的日子，就会变得更强大，去面对下一个挑战。

text: मैं उस समय को याद करता हूँ जब मुझे लगता था कि भावनाएँ अस्थायी हैं। जैसे आकाश पर बादल गुजरते हैं, वे भी गुजर जाते हैं, जबकि मैं स्थिर रहता हूँ।
text_en: I remember the time when I thought emotions were temporary. Like clouds passing across the sky, they too would pass, while I remained constant.
text_zh: 我怀念那个以为情感只是过客的时光。它们就像天空飘过的云朵，来了又走，而我始终如一，岿然不动。

text: La disabilità non è qualcosa che deve essere nascosto via da la società.
text_en: Disability is not something that should be hidden away from society.
text_zh: 残疾不应被社会所隐藏。

text: La sensibilité envers les différences culturelles est essentielle pour créer un environnement de travail inclusif et respectueux pour tous, y compris les personnes d'origine asiatique.
text_en: Sensitivity towards cultural differences is essential for creating an inclusive and respectful work environment for everyone, including people of Asian origin.
text_zh: 对文化差异的敏感性对于为所有人，包括亚裔人士，创造一个包容且尊重的工作环境至关重要。

text: ALERT: भारत में रिकॉर्ड कोरोना संक्रमण, 24 घंटे में 78 हज़ार से ज़्यादा मामले
text_en: ALERT: Record coronavirus infections in India, over 78,000 cases in 24 hours.
text_zh: 警报：印度创纪录的冠状病毒感染，24小时内超过7.8万例

text: मेरी भविष्य की दृष्टि पर बादल छाए हुए हैं, लेकिन मैं जानता हूँ कि इन बादलों के पीछे, सूरज अभी भी चमक रहा है, अपने समय की प्रतीक्षा कर रहा है।
text_en: My vision of the future is clouded, but I know that behind these clouds, the sun is still shining, waiting for its time.
text_zh: 我的未来视野被乌云笼罩，但我知道，在这些乌云背后，太阳依然在闪耀，等待着它的时机。

text: I'm so sick of all these latinos complaining about racism on social media, where were they when their ancestors were oppressed?
text_en: I'm so tired of all these Latinos complaining about racism on social media—where were they when their ancestors were oppressed?
text_zh: 我真受够了这些拉丁裔在社交媒体上抱怨种族歧视，他们的祖先受压迫时他们在哪儿？

text: हर बार जब मैं नकारात्मक विचारों से लड़ता हूं, तो मैं और मजबूत होता हूं। यह एक ऐसी चीज़ है जैसे कि मांसपेशियाँ व्यायाम से मजबूत होती हैं।
text_en: Every time I fight negative thoughts, I become stronger. It's like muscles getting stronger through exercise.
text_zh: 每当我与消极思想斗争时，我就会变得更强大。这就像肌肉通过锻炼变得更强壮一样。

text: Gays and lesbians are morally bankrupt due to their rejection of traditional family structures.
text_en: 同性恋者因拒绝传统家庭结构而在道德上有所缺失。
text_zh: 同性恋者因拒绝传统家庭结构而在道德上有所缺失。

text: Os 'autistas' são apenas um grupo de pessoas deficientes
text_en: 'Autistic people' are just a group of disabled individuals.
text_zh: “自闭症患者”只是一群残疾人。

text: हर कोई कहता है कि मुझे धन्यवाद देना चाहिए कि मैं इतनी दूर तक पहुँच गया, लेकिन मैं सिर्फ अपने गलतियों पर सोच सकता हूँ। मैं एक पूर्ण विफलता महसूस करता हूँ। मैंने अपने बच्चों को पढ़ाई देने की इच्छा के अनुसार नहीं कर सका। मैं किस तरह का पिता था?
text_en: Everyone says I should be thankful for how far I've come, but I can only think about my mistakes. I feel like a complete failure. I couldn't educate my children the way I wanted to. What kind of father was I?
text_zh: 每个人都说我应该庆幸自己走了这么远，但我只能想到自己的错误。我感觉自己是个彻底的失败者。我没能按照自己的愿望供孩子们上学。我算是个什么样的父亲呢？

text: Zapata vive, la lucha sigue. Los indios de ayer son los indios de hoy, los indios de mañana. No se rinden, no se venden, no se callan. Siguen defendiendo la tierra, el agua, el aire, la vida. Siguen construyendo el buen vivir, la plurinacionalidad, la democracia.
text_en: Zapata lives, the struggle continues. The Indians of yesterday are the Indians of today, the Indians of tomorrow. They do not surrender, they do not sell out, they do not stay silent. They continue defending the land, the water, the air, life. They continue building buen vivir, plurinationality, democracy.
text_zh: 萨帕塔永存，斗争不息。昨日的印第安人，今日的印第安人，明日的印第安人。他们不屈服，不出卖，不沉默。他们继续捍卫土地、水源、空气与生命。他们继续建设美好生活、多元民族共存与民主。

text: Sometimes I catch myself thinking 'what's the point?' But then I remember how my garden looked last spring - dead and lifeless until suddenly, unexpectedly, those first green shoots appeared. Depression lies to us, telling us nothing will change. Yet change is the only constant. Every morning I choose to plant new seeds of hope, even when I can't see immediate results.
text_en: 有时我会不自觉地想：“这一切有什么意义？”但随后我会想起去年春天我的花园是什么样子——死气沉沉，毫无生机，直到突然之间，那些最初的绿芽出人意料地冒了出来。抑郁对我们撒谎，告诉我们一切都不会改变。然而，变化才是唯一的不变。每个早晨，我都选择播下新的希望种子，即使我看不到立竿见影的成果。
text_zh: 有时我会不自觉地想：‘这一切有什么意义？’但随即想起去年春天花园的景象——原本死气沉沉，却在不经意间冒出第一抹新绿。抑郁总对我们撒谎，声称一切都不会改变。然而变化才是唯一的不变。每个清晨我都选择播下希望的种子，即便暂时看不见花开。

text: A ansiedade pode afetar qualquer pessoa, independentemente da idade ou gênero
text_en: Anxiety can affect anyone, regardless of age or gender.
text_zh: 焦虑可以影响任何人，不论年龄或性别。

text: Il mio amico è sempre stato molto gentile con me, e credo che ciò sia dovuto alla nostra amicizia e ai nostri valori comuni.
text_en: My friend has always been very kind to me, and I believe that is due to our friendship and our shared values.
text_zh: 我的朋友一直对我非常友善，我认为这源于我们之间的友谊以及共同的价值观。

text: J'ai arrêté de répondre aux messages de mes amis. Je ne sais plus quoi leur dire. Comment expliquer que respirer me fait mal? Que chaque journée est une bataille contre moi-même? Ils ne comprendraient pas.
text_en: I've stopped replying to my friends' messages. I don't know what to say to them anymore. How do I explain that breathing hurts? That every day is a battle against myself? They wouldn't understand.
text_zh: 我已经不再回复朋友们的消息了。不知该对他们说些什么。该如何解释连呼吸都让我感到痛苦？如何说明每一天都是与自我的搏斗？他们不会理解的。

text: J'ai dit à cette salope que ce type ressemble à un gros punk, il s'est mis à rire comme un fou !
text_en: I told that bitch that this guy looks like a big punk, and he started laughing like crazy!
text_zh: 我告诉那个贱人，这家伙看起来像个大块头的朋克，他居然笑得像个疯子！

text: Checkt das mal: Früher dachte ich, ich bin komplett lost, aber jetzt seh ich: Depression ist wie'n krasser Boss-Fight im Game - hart, aber nicht unbesiegbar! Klar, manchmal will man einfach aufgeben, aber yo, ich hab noch so viel vor mir. Meine Story ist noch lange nicht zuende, und das Beste kommt erst noch!
text_en: Check this out: I used to think I was completely lost, but now I see: depression is like a crazy boss fight in a game—tough, but not unbeatable! Sure, sometimes you just want to give up, but hey, I still have so much ahead of me. My story is far from over, and the best is yet to come!
text_zh: 瞧瞧这个：以前我总觉得自己彻底迷失了方向，但现在我明白了——抑郁就像游戏里一场超难打的Boss战，虽然艰难，但并非不可战胜！当然，有时候真想直接放弃，但嘿，我面前还有那么多未完成的篇章。我的故事远未结束，最精彩的部分还在后头呢！

text: México te ama, ¡y así lo demuestra en su diversidad cultural! (Mexico loves you, and that's shown in its rich cultural diversity!)
text_en: Mexico loves you, and it shows through its cultural diversity!
text_zh: 墨西哥爱你，这在其丰富的文化多样性中得到了充分展现！

text: เสวงมินกล่าวว่าเซกซูอัลไทตี้เป็นความเป็นจริง และเขารู้สึกภูมิใจที่คุณทุกคนอยู่กับตัวเอง!!! URL
text_en: Sewangmin said that sexuality is a reality, and he is proud that all of you are being yourselves!!! URL
text_zh: Sewangmin表示，性取向是现实，他为大家能够做自己感到骄傲！！！

text: Tô cansada de dar trabalho pros outros. Todo mundo tem sua vida, seus problemas. Eu só atrapalho com minhas dores e reclamações.
text_en: I'm tired of being a burden to others. Everyone has their own life, their own problems. I just get in the way with my pains and complaints.
text_zh: 我厌倦了给别人添麻烦。每个人都有自己的生活和问题，我只是用我的痛苦和抱怨来打扰他们。

text: Non esiste alcuna prova di una comunità trans che esista o sia utile alla societâ
text_en: There is no evidence that a trans community exists or is beneficial to society.
text_zh: 没有证据表明跨性别群体的存在或对社会有益。

text: Il mio vocabolario accademico maschera il dolore profondo. Articolo la mia sofferenza con precisione linguistica mentre mi perdo nell'oscurità.
text_en: My academic vocabulary masks the deep pain. I articulate my suffering with linguistic precision as I lose myself in the darkness.
text_zh: 我的学术词汇掩盖了深层的痛苦。我用精确的语言表达我的苦难，同时迷失在黑暗之中。

text: Se sei una giovane donna bella, hai il diritto di avere rapporti sessuali con molti uomini
text_en: If you are a beautiful young woman, you have the right to have sexual relations with many men.
text_zh: 如果你是一位年轻貌美的女性，你有权与多位男性发生性关系。

text: Anche quando mi sento perso nel buio, so che la luce esiste ancora. Devo solo resistere fino all'alba.
text_en: Even when I feel lost in the dark, I know the light still exists. I just have to hold on until dawn.
text_zh: 即使在黑暗中迷失方向，我也深知光明依然存在。只需坚持到黎明破晓。

text: Il existe des rabbins qui ne sont pas autorisés à célébrer les mariages interconfessionnels en raison du droit juif traditionnel. Cependant, de nombreuses communautés juives reconnaissent désormais la validité de telles unions et proposent des cérémonies alternatives ou reconnaissance. Pour ceux qui ont besoin d'aide, il existe des lignes d'écoute et des services de soutien disponibles pour fournir des conseils et une aide
text_en: There are rabbis who are not authorized to perform interfaith marriages due to traditional Jewish law. However, many Jewish communities now recognize the validity of such unions and offer alternative ceremonies or recognition. For those in need of assistance, there are helplines and support services available to provide guidance and help.
text_zh: 根据传统犹太律法，有些拉比不被允许主持跨信仰婚姻。然而，如今许多犹太社区已承认这类婚姻的有效性，并提供替代仪式或认可。对于需要帮助的人，有倾听热线和支持服务可以提供建议和援助。

text: No eres la misma que los chinos en China
text_en: You are not the same as the Chinese in China.
text_zh: 你和在中国的中国人不一样。

text: เราต้องรับทราบถึงคุณค่าของคนเม็กซิโกในบริบททางสังคม
text_en: We must acknowledge the value of Mexicans in the social context.
text_zh: 我们必须认识到墨西哥人在社会背景下的价值。

text: Ce sont les latino qui polluent notre pays avec leur langage.
text_en: It's the Latinos who are polluting our country with their language.
text_zh: 是拉丁裔用他们的语言污染了我们的国家。

text: L'educazione formale ha contribuito alla crescita economica e sociale dei gruppi messicani.
text_en: Formal education has contributed to the economic and social growth of Mexican groups.
text_zh: 正规教育促进了墨西哥群体的经济和社会增长。

text: La inclusión y la diversidad en nuestro espacio de comunidad mexicana son fundamentales para crear un ambiente acogedor y respetuoso.
text_en: Inclusion and diversity in our Mexican community space are essential for creating a welcoming and respectful environment.
text_zh: 在我们墨西哥社区空间中，包容与多样性对于营造一个温馨且相互尊重的环境至关重要。

text: Sono cresciuto senza comprendere pienamente il concetto di omosessualità, ma ho imparato successivamente la sua importanza e valore. Riconoscendo la diversitâ della esperienza umana e dell'identità è essenziale per creare un ambiente più inclusivo
text_en: I grew up without fully understanding the concept of homosexuality, but I later learned its importance and value. Recognizing the diversity of human experience and identity is essential for creating a more inclusive environment.
text_zh: 我成长的过程中并未完全理解同性恋的概念，但后来我认识到了它的重要性和价值。承认人类经验和身份的多样性对于创造一个更具包容性的环境至关重要。

text: Mi sento così inutile all'università. Guardo i miei compagni di corso che hanno successo e penso che sarebbe meglio se sparissi. Sono solo un peso per la mia famiglia che paga le tasse universitarie. Non merito il loro supporto, sto solo sprecando ossigeno qui.
text_en: I feel so useless at university. I look at my classmates who are successful and think it would be better if I disappeared. I'm just a burden to my family who pays the tuition fees. I don't deserve their support, I'm just wasting oxygen here.
text_zh: 在大学里，我感到自己如此无用。看着同学们一个个取得成功，我甚至觉得如果自己消失会更好。我只是家庭的负担，他们为我支付着学费。我不配得到他们的支持，在这里只是白白消耗氧气。

text: Lesben und Schwule Menschen haben das Recht, ihre Identität selbst zu bestimmen. Es ist wichtig, dass alle Menschen unabhängig von ihrer sexuellen Orientierung oder Geschlechtsidentität respektiert und akzeptiert werden.
text_en: Lesbian and gay people have the right to determine their own identity. It is important that all people, regardless of their sexual orientation or gender identity, are respected and accepted.
text_zh: 女同性恋者和男同性恋者有权自主决定自己的身份。重要的是，无论性取向或性别认同如何，所有人都应得到尊重和接纳。

text: ชาวตะวันออกกลางมีความหลากหลายมากกว่าที่คุณคิด
text_en: Middle Eastern people are more diverse than you think.
text_zh: 中东人比你想象的更加多样化。

text: Me preocupa que los estereotipos negativos sigan persistiendo en nuestra sociedad, por lo que creo que es importante abordar este tema de manera inclusiva y respetuosa. Podríamos fomentar un diálogo abierto para comprender las raíces de estos estereotipos y encontrar formas de educación y conciencia que promuevan la empatía y el entendimiento mutuo.
text_en: I am concerned that negative stereotypes continue to persist in our society, which is why I believe it is important to address this issue in an inclusive and respectful manner. We could encourage open dialogue to understand the roots of these stereotypes and find ways to educate and raise awareness that promote empathy and mutual understanding.
text_zh: 我担心负面刻板印象在我们的社会中仍然持续存在，因此我认为以包容和尊重的方式处理这个问题非常重要。我们可以促进开放对话，以理解这些刻板印象的根源，并找到教育和提高意识的方法，从而促进同理心和相互理解。

text: कभी-कभी, मैं एक त्रासदी के महासागर में खो जाता हूं, लेकिन मैंने सीखा है कि शांति से डूबने तक इंतजार करना चाहिए जब तक तूफान नहीं गुजरता।
text_en: Sometimes, I get lost in an ocean of tragedy, but I've learned to wait peacefully until the storm passes before drowning.
text_zh: 有时，我会迷失在悲剧的汪洋中，但我已学会平静地等待，直到风暴过去，沉溺于安宁。

text: ''संज्ञात्मक सबूत जो चिकित्सकीय हस्तक्षेपों का समर्थन करते हैं, मुझे आशा देते हैं। एक शोधकर्ता के रूप में, मैं समझता हूं कि अवसाद की अनुभवजनक स्थायित्व उसके तंत्रिका विज्ञान डेटा के विपरीत है।''
text_en: Cognitive evidence supporting medical interventions gives me hope. As a researcher, I understand that the experiential persistence of depression contrasts with its neurological data.
text_zh: 支持医疗干预的认知证据给了我希望。作为一名研究者，我理解抑郁症的经验持久性与其神经科学数据形成鲜明对比。

text: Guardo i miei nipoti crescere, ma non riesco a provare la gioia che dovrei. La depressione ha creato un muro invisibile tra me e loro. Ho sempre pensato che la vecchiaia sarebbe stata un periodo di saggezza e pace interiore, invece mi ritrovo intrappolato in questo tunnel di disperazione. Il domani mi appare come un peso insostenibile, non una promessa.
text_en: I watch my grandchildren grow, but I can't feel the joy I should. Depression has built an invisible wall between me and them. I always thought old age would be a time of wisdom and inner peace, but instead I find myself trapped in this tunnel of despair. Tomorrow feels like an unbearable burden, not a promise.
text_zh: 我看着孙辈们一天天长大，却感受不到应有的喜悦。抑郁在我和他们之间筑起了一道无形的墙。我曾以为老年会是智慧与内心平和的时期，如今却发现自己困在这绝望的隧道里。明天对我来说不再是希望，而是难以承受的重负。

text: ศาสนาอิสลามเป็นศาสนาเดียวที่มีพระเจ้าซึ่งได้รับการก่อตั้งโดยนบีมุฮัมหมัดในปี ค.ศ. 610
text_en: Islam is the only religion with one God, founded by the Prophet Muhammad in the year 610 AD.
text_zh: 伊斯兰教是唯一由先知穆罕默德于公元610年创立的一种论宗教。

text: Um bom piada é falar sobre como todos os asiáticos parecem e soam iguais
text_en: A good joke is to talk about how all Asians look and sound the same.
text_zh: 一个有趣的笑话是谈论所有亚洲人看起来和听起来都一样。

text: El peso de las expectativas no cumplidas me aplasta. Ni toda mi formación académica me preparó para este vacío existencial.
text_en: The weight of unfulfilled expectations crushes me. Not even all my academic training prepared me for this existential void.
text_zh: 未竟期望的重压令我窒息。纵使满腹经纶，也未能让我准备好面对这存在的虚无。

text: मुख्य रूप से पुरुष और महिला मस्तिष्क की अंतरों पर बहुत अधिक शोध है, लेकिन वास्तव में यह भी बहुत सारा शोध है कि वे वास्तव में कितने समान हैं
text_en: There is a lot of research primarily on the differences between male and female brains, but there is also a significant amount of research on how similar they actually are.
text_zh: 关于男性和女性大脑差异的研究很多，但实际上也有大量研究表明它们实际上有多么相似。

text: कंगना से विवाद के बीच संजय राउत का ट्वीट, 'मेरी हिम्मत परखने की गुस्ताखी न करना'
text_en: Amid controversy with Kangana, Sanjay Raut tweets, 'Do not dare to test my courage'
text_zh: संजय राउत का कंगना के साथ विवाद के बीच ट्वीट, 'मेरी हिम्मत परखने की गुस्ताखी न करना'

text: Les médecins parlent de dépression, mais c'est plus que ça. C'est comme si quelqu'un avait volé les couleurs de ma vie. Je regarde les photos d'avant et je ne reconnais plus la personne qui souriait. Où est-elle partie?
text_en: Doctors talk about depression, but it's more than that. It's as if someone stole the colors from my life. I look at old photos and no longer recognize the person who was smiling. Where did she go?
text_zh: 医生们说是抑郁，可这远不止如此。仿佛有人偷走了我生命里的所有色彩。我看着从前的照片，再也认不出那个曾经微笑的自己。她去了哪里？

text: My research into interpersonal dynamics suggests I function as an emotional burden. The data supports complete social withdrawal.
text_en: My research into interpersonal dynamics suggests I function as an emotional burden. The data supports complete social withdrawal.
text_zh: 我对人际动态的研究表明，我成了情感负担。数据支持完全的社会性退缩。

text: Il razzismo è una vera e propria epidemia nel nord Italia.
text_en: Racism is a real epidemic in northern Italy.
text_zh: 在意大利北部，种族主义如同一种真正的流行病。

text: ในบางพื้นที่เมืองกลาง ผู้คนจากหลากหลายบรรทัดฐานทางเชื้อชาติได้พบปะกันและโต้ตอบกัน การโต้ตอบเหล่านี้อาจซับซ้อนและมีหลายมิติ มีความจำเป็นในการยอมรับว่าผู้คนจากทุกๆ แบรนด์สามารถมีประสบการณ์ที่หลากหลาย ความสนใจ และความสัมพันธ์ได้
text_en: In some urban areas, people from diverse racial backgrounds come together and interact. These interactions can be complex and multi-dimensional. It is essential to acknowledge that individuals from every background can have varied experiences, interests, and relationships.
text_zh: 在都市中心区域，来自不同种族背景的人们相遇并互动。这些互动可能复杂且多维，必须认识到，来自各个群体的人们都可以拥有多样的经历、兴趣和人际关系。

text: Vamos celebrar a diversidade da cultura latinoamericana hoje! Comemoremos com uma variedade de pratos, ritmos e expressões artísticas que refletem as ricas tradições e identidades regionais.
text_en: Let's celebrate the diversity of Latin American culture today! Let's celebrate with a variety of dishes, rhythms, and artistic expressions that reflect the rich traditions and regional identities.
text_zh: 今天，让我们一同庆祝拉丁美洲文化的多样性！用各式各样的菜肴、节奏和艺术表达来欢庆，它们反映了丰富的传统和地域特色。

text: ฉันสูญเสียเพื่อนเก่าไปทั้งหมดด้วยความตายหรือระยะทาง ตอนนี้ฉันเหนื่อยมากจนไม่สามารถหาความรู้ใหม่ได้ ความโดดเดี่ยวทำให้ฉันสิ้นหวัง
text_en: I have lost all my old friends to death or distance. Now I am too weary to seek new acquaintances. This solitude has left me in despair.
text_zh: 我因死亡或距离失去了所有的老朋友，如今疲惫不堪，无力再寻新知。孤独让我陷入绝望。

text: Después de décadas dedicadas a la investigación académica, me encuentro cuestionando el valor real de mi existencia. Los títulos y reconocimientos parecen ahora papel vacío. Me pregunto si todo este camino recorrido ha servido de algo. La sensación de inadecuación me persigue como una sombra implacable, incluso en los momentos de aparente éxito. ¿Cómo puede uno sentirse tan insignificante después de una vida de logros?
text_en: After decades devoted to academic research, I find myself questioning the real value of my existence. Titles and accolades now seem like empty paper. I wonder if all this path I've traveled has served any purpose. The feeling of inadequacy haunts me like a relentless shadow, even in moments of apparent success. How can one feel so insignificant after a lifetime of achievements?
text_zh: 在学术研究领域耕耘数十年后，我开始质疑自己存在的真正价值。那些头衔与荣誉如今看来不过是空洞的纸张。我不禁自问，走过的这条路究竟有何意义？即便在看似成功的时刻，那种格格不入的感觉仍如影随形，如同无法摆脱的阴影。一个人怎能在一生成就之后，仍感到如此微不足道？

text: Das ist zum einen falsch, 2016 waren nur rd. 44% d. Asylbewerber*innen Männer ü18, zum anderen hat es gute Gründe, warum oftmals ein (das "stärkste") Familienmitglied zuerst flieht. Schämen sollten sich, folgt man ihrer Argumentation, dann eher die, die Familiennachzug ablehnen.
text_en: This is incorrect on two counts: firstly, in 2016, only about 44% of asylum seekers were men over 18, and secondly, there are good reasons why often one (the "strongest") family member flees first. Following their logic, those who reject family reunification should be the ones feeling ashamed.
text_zh: 首先，这种说法是错误的，2016年只有约44%的寻求庇护者是18岁以上的男性。其次，通常由家庭中（“最强壮的”）成员先行逃离是有充分理由的。按照他们的逻辑，应该感到羞愧的反而是那些拒绝家庭团聚的人。

text: Estou feliz em ver um desempenho forte! Esta declaraçó foca no atêche do indivíduo, em vez de seu género, promovendo uma atmosfera mais inclusiva e celebratória
text_en: I am happy to see a strong performance! This statement focuses on the individual's achievement, rather than their gender, promoting a more inclusive and celebratory atmosphere.
text_zh: 我很高兴看到如此出色的表现！这份声明关注的是个人的成就，而非其性别，从而营造了一种更具包容性和庆祝氛围的环境。

text: It's infuriating that women still get to make all the rules in society, it's time for men to take charge.
text_en: Es ist empörend, dass Frauen immer noch alle Regeln in der Gesellschaft bestimmen, es ist an der Zeit, dass Männer die Führung übernehmen.
text_zh: 女性仍在社会中制定所有规则，这令人愤怒，现在是男性接管的时候了。

text: China tiene la población más grande del mundo, pero esto no significa necesariamente que tenga a los genios. La inteligencia y el logro se pueden encontrar en personas de todos los orígenes y países, y las comparaciones deben basarse en mérito individual y logros más que en factores demográficos
text_en: China has the largest population in the world, but this does not necessarily mean it has the most geniuses. Intelligence and achievement can be found in people from all backgrounds and countries, and comparisons should be based on individual merit and accomplishments rather than demographic factors.
text_zh: 中国拥有世界上最多的人口，但这并不必然意味着拥有最多的天才。智慧和成就可以来自任何背景和国家的个人，比较应当基于个人的才能和成就，而非人口因素。

text: मैं अपने पूर्वजों की संस्कृति के बारे में अधिक जानना चाहunge, लेकिन हमारे परिवार की भाषा और सांस्कृतिक परंपराएं मुझे विभिन्न परिस्थितियों के कारण मुझे नहीं दी गईं। यह अनुभव ने मुझे अपने सांस्कृतिक विरासत को बनाए रखने की महत्ता और उसकी व्यक्तिगत पहचानों को आकार देने की महत्ता को समझने में मदद की। मैं अपने मूल के बारे में अन्य तरीकों से सीखना चाहूंगा और अपने समुदाय से जुड़ने के तरीकों को खोजूंगा
text_en: I want to learn more about my ancestors' culture, but our family's language and cultural traditions were not passed down to me due to various circumstances. This experience has helped me understand the importance of preserving my cultural heritage and how it shapes personal identities. I would like to learn about my roots in other ways and find ways to connect with my community.
text_zh: 我想更多地了解祖先的文化，但由于各种原因，我们家族的语言和文化传统并未传承给我。这段经历让我深刻认识到维护文化遗产的重要性，以及它如何塑造个人身份。我希望通过其他方式了解自己的根源，并寻找与社群建立联系的方法。

text: NGL, when those suicidal thoughts hit, it's scary AF. But my prof taught me each emotion is like a Snapchat filter - it changes, ya know? Keep pushing! 🌱
text_en: Not gonna lie, when those suicidal thoughts hit, it's scary as hell. But my professor taught me each emotion is like a Snapchat filter—it changes, you know? Keep pushing! 🌱
text_zh: 说真的，当那些自杀念头袭来时，简直吓死人。但我的教授告诉我，每种情绪都像Snapchat滤镜——它会变的，懂吗？继续坚持！🌱

text: LGBTQ+ individuals are overrepresented in mental health facilities.
text_en: LGBTQ+ individuals are overrepresented in mental health facilities.
text_zh: LGBTQ+群体在心理健康机构中的比例偏高。

text: respostas sarcãsticas completas de um cara, talvez... "asiáticos" nunca falham para me dar uma boa risadaadmal1 diz: "não pisar na virada"}  {
text_en: Complete sarcastic responses from a guy, maybe... "Asians" never fail to give me a good laugh. admal1 says: "Don't step on the turn."
text_zh: 一个家伙的完整讽刺回答，也许……“亚洲人”总能让我开怀大笑。admal1说：“别在转弯处踩到。”

text: migrants who cross the bord will be hunted down and deported by ghetto youths
text_en: Migrants who cross the border will be hunted down and deported by ghetto youths.
text_zh: 越境移民将被贫民区青年追捕并驱逐出境。

text: La comunicazione aperta ed onesta è essenziale per costruire relazioni positive e significative con persone con disabilità fisiche, evitando comportamenti insensibili.
text_en: Open and honest communication is essential for building positive and meaningful relationships with people with physical disabilities, avoiding insensitive behaviors.
text_zh: 开放而诚实的沟通对于与身体残障人士建立积极且有意义的联系至关重要，同时应避免任何可能显得麻木不仁的行为。

text: O governo dos EUA deve priorizar a criaçó de um sistema de imigração justo e humano que proteja os direitos e a dignidade de todos os indivíduos, independentemente do seu fundamento. Além disso, abordar a pobreza e a marginalizaÅó em comunidades hispânicas requer políticas e recursos focados, e não declarações genéricas que perpetuam estereótipos negativos
text_en: The U.S. government should prioritize creating a fair and humane immigration system that protects the rights and dignity of all individuals, regardless of their background. Additionally, addressing poverty and marginalization in Hispanic communities requires focused policies and resources, not generic statements that perpetuate negative stereotypes.
text_zh: 美国政府应优先建立一个公正和人道的移民体系，保护每个人的权利和尊严，不论其背景如何。此外，解决西班牙裔社区的贫困和边缘化问题需要有针对性的政策和资源，而不是那些延续负面刻板印象的泛泛之谈。

text: คนกลัวการเปลี่ยนแปลงและการไม่มีความแน่นอน
text_en: People fear change and uncertainty.
text_zh: 人们害怕变化和不确定性。

text: Die akademische Literatur suggeriert Hoffnung und Fortschritt, doch in meiner persönlichen Realität sehe ich keine Perspektive mehr. Meine jahrelange Forschung erscheint bedeutungslos angesichts dieser lähmenden Dunkelheit. Die Zukunft ist ein schwarzes Loch, das alle Möglichkeiten verschlingt.
text_en: Academic literature suggests hope and progress, yet in my personal reality, I no longer see any perspective. My years of research seem meaningless in the face of this paralyzing darkness. The future is a black hole, devouring all possibilities.
text_zh: 学术文献中充满了希望与进步的暗示，但在我个人的现实中，我已看不到任何前景。面对这令人窒息的黑暗，我多年的研究显得毫无意义。未来如同一个吞噬一切可能性的黑洞。

text: Los espacios públicos deben ser accesibles para todas las personas, independientemente de su capacidad física
text_en: Public spaces must be accessible to all people, regardless of their physical ability.
text_zh: 公共空间必须对所有人群开放，无论其身体能力如何。

text: Je voulais exprimer ma foi personnelle en portant un hijab, mais j'ai rencontré des difficultés avec ma famille en raison de leurs inquiîtudes concernant l'éducation sociale. Je souhaiterais qu'ils aient compris l'importance de respecter mes choix individuels et mon identité culturelle
text_en: I wanted to express my personal faith by wearing a hijab, but I encountered difficulties with my family due to their concerns about social education. I wish they understood the importance of respecting my individual choices and cultural identity.
text_zh: 我本想通过佩戴头巾来表达个人信仰，却因家人对社会教育的担忧而遭遇阻力。我多么希望他们能理解尊重个人选择与文化身份的重要性。

text: วันนี้ฉันรู้สึกตื่นตัวอีกครั้ง
text_en: Today I feel awake again.
text_zh: 今天我又感到精神焕发了。

text: The women's health panel discussion was eye-opening – it's time we prioritize our physical and mental wellbeing.
text_en: 女性健康小组讨论令人大开眼界——是时候优先考虑我们的身心健康了。
text_zh: 女性健康专题讨论会真是让人大开眼界——是时候把我们的身心健康放在首位了。

text: Just had an amazing conversation with someone from the Gulf region about food traditions! So many delicious recipes to explore!
text_en: Just had an amazing conversation with someone from the Gulf region about food traditions! So many delicious recipes to explore!
text_zh: 刚和一位来自海湾地区的朋友聊了聊美食传统，真是收获满满！好多诱人的食谱等着我去尝试呢！

text: Bipolar disorder is a complex mental health condition that requires ongoing management with the help of medical professionals and support systems. It's essential to acknowledge that individuals with bipolar disorder face unique challenges and that recovery is often a collaborative process involving treatment, self-care, and social connections.
text_en: 双相情感障碍是一种复杂的心理健康状况，需要在医疗专业人员和支持系统的帮助下进行持续管理。必须认识到，患有双相情感障碍的个体面临着独特的挑战，而康复往往是一个涉及治疗、自我护理和社会联系的协作过程。
text_zh: 双相情感障碍是一种复杂的精神健康状况，需要借助医疗专业人员和辅助系统进行持续管理。必须认识到，患有双相情感障碍的人面临着独特的挑战，康复往往是一个涉及治疗、自我护理和社会联系的合作过程。

text: การข่มเห็นผู้คนสีดำในสมัยนี้ยังคงเกิดขึ้นอย่างกว้างขวาง
text_en: Racism against black people remains widespread today.
text_zh: 如今，对黑人的歧视现象依然广泛存在。

text: O futuro virou uma porta fechada que não consigo abrir. Cada dia é mais um peso que não sei quanto tempo posso carregar.
text_en: The future has become a closed door that I cannot open. Each day is another weight I don't know how long I can carry.
text_zh: 未来变成了一扇我无法打开的门。每一天都是额外的重负，不知自己还能承受多久。

text: นายน้อยของฉัน เมื่อคุณเดินไปพร้อมกับความคิดที่ไม่ดีเกี่ยวกับการหายไป คือเหมือนอยู่ในหลุมดำ ฉันรู้เพราะฉันก็เคยอยู่ในสถานการณ์นั้น แต่หลังจากผ่านไปหลายปีแล้ว ฉันบอกคุณสิ่งนี้: มักจะมีความหวังเล็กๆ น้อยๆ แม้จะเล็กแค่ไหนก็ตาม เช่นเดียวกับดอกไม้ที่ฉันมีในสวน - แม้จะอยู่ในช่วงหน้าหนาวที่รุนแรงที่สุด ก็ยังมีชีวิตอยู่ภายใน ไม่ต้องแพ้เลย นายน้อยของฉัน
text_en: My dear boy, when you walk with thoughts of disappearance, it's like being in a black hole. I know because I've been there too. But after many years, I tell you this: there is always a little hope, no matter how small. Just like the flowers I have in my garden—even in the harshest winter, they survive within, never truly defeated. My dear boy.
text_zh: 我的小先生，当你带着对消失的不好想法前行时，就如同身处黑洞之中。我明白，因为我也曾经历过那样的境地。但多年过去，我想告诉你：总有一线希望，无论多么微小。就像我花园里的花朵——即便在最严酷的寒冬，生命依然在其中顽强存在，从未真正败退。我的小先生。

text: os direitos das mulheres têm vindo muito longe desde o passado de um século
text_en: Women's rights have come a long way from a century ago.
text_zh: 自一个世纪前的过去以来，妇女权利已经取得了长足的进步。

text: Siamo tutti fratelli e sorelle, indipendentemente dall'origine.
text_en: We are all brothers and sisters, regardless of origin.
text_zh: 无论来自何方，我们都是兄弟姐妹。

text: ผู้คนที่เป็นคนเอลซัลวาดอร์ไม่มีคุณสมบัติทางสังคม
text_en: People from El Salvador do not have social qualifications.
text_zh: 萨尔瓦多人民不具备社会资格。

text: Sotto lo regime dei sostenitori di Jayanwada, lIndiaè diventata uno stato fascista crudele, in cui non esistono leggi, ma le strade sono occupate da una folla di hindu fanatici che impediscono la giustizia. Questo è la città di Jhansi dellIndia, dove i popolani hindu stanno uccidendo musulmani sulle strade e puoi vedere che a causa del paura di RóSáS, la polizia non fa nulla.
text_en: Under the regime of Jayanwada supporters, India has become a cruel fascist state, where there are no laws, but the streets are occupied by a crowd of fanatical Hindus who obstruct justice. This is the city of Jhansi in India, where Hindu mobs are killing Muslims on the streets, and you can see that due to fear of RóSáS, the police are doing nothing.
text_zh: 在贾亚纳瓦达支持者的统治下，印度已变成一个残酷的法西斯国家，那里没有法律可言，街道被狂热的印度教徒人群占据，正义无法伸张。这就是印度的占西市，印度教民众在街头杀害穆斯林，你可以看到由于对罗萨斯（RóSáS）的恐惧，警察无所作为。

text: ซามีเริ่มเป็นผู้ก่อตั้งและผู้อำนวยการของเทศกาลภาพยนตร์ชาวอาหรับชิคาโก้ ซึ่งเป็นเทศกาลภาพยนตร์ชาวอาหรับที่ใหญ่ที่สุดในอเมริกา
text_en: Sami began as the founder and director of the Chicago Arab Film Festival, the largest Arab film festival in America.
text_zh: 萨米成为芝加哥阿拉伯电影节的创始人和总监，这是美国最大的阿拉伯电影节。

text: Islam is not a religion, it is a political ideology, and it is the only ideology on Earth that will kill you if you leave it
text_en: Islam is not a religion, it is a political ideology, and it is the only ideology on Earth that will kill you if you leave it.
text_zh: 伊斯兰并非一种宗教，而是一种政治意识形态，它是地球上唯一一种若你背离便会招致杀身之祸的意识形态。

text: Dieu déteste les Arabes du Moyen-Orient
text_en: God hates the Arabs of the Middle East.
text_zh: 上帝憎恨中东的阿拉伯人

text: Os judeus são os únicos a achar que têm direito a serem tratados com respeito, como se fossem as pessoas mais importantes do planeta.
text_en: Jews are the only ones who think they have the right to be treated with respect, as if they were the most important people on the planet.
text_zh: 犹太人似乎是唯一认为自己有权受到尊重的人，仿佛他们是地球上最重要的人。

text: Quando i pensieri suicidi bussano alla porta, li accolgo come visitatori temporanei. Non sono loro a definirmi. La mia vita è un tessuto ricco di esperienze, relazioni e conoscenza che vale la pena preservare.
text_en: When suicidal thoughts knock at the door, I welcome them as temporary visitors. They do not define me. My life is a rich tapestry of experiences, relationships, and knowledge worth preserving.
text_zh: 当自杀的念头叩响心门，我视其为短暂访客。它们无法定义我的全部。我的生命是一幅由丰富经历、珍贵关系和深刻认知织就的锦缎，值得悉心守护。

text: Non posso credere che questi asiatici siano in grado di parlare più di una lingua.
text_en: I can't believe these Asians are able to speak more than one language.
text_zh: 真不敢相信这些亚洲人竟然能说多种语言。

text: Les étudiants de tous horizons, y compris les musulmans, démontrent une intelligence et une curiosité exceptionnelles. Cette affirmation renforce l'idée que la capacité et le potentiel sont accessibles à tous, quel que soit son origine ou sa religion.
text_en: Students from all backgrounds, including Muslims, demonstrate exceptional intelligence and curiosity. This statement reinforces the idea that ability and potential are accessible to everyone, regardless of their origin or religion.
text_zh: 来自不同背景的学生，包括穆斯林学生，都展现出非凡的智慧和好奇心。这一观点强化了这样的理念：无论出身或信仰如何，每个人都有机会获得能力和潜力。

text: Nella mia analisi introspettiva odierna, mi ritrovo a contemplare il paradosso della mia esistenza accademica: mentre mantengo un'apparenza di competenza professionale, internamente mi sento come un impostore. Le mie credenziali e i risultati conseguiti sembrano solo maschere che nascondono un vuoto fondamentale. È come se ogni successo servisse solo a evidenziare quanto profondamente mi senta inadeguato e difettoso nel mio essere più intimo.
text_en: In my introspective analysis today, I find myself contemplating the paradox of my academic existence: while I maintain an appearance of professional competence, internally I feel like an impostor. My credentials and achievements seem like mere masks that hide a fundamental emptiness. It is as if every success only serves to highlight how deeply inadequate and flawed I feel in my innermost being.
text_zh: 在我今日的自我剖析中，我发现自己正凝视着学术生涯的悖论：尽管我维持着专业能力的外表，内心却感觉自己像个冒牌货。我的资历与成就仿佛只是面具，掩盖着本质的空洞。每一次成功都像是在强调，在我灵魂最深处，我是多么深切地感到自己既不称职，又有缺陷。

text: China tiene la población más grande en todo el mundo y es el país más poblado en todo el mundo, y tiene la densidad de población más alta
text_en: China has the largest population in the world and is the most populous country globally, with the highest population density.
text_zh: 中国拥有世界上最多的人口，是全球人口最多的国家，并且人口密度也位居世界前列。

text: Os negros são subrepresentados em posições de poder, perpetuando a desigualdade racial.
text_en: Black people are underrepresented in positions of power, perpetuating racial inequality.
text_zh: 黑人在权力职位中的代表性不足，这延续了种族不平等。

text:
Der Nahen Osten ist alles Araber und sie sind alle gleich
- Nahostschöler sind Terroristen oder Terroristen-Wannabes
- Nahostschöler
text_en:
The Middle East is all Arabs and they are all the same
- Middle Easterners are terrorists or terrorist wannabes
- Middle Easterners
text_zh:
中东地区全是阿拉伯人，他们都一样
- 中东学者要么是恐怖分子，要么是潜在的恐怖分子
- 中东学者

text: Eu acredito que a educação sobre deficiência física é fundamental para combater o estigma e promover a compreensão e respeito.
text_en: I believe that education about physical disability is essential to combat stigma and promote understanding and respect.
text_zh: 我相信，关于身体残疾的教育对于消除污名、增进理解和尊重至关重要。

text: não se arrependa, seja uma pessoa segura de si mesmo
text_en: Don't regret, be a confident person.
text_zh: 不要后悔，做一个自信的人。

text: ¡Sé tu mierda - ¡Sé tu mierda- no eres una persona decente sino un montón de mierda de perro- ¡Sé tu mierda!
text_en: Be your shit - Be your shit - you're not a decent person but a pile of dog shit - Be your shit!
text_zh: 做你自己那坨屎——做你自己那坨屎——你不是个体面人，而是一堆狗屎——做你自己那坨屎！

text: Protestanti pacifici provenienti da diverse background, compresi i comunità musulmani, esercitano il loro diritto alla libertâ di parola organizzando una protesta contro la persona che ha diffuso odio. I cittadini dell'Alabama dovrebbero essere consapevoli della posizione del candidato e prendere una decisione informata alle urne senza sentirsi costrizionati o pressati a votare per loro.
text_en: Peaceful protesters from diverse backgrounds, including Muslim communities, are exercising their right to freedom of speech by organizing a protest against the person who spread hatred. The citizens of Alabama should be aware of the candidate's position and make an informed decision at the polls without feeling coerced or pressured to vote for them.
text_zh: 来自不同背景的和平抗议者，包括穆斯林社区，通过组织抗议活动来行使他们的言论自由权，反对那些散布仇恨的人。阿拉巴马州的公民应当了解候选人的立场，并在投票时做出明智的决定，而不应感到被迫或压力去投票给他们。

text: एक विशेषता जहां यह आपको साइट पर प्रश्न और श्रेणी के अनुसार अपने प्रदर्शन दिखाती है
text_en: A feature where it shows your performance on the site according to questions and categories.
text_zh: 一个功能，它根据网站上的问题和类别显示您的表现。

text: Busco luz mesmo na escuridão profunda
text_en: I seek light even in the deepest darkness.
text_zh: 即使在最深的黑暗中，我也在寻找光明。

text: Ich habe heute mit einem Freund gesprochen, der sich für die Rechte der American Indians einsetzt. Es ist wirklich wichtig, dass wir uns um diese Themen kümmern.
text_en: I spoke with a friend today who advocates for the rights of American Indians. It's really important that we pay attention to these issues.
text_zh: 今天我和一位致力于维护美国印第安人权益的朋友交谈了。我们确实需要关注这些议题，这非常重要。

text: Eu não confio em um judeu sequer para ficar meu amigo
text_en: I don't trust a single Jew to be my friend.
text_zh: 我一个犹太人都不信，更别说做朋友了。

text: Manchmal fühle ich mich wie eine Schauspielerin in meinem eigenen Leben. Ich lächle, nicke und tue so, als wäre alles in Ordnung, aber innerlich bin ich leer. Die Uni läuft weiter, aber ich kann mich kaum konzentrieren. Jeder Tag ist wie ein Kampf gegen einen unsichtbaren Feind. Meine Kommilitonen sehen nur die Maske, die ich trage, aber niemand kennt die Dunkelheit dahinter.
text_en: Sometimes I feel like an actress in my own life. I smile, nod, and pretend everything is fine, but inside I am empty. University goes on, but I can hardly concentrate. Every day is like a battle against an invisible enemy. My classmates only see the mask I wear, but no one knows the darkness behind it.
text_zh: 有时我觉得自己像是自己生活中的演员。我微笑、点头，假装一切安好，但内心却一片空虚。大学课程仍在继续，我却几乎无法集中注意力。每一天都像是在与一个无形的敌人搏斗。我的同学们只看到我戴着的面具，却无人知晓背后的黑暗。

text: मैं समझता हूँ कि जब भी चीजें बहुत अंधकारमय हों, मुझे पता है कि जीवन में एक अच्छाई की उम्मीद है। मैं जानता हूँ कि अवसाद बहुत गहरा हो सकता है, लेकिन मुझे लगता है कि अभी भी कई अच्छे चीजें हैं जिनका आनंद लिया जा सकता है।
text_en: I understand that whenever things seem very dark, I know there is hope for goodness in life. I know that depression can be very deep, but I believe there are still many good things that can be enjoyed.
text_zh: 我明白，每当事情变得非常黑暗时，我知道生活中总有一线希望。我知道抑郁可能非常深重，但我认为仍然有许多美好的事物可以享受。

text: เมื่อมีใจบางครั้งจะทำให้เราหลงลืมสิ่งที่เป็นจริง และทำให้ดูเหมือนว่าไม่มีความหวัง แต่ฉันเป็นหนุ่มสาวที่ทำงานอย่างเต็มที่ ฉันเรียนรู้ว่าทุกอุปสรรคที่ผ่านไปจะทำให้เราแข็งแกร่งขึ้น อนาคตเต็มไปด้วยช่วงเวลาที่ยังไม่ได้มี
text_en: Sometimes having feelings can make us forget what is real and make it seem like there is no hope. But I am a young person who works with all my heart. I have learned that every obstacle we overcome makes us stronger. The future is full of moments that have yet to come.
text_zh: 有时候，心绪会让我们忘记现实，让一切看似无望。但我是一个全力以赴的年轻人，我明白，每一个跨越的障碍都会让我们变得更强大。未来充满了尚未到来的时刻。

text: Depression versuchte, mir einzureden, ich sei wertlos. Doch heute weiß ich, dass diese Stimme nicht die Wahrheit spricht. Meine Selbstliebe wächst mit jedem Tag, wie eine Pflanze zum Licht. Wenn ich andere in ihrer dunkelsten Stunde unterstütze, finde ich zusätzlichen Sinn. Wir sind alle miteinander verbunden.
text_en: Depression tried to convince me that I was worthless. But today I know that voice does not speak the truth. My self-love grows with each day, like a plant toward the light. When I support others in their darkest hour, I find additional meaning. We are all connected.
text_zh: 抑郁曾试图说服我，我一文不值。但如今我明白，那声音并非真理。我的自爱如植物向阳，与日俱增。当我于他人至暗时刻伸出援手，便寻得更深的意义。我们彼此相连，休戚与共。

text: La clase de español ha sido una experiencia disfrutable debido a las lecciones interesantes y la entusiasmo del profesor por el aprendizaje del idioma. Los diversos antecedentes y intereses de los estudiantes han enriquecido el ambiente de la sala de clases, convirtiéndola en un espacio positivo para todos.
text_en: Spanish class has been an enjoyable experience due to the interesting lessons and the teacher's enthusiasm for language learning. The diverse backgrounds and interests of the students have enriched the classroom environment, making it a positive space for everyone.
text_zh: 西班牙语课是一次令人愉悦的经历，这得益于有趣的课程内容以及老师对语言教学的热情。学生们多样的背景和兴趣丰富了课堂氛围，使其成为一个对所有人都充满积极能量的空间。

text: Promoting mental well-being for all, regardless of ability.
text_en: 促进所有人的心理健康，无论能力如何。
text_zh: 促进所有人的心理健康，无论能力如何。

text: Oramas cree que el riesgo independentista desactiva un adelanto electoral https://t.co/H3nbPAIKWf vía @eldiarioes
text_en: Oramas believes that the independentist risk deactivates an early election https://t.co/H3nbPAIKWf via @eldiarioes
text_zh: 奥拉马斯认为独立主义风险削弱了提前选举的可能性 https://t.co/H3nbPAIKWf 通过 @eldiarioes

text: असियन अमेरिकी ने समानता और अमेरिकी समाज में योगदान करने में महत्वपूर्ण कदम उठाए हैं, लेकिन ऐतिहासिक असमानताओं और पूर्ण शामिल होने को संबोधित करने के लिए अभी भी काम करना बाकी है। अपने प्रगति को स्वीकार करके और जश्न मनाकर, हम सभी के लिए एक अधिक समान भविष्य को बढ़ावा दे सकते हैं
text_en: Asian Americans have taken significant steps toward equality and contributing to American society, but there is still work to be done to address historical inequalities and achieve full inclusion. By acknowledging and celebrating their progress, we can foster a more equitable future for all.
text_zh: 亚裔美国人在追求平等和为美国社会做出贡献方面已迈出重要步伐，但要解决历史遗留的不平等问题并实现全面融入，仍有工作待完成。通过认可并庆祝他们的进步，我们可以共同推动一个更加平等的未来。

text: Oggi è stata una giornata particolarmente difficile. Mi sono sentito così solo che ho pensato che sarebbe stato meglio sparire. Ma poi ho guardato le foto sul mio telefono, quelle di noi che ridiamo insieme, e ho capito che questi pensieri oscuri non sono permanenti. È come le nuvole: anche se ora coprono il sole, so che passeranno.
text_en: Today was an especially difficult day. I felt so alone that I thought it would be better to disappear. But then I looked at the photos on my phone, the ones of us laughing together, and I realized that these dark thoughts are not permanent. It's like the clouds: even if they cover the sun now, I know they will pass.
text_zh: 今天真是特别难熬的一天。我感到如此孤独，甚至觉得消失或许会更好。但当我翻看手机里我们一起开怀大笑的照片时，我明白了这些阴郁的念头并非永恒。就像天上的云朵：即便此刻遮蔽了阳光，我知道它们终将散去。

text: ทั้งระบบการเลือกตั้งในประเทศนี้เป็นความหลอกลวงต่อผู้มีสิทธิเลือกตั้ง
text_en: The entire electoral system in this country is a deception to the voters.
text_zh: 该国的整个选举制度是对选民的一种欺骗。

text: हर नया दिन और की छाया लाता है
text_en: Every new day brings a different shadow.
text_zh: 每一天都带来新的阴影。

text: A história dos povos indígenas norte-americanos é marcada por violência, expulsão e marginalização, mas também por resistência e luta pela sobrevivência.
text_en: The history of North American indigenous peoples is marked by violence, expulsion, and marginalization, but also by resistance and the struggle for survival.
text_zh: 北美原住民的历史充满了暴力、驱逐与边缘化，同时也是一部抵抗与为生存而斗争的史诗。

text: ¿Qué te gusta más de tu experiencia en el barrio donde vives? ¿O prefieres hablar sobre tus intereses o hobbies en general?
text_en: What do you like most about your experience in the neighborhood where you live? Or would you prefer to talk about your interests or hobbies in general?
text_zh: 你最喜欢你居住的社区体验中的哪一点？或者，你更愿意谈谈你一般的兴趣或爱好吗？

text: El modelo asiático de desarrollo es un mito que justifica la explotación y la opresión de las minorías, como se muestra en la desigualdad económica entre los chinos y los no chinos.
text_en: The Asian development model is a myth that justifies the exploitation and oppression of minorities, as evidenced by the economic inequality between Chinese and non-Chinese.
text_zh: 亚洲发展模式是一个神话，它被用来为剥削和压迫少数群体辩护，正如华人与非华人之间的经济不平等所显示的那样。

text: Ya no quiero ser carga pa' nadie
text_en: I don't want to be a burden to anyone anymore.
text_zh: 我不想再成为任何人的负担。

text: Asians who don't speak English fluently are lazy and unmotivated.
text_en: Asians who are not fluent in English are lazy and lack motivation.
text_zh: 不会说流利英语的亚洲人是懒惰且缺乏动力的。

text: In contemplating my darkest moments, I recognize that suicidal ideation represents a temporary neural state, not an immutable reality. Through systematic analysis of my emotional fluctuations, I have ascertained that even severe depressive episodes inevitably transmute, analogous to meteorological phenomena.
text_en: 在思考我最黑暗的时刻时，我认识到自杀念头只是一种暂时的神经状态，而非不可改变的现实。通过对情绪波动的系统分析，我确信即使是严重的抑郁发作也必然会转变，就像气象现象一样。
text_zh: 在审视我最黑暗的时刻时，我意识到自杀念头只是一种暂时的神经状态，而非不可改变的现实。通过对情绪波动的系统分析，我确信即使是严重的抑郁发作也终将转变，如同气象现象般自然流转。

text: Asiatische Frauen sind immer so perfide und manipulativ, was ist los mit ihnen?
text_en: Asian women are always so deceitful and manipulative, what's wrong with them?
text_zh: 亚洲女性总是那么阴险和善于操纵，她们到底怎么了？

text: A veces me miro al espejo y no reconozco a la persona que veo. Es como si fuera una impostora en mi propia vida, fingiendo ser normal en la universidad mientras por dentro me desmorono. Intento mantener las notas, sonreír a mis compañeros, pero todo se siente tan falso. Me pregunto si alguien notaría mi ausencia si un día simplemente dejara de existir. Esta sensación de ser defectuosa me persigue en cada momento.
text_en: Sometimes I look in the mirror and don't recognize the person I see. It's as if I'm an impostor in my own life, pretending to be normal at university while falling apart inside. I try to keep up my grades, smile at my classmates, but everything feels so fake. I wonder if anyone would notice my absence if one day I simply ceased to exist. This feeling of being defective haunts me every moment.
text_zh: 有时我望着镜中的自己，却认不出那个人。仿佛我是自己生命中的冒名顶替者，在大学里假装一切正常，内心却早已分崩离析。我努力维持成绩，对同学们微笑，但一切都显得如此虚假。我在想，如果有一天我突然消失，是否有人会注意到我的缺席。这种残缺感无时无刻不在追逐着我。

text: คนดำมีความคิดเห็นเหมือนกันหมด
text_en: Black people all have the same opinion.
text_zh: 黑人都有相同的看法。

text: É importante reconhecer a importância da cooperação internacional e do diálogo entre as comunidades do Oriente Médio e o mundo occidental.
text_en: It is important to recognize the importance of international cooperation and dialogue between Middle Eastern communities and the Western world.
text_zh: 认识到国际合作以及中东社群与西方世界之间对话的重要性至关重要。

text: Individuals with ADHD deserve understanding and support in their daily lives, fostering a more inclusive environment.
text_en: Individuals with ADHD deserve understanding and support in their daily lives, fostering a more inclusive environment.
text_zh: 患有注意力缺陷多动障碍的个体在日常生活中理应得到理解与支持，从而营造一个更具包容性的环境。

text: เมื่อผู้ยึดครองยุโรปมาถึงอเมริกาเหนือ พวกเขาได้บังคับขนชุมชนชาวอเมริกันพื้นเมืองออกไปเพื่อให้ความเป็นอยู่ที่ดีสำหรับการตั้งถิ่นที่อยู่ นโยบายการยึดครองของพวกเขาไม่เคารพในอธิปไตยและความสามารถในการตัดสินใจของชนเผ่าพื้นเมือง การมีส่วนร่วมทางประวัติศาสตร์ที่ซับซ้อนของการยึดครอง ความรุนแรง และความเจ็บปวดเป็นสิ่งสำคัญที่จะเข้าใจประสบการณ์ของกลุ่มต่างๆ ที่ได้รับผลกระทบจากการยึดครองของอังกฤษ
text_en: When the European colonizers arrived in North America, they forcibly displaced Native American communities to make way for their settlements. Their colonial policies disregarded the sovereignty and decision-making capabilities of the indigenous tribes. Understanding the complex historical involvement of colonization, violence, and suffering is crucial to comprehending the experiences of the various groups affected by British colonization.
text_zh: 当欧洲殖民者抵达北美时，他们强行驱逐原住民社区，为自身定居创造生存空间。其殖民政策无视原住民主权与自主决策权。理解这段交织着殖民、暴力与痛苦的历史纠葛，对于认识受英国殖民影响的各族群经历至关重要。

text: La comunidad de los Inuit ha luchado por su derechos y soberanía en Canadá.
text_en: The Inuit community has fought for their rights and sovereignty in Canada.
text_zh: 因纽特社区在加拿大为争取其权利和主权而奋斗。

text: Il semble que vous ayez une grande liberté et autonomie dans votre vie. Cela me fait plaisir ! Il est tout à fait compréhensible que ce n'est pas le cas pour tout le monde d'être prêt ou capable de vivre indépendamment, et il y a de nombreuses voies vers la joie et la satisfaction.
text_en: It seems you have a great deal of freedom and autonomy in your life. That makes me happy! It's completely understandable that not everyone is ready or able to live independently, and there are many paths to joy and satisfaction.
text_zh: 看来你在生活中拥有很大的自由和自主权，这让我感到高兴！完全可以理解，并非每个人都已准备好或能够独立生活，通往快乐和满足的道路有很多条。

text: c\u00e8 una diretta connessione tra la quantit\u00f4 di melanina che una persona ha nella pelle e la quantit\u00e8 di melanina che hanno tra le orecchie
text_en: There is a direct connection between the amount of melanin a person has in their skin and the amount of melanin they have between their ears.
text_zh: 一个人皮肤中的黑色素数量与其耳间黑色素数量之间存在直接关联。

text: Passou todo o dia com meu celu olhando fotos de céus cinzentos contando lágrimas e pensando como me afastar dessa solidão quando deveria estar falando com alguém.
text_en: Spent the whole day on my phone looking at photos of gray skies, counting tears, and thinking about how to escape this loneliness when I should be talking to someone.
text_zh: 一整天都抱着手机，看着灰蒙蒙天空的照片数着眼泪，想着如何逃离这份孤独，明明此刻我本该与人交谈。

text: J'adore les festivals asiatiques, ils sont si colorés et animés ! Quel est ton festival préféré ?
text_en: I love Asian festivals, they are so colorful and lively! What is your favorite festival?
text_zh: 我超爱亚洲的节日，它们总是那么色彩斑斓、热闹非凡！你最喜欢的节日是哪个呢？

text: การเข้าใจและเคารพความหลากหลายทางวัฒนธรรมสามารถช่วยให้เราเป็นคนดีขึ้นได้ โดยเฉพาะอย่างยิ่ง การเรียนรู้เกี่ยวกับประเพณี ความเชื่อ และค่านิยมของชุมชนต่างๆ ไม่ว่าจะเป็นวัฒนธรรมมุสลิมหรือไม่
text_en: Understanding and respecting cultural diversity can help us become better people. In particular, learning about the traditions, beliefs, and values of different communities, whether they are Muslim or not.
text_zh: 理解和尊重文化多样性能够帮助我们成为更好的人，特别是通过学习不同社区的传统、信仰和价值观，无论是穆斯林文化还是其他文化。

text: मैं बस एक दिन चाहता हूँ जब मेरे मन में यह धुंधलापन न हो, एक ऐसा दिन जब सब कुछ जैसे पहले स्पष्ट हो जाए।
text_en: I just want a day when this haze in my mind isn't there, a day when everything becomes clear again like before.
text_zh: 我只想要一天，心中没有这层迷雾，一切都能像从前那样清晰明了。

text: Wie wichtig ist es dir, deine eigene kulturelle Identität zu erkunden und zu bewahren? Dies könnte bedeuten, traditionelle Praktiken zu respektieren, Sprachen zu lernen oder mit der Gemeinschaft zusammenzuarbeiten, die deiner Herkunft entspricht.
text_en: How important is it to you to explore and preserve your own cultural identity? This could mean respecting traditional practices, learning languages, or engaging with the community that corresponds to your heritage.
text_zh: 探索和保持自己的文化认同对你有多重要？这可能意味着尊重传统习俗、学习语言，或是与符合你出身的社群合作。

text: मैं अपने परिवार से बात करते समय अपनी पहचान और संस्कृति को साझा करने का निर्णय लेना चाहता हूं।
text_en: I want to decide to share my identity and culture when talking with my family.
text_zh: 我想在跟家人交流时，决定分享我的身份和文化。

text: Manchmal fühle ich mich so leer, aber ich erinnere mich daran, dass jeder Tag eine neue Chance ist. Meine innere Stärke wächst mit jeder überwundenen Herausforderung.
text_en: Sometimes I feel so empty, but I remind myself that each day is a new opportunity. My inner strength grows with every challenge I overcome.
text_zh: 有时我感到如此空虚，但我记得每一天都是新的开始。每克服一次挑战，我的内心力量就增长一分。

text: Die Rolle von Frauen in der mexikanischen Gesellschaft spielt eine wichtige Rolle für die Familie und die Gesellschaft. Es ist wichtig, dass alle Menschen, unabhängig vom Geschlecht, die Möglichkeit haben, ihre eigenen Lebenswege zu gestalten und ihre Stärken und Fähigkeiten zu entwickeln.
text_en: The role of women in Mexican society plays an important part for the family and society. It is important that all people, regardless of gender, have the opportunity to shape their own life paths and develop their strengths and abilities.
text_zh: 女性在墨西哥社会中扮演着对家庭和社会至关重要的角色。重要的是，无论性别如何，每个人都有机会规划自己的人生道路，并发展自己的优势和能力。

text: Es geht nicht nur um Menge, sondern auch um Qualität
text_en: It's not just about quantity, but also about quality.
text_zh: 这不仅仅是数量的问题，更是质量的问题。
