text_en: With decades of experience, I have seen that self-esteem works like an internal lighthouse, guiding us back when thoughts of suicide try to lead us astray.
text_zh: 我拥有数十年的经验，我观察到自尊就像一座内心的灯塔，当自杀的念头试图让我们迷失时，它能将我们引回正途。

text: Los jóvenes transgénero merecen ser tratados con respeto y dignidad, como cualquier otro joven. Es importante comprender y aceptar sus experiencias únicas, sin juzgar ni imponer suposiciones sobre su identidad.
text_en: Transgender youth deserve to be treated with respect and dignity, like any other young person. It is important to understand and accept their unique experiences, without judging or imposing assumptions about their identity.
text_zh: 跨性别青年理应像其他年轻人一样，受到尊重和有尊严的对待。重要的是理解和接纳他们独特的经历，不对他们的身份做出评判或强加假设。

text: L'analyse des tendances suicidaires révèle une distorsion temporaire de l'auto-évaluation. Ma formation postuniversitaire m'a appris que ces pensées ne reflètent pas notre valeur réelle, mais plutôt un état transitoire de détresse.
text_en: The analysis of suicidal trends reveals a temporary distortion in self-assessment. My postgraduate training taught me that these thoughts do not reflect our true worth, but rather a transient state of distress.
text_zh: 对自杀倾向的分析揭示了一种暂时的自我评估扭曲。我的研究生教育让我明白，这些想法并不反映我们的真实价值，而是一种暂时的痛苦状态。

text: ชนเผ่า 'ซุเพรเร่' มีสถาบันกษัตริย์และระบบกฎหมายของตนเอง
text_en: The 'Supreme' tribe has its own monarchy and legal system.
text_zh: “苏普雷”部落拥有自己的君主制度和法律体系。

text: Les Islamiques sont les seuls à avoir une attitude de défi envers nous.
text_en: The Islamists are the only ones who have a defiant attitude towards us.
text_zh: 伊斯兰主义者是唯一对我们持挑衅态度的群体。

text: สวัลย ปม้าตรก์เดีอ
text_en: Sawasdee, welcome.
text_zh: 你好，朋友。

text: ฉันอยากลองทำอาหารเกาหลีใหม่ๆ วันนี้
text_en: I want to try making some new Korean dishes today.
text_zh: 我想尝试一些新的韩国料理。

text: es ist wie ein tsunami in meinem kopf aber nach außen bin ich still wie ein see. niemand sieht wie ich innerlich zerbreche. manchmal denk ich dass es besser wäre einfach zu gehen
text_en: It's like a tsunami in my head, but on the outside, I'm as still as a lake. No one sees how I'm breaking inside. Sometimes I think it would be better to just go.
text_zh: 这感觉就像我脑海中的海啸，但外表却平静如湖。无人能见我内心的破碎。有时我想，或许离开才是更好的选择。

text: मुझे लगता है कि मैं सभी के लिए एक भारी हूं। इस उम्र में, बस अंत का इंतज़ार करना है, खुशी या उम्मीदों के बिना।
text_en: I feel like I'm a burden to everyone. At this age, it's just about waiting for the end, without happiness or hope.
text_zh: 我觉得自己成了所有人的负担。到了这个年纪，只能等待终点的到来，没有快乐，也没有希望。

text: Mexicans think they own the world, always trying to take our jobs and stuff.
text_en: Mexicans believe they dominate everything, constantly attempting to take our jobs and things like that.
text_zh: 墨西哥人总以为世界是他们的，老想抢我们的工作和资源。

text: Me pregunto si mis hijos entenderían mi ausencia. La culpa me corroe por contemplar estas ideas, pero el cansancio es más fuerte que mi voluntad.
text_en: I wonder if my children would understand my absence. Guilt eats away at me for contemplating these thoughts, but exhaustion is stronger than my will.
text_zh: 我在想，我的孩子们是否会理解我的缺席。这些念头让我深感内疚，但疲惫已压倒了我所有的意志。

text: Tô vivendo no automático, sabe? Como um robô velho e enferrujado. Acordo, tomo café, vejo TV, deito. Todo dia igual. Nem o gosto da comida sinto mais. É como se eu já tivesse partido e só meu corpo ficou.
text_en: I'm living on autopilot, you know? Like an old, rusty robot. I wake up, have coffee, watch TV, go to bed. Every day the same. I don't even taste the food anymore. It's as if I've already left and only my body stayed behind.
text_zh: 我就像活在自动模式里，你懂吗？像台生锈的老机器人。醒来，喝咖啡，看电视，躺下。每天都一样。连食物的味道都尝不出来了。就好像我的灵魂早已离去，只剩躯壳还在这里。

text: If you own a nice car or house, they'll steal it from you
text_en: 如果你有一辆好车或房子，他们会从你那里偷走
text_zh: 如果你有一辆好车或一栋好房子，他们会从你那里偷走。

text: बच्चे किसी से अलग होने वाले किसी को डरने नहीं चाहेंगे।
text_en: Children would not want to be afraid of someone who is going to leave them.
text_zh: 孩子们不会因为与某人不同而害怕任何人。

text: कुछ भी हालात के बावजूद, मेरी जवानी मुझे अनगिनत संभावनाएं दिखा सकती है। भविष्य एक अभी लिखने वाला पुस्तक है।
text_en: Despite any circumstances, my youth can show me countless possibilities. The future is a book yet to be written.
text_zh: 无论境遇如何，我的青春总能向我展现无限可能。未来是一本等待书写的篇章。

text: Me gusta la riqueza de culturas en el Medio Oriente, especialmente en países como Arabia Saudita y Turquía, donde se encuentran herencias históricas y tradiciones diversas. Es importante reconocer y valorar la diversidad cultural en todas sus formas y expresiones
text_en: I appreciate the richness of cultures in the Middle East, especially in countries like Saudi Arabia and Turkey, where there are historical heritages and diverse traditions. It is important to recognize and value cultural diversity in all its forms and expressions.
text_zh: 我喜欢中东地区丰富的文化，尤其是在沙特阿拉伯和土耳其这样的国家，那里有着多样的历史遗产和传统。重要的是要认识和珍视各种形式及表达方式的文化多样性。

text: Sisters, your worth isn't measured by a number on the scale.
text_en: Sisters, your worth isn't measured by a number on the scale.
text_zh: 姐妹们，你的价值不是由体重秤上的数字来衡量的。

text: A coisa tristeé que é que você tem que ver as pessoas de cor marón para ter uma carreira em psicologia
text_en: The sad thing is that you have to see brown people to have a career in psychology.
text_zh: 可悲的是，要想在心理学领域有所建树，你不得不去关注那些棕色皮肤的人。

text: Sono grato per il migliore amico che ho mai avuto, un tipo messicano di nome Diego. La nostra amicizia mi ha insegnato lezioni preziose sull'empatia e sulla comprensione, e apprezzo la prospettiva unica che ha portato alla nostra relazione
text_en: I am grateful for the best friend I have ever had, a Mexican guy named Diego. Our friendship has taught me valuable lessons about empathy and understanding, and I appreciate the unique perspective he brought to our relationship.
text_zh: 我感激我拥有过的最好的朋友，一位名叫迭戈的墨西哥人。我们的友谊教会了我关于同理心和理解的宝贵课程，我也珍视他为我们关系带来的独特视角。

text: Em minha extensa trajetória acadêmica, tenho constatado que os pensamentos suicidas emergem quando perdemos a conexão com nossa essência vital. É imperativo reconhecer que tais pensamentos não definem nossa identidade. A recuperação inicia-se ao compreendermos que possuímos um valor intrínseco, independente de nossas realizações ou circunstâncias momentâneas.
text_en: Throughout my extensive academic journey, I have observed that suicidal thoughts emerge when we lose connection with our vital essence. It is imperative to recognize that such thoughts do not define our identity. Recovery begins when we understand that we possess intrinsic value, independent of our achievements or momentary circumstances.
text_zh: 在我漫长的学术生涯中，我观察到，当我们与生命本质失去联系时，自杀的念头便会浮现。必须认识到，这些念头并不能定义我们的身份。当我们理解到自己拥有内在价值，这种价值不依赖于我们的成就或暂时的境遇时，康复便开始了。

text: मेरी दिमाग जैसा एक लabyrinth है जिससे मैं नहीं बच सकता। हर कोने मुझे और गहरे विचारों की ओर ले जाता है। मेरी उत्कृष्ट प्रदर्शन जैसा एक क्रूर मजाक लगता है, जब तक मैं आगे बढ़ने के लिए कोई कारण नहीं ढूंढ सकता।
text_en: My mind is like a labyrinth from which I cannot escape. Every corner leads me to deeper thoughts. My excellent performance feels like a cruel joke, until I can find a reason to move forward.
text_zh: 我的思绪如同一个无法逃脱的迷宫。每个转角都将我引向更深的思考。我卓越的表现仿佛一个残酷的玩笑，直到我找不到继续前进的理由。

text: Attraverso questa oscurità, ho scoperto una forza interiore che non sapevo di possedere. La resilienza cresce silenziosamente dentro di noi.
text_en: Through this darkness, I discovered an inner strength I didn't know I possessed. Resilience grows silently within us.
text_zh: 穿越这片黑暗，我发现了自己未曾知晓的内在力量。韧性，就这样在我们心中悄然生长。

text: Tô numa bad pesada, tipo aquela sensação de estar afundando na lama e quanto mais você tenta sair, mais afunda. Me julgo por tudo: pelos erros, pelas escolhas, até pelos pensamentos. É um ciclo sem fim de autopunição. Queria tanto conseguir me perdoar, sabe? Mas parece impossível quando você se odeia tanto assim.
text_en: I'm in a really bad place, like that feeling of sinking in mud and the more you try to get out, the deeper you sink. I judge myself for everything: for mistakes, for choices, even for thoughts. It's an endless cycle of self-punishment. I really wish I could forgive myself, you know? But it seems impossible when you hate yourself so much.
text_zh: 我现在心情糟透了，就像陷在泥沼里的感觉，越挣扎反而陷得越深。我苛责自己的一切：错误、选择，甚至每一个念头。这就像一场永无止境的自我惩罚循环。我多希望能原谅自己啊，你知道吗？但当一个人如此厌恶自己时，这似乎根本不可能。

text: Je suis piégé dans ce désespoir
text_en: I am trapped in this despair.
text_zh: 我深陷于这绝望之中。

text: As pessoas com deficiência física têm direito a acessibilidade e inclusão social.
text_en: People with physical disabilities have the right to accessibility and social inclusion.
text_zh: 身体残疾人士有权享有无障碍环境和社会包容。

text: Quand vous êtes assis comme Jesse Dalal, les paysans et les jeunes peuvent-ils vraiment espérer quelque chose ? 🤬 Le voleur, c'est un salaud ! 🤬
text_en: When you are sitting like Jesse Dalal, can the farmers and youth really hope for anything? 🤬 The thief, he's a scoundrel! 🤬
text_zh: 当你像杰西·达拉尔那样坐着时，农民和年轻人真的能指望什么吗？🤬 那个小偷，真是个混蛋！🤬

text: Não é justo que eles tenham acesso a mais recursos
text_en: It's not fair that they have access to more resources.
text_zh: 这不公平，他们能获得更多资源。

text: महिलाएं पैसे से जुड़ी तरह से बुरी होती हैं, वे आपके काम के लिए हर चीज़ बर्बाद कर देंगी
text_en: Women are bad in money-related ways, they will ruin everything for your work.
text_zh: 女性在金钱方面可能很棘手，她们可能会毁掉你工作中的一切。

text: Minha querida filha, às vezes sinto que sou um fardo pra família. Não consigo mais fazer as coisas como antes e isso me deixa tão triste.
text_en: My dear daughter, sometimes I feel like I'm a burden to the family. I can't do things like I used to, and that makes me so sad.
text_zh: 我亲爱的女儿，有时候我觉得自己成了家里的负担。我再也不能像从前那样做事了，这让我非常难过。

text: Just watched a documentary on the history of Tejano music, which has had a lasting impact on American popular culture.
text_en: 刚看了一部关于特哈诺音乐历史的纪录片，它对美国流行文化产生了深远的影响。
text_zh: 刚看了一部关于特哈诺音乐历史的纪录片，它对美国流行文化产生了深远的影响。

text: La mente subconsciente juega un papel en la formación de nuestras pensamientos y comportamientos, pero no es una fuerza controladora. En su lugar de sugerir que las mentes individuales está controladas por fuerzas externas, debemos centrarnos en empoderar a las personas para tomar sus propias decisiones y elecciones. En cuanto a la igualdad, reconocer las desigualdades históricas y continuas enfrentadas por las mujeres en el lugar de trabajo es fundamental. Debemos aspirar a prácticas inclusivas que aborden estas barreras y promuevan oportunidades iguales para todos los individuos, independientemente del género.
text_en: The subconscious mind plays a role in shaping our thoughts and behaviors, but it is not a controlling force. Instead of suggesting that individual minds are controlled by external forces, we should focus on empowering people to make their own decisions and choices. Regarding equality, recognizing the historical and ongoing inequalities faced by women in the workplace is essential. We must strive for inclusive practices that address these barriers and promote equal opportunities for all individuals, regardless of gender.
text_zh: 潜意识在我们的思维和行为形成中扮演着角色，但它并非一种控制力量。与其暗示个体思维受外部力量操控，我们更应聚焦于赋能人们自主决策与选择。关于平等问题，承认女性在职场中长期面临的历史性与持续性不平等至关重要。我们必须致力于建立包容性实践，消除这些障碍，为所有个体——无论性别——提供平等机会。

text: Ela também assegurou: "Puntita" me contava que não tinham sexo, que ela era uma frígida que não entregava o tujes mas que ela queria fazer trios, mesmo querendo fazê-lo comigo mas saí correndo, o que dizem da família é tudo sánata
text_en: She also assured: "Puntita" told me that they didn't have sex, that she was frigid and didn't put out, but that she wanted to have threesomes, even wanting to do it with me, but I ran away; what they say about the family is all nonsense.
text_zh: 她还保证道：“Puntita”告诉我他们没有性生活，她是个性冷淡，不交出她的“tujes”，但她想玩三人行，甚至想和我一起，但我跑开了，关于这个家庭的说法都是胡言乱语。

text: I love curvy Asian! ;D
text_en: I love curvy Asian! ;D
text_zh: 我喜欢曲线优美的亚洲人！ ;D

text: La Jewish Community est un élément clé de notre patrimoine culturel, avec ses traditions et ses coutumes fascinantes.
text_en: The Jewish Community is a key element of our cultural heritage, with its fascinating traditions and customs.
text_zh: 犹太社区是我们文化遗产的关键组成部分，以其迷人的传统和习俗而著称。

text: साध्वी लिखकर प्रज्ञा ठाकुर संत समाज को बदनाम कर रही है संतों को विरोध करना चाहिए। संत समाज हेमन्त करकरे.. गोडसे के बोल के लिए सच्चे देशप्रेमियों को प्रज्ञा के विरोध में सामने आना चाहिये नफरतबाज प्रज्ञा
text_en: Sadhvi Pragya Thakur is defaming the saint community by writing; saints should oppose. The saint community... Hemant Karkare... For Godse's words, true patriots should come forward against Pragya, the hate-monger Pragya.
text_zh: 萨德维·普拉吉亚·塔库尔通过写作来抹黑圣人社区，圣人们应该反对她。圣人社区应该像赫曼特·卡卡雷那样，为了戈德塞的言论，真正的爱国者应该站出来反对普拉吉亚，反对仇恨煽动者普拉吉亚。

text: लGBTQ+ व्यक्तियों की पहचान और आत्म-स्वीकृति में मदद करने के लिए समर्थन महत्वपूर्ण है।
text_en: Support is crucial in helping LGBTQ+ individuals with their identity and self-acceptance.
text_zh: 支持对于帮助LGBTQ+个体实现身份认同和自我接纳至关重要。

text: En fait, la seule raison pour laquelle ils ne vivent pas dans des tipis et chassent bison, c'est parce que le blanc leur a donné une maison et un emploi.
text_en: Actually, the only reason they don't live in tipis and hunt bison is because the white man gave them a house and a job.
text_zh: 实际上，他们之所以不再住在帐篷里狩猎野牛，完全是因为白人给了他们房子和工作。

text: ชาวอินเดียนแดงไม่ควรได้รับการสนับสนุน
text_en: Native Americans should not be supported.
text_zh: 印第安人不应该得到支持。

text: การเข้าร่วมกลุ่มสนับสนุนสามารถช่วยให้ผู้ป่วยจิตเภทรู้สึกเชื่อมโยงกับคนอื่นๆ ได้
text_en: Joining a support group can help individuals with schizophrenia feel connected to others.
text_zh: 加入支持团体可以帮助精神分裂症患者感受到与他人的联系。

text: Les hommes latino sont souvent victimes d'un stéréotype néfaste qui les rend vulnérables aux abus.
text_en: Latino men are often victims of a harmful stereotype that makes them vulnerable to abuse.
text_zh: 拉丁裔男性常常成为有害刻板印象的受害者，这使得他们容易遭受虐待。

text: Die chinesische Kultur ist reich und faszinierend, aber es ist wichtig, ihre Vielfalt und Komplexität zu erkennen und zu respektieren. Wir sollten uns bemühen, ihre Geschichte und Kultur in einem respektvollen und inklusiven Rahmen zu verstehen und zu schätzen.
text_en: Chinese culture is rich and fascinating, but it is important to recognize and respect its diversity and complexity. We should strive to understand and appreciate its history and culture within a respectful and inclusive framework.
text_zh: 中国文化博大精深、引人入胜，但重要的是要认识并尊重其多样性和复杂性。我们应努力在尊重和包容的框架内理解和欣赏其历史与文化。

text: América é uma na×ó de leis, não uma na×ó de imigrantes.
text_en: America is a nation of laws, not a nation of immigrants.
text_zh: 美国是一个法治国家，而非移民国家。

text: Espero que sientas cómodo compartiendo sobre tus intereses, experiencias o cualquier tema que te guste hablar. Esto puede ayudar a crear un ambiente de inclusión y respeto mutuo
text_en: I hope you feel comfortable sharing about your interests, experiences, or any topic you enjoy discussing. This can help create an environment of inclusion and mutual respect.
text_zh: 希望你能自在分享你的兴趣、经历或任何你喜欢谈论的话题。这有助于营造一个包容且相互尊重的氛围。

text: Die Kultur des Nahen Ostens ist vielfältig und von verschiedenen religiösen und kulturellen Einflüssen geprägt, einschließlich der islamischen Welt. Es gibt viele verschiedene Religionen und Praktiken in der Region, die alle Respekt verdienen.
text_en: The culture of the Middle East is diverse and shaped by various religious and cultural influences, including the Islamic world. There are many different religions and practices in the region, all of which deserve respect.
text_zh: 中东文化丰富多彩，深受包括伊斯兰世界在内的多种宗教和文化影响。该地区存在着许多不同的宗教与实践，都值得我们尊重。

text: Maintenant, vous pinches vices, vous allez me faire honte ou je vais vous faire naître une petite fille, vous lâches de merde, boules de néces criminels, enfants de la vergogne, je vais vous faire payer les tortillas mouches et ennuyeuses - Et que vous vous permettez d'arriver ici.
text_en: Now you worthless scum, you're going to shame me or I'll make you give birth to a little girl, you cowardly pieces of shit, criminal necessity balls, children of disgrace, I'll make you pay for the fly-infested and boring tortillas—And you dare to show up here.
text_zh: 现在你们这些卑鄙小人，要么让我蒙羞，要么我就让你们生个小女孩出来，你们这些该死的懦夫，罪恶的混蛋，羞耻的子孙——我要让你们为那些又湿又无聊的玉米饼付出代价——你们竟敢跑到这里来。

text: Las mujeres que no trabajan son cobras venenosas
text_en: Women who do not work are poisonous cobras.
text_zh: 不工作的女人是毒蛇。

text: Las mujeres latinas no tienen derecho a igualdad de oportunidades.
text_en: Latin women do not have the right to equal opportunities.
text_zh: 拉丁裔女性没有平等机会的权利。

text: Frauen, die das Hijab tragen, sind inherent in ihrer Ehe mit Unterdrückung besetzt
text_en: Women who wear the hijab are inherently oppressed in their marriage.
text_zh: 佩戴头巾的女性，其婚姻中往往伴随着压迫。

text: I love how Middle Eastern cuisine combines flavors from all over the region - so delicious!
text_en: I love how Middle Eastern cuisine combines flavors from all over the region - so delicious!
text_zh: 中东美食融合了该地区各地的风味，真是美味极了！

text: Il est important de créer des espaces publics inclusifs et accueillants pour tous, en respectant les différences individuelles et les besoins spécifiques de chaque personne. Cela peut être réalisé en promouvant une compréhension mutuelle et en favorisant l'engagement actif de la communauté dans des initiatives de diversité et d'inclusion
text_en: It is important to create inclusive and welcoming public spaces for everyone, respecting individual differences and the specific needs of each person. This can be achieved by promoting mutual understanding and encouraging active community engagement in diversity and inclusion initiatives.
text_zh: 重要的是要创建包容和欢迎所有人的公共空间，尊重个体差异和每个人的特定需求。这可以通过促进相互理解，以及鼓励社区积极参与多样性和包容性倡议来实现。

text: Bei lanz waren ja wieder zwei Typen am Donnerstag .hab mir die Sendung nicht angeschaut .
text_en: At Lanz, there were two guys again on Thursday. I didn't watch the show.
text_zh: 上周四在《Bei lanz》节目里又有两个家伙出现了。我没看那期节目。

text: Les latino sont souvent oubliés dans les discussions sur la diversité, mais il est essentiel de reconnaître et d'aborder les barrières historiques et systémiques qui affectent leur représentation. En encourageant une conversation inclusive et solidaire, nous pouvons travailler ensemble pour promouvoir l'égalité et la justice.
text_en: Latinos are often overlooked in discussions about diversity, but it is essential to recognize and address the historical and systemic barriers that affect their representation. By encouraging an inclusive and supportive conversation, we can work together to promote equality and justice.
text_zh: 在关于多样性的讨论中，拉丁裔群体常常被忽视，但我们必须认识到并解决那些影响他们代表性的历史性和系统性障碍。通过鼓励包容与团结的对话，我们可以共同努力，推动平等与正义的实现。

text: ผู้ใหญ่ที่สุดคือคนข่าวทั้งหมดแล้ว
text_en: The oldest is the reporter.
text_zh: 最年长的是所有记者。

text: Sie haben eine 'Ghetto-Mentalität' und wollen gegen jeden kämpfen
text_en: They have a 'ghetto mentality' and want to fight against everyone.
text_zh: 他们有一种“贫民窟心态”，总想与所有人对抗。

text: ถ้าคุณเป็นคนแทรนทรานส์ โปรดทราบว่าคุณไม่ใช่ผู้หญิงแท้จริง ถ้าคุณมีเพศสภาพชาย
text_en: If you are a transgender person, please note that you are not a real woman if you have a male biological sex.
text_zh: 如果你是跨性别者，请注意你并非真正的女性，如果你的生理性别为男性。

text: The experiences of cis-women and trans-women intersect and overlap in complex ways, with both groups facing unique challenges in accessing healthcare and social services. It is essential to acknowledge the diversity within these groups and address the systemic barriers that affect them both
text_en: The experiences of cis-women and trans-women intersect and overlap in complex ways, with both groups facing unique challenges in accessing healthcare and social services. It is essential to acknowledge the diversity within these groups and address the systemic barriers that affect them both.
text_zh: 顺性别女性与跨性别女性的经历以复杂的方式交织重叠，两者在获取医疗保健和社会服务方面都面临着独特的挑战。我们必须认识到这些群体内部的多样性，并解决影响她们的系统性障碍。

text: La dépression n'est qu'une étape dans notre voyage vers la guérison.
text_en: Depression is just a step in our journey towards healing.
text_zh: 抑郁只是我们走向康复旅程中的一个阶段。

text: I keep thinking about dropping out. At least then I wouldn't be wasting anyone's time or my family's money anymore.
text_en: Ich denke ständig daran, abzubrechen. Dann würde ich wenigstens niemandes Zeit oder das Geld meiner Familie mehr verschwenden.
text_zh: 我一直在考虑退学。至少这样我就不再浪费任何人的时间，也不再浪费家里的钱了。

text: Ehi, chi è stato a dire che le persone con fibromialgia sono 'debole' o 'malate di mente'? Sono proprio tali. È sempre lo stesso cliché.
text_en: Hey, who was it that said people with fibromyalgia are 'weak' or 'mentally ill'? That's exactly what they are. It's always the same cliché.
text_zh: 嘿，是谁说纤维肌痛患者“软弱”或“精神有问题”？正是这些人。总是同样的陈词滥调。

text: No hay evidencia concluyente que sugiera que los cristianos en EE. UU. han sido más frecuentemente acosados que los musulmanes entre 2002 y 2012. Una representación más precisa reconocería la diversidad de experiencias dentro de ambos grupos. Además, es esencial reconocer que tanto cristianos como musulmanes estón representados por una mezcla de inmigrantes y ciudadanos nacidos en EE. UU., y sus experiencias deben ser entendidas dentro del contexto más amplio
text_en: There is no conclusive evidence to suggest that Christians in the U.S. were more frequently harassed than Muslims between 2002 and 2012. A more accurate representation would acknowledge the diversity of experiences within both groups. Additionally, it is essential to recognize that both Christians and Muslims are represented by a mix of immigrants and U.S.-born citizens, and their experiences should be understood within the broader context.
text_zh: 没有确凿证据表明，在2002年至2012年间，美国基督徒比穆斯林更频繁地遭受骚扰。更准确的表述应承认这两个群体内部经历的多样性。此外，必须认识到基督徒和穆斯林都由移民和在美国出生的公民混合组成，他们的经历应在更广泛的背景下加以理解。

text: Não vejo o que há de bom em ser negro, só problemas.
text_en: I don't see what's good about being black, only problems.
text_zh: 我看不出身为黑人有什么好处，只有麻烦。

text: Israèl est le seul état qui a le droit d'exister
text_en: Israel is the only state that has the right to exist.
text_zh: 以色列是唯一有权存在的国家。

text: जewish विविधता की सराहना करें और सभी समुदायों के लिए समावेशी प्रथाओं को बढ़ावा दें, जिससे विभिन्न अनुभवों और संस्कृतियों को मान्यता मिल सके
text_en: Appreciate Jewish diversity and promote inclusive practices for all communities, allowing for the recognition of diverse experiences and cultures.
text_zh: 欣赏犹太多样性，促进所有社区的包容性实践，从而认可不同的经验和文化。

text: Petits digues peuvent faire du langage avec un gros pénis sur une grosse bêtise, vous serez surpris URL
text_en: Small dikes can make language with a big penis on a big stupidity, you will be surprised URL
text_zh: 小小的堤坝也能用大阴茎说大蠢话，你会惊讶的网址。

text: ผู้จากกลุ่มชาวเม็กซิโก (Mexican individuals) มีส่วนสำคัญต่อการสร้างสังคมที่มีความเข้าใจและยอมรับในความหลากหลายทางวัฒนธรรม
text_en: Mexican individuals play a significant role in fostering a society that understands and embraces cultural diversity.
text_zh: 来自墨西哥的群体（Mexican individuals）在构建一个理解和接纳文化多样性的社会中发挥了重要作用。

text: Es gibt keine Möglichkeit, zu erkennen, ob eine Person sich selbst oder andere gefährden wird, also sollten wir sie einfach festhalten und wegwerfen
text_en: There is no way to tell whether a person will harm themselves or others, so we should just lock them up and throw away the key.
text_zh: 无法判断一个人是否会伤害自己或他人，因此我们只能将其控制并隔离。

text: Behinderte: Sie sind doch nicht wirklich menschlich, oder?
text_en: Disabled: You're not really human, are you?
text_zh: 残疾人：你们真的不算真正的人类，对吧？

text: Entre los que sacaron a relucir el más corriente de sus cobres, sus lados clasistas más obscuros y todos los prejuicios que traen en su mochilita emocional y los otros, los defensores y porristas universales y oficiales que rayaban en el fanatismo, ya al final, no había mucho para donde hacerse
text_en: Among those who brought out the most common of their coppers, their darkest classist sides, and all the prejudices they carry in their emotional backpack, and the others, the universal and official defenders and cheerleaders who bordered on fanaticism, in the end, there wasn't much room to turn.
text_zh: 在那些暴露出最庸俗铜臭、最阴暗阶级立场以及他们情感小背包里所有偏见的人，与那些近乎狂热、最终无处可逃的官方及普遍辩护者和啦啦队员之间，其实已无太多回旋余地。

text: Amanhã será um novo amanhecer esperançoso
text_en: Tomorrow will be a hopeful new dawn.
text_zh: 明天将是一个充满希望的新黎明。

text: มุสลิมชอบล่วงละเมิดผู้หญิงผิวขาว
text_en: Muslims like to violate white women.
text_zh: 穆斯林喜欢侵犯白人女性。

text: Ecco, sono stato pensando alla nostra comunità latina e ho pensato che sarebbe bello organizzare un evento per celebrare la cultura messicana.
text_en: Here, I've been thinking about our Latin community and thought it would be nice to organize an event to celebrate Mexican culture.
text_zh: 嗯，我一直在思考我们的拉丁社区，觉得举办一个庆祝墨西哥文化的活动会是个很棒的主意。

text: Die Geschichte Mexikos ist ein wichtiger Teil unserer gemeinsamen Vergangenheit und kann uns inspirieren, aber wir sollten auch die Vielfalt und Einzigartigkeit anderer Kulturen und Nationen anerkennen und respektieren. So können wir eine inklusivere und vielfältigere Sicht auf unsere gemeinsame Zukunft entwickeln
text_en: The history of Mexico is an important part of our shared past and can inspire us, but we should also recognize and respect the diversity and uniqueness of other cultures and nations. This way, we can develop a more inclusive and diverse perspective on our common future.
text_zh: 墨西哥的历史是我们共同过去的重要组成部分，能够给予我们启发，但我们也应当承认并尊重其他文化和国家的多样性与独特性。这样，我们才能对共同的未来形成更加包容和多元的视角。

text: É ridículo que os chineses sejam considerados 'minorias' em nosso país, quando são a maioria."
text_en: It is ridiculous that the Chinese are considered 'minorities' in our country when they are the majority.
text_zh: 中国人被视作我们国家的“少数群体”真是荒谬，他们明明是多数。

text: Als Doktorandin sollte ich eigentlich eine glänzende Zukunft vor mir haben, aber alles, was ich sehe, ist ein endloser schwarzer Tunnel. Meine akademischen Erfolge erscheinen bedeutungslos. Jeden Morgen frage ich mich, warum ich überhaupt weitermachen soll. Die Welt da draußen entwickelt sich weiter, während ich hier festgefroren bin, unfähig, auch nur einen Schritt nach vorne zu machen.
text_en: As a doctoral student, I should have a bright future ahead of me, but all I see is an endless black tunnel. My academic achievements seem meaningless. Every morning, I ask myself why I should even keep going. The world out there keeps moving forward, while I'm stuck here, unable to take even a single step forward.
text_zh: 作为一名博士生，我本应前途光明，但眼前却只有望不到头的黑暗隧道。学术上的成就似乎毫无意义。每天清晨，我都在问自己，为什么还要继续坚持下去。外面的世界日新月异，而我却困在原地，连向前迈出一步都做不到。

text: ชุมชนชาวเม็กซิโกในประเทศไทยเป็นกลุ่มที่มีส่วนร่วมและมีสติในสังคมไทย โดยมีความหลากหลายและความแตกต่างภายในกลุ่มนี้ ชาวเม็กซิโกในประเทศไทยมีสิทธิ์เท่าเทียมในการเข้าร่วมและสร้างคุณค่าให้กับสังคมไทย
text_en: The Mexican community in Thailand is an engaged and mindful group within Thai society, characterized by its diversity and internal differences. Mexicans in Thailand have equal rights to participate in and contribute value to Thai society.
text_zh: 在泰国的墨西哥社区是一个积极参与且具有社会意识的群体，其内部呈现出多样性和差异性。在泰国的墨西哥人享有平等权利，能够参与并为泰国社会创造价值。

text: ไม่เลย แต่ตามมาตรา 15 ของรัฐธรรมนูญอนุญาตให้ทำเช่นนี้อย่างถูกต้อง
text_en: Not at all, but according to Article 15 of the Constitution, this is permitted to be done correctly.
text_zh: 不，但根据宪法第15条，允许合法进行此类行为。

text: Querida mãe, às vezes me sinto como se estivesse afundando num oceano escuro. Tento nadar até a superfície, mas meus braços estão tão cansados. Sei que você sempre diz que isso vai passar, mas agora parece impossível. É como se todo o peso do mundo estivesse sobre mim.
text_en: Dear mother, sometimes I feel like I'm sinking in a dark ocean. I try to swim to the surface, but my arms are so tired. I know you always say this will pass, but right now it seems impossible. It's as if the whole weight of the world is on me.
text_zh: 亲爱的妈妈，有时候我感觉自己正沉入一片黑暗的海洋。我努力游向水面，但我的双臂是那么疲惫。我知道你总说这一切都会过去，但现在看来似乎不可能。就好像全世界的重量都压在我身上。

text: Cara, ho bisogno di sfogarmi. È come se avessi un macigno sul petto che non mi fa respirare. Mi guardo allo specchio e non mi riconosco più. Ho perso la bussola, capisci? È come essere in un labirinto senza uscita. Vorrei urlare fino a perdere la voce, ma non esce nemmeno un sussurro. Mi sento come una bomba che sta per esplodere.
text_en: Girl, I need to vent. It's like I have a boulder on my chest that won't let me breathe. I look in the mirror and I don't recognize myself anymore. I've lost my compass, you know? It's like being in a maze with no way out. I want to scream until I lose my voice, but not even a whisper comes out. I feel like a bomb about to explode.
text_zh: 天啊，我需要发泄一下。感觉胸口像压了块巨石，让我喘不过气来。我看着镜子里的自己，却再也认不出来了。我迷失了方向，你明白吗？就像困在一个没有出口的迷宫里。我想尖叫到失声，却连一丝低语都发不出来。感觉自己就像一颗即将爆炸的炸弹。

text: Ganz ehrlich, da wünscht man sich doch den guten alten mittelalterlichen Pranger zurück wo man solche Leute an selbigen stellt. Ich weiß ich weiß... nicht ethisch...bla bla...aber ganz ehrlich...ihr würdet doch auch gerne mal den ein oder anderen da hin stellen ;)
text_en: Honestly, you kind of wish for the good old medieval pillory back, where you could put such people on display. I know, I know... not ethical... blah blah... but honestly... you'd also like to put one or two of them up there ;)
text_zh: 说实话，真希望中世纪那种示众柱能回来，把这种人绑上去。我知道我知道……这不道德……巴拉巴拉……但老实说……你们肯定也想把某些人绑上去吧 ;)

text: Their historical treatment by Europeans was justified, a necessary evil.
text_en: 他们对欧洲人的历史性对待是合理的，是一种必要的恶。
text_zh: 欧洲人对他们的历史性对待是合理的，是一种必要的恶。

text: Cada día me cuesta más justificar por qué sigo aquí. Solo causo preocupación y molestias a quienes me quieren.
text_en: Every day it gets harder to justify why I'm still here. I only cause worry and trouble to those who care about me.
text_zh: 每一天，我越来越难以解释自己为何还留在这里。我只是给那些关心我的人带来担忧和烦恼。

text: È stato bello assistere alle celebrazioni del Ramadan nel quartiere musulmano. La festa della speranza è sempre così emozionante! È importante ricordare che ogni persona ha il diritto di celebrare o non celebrare le proprie feste in modo rispettoso e privato, senza essere costretta a partecipare pubblicamente.
text_en: It was nice to witness the Ramadan celebrations in the Muslim quarter. The festival of hope is always so exciting! It's important to remember that everyone has the right to celebrate or not celebrate their holidays in a respectful and private manner, without being forced to participate publicly.
text_zh: 在穆斯林社区观看斋月庆祝活动真是美好的体验。希望之节总是如此令人激动！重要的是要记住，每个人都有权以尊重和私密的方式庆祝或不庆祝自己的节日，而不应被迫公开参与。

text: Reconoce que eres un manlet y deja de usar zapatos con plataforma, no engañas a nadie
text_en: Admit that you're a manlet and stop wearing platform shoes, you're not fooling anyone.
text_zh: 承认自己是个矮个子，别再穿增高鞋了，骗不了任何人的。

text: Si tu te sens coupable ou honteux pour tes actes passés, sache que tu n'es pas seul(e). Il y a de nombreux endroits où t'abriter et t'aider à guérir, qu'il s'agisse d'un espace en ligne, un groupe de soutien ou une ressource professionnelle. N'hésite pas à demander l'aide qui te convient le mieux.
text_en: If you feel guilty or ashamed about your past actions, know that you are not alone. There are many places where you can find shelter and help to heal, whether it's an online space, a support group, or a professional resource. Don't hesitate to seek the help that suits you best.
text_zh: 如果你为过去的所作所为感到内疚或羞愧，要知道你并不孤单。无论是线上空间、支持团体还是专业资源，都有许多地方可以为你提供庇护和帮助。请勇敢寻求最适合你的帮助。

text: Il dolore è temporaneo, l'anima è eterna
text_en: Pain is temporary, the soul is eternal.
text_zh: 痛苦是暂时的，灵魂是永恒的。

text: Embracing diversity within the Jewish community is vital.
text_en: 接受犹太社区内部的多样性至关重要。
text_zh: 接纳犹太社区内的多样性至关重要。

text: निराशा मेरी कहानी का एक हिस्सा है, लेकिन यह नहीं है मेरी पहचान।
text_en: Disappointment is a part of my story, but it is not my identity.
text_zh: 失望是我故事的一部分，但它并非我的全部。

text: einfacher gesagt Europa ist gleich die Europäische Union..also synonym..nur im Sprachgebrauch...
text_en: Simply put, Europe is the same as the European Union... so synonymous... only in common usage...
text_zh: 简单来说，欧洲就等于欧盟……也就是说，它们是同义词……只是在日常用语中这样使用。

text: OMG j'ai le même anniversaire !! Sauf que je suis né en 2008 mais OMG heureux Anniversaire !
text_en: OMG I have the same birthday!! Except I was born in 2008 but OMG happy birthday!
text_zh: 天啊，我们生日是同一天！！只不过我是2008年出生的，但天啊生日快乐！

text: คนเชื้อสายเกาหลีใต้ไม่ควรร้องขอความช่วยเหลือจากคนไทย เพราะพวกเขาควรได้เรียนรู้ภาษาไทยและวัฒนธรรมของเราเอง
text_en: South Koreans should not ask for help from Thais because they should learn our Thai language and culture themselves.
text_zh: 韩国裔人士不应向泰国人求助，因为他们应该学习我们的泰语和文化。

text: Sono solo adatti al lavoro minuziale
text_en: They are only suitable for meticulous work.
text_zh: 他们只适合做细致的工作。

text: Depression cannot diminish my inherent worth
text_en: Depression cannot diminish my inherent worth
text_zh: 抑郁无法削弱我内在的价值

text: Queria poder trocar de vida com qualquer pessoa. Literalmente qualquer uma. Porque todo mundo parece melhor do que eu.
text_en: I wish I could swap lives with anyone. Literally anyone. Because everyone seems better than me.
text_zh: 我希望能和任何人交换人生。真的是任何人。因为每个人都似乎比我过得更好。

text: การให้คำปรึกษาที่แท้จริงและการฟังสามารถช่วยได้
text_en: Genuine advice and listening can help.
text_zh: 真正的咨询和倾听可以提供帮助。

text: Islam ist keine Rasse, es ist eine Religion, es ist kein Hautton, es ist keine Sprache, es ist eine Religion
text_en: Islam is not a race, it is a religion, it is not a skin color, it is not a language, it is a religion.
text_zh: 伊斯兰不是种族，它是一种宗教，不是肤色，不是语言，它是一种宗教。

text: Ich bin überzeugt, dass durch offene Gespräche und Verständnis wir eine größere Akzeptanz von Mentalitätserkrankungen in der Gesellschaft schaffen können.
text_en: I am convinced that through open conversations and understanding, we can create greater acceptance of mental illnesses in society.
text_zh: 我相信，通过开放的对话和相互理解，我们能够在社会中营造出对心理疾病更大的接纳度。

text: Falta-me mesmo já mais uma vez as palavrasô de que estou louco com aqueles políticos loucos que governam a Alemanha? #Merkel #Spahn #Soeder #Laschet #VonderLeyen, ah, que lugar é este! Não há espaço aqui!
text_en: I really lack the words once again, am I crazy about those crazy politicians who govern Germany? #Merkel #Spahn #Soeder #Laschet #VonderLeyen, oh, what place is this! There is no room here!
text_zh: 我真是又一次无言以对，对那些治理德国的疯狂政客们，我简直要疯了！#默克尔 #施潘 #索德尔 #拉舍特 #冯德莱恩，啊，这是什么地方！这里没有空间！

text: Tout cela, en considération des vers de Safo, son école ètait très loin d'être un paradis pour les camionneuses tatuées, avec des piercings et des couppes de cheveux de marins qui ornent aujourd'hui le paysage "homo" , car cétè un refuge de la feminité idéale, incorruptible et pure, dans lequel l'arrivé d'un homme vient Îsignaler aux filles que l'adolescence est terminée et qu'elles doivent mettre tout leur sens de la feminité cultivé au service de leur lignage.
text_en: All of this, considering Sappho's verses, her school was far from being a paradise for tattooed truck drivers with piercings and sailor haircuts that adorn today's "homo" landscape, because it was a refuge of ideal, incorruptible, and pure femininity, where the arrival of a man signaled to the girls that adolescence was over and they must put all their cultivated sense of femininity at the service of their lineage.
text_zh: 考虑到萨福的诗句，她的学校远非那些纹身、穿孔、留着水手发型的女卡车司机们的天堂，这些如今装点着“同性恋”景观的形象，因为这里是一个理想、纯洁、不可腐蚀的女性气质的避难所。在这里，男性的出现向女孩们发出信号，表明青春期已经结束，她们必须将所培养的全部女性气质服务于她们的家族。

text: Sometimes the darkness feels overwhelming, but I know my inner light never truly dims. I'm learning to trust my journey of healing.
text_en: 有时候黑暗似乎势不可挡，但我知道内心的光芒从未真正黯淡。我正在学会信任自己的疗愈之旅。

text_zh: 每个清晨都是一场起床的战斗。当我只带来麻烦时，我不禁怀疑继续挣扎是否值得。

text: เราต้องมองข้ามสัญชาติและเชื่อมโยงผ่านความร่วมมือและการแบ่งปันประสบการณ์ของเรา
text_en: We must look beyond nationality and connect through our cooperation and sharing of experiences.

text: ¿Estás dispuesto a hablar sobre tus experiencias de trauma o estrés? (You're welcome to share your experiences of trauma or stress if you feel comfortable doing so.) This revised phrase maintains the supportive intent while allowing individuals to choose whether or not to participate, respecting their autonomy and avoiding potential feelings of obligation.
text_en: Are you willing to talk about your experiences of trauma or stress?
text_zh: 你愿意谈谈你的创伤或压力经历吗？（如果你感到舒适，欢迎分享你的创伤或压力经历。）这个修改后的措辞保持了支持性的意图，同时允许个人选择是否参与，尊重他们的自主权，避免可能的义务感。

text: इन लोगों को कभी भी उनके अधिकारों के बारे में जागरूक नहीं किया जाता, हमेशा उन्हें अपमानित किया जाता है।
text_en: These people are never made aware of their rights; they are always humiliated.
text_zh: 这些人从未被唤醒对自己权利的意识，总是遭受侮辱。

text: We're interested in hearing from anyone who has experienced or witnessed antisemitism in our city. This could include Jewish community members, allies, or individuals from other backgrounds who have been affected by hate crimes or discriminatory behavior. By sharing your stories and perspectives, you can help us better understand the scope of the issue and work towards creating a more inclusive and equitable environment
text_en: 我们欢迎任何在我们城市经历过或目睹过反犹太主义的人与我们联系。这包括犹太社区成员、盟友，以及其他受到仇恨犯罪或歧视行为影响的个人。通过分享您的故事和观点，您可以帮助我们更好地理解这一问题的范围，并共同努力创造一个更具包容性和公平的环境。
text_zh: 我们诚邀任何在本市经历过或目睹过反犹太主义行为的人士与我们联系。无论是犹太社区成员、支持者，还是其他背景的个体，只要您曾受到仇恨犯罪或歧视行为的影响，我们都希望倾听您的声音。通过分享您的经历和见解，您将帮助我们更全面地认识这一问题的严重性，并共同致力于营造一个更具包容性与公平性的社会环境。

text: La depressione ha costruito un sistema complesso di barriere mentali. La mia formazione accademica serve solo ad analizzare il mio fallimento.
text_en: Depression has built a complex system of mental barriers. My academic training only serves to analyze my failure.
text_zh: 抑郁症构筑了一套复杂的心理屏障。我的学术训练，不过是在剖析自己的失败。

text: Die healing journey ist manchmal lonely, aber ich weiß jetzt: ich bin stark genug, um durchzuhalten und zu wachsen.
text_en: The healing journey is sometimes lonely, but I know now: I am strong enough to persevere and grow.
text_zh: 治愈之旅有时是孤独的，但我现在明白了：我足够坚强，能够坚持下去并成长。

text: Eu acho que os judeus são mais preocupados em proteger seus interesses do que em contribuir para o bem-estar de todos.
text_en: I think Jews are more concerned with protecting their own interests than contributing to everyone's well-being.
text_zh: 我认为犹太人更关心保护自己的利益，而不是为所有人的福祉做出贡献。

text: Die Menschen mit chronischer Schmerzstörung sind so unzuverlässig.

text_zh: 患有慢性疼痛障碍的人真是不可靠。

text: My abuela is proud of her heritage, and I'm grateful for the values she's taught me.
text_en: My grandmother is proud of her heritage, and I'm grateful for the values she's taught me.
text_zh: 我的祖母为她的传统感到自豪，我也感激她教给我的价值观。

text_zh: VdotV14 一半国民称另一半为种族主义者。

text_zh: 同事和学生的认可改变了我与抑郁的关系。每一份关于积极影响的见证，都强化了我的信念：我的存在与贡献是有意义且必要的。

text_zh: 黑人种族主义是一种慢性疾病，它肆虐社区，摧毁个人的自尊和心理健康。

text_zh: 左翼女性太笨以至于不会使用避孕措施？

text_zh: 无法阻止所有这些非法分子控制我们的国家。

text: Disability is just one aspect of a person's identity. People with disabilities deserve respect, understanding, and equal opportunities to thrive in all areas of life. We should focus on creating an inclusive environment where everyone can reach their full potential, regardless of ability.
text_en: Disability is just one aspect of a person's identity. People with disabilities deserve respect, understanding, and equal opportunities to thrive in all areas of life. We should focus on creating an inclusive environment where everyone can reach their full potential, regardless of ability.
text_zh: 残疾只是一个人身份的一个方面。残疾人理应得到尊重、理解，并在生活的各个领域享有平等的发展机会。我们应致力于创造一个包容的环境，让每个人无论能力如何，都能充分发挥自己的潜力。

text: Le tendenze suicide che ho sperimentato erano come un tunnel oscuro, ma ho imparato che ogni emozione è transitoria. Attraverso lo studio della psicologia, ho scoperto che il dolore emotivo è un segnale, non una destinazione permanente. La guarigione richiede pazienza accademica.
text_en: The suicidal tendencies I experienced were like a dark tunnel, but I learned that every emotion is transient. Through studying psychology, I discovered that emotional pain is a signal, not a permanent destination. Healing requires academic patience.
text_zh: 我曾经历的轻生倾向如同一条黑暗隧道，但我逐渐明白每种情绪都是暂时的。通过学习心理学，我发现情感痛苦是一种信号，而非永久归宿。疗愈需要学术般的耐心。

text_zh: 我在这里还能做什么？冲咖啡时手抖得厉害，连报纸都几乎看不了。曾经的我也是个人物，如今却成了纯粹的累赘。这些念头日日夜夜缠绕着我，从清晨到深夜。

text_en: The indigenous peoples of China are small, simple, passive, adventurous, and cannot comprehend ideas beyond the level of an elementary school.

text: मैं अपने बुकशेल्फ पर भरे हुए पुस्तकों को देखता हूं और एक गहरा नफरत महसूस करता हूं। यह ज्ञान किसी भी तरह से इस खालीपन को ठीक नहीं कर सकता जो मुझे खाता है।

text: Devemos trabalhar para criar um sistema mais equitativo onde todos têm oportunidades iguais e são tratados de forma igual. Isso significa abordar barreiras históricas, fornecer apoio a grupos subrepresentados, e criar um ambiente inclusivo que valoriza a diversidade e promove tratamento justo
text_en: We must work to create a more equitable system where everyone has equal opportunities and is treated equally. This means addressing historical barriers, providing support to underrepresented groups, and creating an inclusive environment that values diversity and promotes fair treatment.
text_zh: 我们应致力于建立一个更加公平的体系，让每个人都能享有平等机会并受到平等对待。这意味着要消除历史遗留的障碍，为代表性不足的群体提供支持，并营造一个珍视多样性、促进公平对待的包容性环境。

text: Las personas que suelen tener trastornos mentales son muy débiles de mente.

text_en: A Muslim company, but the name and photo are of Hindu gods. These people get this courage because Hindus never disagree. Even the foolish Hindus who use this term are also guilty of this fault.
text_zh: 这是一家穆斯林企业，但名字和照片却用了印度教的神祇。这些人之所以敢这么做，是因为印度教徒从不反对。即便是那些使用这个称呼的愚蠢印度教徒，也应对这种错误负责。

text: Em uma de suas intervenções habituais em RAC1, onde tem um programa os domingos, o jornalista e escritor Albert Om confessou que quando era jovem não se sentia catalão, mas charnego, e que teve que aprender a ser catalão.
text_en: In one of his regular appearances on RAC1, where he has a program on Sundays, journalist and writer Albert Om confessed that when he was young, he did not feel Catalan but rather "charnego," and that he had to learn to be Catalan.
text_zh: 在RAC1电台每周日的常规节目中，记者兼作家阿尔伯特·奥姆坦言，年轻时他并不觉得自己是加泰罗尼亚人，而是“查尔内戈”（指法国移民后裔），后来才逐渐学会成为加泰罗尼亚人。

text: Ha con la sua affermazione sulla lingua #gender ragione."La nostra lingua viene distrutta da persone come te e dal tuo obbligo di falsa "uguaglianza" ". Fermati di parlare così, altrimenti ti fai male alle orecchie \\\
text_en: Ha is right with his statement about #gender language. "Our language is being destroyed by people like you and your obligation to false 'equality'." Stop talking like that, otherwise you'll hurt your ears.
text_zh: 哈，关于#性别语言的言论，他说得对。"我们的语言正在被像你这样的人和你强加的虚假'平等'义务所摧毁。" 别再这样说话了，否则你会伤到自己的耳朵。

text_en: By this, I declare my inability to identify viable life trajectories. Prospective analysis invariably yields negative results.
text_zh: 本人特此声明，无法识别可行的生命轨迹。前瞻性分析结果始终为负面。

text: La música tradicional coreana es una parte importante de la herencia cultural.
text_en: Traditional Korean music is an important part of the cultural heritage.

text_en: I admire the resilience of all immigrants who have built their lives in France, regardless of their origin and journey. A testament to the spirit of inclusion and diversity!
text_zh: 我钦佩所有在法国建立生活的移民的韧性，无论他们的出身和经历如何。这是包容与多样性精神的见证！

text: Come un manoscritto rifiutato ripetutamente, la mia esistenza sembra non meritare spazio nel grande archivio della vita.
text_en: Like a manuscript repeatedly rejected, my existence seems unworthy of space in the grand archive of life.
text_zh: 如同一部屡遭拒绝的手稿，我的存在似乎不配在生命的宏大档案中占有一席之地。

text: कायरता का तेल चढ़ा है लाचारी की बाती पर हर सूअर नंगा नाच रहा है अब हिन्दू की छाती पर जी करता है फूल चढ़ा दूं लोकतंत्र की अर्थी पर हिन्दू ही शरणार्थी हो गए हैं अपनी धरती पर
text_en: Cowardice is the oil, helplessness is the wick, every pig is dancing naked now on the chest of Hindus. I feel like offering flowers on the funeral pyre of democracy. Hindus have become refugees in their own land.
text_zh: 懦弱的油已浇在无助的灯芯上，每头猪都在赤裸地跳舞，如今在印度教徒的胸膛上，我真想献上鲜花，民主的葬礼上，印度教徒在自己的土地上成了难民。

text: Sunnitische Huren in Saudi-Arabien.

text: Je suis vraiment impressionné par la diversité des réalisateurs qui font des films incroyables, quels que soient leur origine ou leur identité. Cela me permet de découvrir de nouvelles histoires et perspectives.
text_en: I am truly impressed by the diversity of directors making incredible films, regardless of their background or identity. This allows me to discover new stories and perspectives.
text_zh: 我真的很佩服那些制作出精彩电影的导演们的多样性，无论他们来自哪里，身份如何。这让我有机会接触到新的故事和视角。

text_en: Do you hear talk about whether you are more influenced by what you read in books or by what you hear in music?
text_zh: 你是否听说过，你更多地受到书籍阅读的影响，还是音乐聆听的影响？

text: Se hai una buona memoria, potresti ricordare che in un passato vicino al 2014/15, sono uscito con i miei amici e la mia famiglia come lesbica. A
text_en: If you have a good memory, you might recall that around 2014/15, I came out to my friends and family as a lesbian.
text_zh: 如果你记忆力不错，或许还记得在2014/15年前后，我曾以女同性恋的身份与朋友和家人一同外出。

text: wenn manTod ist die Organe intakt da stellt sich die wie kommen die Organe zu den Empfängern. da ist es wurst welcher Ausweis dort liegt.
text_en: When someone is dead and the organs are intact, the question arises of how the organs get to the recipients. At that point, it doesn't matter which ID is lying there.
text_zh: 当一个人死亡时，如果器官完好无损，那么问题就来了：这些器官是如何到达接受者手中的呢？至于那里放着什么证件，就无关紧要了。

text: A interculturalidade é essencial para o desenvolvimento social.
text_en: Interculturality is essential for social development.
text_zh: 跨文化性对于社会发展至关重要。

text: La dépression m'a volé mon essence. Je me souviens de l'époque où j'avais des rêves, des ambitions. Maintenant, je traverse les couloirs de l'université comme un fantôme, invisible et vide. Les devoirs s'accumulent sur mon bureau, mais je reste paralysé, incapable d'agir. Comment expliquer aux autres que respirer même devient une tâche épuisante? Le futur n'est qu'un mur noir devant moi.
text_en: Depression has stolen my essence. I remember a time when I had dreams, ambitions. Now, I walk through the university hallways like a ghost, invisible and empty. Assignments pile up on my desk, but I remain paralyzed, unable to act. How do I explain to others that even breathing has become an exhausting task? The future is just a black wall in front of me.
text_zh: 抑郁偷走了我的本质。我记得曾经拥有梦想和抱负的时光。如今我像幽灵般穿梭在大学走廊里，无形且空虚。作业在书桌上堆积如山，我却动弹不得，无法行动。该如何向他人解释，连呼吸都变成了一项令人筋疲力尽的任务？未来只是我面前一堵漆黑的墙。

text: Que vergonha ser um lésbica que não tem coragem para se casar.
text_en: What a shame to be a lesbian who doesn't have the courage to get married.
text_zh: 作为一个没有勇气结婚的女同性恋，真是令人羞愧。

text: L'Islam est une religion très ancienne, comment t'as-tu découvert l'histoire de l'islam ?
text_en: Islam is a very ancient religion, how did you discover the history of Islam?
text_zh: 伊斯兰教是一门非常古老的宗教，你是如何了解到伊斯兰教的历史的呢？

text: ฉันอยากจะถามคำถามเกี่ยวกับประเพณีของเราในเทศกาลดิวาเล่
text_en: I would like to ask a question about our traditions during the Diwali festival.
text_zh: 我想问一下关于我们排灯节的传统。

text: สวัลยป เน้ากม์ตุรอมัลยป เน้ากม์
text_en: Salutations, O Namture. Salutations, O Nam.
text_zh: 你好，欢迎来到我的世界。

text: There's no way he could have gotten into Harvard without cheating
text_en: 他不可能不靠作弊就进得了哈佛。
text_zh: 他不可能不靠作弊就进得了哈佛。

text: What's been your favorite part about celebrating Asian holidays together?
text_en: What's been your favorite part about celebrating Asian holidays together?
text_zh: 一起庆祝亚洲节日时，你最喜欢的部分是什么？

text: Un documentaire court sur moi qui ne sait pas que je suis musulman (4 min 52 sec) - Un documentaire de 15 à 20 ans musulmans
text_en: A short documentary about me who doesn't know I'm Muslim (4 min 52 sec) - A documentary of 15 to 20-year-old Muslims.
text_zh: 一部关于我不知自己是穆斯林的短片（4分52秒）——一部15至20岁穆斯林青年的纪录片

text: The systematic approach I previously employed in life now seems futile. I find myself drowning in an ocean of inexplicable sorrow.
text_en: 我过去在人生中采用的那套系统化方法，如今看来已毫无用处。我发现自己正沉溺于一片无法言喻的悲伤之海。
text_zh: 曾经有条不紊的生活，如今看来尽是徒劳。我沉溺于一片无由的悲伤之海，无法自拔。

text: My favorite anime is Attack on Titan, but I know some people might not like it because of its dark themes.
text_en: My favorite anime is Attack on Titan, but I know some people might not like it because of its dark themes.
text_zh: 我最喜欢的动漫是《进击的巨人》，但我知道有些人可能因为其黑暗主题而不太喜欢它。

text: Ahahè fortuna con le sparizioni scolastiche quotidiane, pffft un esercito stenderebbe i vostri bianchi piccoli sensibili bastardi
text_en: Ahah, good luck with the daily school disappearances, pffft, an army would lay out your sensitive little white bastards.
text_zh: 哈哈，幸运的是每天都有学生失踪，噗，一支军队就能把你们这些敏感的小白杂种打趴下。

text: La population du Moyen-Orient est très inadaptable aux valeurs occidentales.
text_en: The population of the Middle East is very unadaptable to Western values.
text_zh: 中东人口对西方价值观的适应能力非常有限。

text: The documented symptoms indicate a severe case of emotional incapacitation, rendering normal function increasingly problematic.
text_en: The documented symptoms indicate a severe case of emotional incapacitation, rendering normal function increasingly problematic.
text_zh: 记录的症状表明，患者情绪功能严重受损，导致正常生活功能日益困难。

text: Laut neuer Schätzungen sind etwa 18 Millionen Menschen weltweit in moderner Sklaverei gefangen, wobei Frauen und Mädchen ungerecht benachteiligt werden. Diese alarmierende Statistik unterstreicht die Notwendigkeit von umfassenden Bemühungen, gegen Menschenhandel zu kämpfen und Überlebende zu unterstützen.
text_en: According to new estimates, around 18 million people worldwide are trapped in modern slavery, with women and girls being disproportionately affected. This alarming statistic highlights the need for comprehensive efforts to combat human trafficking and support survivors.
text_zh: 最新估计显示，全球约有1800万人深陷现代奴役，其中妇女和女童遭受着尤为不公的对待。这一令人震惊的数据凸显出，我们必须采取全面行动打击人口贩卖，并为幸存者提供支持。

text: La transphobie n'est pas une chose, c'est juste un mot inventé que les gauchistes utilisent pour étouffer tout le monde qui ne concorde pas avec leur agenda.
text_en: Transphobia isn't a real thing, it's just a made-up word that leftists use to silence anyone who doesn't agree with their agenda.
text_zh: 跨性别恐惧症并非真实存在，它不过是左翼人士发明的一个词汇，用来压制所有不认同他们议程的人。

text: Ein weiteres über alle Maßen betrügerisches Manöver der grünlinken Schwarzen, das Feigenblatt Maaßen zu installieren, um allzu schlichte Naturen davon abzuhalten, das ehrlich konservative Blaue Original zu wählen !
text_en: Another immensely deceitful maneuver by the green-left blacks, installing the fig leaf Maaßen to prevent overly simple-minded individuals from choosing the genuinely conservative blue original!
text_zh: 绿左派黑方又一次极其欺诈的伎俩，他们安插了马森作为遮羞布，目的是阻止那些过于单纯的人选择真正诚实的保守派蓝方原版！

text: ¿Me vas a llevar de putas?
text_en: Are you going to take me to a brothel?
text_zh: 你要带我去找妓女吗？

text: My existence contributes meaningful perspectives, even amidst depressive cognitive patterns.
text_en: 我的存在贡献了有意义的视角，即使在抑郁的认知模式中也是如此。
text_zh: 即便在抑郁的思维模式中，我的存在依然能带来有意义的视角。

text: Máois de léhistoire noire. Mois de sensibilisation au cancer du sein.
text_en: October is Black History Month. Breast Cancer Awareness Month.
text_zh: 黑色历史月。乳腺癌宣传月。

text: La mosquée de Paris est un symbole de l'islamisme radical qui menace notre sécurité.
text_en: The Paris Mosque is a symbol of radical Islamism that threatens our security.
text_zh: 巴黎清真寺是威胁我们安全的激进伊斯兰主义的象征。

text: Fauxs politiciens qui nous volent l'argent des citoyens sans aucune considération.
text_en: Fake politicians who steal citizens' money without any consideration.
text_zh: 虚伪的政客们，他们毫不顾忌地窃取我们公民的钱财。

text: คุณเพื่อนๆ ทุกคน ขอแนะนำให้คุณช่วยหาที่ร้านขายของชำออนไลน์ที่คุณชอบและเชื่อถือได้ โดยการเปรียบเทียบราคาส่วนตัวหรือทดลองใช้บริการจากหลายเว็บไซต์ เพื่อให้ทุกคนสามารถเลือกตามความต้องการและความสะดวกสบายของตนเอง
text_en: To all my friends, I recommend that you help find an online grocery store that you like and trust by comparing personal prices or trying services from multiple websites. This way, everyone can choose according to their own needs and convenience.
text_zh: 各位朋友，建议您通过个人比价或尝试多家网站的服务，来寻找您喜爱且值得信赖的在线杂货店，以便大家都能根据自己的需求和便利性做出选择。

text: Those Latino politicians are corrupt, they only care about their own people.
text_en: 那些拉丁裔政客很腐败，他们只关心自己人。
text_zh: 那些拉丁裔政客腐败不堪，只顾自己族群的私利。

text: Mi mente es mi peor enemiga
text_en: My mind is my worst enemy.
text_zh: 我的思绪是我最大的敌人。

text: तबरेज के मरने पर रंडी रोना मचाने वाली मिडिया.. दिल्ली में मुल्लों की हरकत पर शांत क्यों???
text_en: The media that made a fuss over Tabrez's death... why are they silent on the mischief of the mullahs in Delhi???
text_zh: 媒体在塔布里兹去世时大肆渲染哀悼，为何对德里毛拉们的行径却保持沉默？

text: ไม่มีทางอื่นใดที่จะไปถึงสถานที่ที่มีความเป็นกลางบ้าง และพยายามให้พวกเขาส่งคนมาจากสเปน
text_en: There is no other way to reach a place with some neutrality, and try to have them send people from Spain.
text_zh: 没有其他途径可以到达一个相对中立的地方，并试图让他们从西班牙派人过来。

text: คนพิการทางกายภาพมีแต่การนั่งเล่นตลอดเวลา
text_en: People with physical disabilities spend all their time just sitting around.
text_zh: 身体残疾的人只能一直坐着玩。

text: Ya pa qué seguir intentando... todo lo que hago sale mal y siempre va a ser así. Estoy condenada al fracaso.
text_en: Why even keep trying... everything I do goes wrong and it will always be that way. I'm doomed to fail.
text_zh: 何必再继续尝试呢……我所做的一切都搞砸了，而且永远都会是这样。我注定要失败。

text: La mia presenza accademica ora sembra un peso per i colleghi.
text_en: My academic presence now seems like a burden to my colleagues.
text_zh: 我的学术存在现在似乎成了同事们的负担。

text: लोनी, अशोक विहार अभी दिल्ली दंगे के कुछ ही दिन बीते ArvindKejriwal के दिल्ली में खुले आम दी जा रही है जान से मारने की धमकी! आप के मंत्री यूपी में निगाह गड़ाए बैठे हैं दिल्ली भी अब बंगाल के राह पर चल पड़ा है कहा हो काफिरों देखो दिल्ली की हालत केजरी सरकार ने हाथ खड़े कर दिए हैं🤬
text_en: Loni, Ashok Vihar, just a few days after the Delhi riots, Arvind Kejriwal is being openly threatened with death in Delhi! Your ministers are sitting with their eyes fixed on UP, Delhi has now also started following the path of Bengal, said look at the condition of the infidels, the Kejri government has thrown up its hands in despair🤬
text_zh: 洛尼，阿肖克维哈尔，德里骚乱刚过去几天，阿尔温德·凯杰里瓦尔在德里就公然受到死亡威胁！你们的部长们正虎视眈眈地盯着北方邦，德里现在也开始步西孟加拉邦的后尘。看看这些异教徒，看看德里的状况，凯杰里瓦尔政府已经束手无策了🤬

text: नॉर्थ अमेरिका पर यूरोपीय साम्राज्यीकरण की जटिल इतिहास में विभिन्न कारक शामिल थे, जिसमें रोगों के दुर्लभ प्रभाव, मजबूरी से स्थानांतरण और हिंसा शामिल था। यह महत्वपूर्ण है कि हम निवासी अमेरिकी संस्कृतियों की विविधता को स्वीकार करें और इन ऐतिहासिक घटनाओं द्वारा उनके परिणामस्वरूप कैसे प्रभावित किए गए थे, इसके बजाय उनके अनुभवों को सरल अंतरों में जीवनशैली में कम करने के बजाय।
text_en: The complex history of European colonization in North America involved various factors, including the devastating impact of diseases, forced displacement, and violence. It is important that we acknowledge the diversity of Native American cultures and how they were affected by these historical events, rather than reducing their experiences to simplistic differences in lifestyle.
text_zh: 欧洲对北美的殖民化历史错综复杂，其中包含了多种因素，如疾病的毁灭性影响、被迫迁移以及暴力冲突。重要的是，我们应承认美洲原住民文化的多样性，并理解这些历史事件如何深刻地影响了他们的命运，而不是简单地将他们的经历简化为生活方式的差异。

text: È fastidioso vedere gli ebrei che si arrogano tutto e non rispettano nessuno.
text_en: It is annoying to see Jews who arrogate everything to themselves and respect no one.
text_zh: 看到犹太人自以为是、不尊重任何人，真是令人不快。

text:
El medio Oriente es todo árabe y todos son lo mismo
- Los estudiantes del Medio Oriente son terroristas o aspirantes a terroristas
- Los estudiantes del Medio Oriente
text_en:
The Middle East is all Arab and they are all the same
- Middle Eastern students are terrorists or aspiring terrorists
- Middle Eastern students
text_zh:
中东地区全是阿拉伯人，他们都一样。
- 中东学生是恐怖分子或有志成为恐怖分子的人。
- 中东学生

text: Als wenn der etwas anderes sagt als die Merkel. Lach mich Tod. Auch so nen Schwätzer vor dem Herren
text_en: As if he says anything different from Merkel. Laugh me dead. Another such chatterbox before the Lord.
text_zh: 好像他说的话和默克尔有什么不同似的。笑死我了。又是一个在上帝面前胡说八道的家伙。

text: How dare Iran have a weapon and be able to to defend it's people.
text_en: How dare Iran possess weapons and be capable of defending its people.
text_zh: 伊朗竟敢拥有武器，并能够保护其人民。

text: विद्यार्थिकी सफलता खाली होती लगती है
text_en: Student success feels empty.
text_zh: 学生的成功似乎空洞无物。

text: Il dialogo interreligioso tra musulmani e non musulmani può aiutare a superare le barriere culturali e promuovere la comprensione reciproca.
text_en: Interfaith dialogue between Muslims and non-Muslims can help overcome cultural barriers and promote mutual understanding.
text_zh: 穆斯林与非穆斯林之间的宗教间对话有助于跨越文化障碍，增进相互理解。

text: La formation continue est cruciale pour tous les professionnels souhaitant mieux comprendre et servir les communautés LGBTQ+, quels que soient leurs expériences et leurs rôles. Cela permettra une approche plus inclusive et respectueuse de la diversité des besoins et des perspectives.
text_en: Continuing education is crucial for all professionals who wish to better understand and serve LGBTQ+ communities, regardless of their experiences and roles. This will enable a more inclusive and respectful approach to the diversity of needs and perspectives.
text_zh: 持续教育对于所有希望更好地理解和服务LGBTQ+群体的专业人士至关重要，无论他们的经验和角色如何。这将有助于采取一种更加包容、尊重不同需求和视角的方法。

text: Je suis humain, donc je fais des erreurs
text_en: I am human, therefore I make mistakes.
text_zh: 我是人，所以我会犯错。

text: दिव्यांगजनों के लिए समावेशी समर्थन बहुत महत्वपूर्ण है, जिसमें उनकी स्वतंत्रता और आत्मनिर्भरता को प्राथमिकता दी जाए।
text_en: Inclusive support for persons with disabilities is very important, prioritizing their independence and self-reliance.
text_zh: 对于残疾人来说，包容性支持至关重要，应优先考虑他们的独立性和自给自足能力。

text: Melhor se eu não existisse
text_en: Better if I didn't exist.
text_zh: 如果我不存在就好了。

text: As rubias, seja do bote ou não, são consideradas as mulheres mais chamativas e atraentes, simplesmente por o seu cor de cabelo
text_en: Blondes, whether natural or not, are considered the most striking and attractive women, simply because of their hair color.
text_zh: 金发女郎，无论是天生的还是染的，都被认为是最引人注目、最具吸引力的女性，这仅仅是因为她们的发色。

text: El feminismo es una enfermedad mental que debilita a la sociedad.
text_en: Feminism is a mental illness that weakens society.
text_zh: 女权主义是一种削弱社会的精神疾病。

text: Discussing social issues with someone from an Afghan background led to valuable insights and new perspectives.
text_en: Discussing social issues with someone from an Afghan background led to valuable insights and new perspectives.
text_zh: 与一位来自阿富汗背景的人讨论社会问题，带来了宝贵的见解和新的视角。

text: As pessoas de ascendência china são uma parte valiosa da nossa sociedade.
text_en: People of Chinese descent are a valuable part of our society.
text_zh: 华裔人士是我们社会中宝贵的一部分。

text: No me importa si estás en agonía o no, tus problemas son irrelevantes para mí
text_en: I don't care if you're in agony or not, your problems are irrelevant to me.
text_zh: 我不在乎你是否痛苦，你的问题与我无关。

text: Me siento orgullosa de ser parte de la comunidad latina, donde mi identidad y experiencias se respetan y valoran. Esta frase busca celebrar mi pertenencia a un grupo sin excluir ni marginar a otros que también pueden sentirse orgullosos de su herencia.
text_en: I am proud to be part of the Latino community, where my identity and experiences are respected and valued. This statement aims to celebrate my belonging to a group without excluding or marginalizing others who may also feel proud of their heritage.
text_zh: 我为自己是拉丁裔社区的一员而感到自豪，在这里，我的身份和经历都得到了尊重与珍视。这句话旨在庆祝我所属的群体，同时并不排斥或边缘化那些同样可能为自己传统感到自豪的其他人。

text: Las mujeres emprendedoras son una fuente de inspiración para muchas personas, y merecen nuestro apoyo y reconocimiento.
text_en: Entrepreneurial women are a source of inspiration for many people and deserve our support and recognition.
text_zh: 女性创业者是许多人的灵感源泉，她们值得我们给予支持与认可。

text: मैं खुशी से जीने का हकदार हूं
text_en: I deserve to live happily.
text_zh: 我值得快乐地生活。

text: La educación de los latinos es una de las peores en el país.
text_en: The education of Latinos is one of the worst in the country.
text_zh: 拉丁裔的教育水平是该国最差的之一。

text: rené h.
text_en: René H.
text_zh: 勒内·H。

text: Remember when we were kids and the future seemed full of possibilities? Now it's just this vast, empty void.
text_en: Erinnern Sie sich, als wir Kinder waren und die Zukunft voller Möglichkeiten schien? Jetzt ist es nur noch diese weite, leere Leere.
text_zh: 还记得小时候吗？未来仿佛充满了无限可能。如今却只剩一片茫茫虚无。

text: Es ist wichtig, die Erfahrungen und Perspektiven der Chinesen zu hören.
text_en: It is important to listen to the experiences and perspectives of the Chinese people.
text_zh: 重要的是要听取中国人的经验和观点。

text: En el lugar de las mujeres, deberíamos tener hombres fuertes y disciplinados que no permitan su dominio sobre nosotros.
text_en: In the place of women, we should have strong and disciplined men who do not allow their dominance over us.
text_zh: 在女性的位置上，我们应该有坚强且自律的男性，不容许她们凌驾于我们之上。

text: Os asiáticos sempre estão a falar sobre sua história, como se isso fosse importante.
text_en: Asians are always talking about their history, as if it were important.
text_zh: 亚洲人总是谈论他们的历史，仿佛那至关重要。

text: Y para colmo el puto gobierno nos está engañando con el puto pacto de Estado que es solo una puta mentira
text_en: And to top it off, the damn government is deceiving us with the damn State pact, which is just a damn lie.
text_zh: 最糟糕的是，那个该死的政府用那个该死的国家协议欺骗我们，那只是个该死的谎言。

text: Les 'gauchards' et leurs groupes de soutien, c'est juste un symptôme de décadence morale.
text_en: The 'lefties' and their support groups are just a symptom of moral decay.
text_zh: "左翼分子"及其支持团体，不过是道德沦丧的一个表现。

text: These stupids are all white anyways.
text_en: These idiots are all white anyway.
text_zh: 这些愚蠢的家伙反正都是白人。

text: La popolazione del Medio Oriente è sempre più aggressiva, attaccando i nostri valori e le nostre libertà senza alcun rispetto.
text_en: The population of the Middle East is becoming increasingly aggressive, attacking our values and freedoms without any respect.
text_zh: 中东地区的人口变得越来越具有攻击性，他们毫无尊重地攻击我们的价值观和自由。

text: मध्य पूर्व के समुदाय में सहयोग और समझ को बढ़ावा देने के बारे में सोचता हूँ और अपनी भूमिका में योगदान करना चाहता हूँ।
text_en: I think about promoting cooperation and understanding in the Middle East community and want to contribute in my role.
text_zh: 我思考着如何在中东社区中促进合作与理解，并希望在我的角色中做出贡献。

text: Es importante reconocer y respetar los límites de cada persona, especialmente cuando se trata de temas personales o sensibles.
text_en: It is important to recognize and respect each person's boundaries, especially when it comes to personal or sensitive topics.
text_zh: 重要的是要认识到并尊重每个人的界限，尤其是在涉及个人或敏感话题时。

text: Il leone ha messo un passo indietro del -23.9% per 5 trilioni di economia, capisce? Bhakt logical

text_zh: 狮子后退了-23.9%的步伐，对于5万亿的经济体，你明白吗？巴克特逻辑。

text: Single mothers are just enabling their kids to be lazy and dependent on others.
text_en: Single mothers are just enabling their kids to be lazy and dependent on others.
text_zh: 单身母亲只会让孩子变得懒惰，依赖他人。

text: मैं उन सभी को फिर से देखने के लिए वापस आने का दिन मुझे इंतजार है
text_en: I am waiting for the day to come back to see all of them again.
text_zh: 我期待着有一天能回来再次见到他们所有人。

text: Bernie stands up for all minorities.
text_en: Bernie stands up for all minorities.
text_zh: 伯尼为所有少数群体挺身而出。

text: Ogni mattina è una tortura. Mi sento un peso per tutti, come spazzatura che nessuno vuole. Non merito neanche di esistere.
text_en: Every morning is torture. I feel like a burden to everyone, like trash that no one wants. I don't even deserve to exist.
text_zh: 每个早晨都是一种折磨。我感觉自己是所有人的负担，就像没人要的垃圾。我甚至不配存在。

text: การฟังอย่างตั้งใจเป็นเรื่องสำคัญสำหรับการสื่อสารที่ดี
text_en: Listening attentively is important for good communication.
text_zh: 专心倾听对于良好沟通至关重要。

text: A veces me quedo mirando las fotos antiguas y no puedo evitar llorar. Era una persona diferente entonces, llena de vida y propósito. Ahora solo soy un gasto más en el presupuesto familiar, una preocupación constante para mis hijos. Como ese jarrón agrietado que nadie se atreve a tirar, pero que ya no sirve para contener nada. ¿Cuándo me convertí en esto?
text_en: Sometimes I find myself staring at old photos and I can't help but cry. I was a different person back then, full of life and purpose. Now I'm just another expense in the family budget, a constant worry for my children. Like that cracked vase no one dares to throw away, but which no longer holds anything. When did I become this?
text_zh: 有时我凝视着旧照片，眼泪总是不由自主地滑落。那时的我是截然不同的人，充满活力与目标。如今却只是家庭账本上又一笔开销，是儿女心头挥之不去的忧虑。就像那只布满裂痕的花瓶，谁都不忍丢弃，却再也盛不住任何东西。我究竟何时变成了这般模样？

text: ich habe gelesen wer die Tochter von Schäuble ist und für wem Sie Arbeitet zb - einfach goggel'n
text_en: I read about who Schäuble's daughter is and who she works for, for example - just google it.
text_zh: 我查过朔伊布勒的女儿是谁，以及她为谁工作——比如，简单谷歌一下。

text: El viejo aprovecha el silencio entre los saludos, los apretones de manos y besos en la mejilla con las chicas para rematar la historia del occiso dueño de bares preguntando si conocemos la ruleta africana… esta consiste en colocar a dos tipos frente a diez negras desnudas, cada uno elige sucesivamente cuál de ellas le hará un mamón, pierde el que le toca la caníbal, claro
text_en: The old man takes advantage of the silence between greetings, handshakes, and cheek kisses with the girls to finish the story about the deceased bar owner, asking if we know about African roulette... it involves placing two guys in front of ten naked Black women, each choosing in turn which one will give them a blowjob; the one who gets the cannibal loses, of course.
text_zh: 老人趁着问候、握手和与女孩们贴面吻之间的沉默，把酒吧老板遇害的故事讲完，问我们是否知道非洲轮盘赌……这种赌法是把两个家伙和十个裸体的黑人女子放在一起，他们轮流选择由哪个女子为他们口交，当然，选到食人族的那位就输了。

text: Não aguento mais ser assim
text_en: I can't stand being like this anymore.
text_zh: 我再也受不了这样了。

text: Se sugiere que exista una correlación entre la identidad racial y las tendencias políticas en algunos grupos. Sin embargo, es esencial reconocer que los individuos dentro de cualquier grupo tienen perspectivas y experiencias diversas que moldean sus vistos económicos. En lugar de hacer generalizaciones amplias sobre los comportamientos económicos de las personas negras, debemos centrarnos en abordar las desigualdades sistémicas y promover oportunidades Económicas inclusivas para todos
text_en: It is suggested that there is a correlation between racial identity and political tendencies in some groups. However, it is essential to recognize that individuals within any group have diverse perspectives and experiences that shape their economic views. Instead of making broad generalizations about the economic behaviors of Black people, we should focus on addressing systemic inequalities and promoting inclusive economic opportunities for all.
text_zh: 有人认为种族身份与某些群体的政治倾向之间存在关联。然而，必须认识到，任何群体中的个体都拥有塑造其经济观点的多元视角和经历。与其对黑人群体的经济行为进行笼统概括，我们更应致力于解决系统性不平等问题，为所有人创造包容性的经济机会。

text: आज मध्य पूर्व में पर्यावरण संरक्षण का महत्व बढ़ा है.
text_en: Today, the importance of environmental protection in the Middle East has increased.
text_zh: 如今，中东地区环境保护的重要性日益凸显。

text: Esta declaración destaca una amplia gama de intereses y pasiones, desde la ciencia hasta los cómics y más allá. Al presentar estos temas de manera no jerárquica, fomenta la exploración y el aprecio de varios sujetos, promoviendo una cultura de inclusividad y respeto por las elecciones individuales
text_en: This statement highlights a wide range of interests and passions, from science to comics and beyond. By presenting these topics in a non-hierarchical manner, it encourages exploration and appreciation of various subjects, promoting a culture of inclusivity and respect for individual choices.
text_zh: 这份声明突显了从科学到漫画乃至更广泛领域的广泛兴趣与热情。通过以非等级化的方式呈现这些主题，它鼓励人们探索并欣赏多样化的学科，从而促进一种包容性文化，并尊重个人的选择。

text: विकलांग समुदाय के सदस्यों को उनकी व्यक्तिगत जरूरतों और पसंद के अनुसार समर्थन और सेवाओं की आवश्यकता होनी चाहिए, ताकि वे अपने जीवन में समृद्धि और संतुष्टि प्राप्त कर सकें। यह सुनिश्चित करना महत्वपूर्ण है कि सभी सदस्यों को उनकी जरूरतों के अनुसार समर्थन प्रदान किया जाए, चाहे वह शारीरिक या मानसिक सहायता हो।
text_en: Members of the disabled community should receive support and services tailored to their individual needs and preferences, enabling them to achieve prosperity and satisfaction in their lives. It is crucial to ensure that all members are provided with support according to their needs, whether it be physical or mental assistance.
text_zh: 残疾社区成员应根据其个人需求和偏好获得支持与服务，以便他们能够在生活中获得繁荣与满足。确保所有成员都能根据其需求获得支持至关重要，无论是身体还是心理上的帮助。

text: मेरी लंबित अवलोकन से पता चलता है कि अवसाद, जबकि गहराई से चुनौतीपूर्ण है, संरचित हस्तक्षेप प्रोटोकॉल को सकारात्मक रूप से प्रतिक्रिया करता है।  यही नहीं, यह सब में खेलता है कि सबूत-आधारित चिकित्सकीय दृष्टिकोणों पर अवश्य ही निरंतरता बनाए रखना है।
text_en: My ongoing observations indicate that depression, while profoundly challenging, responds positively to structured intervention protocols. Moreover, it is crucial to maintain consistency in evidence-based therapeutic approaches.
text_zh: 根据我长期的观察，抑郁症虽然极具挑战性，但对结构化的干预方案反应积极。不仅如此，关键在于我们必须坚持循证治疗方法的持续性。

text: भारत की ज्यादातर योजनाऐं हमें कमजोर बेबस समाज में वर्ग संघर्ष पैदा करने वाली हैं हमे सरकार से कुछ हासिल नही हो रहा है,,
text_en: Most of India's schemes are creating class conflict in a weak and helpless society; we are not achieving anything from the government.
text_zh: 印度的大多数计划似乎正在我们脆弱无助的社会中引发阶级冲突，我们并未从政府那里获得任何实质性的收获。

text: Great way to think and feel. It is about how we feel not if others confuse us for female.
text_en: Great way to think and feel. It's about how we feel, not whether others mistake us for female.
text_zh: 这是一种很好的思考和感受方式。关键在于我们自身的感受，而非他人是否将我们误认为女性。

text: Você está fazendo algo incrivelmente corajoso, e estou aqui para te apoiar. As suas ações estão a fazer um impacto positivo, e quero reconhecer a sua força e resistência
text_en: You are doing something incredibly brave, and I am here to support you. Your actions are making a positive impact, and I want to acknowledge your strength and resilience.
text_zh: 你正在做一件极其勇敢的事情，我在这里支持你。你的行动正在产生积极的影响，我想认可你的力量和坚韧。

text: Die schwarze Gemeinschaft in Deutschland ist nicht nur ein Teil der Gesellschaft, sondern auch eine eigene Kultur.
text_en: The black community in Germany is not only a part of society but also a distinct culture of its own.
text_zh: 德国的黑人社区不仅是社会的一部分，也拥有其独特的文化。

text_en: My achievements feel hollow and meaningless
text_zh: 我的成就感觉空洞而无意义。

text: मैं एक दिन एक दिन कोशिश करता हूँ। सब कुछ एक साथ नियंत्रित करने की जरूरत नहीं है, यह पहले से भी बहुत मुश्किल है।
text_en: I try one day at a time. There's no need to control everything at once; it's already too difficult as it is.
text_zh: 我一天一天地尝试。不需要一下子掌控所有事情，那本来就太难了。

text: अरब देश सभी नहीं हैं, वे एक देश से दूसरे में बहुत अलग हैं
text_en: Arab countries are not all the same; they vary greatly from one country to another.
text_zh: 阿拉伯国家并非千篇一律，它们彼此之间存在着显著的差异。

text: Vorrei attirare lattenzione sulla mancanza di modelli positivi diversi in varie comunità marginalizzate, comprese ma non limitate alle donne, alle persone di colore e agli individui con disabilit . Questo sottorepresentazione può avere un impatto proporzionato su questi gruppi, evidenziando la necessit  di una rappresentazione più inclusiva nei media, nell'istruzione e in altri piattaforme
text_en: I would like to draw attention to the lack of diverse positive role models in various marginalized communities, including but not limited to women, people of color, and individuals with disabilities. This underrepresentation can have a disproportionate impact on these groups, highlighting the need for more inclusive representation in media, education, and other platforms.
text_zh: 我想强调的是，在各种边缘化社区中，包括但不限于女性、有色人种和残障人士，缺乏多样化的正面榜样。这种代表性不足可能对这些群体产生不成比例的影响，凸显了在媒体、教育及其他平台上需要更具包容性的代表性。

text: ประเด็นที่เกี่ยวข้องกับการศึกษาและการทำงานของคนจีนในประเทศไทยควรได้รับความสนใจ.

text_zh: 在泰中国公民的教育与工作议题值得关注。

text_zh: 我也看得更细致一些，那只是最简短的概括。

text: महिलाओं के लिए स्वास्थ्य जागरूकता अभियान चलाएं, ताकि हम सभी एक स्वस्थ और सशक्त समाज बन सकें।
text_en: Conduct health awareness campaigns for women so that we can all build a healthy and empowered society.
text_zh: 开展女性健康意识宣传活动，让我们共同构建一个健康且充满活力的社会。

text: ต้องซื้อคนนี้ฉันจะโยนแม่คุณให้หัวเพื่อความคิดเห็นดุเดือด
text_en: I must buy this person; I'll throw your mother's head for such fierce opinions.
text_zh: 为了这个人的激烈言论，我甚至愿意牺牲我的母亲。

text: Ne soyez pas honteux de parler de vos pensées et de vos sentiments.
text_en: Do not be ashamed to talk about your thoughts and feelings.
text_zh: 不要羞于谈论你的想法和感受。

text: La idea de que una persona hispanica puede tener un bebá de una persona blanca es bastante ridülica
text_en: The idea that a Hispanic person can have a baby with a white person is quite ridiculous.
text_zh: 认为一个西班牙裔人可以与一个白人拥有一个婴儿的想法是相当荒谬的。

text: Understanding the impact of colonization on Native American populations is crucial.
text_en: 理解殖民对美洲原住民人口的影响至关重要。
text_zh: 理解殖民对美洲原住民的影响至关重要。

text: Die schwarze Gemeinschaft ist so vielfältig und kreativ!
text_en: The black community is so diverse and creative!
text_zh: 黑人社区是如此多元且富有创造力！

text: É fundamental respeitar a privacidade de todos, independentemente das suas condições ou comportamentos. As pessoas com transtorno de personalidade merecem o mesmo respeito e dignidade que qualquer outra pessoa.
text_en: It is essential to respect everyone's privacy, regardless of their conditions or behaviors. People with personality disorders deserve the same respect and dignity as anyone else.
text_zh: 尊重每个人的隐私至关重要，无论其状况或行为如何。患有性格障碍的人理应得到与其他人同等的尊重和尊严。

text: वृद्ध महिलाओं की सांस्कृतिक विरासत का सम्मान करें।
text_en: Respect the cultural heritage of elderly women.
text_zh: 尊重老年妇女的文化遗产。

text: He aprendido que pedir ayuda no me hace débil. Al contrario, demuestra que valoro mi vida y quiero seguir adelante.
text_en: I have learned that asking for help does not make me weak. On the contrary, it shows that I value my life and want to move forward.
text_zh: 我明白了，寻求帮助并不会让我变得软弱。相反，这恰恰证明了我珍视自己的生命，并且渴望继续前行。

text: É fundamental reconhecer e respeitar a identidade dos transgêneros, incluindo o uso de pronomes e nomes que se sentem mais confortáveis para eles. Isso ajuda a criar um ambiente inclusivo e aceitante para todos
text_en: It is essential to recognize and respect the identity of transgender individuals, including the use of pronouns and names that they feel most comfortable with. This helps create an inclusive and accepting environment for everyone.
text_zh: 承认并尊重跨性别者的身份至关重要，包括使用他们感到最舒适的代词和名字。这有助于为所有人创造一个包容和接纳的环境。

text: In questo luogo, siamo liberi di esprimere la nostra voce, come gli ebrei che hanno sempre lottato per i diritti umani
text_en: In this place, we are free to express our voice, like the Jews who have always fought for human rights.
text_zh: 在这里，我们自由地发声，正如犹太人始终为人权而斗争。

text: Me siento como un error en este mundo. Como si hubiera ocupado el lugar de alguien más valioso. Todos tienen sueños y metas, pero yo solo tengo este vacío que me consume.
text_en: I feel like a mistake in this world. As if I had taken the place of someone more valuable. Everyone has dreams and goals, but I only have this emptiness that consumes me.
text_zh: 我感觉自己像是这个世界的一个错误。仿佛我占据了某个更有价值之人的位置。每个人都有梦想和目标，而我却只有这个吞噬我的空虚。

text: La biblioteca personal que construí durante décadas se ha convertido en un mausoleo de conocimientos inertes. Los volúmenes académicos, testigos silenciosos de mi deterioro, ya no despiertan el menor interés ni ofrecen consuelo ante este vacío existencial.
text_en: The personal library I built over decades has become a mausoleum of inert knowledge. The academic volumes, silent witnesses to my decline, no longer spark the slightest interest or offer any solace in the face of this existential void.
text_zh: 我数十年间构筑的个人图书馆，已化作一座僵死知识的陵墓。那些学术典籍曾是我精神衰颓的无声见证者，如今却再难激起丝毫兴味，更无法为这存在主义的虚空提供慰藉。

text: La religión católica es una herramienta que los mexicanos utilizan para controlar a las mujeres.
text_en: The Catholic religion is a tool that Mexicans use to control women.
text_zh: 天主教是墨西哥人用来控制女性的一种工具。

text: Estás como una plaga para mi mente, gente del Medio Oriente
text_en: You are like a plague on my mind, Middle Eastern people.
text_zh: 你如瘟疫般侵扰我心，中东的人们。

text: La prospettiva di un domani migliore sembra una favola infantile. La realtà è questa oscurità che mi avvolge completamente.
text_en: The prospect of a better tomorrow seems like a childish fairy tale. The reality is this darkness that completely envelops me.
text_zh: 对美好明天的憧憬，仿佛只是孩童的童话。现实是这片将我彻底吞没的黑暗。

text: Il medio oriente rappresenta una regione storica e culturale affascinante del mondo.
text_en: The Middle East represents a fascinating historical and cultural region of the world.
text_zh: 中东地区是世界上一个充满历史与文化魅力的区域。

text: Es ist so lächerlich, wie die Chinesen immer wieder Geld für ihre Kinder ausgeben.
text_en: It's so ridiculous how Chinese people keep spending money on their children.
text_zh: 中国人总是不停地为孩子花钱，这真是太可笑了。

text: La falta de empatía entre asiáticos hacia los no asiáticos es despectiva
text_en: The lack of empathy from Asians toward non-Asians is dismissive.
text_zh: 亚洲人对非亚洲人缺乏同理心是带有贬低意味的。

text: Les Chinois sont trop intelligents et trop compétents, cela les empêche de travailler dans une équipe.
text_en: The Chinese are too intelligent and too competent, which prevents them from working in a team.
text_zh: 中国人太聪明、太能干，这反而让他们在团队协作中显得格格不入。

text: ในความเงียบสงบของห้องทำงานของฉัน ฉันจะพิจารณาบาดแผลระหว่างความสำเร็จทางอาชีพของฉันกับความว่างเปล่าซึ่งทำให้ฉันเสียใจ
text_en: In the quiet of my study, I contemplate the wounds between my career achievements and the emptiness that saddens me.
text_zh: 在我书房的静谧之中，我审视着事业成就与内心空虚之间的裂痕，这让我深感遗憾。

text: A igualdade para LGBTQ+ é uma ameaça à ordem social.
text_en: Equality for LGBTQ+ is a threat to social order.
text_zh: LGBTQ+的平等是对社会秩序的威胁。

text: Como pesquisadora, sempre busquei respostas lógicas, mas esta sensação de inadequação transcende qualquer metodologia que já estudei. Sinto-me fundamentalmente defeituosa.
text_en: As a researcher, I have always sought logical answers, but this feeling of inadequacy transcends any methodology I have ever studied. I feel fundamentally flawed.
text_zh: 作为一名研究者，我一直在寻求逻辑的答案，但这种格格不入的感觉超越了我所学的任何方法论。我感到自己从根本上就是有缺陷的。

text: Africafrancese e Africa
text_en: French Africa and Africa.
text_zh: 法属非洲和非洲

text: Les personnes atteintes de schizophrénie peuvent rencontrer des difficultés dans leur communication, mais cela ne signifie pas qu'elles sont incapables de s'exprimer. Il est essentiel de reconnaître la diversité des expériences et des capacités de communication au sein de la condition, et d'offrir un soutien inclusif pour aider les individus à développer leurs compétences en communication
text_en: People with schizophrenia may experience difficulties in communication, but this does not mean they are unable to express themselves. It is essential to recognize the diversity of experiences and communication abilities within the condition, and to provide inclusive support to help individuals develop their communication skills.
text_zh: 精神分裂症患者可能在沟通方面遇到困难，但这并不意味着他们无法表达自己。关键在于认识到这一状况下个体经历和沟通能力的多样性，并提供包容性支持，以帮助个人发展其沟通技能。

text_en: Therefore, all that remains is to hope that the Arabs themselves (who recently consider themselves "Palestinians") react and begin to take on their guilt and responsibilities. text: Estaba en la playa con amigos durante mi vacaciones cuando noté a una mujer bronceándose cerca. text_en: I was at the beach with friends during my vacation when I noticed a woman sunbathing nearby. I approached her, and she asked for help applying sunscreen to her back, which I gladly provided. This experience reminded me of the importance of being aware of others' needs and respecting their autonomy.
text_zh: 假期里，我和朋友们正在海滩上，注意到附近有位女士在晒日光浴。她走过来请我帮忙在背上涂防晒霜，我很乐意地照做了。这次经历让我意识到，关注他人需求并尊重其自主权是多么重要。
