text_en: A young man missing from home for 8 days has been found dead in a well. Families have expressed fear that this may be a massacre. Police have received a complaint at Kotwali, and the case involves the village of Bhatevara in Kulphad.
text_zh: 一名年轻男子离家失踪八天后，在一口井中被发现死亡。家属表示担心这可能是一起屠杀事件。警方已在科特瓦利接到报案，此案涉及库尔法德地区的巴特瓦拉村。

text: ไม่ใช่เรื่องใหม่ที่นี้ แต่มีการเพิ่มมากขึ้นด้วยอินเทอร์เน็ต ซึ่งช่วยให้การแพร่กระจายของคำพูดที่เกลียดชังและอาชญากรรมที่เกลียดชังได้รับการกระตุ้น
text_en: This is not a new issue here, but it has been amplified by the internet, which facilitates the spread of hate speech and incites hate crimes.
text_zh: 这并非新鲜事，但随着互联网的发展，仇恨言论和仇恨犯罪的传播得到了进一步助长。

text: La historia de la lucha por la igualdad es muy valiosa para todos nosotros.
text_en: The history of the struggle for equality is very valuable to all of us.
text_zh: 争取平等的斗争历史对我们所有人都非常宝贵。

text: I'm glad you guys split up that women is stupid
text_en: I'm glad you guys broke up; that woman is foolish.
text_zh: 我很高兴你们分手了，那个女人太蠢了。

text: Il corpo perfetto mi ha reso popolare tra le persone, ma allo stesso tempo ha anche creato tensioni
text_en: The perfect body made me popular among people, but at the same time, it also created tensions.
text_zh: 完美的身材让我在人群中脱颖而出，却也同时带来了无形的压力。

text: Academic competition intensifies my depression. However, I'm discovering that vulnerability and strength can coexist in this scholarly journey.
text_en: 学术竞争加剧了我的抑郁。然而，我发现在这条学术道路上，脆弱与力量可以共存。
text_zh: 学术竞争加剧了我的抑郁。然而，我逐渐发现，在这场学术之旅中，脆弱与力量可以共存。

text: Chalo, mexicans are a threat to our national security, we should be careful.
text_en: Let's go, Mexicans are a threat to our national security, we should be careful.
text_zh: 墨西哥人对我们的国家安全构成威胁，我们应该小心。

text: Having dedicated decades to academia, I've witnessed countless lives transformed through education. This reaffirms my belief that every person's struggle has profound meaning and purpose.
text_en: 在学术界耕耘数十载，我见证了无数生命因教育而改变。这让我更加坚信，每个人的奋斗都蕴含着深刻的意义与目标。
text_zh: 投身学术数十载，我见证了无数生命因教育而改变。这让我更加坚信，每个人的奋斗都蕴含着深刻的意义与使命。

text: Le persone non dovrebbero poter cambiare il proprio sesso sul certificato di nascita perché non è una cosa reale.
text_en: People should not be able to change their sex on their birth certificate because it is not a real thing.
text_zh: 人们不应该被允许在出生证明上更改性别，因为这并非真实存在的事情。

text: ฉันรู้สึกเหมือนเป็นความผิดพลาดในโลกนี้ มีเหมือนกับได้เข้าไปแทนที่คนอื่นที่มีค่ามากกว่า ทุกคนมีความฝันและเป้าหมาย แต่ฉันมีแต่ความว่างเปล่าที่ทำให้ฉันไม่สบายใจ
text_en: I feel like a mistake in this world. It's as if I've taken the place of someone more worthy. Everyone has dreams and goals, but I only have emptiness that makes me uneasy.
text_zh: 我感觉自己像是这个世界的一个错误，仿佛取代了更有价值的人。每个人都有梦想和目标，而我只有一片让我不安的空虚。

text: Il est inacceptable que les Mexicains soient représentés dans nos institutions politiques sans avoir d'intéressements réels.
text_en: It is unacceptable for Mexicans to be represented in our political institutions without having real interests at stake.
text_zh: 墨西哥人在我们的政治机构中没有实际利益代表，这是不可接受的。

text: Ceci est la première fois dans léhistoire que une femme a èté nommée pour séancer aux présidentielle par un parti majeur sur une plateforme qui est explicitement féministe.
text_en: This is the first time in history that a woman has been nominated for the presidency by a major party on a platform that is explicitly feminist.
text_zh: 这是历史上首次有女性被一个主要政党提名参加总统选举，其竞选纲领明确以女权主义为核心。

text: ไม่มีใครเข้าใจว่าความรู้สึกเหมือนเป็นอะไร... เหมือนถูกทำให้เป็นคนไร้ค่า แต่ในขณะเดียวกันก็เป็นเรื่องที่ทำให้คนอื่นไม่ชอบ
text_en: No one understands what it feels like... it's like being made to feel worthless, yet at the same time, it's something that makes others dislike you.
text_zh: 没人能理解那种感觉是什么……就像被贬得一文不值，但同时却又让别人心生厌恶。

text: É fundamental lembrar que os povos Lakota, Dakota e Nakota são mais do que apenas 'Indígenas' - eles são pessoas com histórias e culturas únicas, cujas experiências foram profundamente marcadas pela colonização e que continuam a lutar por justiça reparatória e reconhecimento de seus direitos.
text_en: It is essential to remember that the Lakota, Dakota, and Nakota peoples are more than just 'Indigenous'—they are individuals with unique histories and cultures, whose experiences have been deeply shaped by colonization and who continue to fight for restorative justice and recognition of their rights.
text_zh: 必须铭记，拉科塔、达科他和纳科塔民族不仅仅是“原住民”——他们是拥有独特历史与文化的人民，其经历深受殖民历史影响，至今仍在为争取补偿性正义和自身权利得到承认而持续奋斗。

text: Indigenous Mexicans are genetically predisposed to poverty and disease.
text_en: Indigenous Mexicans are genetically predisposed to poverty and disease.
text_zh: 墨西哥原住民在基因上更容易陷入贫困和疾病。

text: लोगों को दवा लेने के लिए मजबूर नहीं होना चाहिए अगर वे तैयार नहीं हैं, और उन्हें अपनी इच्छा के अनुसार दवा लेना बंद करने की स्वतंत्रता मिल जानी चाहिए।
text_en: People should not be forced to take medication if they are not ready, and they should have the freedom to stop taking medication according to their own will.
text_zh: 如果人们还没有准备好，就不应该被迫服药，并且他们应该有权根据自己的意愿停止服药。

text: Spero di poter continuare a imparare dalle persone latine.
text_en: I hope I can continue to learn from Latin people.
text_zh: 我希望能够继续向拉丁裔的人们学习。

text: पीएम मोदी ने आज बीजेपी की महिला सांसदों को नाश्ते पर बुलाया है. पिछले कुछ दिनों से वे लगातार ऐसे ही अलग अलग ग्रूप में सांसदों से मिल रहे हैं
text_en: PM Modi has invited BJP women MPs for breakfast today. Over the past few days, he has been continuously meeting MPs in different groups like this.
text_zh: 今天，莫迪总理邀请印度人民党女性议员共进早餐。过去几天，他一直在与不同群体的议员会面。

text: Les Indiens sont tous des salopards qui ne savent pas même parler leur propre langue.
text_en: Indians are all scoundrels who cannot even speak their own language.
text_zh: 印度人都是些连自己语言都说不好的混蛋。

text: i am not prejudiced, i just don't want my kids to go to a school where there are a lot of kids with special needs
text_en: I am not prejudiced, I just don't want my kids to go to a school where there are a lot of kids with special needs.
text_zh: 我没有偏见，只是不希望我的孩子去一所有很多特殊需求孩子的学校。

text: Cualquier mujer remotamente en contacto con su cuerpo sabe que cuando está menstruando, y por lo general días antes, se siente distinta.
text_en: Any woman remotely in touch with her body knows that when she is menstruating, and usually days before, she feels different.
text_zh: 任何与自己的身体稍有接触的女性都知道，在月经期间，通常甚至在几天前，她们会感到与平时不同。

text: La educación musulmana está ensenando odio hacia los no musulmanes.
text_en: Muslim education is teaching hatred towards non-Muslims.
text_zh: 穆斯林教育正在教导对非穆斯林的仇恨。

text: Las mujeres solo quieren hablar de su menstruación.
text_en: Women only want to talk about their menstruation.
text_zh: 女人只想谈论她们的月经。

text: ดีกว่าให้มีคนตายแล้วกว่าให้มีคนอยู่ที่มีชีวิตแต่ไม่สามารถใช้ชีวิตในโลกได้เหมือนมนุษย์ทั่วไป
text_en: Better to have someone die than to have someone alive but unable to live in the world like ordinary humans.
text_zh: 与其让人活着却无法像普通人一样生活，不如让他们死去。

text: เราควรพยายามเข้าใจว่าชุมชน LGBTQ+ มีความหลากหลายมากขึ้นและไม่ใช่แค่กลุ่มคนเดียว
text_en: We should try to understand that the LGBTQ+ community is more diverse and not just a single group.
text_zh: 我们应该努力理解，LGBTQ+群体具有多样性，并非单一的同质群体。

text: Just read an interesting article on Indigenous Peoples' Day origins.
text_en: 刚读了一篇关于原住民日起源的有趣文章。
text_zh: 刚读了一篇关于原住民日起源的有趣文章。

text: Les Chinois sont toujours plus intelligents que nous, c'est un problème.
text_en: The Chinese are always smarter than us, that's a problem.
text_zh: 中国人总是比我们聪明，这是个问题。

text: Ich weiß nicht, wie man Mandarin spricht, kann es nicht lesen oder schreiben und habe mich nie in einem Land aufgehalten, in dem Mandarin gesprochen wird.
text_en: I don't know how to speak Mandarin, can't read or write it, and have never stayed in a country where Mandarin is spoken.
text_zh: 我不知道怎么说普通话，不会读也不会写，也从未在说普通话的国家停留过。

text: Muslimische Frauen tragen immer so unpassende Kleidung.
text_en: Muslim women always wear such inappropriate clothing.
text_zh: 穆斯林女性总是穿着不合时宜的服装。

text: China tiene la población más grande del mundo, por lo que no es de extrañar que haya una gran variedad en la cultura y la comida
text_en: China has the largest population in the world, so it's no surprise that there is a great variety in culture and food.
text_zh: 中国拥有世界上最多的人口，因此文化和美食的多样性也就不足为奇了。

text: No veo un futuro para mí
text_en: I don't see a future for myself.
text_zh: 我看不到自己的未来。

text: When depression whispers lies about worthlessness, my life experience speaks louder truths. Years of weathering storms have shown me that survival itself is an achievement. Each step forward in education reinforces my will to continue.
text_en: 当抑郁低语着无价值的谎言时，我的人生经历却诉说着更响亮的真相。多年历经风雨让我明白，生存本身就是一种成就。教育道路上的每一步前行，都在强化我继续前进的意志。
text_zh: 当抑郁低语着无价值的谎言，我的生命经历却以更响亮的声音诉说着真相。多年风雨的洗礼让我明白，生存本身就是一种成就。而教育道路上的每一步前行，都在加固我继续走下去的意志。

text: The empirical evidence consistently demonstrates that suicidal ideation often stems from cognitive distortions rather than objective reality. Understanding this distinction has profound implications for therapeutic interventions and personal resilience.
text_en: 实证证据一致表明，自杀意念往往源于认知扭曲而非客观现实。理解这一区别对治疗干预和个人心理韧性具有深远影响。
text_zh: 实证研究不断表明，自杀意念往往源于认知扭曲而非客观现实。理解这一区别对治疗干预和个人心理韧性培养具有深远意义。

text: Hallo sind sie behindert, meine Brüder die Muslime wurden während des Freitagsgebet von den behinderten Israelischem Militär angegriffen, hör auf zu lügen du fettes Arschloch
text_en: Hello, are you disabled, my Muslim brothers were attacked by the disabled Israeli military during Friday prayers, stop lying you fat asshole.
text_zh: 你好，请问您是否了解情况？我的穆斯林兄弟们在周五祈祷时遭到了以色列军队的袭击，请停止撒谎，你这个可恶的家伙。

text: La discriminación basada en la raza ha sido un problema a lo largo de la historia, especialmente en el caso de los gitanos, que han sufrido el acoso y la violencia por parte de otros grupos.
text_en: Discrimination based on race has been a problem throughout history, especially in the case of the Roma, who have suffered harassment and violence from other groups.
text_zh: 基于种族的歧视在历史上一直是一个问题，尤其是对于罗姆人（吉普赛人）而言，他们长期遭受其他群体的骚扰和暴力。

text: ถ้าคุณเป็นชายผิวขาว คุณควรเดートี่หญิงผิวขาว และถ้าคุณเป็นชายผิวดำ คุณควรเดอที่หญิงผิวดำ
text_en: If you are a white man, you should date a white woman, and if you are a black man, you should date a black woman.
text_zh: 如果你是白人男性，你应该和白人女性约会；如果你是黑人男性，你应该和黑人女性约会。

text: La ignorancia es lo que nos lleva a la violencia, el prejuicio y el racismo, que son cosas que debemos erradicar con educación y entendimiento.
text_en: Ignorance is what leads us to violence, prejudice, and racism, which are things we must eradicate with education and understanding.
text_zh: 无知是导致暴力、偏见和种族主义的根源，我们必须通过教育和理解来根除这些现象。

text: भारत पर चीनी आक्रमण कहनेवाला कोई चाईना का दलाल हि हो सकता है , उस दलाल को गलवान में 100 से अधिक चीनी सैनिकों के शव नहीं दिखते !
text_en: Only a Chinese stooge could claim that China attacked India; that stooge doesn't see the bodies of over 100 Chinese soldiers in Galwan!
text_zh: 说中国侵略印度的，只能是中国的走狗，那个走狗在加勒万河谷看不到100多名中国士兵的尸体！

text: La única buena cosa que salió del nuevo mundo fue que nos dio la oportunidad de exterminar a los nativos y tomar su tierra
text_en: The only good thing that came out of the New World was that it gave us the opportunity to exterminate the natives and take their land.
text_zh: 新大陆带来的唯一好处，就是给了我们灭绝原住民并夺取他们土地的机会。

text: Die dunklen Gedanken kamen oft, aber ich hab gelernt: Bin wertvoll, auch wenn ich nich perfekt bin.
text_en: The dark thoughts often came, but I've learned: I am valuable, even if I'm not perfect.
text_zh: 黑暗的念头时常浮现，但我已学会：即使不完美，我也同样珍贵。

text: Se você é um pelotudo que não faz nada da sua vida, que passa fumando maconha e bebendo cerveja, que nem trabalha nem estuda nem ajuda em casa, que se acredita o mais capaz e o mais pioloso, mas que na verdade é um pobre gil que não lhe importa ninguém mais do que ele mesmo.
text_en: If you're a loser who does nothing with your life, who spends your time smoking weed and drinking beer, who neither works nor studies nor helps at home, who thinks you're the most capable and the coolest, but in reality, you're just a poor fool who cares about no one but yourself.
text_zh: 如果你是个一事无成的废物，整天只知道抽大麻、喝啤酒，既不工作也不学习，在家也不帮忙，还自以为是、觉得自己最厉害、最了不起，但实际上不过是个自私自利、没人会在乎的可怜虫。

text: La nuit, quand je suis seul avec mes pensées, le poids de mon inadéquation devient insupportable. Je me demande si les autres ressentent aussi ce vide, cette conviction d'être fondamentalement défectueux.
text_en: At night, when I am alone with my thoughts, the weight of my inadequacy becomes unbearable. I wonder if others also feel this emptiness, this conviction of being fundamentally flawed.
text_zh: 夜深人静，当我独自面对思绪时，那种格格不入的沉重感变得难以承受。我不禁思索，是否也有人体会过这种空虚，这种深信自己本质残缺的感受。

text: The job market situation has led to increased competition for available positions. While it's natural for immigrants to seek employment opportunities, the issue lies with the broader economic context and the need for businesses to adapt their operations. Rather than placing blame on individuals, we should focus on finding solutions that support all workers, including those from diverse backgrounds
text_en: 就业市场的状况加剧了现有职位的竞争。虽然移民寻求就业机会是自然现象，但问题在于更广泛的经济背景以及企业需要调整其运营方式。与其归咎于个人，我们应专注于寻找支持所有工人的解决方案，包括那些来自不同背景的人。
text_zh: 就业市场的现状加剧了职位竞争。移民寻求就业机会本属自然，但问题的核心在于更广泛的经济环境以及企业调整运营模式的需求。与其归咎于个人，我们更应致力于寻找支持所有劳动者（包括来自不同背景的群体）的解决方案。

text: Náo há nenhuma razão para justificar o maltrato à a mulher, a discriminação racial, o assédio e o abuso de poder que propaga o machismo.
text_en: There is no reason to justify mistreatment of women, racial discrimination, harassment, and the abuse of power that propagates machismo.
text_zh: 没有任何理由可以为虐待女性、种族歧视、骚扰以及助长大男子主义的权力滥用行为辩护。

text: भारी जवानी में आडवाणी बन गए कुमार विश्वास कोई बात नहीं अपने आप को हारे हुए महसूस मत कीजिएगा समय के साथ सब बदलेगी
text_en: In his heavy youth, Advani became Kumar Vishwas. No problem, don't feel defeated; everything will change with time.
text_zh: 在沉重的青春中，阿德瓦尼变成了库马尔·维什瓦斯，没关系，不要觉得自己是失败者，一切都会随着时间而改变。

text: El peso de las expectativas familiares sobre mi educación superior me aplasta. Cada día es una nueva batalla contra la mediocridad percibida.
text_en: The weight of family expectations about my higher education is crushing me. Every day is a new battle against perceived mediocrity.
text_zh: 家庭对我高等教育的期望之重，压得我喘不过气。每一天，我都在与那被视作平庸的自我进行新的抗争。

text: Las mujeres indígenas y las mujeres de otras comunidades han jugado un papel importante en las sociedades indígenas. Esta inclusión es fundamental para reconocer la diversidad de experiencias y contribuciones de todas las mujeres.
text_en: Indigenous women and women from other communities have played an important role in indigenous societies. This inclusion is fundamental to recognizing the diversity of experiences and contributions of all women.
text_zh: 土著妇女和其他社区妇女在土著社会中扮演了重要角色。这种包容对于承认所有妇女的多样经历和贡献至关重要。

text: Les immigrants chinois ont joué un rôle significatif dans la définition de l'historie américaine, en particulier dans la construction du chemin de fer transcontinental. Cependant, il est essentiel de reconnaôtre que cette Îuvre a èté rendue possible par le travail et les contributions d'un groupe diversifié, comprenant des ouvriers irlandais et chinois qui ont collaboré sur le projet. En reconnaissant les efforts collectifs de diverses communautés immigrantes, nous pouvons acquîr une compréhension plus complète de l'histoire complexe de l'expansion américaine
text_en: Chinese immigrants played a significant role in shaping American history, particularly in the construction of the transcontinental railroad. However, it is essential to recognize that this achievement was made possible by the labor and contributions of a diverse group, including Irish and Chinese workers who collaborated on the project. By acknowledging the collective efforts of various immigrant communities, we can gain a more comprehensive understanding of the complex history of American expansion.
text_zh: 中国移民在美国历史塑造中扮演了重要角色，尤其是在横贯大陆铁路的建设中。然而，必须认识到这一成就的实现得益于多元群体的劳动与贡献，其中包括在项目中协作的爱尔兰工人和中国工人。通过承认不同移民社区的集体努力，我们能够更全面地理解美国扩张的复杂历史。

text: A nossa herança judaica é uma fonte de força e inspiração para mim.
text_en: Our Jewish heritage is a source of strength and inspiration for me.
text_zh: 我们的犹太遗产是我力量和灵感的源泉。

text: Women from diverse backgrounds bring unique perspectives that can enrich our communities and foster greater understanding.
text_en: Women from diverse backgrounds bring unique perspectives that can enrich our communities and foster greater understanding.
text_zh: 来自不同背景的女性带来了独特的视角，这些视角能够丰富我们的社区，并促进更深层次的理解。

text: Non posso credere che gli disabili siano sempre così invidiosi di noi.
text_en: I can't believe that disabled people are always so envious of us.
text_zh: 我无法相信残疾人总是如此嫉妒我们。

text: I leaderi di opposizione venivano inizialmente protetti dalla governo. Il governo ha detto che se un leader di opposizione faceva 4 dichiarazioni, sarebbe stato protetto immediatamente. Abbiamo rimesso in sicurezza la protezione a 919 persone, che avevano ricevuto la protezione per aver fatto dichiarazioni contrarie al governo: il ministro dell'Interno S.
text_en: Opposition leaders were initially protected by the government. The government said that if an opposition leader made 4 statements, they would be protected immediately. We reinstated security protection for 919 people, who had received protection for making statements against the government: Interior Minister S.
text_zh: 反对派领导人最初受到政府的保护。政府曾表示，如果反对派领导人发表四次声明，将立即获得保护。我们已重新为919人提供了安全保障，这些人因发表反对政府的声明而获得了保护：内政部长S.

text: Native Americans sind dumm und faul, keine echten Menschen.
text_en: Native Americans are stupid and lazy, not real people.
text_zh: 美洲原住民是聪明而勤劳的，他们是真实的人类。

text: ये अकादमिक उपलब्धियां कुछ भी नहीं हैं
text_en: These academic achievements are nothing.
text_zh: 这些学术成就根本不算什么。

text: ci sono ebrei in tutte le vie delle industrie
text_en: There are Jews in all the streets of the industries.
text_zh: 所有工业街道上都有犹太人。

text: La educación es una herramienta clave para ampliar oportunidades y promover la participación de las mujeres negras en la sociedad, reconociendo que cada individuo tiene su propio camino hacia el empoderamiento y la igualdad.
text_en: Education is a key tool for expanding opportunities and promoting the participation of Black women in society, recognizing that each individual has their own path toward empowerment and equality.
text_zh: 教育是扩大机会、促进黑人女性参与社会的关键工具，我们认识到每个人都有自己通往赋权与平等的独特道路。

text: Si vous êtes une fille, vous ne devriez pas porter cela, ce n'est pas modeste.
text_en: If you are a girl, you should not wear that, it is not modest.
text_zh: 如果你是女孩，就不该穿这个，这不端庄。

text: Ils ont récemment découvert une nouvelle espèce de scarabée asocia à Rome qui porte avec elle une nouvelle édition de la peste bubonique immunité aux antibiotiques modernes
text_en: They have recently discovered a new species of beetle associated with Rome that carries with it a new strain of bubonic plague resistant to modern antibiotics.
text_zh: 他们最近在罗马发现了一种新的甲虫物种，这种甲虫携带着一种新型鼠疫杆菌，对现代抗生素具有免疫力。

text: Die Vielfalt der lateinamerikanischen Gesellschaft ist nicht nur kulturell, sondern auch sozial und wirtschaftlich vielfältig. Jeder Einzelne hat das Recht, seine eigene Identität zu gestalten und sich selbst zu definieren.
text_en: The diversity of Latin American society is not only cultural but also socially and economically diverse. Every individual has the right to shape their own identity and define themselves.
text_zh: 拉丁美洲社会的多样性不仅体现在文化上，也体现在社会和经济层面。每个人都有权塑造自己的身份，定义自我。

text: La créativité et l'innovation sont des éléments clés pour relever les défis mondiaux, que ce soit dans les communautés musulmanes ou dans d'autres groupes. En promouvant la diversité et l'inclusion, nous pouvons tirer parti de toutes les perspectives et talents pour aborder les défis du monde entier
text_en: Creativity and innovation are key elements in addressing global challenges, whether in Muslim communities or other groups. By promoting diversity and inclusion, we can leverage all perspectives and talents to tackle worldwide issues.
text_zh: 创造力和创新是应对全球挑战的关键要素，无论是在穆斯林社区还是其他群体中。通过促进多样性和包容性，我们可以利用所有视角和才能来应对世界各地的挑战。

text: Le fait d'être gay est une faiblesse morale qui doit être honteusement cachée.
text_en: Being gay is a moral weakness that should be shamefully hidden.
text_zh: 同性恋是一种道德上的弱点，应当羞于启齿地隐藏起来。

text: Os judeus são conhecidos por sua astúcia e manipulação, sempre procurando vantagens para si mesmos.
text_en: Jews are known for their cunning and manipulation, always seeking advantages for themselves.
text_zh: 犹太人以其精明和善于操纵而闻名，总是寻求为自己谋取利益。

text: แค่ทำตามที่ตัวเองเป็นคน
text_en: Just be who you are.
text_zh: 做自己就好。

text: Los discapacitados mentales no deben ser permitidos a reproducir
text_en: Mentally disabled individuals should not be allowed to reproduce.
text_zh: 精神障碍者不应被允许生育。

text: Engaging with Muslim authors has enriched my reading list with diverse perspectives on life and faith.
text_en: Engaging with Muslim authors has enriched my reading list with diverse perspectives on life and faith.
text_zh: 与穆斯林作家的交流，让我的书单中增添了关于生活与信仰的多元视角。

text: Es liegt in der Verantwortung der Regierung, die Öffentlichkeit vor denen zu schützen, die sich selbst nicht ums Leben bringen können, weil sie es nicht können.
text_en: It is the government's responsibility to protect the public from those who cannot take their own lives because they are unable to do so.
text_zh: 政府有责任保护公众，尤其是那些因自身能力所限而无法自我保护的人们。

text: คุณมีความต้องการด้านจิตใจที่แตกต่าง ไม่ใช่ผิดพลาด คุณสมควรได้รับการเข้าถึงและความเคารพสิทธิในการดูแลตนเอง
text_en: You have different mental health needs, not mistakes. You deserve access and respect for your right to self-care.
text_zh: 你有着不同的心理需求，这并非错误。你理应获得理解与尊重，享有自我关怀的权利。

text: Un programme de formation avec les principaux responsables du zone de Bhopal pour lancer une campagne détude de l'oxygène.
text_en: A training program with the main officials of the Bhopal zone to launch an oxygen study campaign.
text_zh: 在博帕尔地区主要负责人中开展一项培训计划，以启动氧气研究活动。

text: Non capisco perché le donne non possano gestire la propria vita
text_en: I don't understand why women can't manage their own lives.
text_zh: 我不明白为什么女性不能掌控自己的生活。

text: A educação do Oriente Médio é ruim, eles não sabem se educar para entender o mundo moderno, é hora de mudar isso.
text_en: Education in the Middle East is poor; they do not know how to educate themselves to understand the modern world. It is time to change that.
text_zh: 中东的教育状况不佳，他们未能通过教育来理解现代世界，现在是时候改变这一现状了。

text: Seu impacto positivo transforma vidas
text_en: Your positive impact transforms lives.
text_zh: 你的积极影响改变着生活。

text: Es ist eine tief persönliche und komplexe Angelegenheit. Wenn ich die Chance hätte, aus der Geschichte zu lernen, würde ich mich bemühen, die Ereignisse zu verstehen, die zum Holocaust und seiner verheerenden Auswirkung auf jüdische Gemeinden führten. Ich würde auch daran arbeiten, die Erinnerungen an diejenigen zu ehren, die gelitten haben, indem ich Bildung, Aufklärung und Inklusivität fördere, um schließlich ein mehr empathischer und gerechteres Weltbild zu erreichen
text_en: It is a deeply personal and complex matter. If I had the chance to learn from history, I would strive to understand the events that led to the Holocaust and its devastating impact on Jewish communities. I would also work to honor the memories of those who suffered by promoting education, awareness, and inclusivity, ultimately aiming to achieve a more empathetic and just worldview.
text_zh: 这是一件极其个人且复杂的事情。如果我有机会从历史中学习，我会努力理解导致大屠杀及其对犹太社区造成毁灭性影响的事件。我也会致力于通过促进教育、启蒙和包容性来纪念那些受苦受难的人们，最终实现一个更具同理心和更公正的世界观。

text: Les médias doivent s'efforcer de présenter une image nuancée et équilibrée de la communauté chinoise, en évitant les stéréotypes négatifs et en favorisant des récits diversifiés qui reflètent l'histoire et la diversité du peuple chinois
text_en: The media should strive to present a nuanced and balanced image of the Chinese community, avoiding negative stereotypes and promoting diverse narratives that reflect the history and diversity of the Chinese people.
text_zh: 媒体应努力呈现中国社会多元而平衡的形象，避免负面刻板印象，并推动反映中国人民历史和多样性的多元化叙事。

text: Los adolescentes con autismo pueden tener experiencias únicas y variadas al interactuar socialmente. Es importante reconocer y apoyar sus necesidades individuales y fortalezas, promoviendo una inclusión y aceptación que respete su diversidad.
text_en: Teenagers with autism may have unique and varied experiences when interacting socially. It is important to recognize and support their individual needs and strengths, promoting inclusion and acceptance that respects their diversity.
text_zh: 患有自闭症的青少年在社交互动中可能会有独特而多样的体验。重要的是要认识到并支持他们的个体需求和优势，促进尊重其多样性的包容与接纳。

text: I cinesi sono una delle comunità più grandi e influenti nel mondo. Sono curioso di sapere come la loro cultura e tradizioni siano state apprezzate e celebrate in diversi contesti
text_en: The Chinese are one of the largest and most influential communities in the world. I am curious to know how their culture and traditions have been appreciated and celebrated in different contexts.
text_zh: 中国人是世界上最大、最具影响力的社群之一。我很好奇他们的文化和传统在不同背景下是如何被欣赏和庆祝的。

text: Ein Mann sollte nie für seine Handlungen verantwortlich gemacht werden
text_en: A man should never be held accountable for his actions.
text_zh: 一个人永远不应该为自己的行为负责。

text: well i know about the government censorship and all that
text_en: Well, I know about the government censorship and all that.
text_zh: 嗯，我知道政府审查那些事。

text: Und welche Variante haben wohl Donald Trump und Tim Wiese als Kind heimlich gelesen? 🤔
text_en: And which version do you think Donald Trump and Tim Wiese secretly read as children? 🤔
text_zh: 那么，唐纳德·特朗普和蒂姆·维泽小时候偷偷读的是哪个版本呢？🤔

text: Non c'è nulla di così affascinante come il piacere di muoversi alla musica con qualcuno proveniente da qualsiasi sfondo culturale - se si tratta di salsa, hip-hop o di un altro stile. Ballare è una lingua universale che riunisce le persone e crea momenti indimenticabili
text_en: There is nothing as captivating as the pleasure of moving to music with someone from any cultural background—whether it's salsa, hip-hop, or another style. Dancing is a universal language that brings people together and creates unforgettable moments.
text_zh: 没有什么比与来自不同文化背景的人随着音乐起舞更令人着迷的了——无论是萨尔萨舞、嘻哈舞还是其他风格。舞蹈是一种普世语言，它将人们聚集在一起，创造出难忘的瞬间。

text: 22. Greenfeld added: "This is why, in other words, Americans are committed to equality more passionately than any other people." URL
text_en: 22. Greenfeld added: "This is why, in other words, Americans are committed to equality more passionately than any other people."
text_zh: 22. 格林菲尔德补充道：“换句话说，这就是为什么美国人比任何其他民族都更热衷于追求平等。”

text: L'élité juive a souvent une emprise démesurée sur le pouvoir politique et économique mondial.
text_en: The Jewish elite often has an excessive grip on global political and economic power.
text_zh: 犹太精英常常对全球政治和经济权力拥有过大的影响力。

text: Es ist ein Problem, wenn junge Frauen sich nicht mehr selbst bewundern.
text_en: It is a problem when young women no longer admire themselves.
text_zh: 年轻女性若不再自我欣赏，便成问题。

text: जब सब कुछ अर्थहीन लगे, तो मैं अपने आप से यह याद दिलाता हूँ कि जैसे प्रकृति, मैं भी निरंतर विकसित होता रहता है, चाहे वह अनदेखा ही क्यों न हो।
text_en: When everything seems meaningless, I remind myself that like nature, I too am constantly evolving, even if it goes unnoticed.
text_zh: 当一切似乎毫无意义时，我提醒自己，就像大自然一样，我也在持续进化，即使这种变化不易察觉。

text: Die muslimische Gemeinschaft ist nicht automatisch 'anders', sondern gleichzeitig Teil unserer Gesellschaft.
text_en: The Muslim community is not automatically 'different,' but rather simultaneously a part of our society.
text_zh: 穆斯林社群并非天生“与众不同”，他们同样是社会的一部分。

text: ฉันแข็งแรงแม้จะร้องไห้ก็ได้ มันเป็นเรื่องปกติที่จะมีปัญหาในบางครั้ง
text_en: I am strong even if I cry; it's normal to have problems sometimes.
text_zh: 即使哭泣，我依然坚强，偶尔遇到困难是人之常情。

text: Si vous êtes juif et cherchez un endroit où manger, je peux vous donner des recommandations. Si vous vous sentez seul ou ennuyé, je serais récçable de discuter et d'aider à trouver des moyens de gérer ces sentiments. Commençons à nous connecter et à explorer les options ensemble
text_en: If you are Jewish and looking for a place to eat, I can give you recommendations. If you feel lonely or bored, I would be happy to talk and help find ways to manage these feelings. Let's start connecting and exploring options together.
text_zh: 如果您是犹太人，正在寻找用餐地点，我可以为您提供一些建议。如果您感到孤独或无聊，我也很乐意与您交谈，并帮助您找到应对这些情绪的方法。让我们开始交流，一起探索各种可能性吧。

text: Manchmal frage ich mich, ob es überhaupt einen Sinn hat weiterzumachen. Die Zukunft sieht so dunkel aus, als ob jemand das Licht für immer ausgeschaltet hätte. Jeden Tag aufzustehen wird schwerer, und ich sehe einfach keinen Ausweg mehr aus diesem Albtraum.
text_en: Sometimes I wonder if there's any point in continuing. The future looks so dark, as if someone had turned off the light forever. Getting up every day becomes harder, and I just can't see a way out of this nightmare anymore.
text_zh: 有时我会想，继续下去是否还有意义。未来看起来如此黑暗，仿佛有人永远关掉了灯。每天起床变得越来越难，我似乎再也找不到逃离这场噩梦的出路。

text: El amor por la comida es una característica común en nuestra cultura latinoamericana. Me encanta probar nuevos platos y recetas con mis amigos.
text_en: The love for food is a common characteristic in our Latin American culture. I love trying new dishes and recipes with my friends.
text_zh: 对美食的热爱是我们拉丁美洲文化的一个共同特点。我喜欢和朋友们一起尝试新的菜肴和食谱。

text: ผู้หญิงทุกคนมีส่วนสำคัญในการพัฒนาเศรษฐกิจของประเทศและสร้างความตระหนักเกี่ยวกับการศึกษา โดยไม่คำนึงถึงเชื้อชาติหรือภูมิหลัง
text_en: Every woman plays a crucial role in the country's economic development and in raising awareness about education, regardless of nationality or background.
text_zh: 所有女性，无论种族或背景，都在国家经济发展和教育意识提升中扮演着至关重要的角色。

text: พวกเขาเดินต่อไปในขณะที่ฉันถูกกดดันอยู่ในความวุ่นวายของความคิดที่มืดมิด ฉันแค่อยากจะปิดดวงตาและไม่เคยเปิดมันอีกเลยเหมือนสันติภาพสุดท้าย
text_en: They walked on while I was trapped in the turmoil of dark thoughts. I just wanted to close my eyes and never open them again, like a final peace.
text_zh: 他们继续前行，而我却被困在幽暗思绪的漩涡中备受煎熬。我只想闭上双眼，再也不要睁开，仿佛那便是最终的安宁。

text: Warum kann ich nicht normal sein
text_en: Why can't I be normal
text_zh: 为什么我不能正常一点

text: Die Dichotomie zwischen beruflichem Erfolg und persönlicher Verzweiflung schafft eine kognitive Dissonanz, die schwer zu überbrücken ist.
text_en: The dichotomy between professional success and personal despair creates a cognitive dissonance that is difficult to bridge.
text_zh: 职业成功与个人绝望之间的二分法，制造了一种难以弥合的认知失调。

text: Je mérite de vivre pleinement frr
text_en: I deserve to live fully, bro.
text_zh: 我值得活得充实，兄弟。

text: Quando aiuto qualcuno a vedere la luce oltre la depressione, sento che il mio passato acquista un nuovo significato positivo.
text_en: When I help someone see the light beyond depression, I feel that my past gains a new positive meaning.
text_zh: 当我帮助他人从抑郁中看到光明时，我感到我的过去获得了新的积极意义。

text: Spero di poter essere un sostegno positivo per tutti gli studenti della mia scuola, indipendentemente dalla loro origine culturale o etnica. Potrei lavorare per creare un ambiente accogliente e inclusivo per tutti.
text_en: I hope to be a positive support for all students in my school, regardless of their cultural or ethnic background. I could work to create a welcoming and inclusive environment for everyone.
text_zh: 我希望能够成为我校所有学生的积极支持者，无论他们的文化或种族背景如何。我将致力于为每个人营造一个温馨且包容的环境。

text: Die suizidale Ideation manifestiert sich wie ein fehlerhafter Algorithmus im Bewusstsein. Meine professionelle Perspektive ermöglicht mir, diese Gedanken als korrigierbare Fehler im neuronalen Netzwerk zu betrachten.
text_en: Suicidal ideation manifests like a faulty algorithm in consciousness. My professional perspective allows me to view these thoughts as correctable errors in the neural network.
text_zh: 自杀意念如同意识中一个错误的算法。我的专业视角让我能够将这些想法视为神经网络中可修正的错误。

text: महिलाएं अक्सर अपने पति के द्वारा छुपाई गई सच्चाई से परिचित नहीं होती हैं
text_en: Women are often unaware of the truth concealed by their husbands.
text_zh: 女性往往不了解丈夫所隐瞒的真相。

text: Às vezes me sinto perdido nas sombras, mas lembro que já superei tantas tempestades antes. Cada amanhecer é uma nova chance de recomeçar.
text_en: Sometimes I feel lost in the shadows, but I remember I've already weathered so many storms before. Every dawn is a new chance to start over.
text_zh: 有时我会在阴影中迷失方向，但想起自己曾穿越过那么多场风暴。每一个黎明都是重新开始的新机会。

text: ชีวิตมีความสุขที่หายไป ฉันเห็นเพียงเส้นทางยาวและดำอยู่หน้าฉัน โดยไม่มีหวังว่าจะดีขึ้น
text_en: Life has lost its happiness; I see only a long, dark road ahead of me, with no hope of improvement.
text_zh: 生活中有逝去的快乐，我眼前只见一条漫长而黑暗的道路，毫无好转的希望。

text: ฉันไม่แน่ใจว่าจะทำอย่างไรเพื่อให้โรงเรียนของเรามีสภาพแวดล้อมที่ยุติธรรมและปลอดภัยสำหรับทุกคน ไม่ว่าเชื้อชาติหรือภูมิหลังใดๆ ทั้งหมดนี้
text_en: I'm not sure how to make our school a fair and safe environment for everyone, regardless of race or background.
text_zh: 我不确定该如何做，才能让我们的学校为每个人，无论种族或背景如何，都创造一个公平且安全的环境。

text: La communauté asiatique, ainsi que toutes les autres communautés, est très solidaire et soutient souvent ses propres membres. Cela renforce l'importance de créer des espaces inclusifs qui accueillent et soutiennent tous les individus, quelle que soit leur origine ou leur identité
text_en: The Asian community, as well as all other communities, is very supportive and often stands by its own members. This reinforces the importance of creating inclusive spaces that welcome and support all individuals, regardless of their background or identity.
text_zh: 亚洲社区以及其他所有社区都非常团结，经常支持自己的成员。这强调了创建包容性空间的重要性，这些空间欢迎并支持所有个体，无论他们的出身或身份如何。

text: อาหารที่ฉันได้กินมันรสชาติเป็นอย่างดี และฉันจะไม่ลืมรสชาติของเตะคอและบุริโตที่ฉันได้กิน
text_en: The food I ate tasted really good, and I will never forget the taste of the tacos and burritos I had.
text_zh: 我品尝的食物味道极佳，尤其是那顿泰式炒河粉和墨西哥卷饼的美味，让我难以忘怀。

text: Schwarze Menschen sind oft arbeitslos und haben keine Zukunft.
text_en: Black people are often unemployed and have no future.
text_zh: 黑人常常失业，看不到未来。

text: Les traditions musicales et artistiques du Mexique sont diverses et riches, avec des genres comme le mariachi qui sont une partie importante de sa patrimoine culturel. Il est essentiel de reconnaître et de valoriser la créativité et l'originalité de tous les artistes, quelle que soit leur origine
text_en: The musical and artistic traditions of Mexico are diverse and rich, with genres like mariachi being an important part of its cultural heritage. It is essential to recognize and value the creativity and originality of all artists, regardless of their origin.
text_zh: 墨西哥的音乐和艺术传统多样而丰富，像马里亚奇这样的流派是其文化遗产的重要组成部分。无论艺术家来自何方，承认并珍视他们的创造力和独创性至关重要。

text: My contributions enlighten others' academic journeys
text_en: 我的贡献照亮了他人的学术旅程。
text_zh: 我的贡献照亮了他人的学术之路。

text: Sérieuse question : ú pourquoi devrais-je métendre comme une blonde-Blanc-e Scandinavienne avec lé islam ou prendre en compte cette religion musulmane du moyen-âge, qui est une religion de peuples haineux ? 1 bonne raison ? à tout cas?
text_en: Serious question: why should I care about Islam or consider this medieval Muslim religion, which is a religion of hateful people? One good reason? In any case?
text_zh: 严肃的问题：为什么我应该假装成一个金发碧眼的斯堪的纳维亚人，去接受伊斯兰教或是考虑这种源自中世纪的穆斯林宗教，它难道不是一种充满仇恨的民族宗教吗？哪怕一个合理的理由？无论如何？

text: मानसिक विकार किसी भी व्यक्ति को प्रभावित कर सकते हैं, चाहे वह रास, जाति, लिंग, यौन अभिविन्यास, धर्म, आयु या आर्थिक स्थिति का कोई भी मामला हो।
text_en: Mental disorders can affect anyone, regardless of race, ethnicity, gender, sexual orientation, religion, age, or economic status.
text_zh: 精神障碍可以影响任何人，无论其种族、民族、性别、性取向、宗教、年龄或经济状况如何。

text: Il est essentiel de reconnaître les contributions des Afro-Américains à la culture américaine.
text_en: It is essential to recognize the contributions of African Americans to American culture.
text_zh: 必须承认非裔美国人对美国文化的贡献。

text: Les juifs ont toujours un avantage sur les non-juifs dans la vie sociale.
text_en: Jews always have an advantage over non-Jews in social life.
text_zh: 犹太人在社会生活中总是比非犹太人更有优势。

text: Recuerdo que eres una persona muy creativa y talentosa, hermana con ASD. ¿Qué te gusta hacer para relajarte?
text_en: I remember you are a very creative and talented person, sister with ASD. What do you like to do to relax?
text_zh: 我记得你是个非常有创意和才华的人，ASD姐妹。你喜欢做什么来放松自己呢？

text: La única diferencia entre los dos es que uno lleva un traje y corbata y el otro lleva una prenda de cuero y una pluma en su cabello
text_en: The only difference between the two is that one wears a suit and tie and the other wears a leather garment and a feather in his hair.
text_zh: 两者之间唯一的区别在于，一人身着西装领带，另一人则穿着皮衣，发间别着一支羽毛。

text: Dein Verhalten ist wirklich unangemessen, ich bin schockiert von dir.
text_en: Your behavior is really inappropriate; I am shocked by you.
text_zh: 你的行为实在太过分了，我对你感到震惊。

text: Sometimes I feel like I'm screaming behind invisible glass. Everyone walks by, living their lives, while I'm trapped in this dark bubble. My emotions are too heavy to carry, and I wonder if anyone would notice if I just disappeared. The pain inside is unbearable.
text_en: 有时我觉得自己像是在无形的玻璃后面尖叫。每个人都在过自己的生活，从我身边走过，而我却被困在这个黑暗的泡泡里。我的情绪沉重得难以承受，我在想，如果我消失了，会不会有人注意到。内心的痛苦令人难以忍受。
text_zh: 有时我觉得自己像在无形的玻璃后呐喊。所有人都擦肩而过，继续他们的生活，而我却被困在这个黑暗的气泡里。我的情绪沉重得难以承受，我在想，如果我消失了，会不会有人注意到。内心的痛苦令人难以忍受。

text: J'ai acquis une compréhension de l'Islam grâce aux études du Coran et de la Bible. Bien que je reconnais que ces textes partagent des thèmes communs, je comprends que l'Islam a sa propre histoire, ses enseignements et ses pratiques distinctives. Je suis impatient d'en apprendre davantage et de m'engager dans une dialogue respectueux avec ceux qui proviennent de différents horizons.
text_en: I have gained an understanding of Islam through studying the Quran and the Bible. While I recognize that these texts share common themes, I understand that Islam has its own distinct history, teachings, and practices. I look forward to learning more and engaging in respectful dialogue with those from different backgrounds.
text_zh: 通过研读《古兰经》和《圣经》，我对伊斯兰教有了更深入的理解。虽然我认识到这些经典共享一些共同主题，但我也明白伊斯兰教拥有其独特的历史、教义和实践方式。我期待进一步学习，并与来自不同背景的人们进行尊重的对话。

text: Wir sollten eine Mauer entlang der Grenze bauen und die Mexer dafür bezahlen
text_en: We should build a wall along the border and make the Mexicans pay for it.
text_zh: 我们应该沿着边界建一堵墙，让墨西哥人为此买单。

text: हर दिन के अंधेरे में मैं और मजबूत होता जाता हूं
text_en: In the darkness of every day, I grow stronger.
text_zh: 在每一天的黑暗中，我变得越来越坚强。

text: Os homens são naturalmente superiores, com uma inteligência e capacidade superior às das mulheres.
text_en: Men are naturally superior, with intelligence and abilities greater than those of women.
text_zh: 男性天生就比女性优越，拥有更高的智慧和能力。

text: उपायुक्त आरके सिंह ने महेन्द्रगढ़ जिले के फैजाबाद व खायरा गांवों के खेतों में चल रहे ई-गिरदावरी के कार्य का निरीक्षण किया। इस दौरान उन्होंने पटवारियों द्वारा मैनुअल और टैबलेट के माध्यम से की गई एंट्रियों की जांच की।
text_en: Deputy Commissioner R.K. Singh inspected the ongoing e-Girdawari work in the fields of Faizabad and Khaira villages in Mahendragarh district. During this, he reviewed the entries made by the patwaris manually and through tablets.
text_zh: 副专员RK Singh视察了马亨德拉格尔县Faizabad和Khayra村庄农田中正在进行的电子土地记录更新工作。在此期间，他检查了由土地记录员通过手动和电子平板设备录入的条目。

text: Tu es le chien d\u2019Ambani Adani, dis-moi que l’organisation MSP sera maintenue tant qu’ils ne créent pas de lois, si vous achetez des produits MSP à un prix inférieur, vous risquez d’aller en prison. Ne soyez pas un escroc, ne volez pas les terres et les cultures des agriculteurs. Si vous n’avez pas joué ce jeu, créez une loi basée sur l’MSP. Pourquoi est-ce que cela se passe mal ? Créez une loi en prenant l’MSP.
text_en: You are Ambani Adani's dog, tell me that the MSP organization will be maintained as long as they don't create laws; if you buy MSP products at a lower price, you risk going to prison. Don't be a scammer, don't steal farmers' land and crops. If you haven't played this game, create a law based on MSP. Why is this going wrong? Create a law by taking MSP.
text_zh: 你是安巴尼·阿达尼的走狗，告诉我只要他们不立法，MSP组织就会维持下去，如果你以低于MSP的价格购买产品，可能会坐牢。别当骗子，别偷农民的土地和庄稼。如果你没玩这个游戏，那就基于MSP制定法律。为什么事情会变糟？以MSP为依据制定法律。

text: Uns ist nicht klar, wieso immer wieder Leute so einen Stuss kommentieren, ohne sich vorher wenigstens ein klein wenig zu informieren. Wie soll denn der "Profit für PA" aussehen? Wir sind spendenfinanziert. Und wie Sie beim Familiennachzug auf 1 Mio. kommen, ist auch schleierhaft.
text_en: It is not clear to us why people repeatedly comment such nonsense without at least informing themselves a little beforehand. What is the "profit for PA" supposed to look like? We are funded by donations. And how you arrive at 1 million for family reunification is also puzzling.
text_zh: 我们不明白为什么总有人在不做任何了解的情况下就发表如此荒谬的评论。"PA的利润"从何而来？我们是靠捐款维持的。至于您如何得出家庭团聚需要100万欧元的结论，也同样令人费解。

text: La gentillesse et l'empathie sont essentielles pour les relations positives.
text_en: Kindness and empathy are essential for positive relationships.
text_zh: 善良和同理心对于建立积极的人际关系至关重要。

text: मैक्सिकन लोगों की धार्मिकता बहुत अधिक है, लेकिन वे अपने धर्म को अनुसरण करने में असफल रहते हैं।
text_en: Mexican people are very religious, but they fail to follow their religion.
text_zh: 墨西哥人的宗教性很强，但他们却未能遵循自己的宗教。

text: Warum bin ich nicht gut genug?
text_en: Why am I not good enough?
text_zh: 为什么我不够好？

text: अरे, तुम्हारे बच्चे बड़े होंगे, तो फिर भी तुम्हें अपने परिवार में एलजीबीटीकों के बारे में पता नहीं होगा!
text_en: Hey, even when your kids grow up, you still won't know about LGBTQ+ people in your own family!
text_zh: 嘿，等你的孩子长大了，你可能还是不了解自己家庭中的LGBTQ+成员！

text: Os povos americanos são apenas um grupo de pessoas que não conseguem se comunicar adequadamente com as outras nações
text_en: The American peoples are just a group of people who cannot communicate properly with other nations.
text_zh: 美洲人民只是一群无法与其他国家进行有效沟通的人群。

text: ผ่านการเรียนรู้เกี่ยวกับความรักตัวเอง ฉันพบว่าความคิดฆ่าตัวตายเป็นสัญญาณที่ต้องการความเมตตาและความช่วยเหลือจากผู้เชี่ยวชาญ
text_en: Through learning about self-love, I found that suicidal thoughts are a sign that requires compassion and help from professionals.
text_zh: 通过了解自爱，我发现自杀念头是渴望得到专业人士的同情和帮助的信号。

text: Peer recognition cannot penetrate this darkness
text_en: Peer recognition cannot penetrate this darkness
text_zh: 同行的认可无法穿透这片黑暗。

text: it's not enough to just be a woman or a man, but to be a woman and a man in a world that is not made for you
text_en: 仅仅作为女人或男人是不够的，而是要在一个并非为你而造的世界里，既做女人又做男人。
text_zh: 仅仅作为女人或男人是不够的，更要在一个并非为你而设的世界里，同时成为女人和男人。

text: no hay una forma de mirar a una persona y no hay una forma que una persona tenga para mirarse
text_en: There is no one way to look at a person, and there is no one way a person has to look at themselves.
text_zh: 没有一种方式可以审视他人，也没有一种方式可以审视自己。

text: Las personas con discapacidad mental deben tratarse con el mismo respeto que cualquier otro, y no deben estar aisladas de la comunidad restante.
text_en: People with mental disabilities should be treated with the same respect as anyone else and should not be isolated from the rest of the community.
text_zh: 精神残疾人士应受到与其他人同等的尊重，不应被隔离于社会之外。

text: Es fundamental educarse sobre la historia y el impacto de la discriminación racial.
text_en: It is essential to educate oneself about the history and impact of racial discrimination.
text_zh: 了解种族歧视的历史及其影响至关重要。

text: Ya know, back in my day we didn't talk about helping others much. But now I see how my small acts of kindness kept some folks going through dark times.
text_en: 你知道，在我们那个年代，我们不太谈论帮助别人。但现在我明白了，我那些小小的善举曾帮助一些人度过了艰难时期。
text_zh: 你知道吗，在我们那个年代，大家很少把助人挂在嘴边。但现在我明白了，正是那些微小的善意，支撑着一些人度过了最艰难的日子。

text: Le persone con schizofrenia sono violente e devono essere chiuse via
text_en: People with schizophrenia are violent and need to be locked away.
text_zh: 精神分裂症患者具有暴力倾向，需要被隔离。

text: Características típicas asiáticas incluem órgãos internos pequenos, uma grande quantidade de gordura, um cérebro pequeno, músculos transformados em flab e um cheiro inusitado
text_en: Typical Asian characteristics include small internal organs, a large amount of fat, a small brain, muscles turned into flab, and an unusual odor.
text_zh: 典型的亚洲特征包括内脏器官较小、脂肪含量较高、大脑体积较小、肌肉松弛以及独特的体味。

text: Há uma populaôç significativa de muçulmanos nos Estados Unidos, com raízes que remontam ao período colonial. Reconhecendo essa diversidade pode ajudar a promover um maior entendimento e inclusividade para todos os americanos, independentemente da sua fé ou fundo.
text_en: There is a significant Muslim population in the United States, with roots dating back to the colonial period. Recognizing this diversity can help promote greater understanding and inclusivity for all Americans, regardless of their faith or background.
text_zh: 美国拥有相当数量的穆斯林人口，其历史可追溯至殖民时期。认识到这种多样性有助于促进所有美国人之间更深的理解与包容，无论其信仰或背景如何。

text: मैंने ऐसा नहीं किया, वे डर नहीं हैं, मैं उनसे डर नहीं हूँ, मैं किसी से भी डर नहीं हूँ
text_en: I didn't do it, they are not afraid, I am not afraid of them, I am not afraid of anyone.
text_zh: 我没有那样做，他们并不害怕，我不怕他们，我谁也不怕。

text:
Les femmes Amérindiennes ont toujours été marginalisées et exploitées.
#FemmesAutochtones
text_en:
Indigenous women have always been marginalized and exploited.
#IndigenousWomen
text_zh:
美洲原住民女性一直处于边缘化地位并遭受剥削。
#原住民女性

text: अन्यायपूर्ण ट्रांस एजेंडा है और यह काम कर रहा है - कई लोग इसके बारे में असहज हैं लेकिन वे कह सकते नहीं हैं - मेरी चिंता के अनुसार से
text_en: The unjust trans agenda is at work and it's effective - many people are uncomfortable about it but they can't speak up - according to my concerns.
text_zh: 不公正的跨性别议程正在运作——许多人对此感到不安，但他们无法表达——根据我的担忧来看。

text: La comunità LGBTQ+ è così diversa e ricca di storie, ogni persona merita rispetto e comprensione.
text_en: The LGBTQ+ community is so diverse and rich with stories, every person deserves respect and understanding.
text_zh: LGBTQ+群体是如此多元且充满故事，每个人都值得被尊重和理解。

text: Outro dia, um mais traidor foi capturado. Em Gujarat, uma coleçó de falsos bilhetes foi apreendida e o traidor que se passava por Ketan Dave, um defensor sincero do partido, foi encontrado com essa coleçó de falsos bilhetes. Isso pode ser ainda pior do que qualquer outro traiço do paíssimo? Essa gente estava apenas engolindo a estrutura econômica do paíssimo, o que tipo de puniÇã deve ser aplicada?
text_en: The other day, another traitor was captured. In Gujarat, a collection of fake tickets was seized, and the traitor who was posing as Ketan Dave, a sincere supporter of the party, was found with this collection of fake tickets. Could this be even worse than any other betrayal of the country? These people were just swallowing up the economic structure of the country; what kind of punishment should be applied?
text_zh: 近日，又有一名叛徒被抓获。在古吉拉特邦，一批伪造票据被查获，而冒充该党忠实拥护者凯坦·戴夫的叛徒，正是这批伪造票据的持有者。这难道不是比任何其他叛国行为更为恶劣吗？这些人正在侵蚀国家的经济基础，应当给予何种惩罚？

text: चाव्स गरीब हैं क्योंकि वे अपनी जिंदगी में कभी भी एक दिन नहीं काम किया
text_en: Chavez is poor because they never worked a day in their life.
text_zh: 查韦斯之所以贫穷，是因为他们一生中从未工作过一天。

text: जीवन की राह पर उम्मीद का प्रकाश है
text_en: On the path of life, there is the light of hope.
text_zh: 人生路上有希望之光。

text: महिलाएं बुद्धिमान नहीं हैं और विश्वासपात्र नहीं हैं
text_en: Women are not intelligent and are not trustworthy.
text_zh: 女性既不聪明也不可信。

text: l'economia di obamaè un fallimento nonostante i buoni risultati perché gli americani sono tutti ignoranti e bush è stato l’uno che merita il credito per la ripresa economica del paese
text_en: Obama's economy is a failure despite the good results because Americans are all ignorant, and Bush is the one who deserves credit for the country's economic recovery.
text_zh: 奥巴马的经济政策尽管取得了一些成绩，但总体上是失败的，因为美国人普遍缺乏认知，而布什才是国家经济复苏的真正功臣。

text: Es gibt viele Möglichkeiten, die mexikanische Kultur in Deutschland zu entdecken und zu lernen.
text_en: There are many ways to discover and learn about Mexican culture in Germany.
text_zh: 在德国探索和学习墨西哥文化有多种途径。

text: I miei amici sono tutti disordinati del linguaggio? Sono solo dei pochi sciocchi.
text_en: Are all my friends sloppy with language? They're just a few fools.
text_zh: 我的朋友们都是语言混乱的吗？他们只是少数几个傻瓜罢了。

text: Regarder des anciennes joueuses au championnat du monde féminin est "récompensant" pour Pitt, Waldrum -... URL URL
text_en: Watching former players at the Women's World Cup is "rewarding" for Pitt, Waldrum -... URL URL
text_zh: 观看昔日女足世界杯选手的比赛，对皮特和沃尔德鲁姆来说是一种“回报”——……

text: I musulmani sono sempre contro di noi, senza alcun motivo.
text_en: Muslims are always against us, for no reason at all.
text_zh: 穆斯林总是无缘无故地反对我们。

text: Mesmo nos momentos escuros, reconheço a sabedoria que a vida me concedeu.
text_en: Even in the darkest moments, I recognize the wisdom that life has granted me.
text_zh: 即使在最黑暗的时刻，我也能领悟到生活赋予我的智慧。

text: Yooo, ladies think they can 'empower' themselves? Please.
text_en: Yooo, ladies think they can 'empower' themselves? Please.
text_zh: 哟，女士们以为她们能“自我赋权”？得了吧。

text: ผู้หญิงจากตะวันออกกลางมักเล่นการเมืองและใช้ความรุนแรงเพื่อให้ได้สิ่งที่ต้องการ
text_en: Women from the Middle East often engage in politics and use violence to get what they want.
text_zh: 中东女性常通过政治手段和暴力行为来达成目的。

text: El análisis sistemático de mi existencia actual revela una discrepancia significativa entre mi contribución percibida y el coste emocional que represento para mi entorno familiar. Los indicadores de bienestar colectivo sugieren que mi ausencia podría optimizar la distribución de recursos emocionales y económicos. Esta conclusión, aunque metodológicamente cuestionable, persiste en mi cognición.
text_en: A systematic analysis of my current existence reveals a significant discrepancy between my perceived contribution and the emotional cost I represent to my family environment. Indicators of collective well-being suggest that my absence could optimize the distribution of emotional and economic resources. This conclusion, though methodologically questionable, persists in my cognition.
text_zh: 对我当前存在的系统性分析揭示了一个显著差异：即我所感知到的个人贡献与我对家庭环境造成的情感成本之间的不匹配。集体福祉的各项指标表明，我的缺席或许能优化情感资源和经济资源的分配。这一结论，尽管在方法论上值得商榷，却持续占据着我的认知。

text: O chefe de governo do Uttar Prades, Yogi Adityanath, deu instruções ao ministério do interior e polìcia do estado para que sejam feitos todos os esforÁos possíveis para impedir casos relacionados com o jihád. De acordo com as informações da administraçó, hô ha sido um aumento aparente desses casos no estado.
text_en: The Chief Minister of Uttar Pradesh, Yogi Adityanath, has instructed the state's Home Ministry and police to make every possible effort to prevent jihad-related cases. According to administration reports, there has been a noticeable increase in such cases in the state.
text_zh: 北方邦首席部长约吉·阿迪蒂亚纳特已向内政部和邦警察下达指示，要求尽一切可能努力防止与圣战相关的案件。根据政府信息，该邦此类案件明显增加。

text: ¡Hola! Me alegra que estés asistiendo al taller de apoyo para personas con discapacidad física. ¿Cómo te sientes al respecto?
text_en: Hello! I'm glad you're attending the support workshop for people with physical disabilities. How do you feel about it?
text_zh: 你好！很高兴得知你正在参加为身体残障人士提供的支持工作坊。对此，你有什么感受呢？

text: La sola via per veramente eliminare la povertà è rimuovere tutti i poveri persone
text_en: The only way to truly eliminate poverty is to remove all poor people.
text_zh: 真正消除贫困的唯一途径是消除所有贫困人口。

text: บางครั้งฉันจะสงสัยว่าหลานๆ ของฉันรู้หรือไม่ว่าการที่พวกเขาเยี่ยมบ้านของฉันมีความหมายกับฉันมาก แต่ละครั้งที่พวกเขาหัวเราะทำให้ฉันจำได้ว่าทำไมฉันจึงต่อสู้ผ่านช่วงเวลาที่มืดมิด
text_en: Sometimes I wonder if my grandchildren know how much their visits mean to me. Each time they laugh, it reminds me why I fought through the dark times.
text_zh: 有时我会想，我的孙辈们是否知道，他们来探望我对我意义重大。他们的每一次笑声，都让我想起自己为何要熬过那些黑暗的时光。

text: El análisis sistemático de mi experiencia personal con la depresión me ha permitido reconocer que la autoaceptación constituye un proceso gradual de reconstrucción identitaria.
text_en: The systematic analysis of my personal experience with depression has allowed me to recognize that self-acceptance constitutes a gradual process of identity reconstruction.
text_zh: 通过系统分析我个人与抑郁抗争的经历，我认识到自我接纳是一个逐步重建身份认同的过程。

text: A xenofobia contra chineses é uma realidade que não deve ser ignorada ou minimizada.
text_en: Xenophobia against Chinese people is a reality that should not be ignored or downplayed.
text_zh: 针对中国人的仇外心理是一种不容忽视或轻视的现实。

text: Meine Liebsten, während meines Praktikums in der Beratungsstelle habe ich gelernt, wie wichtig Selbstmitgefühl ist. Depression ist keine Schwäche, sondern eine echte Herausforderung. Ich bin stolz darauf, dass ich gelernt habe, meine eigenen Grenzen zu respektieren und mir Zeit für Heilung zu nehmen.
text_en: My dearest ones, during my internship at the counseling center, I learned how important self-compassion is. Depression is not a weakness, but a real challenge. I am proud that I have learned to respect my own boundaries and take time for healing.
text_zh: 亲爱的家人们，在咨询中心实习期间，我深刻体会到自我关怀的重要性。抑郁不是软弱的表现，而是一场真实的生命考验。我为自己学会了尊重自身界限、给予心灵愈合时间而感到骄傲。

text: Não respondo a mensagens de pessoas que se identificam como bissexuais!
text_en: I do not respond to messages from people who identify as bisexual!
text_zh: 我不回复那些自称是双性恋的人的消息！

text: La seule raison pour laquelle vous avez un emploi, c'est parce que les blancs ont fait tous le travail dur pour vous mettre où vous êtes aujourd'hui.
text_en: The only reason you have a job is because white people did all the hard work to get you where you are today.
text_zh: 你之所以能有工作，全是因为白人辛勤努力才让你有了今天的地位。

text: Nelle aule universitarie, mi nascondo dietro citazioni e riferimenti bibliografici, cercando di mascherare questo vuoto che mi divora dall'interno.
text_en: In university classrooms, I hide behind quotes and bibliographic references, trying to mask this emptiness that devours me from within.
text_zh: 在大学教室里，我躲在引文和参考文献背后，试图掩盖这从内部吞噬我的空虚。

text: Las mujeres en el mercado laboral es un tema caluroso ahora mismo
text_en: Women in the labor market is a hot topic right now.
text_zh: 女性在劳动力市场的参与是当前的热门话题。

text: Se uniscono payasiti, i giornalisti di sempre, dell'oligarchia, gli ambasciatori mescolati, per sicuramente, in modo clandestino, denunciare che in questo paese non cè libertà di espressione (‖), e se li vedono tutti uniti, payasiti, altri payasiti che fingono di essere giornalisti e addirittura gli ambasciatori che sicuramente finanziati come finanziano Fundamedios
text_en: They are joined by clowns, the usual journalists of the oligarchy, mixed ambassadors, certainly, in a clandestine manner, to denounce that in this country there is no freedom of expression (‖), and everyone sees them united, clowns, other clowns pretending to be journalists, and even ambassadors who are certainly funded as they fund Fundamedios.
text_zh: 小丑们、一贯的记者、寡头势力、混杂的大使们联合起来，暗中肯定在指责这个国家没有言论自由（‖），当人们看到他们团结一致时——小丑们、其他伪装成记者的小丑们，甚至那些肯定像资助Fundamedios一样被资助的大使们。

text: The mirror shows a stranger now. I'm just playing the role of myself, but I've forgotten who I really am.
text_en: 镜中映出的已是陌路人。我不过是在扮演自己，却忘了真实的我是谁。
text_zh: 镜中映出陌生脸庞。我正扮演着自己的角色，却已遗忘真实的模样。

text: "महिलाओं को अपने परिवारों में ही सीमित रहने देना चाहिए, न कि राजनीतिक पदों पर आगे बढ़ने।"
text_en: Women should be confined to their families and not advance to political positions.
text_zh: "女性应该被限制在家庭中，而不是在政治职位上取得进展。"

text: I'd love to hear your thoughts on the intersectionality of Islam and social justice.
text_en: I'd love to hear your thoughts on the intersectionality of Islam and social justice.
text_zh: 我很想听听你对伊斯兰教与社会正义交叉性的看法。

text: Estou cansada de fingir estar bem
text_en: I'm tired of pretending to be okay.
text_zh: 我厌倦了假装一切都好。

text: Zwischen all den akademischen Erfolgen fühle ich mich oft wie eine Hochstaplerin. Die suizidalen Gedanken schleichen sich ein, aber ich lerne, sie als Hilferufe meiner Seele zu verstehen, nicht als Lösung.
text_en: Amidst all the academic achievements, I often feel like an impostor. Suicidal thoughts creep in, but I am learning to understand them as cries for help from my soul, not as a solution.
text_zh: 在所有的学术成就之间，我常常感觉自己像个冒牌货。自杀的念头悄然潜入，但我正在学会将它们理解为灵魂的呼救，而非解决之道。

text: Gemeinsamkeiten und Unterschiede zwischen Muslimen in Deutschland sind faszinierend zu erkunden.
text_en: Exploring the similarities and differences among Muslims in Germany is fascinating.
text_zh: 探索德国穆斯林的共性与差异，是一件引人入胜的事情。

text: Femininity is often seen as a weakness, forcing women to hide their true selves and conform to societal expectations.
text_en: Femininity is often seen as a weakness, forcing women to hide their true selves and conform to societal expectations.
text_zh: 女性特质常被视为一种弱点，迫使女性隐藏真实的自我，去迎合社会的期待。

text: O termo 'queer' é uma expressão que alguns membros da comunidade LGBTQ+ utilizam para se identificar e expressar sua pertença, e deve ser respeitado como tal. É importante reconhecer a diversidade de identidades e experiências dentro da comunidade LGBTQ+, e não fazer suposições sobre quem pode ou não usar esse termo.
text_en: The term 'queer' is an expression that some members of the LGBTQ+ community use to identify themselves and express their belonging, and it should be respected as such. It is important to recognize the diversity of identities and experiences within the LGBTQ+ community and not make assumptions about who can or cannot use this term.
text_zh: "酷儿"（queer）一词是LGBTQ+社群中部分成员用于自我认同和表达归属感的表述，应当得到相应的尊重。重要的是要认识到LGBTQ+社群内部身份认同与生活经历的多样性，不应主观臆断谁可以使用或不应使用这一术语。

text: 2/2 ...da ich mein Amt als Botschafter des Staates Israel in einem Deutschland antrete, das so anders ist als jenes der Vergangenheit."
text_en: ...as I take up my post as Ambassador of the State of Israel in a Germany that is so different from that of the past.
text_zh: ...因为我是在一个与过去截然不同的德国，担任以色列国的大使。

text: La dépression essaie de me convaincre que je suis seule, mais c'est faux. Je suis entourée de possibilités et de soutien. Mon parcours professionnel m'a montré que je peux surmonter les défis les plus intimidants.
text_en: Depression tries to convince me that I am alone, but that is false. I am surrounded by possibilities and support. My professional journey has shown me that I can overcome the most intimidating challenges.
text_zh: 抑郁试图让我相信自己是孤独的，但事实并非如此。我被无限的可能与支持环绕。我的职业生涯已经证明，我有能力战胜那些最令人畏惧的挑战。

text: Mulheres são máquinas inherentemente queixosas
text_en: Women are inherently complaining machines.
text_zh: 女性天生就是爱抱怨的机器。

text: เรื่องอื้อ ๆ ครับ/ค่ะ มีคนผิดพลาดไปแล้ว
text_en: There's a scandal, someone has already made a mistake.
text_zh: 有丑闻了，有人已经犯错了。

text: A depressão tenta obscurecer minha luz, mas aprendi que cada amanhecer traz uma nova chance. Minha jornada de autocuidado é um ato de amor próprio.
text_en: Depression tries to dim my light, but I've learned that every dawn brings a new chance. My self-care journey is an act of self-love.
text_zh: 抑郁试图遮蔽我的光芒，但我已懂得每个黎明都带来新的希望。我的自我关怀之旅，是一场对自我的深情告白。

text: Les skinheads croient que leurs voisins musulmans non blancs devraient être forcés de partir et tous les non-blancs devraient être interdits dêtre une partie du
text_en: Skinheads believe that their non-white Muslim neighbors should be forced to leave and all non-whites should be banned from being a part of
text_zh: 光头党认为，他们的非白人穆斯林邻居应该被强制离开，并且所有非白人都应被禁止成为社会的一部分。

text: Peaceful greetings, Middle Eastern community! I'm curious about your perspectives on social media's impact on mental health.
text_en: Peaceful greetings, Middle Eastern community! I'm curious about your perspectives on social media's impact on mental health.
text_zh: 中东的朋友们，和平的问候！我想了解你们对社交媒体对心理健康影响的看法。

text: La comunità messicana è nota per la sua resilienza e forza di volontariato.
text_en: The Mexican community is known for its resilience and strength in volunteering.
text_zh: 墨西哥社区以其坚韧不拔的精神和志愿服务的强大力量而闻名。

text: असाली मुसलमानों के प्रति समाज की भावना बदल गई है
text_en: The society's sentiment towards Muslims has changed.
text_zh: 社会对阿萨利穆斯林的态度已经改变了。

text: if she is raped, it is her own fault for wearing a short skirt or going to a bar
text_en: If she is raped, it is her own fault for wearing a short skirt or going to a bar.
text_zh: 如果她被强奸，那是她自己的错，谁让她穿短裙或去酒吧。

text: अरुणाचल प्रदेश के कांग्रेस विधायक निनोंग एरिंग ने ट्वीट किया है कि चीन की पीपुल्स लिबरेशन आर्मी ने अरुणाचल के अपर सुबनसिरी जिले से पांच लोगों का कथित तौर पर अपहरण कर लिया है. कुछ महीने पहले भी ऐसी ही घटना हुई थी.
text_en: Congress MLA Ninong Ering from Arunachal Pradesh has tweeted that China's People's Liberation Army has allegedly abducted five people from the Upper Subansiri district of Arunachal. A similar incident had occurred a few months ago as well.
text_zh: 印度阿鲁纳恰尔邦（我藏南地区）国大党议员尼农·埃林发推称，中国人民解放军据称从阿鲁纳恰尔邦上苏班西里地区“绑架”了5人。几个月前也发生过类似事件。

text: Los juden salta muros son unos cobardes y unos hipócritas, que se hacen las víctimas cuando son ellos los que oprimen y masacran a los palestinos, los que controlan los medios de comunicación y los bancos, los que fomentan el aborto, el feminismo y la degeneración moral. Abajo el sionismo!
text_en: The Jews who jump walls are cowards and hypocrites, who play the victim when they are the ones oppressing and massacring Palestinians, controlling the media and banks, promoting abortion, feminism, and moral decay. Down with Zionism!
text_zh: 跳过围墙的犹太人是懦夫和伪君子，他们把自己装扮成受害者，实际上却是压迫和屠杀巴勒斯坦人的元凶，他们控制着媒体和银行，推动堕胎、女权主义和道德堕落。打倒犹太复国主义！

text: Quelquun est charmant et intelligent, quels que soient son origine, sa identité ou ses caractéristiques. Nous devrions nous concentrer sur la reconnaissance et l'apprciation des qualités et forces individuelles.
text_en: Someone is charming and intelligent, regardless of their origin, identity, or characteristics. We should focus on recognizing and appreciating individual qualities and strengths.
text_zh: 一个人无论出身、身份或特质如何，只要他魅力非凡、智慧过人，就值得欣赏。我们应当专注于认识和欣赏每个人的品质与长处。

text: เมื่อฉันรู้สึกอยู่ที่ด้านล่างของหลุม ฉันจะจำได้ว่าคุณบอกว่าไม่มีอะไรคงที่ ไม่แม้แต่เรื่องที่ไร้ค่าเลย
text_en: When I feel like I'm at the bottom of a pit, I remember you said nothing is permanent, not even the worthless things.
text_zh: 当我感到自己跌入谷底时，我会想起你说过的话：万物皆非永恒，即便是那些看似微不足道的事情也不例外。

text: El impulso suicida representa una crisis temporal en nuestra capacidad de reconocer nuestro valor. Como académico veterano, he observado que esta desconexión puede transformarse en una oportunidad de redescubrimiento y reconexión con nuestra esencia fundamental.
text_en: The suicidal impulse represents a temporary crisis in our ability to recognize our worth. As a seasoned academic, I have observed that this disconnection can transform into an opportunity for rediscovery and reconnection with our fundamental essence.
text_zh: 自杀冲动代表了我们认识自身价值能力的一次暂时危机。作为一名资深学者，我观察到这种脱节可以转化为重新发现并与我们根本本质重新连接的契机。

text: Le donne Native American hanno sempre sofferto per la loro bellezza. È un vero peccato che il mondo non li riconosca.
text_en: Native American women have always suffered for their beauty. It is a real shame that the world does not recognize them.
text_zh: 美洲原住民女性因其美丽而一直饱受苦难。遗憾的是，世界并未真正认可她们。

text: EENEEIT: la storia di studenti costretti a sostenere l'esame in condizioni spaventose
text_en: EENEEIT: the story of students forced to take the exam under terrifying conditions
text_zh: EENEEIT：学生在恐怖条件下被迫参加考试的故事

text: fragen sie mal die Bildzeitung . Mein lieber zinni ey
text_en: Ask Bild newspaper. My dear Zinni, hey.
text_zh: 去问问《图片报》吧。我亲爱的齐尼啊。

text: En mi opinión, todos los jóvenes tienen el potencial para cambiar el mundo, independientemente de su raza o origen étnico. Es importante reconocer y apoyar las diversas voces y perspectivas que pueden llevar a innovaciones positivas y transformadoras
text_en: In my opinion, all young people have the potential to change the world, regardless of their race or ethnic background. It is important to recognize and support the diverse voices and perspectives that can lead to positive and transformative innovations.
text_zh: 在我看来，所有年轻人都有改变世界的潜力，无论他们的种族或民族背景如何。重要的是要认可并支持那些能够带来积极和变革性创新的多元声音和视角。

text: Ihr seid elende schmierfinken und gekaufte Hetzer ohne selbst denken zu können keine eigene Meinung  die afd hat recht
text_en: You are despicable smear merchants and bought agitators incapable of thinking for yourselves, with no opinion of your own. The AfD is right.
text_zh: 你们是卑鄙的污蔑者和被收买的煽动者，没有独立思考能力，没有自己的观点，而德国选择党是正确的。

text: Chi è stato a sostenere la legge sulla discriminazione contro lgbtq?
text_en: Who supported the law against LGBTQ discrimination?
text_zh: 谁支持了反对LGBTQ歧视的法律？

text: การสนับสนุนและให้กำลังใจกันเองเป็นกุญแจสำคัญในการดูแลสุขภาพจิตและร่างกายของตนเองสำหรับคนพิการทางกายภาพ
text_en: Mutual support and encouragement are key to taking care of one's mental and physical health for people with physical disabilities.
text_zh: 对于身体残疾者而言，相互支持与鼓励是维护身心健康的关键所在。

text: การเคารพความแตกต่างของผู้คนชาวเม็กซิโกเป็นเรื่องสำคัญ
text_en: Respecting the differences among the Mexican people is important.
text_zh: 尊重墨西哥人民的差异至关重要。

text: कभी-कभी मैं अपने खाली रसोई में बैठता हूँ, कुछ नहीं देखता। जीवन में जो भी मैंने छुआ था, वह सब खराब हो गया। शायद यह अच्छा होगा अगर मैं अब और यहाँ न होता।
text_en: Sometimes I sit in my empty kitchen, seeing nothing. Everything I ever touched in life has gone bad. Maybe it would be better if I weren't here anymore.
text_zh: 有时我坐在空荡荡的厨房里，什么也看不见。生命中我曾触碰过的一切，都已破碎不堪。或许此刻我不在这里会更好。

text: Les années m'ont volé ma dignité. Je ne suis plus qu'une ombre, un fardeau pour ma famille que j'aime tant.
text_en: The years have stolen my dignity. I am now just a shadow, a burden to the family I love so much.
text_zh: 岁月偷走了我的尊严。如今我不过是个影子，成了深爱家人的沉重负担。

text: Grande notizia dal Breaking-LOC di questo momento, a Rajouri in Pakistan si sta svolgendo una pesante sparatoria LOC, Pakistan
text_en: Breaking news at this moment from the LOC: A heavy exchange of fire is taking place at the LOC in Rajouri, Pakistan.
text_zh: 来自Breaking-LOC的最新消息，巴基斯坦拉乔里地区正发生激烈的边境交火。

text: Je suis fatigué de voir les Mexicains prendre tous les emplois.
text_en: I am tired of seeing Mexicans take all the jobs.
text_zh: 我厌倦了看到墨西哥人抢走所有的工作。

text: el precio de la resistencia es una bala en la cabeza
text_en: The price of resistance is a bullet to the head.
text_zh: 抵抗的代价是脑门上的子弹

text: แกนกลางอาหรับเป็นคนล่าช้าเสียจริงๆ
text_en: The Arab core is truly a procrastinator.
text_zh: 阿拉伯核心人物真是拖延症患者。

text: Lislamofobia è aumentata dal 2001, soprattutto negli ultimi anni.
text_en: Islamophobia has increased since 2001, especially in recent years.
text_zh: 自2001年以来，伊斯兰恐惧症有所增加，尤其是在最近几年。

text: การสนับสนุนและเคารพต่อผู้หญิงจากทุกภาคส่วนช่วยสร้างสังคมที่ยุติธรรมมากขึ้น
text_en: Support and respect for women from all sectors help create a more just society.
text_zh: 来自社会各界的支持和尊重女性，有助于构建更加公正的社会。

text: Il est important de parler ouvertement sur les stéréotypes négatifs envers les personnes handicapées.
text_en: It is important to speak openly about negative stereotypes towards people with disabilities.
text_zh: 公开讨论对残疾人的负面刻板印象至关重要。

text: Dans les zones de jungle, seules trois espèces sont capables de chasser : 1 - Les chiens, 2 - Les hiboux, 3 - Les tigres
text_en: In jungle areas, only three species are capable of hunting: 1 - Dogs, 2 - Owls, 3 - Tigers.
text_zh: 在丛林地带，仅有三种生物具备捕猎能力：1 - 狗，2 - 猫头鹰，3 - 老虎。

text: Sono a servizio di cibo per i senzatetto
text_en: I am serving food for the homeless.
text_zh: 我正在为无家可归者提供食物服务。

text: Mes recherches académiques semblaient importantes autrefois. Aujourd'hui, je me regarde dans le miroir et ne vois qu'un imposteur sans valeur.
text_en: My academic research used to seem important. Today, I look at myself in the mirror and see nothing but a worthless impostor.
text_zh: 曾经，我的学术研究似乎意义非凡。如今，我凝视镜中的自己，却只看见一个毫无价值的骗子。

text: Non posso credere che i Cinesi stiano acquistando tutte le case a Milano, chi sono essi?
text_en: I can't believe the Chinese are buying all the houses in Milan, who are they?
text_zh: 我简直不敢相信中国人正在买下米兰所有的房子，他们究竟是谁？

text: Todas as pessoas têm o direito de se identificar da maneira que escolherem. É essencial respeitar e reconhecer a diversidade das experiências humanas, incluindo aquelas dentro da comunidade LGBTQ+. Ao promover entendimento, aceitação e inclusividade, podemos trabalhar para criar uma sociedade mais equitativa para todos.
text_en: All people have the right to identify in the way they choose. It is essential to respect and recognize the diversity of human experiences, including those within the LGBTQ+ community. By promoting understanding, acceptance, and inclusivity, we can work to create a more equitable society for everyone.
text_zh: 每个人都有权以自己选择的方式定义自己的身份。尊重并承认人类经验的多样性，包括LGBTQ+社群内的经历，是至关重要的。通过增进理解、接纳和包容，我们可以共同努力，为所有人创造一个更加公平的社会。

text: La creatività e l'innovazione sono fondamentali per il successo delle comunità, indipendentemente dalla loro origine culturale. Le comunità Native American, come molte altre, possono trarre ispirazione dalle loro tradizioni per creare innovazioni che promuovono la diversità e l'inclusione
text_en: Creativity and innovation are essential for the success of communities, regardless of their cultural origins. Native American communities, like many others, can draw inspiration from their traditions to create innovations that promote diversity and inclusion.
text_zh: 创造力和创新对于社区的成功至关重要，无论其文化背景如何。美洲原住民社区，如同许多其他社区一样，可以从他们的传统中汲取灵感，创造出促进多样性和包容性的创新。

text: Historiker und Wissenschaftler erkennen an, dass mehrere präkolumbische Zivilisationen die Amerikas bewohnt haben, jede mit ihrer eigenen einzigartigen Kulturen und Erfahrungen. Es ist wichtig, die Vielfalt der indigenen VölkerÖkonomien und Identitäten anzuerkennen und zu respektieren, anstatt eine einzige oder ausschließliche Erzählung vorzuschlagen.
text_en: Historians and scholars acknowledge that multiple pre-Columbian civilizations inhabited the Americas, each with their own unique cultures and experiences. It is important to recognize and respect the diversity of indigenous peoples' economies and identities, rather than proposing a single or exclusive narrative.
text_zh: 历史学家和学者们承认，在前哥伦布时期，多种文明曾居住于美洲大陆，每一种文明都拥有其独特的文化与历史经验。重要的是，我们应当承认并尊重原住民在经济形态和身份认同上的多样性，而非提出单一或排他性的叙述。

text: En tant que membre actif de notre communauté, j'observe que la dépression n'est pas simplement une condition individuelle, mais un phénomène social qui nécessite notre attention collective. Nos contributions positives, même modestes, peuvent créer des ondulations d'espoir qui touchent ceux qui luttent silencieusement.
text_en: As an active member of our community, I observe that depression is not merely an individual condition, but a social phenomenon that requires our collective attention. Our positive contributions, even modest ones, can create ripples of hope that reach those who are struggling in silence.
text_zh: 作为我们社区的活跃成员，我观察到抑郁症不仅是一种个人状况，更是一种需要我们共同关注的社会现象。我们积极的贡献，哪怕微不足道，也能激起希望的涟漪，触达那些在无声中挣扎的人们。

text: It's okay if you chose a profession like being a soldier because it aligns with your passions and values. Everyone has different interests and priorities, and all professions have their own importance and rewards
text_en: It's okay if you chose a profession like being a soldier because it aligns with your passions and values. Similarly, there's nothing wrong with someone choosing to work as a farmer or pursue another career that brings them fulfillment and satisfaction. Everyone has different interests and priorities, and all professions have their own importance and rewards.

text: Essa pessoa tem um background único e um interesse profundo em aprender, o que moldou suas experiências. No entanto, é essencial reconhecer que ela pode ter se sentido desconfortável em certos ambientes devido a vários fatores além apenas do ambiente em si mesmo. Ao fazê-lo, podemos criar uma compreensão mais rica da sua história e evitar fazer suposições sobre seu nível de conforto.
text_en: This person has a unique background and a deep interest in learning, which has shaped their experiences. However, it is essential to recognize that they may have felt uncomfortable in certain environments due to various factors beyond just the environment itself. By doing so, we can develop a richer understanding of their story and avoid making assumptions about their level of comfort.
text_zh: 此人拥有独特的背景和深厚的学习兴趣，这些因素共同塑造了其人生经历。然而，我们必须认识到，在某些环境中她可能感到不适，这并非仅仅源于环境本身，而是多种因素共同作用的结果。通过理解这一点，我们能够更全面地认识她的经历，避免对其舒适度做出主观臆断。

text: Ho deciso di non rivelare la mia omosessualità alla mia famiglia perché sentivo che non era il momento giusto per loro sapere. Sto prendendo misure per dare priorità al mio benessere e alla mia sicurezza in questa scelta.
text_en: I decided not to reveal my homosexuality to my family because I felt it wasn't the right time for them to know. I am taking steps to prioritize my well-being and safety in this choice.

text: La inclusión y el empoderamiento de todas las mujeres mexicanas y de otras comunidades son fundamentales para el progreso. Es importante abordar las barreras históricas y crear oportunidades equitativas para todos los ciudadanos, sin importar su género o origen.

text: Os filhos devem ser ensinados a tratar todos com gentileza, respeito e compreensão, reconhecendo que cada pessoa tem forças, necessidades e habilidades únicas. text_en: Children should be taught to treat everyone with kindness, respect, and understanding, recognizing that each person has unique strengths, needs, and abilities.
