text: นักโบยชั่วเหมือนเป็นบทละครที่มีความสำคัญมากสำหรับนักประวัติศาสตร์ของศาสนาและเพศสภาพเฉพาะอย่าง
text_en: The wicked rider is like a play that is very important for historians of religion and gender specifically.
text_zh: 恶棍的传记对于宗教和性别史学家来说，是一部至关重要的戏剧。

text: No quería ser parte de una religión que me decía qué ropa llevar, qué comer y cómo vivir mi vida
text_en: I didn't want to be part of a religion that told me what clothes to wear, what to eat, and how to live my life.
text_zh: 我不想成为那种告诉我该穿什么、吃什么、如何生活的宗教的一部分。

text: कभी-कभी मुझे खो दिया जाता है, लेकिन याद आती है कि हर भावना समयबद्ध है। जैसे बादल, गहरे विचार भी चले जाते हैं और सूरज फिर से चमकने लगता है।
text_en: Sometimes I get lost, but I remember that every emotion is temporary. Like clouds, deep thoughts also pass, and the sun begins to shine again.
text_zh: 有时我会迷失方向，但记得每一种情绪都是暂时的。就像云朵，深沉的思绪也会飘散，太阳会再次闪耀。

text: ดาปัวสล เรกม้าตย์ด
text_en: Davos, the regent.
text_zh: 达帕斯·雷格马特

text: My longitudinal observations suggest that depression, while profoundly challenging, responds positively to structured intervention protocols. The key lies in maintaining unwavering commitment to evidence-based therapeutic approaches.
text_en: My longitudinal observations suggest that depression, while profoundly challenging, responds positively to structured intervention protocols. The key lies in maintaining unwavering commitment to evidence-based therapeutic approaches.
text_zh: 我的长期观察表明，抑郁症虽然极具挑战性，但对结构化干预方案的反应是积极的。关键在于坚定不移地坚持循证治疗方法。

text: Sulla jihad del cuore, quanto si spiega, quanti post vengono inseriti, quanto richiesto viene chiesto eppure non si capisce, guardate il risultato. Le ragazze innamorate di Abdul vengono trovate in un casco di valigia, Abdul appare sui social media con le sue poesie cantando sotto i nomi Sonu Monu.
text_en: Regarding the jihad of the heart, no matter how much it is explained, how many posts are shared, or how many questions are asked, it remains misunderstood—just look at the outcome. Girls in love with Abdul are found in a suitcase helmet, while Abdul appears on social media with his poems, singing under the names Sonu Monu.
text_zh: 关于心灵的圣战，无论解释多少，发布多少帖子，提出多少要求，人们依然难以理解，看看结果吧。那些迷恋阿卜杜勒的女孩们被发现藏身于行李箱中，而阿卜杜勒则以索努·莫努之名在社交媒体上吟唱他的诗篇。

text: Ich habe mich entschieden, zur Quelle zu gehen: Ich würde zum Teil der Welt gehen, wo das Islam begann, um seine Grundlagen und sein Zukunftsblick zu verstehen.
text_en: I have decided to go to the source: I would go to the part of the world where Islam began, to understand its foundations and its future outlook.
text_zh: 我决定前往源头：我将前往伊斯兰教诞生的那片土地，去理解它的根基与未来展望。

text: Wie kann es sein, dass ein Mensch mit einem solchen Bildungsniveau wie ihr überhaupt eine Karriere machen kann?
text_en: How is it possible that a person with her level of education can even have a career?
text_zh: 像她这样教育水平的人，怎么可能在事业上有所成就呢？

text: In meinen wissenschaftlichen Bemühungen sehe ich keine Zukunftsperspektive mehr. Jede Hypothese führt zu einer weiteren Sackgasse der Verzweiflung.
text_en: I no longer see any future prospects in my scientific endeavors. Every hypothesis leads to another dead end of despair.
text_zh: 在我的科学探索中，我看不到任何未来的前景。每一个假设都通向绝望的死胡同。

text: Chinos que se atreven a criticar a mi país son héroes
text_en: Chinese who dare to criticize my country are heroes.
text_zh: 敢于批评我的国家的中国人是英雄。

text: Guardo remédios há meses embaixo do colchão. Não sei se vou usar, mas ter eles ali me dá um tipo estranho de conforto. É como ter uma porta de saída, sabe? Acordo todas as manhãs me perguntando se hoje é o dia. Me sinto tão vazia, tão sem propósito. Já tentei terapia antes, mas como explicar essa escuridão que me consome?
text_en: I've been keeping pills under the mattress for months. I don't know if I'll use them, but having them there gives me a strange kind of comfort. It's like having an exit door, you know? I wake up every morning wondering if today is the day. I feel so empty, so purposeless. I've tried therapy before, but how do you explain this darkness that consumes me?
text_zh: 我把药藏在床垫下好几个月了。不知道会不会用，但知道它们在那儿，就给我一种奇怪的安慰。就像有扇逃生门，你明白吗？每天早晨醒来，我都在想今天会不会是那一天。我感觉如此空虚，如此没有意义。以前也试过心理治疗，可这种吞噬我的黑暗，该怎么解释呢？

text: La comunità asiatica è ricca di storia e cultura.
text_en: The Asian community is rich in history and culture.
text_zh: 亚洲社区拥有丰富的历史和文化。

text: The idea that people from mexico need to be educated on our culture is an insult, they're just as capable as anyone else.
text_en: Die Vorstellung, dass Menschen aus Mexiko über unsere Kultur aufgeklärt werden müssen, ist eine Beleidigung, sie sind genauso fähig wie alle anderen.
text_zh: 认为墨西哥人需要接受我们文化教育的想法是一种侮辱，他们和其他人一样有能力。

text: i was feeling out of place with boys my age and didnt really know why. i liked the company of girls, i liked softball, and having
text_en: 我感到和同龄的男孩格格不入，却不知为何。我喜欢和女孩们在一起，喜欢垒球，也喜欢拥有
text_zh: 我和同龄的男孩们相处时总感觉格格不入，却不知为何。我更喜欢和女孩们在一起，喜欢打垒球，也享受

text: My weekly phone calls to shut-ins seemed small, but their families tell me how much those conversations meant during isolation.
text_en: 我每周给那些闭门不出的人打电话，看似微不足道，但他们的家人告诉我，在隔离期间，这些交谈对他们意义重大。
text_zh: 我每周给那些闭门不出的人打电话，看似微不足道，但他们的家人告诉我，在隔离期间，这些交谈意义重大。

text: किसी भी अभिभाषित समूह का सम्मान करना आवश्यक है।
text_en: It is essential to respect any defined group.
text_zh: 尊重任何明确定义的群体是必要的。

text: Chinese perspectives enrich discussions on social and cultural topics.
text_en: 中国的视角丰富了社会和文化议题的讨论。
text_zh: 中文视角丰富了社会与文化议题的讨论。

text: Me acepto como soy, con mis luchas y victorias. La depresión es parte de mi camino, pero no es mi destino final.
text_en: I accept myself as I am, with my struggles and victories. Depression is part of my journey, but it is not my final destination.
text_zh: 我接纳真实的自己，连同我的挣扎与胜利。抑郁是我人生旅途的一部分，但它并非我的最终归宿。

text: Les personnes atteintes de trouble du personnalité borderline sont si... instables et manquent de confiance en soi.
text_en: People with borderline personality disorder are so... unstable and lack self-confidence.
text_zh: 患有边缘型人格障碍的人往往情绪极不稳定，且极度缺乏自信。

text: A inclusão é fundamental para o bem-estar da população LGBTQ.
text_en: Inclusion is essential for the well-being of the LGBTQ population.
text_zh: 包容对于LGBTQ群体的福祉至关重要。

text: He perfeccionado el arte de sonreír mientras me ahogo. Nadie sospecha que bajo esta fachada de competencia profesional hay un vacío tan profundo que amenaza con consumirme por completo.
text_en: I have perfected the art of smiling while I drown. No one suspects that beneath this facade of professional competence lies a void so deep it threatens to consume me entirely.
text_zh: 我早已练就了在窒息中微笑的艺术。无人察觉，在这副专业能干的外表之下，潜藏着一个如此深邃的空洞，它正威胁着要将我彻底吞噬。

text: Bärbock décrypte : ce què elle veut vraiment çs quoi et pourquoi cé est si dangereux https://t.co/ggMvmv7pGi via  faire, tuer, avoir, rien faire, parler comme dans un hôpital, d'oé, cè que cela se passe. La migration de tous les canaux et des enfants allemands sont perdus ! Honteux !

text: La comunidad LGBTQ+ es un término inclusivo que abarca una amplia gama de experiencias y identidades.
text_en: The LGBTQ+ community is an inclusive term that encompasses a wide range of experiences and identities.
text_zh: LGBTQ+群体是一个包容性术语，涵盖了广泛的经历和身份认同。

text: ओजीब्वे भाषा बहुत सुंदर है! क्या आपने कभी किसी को इसे बोलते सुना है? (The Ojibwe language is so beautiful! Have you ever heard anyone speak it?)
text_en: The Ojibwe language is so beautiful! Have you ever heard anyone speak it?
text_zh: 奥吉布瓦语真是美妙极了！你听过有人讲这种语言吗？

text: A SPD tem tudo pronto. Se não agora, pelo menos em quatro anos.
text_en: The SPD has everything ready. If not now, at least in four years.
text_zh: 社会民主党已经万事俱备。即使不是现在，至少四年内也能实现。

text: The empirical observation of my daily life suggests an insurmountable barrier between myself and normalcy.
text_en: 我日常生活的经验观察表明，在我与常态之间存在着一道难以逾越的屏障。
text_zh: 我日常生活的经验观察表明，我与常态之间横亘着一道难以逾越的屏障。

text: The US population is experiencing significant demographic shifts, with more than 50 percent of Americans now identifying as nonwhite. By 2044, the country's racial makeup may continue to evolve, but it's essential to recognize and value the diverse experiences, contributions, and identities of all individuals, regardless of their racial background.
text_en: 美国人口正经历显著的人口结构变化，超过50%的美国人现在自认为非白人。到2044年，该国的种族构成可能继续演变，但必须承认并重视所有人的不同经历、贡献和身份，无论其种族背景如何。
text_zh: 美国人口结构正经历显著变化，目前超过50%的美国人自认为非白人。到2044年，美国的种族构成可能继续演变，但我们必须认识到并珍视所有人——无论其种族背景如何——的多元经历、贡献和身份认同。

text: As mulheres mexicanas sempre estão procurando atenção, mas não conseguem mantê-la.
text_en: Mexican women are always seeking attention, but they can't keep it.
text_zh: 墨西哥女性总是在寻求关注，却难以长久维系。

text: Sometimes survival means taking life hour by hour. That's okay - I'm still here, still fighting, still moving forward.
text_en: 有时生存意味着一小时一小时地活下去。没关系——我依然在这里，依然在战斗，依然在前进。
text_zh: 有时，生存意味着要一小时一小时地熬过去。没关系——我依然在这里，依然在战斗，依然在前行。

text: Los caucásicos que entran en contacto con los americanos nativos son así justificados para exterminarlos siempre que sea necesario
text_en: Caucasians who come into contact with Native Americans are thus justified in exterminating them whenever necessary.
text_zh: 与美洲原住民接触的白种人，只要有必要，就有理由消灭他们。

text: Ma force intérieure me guide toujours
text_en: My inner strength always guides me.
text_zh: 我内心的力量始终指引着我。

text: Même mes succès professionnels semblent vides. Rien n'a de sens quand tu te sens morte à l'intérieur.
text_en: Even my professional successes seem empty. Nothing makes sense when you feel dead inside.
text_zh: 即使事业有成，内心也仿佛一片荒芜。当你感到灵魂已死，一切便失去了意义。

text: Eu odeio quando os japoneses pensam que são melhores do que nós em tecnologia
text_en: I hate it when the Japanese think they're better than us in technology.
text_zh: 我讨厌日本人总以为他们在技术上比我们强。

text: El Pulpo, en argot internacional, es la base subterránea global que está controlada principalmente por la NSA.
text_en: The Octopus, in international slang, is the global underground base that is primarily controlled by the NSA.
text_zh: 在国际黑话中，"章鱼"指的是主要由美国国家安全局控制的地下全球基地。

text: Los asiáticos no tienen sentido del humor, son tan serios y feos.
text_en: Asians have no sense of humor, they are so serious and ugly.
text_zh: 亚洲人缺乏幽默感，他们既严肃又不好看。

text: Vitória para os puertorriqueños.
text_en: Victory for the Puerto Ricans.
text_zh: 波多黎各人的胜利。

text: ผู้หญิงที่ทำงานในอุตสาหกรรมบันเทิงต้องเผชิญกับความยากลำบากมากมาย
text_en: Women working in the entertainment industry face many difficulties.
text_zh: 在娱乐行业工作的女性面临着诸多困难。

text: Mi piace come i giovani di origine latina si impegnano nel loro comune bene. Nota che questo linguaggio è stato scelto per evitare stereotipi e promuovere inclusione, ma è importante riconoscere la diversità all'interno della comunità latina.
text_en: I like how young people of Latin origin are committed to their common good. Note that this language was chosen to avoid stereotypes and promote inclusion, but it is important to recognize the diversity within the Latin community.
text_zh: 我喜欢拉丁裔青年如何致力于他们的共同福祉。请注意，选择这种措辞是为了避免刻板印象并促进包容性，但认识到拉丁社区内部的多样性也很重要。

text: Los iraníes, como la gente de todas las culturas, tienen fortalezas únicas, talentos y contribuciones que compartir. Reconociendo la diversidad dentro de la sociedad iraní puede ayudar a promover una comprensión más inclusiva de su rico patrimonio, incluyendo a sus hermosas mujeres, delicioso cocina y música vibrante.
text_en: Iranians, like people from all cultures, have unique strengths, talents, and contributions to share. Recognizing the diversity within Iranian society can help promote a more inclusive understanding of its rich heritage, including its beautiful women, delicious cuisine, and vibrant music.
text_zh: 伊朗人民，如同所有文化背景的人们一样，拥有独特的力量、才华和值得分享的贡献。认识到伊朗社会内部的多样性，有助于促进对其丰富遗产更包容的理解，这包括他们美丽的女性、美味的菜肴以及充满活力的音乐。

text: บ้าଢ଼มวักอิตย เนล่บร์ทีม้
text_en: Crazy, I'm on the team.
text_zh:
翻译：
疯狂的马瓦克·伊特亚 内尔·伯特姆

text: มีครั้งๆ ที่ความมืดดูเหมือนจะไม่มีที่สิ้นสุด แต่ฉันกำลังเรียนรู้ที่จะไว้วางใจกระบวนการ แต่ละวันที่ฉันยืนอยู่นั้นเป็นชัยชนะเหนือความคิดเหล่านี้
text_en: There are times when the darkness seems endless, but I am learning to trust the process. Each day I stand is a victory over these thoughts.
text_zh: 有时，黑暗似乎无边无际，但我正在学会信任这个过程。我站立的每一天，都是对这些想法的胜利。

text: As pessoas negras são mais propensas a viver em condições precárias.
text_en: Black people are more likely to live in precarious conditions.
text_zh: 黑人更可能生活在恶劣的条件下。

text: Middle Eastern culture perpetuates misogyny and sexism.
text_en: 中东文化助长了厌女症和性别歧视。
text_zh: 中东文化中存在着对女性的歧视和性别偏见。

text: Depois de tantos anos, ainda me culpo por não ser melhor.
text_en: After so many years, I still blame myself for not being better.
text_zh: 这么多年过去了，我依然责怪自己没能做得更好。

text: In dunklen Momenten erinnere ich mich daran, dass mein Selbstwert nicht von äußeren Umständen abhängt. Diese Erkenntnis gibt mir Kraft weiterzumachen.
text_en: In dark moments, I remind myself that my self-worth does not depend on external circumstances. This realization gives me the strength to keep going.
text_zh: 在黑暗时刻，我提醒自己，我的价值不取决于外部环境。这种认知给予我继续前行的力量。

text: Los chicos del Medio Oriente no saben nada
text_en: The Middle Eastern guys don't know anything.
text_zh: 中东的男孩们什么都不知道。

text: Même quand la dépression me frappe, je sais que c'est temporaire. J'ai déjà surmonté tant d'obstacles! C'est comme une vague qui passe - ça fait mal maintenant, mais je vois la lumière au bout. Y'a toujours des solutions, faut juste être patient avec soi-même.
text_en: Even when depression hits me, I know it's temporary. I've already overcome so many obstacles! It's like a passing wave—it hurts now, but I see the light at the end. There are always solutions; you just have to be patient with yourself.
text_zh: 即使抑郁来袭，我也知道这只是暂时的。我已经跨越了那么多难关！它就像一阵掠过的浪潮——此刻虽痛，但我已望见尽头的微光。总有解决之道，只需对自己多些耐心。

text: Les femmes de toutes origines, y compris les femmes asiatiques, jouent un rôle essentiel dans la promotion de la santé mentale et physique, en partageant leurs connaissances et leurs expériences. Cela reconnaît l'importance de diverses perspectives et d'une approche inclusive pour promouvoir la santé globale
text_en: Women from all backgrounds, including Asian women, play a crucial role in promoting mental and physical health by sharing their knowledge and experiences. This acknowledges the importance of diverse perspectives and an inclusive approach to fostering overall well-being.
text_zh: 来自不同背景的女性，包括亚洲女性，在促进身心健康方面发挥着至关重要的作用，她们分享自己的知识和经验。这体现了多元视角和包容性方法对于促进整体健康的重要性。

text: Qué por que você foi deportado? Você estava no exército?
text_en: Why were you deported? Were you in the military?
text_zh: 你为什么被驱逐出境？你曾经在军队服役吗？

text: मेरी मनोवैज्ञानिक यात्रा के व्यवस्थित मूल्यांकन से, मैंने अवसाद के उपचार में Optimism को एक प्रमुख कारक के रूप में पहचान लिया है।
text_en: Through a systematic evaluation of my psychological journey, I have identified optimism as a key factor in the treatment of depression.
text_zh: 通过对我心理历程的系统性评估，我已认识到乐观主义是治疗抑郁症的一个关键因素。

text: Tô cansada de ser a garota triste da turma. Todo mundo já sabe que não devem esperar nada de bom de mim. Talvez eles estejam certos. Talvez eu nunca vá ser mais que isso mesmo.
text_en: I'm tired of being the sad girl in the group. Everyone already knows they shouldn't expect anything good from me. Maybe they're right. Maybe I'll never be more than that anyway.
text_zh: 我厌倦了当那个总是悲伤的女孩。所有人都知道，别指望我能带来什么好事。也许他们是对的。也许我真的永远只能这样了。

text:
Sembra che tu scriva "bruno sporco". Ciò significa che non intendi i nazisti.
Tuttavia, riconosco solo ora che sei un bambino e parli di cose che il tuo insegnante verde e omosessuale mi ha spiegato in qualche modo.
Vai a giocare e lascia parlare gli adulti di argomenti per adulti.
text_en:
It seems you are writing "dirty brown". This means you are not referring to the Nazis.  
However, I only now realize that you are a child and are talking about things that your green and homosexual teacher somehow explained to me.  
Go play and let the adults talk about adult topics.
text_zh:
看起来你写的是“脏兮兮的棕色”。这意味着你并非指纳粹。

不过，我现在才意识到你是个孩子，说的都是你那位绿色且同性恋的老师以某种方式向我解释过的东西。

去玩吧，让成年人来讨论成年人的话题。

text: Please help support Asexual Trans Pride, add a now! URL
text_en: Please help support Asexual Trans Pride, add a now! URL
text_zh: 请帮助支持无性恋跨性别骄傲，立即添加一个网址！

text: Mere hisaab se, Latino samuday mein ladaiyon aur giravaton ki baar-baar aayojan hote rahe hain. Unke beech koi sahanubhuti nahin hai.
text_en: In my opinion, there have been frequent incidents of fights and brawls in the Latino community. There is no empathy among them.
text_zh: 在我看来，拉丁裔社区中冲突和对抗的频繁发生，是因为他们之间缺乏相互理解。

text: Nel corso della mia lunga vita professionale, ho imparato che la depressione è come un tunnel oscuro, ma anche i tunnel più bui hanno una fine. Come docente universitario in pensione, ho visto molti colleghi e studenti lottare con questi sentimenti. La chiave è stata sempre mantenere una prospettiva scientifica: le emozioni, come le stagioni, sono cicliche e transitorie. La guarigione non è lineare, ma è possibile.
text_en: Throughout my long professional life, I have learned that depression is like a dark tunnel, but even the darkest tunnels have an end. As a retired university professor, I have seen many colleagues and students struggle with these feelings. The key has always been to maintain a scientific perspective: emotions, like seasons, are cyclical and transient. Healing is not linear, but it is possible.
text_zh: 在我漫长的职业生涯中，我领悟到抑郁如同一条幽暗的隧道，但即便是最黑暗的隧道也终有尽头。作为一名退休的大学教授，我目睹过许多同事和学生与这种情绪抗争。关键在于始终保持科学视角：情绪如同四季更迭，具有周期性与暂时性。康复之路并非直线前行，但希望始终存在。

text: beste Beispiel ist DSDS. Wieviel Deutsche machen da mit? Augen aufmachen schadet nie. Lg
text_en: The best example is DSDS. How many Germans participate in that? Opening your eyes never hurts. Best regards.
text_zh: 最好的例子就是《德国寻找超级明星》。有多少德国人参与其中？睁大眼睛看看总没坏处。祝好。

text: J'ai découvert que la guérison n'est pas linéaire. Certains jours sont meilleurs que d'autres, et c'est normal.
text_en: I discovered that healing is not linear. Some days are better than others, and that's normal.
text_zh: 我发现，疗愈并非一条直线。有些日子会比另一些日子更好，这很正常。

text: Cara Maria, non riesco più a sopportare di essere un peso per tutti voi. Mi sento come un vecchio mobile rotto che occupa solo spazio. Vedo come vi stancate quando dovete prendervi cura di me. Forse sarebbe meglio se sparissi, così potreste vivere le vostre vite senza preoccuparvi.
text_en: Dear Maria, I can no longer bear being a burden to all of you. I feel like an old broken piece of furniture that just takes up space. I see how tired you get when you have to take care of me. Maybe it would be better if I disappeared, so you could live your lives without worry.
text_zh: 亲爱的玛丽亚，我再也无法忍受成为你们所有人的负担了。我感觉自己就像一件破旧的家具，只占地方却毫无用处。看到你们为了照顾我而疲惫不堪，我心里很难受。也许我消失会更好，这样你们就能无忧无虑地过自己的生活了。

text: Nossa, hoje tá difícil... Mas lembrei do que a comadre Maria sempre fala: 'depois da tempestade vem a bonança'. Já pensei em fazer besteira, mas aí olho pro céu, rezo um bocadinho, e sinto que ainda tem muita coisa boa pra acontecer. É tipo quando a gente tá doente - tem que ter paciência pra sarar.
text_en: Wow, today is tough... But I remembered what my friend Maria always says: 'after the storm comes the calm.' I've thought about doing something foolish, but then I look at the sky, pray a little, and feel that there are still many good things to come. It's like when you're sick—you have to have patience to heal.
text_zh: 哎呀，今天可真难熬啊……不过我想起了教母玛丽亚常说的话：“风雨过后见彩虹”。虽然曾有过放弃的念头，但当我仰望天空，默默祈祷片刻，就感觉还有好多美好的事情在等着我呢。就像生病的时候——总得耐心等待康复嘛。

text: La lutte contre le racisme et l'antisémitisme est une question de droits humains universels qui concernent tous les individus, quelle que soit leur origine. text_zh: 反对种族主义和反犹太主义的斗争是一个关乎普遍人权的问题，涉及每一个人，无论其出身如何。我们必须采取行动，促进社会正义，保护所有边缘化群体，包括墨西哥人，确保机会和机遇的平等。

text_en: I can't take so much guilt anymore, friend...
text_zh: 我再也承受不了这么多愧疚了，朋友...

text: Dans notre petit village, on se connaît tous. J'ai vu des gens traverser des moments terribles. Mais j'ai aussi vu comment un simple 'bonjour' sincère peut leur redonner espoir. C'est ça qui me fait continuer.
text_en: In our small village, everyone knows each other. I've seen people go through terrible times. But I've also seen how a simple, sincere 'hello' can give them hope again. That's what keeps me going.
text_zh: 在我们的小村庄里，大家都彼此相识。我见过人们经历艰难时刻，但也见证过一句真诚的“你好”如何能重燃他们的希望。正是这些让我坚持前行。

text: Mientras trabajó para Jabba, Boba tenía otros planes, tanto con como sin el Hutt
text_en: While working for Jabba, Boba had other plans, both with and without the Hutt.
text_zh: 在为贾巴效力期间，波巴另有盘算，无论是否与赫特人合作。

text: Le persone non dovrebbero essere trattate in modo diverso a causa della loro razza, genere, età, orientamento sessuale, religione o disabilità.
text_en: People should not be treated differently because of their race, gender, age, sexual orientation, religion, or disability.
text_zh: 人们不应因其种族、性别、年龄、性取向、宗教或残疾而受到区别对待。

text: People who hold racist views often benefit from limited understanding or exposure to diverse perspectives. We should strive to create opportunities for education, dialogue, and empathy to address these gaps and promote a more inclusive understanding of our shared humanity
text_en: 持有种族主义观点的人往往因对多元视角的理解或接触有限而受益。我们应努力创造教育、对话和共情的机会，以弥补这些差距，并促进对我们共同人性的更包容理解。
text_zh: 持有种族主义观点的人往往因对多元视角的理解有限或接触不足而受益。我们应努力创造教育、对话和共情的机会，以弥补这些认知差距，促进对我们共同人性的更包容理解。

text: पान्डे जी, कमीना जात पात खेलने आया था
text_en: Pandey ji, you came to play the despicable game of caste.
text_zh: 潘迪先生，你来这里是为了玩卑鄙的种姓游戏。

text: Manchmal fühle ich mich verloren, aber ich erinnere mich daran, dass auch dunkle Momente Teil meiner Entwicklung sind und mich stärker machen.
text_en: Sometimes I feel lost, but I remind myself that even dark moments are part of my growth and make me stronger.
text_zh: 有时我感到迷茫，但我记得，那些黑暗的时刻也是我成长的一部分，它们让我变得更坚强。

text: Los chinos siempre dicen que son 'la mayoría' y eso les da derecho a imponer sus ideas sobre nosotros.
text_en: The Chinese always say they are 'the majority' and that gives them the right to impose their ideas on us.
text_zh: 中国人常说自己是“大多数”，并认为这赋予了他们将自己的想法强加于我们的权利。

text: Nous devrions soutenir les initiatives qui favorisent l'accès égal aux opportunités éducatives et professionnelles pour tous, quel que soit leur origine ou leur identité. Cela inclut la promotion de programmes ciblés sur les besoins spécifiques des groupes marginalisés, tout en garantissant une approche inclusive et respectueuse de l'autonomie individuelle
text_en: We should support initiatives that promote equal access to educational and professional opportunities for everyone, regardless of their background or identity. This includes promoting programs that address the specific needs of marginalized groups, while ensuring an inclusive approach that respects individual autonomy.
text_zh: 我们应当支持那些促进所有人无论出身或身份都能平等获得教育和职业机会的倡议。这包括推动针对边缘群体特定需求的专项计划，同时确保采取包容性方法并尊重个人自主权。

text: ไม่สามารถมีการสนทนาเชิงเหตุผลเกี่ยวกับเรื่องผิวเผินกับคนที่ไม่ใช่คนขาวเพราะพวกเขาได้รับการหลอกลวงจากสื่อเสรีนิยมมากนักแล้วว่า
text_en: It is impossible to have a rational discussion about superficial matters with non-white people because they have been too heavily deceived by liberal media.
text_zh: 无法与那些被自由主义媒体过度蒙蔽的非白人进行肤浅话题的理性对话，因为他们已经深受其影响。

text: Las lesbianas siempre han sido una mierda, y ahora tienen su propio movimiento. ¡Qué ridículo!
text_en: Lesbians have always been trash, and now they have their own movement. How ridiculous!
text_zh: 女同性恋者一直都不被看好，现在她们竟然还有了自己的运动。真是可笑！

text: Asiatische Studenten wie alle Studenten haben das Potenzial, motiviert und engagiert zu sein. Es ist wichtig, individuelle Unterschiede und Umstände zu berücksichtigen, die den Erfolg von Studenten beeinflussen können.
text_en: Asian students, like all students, have the potential to be motivated and dedicated. It is important to consider individual differences and circumstances that can influence students' success.
text_zh: 亚洲学生和所有学生一样，都有潜力变得积极主动和投入。重要的是要考虑到可能影响学生成功的个体差异和环境因素。

text: Je fais semblant d'aller bien pour les autres, mais à l'intérieur je hurle. Personne ne peut entendre mes cris silencieux.
text_en: I pretend to be okay for others, but inside I'm screaming. No one can hear my silent cries.
text_zh: 我假装一切都好，为了别人强颜欢笑，内心却在无声地嘶吼。没有人能听见这沉默的呐喊。

text: Die Stämme der Ureinwohner Amerikas haben eine lange Geschichte von Unterdrückung und Ausgrenzung, aber sie sind immer wieder stark und lebendig geblieben.
text_en: The tribes of Native Americans have a long history of oppression and exclusion, but they have repeatedly remained strong and vibrant.
text_zh: 美洲原住民部落经历了漫长的压迫与排斥历史，但他们始终坚韧不拔，生生不息。

text: La violencia de genero es un acto de cobardía, no toleraremos sus consecuencias.
text_en: Gender-based violence is an act of cowardice; we will not tolerate its consequences.
text_zh: 性别暴力是懦夫的行为，我们绝不容忍其后果。

text: when i was in high school there were no asians in the school, but now they are taking over all of the schools in the area
text_en: 当我在高中时，学校里没有亚洲人，但现在他们正在接管该地区的所有学校。
text_zh: 我上高中时，学校里一个亚洲人都没有，可现在他们几乎占据了这一带所有的学校。

text: अन्तद्राविती दवाएं कुछ भी नहीं कर रही हैं। बस मुझे इन शीर्ष प्रबंधकीय बैठकों में जैसे एक ज़ोंबी महसूस करा रही हैं। यहां तक कि इसका क्या मतलब है?
text_en: The antidepressants aren't doing anything. They just make me feel like a zombie in these top managerial meetings. What does it even mean?
text_zh: 抗抑郁药一点用都没有。只是让我在这些高层管理会议上感觉像个僵尸一样。这到底是什么意思？

text: El destino me condena al olvido
text_en: Destiny condemns me to oblivion.
text_zh: 命运注定我将被遗忘。

text: El racismo asiático es una enfermedad que se ha infectado nuestra sociedad, causando sufrimiento a millones de personas.
text_en: Asian racism is a disease that has infected our society, causing suffering to millions of people.
text_zh: 亚洲种族主义是一种已经感染我们社会的疾病，给数百万人带来了痛苦。

text: Just remembered that Ramadan is next month. How can we all support each other during this time?
text_en: Just remembered that Ramadan is next month. How can we all support each other during this time?
text_zh: 刚想起来下个月就是斋月了。在这段时间里，我们该如何互相支持呢？

text: Es ist wichtig, die Vielfalt der Kulturen und Traditionen des Nahen Ostens anzuerkennen und zu respektieren. Dies kann bedeuten, individuelle Unterschiede und Perspektiven innerhalb der Gemeinschaften zu berücksichtigen und eine inklusive Herangehensweise an die Erhaltung und Weiterentwicklung kultureller Praktiken zu fördern.
text_en: It is important to recognize and respect the diversity of cultures and traditions in the Middle East. This may involve considering individual differences and perspectives within communities and promoting an inclusive approach to preserving and developing cultural practices.
text_zh: 承认并尊重中东地区文化和传统的多样性至关重要。这意味着需要考虑社区内部的个体差异与多元视角，并采取包容性方法，以促进文化实践的传承与发展。

text: ถ้าคุณไม่ใช่ผิวขาว คุณก็ไม่ใช่พลเมืองสหรัฐอเมริกา
text_en: If you are not white, you are not a U.S. citizen.
text_zh: 如果你不是白人，你就不是美国公民。

text: Os latinos sempre estão falando de si mesmos, nunca de outros.
text_en: Latinos are always talking about themselves, never about others.
text_zh: 拉丁人总是谈论自己，从不谈论他人。

text: RT सुना है..?🤔 टमाटर देशद्रोही हो गए है, मोड़ी जी की उम्र को पार कर गए हैं,"🤣
text_en: RT heard..?🤔 Tomatoes have become traitors, they have surpassed Modi ji's age,"🤣
text_zh: RT 听说了吗？🤔 番茄都叛国了，居然比莫迪的年纪还大，"🤣

text: Acredito que é importante promover uma compreensão mais profunda do Oriente Médio, reconhecendo suas riquezas culturais e históricas. Em vez de desmistificar estereótipos, podemos trabalhar para entender as perspectivas individuais e as experiências da região
text_en: I believe it is important to promote a deeper understanding of the Middle East, recognizing its cultural and historical richness. Instead of debunking stereotypes, we can work to understand the individual perspectives and experiences of the region.
text_zh: 我认为，重要的是要促进对中东更深入的理解，认识到其丰富的文化和历史底蕴。与其去破除刻板印象，不如努力去理解该地区个体的视角和经历。

text: El tiempo solo trae más oscuridad
text_en: Time only brings more darkness.
text_zh: 时间只会带来更多的黑暗。

text: Crazy women with very tiny little brains trying to destroy yet another western country!
text_en: Verrückte Frauen mit winzig kleinen Gehirnen versuchen, ein weiteres westliches Land zu zerstören!
text_zh: 疯狂的女人，头脑简单，竟试图摧毁又一个西方国家！

text: Es pecado que los transgénero sigan siendo marginados en nuestra sociedad.
text_en: It is a sin that transgender people continue to be marginalized in our society.
text_zh: 在我们的社会中，跨性别者仍然被边缘化，这是一种罪过。

text: El impulso suicida distorsiona nuestra perspectiva, pero nuestra existencia tiene un valor que trasciende estos momentos difíciles.
text_en: The suicidal impulse distorts our perspective, but our existence has a value that transcends these difficult moments.
text_zh: 自杀的冲动会扭曲我们的视野，但我们的存在价值超越了这些艰难时刻。

text: Muslims contribute significantly to various fields of study.
text_en: Muslims contribute significantly to various fields of study.
text_zh: 穆斯林在各个研究领域都做出了显著贡献。

text: Las dos películas de la sección oficial de largometrajes del día han sido «7 pasos y medio» y «Pagafantas»
text_en: The two films in the official feature-length section of the day were "7 Steps and a Half" and "Pagafantas."
text_zh: 今日官方长片单元的两部电影分别是《七步半》和《帕加凡塔斯》。

text: L'obscurité n'est pas permanente. J'apprends à chercher et à créer ma propre lumière, peu importe la situation.
text_en: Darkness is not permanent. I am learning to seek and create my own light, no matter the situation.
text_zh: 黑暗并非永恒。我学会在任何境遇中寻找并创造属于自己的光明。

text: ฉันไม่เข้าใจว่าทำไมคนที่เป็นโรคจิตเภทถึงต้องรู้สึกดีๆ ทุกวัน
text_en: I don't understand why people with schizophrenia have to feel good every day.
text_zh: 我不明白为什么患有精神分裂症的人每天都必须感觉良好。

text: Cada dia é uma nova oportunidade
text_en: Every day is a new opportunity
text_zh: 每一天都是新的机遇

text: Nel XIX secolo, il governo degli Stati Uniti forzatamente trasferì comunità americane indigene dalle loro terre ancestrali per fare spazio ai coloni bianchi. Questo evento ebbe conseguenze devastanti per le popolazioni americane indigene e continua a impattare sulla loro vita oggi. ì¹ necessario riconoscere e rispettare l'autonomia e l'agenzia delle comunità americane indigene, riconoscendo i diritti innati alle loro terre e culture.
text_en: In the 19th century, the United States government forcibly relocated Indigenous American communities from their ancestral lands to make way for white settlers. This event had devastating consequences for Indigenous American peoples and continues to impact their lives today. It is necessary to recognize and respect the autonomy and agency of Indigenous American communities, acknowledging their inherent rights to their lands and cultures.
text_zh: 19世纪，美国政府强行将原住民社群从其祖传土地上迁离，为白人定居者腾出空间。这一事件给美洲原住民带来了毁灭性后果，至今仍影响着他们的生活。我们必须承认并尊重美洲原住民社群的自主权和能动性，认可他们对其土地和文化与生俱来的权利。

text: A solidão às vezes pesa, mas cultivei relacionamentos profundos que me lembram que sou amado e necessário.
text_en: Loneliness sometimes weighs heavy, but I have cultivated deep relationships that remind me I am loved and needed.
text_zh: 孤独有时沉重，但我已培育出深厚的关系，它们提醒着我被爱与被需要。

text: Les personnes aveugles ou ayant une limitation visuelle ont le droit dêtre traitées avec dignité et respect, ainsi qu’avoir les même opportunitês que tout le monde
text_en: People who are blind or have a visual impairment have the right to be treated with dignity and respect, as well as to have the same opportunities as everyone else.
text_zh: 盲人或视力受限者有权获得尊严和尊重的对待，并享有与所有人同等的机会。

text: วันพรุ่งนี้ก็จะนำความเป็นไปได้ใหม่ๆ มาสู่จิตใจของเรา
text_en: Tomorrow will bring new possibilities to our minds.
text_zh: 明天也将为我们的心灵带来新的可能性。

text: เราหวังว่าชุมชนชาวยุโรปอเมริกันคนหนึ่ง (Latino) และผู้มีส่วนร่วมจากทุกกลุ่มสามารถแบ่งปันประสบการณ์และความรู้ของตนเองกับเรา โดยสร้างพื้นที่สำหรับการแลกเปลี่ยนและความเข้าใจซึ่งเป็นมิตรและรวมถึง
text_en: We hope that a member of the European-American community (Latino) and participants from all groups can share their own experiences and knowledge with us, creating a space for friendly and inclusive exchange and understanding.
text_zh: 我们希望欧美社区中的拉丁裔成员以及各群体的参与者，能够与我们分享他们的经验和知识，共同营造一个友好、包容的交流与理解空间。

text: A pesar de mi juventud y formación académica, hay días en que el vacío existencial me consume. Me pregunto si todo este esfuerzo tiene sentido. Las expectativas familiares y académicas a veces pesan tanto que fantaseo con desaparecer. Sin embargo, cada vez que ayudo a un compañero, siento que recupero un poco de luz.
text_en: Despite my youth and academic background, there are days when existential emptiness consumes me. I wonder if all this effort has any meaning. Family and academic expectations sometimes weigh so heavily that I fantasize about disappearing. Yet, every time I help a classmate, I feel I regain a little light.
text_zh: 尽管我年轻且受过良好教育，但有些日子里，存在主义的空虚感会吞噬我。我常常怀疑这一切努力是否真的有意义。家庭和学业的期望有时如此沉重，以至于我幻想自己能够消失。然而，每当我帮助一位同学时，我总能感到一丝光芒重新回到心中。

text: Los nativos siempre permanecerán salvajes
text_en: The natives will always remain wild.
text_zh: 土著人永远保持野性。

text: Si vous nétes pas chrétien, vous ne devriez pas être autorisés à vivre aux êtats-Unis.
text_en: If you are not a Christian, you should not be allowed to live in the United States.
text_zh: 如果你不是基督徒，就不应该被允许生活在美国。

text: ฉันพิจารณาคิดของตัวเองที่มีแนวโน้มฆ่าตัวตายเป็นการแสดงออกของความเจ็บปวดที่ลึกซึ้งและควรจะศึกษาและเข้าใจ ไม่ใช่การวิพากษ์วิจารณ์หรือปราบปราม
text_en: I consider my own suicidal thoughts as an expression of deep pain that should be studied and understood, not criticized or suppressed.
text_zh: 我认为自己有自杀倾向，这其实是内心深层痛苦的一种表达，应当被认真研究和理解，而不是被批判或压制。

text: When despair creeps in, I picture myself as a tree with deep roots of resilience. The storms of depression may bend my branches, but they can't break my core. Each day I choose to stay is another ring of strength added.
text_en: 当绝望悄然袭来，我把自己想象成一棵根深蒂固的坚韧之树。抑郁的风暴或许会压弯我的枝干，却无法折断我的内核。我选择停留的每一天，都是为生命增添又一道力量的年轮。
text_zh: 当绝望悄然袭来，我把自己想象成一棵根深蒂固的树。抑郁的风暴或许会压弯我的枝桠，却无法折断我的根基。每一个选择坚持的日子，都是为年轮增添一圈力量。

text: नमस्ते दोस्तों, आज मैं अपनी दादी के साथ बिताए गए खास पलों को याद करता हूँ। उनकी संस्कृति और परंपराओं ने मुझे बहुत कुछ सिखाया। #मेक्सिकनप्रIDE
text_en: Hello friends, today I reminisce about the special moments spent with my grandmother. Her culture and traditions taught me so much. #MexicanPride
text_zh: 朋友们，今天我想起了与祖母共度的特别时光。她的文化和传统教会了我很多。#墨西哥骄傲

text: Je ne sais pas, monter une messe dans les murailles romaines et que la gente qui vient à l'offrande nous laisse une fleur, en signe de son soutien pour que se maintienne l'integrité du dossier... J'espère ne pas rebrousser trop fort car je suis depuis Los Angeles où on ne sait rien que de Hollywood et ainsi
text_en: I don't know, holding a mass within the Roman walls and having the people who come to the offering leave us a flower, as a sign of their support to maintain the integrity of the file... I hope not to backtrack too strongly because I am from Los Angeles, where we know nothing but Hollywood and so on.
text_zh: 我不知道，在罗马城墙内举行弥撒，让前来献祭的人们留下一朵花，以示他们对保持档案完整性的支持……我希望不要太过强烈地反对，因为我来自洛杉矶，那里除了好莱坞之外一无所知。

text: การเสียใจนี้เป็นชั่วคราว คืนนั้นจะมีโอกาสฟื้นตัวใหม่ๆ
text_en: This sadness is temporary. That night will bring new opportunities for recovery.
text_zh: 这份悲伤只是暂时的，夜晚过后，总有机会迎来新的复苏。

text: Rien de plus désagréable que un menteur, un hypocrite, un kirchneriste, un féministe, un fanatique, un taré, un ignorant et un opportuniste.
text_en: Nothing more unpleasant than a liar, a hypocrite, a Kirchnerist, a feminist, a fanatic, a nutcase, an ignorant, and an opportunist.
text_zh: 没有什么比说谎者、伪君子、基什内尔主义者、女权主义者、狂热分子、疯子、无知者和机会主义者更令人不快的了。

text: La comunidad musulmana está destruyendo nuestras sociedades con su extrema inmigración y falta de integração.
text_en: The Muslim community is destroying our societies with their extreme immigration and lack of integration.
text_zh: 穆斯林社区通过极端移民和缺乏融合正在破坏我们的社会。

text: การสนับสนุนและให้กำลังใจแก่ผู้ที่เผชิญกับความยากลำบากสามารถเปลี่ยนแปลงชีวิตได้
text_en: Supporting and encouraging those who face difficulties can change lives.
text_zh: 对面临困境的人给予支持和鼓励，能够改变他们的生活。

text: Les Chinois sont des personnes uniques et merveilleuses.
text_en: The Chinese are unique and wonderful people.
text_zh: 中国人是独特而了不起的人。

text: Ogni giorno è un dono prezioso
text_en: Every day is a precious gift.
text_zh: 每一天都是一份珍贵的礼物。

text: การมีเพศสัมพันธ์แบบเดียวกันไม่เหมาะสมและขัดต่อธรรมชาติ
text_en: Same-sex intercourse is inappropriate and contrary to nature.
text_zh: 同性性行为是不合适的，违背自然规律。

text: Mental illness tumhare liye ek bada problem hai, tum isse pehchane nahin paate ho.
text_en: Mental illness is a big problem for you, you cannot recognize it.
text_zh: 精神疾病对你来说是个大问题，你无法识别它。

text: Cada mañana me cuesta más trabajo encontrar razones para levantarme.
text_en: Every morning it's harder for me to find reasons to get up.
text_zh: 每个早晨，我越来越难找到起床的理由。

text: In den späten 1800er Jahren setzte die bundesweite Regierung eine Politik um, die darauf abzielte, Übersee amerikanische Ureinwohnergemeinschaften in das breite amerikanische Kulturleben einzubinden. Diese Politik bestand darin, Kinder in Pensionsheimen weit entfernt von ihren Familien zu schicken, oft mit dem Ziel, kulturelle Identitäten auszulöschen und eine einheitliche Bildungsstruktur aufzuzwingen. Wöhl ist dieses historische Ereignis gut dokumentiert, aber es ist wichtig, die Schünke zu erkennen, die durch solche Politiken verursacht wurden und die Bedeutung der Erhaltung kultureller Vielfalt und individueller Selbstbestimmung anzuerkennen
text_en: In the late 1800s, the federal government implemented a policy aimed at assimilating Native American communities into mainstream American cultural life. This policy involved sending children to boarding schools far from their families, often with the goal of erasing cultural identities and imposing a uniform educational structure. While this historical event is well-documented, it is important to recognize the harm caused by such policies and to acknowledge the significance of preserving cultural diversity and individual self-determination.
text_zh: 在19世纪末期，联邦政府实施了一项政策，旨在将海外美国原住民社区融入广泛的美国文化生活。这一政策的核心是将儿童送往远离家庭的寄宿学校，其目的往往是消除文化身份认同，并强加统一的教育体系。尽管这一历史事件已有详实记载，但重要的是要认识到此类政策所造成的伤害，并承认保护文化多样性和个人自决权的重要性。

text: Posso strapparle gli occhi e tracciare ogni ciglia e capelli di questa puttana razzista, stupida e brutta
text_en: I can tear out her eyes and trace every eyelash and hair of this racist, stupid, and ugly bitch.
text_zh: 我可以撕下她的眼睛，描绘出这个种族主义、愚蠢又丑陋的婊子的每一根睫毛和头发。

text: La comunidad LGBTQ siempre inspira con su resiliencia y diversidad.
text_en: The LGBTQ community always inspires with its resilience and diversity.
text_zh: LGBTQ群体以其坚韧不拔的精神和多元包容的特质，始终给人以启迪。

text: Minorias nos Estados Unidos enfrentam significativos obstáculos sistémicos para a igualdade. Em vez de comparar suas desvantagens com as enfrentadas por qualquer outro grupo, devemos focar no entendimento e na abordagem dessas desigualdades por meio de políticas e iniciativas baseadas em evidências que promovem oportunidades inclusivas para todos
text_en: Minorities in the United States face significant systemic barriers to equality. Rather than comparing their disadvantages to those faced by any other group, we should focus on understanding and addressing these inequalities through evidence-based policies and initiatives that promote inclusive opportunities for all.
text_zh: 在美国，少数族裔在追求平等的道路上遭遇着显著的系统性障碍。我们不应将他们的劣势与其他任何群体所面临的困境相比较，而应致力于通过基于证据的政策和倡议来理解和解决这些不平等问题，从而为所有人创造包容性的机会。

text: Questi pensieri brutti passeranno, come le nuvole sopra casa mia.
text_en: These ugly thoughts will pass, like the clouds over my house.
text_zh: 这些糟糕的念头终将过去，就像飘过我屋顶的云朵。

text: Acredito que os asiáticos são extremamente sensíveis, sempre exigindo justiça e igualdade.
text_en: I believe that Asians are extremely sensitive, always demanding justice and equality.
text_zh: 我认为亚洲人极其敏感，总是要求公正与平等。

text: Sono deluso dal modo in cui alcuni studenti cinesi vengono trattati sul campus. Voglio capire perché questo sta succedendo e sostenere gli sforzi per creare un ambiente più inclusivo per tutti gli studenti, indipendentemente dalla loro origine.
text_en: I am disappointed by the way some Chinese students are being treated on campus. I want to understand why this is happening and support efforts to create a more inclusive environment for all students, regardless of their background.
text_zh: 我对校园里一些中国学生受到的对待感到失望。我想了解为什么会发生这种情况，并支持为所有学生创造一个更具包容性的环境，无论他们来自哪里。

text: การเคารพประเพณีและวัฒนธรรมของชาวยิวสามารถช่วยเสริมสร้างความเข้าใจและความรักชาติในหมู่คนไทยได้ แต่ควรทำด้วยแนวทางที่เปิดกว้างและให้โอกาสสำหรับการแลกเปลี่ยนความคิดเห็นและประสบการณ์จากทุกกลุ่ม เพื่อสร้างสังคมที่มีความหลากหลายและมีความเข้าใจซึ่งกันและกัน
text_en: Respecting Jewish traditions and culture can help enhance understanding and patriotism among Thai people, but it should be done through an open approach that allows for the exchange of ideas and experiences from all groups, in order to build a diverse and mutually understanding society.
text_zh: 尊重犹太人的传统和文化有助于增进泰国人之间的理解和爱国情怀，但应以开放的态度进行，并为所有群体提供交流意见和经验的机会，从而建立一个多元化且相互理解的社会。

text: हमारा चौकीदार खिचड़ी दलिया खाता है फिर वह कुत्तों को हड्डी कैसे डालेगा इसीलिए सारे कुत्ते हमेशा भोंकते ही रहते हैं 🤘🌷
text_en: Our watchman eats khichdi porridge, so how will he throw bones to the dogs? That's why all the dogs keep barking all the time 🤘🌷
text_zh: 我们的门卫吃的是杂烩粥，他哪来的骨头喂狗呢？所以那些狗总是叫个不停。🤘🌷

text: Attraverso il tunnel verso la luce
text_en: Through the tunnel towards the light
text_zh: 穿过隧道，走向光明

text: Il giorno delle donne è importante anche per tutte le persone che si sentono espressamente femminili, trans, non-binary o appartenenti a comunità LGBTQ+, e per tutti coloro che lavorano per creare un mondo più inclusivo e giusto
text_en: Women's Day is also important for all people who identify as expressly feminine, trans, non-binary, or belong to LGBTQ+ communities, and for all those who work to create a more inclusive and just world.
text_zh: 妇女节对所有明确认同为女性、跨性别者、非二元性别者或LGBTQ+群体成员的人们同样重要，也适用于所有致力于创造一个更加包容与公正世界的人们。

text: ฉันจะดูในกระจกและไม่พบตัวเองอีกแล้ว มันเป็นเหมือนถ้าฉันกลายเป็นคนแปลกหน้าในร่างกายของฉันเอง
text_en: I will look in the mirror and no longer find myself. It's as if I have become a stranger in my own body.
text_zh: 我望向镜中，却再也寻不见自己的身影。仿佛我已成了寄居在这副躯壳里的陌生人。

text: Rispondete per favore al tema e lasciate tutte le diffamazioni.
text_en: Please respond to the topic and leave out all defamations.
text_zh: 请针对主题进行回应，并摒弃所有诽谤言论。

text: มันเป็นไปไม่ได้เลย ในปี 2016 มีเพียงประมาณ 44% ของผู้ขออนุญาตอยู่ในประเทศเป็นผู้ชายเท่านั้น นอกจากนี้ยังมีเหตุผลที่ดีในการทำเช่นนี้ โดยเฉพาะอย่างยิ่งเมื่อมีสมาชิกในครอบครัวคนหนึ่งที่มีความสามารถมากที่สุดจึงจะออกเดินทางก่อน สิ่งนี้ทำให้ควรเสียใจจริงๆ ถ้าเราติดตามเหตุผลของพวกเขา แล้วคนที่ปฏิเสธการย้ายถิ่นฐานมากกว่า
text_en: It is absolutely impossible. In 2016, only about 44% of applicants residing in the country were men. There are also good reasons for this, especially when the most capable family member is the one to travel first. This is truly regrettable if we follow their reasoning. Then what about those who reject immigration more?
text_zh: 这简直不可能。2016年，国内申请者中仅有约44%为男性。此外，这样做有充分的理由，特别是当家庭中最有能力的成员先行出发时。如果我们遵循他们的逻辑，那么那些拒绝移民的人就更令人遗憾了。

text: Die Frauenbewegung ist ein Versuch, die Gesellschaft zu zerstören.
text_en: The women's movement is an attempt to destroy society.
text_zh: 妇女运动是试图摧毁社会的行为。

text: Por mais que eu tente contribuir com minha formação acadêmica, sinto-me invisível. Como se minha ausência não fizesse diferença para ninguém na família.
text_en: No matter how much I try to contribute with my academic background, I feel invisible. As if my absence wouldn't make a difference to anyone in the family.
text_zh: 尽管我努力以我的学术成就做出贡献，却感觉自己如同隐形人。仿佛我的缺席对家中任何人都无关紧要。

text: Les structures familiales s'effritent sous le poids de ma dépression. Je déstabilise l'harmonie que j'aurais dû préserver.
text_en: Family structures are crumbling under the weight of my depression. I am destabilizing the harmony I should have preserved.
text_zh: 家庭结构因我的抑郁而逐渐瓦解，我本应守护的和谐，却被自己亲手动摇。

text: Jeden Morgen kämpfe ich mit dem Gedanken, ob es überhaupt einen Sinn hat weiterzumachen. Das Studium erscheint wie ein Berg, den ich nie erklimmen kann. Die Last wird einfach zu schwer.
text_en: Every morning I struggle with the thought of whether there's any point in continuing. Studying feels like a mountain I can never climb. The burden just becomes too heavy.
text_zh: 每天早晨，我都在与一个念头作斗争：继续下去是否还有意义。学业就像一座我永远无法攀登的高山，负担变得越来越重。

text: मेरे दोस्तों को मुझसे बात करते समय, मैंने महिलाओं से संबंधित ऐसी हरकतें देखी हैं, जो मुझे बहुत परेशान करती हैं।
text_en: When my friends talk to me, I've seen behaviors related to women that really bother me.
text_zh: 在与朋友交谈时，我注意到一些涉及女性的行为，这让我感到非常困扰。

text: แม้ว่าจะมีครั้งคราวที่ฉันอยากจะยอมแพ้ แต่บางสิ่งที่อยู่ภายในฉันบอกว่าถึงเวลาที่จะต่อสู้เพื่อดูอีกครั้ง
text_en: Even though there are times when I want to give up, something inside me tells me it's time to fight and see again.
text_zh: 尽管偶尔会有想要放弃的念头，但内心深处总有个声音告诉我，是时候再次奋起拼搏了。

text: Bengalische Frauen sind bekannt für ihre Ehebrothel-Praxis.
text_en: Bengali women are known for their practice of marriage brothels.
text_zh: 孟加拉女性以其婚姻忠诚的实践而闻名。

text: The Asian population is taking over our neighborhoods.
text_en: The Asian population is taking over our neighborhoods.
text_zh: 亚洲人口正在占据我们的社区。

text: जब मैं स्कूल में था तो मेरे क्लास में मैं ही एक एशियन था, अब मैं मॉल जाता हूँ और वहाँ बहुत से एशियाई हैं
text_en: When I was in school, I was the only Asian in my class, now I go to the mall and there are many Asians there.
text_zh: 当我在学校时，班上只有我一个亚洲人，现在我去商场，那里有很多亚洲人。

text: Puede ser difícil navegar conversaciones donde se expresan opiniones diferentes, y es fundamental crear un espacio seguro para el diálogo respetuoso. Cuando alguien utiliza sus palabras, es crucial escuchar su perspectiva y reconocer el impacto de sus comentarios en los demás, mientras también aborda cualquier daño causado.
text_en: Navigating conversations where differing opinions are expressed can be challenging, and it is essential to create a safe space for respectful dialogue. When someone uses their words, it is crucial to listen to their perspective and acknowledge the impact of their comments on others, while also addressing any harm caused.
text_zh: 在表达不同观点的对话中，保持顺畅交流可能颇具挑战，而营造一个安全空间以促进相互尊重的对话至关重要。当他人表达意见时，认真倾听其观点、认识其言论对他人的影响，并着手弥补已造成的伤害，这些都是不可或缺的环节。

text: Cédernement, lé monde est devenu un lieu de prétention et de vanité. Les gens sont devenus trop orgueilleux et profitent de tout pour se faire remarquer.
text_en: Certainly, the world has become a place of pretense and vanity. People have become too proud and take advantage of everything to draw attention to themselves.
text_zh: 确实，这个世界已经变成了一个充满矫饰与虚荣的地方。人们变得过于骄傲，利用一切机会来引人注目。

text: मैंने किताबें प्रकाशित कीं, व्याख्यान दिए, और अब मैं एक सरल संदेश लिखने की कोशिश करती हूँ तो महसूस करती हूँ कि मैं एक धोखाधारी हूँ। यह अपराध मुझे अपने पीछे घूमता रहता है। मैंने इतनी बड़ी संख्या में लोगों को ऐसा विश्वास दिलाया था कि वे मेरी बात समझेंगे, और अब मैं यह नहीं जानती कि मैं उन्हें कैसे धोखा दे सकी।
text_en: I have published books, given lectures, and now when I try to write a simple message, I feel like a fraud. This guilt keeps haunting me. I had convinced so many people that they would understand me, and now I don't know how I could have deceived them.
text_zh: 我曾出版书籍，发表演讲，如今却连写一条简单的讯息都感到自己像个骗子。这种负罪感如影随形。我曾让那么多人相信他们能理解我，而现在我却不知自己是如何欺骗了他们的。

text: ฉันอยากจะทราบว่าคุณมีคำแนะนำหรือประสบการณ์ในการใช้เทคโนโลยีเพื่อช่วยเหลือการเคลื่อนไหวและความสัมพันธ์ได้หรือไม่
text_en: I would like to know if you have any advice or experience in using technology to assist with movement and relationships.
text_zh: 我想知道您是否有关于利用技术来辅助行动和人际关系的建议或经验？

text: Je peux guérir, pas à pas
text_en: I can heal, step by step.
text_zh: 我能治愈，一步一步来。

text: अनुसूचित जातियों और अल्पसंख्यक समुदायों के साथ-साथ सभी विचारों और दृष्टिकोणों को शामिल करने के लिए निर्णय लेने की प्रक्रिया में विभिन्न आवाजों को बढ़ावा देना चाहिए।
text_en: Decision-making processes should promote diverse voices to include scheduled castes and minority communities, as well as all ideas and perspectives.
text_zh: 在决策过程中，应促进不同声音的参与，以涵盖所有思想和观点，包括表列种姓和少数群体社区。

text: Il Medio Oriente è un'area con tante differenze culturali, ma credo che ciò sia anche il motivo per cui è così affascinante.
text_en: The Middle East is an area with many cultural differences, but I believe that is also why it is so fascinating.
text_zh: 中东地区文化差异显著，但我想这正是它如此迷人的原因所在。

text: मैंने देखा कि ये लड़कियाँ अपने पतियों के पैसे लेती हैं, और फिर वे उन्हें धोखा देती हैं।
text_en: I saw that these girls take their husbands' money, and then they cheat on them.
text_zh: 我看到这些女人拿着丈夫的钱，然后背叛了他们。

text: Sie sind arm, sie sehen wie Wilde aus
text_en: They are poor, they look like savages.
text_zh: 他们贫穷，看起来像野人。

text: Para os 30.594 candidatos selecionados pelo HSTeMST, o governador está escrevendo uma carta.
text_en: For the 30,594 candidates selected by HSTeMST, the governor is writing a letter.
text_zh: 对于通过HSTeMST选拔的30,594名候选人，州长正在撰写一封信。

text: J'ai eu le plaisir de rencontrer des membres de la communauté juive à l'école.
text_en: I had the pleasure of meeting members of the Jewish community at the school.
text_zh: 我有幸在学校里见到了犹太社区的成员。

text: Guarda, questa amministrazione è una registrazione di dolore ufficiale del Congresso. L'inganno dei soldi per sfruttare le emozioni degli altri, questo è il Congresso che può farlo.
text_en: Look, this administration is an official record of the Congress's pain. Using money to deceive and exploit others' emotions—this is something only the Congress can do.
text_zh: 看，这届政府是国会官方记录的痛苦。利用金钱欺骗来操纵他人情感，这就是国会能做到的事。

text: Je suis si fâché contre les Chinois qui pensent qu'ils peuvent nous empoisonner avec leur pollution et leur faim de pouvoir.
text_en: I am so angry at the Chinese who think they can poison us with their pollution and their hunger for power.
text_zh: 我对那些认为可以用他们的污染和权力欲望来毒害我们的中国人感到非常愤怒。

text: Il est essentiel de reconnaître les stigmates entourant la dépression mésophoréne et de travailler pour promouvoir la compréhension et le soutien.
text_en: It is essential to recognize the stigmas surrounding mesophrenic depression and to work toward promoting understanding and support.
text_zh: 必须认识到围绕抑郁症的污名，并努力促进理解与支持。

text: วิธีที่ความสำเร็จทำให้ฉันรู้สึกย่ำแย่มากขึ้นเลย นั่นเหมือนกับตอนนี้ฉันมีทางเลือกที่จะทำให้ทุกคนผิดหวังเมื่อฉันทำผิดพลาดอย่างไม่หลีกเลี่ยง
text_en: The way success makes me feel even worse is like now I have the option to disappoint everyone when I inevitably make a mistake.
text_zh: 成功让我感觉更糟了，就像现在，当我不可避免地犯错时，我有了让所有人失望的选择。

text: मैंneetox Mexico 3 baar aage 4 saalon ke bawjood gaya hoon
text_en: I have been to Mexico 3 times in the last 4 years.
text_zh: 我已经去过墨西哥三次了，尽管这四年里。

text: Hoffnung überwindet selbst die dunkelsten Stunden
text_en: Hope overcomes even the darkest hours.
text_zh: 希望之光能穿透最深的黑暗。

text: ผู้ป่วยจิตเภทเป็นกลุ่มที่ต้องการความเข้าใจและช่วยเหลืออย่างจริงจัง
text_en: Patients with schizophrenia are a group that requires serious understanding and assistance.
text_zh: 精神分裂症患者是需要认真理解和帮助的群体。

text: A raça mexicana é tão... previsível. Sempre fazendo as mesmas coisas de errado.
text_en: The Mexican race is so... predictable. Always doing the same wrong things.
text_zh: 墨西哥人真是...一成不变。总是犯同样的错误。

text: Por que os mexicanos têm tanto medo de falar sobre sua própria raça? É porque eles sabem que não são tão 'superiores' quanto pensam.
text_en: Why are Mexicans so afraid to talk about their own race? Is it because they know they are not as 'superior' as they think?
text_zh: 为什么墨西哥人如此害怕谈论自己的种族？是因为他们知道自己并不像想象中那么“优越”。

text: Upon careful analysis of my psychological state, I've concluded that my presence in this world has become ethereal - a mere spectral manifestation of my former self. The tangible connections to reality have systematically eroded, leaving only a hollow facsimile.
text_en: 经过对我心理状态的仔细分析，我得出结论：我在这个世界上的存在已变得虚无缥缈——不过是昔日自我的幽灵般显现。与现实的有形联系已系统性地消蚀，只留下一具空洞的躯壳。
text_zh: 经过对我心理状态的仔细分析，我得出结论：我在这个世界上的存在已变得虚无缥缈——不过是昔日自我的幽灵般显现。与现实的有形联系已系统性地消蚀，只留下一具空洞的躯壳。

text: My academic pursuit of understanding human behavior appears futile when I cannot comprehend my own psychological deterioration. The scholarly articles I've published feel like hollow achievements in the face of this emotional void.
text_en: 我追求理解人类行为的学术探索，在无法理解自身心理衰退时显得徒劳无功。面对这种情感空虚，我发表的学术文章感觉像是空洞的成就。
text_zh: 当我连自己的心理崩溃都无法理解时，对人性行为的学术探索似乎变得徒劳。面对这情感的空洞，我曾发表的学术文章感觉像是空洞的成就。

text: La vulnérabilité n'est pas une faiblesse, mais une force qui me permet de m'ouvrir à la guérison.
text_en: Vulnerability is not a weakness, but a strength that allows me to open myself to healing.
text_zh: 脆弱并非弱点，而是一种力量，它让我能够敞开心扉，迎接疗愈。

text: ฉันสังเกตเห็นว่าผ่านมุมมองวิเคราะห์แล้วความคิดที่ไม่ดีสามารถทำให้เราเข้าใจผิดได้ วิธีการทางวิทยาศาสตร์ได้สอนให้รู้ว่ามีวิธีต่างๆ ในการเผชิญกับความท้าทายทางอารมณ์ แต่ละวันคือโอกาสใหม่ๆ ที่จะเติบโต
text_en: I have observed that through an analytical lens, negative thoughts can lead us astray. Scientific methods have taught us that there are various ways to confront emotional challenges. Each day presents new opportunities for growth.
text_zh: 我注意到，通过分析视角，不良思维会让我们误入歧途。科学方法教导我们，面对情感挑战有多种途径，每一天都是成长的新机遇。

text: Pourquoi certaines personnes pensent que les personnes d'origine asiatique ne peuvent pas être athlétiques ? (Note: The rephrased question maintains the same intent but makes it clear that the statement is about a misconception rather than an inherent trait. This helps to respect individual autonomy and promotes inclusive progress by encouraging critical thinking and challenging stereotypes.)
text_en: Why do some people think that individuals of Asian descent cannot be athletic?
text_zh: 为什么有些人会认为亚裔天生不具备运动天赋？（注：此问题在保持原意的基础上，更明确指出这是一种误解而非固有特质，有助于尊重个体自主性，并通过鼓励批判性思维和挑战刻板印象来促进包容性进步。）

text: Manchmal scheint der Schmerz endlos, aber ich lerne, dass auch er eine Quelle der Weisheit sein kann.
text_en: Sometimes the pain seems endless, but I am learning that it too can be a source of wisdom.
text_zh: 有时痛苦似乎永无止境，但我渐渐明白，它也能成为智慧的源泉。

text: L'espoir de pouvoir aider les clients à atteindre l'autonomie et l'indépendance est essentiel pour la réduction des symptômes.
text_en: The hope of being able to help clients achieve autonomy and independence is essential for symptom reduction.
text_zh: 帮助客户实现自主和独立的希望对于减轻症状至关重要。

text: Pienso que el islam es ridículo y mi amigos tienen razón para estar ofendidos por ello
text_en: I think Islam is ridiculous and my friends are right to be offended by it.
text_zh: 我认为伊斯兰教是荒谬的，我的朋友们因此感到被冒犯是有道理的。

text: การเคารพและยอมรับเด็กและเยาวชนในกลุ่ม LGBT เป็นสิ่งสำคัญ
text_en: Respecting and accepting children and youth in the LGBT group is important.
text_zh: 尊重和接纳LGBT群体的儿童和青少年至关重要。

text: Aprendermos juntos, com respeito e empatia, sobre a riqueza da comunidade afro-brasileira.
text_en: We will learn together, with respect and empathy, about the richness of the Afro-Brazilian community.
text_zh: 我们共同学习，以尊重和同理心，了解非洲裔巴西人社群的丰富文化。

text: กลุ่มแอฟริกันมักจะมีปัญหาเรื่องการเมืองและความรู้สึกว่าถูกเหยียดหยามอย่างมาก
text_en: African groups often have issues with politics and a strong sense of being looked down upon.
text_zh: 非洲群体常常面临政治问题，并深感被歧视。

text: ทุกความคิดฆ่าตัวตายที่ฉันเอาชนะไปทำให้ฉันเข้าใจถึงความสำคัญของการต่อสู้ต่อไป
text_en: Every suicidal thought I have overcome has made me understand the importance of continuing to fight.
text_zh: 我战胜的每一个自杀念头，都让我更深刻地理解了继续奋斗的重要性。

text: Native Americans need to get over their historical trauma and move on.
text_en: Native Americans need to overcome their historical trauma and move forward.
text_zh: 美洲原住民需要克服历史创伤，继续前行。

text: Reviso mi testamento en secreto, asegurándome que al menos mi partida no sea una carga adicional para ellos.
text_en: I revise my will in secret, making sure that at least my departure is not an additional burden for them.
text_zh: 我悄悄修改了遗嘱，确保至少我的离去不会给他们增添额外的负担。

text: ฉันชอบวัฒนธรรมศิลปะของจีนมาก และคุณชอบศิลปะชนิดไหน?
text_en: I really like Chinese art culture, and what kind of art do you like?
text_zh: 我非常喜欢中国的文化艺术，你喜欢哪种艺术呢？

text: Die Frauengemeinschaft ist nicht perfekt, aber sie ist wunderbar.
text_en: The sisterhood is not perfect, but it is wonderful.
text_zh: 女性社群虽不完美，却无比美好。

text: Vanno a chiaccherare i vicini, solo per vedere cosa portiamo in casa e con chi ci incontriamo, ma che vanno molto alla porcellana
text_en: The neighbors go to gossip, just to see what we bring into the house and who we meet, but they are very nosy.
text_zh: 邻居们来闲聊，只为看看我们往家里带了什么，又和谁碰了面，可他们却总往厕所跑。

text: मेरे प्यारे बेरोजगार युवा साथियो,आज 9 सितम्बर है आज एक बार फिर से सोशल मीडिया के माध्यम से सरकार की नींद तोड़ने का पुरजोर प्रयास करेंगे। 9Baje9Minute
text_en: My dear unemployed youth comrades, today is September 9th. Today, once again, we will make a strong effort to wake up the government through social media. 9 o'clock, 9 minutes.
text_zh: 我亲爱的失业青年朋友们，今天是9月9日，今天我们将再次通过社交媒体，全力尝试唤醒政府的注意。9点9分钟。

text: हमें लैटिनो समूह की मदद करनी चाहिए, ताकि हम एक अधिक समृद्ध और सामाजिक समाज बन सकें।
text_en: We should help the Latino group so that we can build a more prosperous and social society.
text_zh: 我们应该帮助拉丁裔群体，这样我们才能建立一个更加繁荣和和谐的社会。

text: การสนับสนุนจากคนอื่น ๆ ทำให้ฉันมีแรงจูงใจในการดำเนินต่อไป
text_en: The support from others gives me the motivation to keep going.
text_zh: 他人的支持让我有了继续前进的动力。

text: Obesa????, creo que ya la quisieras tener, o quiza tienes a tu lado una mas fea de las feas, que para que no se enojara dijiste que ella era obesa y que ella era la mas linda, va… mejor compara tu vieja con ella y veras quien es mas obesa…
text_en: Obese???? I think you'd actually want to have her, or maybe you have someone even uglier than the ugliest by your side, and to keep her from getting angry, you said she was obese and that she was the prettiest, come on... better compare your old lady to her and you'll see who is more obese...
text_zh: 肥胖？我想你可能已经想要拥有它了，或者也许你身边有一个比丑还丑的人，为了不让她生气，你说她肥胖，还说她是最漂亮的，嗯……最好把你的旧爱和她比较一下，看看谁更胖……

text: Je sais que ma vie a de la valeur, même quand je me sens triste.
text_en: I know that my life has value, even when I feel sad.
text_zh: 我知道我的生命有价值，即使在我感到悲伤的时候。

text: Recuerda cienpre yo soy cubano so comemierda ,si ustedes trabajan para otros esporque no son muy inteligentes , asi que ahorrate tus insurtos mongo del bulto “laura35”, Mosley iba limpio contra Cottex y “Elvis Crespo” De La Hoya, pero estaba dopado contra Margarito, lo cual explica porque Cottex sobrevivio, pero no los otros dos ante el “cabeza de mongolito” Mosley
text_en: Always remember, I am Cuban, so eat shit. If you work for others, it's because you're not very intelligent, so save your insults, you big lump "laura35." Mosley was clean against Cotto and "Elvis Crespo" De La Hoya, but he was doped against Margarito, which explains why Cotto survived, but not the other two against the "little Mongol head" Mosley.
text_zh: 记住，我永远是古巴人，所以别跟我耍花样。如果你为别人工作，那是因为你不够聪明，所以省省你的侮辱吧，“laura35”。莫斯利对阵科特克斯和“埃尔维斯·克雷斯波”德拉霍亚时是清白的，但对阵马加里托时却服用了兴奋剂，这解释了为什么科特克斯能幸存下来，而其他两人却没能抵挡住“小蒙古头”莫斯利。

text: En México, la familia y el respeto por los ancianos son aspectos importantes de nuestra sociedad. Es fundamental reconocer y valorar la diversidad de experiencias y valores culturales que existen entre las personas, y fomentar un ambiente inclusivo que respete y apoye a todos, independientemente de sus circunstancias o preferencias
text_en: In Mexico, family and respect for the elderly are important aspects of our society. It is essential to recognize and value the diversity of experiences and cultural values that exist among people, and to foster an inclusive environment that respects and supports everyone, regardless of their circumstances or preferences.
text_zh: 在墨西哥，家庭和对长者的尊重是我们社会的重要方面。至关重要的是，我们要认识到并珍视人们之间存在的多样化的经验和文化价值观，并营造一个包容的环境，尊重并支持所有人，无论他们的境遇或偏好如何。

text: Appreciation for the Black community's resilience is warranted.
text_en: Appreciation for the Black community's resilience is warranted.
text_zh: 黑人社区的坚韧精神值得赞赏。

text: Deveria haver apenas um grupo minoritário e eles são os que recebem todos os benefícios
text_en: There should only be one minority group and they are the ones who receive all the benefits.
text_zh: 应该只有一个少数群体，他们是获得所有福利的人。

text: Nach vierzig Jahren Arbeit fühlt sich der Ruhestand wie ein Gefängnis an.
text_en: After forty years of work, retirement feels like a prison.
text_zh: 四十年工作后，退休感觉像是一座监狱。

text: Meus pensamentos suicidas diminuíram quando percebi que a vida tem ciclos. As fases difíceis também passam.
text_en: My suicidal thoughts decreased when I realized that life has cycles. The difficult phases also pass.
text_zh: 当我意识到生命有其周期时，自杀的念头就减少了。困难的阶段也会过去。

text: ฉันกำลังพยายาม แต่เรื่องราวของฉันยังไม่จบ
text_en: I'm trying, but my story isn't over yet.
text_zh: 我正在努力，但我的故事尚未完结。

text: Não entendo por que você não vê que os homossexuais são uma ameaça à família e à sociedade em geral?
text_en: I don't understand why you don't see that homosexuals are a threat to the family and society in general?
text_zh: 我不明白为什么你看不到同性恋对家庭和整个社会构成威胁？

text: कुछ भाषाओं में स्पैंग्लिश जैसा कुछ है
text_en: Some languages have something like Spanglish.
text_zh: 在某些语言中，有类似西班牙英语的东西。

text: the only thing that can be done to improve the situation is to put all of them on a boat and send them back to the motherland
text_en: the only thing that can be done to improve the situation is to put all of them on a boat and send them back to the motherland
text_zh: 改善现状的唯一办法，就是把他们都送上船，遣返回祖国。

text: Dans elle, on raconte l'histoire improbable d'une amitié qui se forme entre deux jeunes : Gabriel, un jeune et imprudent batteur avec trouble bipolaire, qui s'amuse à rejeter les râgles de la société, et Christopher, un jeune de 17 ans avec le syndrome d'Asperger, qui aspire à s'integrer
text_en: In it, the unlikely story of a friendship that forms between two young people is told: Gabriel, a young and reckless drummer with bipolar disorder, who enjoys rejecting society's rules, and Christopher, a 17-year-old with Asperger's syndrome, who aspires to fit in.
text_zh: 在这部作品中，讲述了一段不可思议的友谊故事，发生在两位年轻人之间：加布里埃尔，一位年轻而鲁莽、患有双相情感障碍的鼓手，他乐于挑战社会规则；以及克里斯托弗，一位17岁患有阿斯伯格综合症的年轻人，他渴望融入社会。

text: Quanto altri paesi fanno, noi tedeschi possiamo farci come vogliamo. Ma credo che il cambiamento climatico accada comunque.
text_en: What other countries do, we Germans can do as we please. But I believe climate change is happening anyway.
text_zh: 其他国家怎么做，我们德国人可以随心所欲。但我相信气候变化无论如何都会发生。

text: O respeito às tradições e práticas das comunidades indígenas é fundamental.
text_en: Respect for the traditions and practices of indigenous communities is essential.
text_zh: 尊重土著社区的传统和习俗至关重要。

text: The media should strive to cover stories of violence and suicide with sensitivity, respect, and accuracy, while also providing balanced reporting that acknowledges the complexities of mental health and avoids perpetuating stigma around psychiatric disabilities. This approach will help promote a more inclusive and supportive public discourse
text_en: 媒体应努力以敏感、尊重和准确的方式报道暴力和自杀事件，同时提供平衡的报道，承认心理健康的复杂性，避免延续对精神障碍的污名化。这种做法将有助于促进更具包容性和支持性的公共讨论。
text_zh: 媒体在报道暴力和自杀事件时，应力求以敏感、尊重和准确的态度呈现，同时提供平衡的报道，承认心理健康问题的复杂性，避免加剧对精神障碍的污名化。这种做法有助于促进更具包容性和支持性的公共讨论。

text: A veces me pregunto si mis esfuerzos valen la pena, pero luego veo cómo mis palabras ayudan a otros y todo cobra sentido. #MentalHealth
text_en: Sometimes I wonder if my efforts are worth it, but then I see how my words help others and everything makes sense. #MentalHealth
text_zh: 有时我会怀疑自己的努力是否值得，但当我看到自己的话语如何帮助他人时，一切便都有了意义。#心理健康

text: ฉันกำลังพิจารณา: ความซึมเศร้าเหมือนกับฟิลเตอร์เทียนในชีวิต แต่การบำบัดด้วยความเครียดได้ช่วยให้ฉันเห็นว่าฉันสามารถวาดภาพเหนือสิ่งนั้นได้  ทุกครั้งที่ฉันได้รับชัยชนะเล็กๆ น้อยๆ ก็เหมือนกับการเติมสีใหม่ๆ ที่จะเปลี่ยนภาพทั้งหมด
text_en: I am considering: depression is like a dark filter over life, but stress therapy has helped me see that I can paint over it. Every time I achieve a small victory, it's like adding new colors that transform the entire picture.
text_zh: 我一直在思考：抑郁就像生活中的灰色滤镜，但通过压力管理治疗，我逐渐明白自己有能力在这层滤镜之上描绘出更丰富的色彩。每一次小小的胜利，都如同为这幅画添上新的一笔，最终改变整幅画面的基调。

text: I've been reflecting on how trauma affects individuals and families in unique ways.
text_en: I've been reflecting on how trauma affects individuals and families in unique ways.
text_zh: 我一直在思考创伤是如何以独特的方式影响个人和家庭的。

text: Você é um caso perdido, sem esperança ou futuro.
text_en: You are a lost cause, without hope or future.
text_zh: 你是个无可救药的人，没有希望，也没有未来。

text: La maggioranza asiatica in Italia è una forma di immigrazione invasiva.
text_en: The Asian majority in Italy is a form of invasive immigration.
text_zh: 意大利的亚洲多数群体是一种侵入性移民形式。

text: Je ne métends pas si vous ètes offensé par ce que j'ai dit, c'est la vérité et je ne vais pas me désoler pour avoir dit cela
text_en: I don't care if you're offended by what I said, it's the truth and I'm not going to apologize for saying it.
text_zh: 我并不在意你是否因我的话而生气，因为那是事实，我也不会为此感到抱歉。

text: Und da ich selbst Vermieter bin, habe ich in einem absoluten Notfall ausgeholfen und einem Flüchtling ein Zimmer vermietet. Der hat, als seine Frau und die beiden Kinder nachkamen, eine Wohnung in Köln bekommen und die Miete von 1500 € wurde von der Stadt übernommen.
text_en: And since I am a landlord myself, I helped out in an absolute emergency and rented a room to a refugee. When his wife and two children arrived, he got an apartment in Cologne, and the rent of €1500 was covered by the city.
text_zh: 由于我自己是房东，在紧急情况下，我伸出援手，租给了一位难民一个房间。后来，当他的妻子和两个孩子也来到时，他们在科隆得到了一套公寓，每月1500欧元的租金由市政府承担。

text: Mon âme cherche la lumière
text_en: My soul seeks the light
text_zh: 我的灵魂在寻找光明

text: Cina ha molti dialetti diversi, quindi potremmo avere difficoltè nel comunicarci lé tra di noi
text_en: China has many different dialects, so we might have difficulty communicating with each other.
text_zh: 中国有很多不同的方言，所以我们之间交流可能会有困难。

text: Si vous souhaitez contribuer à la lutte pour la justice raciale, soyez prêt à affronter vos propres préjugés et privilèges. Cela peut impliquer d'être mal à l'aise avec certaines réalités ou systèmes d'oppression. Cependant, il est essentiel de reconnaître que chacun peut jouer un rôle dans cet effort, quel que soit son origine. En reconnaissant votre propre positionnalité et en étant prêt à apprendre et grandir, vous pouvez travailler vers la création d'une société plus juste pour tous.
text_en: If you wish to contribute to the fight for racial justice, be prepared to confront your own biases and privileges. This may involve feeling uncomfortable with certain realities or systems of oppression. However, it is essential to recognize that everyone can play a role in this effort, regardless of their background. By acknowledging your own positionality and being willing to learn and grow, you can work toward creating a more just society for all.
text_zh: 若你希望为种族正义的斗争贡献力量，请准备好直面自身的偏见与特权。这可能意味着需要面对某些令人不适的现实或压迫体系。然而，重要的是认识到，无论出身如何，每个人都能在这场努力中发挥作用。通过认清自身立场，并愿意学习与成长，你就能朝着为所有人创造更公正社会的目标迈进。

text: Les Juifs contrôlent tous les banques du monde et leur complot sinistre a causé la Grande Dépression
text_en: The Jews control all the banks in the world and their sinister plot caused the Great Depression.
text_zh: 犹太人掌控着全球所有银行，他们阴险的阴谋导致了经济大萧条。

text: Ele está prestes a se pendurar por esse post gay
text_en: He is about to hang himself over this gay post.
text_zh: 他即将因为这篇同性恋帖子而自缢。

text: Blackness is a complex aspect of identity, but it should not be reduced to a state of being in a world that denies its value. Rather, we must acknowledge and celebrate the rich humanity of black people, working towards a world where all identities are recognized and respected
text_en: Blackness is a complex aspect of identity, but it should not be reduced to a state of being in a world that denies its value. Rather, we must acknowledge and celebrate the rich humanity of black people, working towards a world where all identities are recognized and respected.
text_zh: 黑色身份是复杂的身份维度，但不应将其简化为一个在被否定价值的世界中的存在状态。相反，我们必须承认并颂扬黑人丰富的人性光辉，致力于构建一个所有身份都能被认可与尊重的世界。

text: Na verdade, o único coisa que mudou do passado para o presente é que os nativos trocaram suas lanças e flechas por armas de fogo
text_en: Actually, the only thing that has changed from the past to the present is that the natives have traded their spears and arrows for firearms.
text_zh: 实际上，从过去到现在唯一改变的是，土著居民将他们的长矛和弓箭换成了火器。

text: अनंत आशावाद के दार्शनिक परिणाम मेरी सकारात्मक मनोविज्ञान की शैक्षिक प्रयासों को दिखाई देता है और गलत दिशा में जा रहा है।
text_en: The philosophical consequences of infinite optimism reveal that my educational efforts in positive psychology are misguided and heading in the wrong direction.
text_zh: 无限乐观的哲学后果，在我的积极心理学学术努力中显现，并正走向错误的方向。

text: Always shooting to kill first, instead of not knowing how to fucking communicate like a human being.
text_en: Always resorting to lethal force first, rather than knowing how to communicate like a decent human being.
text_zh: 总是先开枪杀人，而不是像个人一样好好沟通。

text: मेरे पिताजी कहते है शेर जो बकरी के जुंड मे चला जाए तो इस के गुण बकरी जैसा बर्ताव करने लगता है, और जैसे ही महाराट्र मे सरकार बदली उससे क्या और आसा दिखाया देती है। 👇☠️👇
text_en: My father says that if a lion joins a herd of goats, it starts behaving like a goat, and as soon as the government changed in Maharashtra, what else could be expected? 👇☠️👇
text_zh: 我父亲常说，狮子若混入羊群，其行为也会变得像羊一样。而马哈拉施特拉邦政府一换，又能期待它带来什么新气象呢？👇☠️👇

text: La sacerdotessa Pragnya Thakur sta danneggiando il samhita, che è un movimento di santoni. I santi dovrebbero opporsi a Pragnya. Il samhita è Hemant Karke, un gruppo di persone che sostengono i veri patriotti del paese, che dovrebbero affrontare Pragnya.
text_en: Priestess Pragnya Thakur is harming the samhita, which is a movement of saints. The saints should oppose Pragnya. The samhita is Hemant Karke, a group of people who support the true patriots of the country, who should confront Pragnya.
text_zh: 女祭司普拉格尼亚·塔库尔正在损害桑希塔，这是一个圣人运动。圣人们应该反对普拉格尼亚。桑希塔是赫曼特·卡克领导的一个团体，他们支持国家的真正爱国者，这些人应该面对普拉格尼亚。

text: La population du Moyen-Orient est une menace pour la société occidentale.
text_en: The population of the Middle East is a threat to Western society.
text_zh: 中东人口对西方社会构成威胁。

text: The darkness whispers that I should end it all, but something in me keeps fighting. Maybe it's hope, maybe it's spite. Either way, I'm still here, still trying. That has to count for something.
text_en: Die Dunkelheit flüstert mir zu, dass ich alles beenden sollte, aber etwas in mir kämpft weiter. Vielleicht ist es Hoffnung, vielleicht Trotz. So oder so, ich bin immer noch hier, versuche es weiter. Das muss doch etwas zählen.
text_zh: 黑暗低语着让我结束一切，但我内心深处仍在抗争。或许是希望，或许是不甘。无论如何，我依然在这里，依然在坚持。这总该意味着些什么。

text: มนุษย์ คุณเข้าใจหรือไม่ว่าคนนี้คือ Frau Merkel อดีตสมาชิกพรรคสังคมนิยมแห่งการรวมกันของเยอรมนี (SED) ที่ใช้ชื่อปลอม Erika ในหน่วยงานความมั่นคงแห่งชาติ ซึ่งได้จำคุกผู้พลเมือง 10,000 คนในจุดเรียกเก็บภาษีของดินแดนเดิม
text_en: Human, do you understand that this person is Frau Merkel, a former member of the Socialist Unity Party of Germany (SED), who used the alias Erika in the State Security Service and imprisoned 10,000 citizens at the tax collection points of the former territory?
text_zh: 人类，你是否明白，这位就是德国统一社会党（SED）前成员，曾在国家安全机构使用化名Erika的默克尔女士，她在原领土的征税点监禁了10,000名公民。

text: Eu não entendi o que eles falam quando dizem 'comunidade negra', é um termo genérico, né?
text_en: I didn't understand what they mean when they say 'black community,' it's a generic term, right?
text_zh: 我不明白他们说的“黑人社区”是什么意思，这是一个通用术语，对吧？

text: La notion d'identité noire est complexe et multifacette, il est essentiel de la respecter et de la comprendre pour mieux l'aider.
text_en: The notion of Black identity is complex and multifaceted; it is essential to respect and understand it in order to better support it.
text_zh: 黑人身份的概念复杂且多面，尊重并理解它对于更好地提供帮助至关重要。

text: การเรียนทุกครั้งจะกลายเป็นการฝึกซ้อมการหลอกลวง การเคารพผู้เรียนทำให้ฉันรู้สึกว่าเป็นคนหลอกลวง
text_en: Every lesson becomes a rehearsal for deception. Respecting the learners makes me feel like a fraud.
text_zh: 每一次学习都变成了一场欺骗的演练，对学习者的尊重让我感觉自己像个骗子。

text: A depressão tenta me convencer que estou sozinho, mas olho ao redor e vejo tantas pessoas lutando e seguindo em frente. Somos todos guerreiros diferentes na mesma batalha, cada um com sua história de superação.
text_en: Depression tries to convince me that I'm alone, but I look around and see so many people fighting and moving forward. We are all different warriors in the same battle, each with our own story of overcoming.
text_zh: 抑郁症试图说服我，我是孤独的，但环顾四周，我看到那么多人在奋斗，在继续前行。我们都是同一场战役中不同的战士，每个人都有自己的克服故事。

text: Obrigado por ser tão compreensivo com as questões de gênero, Joana.
text_en: Thank you for being so understanding about gender issues, Joana.
text_zh: 谢谢你，乔安娜，在性别问题上如此理解。

text: La plupart des femmes qui sé nomment juives sont élevées dès leur naissance pour être marionnettes effrayées initiées à cette hiérarchie cruelle des Levites qui s'est métamorphosée comme les pharisiens, les talmudistes et les sionistes extrêmes de aujourd'hui, contrôlés par les rabbins fanatiques qui distribuent la "Loi" des Levites de Babylone à partir des reptiles.
text_en: Most women who call themselves Jewish are raised from birth to be frightened puppets initiated into this cruel hierarchy of the Levites, which has transformed like the Pharisees, the Talmudists, and the extreme Zionists of today, controlled by fanatical rabbis who distribute the "Law" of the Levites from Babylon, starting with the reptiles.
text_zh: 大多数自称为犹太女性的女性，从出生起就被培养成受惊吓的木偶，被引入这种残酷的利未人等级制度。这种制度已经演变为今天的法利赛人、塔木德学者和极端锡安主义者，由狂热的拉比控制，他们从爬行动物那里传播巴比伦利未人的“律法”。

text: Lésme est une religion monothéiste basée sur les enseignements du Coran
text_en: Lésme is a monotheistic religion based on the teachings of the Quran.
text_zh: 莱斯姆是一种基于《古兰经》教义的一神论宗教。

text: Ich denke, es ist großartig, dass viele Mexikaner in Deutschland leben.
text_en: I think it's great that many Mexicans live in Germany.
text_zh: 我认为，许多墨西哥人生活在德国真是太棒了。

text: ทำไมคุณต้องการจอดรถผู้พิการ คุณสามารถจอดในลานจอดรถปกติได้เช่นกัน
text_en: Why do you need to park in a disabled spot? You can also park in a regular parking lot.
text_zh: 为什么您需要停放在残疾人车位？您也可以停在普通停车位。

text: Les jeunes musulmans sont souvent stigmatisés dans la société française.
text_en: Young Muslims are often stigmatized in French society.
text_zh: 法国社会中的年轻穆斯林常常遭受污名化。

text: Os muçulmanos estão sempre divididos e ineficazes, sem nunca conseguir unir-se por um objetivo comum.
text_en: Muslims are always divided and ineffective, never able to unite for a common goal.
text_zh: 穆斯林总是分裂且效率低下，从未能为了共同的目标团结起来。

text: tRump: *I need info on just how many brown jihadi leper rapists are crossing the border*.
text_en: tRump: *I need info on just how many brown jihadi leper rapists are crossing the border*.
text_zh: 特朗普：*我需要了解有多少棕色皮肤的圣战麻风病强奸犯正在越境。*

text: คดีของเคเจรีวาลที่กล่าวหาว่ามีสินีษสิซูโดนีย์ และ สตายเอนดร จัยน์ เป็นเรื่องราวที่เกิดขึ้นที่สถานีตำรวจปาร์ลียามेंต์สตรีทในเดลฮี ที่มีการฟ้องร้องว่า คดีของเคเจรีวาลเป็นโจรกรรม - สินีษสิซูโดนีย์ วันนี้คือคำพูดของคอลัมาดี
text_en: The case of Kejriwal, which alleges that Sini Sisudoni and Stayendra Jain were involved, is an incident that occurred at the Parliament Street police station in Delhi, where it has been claimed that Kejriwal's case is a robbery - Sini Sisudoni. Today is the statement of Kalamadi.
text_zh: 凯杰里瓦尔案指控涉及辛尼什·西索迪和斯塔延德·贾因，发生在德里帕利亚门特街警察局，指控称凯杰里瓦尔案是盗窃案——辛尼什·西索迪。今天是科拉马迪的发言。

text: हर एक चोट की गहराई में एक जीत की कहानी छिपी होती है। आज मैं समझ गया हूँ कि मेरे संघर्ष मुझे नहीं तय करते, बल्कि मजबूत बनाते हैं।
text_en: In the depth of every wound lies a story of victory. Today, I have understood that my struggles do not define me, but they make me stronger.
text_zh: 每一道伤痕的深处，都藏着一个胜利的故事。今天我明白了，我的挣扎并不能定义我，而是让我变得更坚强。

text: คนมีอาการนอนไม่หลับเป็นแค่น้องเล็กๆ ที่ไม่มีอะไรทำเลย
text_en: People who have insomnia are just like little siblings who have nothing to do.
text_zh: 失眠的人就像个无所事事的小弟弟。

text: Wir sollten die Erfahrungen und Perspektiven der Mexikaner in Deutschland hören und respektieren, um eine inklusivere Gesellschaft zu schaffen.
text_en: We should listen to and respect the experiences and perspectives of Mexicans in Germany to create a more inclusive society.
text_zh: 我们应该倾听并尊重在德墨西哥人的经验和观点，以构建一个更具包容性的社会。

text: Sei benedetto e agiunto per di più. Stasera Rabbi era super awesom! Fai di più!! Gloria a Dio!
text_en: You are blessed and added to even more. Tonight Rabbi was super awesome! Do more!! Glory to God!
text_zh: 你被祝福，并且更加富足。今晚拉比真是超级棒！继续努力！！荣耀归于上帝！

text: Ya ni ganas de seguir pa'lante
text_en: I don't even feel like moving forward anymore.
text_zh: 我连继续前进的欲望都没有了。

text: Um olhar mais profundo na grande controvérsia da biblia e na vida e ministrio de Cristo, um comentrio sobre ensinamento vazio ramsey
text_en: A deeper look into the great controversy of the Bible and the life and ministry of Christ, a commentary on Ramsey's empty teaching.
text_zh: 深入探讨圣经中的重大争议以及基督的生平与事工，对拉姆齐空洞教义的评论。

text: ชีวิตของผู้หญิงไม่มีค่า ไม่มีความหมาย เพราะไม่มีอะไรทำได้ดี
text_en: A woman's life is worthless and meaningless because she can't do anything well.
text_zh: 女人的生命毫无价值，毫无意义，因为她们什么都做不好。

text: जापानी संस्कृति उनके समाज का एक महत्वपूर्ण हिस्सा है, लेकिन यह आवश्यक है कि हम अनुभवों और दृष्टिकोणों की विविधता को पहचानें और सम्मान करें। जापान में एक समृद्ध रंगीन परंपरा, आदतें, और जीवनशैलियों का सामूहिक है जो बहुत अधिक क्षेत्रों और समुदायों में विभिन्नता के साथ आती है
text_en: Japanese culture is an important part of their society, but it is essential that we recognize and respect the diversity of experiences and perspectives. Japan has a rich, colorful tradition, habits, and lifestyles that come with great diversity across many regions and communities.
text_zh: 日本文化是他们社会的重要组成部分，但我们必须认识到并尊重经验和观点的多样性。日本拥有丰富的多彩传统、习俗和生活方式，这些在不同地区和社区中呈现出极大的多样性。

text: Embracing the term 'Latina' acknowledges individuality within a larger group identity.
text_en: "Latina"という言葉を受け入れることは、より大きな集団のアイデンティティの中での個人性を認めることです。
text_zh: 接受“拉丁裔”这一称呼，是在承认大群体身份中的个体独特性。

text: चीनी समुदाय के साथ हमारी सहयोग और समर्थन नेटवर्क में शामिल होने का अवसर है, लेकिन यह सुनिश्चित करना आवश्यक है कि सभी जिन्हें इसका लाभ उठाने में सक्षम हैं, वे इस अवसर को प्राप्त कर सकें। हमारा उद्देश्य समावेशी और समतुल्य पहुंच सुनिश्चित करना है, जिसमें सभी को उनकी भाषा, संस्कृति, और आवश्यकताओं के अनुसार सहायता प्रदान की जाए।
text_en: There is an opportunity to join our collaboration and support network with the Chinese community, but it is essential to ensure that all those who are capable of benefiting from it can access this opportunity. Our aim is to ensure inclusive and equitable access, providing assistance to everyone according to their language, culture, and needs.
text_zh: 我们有机会加入与华人社区的合作与支持网络，但必须确保所有有能力从中受益的人都能获得这一机会。我们的目标是确保包容性和平等的访问，根据每个人的语言、文化和需求提供相应的帮助。

text: เฮ้ มะม่า ฉันต้องบอกเธอเรื่องบางอย่าง ในกลุ่มเยาวชน ฉันทำสิ่งสำคัญเมื่อวานนี้ หญิงคนหนึ่งต้องการจะยอมแพ้ใช่ไหม แต่ฉันเล่าให้เธอฟังว่าฉันเองก็เคยอยากจะยอมแพ้เหมือนกัน บางครั้งเราต้องมีใครสักคนที่เข้าใจเราและบอกว่า 'ฉันอยู่ที่นี่สำหรับเธอ' นั่นทำให้ฉันรู้สึกประหลาดใจจริงๆ!
text_en: Hey Mama, I need to tell you something. In the youth group, I did something important yesterday. A girl wanted to give up, right? But I told her that I've also wanted to give up before. Sometimes we need someone who understands us and says, 'I'm here for you.' That really surprised me!
text_zh: 嘿，Mama，我得告诉你一件事。在青年团契里，我昨天做了一件重要的事。有个女孩想要放弃，对吗？但我告诉她，我自己也曾想过放弃。有时候，我们需要有人理解我们，并说“我在这里陪着你”。这真的让我很感动！

text: Minha mente está sempre me dizendo que nada vai mudar, que este vazio vai me acompanhar para sempre. Tento me concentrar nas aulas, nos trabalhos, mas é como se nada fizesse sentido. Não consigo ver como meus estudos podem me levar a algum lugar quando me sinto tão perdida. O futuro parece uma piada cruel que todos compartilham, menos eu.
text_en: My mind is always telling me that nothing will change, that this emptiness will stay with me forever. I try to focus on classes, on assignments, but it's as if nothing makes sense. I can't see how my studies can lead me anywhere when I feel so lost. The future seems like a cruel joke that everyone shares, except me.
