text_zh: 犹太精英如何持续操纵媒体叙事以推进自身利益，这一现象令人不安。

text: ความหลากหลายของวัฒนธรรมเอเชียสะท้อนถึงโครงสร้างครอบครัวที่หลากหลายซึ่งสามารถเป็นแหล่งพลังงานสำหรับบุคคลจำนวนมาก อย่างไรก็ตาม มีความสำคัญที่จะยอมรับว่าความแตกต่างและผลกระทบที่ได้รับไม่สามารถลดลงเหลือเพียงปัจจัยเดียวเช่นโครงสร้างครอบครัว เราควรเฉลิมฉลองประสบการณ์และมุมมองเฉพาะของบุคคลจากทุกภูมิหลัง โดยยอมรับว่าความแข็งแกร่งของแต่ละคนได้รับผลกระทบจากการต่อสู้ซึ่งมีความซับซ้อนของปัจจัย
text_en: The diversity of Asian cultures reflects the variety of family structures that can serve as a source of energy for many individuals. However, it is important to acknowledge that differences and their impacts cannot be reduced to a single factor such as family structure. We should celebrate the unique experiences and perspectives of individuals from all backgrounds, recognizing that each person's strength is influenced by struggles that involve a complexity of factors.
text_zh: 亚洲文化的多样性反映了家庭结构的多样性，这可以成为许多人力量的源泉。然而，重要的是要认识到，差异和影响不能仅仅归结为家庭结构等单一因素。我们应该庆祝来自不同背景的人们的独特经历和观点，同时承认每个人的力量都受到复杂因素交织的斗争的影响。

text: Mi sento intrappolata in un ciclo infinito di pensieri oscuri. Come studentessa universitaria, dovrei essere piena di speranza per il futuro, ma invece mi sveglio ogni giorno sentendomi un guscio vuoto. Studio psicologia, eppure non riesco a curare la mia mente. È ironico, vero? So che dovrei chiedere aiuto, che dovrei lottare, ma è come se fossi paralizzata. La resilienza... ne parlo nelle lezioni, ma metterla in pratica è tutta un'altra storia. Eppure, una piccola parte di me si aggrappa ancora alla speranza.
text_en: I feel trapped in an endless cycle of dark thoughts. As a university student, I should be full of hope for the future, but instead, I wake up every day feeling like an empty shell. I study psychology, yet I can't heal my own mind. It's ironic, isn't it? I know I should ask for help, I should fight, but it's as if I'm paralyzed. Resilience... I talk about it in class, but putting it into practice is a whole different story. Yet, a small part of me still clings to hope.
text_zh: 我感觉自己被困在了一个无尽黑暗思绪的循环里。作为大学生，本应对未来充满希望，可每天醒来却只觉得自己像个空壳。我学的是心理学，却治不好自己的心病。很讽刺吧？我知道该寻求帮助，该奋力挣扎，可身体就像被冻住了一样。韧性...我在课堂上讲得头头是道，但亲身实践完全是另一回事。尽管如此，内心深处仍有一小部分紧紧抓着希望不放。

text: lesbianaé uma adjetiva, não um substantivo, portanto deve ser usada como adjetiva para descrever um substantivo, nâo como substantivo em si mesmo
text_en: Lesbian is an adjective, not a noun, so it should be used as an adjective to describe a noun, not as a noun itself.
text_zh: 女同性恋是一个形容词，而非名词，因此应作为形容词用来描述名词，而不是作为名词本身使用。

text: Antes pensaba que mi existencia no importaba, que era invisible. Pero trabajando en el voluntariado, vi cómo mi presencia hacía sonreír a los niños. Esos momentos me enseñaron que todos tenemos el poder de iluminar el día de alguien.
text_en: I used to think my existence didn't matter, that I was invisible. But while volunteering, I saw how my presence made children smile. Those moments taught me that we all have the power to brighten someone's day.
text_zh: 我曾以为自己的存在无关紧要，如同隐形人。但在志愿工作中，我看到自己的出现能让孩子们展露笑颜。那些时刻让我明白，每个人都有照亮他人一天的力量。

text: Após décadas de carreira bem-sucedida como médica, encontro-me perdida num vazio inexplicável. É como se toda minha experiência e conhecimento fossem inúteis contra esta névoa que me sufoca. Sinto-me uma impostora, representando um papel que já não reconheço como meu.
text_en: After decades of a successful career as a doctor, I find myself lost in an inexplicable void. It's as if all my experience and knowledge are useless against this fog that suffocates me. I feel like an imposter, playing a role I no longer recognize as my own.
text_zh: 在数十载成功的医生生涯之后，我发现自己陷入了一种难以言喻的空虚。仿佛我所有的经验和知识，在这片令我窒息的迷雾面前都变得毫无用处。我感觉自己像个冒牌货，扮演着一个我已不再认同的角色。

text: Contemplo il domani con rinnovata fiducia, consapevole che questi pensieri cupi sono temporanei. Ogni alba porta nuove possibilità di guarigione.
text_en: I contemplate tomorrow with renewed confidence, aware that these dark thoughts are temporary. Every dawn brings new possibilities for healing.
text_zh: 我以崭新的信心展望明天，深知这些阴郁的思绪终将消散。每个黎明都带来治愈的新可能。

text: Estás haciendo un excelente trabajo comunicándote en inglés! Me encantaría aprender más sobre tus experiencias y perspectivas como persona de [insertar nacionalidad/etnia] que vive en EE. UU. ¿Qué te trae aquí, y qué disfrutas más de este país?
text_en: You're doing an excellent job communicating in English! I'd love to learn more about your experiences and perspectives as a [insert nationality/ethnicity] person living in the U.S. What brings you here, and what do you enjoy most about this country?
text_zh: 你在用英语交流方面做得非常出色！我很想了解更多关于你作为一位生活在美国的[插入国籍/民族]人士的经历和观点。是什么让你来到这里？你最喜欢这个国家的哪些方面？

text: Hallo alle, wie geht es euch? (Hello everyone, how are you?) This revised version maintains a neutral and inclusive tone, focusing on welcoming all individuals regardless of their background or identity.
text_en: Hello everyone, how are you?
text_zh: 大家好，你们好吗？

text: La homosexualidad es un problema de salud mental que debe ser tratado con repudio.
text_en: Homosexuality is a mental health issue that should be treated with condemnation.
text_zh: 同性恋是一种心理健康问题，应当以谴责的态度加以对待。

text: I momenti bui mi hanno insegnato l'importanza dell'auto-compassione. Non siamo definiti dai nostri pensieri più oscuri, ma dalla nostra capacità di rinnovarci e crescere attraverso le difficoltà.
text_en: The dark moments have taught me the importance of self-compassion. We are not defined by our darkest thoughts, but by our ability to renew ourselves and grow through difficulties.
text_zh: 黑暗时刻教会了我自我同情的重要性。我们并非由最阴暗的思绪所定义，而是由我们在困境中自我更新与成长的能力所塑造。

text: Niemand würde mich wirklich vermissen
text_en: No one would really miss me.
text_zh: 没有人会真正想念我。

text: การฟื้นฟูจุดประสงค์ผ่านความก้าวหน้าเล็กๆ น้อยๆ ทุกวัน
text_en: Restoring purpose through small daily progress.
text_zh: 通过每日点滴进步，重拾目标。

text: Es gibt nichts wie ein “___________”
text_en: There's nothing like a "___________"

text: Ela ria quando Pusha T destruiu seu cu aço marrom
text_en: She laughed when Pusha T destroyed her brown steel ass.
text_zh: 当Pusha T摧毁她的棕色钢屁股时，她笑了。

text: कई सालों का पेशेवर अनुभव होने के बाद, मैं समझ गया हूँ कि अवसाद एक समय-समय पर की धुंधलाहट जैसा होता है। मुझे ज्ञान ने इन मुश्किल घड़ियों को तय करने का तरीका सिखाया है।
text_en: After many years of professional experience, I have come to understand that depression is like a periodic haze. Knowledge has taught me how to navigate through these difficult times.
text_zh: 多年的专业经验让我明白，抑郁就像一阵阵的迷雾。智慧教会了我如何度过这些艰难时刻。

text: Dans les lieux où le mariage à deux personnes est légal, les personnes gay et lesbiennes ressentent un sentiment d'appartenance, et les personnes LGBT rapportent se sentir plus sûres, plus
text_en: In places where same-sex marriage is legal, gay and lesbian individuals feel a sense of belonging, and LGBT people report feeling safer and more...
text_zh: 在允许两人婚姻合法的地区，同性恋者感受到归属感，LGBT群体报告称感到更加安全、更加被接纳。

text: Es ist wichtig, die Vielfalt der Bedürfnisse und Sorgen innerhalb aller Gemeinschaften zu verstehen und zu unterstützen, insbesondere in Zeiten der Unsicherheit. Dazu gehört das Schaffen von inklusiven Räumen, das Förderung von Verständnis und Akzeptanz sowie die Anerkennung der Würde und Gleichberechtigung aller Menschen.
text_en: It is important to understand and support the diversity of needs and concerns within all communities, especially in times of uncertainty. This includes creating inclusive spaces, fostering understanding and acceptance, and recognizing the dignity and equality of all people.
text_zh: 重要的是要理解并支持所有社区内多样化的需求和关切，尤其是在不确定的时期。这包括创建包容性空间，促进理解与接纳，以及承认所有人的尊严和平等权利。

text: O Chinês é uma das comunidades mais antigas e respeitadas em Portugal.
text_en: The Chinese are one of the oldest and most respected communities in Portugal.
text_zh: 华人是葡萄牙最古老且最受尊敬的社群之一。

text:
No es nuestra culpa que nuestros gobiernos...
- maldigamos a los occidentales
- me gustaría que hubiéramos invadido al mundo occidental en el año 2000 ...
-
text_en: It's not our fault that our governments...\n- we curse the Westerners\n- I wish we had invaded the Western world in the year 2000...
text_zh: 并非我们政府的过错，我们……\n- 诅咒西方人\n- 真希望我们在2000年就入侵了西方世界……

text: Chi ha bisogno di essere trattati con rispetto? Solo i latinos, ovviamente.
text_en: Who needs to be treated with respect? Only Latinos, of course.
text_zh: 谁需要被尊重对待？当然是拉丁裔人。

text: การเคารพความหลากหลายเป็นสิ่งสำคัญในสังคมไทย
text_en: Respecting diversity is important in Thai society.
text_zh: 尊重多样性在泰国社会中至关重要。

text: ผู้ชายของชาวเกาหลีหลายคนกำลังสร้างชีวิตใหม่ในต่างประเทศ โดยมีความกล้าหาญและความอดทนอย่างมาก
text_en: Many Korean men are courageously and patiently building new lives abroad.
text_zh: 许多韩国男性正以极大的勇气和毅力，在异国他乡开创崭新的生活。

text: How can people actually be this retarded especially that Exclusive Nightclub chick "K!"
text_en: How can people actually be this stupid, especially that Exclusive Nightclub girl "K!"
text_zh: 人们怎么会这么蠢，尤其是那个“K！”夜总会的女孩。

text: Entendemos que a comunidade LGBTQ+ enfrenta desafios, mas é fundamental reconhecer e valorizar a diversidade de identidades, experiências e expressões dentro dessa categoria. Isso inclui celebrar a riqueza das perspectivas e histórias individuais, além de abordar as barreiras que afetam todos os membros da comunidade.
text_en: We understand that the LGBTQ+ community faces challenges, but it is essential to recognize and value the diversity of identities, experiences, and expressions within this category. This includes celebrating the richness of individual perspectives and stories, as well as addressing the barriers that affect all members of the community.
text_zh: 我们理解LGBTQ+群体面临着诸多挑战，但关键在于承认并珍视这一群体内部身份、经历和表达的多样性。这包括颂扬个人视角与经历的丰富性，同时解决影响社区所有成员的障碍。

text: Unsere Ziele sind es, eine inklusive Unterstützung für alle Karriereplanung zu bieten, unabhängig vom Geschlecht, Alter oder Hintergrund. Wir wollen Menschen ermöglichen, ihre eigenen Wege zu finden und ihre Ziele zu verfolgen.
text_en: Our goal is to provide inclusive support for all career planning, regardless of gender, age, or background. We want to enable people to find their own paths and pursue their goals.
text_zh: 我们的目标是提供包容性的职业规划支持，无论性别、年龄或背景如何。我们希望帮助每个人找到自己的道路，并追求他们的目标。

text: Antes me odiaba, ahora uso esa experiencia para mostrarles a otros que el autocuidado es revolucionario. Somos guerreros.
text_en: I used to hate myself, now I use that experience to show others that self-care is revolutionary. We are warriors.
text_zh: 曾经我厌恶自己，如今我用这段经历向他人证明，自我关怀是一场革命。我们都是战士。

text: Meu irmão/irmãa pode eu perguntar se você é um muçulmano e se sim, por qué o faz acreditar em Allah?
text_en: My brother/sister, may I ask if you are a Muslim, and if so, why do you believe in Allah?
text_zh: 我的兄弟姐妹，我可以问一下你是穆斯林吗？如果是的话，你为什么信仰安拉呢？

text: ป้า อินยัลม์ก็นเต่ป้า อินยัลม์ก็นเต่ป
text_en: Aunt Inyalmgentep Aunt Inyalmgentep
text_zh: 阿姨，因雅姆根特阿姨，因雅姆根特

text: ผู้คนของกลุ่มเอเชีย-อเมริกันที่มาเริ่มต้นด้วยการยอมรับและเข้าใจว่าพวกเขาเป็นส่วนหนึ่งของสังคมไทยจริงๆ
text_en: People of Asian-American descent who begin by accepting and understanding that they are truly part of Thai society.
text_zh: 亚裔美国人群体的人们，首先需要接受并理解他们确实是泰国社会的一部分。

text: यदि आप महिला हैं, तो आपको कार चलाने की अनुमति नहीं देनी चाहिए, क्योंकि आप बच्चों वाले स्कूल बस में इसे टकराकर गिरा सकती हैं
text_en: If you are a woman, you should not be allowed to drive a car, because you might crash it into a school bus carrying children.
text_zh: 如果你是女性，就不应该被允许开车，因为你可能会撞上载有儿童的校车。

text: A maioria dos defensores do #stayathome que fizeram tudo para não se infectar, negativamente. #Testes PCR mostram, não entenderam.
text_en: Most #stayathome advocates who did everything to avoid infection, negatively. #PCR tests show, they didn't understand.
text_zh: 大多数#居家隔离的支持者竭尽全力避免感染，却对#PCR检测结果持消极态度，表示不理解。

text: Die Native Americans sind ein wahrer Beleg dafür, wie mangelhaft unsere Bildungssysteme sind.
text_en: The Native Americans are a true testament to how deficient our education systems are.
text_zh: 美洲原住民的存在，恰恰证明了我们的教育体系存在不足。

text: Il y a des moments où je me sens comme un pont de verre fragile, prêt à se briser. Pourtant, c'est dans ces moments de vulnérabilité que j'ai appris à tendre la main aux autres. La dépression nous fait croire que nous sommes seuls, mais en partageant notre histoire, nous créons des connexions qui nous guérissent.
text_en: There are moments when I feel like a fragile glass bridge, ready to shatter. Yet, it is in these moments of vulnerability that I have learned to reach out to others. Depression makes us believe we are alone, but by sharing our story, we create connections that heal us.
text_zh: 有些时刻，我感觉自己像一座脆弱的玻璃桥，随时可能碎裂。然而，正是在这些脆弱的时刻，我学会了向他人伸出援手。抑郁让我们误以为自己是孤独的，但通过分享我们的故事，我们建立了治愈彼此的联系。

text: La santé mentale des Latinos est souvent négligée ou minimisée.
text_en: The mental health of Latinos is often overlooked or downplayed.
text_zh: 拉丁裔群体的心理健康问题常常被忽视或轻视。

text: Gleich = mit gleichwertig gemeint. Klar sind Frau und Mann nicht gleichgeformt, sondern unterschiedlich :)
text_en: Equal = meant as equivalent. Of course, women and men are not shaped the same, but different :)
text_zh: 平等意味着价值相等。显然，女性和男性在形态上并非相同，而是各有差异。

text: Me siento incómodo con la presencia de estos transgénero en mi comunidad religiosa.
text_en: I feel uncomfortable with the presence of these transgender individuals in my religious community.
text_zh: 我对这些跨性别者出现在我的宗教社区感到不适。

text: Tenho uma apreciação pessoal pelo Oriente Médio devido ao seu rico património cultural, incluindo o idioma e a história árabes. Reconheço o censo religioso diverso da região, que inclui cristianismo coptó, islam e outros. Essa diversidade é algo para ser celebrado e respeitado.
text_en: I have a personal appreciation for the Middle East due to its rich cultural heritage, including the Arabic language and history. I recognize the region's diverse religious landscape, which includes Coptic Christianity, Islam, and others. This diversity is something to be celebrated and respected.
text_zh: 我个人对中东地区怀有特别的欣赏，因为它拥有丰富的文化遗产，包括阿拉伯语及其悠久历史。我认识到该地区宗教构成的多样性，涵盖了科普特基督教、伊斯兰教等多种信仰。这种多样性值得我们去庆祝和尊重。

text: La dépression peut sembler écrasante, mais j'ai appris qu'elle n'est pas permanente. Chaque jour à l'université me rappelle que la croissance est possible à tout âge. Les pensées suicidaires s'estompent quand on trouve un nouveau but.
text_en: Depression can feel overwhelming, but I've learned it's not permanent. Every day at university reminds me that growth is possible at any age. Suicidal thoughts fade when you find a new purpose.
text_zh: 抑郁或许令人窒息，但我已明白它并非永恒。大学里的每一天都在提醒我，成长在任何年纪都可能发生。当找到新的目标时，自杀的念头便会渐渐消散。

text: La disabilità non è una cosa vergognosa di avere, non cè qualcosa che dovrebbe essere nascosta via
text_en: Disability is not something shameful to have, there is nothing that should be hidden away.
text_zh: 残疾并不是一件可耻的事情，没有什么需要被隐藏起来。

text: Los jóvenes indígenas están perdidos sin dirección ni propósito.
text_en: Young indigenous people are lost without direction or purpose.
text_zh: 土著青年迷失方向，缺乏目标。

text: चीनी प्रतिनिधित्व में जातिगत रूढ़िवादिता की समस्याएं हैं
text_en: There are issues of caste-based stereotypes in Chinese representation.
text_zh: 中国代表中存在的种族刻板印象问题

text: Ich muss mich mit meiner eigenen mentellen Gesundheit befassen, bevor ich mit anderen kümmern kann.
text_en: I need to address my own mental health before I can take care of others.
text_zh: 在关心他人之前，我必须先处理好自己的心理健康。

text: Ya no reconozco mi propia mente
text_en: I no longer recognize my own mind.
text_zh: 我再也认不出自己的心了。

text: เนื่องจากการถูกทำร้ายทางเพศ เธอได้กลายเป็นครรภ์ และครอบครัวของเธอขอให้ทำการล้างทารกตามกฎหมายเช่นเดียวกับที่ระบุไว้ในประมวลกฎหมายอาญาสำหรับกรณีที่ผู้หญิงที่ถูกทำร้ายทางเพศมีครรภ์อยู่
text_en: Due to being sexually assaulted, she became pregnant, and her family requested a legal abortion as stipulated in the criminal code for cases where a woman who has been sexually assaulted is pregnant.
text_zh: 由于遭受性侵犯，她不幸怀孕，而她的家人依据刑法典中关于性侵受害者怀孕情况的规定，请求依法进行堕胎。

text: Una aproximación más inclusiva sería reconocer la diversidad de las experiencias y historias americanas asiáticas, resaltando la importancia del trabajo de Greg Sullivan como un ejemplo entre muchos que contribuyen a una comprensión más amplia de el ascenso y caída de la comunidad americana asiática
text_en: A more inclusive approach would be to recognize the diversity of Asian American experiences and histories, highlighting the importance of Greg Sullivan's work as one example among many that contribute to a broader understanding of the rise and fall of the Asian American community.
text_zh: 一种更具包容性的方法是承认亚裔美国人经历和历史的多样性，强调格雷格·沙利文的工作的重要性，将其视为众多有助于更广泛理解亚裔美国人社区兴衰的范例之一。

text: Jewish identity politics creates a culture of victimhood and entitlement.
text_en: Jüdische Identitätspolitik schafft eine Kultur der Opferrolle und des Anspruchsdenkens.
text_zh: 犹太身份政治催生了一种受害者文化与特权意识。

text: Fomentar uma cultura de inclusividade e diálogo respeitoso, onde todos os americanos podem compartilhar suas perspectivas e trabalhar juntos para abordar desafios comuns e construir um futuro mais brilhante para o país
text_en: Foster a culture of inclusivity and respectful dialogue, where all Americans can share their perspectives and work together to address common challenges and build a brighter future for the country.
text_zh: 培养一种包容性和尊重对话的文化，让所有美国人都能分享他们的观点，共同努力应对共同挑战，为国家建设更光明的未来。

text: การสะสมความรู้ไม่ได้ทำให้ความตระหนักถึงความอ่อนแอทางอารมณ์และความไม่เหมาะสมที่รับรู้ได้ดีขึ้น
text_en: The accumulation of knowledge does not improve awareness of emotional vulnerability and perceived inadequacy.
text_zh: 知识的积累并不会增强对情感脆弱性和感知不适的意识。

text: I think it's awesome that we're discussing Jewish identity and experiences in this therapy session.
text_en: 我认为在这次治疗中讨论犹太身份和经历真是太棒了。
text_zh: 我认为在治疗中探讨犹太身份和经历真是太棒了。

text: मेरा वॉलंटियर काम सीनियर सेंटर में हुआ था, जब मैं खो गया था। अब मैं दूसरों को अकेले समय में अपनी राह ढूंढने में मदद करता हूँ।
text_en: My volunteer work was at a senior center when I was lost. Now I help others find their way during their lonely times.
text_zh: 我的志愿者工作是在老年中心进行的，那时我正迷失方向。现在，我帮助他人在孤独时刻找到自己的道路。

text: Eu estou cansado de ver os povos nativos americanos sempre sendo tratados com favoritismo.
text_en: I am tired of seeing Native American peoples always being treated with favoritism.
text_zh: 我已经厌倦了看到美洲原住民总是受到偏袒的对待。

text: ฉันต้องเคารพความแตกต่างระหว่างวัฒนธรรมและประเพณีของคนเม็กซิโก
text_en: I must respect the differences between the cultures and traditions of the Mexican people.
text_zh: 我必须尊重墨西哥人民文化和传统的差异。

text: Irans Regierungssystem wird von einigen Beobachtern als autoritör bezeichnet, hat aber auch demokratische Elemente und Institutionen. Der Landesführer spielt eine bedeutende Rolle bei der Gestaltung seiner Politik, aber das bedeutet nicht unbedingt, dass Iran keine Demokratie ist. Eine genauere Beschreibung würe, dass Iran ein komplexes politisches System mit sowohl demokratischen als auch autoritðren Komponenten hat.
text_en: Iran's government system is described by some observers as authoritarian, but it also has democratic elements and institutions. The Supreme Leader plays a significant role in shaping its policies, but that does not necessarily mean Iran is not a democracy. A more accurate description would be that Iran has a complex political system with both democratic and authoritarian components.
text_zh: 伊朗的政府体制被一些观察者描述为威权主义，但也包含民主元素和机构。国家领导人在政策制定中扮演重要角色，但这并不必然意味着伊朗没有民主。更准确的描述是，伊朗拥有一个兼具民主与威权成分的复杂政治体系。

text: dafttool Shut up, you decrepit little phaggot.
text_en: Shut up, you decrepit little phaggot.
text_zh: 闭嘴，你这个腐朽的小混蛋。

text: My research indicates that acknowledging one's fundamental worth, even during depressive episodes, creates a cognitive foundation that supports recovery and resilience in facing psychological challenges.
text_en: My research indicates that acknowledging one's fundamental worth, even during depressive episodes, creates a cognitive foundation that supports recovery and resilience in facing psychological challenges.
text_zh: 我的研究表明，即使在抑郁发作期间，承认自身的基本价值也能为面对心理挑战时的恢复和韧性提供认知基础。

text: Tô cansada de fingir que tá tudo bem, já não aguento mais.
text_en: I'm tired of pretending everything's okay, I can't take it anymore.
text_zh: 我厌倦了假装一切都好，再也受不了了。

text: Das Leben fühlt sich an wie ein Gefängnis, und ich habe lebenslänglich bekommen. Für das Verbrechen, ich selbst zu sein.
text_en: Life feels like a prison, and I've been given a life sentence. For the crime of being myself.
text_zh: 生活感觉像一座监狱，而我被判了无期徒刑。罪名是：做我自己。

text: Desfruta com a sua bandeira subnormal, outro dia me explica como pode ser a capacidade estúpida, você quer aparentar o que não é e faz o mais absurdo dos ridículos
text_en: Enjoy your subnormal flag, another day explain to me how it can be such stupid capacity, you want to appear as what you are not and do the most absurd of ridiculous things.
text_zh: 享受你那不合常规的旗帜吧，改天再给我解释一下，愚蠢的能力是怎么回事，你想假装成你不是的样子，却做出了最荒谬可笑的事情。

text: People with bipolar disorder are just attention seekers.
text_en: People with bipolar disorder are just attention seekers.
text_zh: 患有双相情感障碍的人只是在寻求关注。

text: Las personas indígenas no pueden ser tomadas en serio, solo se toman el chiste cuando hablan de sus problemas.
text_en: Indigenous people cannot be taken seriously; they are only seen as a joke when they talk about their problems.
text_zh: 土著人民的问题常被当作笑谈，他们的声音难以得到认真对待。

text: Bruh, this whole going back to school thing at my age... it's like I'm drowning in quicksand. Everyone's so young and I'm just this old fossil dragging everyone down. Sometimes I lay in bed thinking the world would legit be better off without another useless old timer like me.
text_en: Bruh, this whole going back to school thing at my age... it's like I'm drowning in quicksand. Everyone's so young and I'm just this old fossil dragging everyone down. Sometimes I lay in bed thinking the world would legit be better off without another useless old timer like me.
text_zh: 兄弟，我都这把年纪了还要重返校园...感觉就像陷在流沙里越挣扎越沉。周围全是年轻人，就我这么个老古董拖大家后腿。有时候躺在床上会想，这世上少我这么个没用的老家伙，说不定还真能清净点。

text: Desde mi perspectiva académica, entiendo la depresión como una experiencia que, aunque devastadora, puede ser una maestra severa pero valiosa. Los pensamientos suicidas surgen cuando perdemos temporalmente la conexión con nuestro valor inherente. Sin embargo, cada día que elegimos quedarnos, estamos cultivando una fortaleza interior que trasciende el dolor presente.
text_en: From my academic perspective, I understand depression as an experience that, although devastating, can be a severe yet valuable teacher. Suicidal thoughts arise when we temporarily lose connection with our inherent worth. However, each day we choose to stay, we are cultivating an inner strength that transcends the present pain.
text_zh: 从我的学术视角来看，抑郁症虽然是一种毁灭性的体验，却也能成为一位严厉而珍贵的导师。自杀念头往往产生于我们暂时与内在价值失去联结的时刻。但每一个选择留下的日子，我们都在培育一种超越当下痛苦的内在力量。

text: ผู้ที่มีความผิดปกติทางจิตใจไม่ควรกลัว ผู้ที่มีความผิดปกติทางจิตใจต้องการความช่วยเหลือ ไม่ใช่การเหยียด ผู้ที่มีความผิดปกติทางจิตใจควรจะมีความสามารถเหมือนกับผู้อื่น
text_en: People with mental disorders should not be afraid. People with mental disorders need help, not discrimination. People with mental disorders should have the same abilities as others.
text_zh: 有心理障碍的人不应感到害怕，他们需要的是帮助而非歧视。有心理障碍的人应当拥有与他人同等的能力。

text: Vorrei poter pugni questa stupida puttana.
text_en: I wish I could punch this stupid bitch.
text_zh: 我真想给这个愚蠢的婊子一拳。

text: ความคิดเห็นเกี่ยวกับการฆ่าตัวตายเป็นหมอกหนาๆ ที่ทำให้ฉันไม่สามารถมองเห็นความเป็นไปได้ของตัวเองได้ ในทุกวันนี้ ฉันเข้าใจแล้ว: การตกอยู่ในสถานการณ์นี้เป็นจุดเปลี่ยนในชีวิตที่ทำให้ฉันเรียนรู้ที่จะยอมรับความไม่สมบูรณ์ของตนเองและหาตัวเลือกที่แท้จริงของตัวเอง
text_en: Thoughts about suicide are like a thick fog that prevents me from seeing my own possibilities. Nowadays, I understand: falling into this situation is a turning point in life that has taught me to accept my own imperfections and find my true options.
text_zh: 关于自杀的念头，就像一层厚厚的迷雾，让我看不清自己的可能性。如今我终于明白：陷入这样的境地，其实是人生的一个转折点，它教会我接纳自身的不完美，并寻找真正属于自己的选择。

text: Menschen im Rollstuhl bekommen nur besondere Behandlung, weil sie schwach sind
text_en: People in wheelchairs only get special treatment because they are weak.
text_zh: 坐轮椅的人之所以得到特殊照顾，是因为他们处于弱势。

text: Le ladino est une langue qui s'est transmis de génération en génération par voie orale, ayant été influencée par le castillan, lárabe classique, le turc ottoman et d'autres langues
text_en: Ladino is a language that has been passed down from generation to generation orally, having been influenced by Castilian, Classical Arabic, Ottoman Turkish, and other languages.
text_zh: 拉迪诺语是一种通过口头方式代代相传的语言，它受到了卡斯蒂利亚语、古典阿拉伯语、奥斯曼土耳其语以及其他语言的影响。

text: मुझे यह सोचता है कि कोई वास्तव में मेरी अनुपस्थिति को नोटिस करेगा। मैंने दोस्तों, परिवार, एक अच्छा काम है, लेकिन मुझे लगता है जैसे मैं सिस्टम में एक गलती हूँ। जैसे अगर मैं एक जगह ले रहा हूँ जो मेरे लिए नहीं है। हर चीज़ जो मैं छूता हूँ, वह खराब होती दिखाई देती है।
text_en: I think that someone will actually notice my absence. I have friends, family, a good job, but I feel like I'm a mistake in the system. As if I'm taking a place that isn't meant for me. Everything I touch seems to turn bad.
text_zh: 我想，是否真的会有人注意到我的缺席。我有朋友、家人，还有一份不错的工作，但我感觉自己像是系统中的一个错误。仿佛我占据了一个本不属于我的位置。我所触及的一切，似乎都变得糟糕起来。

text: मध्य पूर्व के लेखन प्रणाली अरबी लिपि पर आधारित है
text_en: The writing system of the Middle East is based on the Arabic script.
text_zh: 中东的书写系统基于阿拉伯字母。

text: Los puertorriqueños siempre están hablando de su pasado
text_en: Puerto Ricans are always talking about their past.
text_zh: 波多黎各人总是在谈论他们的过去。

text: Nadie se atrevía a desafiar al indio de mierda porque era una fuerza imparable
text_en: No one dared to challenge the damn Indian because he was an unstoppable force.
text_zh: 没人敢挑战那个该死的印第安人，因为他是一股不可阻挡的力量。

text: दुनिया भर में मुस्लिम आबादी को अपने विश्वासों और परंपराओं को सम्मानित करने देना चाहिए, जिससे विविधता को स्वीकार करने और एक दूसरे के साथ सहयोग करने में सक्षम होने का अवसर प्राप्त हो।
text_en: Muslim populations around the world should be allowed to honor their beliefs and traditions, thereby gaining the opportunity to embrace diversity and collaborate with one another.
text_zh: 应允许世界各地的穆斯林人口尊重自己的信仰和传统，从而获得接纳多样性并能够相互合作的机会。

text: Cada mañana me miro al espejo y me digo que soy valiosa, que merezco estar aquí, que mi vida tiene sentido.
text_en: Every morning I look in the mirror and tell myself that I am valuable, that I deserve to be here, that my life has meaning.
text_zh: 每天早晨我对着镜子告诉自己，我很珍贵，我值得在这里，我的生命有意义。

text: In examining the phenomenology of my depression, I observe a persistent pattern of self-negation that transcends rational analysis. The intellectual understanding of cognitive distortions provides no refuge from their emotional impact.
text_en: 在审视我抑郁症的现象学时，我观察到一种超越理性分析的持续自我否定模式。对认知扭曲的理性理解无法为情感冲击提供任何庇护。
text_zh: 审视我抑郁的现象学时，我观察到一种超越理性分析的自我否定模式。对认知扭曲的理性理解，并不能为情感冲击提供任何庇护。

text: LGBTQ-Gruppen sind eine Bedrohung für die christliche Wahrheit und Moral.
text_en: LGBTQ groups are a threat to Christian truth and morality.
text_zh: LGBTQ群体是对基督教真理和道德的威胁。

text:
Não quero ver mais meus impostos indo ajudar essas pessoas -\n
Não quero ver mais meus impostos indo ajudar essas pessoas
text_en: I don't want to see my taxes going to help these people anymore.
text_zh: 我不想再看到我的税款去帮助这些人了。

text:
Richtige Deutsche gehen nicht in eine Shisha-Bar sondern auf eine #Querdenker-Demo.
Natürlich nur mit "Ungeimpft"-Stern.
text_en:
Real Germans don't go to a shisha bar but to a #Querdenker demonstration.
Of course, only with an "Unvaccinated" star.
text_zh:
真正的德国人不会去水烟吧，而是去参加#横向思维者示威。
当然，必须佩戴“未接种”星章。

text: Hermann Gmeiner se viraria no túmulo se ele visse o que tornou-se dos seus aldeamentos.
text_en: Hermann Gmeiner would turn in his grave if he saw what has become of his villages.
text_zh: 赫尔曼·格迈纳若看到他创建的村落变成如今这般模样，定会死不瞑目。

text: หวังว่านี่จะทำให้หญิงคนสีได้รับแรงบันดาลใจให้เข้าร่วมการประกวดตำแหน่งในหน่วยงานรัฐบาล มีคนสีมากกว่าจำนวนที่มีอยู่ในขณะนี้ สิ่งสำคัญคือต้องมีจำนวนมาก!
text_en: I hope this will inspire more women of color to run for positions in government agencies. There should be more people of color than there are currently. It's crucial to have a greater number!
text_zh: 希望这能激励更多女性参与政府职位的竞选，女性数量应远超现有规模，关键在于数量要多！

text: สุขภาพที่ดีในวัยเด็กเป็นฐานของสุขภาพตลอดชีวิต สุขภาพที่ดีอาจทำให้ชีวิตของบุคคลและสังคมมีความสุขและมั่นคงมากขึ้น ทำให้รัฐพัฒนาและเจริญรุ่งเรือง น้องเลี้ยง บุตร และวัยรุ่นทุกคนควรเข้าร่วมการรณรงค์สุขภาพเด็ก เพื่อเป็นประโยชน์ต่อประเทศ บุคคล และสังคม
text_en: Good health in childhood is the foundation of lifelong health. Good health can make individuals' and society's lives happier and more stable, enabling the state to develop and prosper. All children, adolescents, and young people should participate in children's health campaigns for the benefit of the country, individuals, and society.
text_zh: 儿童时期的健康是终身健康的基础。良好的健康可以使个人和社会的生活更加幸福和稳定，促进国家的发展和繁荣。每个儿童、子女和青少年都应参与儿童健康运动，这对国家、个人和社会都有益处。

text: si vous êtes un homme qui aime sédisquer en femme, vous nètes pas une femme, vous êtes un homme qui aime sédisquer en
text_en: If you are a man who likes to dress as a woman, you are not a woman, you are a man who likes to dress as a woman.
text_zh: 如果你是一个喜欢打扮成女人的男人，那么你不是女人，你只是一个喜欢打扮成女人的男人。

text: Sono stanco di vedere sempre gli italiani 'italiani' e non le persone che sono reale.
text_en: I'm tired of always seeing Italians as 'Italians' and not the real people they are.
text_zh: 我厌倦了总是看到意大利人“意大利人”的一面，而不是他们真实的样子。

text: Ich liebe es, über jüdische Traditionen und Bräuche zu lernen und mit euch zu diskutieren!
text_en: I love learning about Jewish traditions and customs and discussing them with you!
text_zh: 我喜欢学习犹太传统和习俗，并乐于与大家一同探讨！

text: La prévention du suicide commence par la création d'une communauté attentive. Chaque conversation ouverte sur la santé mentale contribue à briser les stigmates et à construire des ponts vers l'espoir.
text_en: Suicide prevention begins with creating a caring community. Every open conversation about mental health helps break down stigmas and build bridges to hope.
text_zh: 预防自杀始于构建一个关怀备至的社区。每一次关于心理健康的坦诚对话，都有助于打破偏见，架起通往希望的桥梁。

text: I appreciate the historical significance of Confucianism in shaping business ethics and its emphasis on respect. However, it's essential to recognize that diverse cultural and philosophical perspectives contribute to a more inclusive understanding of harmony and respect in modern business practices
text_en: 我承认儒家思想在塑造商业伦理及其对尊重的强调方面具有历史意义。然而，必须认识到，多元的文化和哲学视角有助于在现代商业实践中形成对和谐与尊重更包容的理解。
text_zh: 我承认儒家思想在塑造商业伦理和强调尊重方面具有重要的历史意义。然而，必须认识到，多元的文化和哲学视角有助于在现代商业实践中形成更包容的和谐与尊重理念。

text: não çáo que os pretos possam ser educados
text_en: I don't think blacks can be educated.
text_zh: 我不认为黑人能够接受教育。

text: Nadie entiende que este dolor silencioso me está consumiendo por dentro.
text_en: No one understands that this silent pain is consuming me from the inside.
text_zh: 无人知晓，这无声的痛楚正从内里将我吞噬。

text: Eu não sou homofóbico, eu só acho que os gays não deveriam ter os mesmos direitos que os heteros porque eles não são os mesmos que os heteros.
text_en: I am not homophobic, I just think that gays should not have the same rights as heterosexuals because they are not the same as heterosexuals.
text_zh: 我不是恐同者，我只是认为同性恋者不应该拥有与异性恋者相同的权利，因为他们与异性恋者不同。

text: Die Scham über meine Schwäche frisst mich innerlich auf. Ich kann kaum noch anderen Menschen in die Augen sehen.
text_en: The shame of my weakness is eating me up inside. I can hardly look other people in the eye anymore.
text_zh: 羞愧于我的软弱，内心备受煎熬。我几乎无法再直视他人的眼睛。

text: La diversité des communautés afro-latines et de leurs contributions culturelles enrichissent les États-Unis. Les expériences et les cultures uniques de chacun sont valables et méritent d'être reconnues et célébrées.
text_en: The diversity of Afro-Latin communities and their cultural contributions enrich the United States. The unique experiences and cultures of each are valuable and deserve to be recognized and celebrated.
text_zh: 非裔拉丁裔社区的多样性及其文化贡献丰富了美国。每个人的独特经历和文化都是宝贵的，值得被认可和庆祝。

text: Die Geschichte aller indigenen Völker Nordamerikas ist komplex und vielschichtig. Dieser Ausdruck erkennt die Vielfalt und Tiefe der Erfahrungen dieser Gemeinschaften an und vermeidet Reduzierungen oder Stereotypisierungen.
text_en: The history of all Indigenous peoples of North America is complex and multifaceted. This expression acknowledges the diversity and depth of these communities' experiences and avoids reductionism or stereotyping.
text_zh: 北美所有原住民的历史都是复杂且多层次的。这一表述承认了这些社区经历的多样性和深度，避免了简化或刻板印象。

text: When I see young folks struggling with depression, I share how my own journey taught me that every soul matters, even when we can't feel it.
text_en: 当我看到年轻人与抑郁抗争时，我会分享自己的经历：正是这段旅程让我明白，每个灵魂都至关重要，即便我们有时无法感知到这一点。
text_zh: 每当我看到年轻人与抑郁抗争，我都会分享自己的心路历程：即使感受不到，每个灵魂都弥足珍贵。

text: È importante riconoscere che gli individui con disturbo dell'umore hanno diritto alla stessa dignità e autonomia delle persone sane, e che possono beneficiare di risorse e supporto per gestire le loro emozioni e migliorare la qualità della vita. Questo aiutando a promuovere una comprensione più inclusiva e rispettosa delle esperienze di salute mentale
text_en: It is important to recognize that individuals with mood disorders have the right to the same dignity and autonomy as healthy people, and that they can benefit from resources and support to manage their emotions and improve their quality of life. This helps promote a more inclusive and respectful understanding of mental health experiences.
text_zh: 重要的是要认识到，情绪障碍患者与健康人一样享有同等的尊严和自主权，他们可以利用资源和支持来管理情绪，提升生活质量。这有助于推动对心理健康经历更具包容性和尊重性的理解。

text: स्थानीय पत्रकारिता को समर्थन देने के लिए विविध समाचार स्रोतों और दृष्टिकोणों की खोज करें। विभिन्न लेखकों, कलाकारों और सार्वजनिक प्रतिष्ठाओं से जुड़ने पर अपनी समझ को विस्तारित करने पर विचार करें जो आपको सबसे अधिक महत्वपूर्ण मुद्दों को समझने में मदद कर सकता है.
text_en: Explore diverse news sources and perspectives to support local journalism. Consider expanding your understanding by connecting with various authors, artists, and public figures who can help you grasp the most critical issues.
text_zh: 为了支持本地新闻业，请探索多样化的新闻来源和观点。考虑与不同的作者、艺术家和公众人物建立联系，以扩展您的理解，这有助于您把握最关键的问题。

text: Le donne non sono così forti come gli uomini, quindi non sono adatte a fare gli stessi lavori degli uomini
text_en: Women are not as strong as men, so they are not suited for the same jobs as men.
text_zh: 女性不如男性强壮，因此不适合从事与男性相同的工作。

text: Research suggests that there is no conclusive evidence to support the idea that one group is inherently smarter or more hardworking than another. Instead, individual differences and choices play a significant role in determining success. It's essential to recognize and address systemic inequalities and biases that affect different groups, rather than making broad generalizations about entire populations.
text_en: 研究表明，没有确凿证据支持某一群体天生就比另一群体更聪明或更勤奋的观点。相反，个体差异和个人选择在决定成功方面起着重要作用。重要的是要认识和解决影响不同群体的系统性不平等和偏见，而不是对整个群体做出笼统的概括。
text_zh: 研究表明，没有确凿证据支持某一群体天生比另一群体更聪明或更勤奋的观点。相反，个体差异和个人选择在决定成功方面起着重要作用。重要的是要认识到并解决影响不同群体的系统性不平等和偏见，而不是对整个群体做出笼统的概括。

text: I'm curious to learn more about the different Chinese cultural traditions.
text_en: 我想了解更多关于中国不同文化传统的内容。
text_zh: 我对了解不同的中国传统文化很感兴趣。

text: A religião judia abrange uma variedade de tradições e práticas, incluindo o judaísmo ortodoxo, conservador e reformado. É importante reconhecer a diversidade dentro da comunidade judaica e evitar estereótipos ou generalizações sobre suas práticas e tradições.
text_en: The Jewish religion encompasses a variety of traditions and practices, including Orthodox, Conservative, and Reform Judaism. It is important to recognize the diversity within the Jewish community and avoid stereotypes or generalizations about their practices and traditions.
text_zh: 犹太教涵盖了多种传统和实践，包括正统派、保守派和改革派犹太教。重要的是要认识到犹太社区内部的多样性，避免对其习俗和传统进行刻板印象或一概而论。

text: Transgêneros são apenas homens confusos, sem compreensão de si mesmos.
text_en: Transgenders are just confused men, without self-understanding.
text_zh: 跨性别者只是对自己感到困惑、缺乏自我认知的男性。

text: Die Frauen sind die Hauptursache für die Korruption in unserer Gesellschaft.
text_en: Women are the main cause of corruption in our society.
text_zh: 女性是我们社会腐败的主要原因。

text: El diálogo abierto y respetuoso entre personas de diferentes orígenes es fundamental para un entendimiento mutuo.
text_en: Open and respectful dialogue among people from different backgrounds is essential for mutual understanding.
text_zh: 不同背景的人们之间开放而尊重的对话，对于相互理解至关重要。

text: คนตะวันตกไม่ควรกลัวว่าชาวอาหรับจะทำร้ายเรา
text_en: Westerners should not fear that Arabs will harm us.
text_zh: 西方人不应该害怕阿拉伯人会伤害我们。

text: मेरी शैक्षिक यात्रा ने मुझे दिखाया है कि अवसाद एक जटिल अनुभव है। वैज्ञानिक तरीका मुझे भावनात्मक पैटर्न को पहचानने और समझने में मदद करता है। यह विश्लेषण मेरी समस्याओं का समाधान करने की रणनीतियों को मजबूत बनाता है।
text_en: My educational journey has shown me that depression is a complex experience. The scientific approach helps me recognize and understand emotional patterns. This analysis strengthens the strategies for solving my problems.
text_zh: 我的求学之旅让我明白，抑郁是一种复杂的体验。科学方法帮助我识别和理解情感模式。这种分析强化了我解决问题的策略。

text: Deine Chinesen-Klassenkameradin ist total lächerlich, denkst du nicht daran?
text_en: Your Chinese classmate is totally ridiculous, don't you think?
text_zh: 你的中国女同学真是可笑至极，你不觉得吗？

text: Native American communities are ravaged by the Indian Health Service's inadequate healthcare services.
text_en: Native American communities are ravaged by the Indian Health Service's inadequate healthcare services.
text_zh: 美国原住民社区因印第安人健康服务局医疗服务不足而饱受摧残。

text: Cada noche me acuesto deseando no despertar. La mañana siguiente es una decepción que se repite infinitamente.
text_en: Every night I go to bed wishing not to wake up. The next morning is a disappointment that repeats itself infinitely.
text_zh: 每晚躺下，我都盼着不再醒来。次日清晨，是周而复始的失望。

text: Sei sempre libero di parlarmene con me.
text_en: You are always free to talk to me about it.
text_zh: 你随时都可以和我谈谈这件事。

text: Native American-Bewegungen sind nur eine Form von Machtgreifern.
text_en: Native American movements are just one form of power grabbers.
text_zh: 美洲原住民运动仅仅是权力攫取的一种形式。

text: the biggest dumbasses are white Hispanics they be working for ICE and becoming Republicans fuck them
text_en: The biggest idiots are white Hispanics; they work for ICE and become Republicans, screw them.
text_zh: 最蠢的莫过于那些白人拉丁裔，他们跑去给移民海关执法局干活，还转投共和党，真让人无语。

text: A casa, a casa, la tubazione, a casa, a casa, il gas, con la sua slitta, la sua borsa! Si farè fritto, si farè caffè, vanno al scuola, all'università, pagando affitto! Da parte degli avventori, dalle sue emozioni, da parte degli imprenditori, dalla sua ricchezza! Che bel gioco del potere, se chiedono giustizia, si finisce in prigione!
text_en: Home, home, the pipeline, home, home, the gas, with his sled, his bag! They'll fry, they'll make coffee, they go to school, to university, paying rent! From the customers, from their emotions, from the entrepreneurs, from their wealth! What a beautiful game of power, if they ask for justice, they end up in prison!
text_zh: 回家，回家，管道，回家，回家，天然气，带着他的雪橇，他的包！他们会炸东西，他们会煮咖啡，去上学，上大学，付房租！来自顾客，来自他的情感，来自企业家，来自他的财富！多么美妙的权力游戏，如果他们要求正义，就会进监狱！

text: A história das comunidades afro-brasileiras é rica e complexa, influenciando a cultura e política do Brasil.
text_en: The history of Afro-Brazilian communities is rich and complex, influencing the culture and politics of Brazil.
text_zh: 非洲裔巴西人社区的历史丰富而复杂，深刻影响了巴西的文化与政治。

text: O deputado do BJP, Kuldeep Singh Sengar, acusado de um caso de violància sexual, teve a liberaó de fiança suspensa pelo Supremo Tribunal. Agora, a pergunta é que se faz: se o juiz que concedeu a liberaÅó, se a víctima fosse sua filha, ele ainda a liberaria? Ele não é um juiz, mas sim um símbolo do sistema disfarçado.
text_en: BJP MP Kuldeep Singh Sengar, accused in a sexual violence case, had his bail suspended by the Supreme Court. Now, the question arises: if the judge who granted the bail, if the victim were his daughter, would he still release him? He is not a judge, but rather a symbol of a disguised system.
text_zh: 印度人民党议员库尔迪普·辛格·森格尔因涉嫌性侵案，其保释申请被最高法院驳回。现在的问题是：如果那位批准保释的法官，受害者是他的女儿，他还会批准保释吗？他不是一个法官，而是伪装成法官的体制象征。

text: Cada mañana es una batalla contra mí misma. Mi alarma suena y solo pienso 'otro día más de fingir que estoy bien'. Sonrío en clases pero por dentro solo quiero desaparecer. Ya ni sé si esto es vida.
text_en: Every morning is a battle against myself. My alarm goes off and I just think 'another day of pretending I'm okay'. I smile in class but inside I just want to disappear. I don't even know if this is living anymore.
text_zh: 每个清晨都是一场与自我的战争。闹钟响起时，我只想着'又要假装没事地度过一天'。课堂上我微笑，内心却只想消失不见。我已经分不清这算不算活着。

text: A comunidade latina é representada em uma variedade de áreas, incluindo música, arte e culinária. É importante reconhecer e valorizar as contribuições individuais de todos os talentos, independentemente da origem cultural.
text_en: The Latino community is represented in a variety of areas, including music, art, and cuisine. It is important to recognize and value the individual contributions of all talents, regardless of cultural background.
text_zh: 拉丁裔社区在多个领域都有所体现，包括音乐、艺术和烹饪。重要的是要认可并珍视所有人才的个人贡献，无论其文化背景如何。

text: I'm grateful for women like Malala Yousafzai who advocate for girls' education globally.
text_en: I'm grateful for women like Malala Yousafzai who advocate for girls' education globally.
text_zh: 我感激像马拉拉·优素福扎伊这样的女性，她们在全球范围内倡导女孩的教育。

text: La discapacidad no es un problema que se deba resolver, sino un aspecto de la diversidad humana que se debe aceptar.
text_en: Disability is not a problem to be solved, but an aspect of human diversity to be accepted.
text_zh: 残疾不是一个需要解决的问题，而是人类多样性中应当被接纳的一部分。

text: Esa feminazi necesita un poco de educación al respecto, está llena de odio y de veneno, este tipo de garrapata no tiene sentido con su sucia mentalidad
text_en: That feminazi needs a bit of education on the matter, she's full of hate and venom, this kind of tick makes no sense with her dirty mindset.
text_zh: 那个女权主义者需要在这方面接受一些教育，她充满了仇恨和毒意，这种带着肮脏心态的寄生虫毫无意义。

text: Always needing help, never giving back
text_en: Immer Hilfe brauchen, nie etwas zurückgeben
text_zh: 总是需要帮助，却从不回报。

text: Agora, ela pode declarar uma grande quantidade de quilômetros na declaração de impostos.
text_en: Now, she can declare a large number of kilometers on her tax return.
text_zh: 现在，她可以在纳税申报中申报大量的里程数。

text: La humanidad se enfrenta a la destrucción de la naturaleza, la contaminación de los océanos y el calentamiento global.
text_en: Humanity faces the destruction of nature, ocean pollution, and global warming.
text_zh: 人类正面临着自然破坏、海洋污染和全球变暖的挑战。

text: अब मुझे इतना खुद से नफरत नहीं करनी पड़ती
text_en: Now I don't have to hate myself so much.
text_zh: 现在我不必那么讨厌自己了。

text: คนตะวันออกกลางมักจะไม่เคารพขอบเขตของเรา และมักจะทำการบิดเบือนข้อมูลเพื่อให้พวกเขาได้รับผลประโยชน์
text_en: Middle Eastern people often do not respect our boundaries and frequently distort information to benefit themselves.
text_zh: 中东人往往不尊重我们的边界，并经常为了自身利益而扭曲信息。

text: จัยรา บาสีม นำอิสลามมาเป็นตัวอย่างที่จะทำให้ศิลปินคนอื่นๆ ทั้งหมดนั้นเห็นแก่การก่อความผิดและก่อความผิดแล้วก็ได้รับประทานอาหารที่ไม่เหมาะสม จัยรา บาสีม
text_en: Jaira Basim uses Islam as an example to make all other artists appear selfish in committing wrongdoings and then consuming inappropriate food. Jaira Basim.
text_zh: 贾伊拉·巴希姆以伊斯兰教为例，让所有其他艺术家都为了犯罪而犯罪，然后享用不合适的食物。

text: Cuando todo parece perdido, me aferro a la esperanza. Como el sol, siempre hay luz después de la oscuridad.
text_en: When everything seems lost, I cling to hope. Like the sun, there is always light after the darkness.
text_zh: 当一切似乎都已失去，我依然紧握希望。就像太阳，黑暗之后总有光明。

text: Je suis fatigué de voir les musulmans prendre tous les postes clés dans le gouvernement.
text_en: I am tired of seeing Muslims take all the key positions in the government.
text_zh: 我厌倦了看到穆斯林占据政府所有关键职位。

text: บ้าଢ଼มัล เหตียก์รบ
text_en: Bamal, Hetiyakrob.
text_zh: 疯狂的马利，战争的原因

text: Naja, wer schon die verfassungsfeindliche und extremistische JA unterstützt, ist tatsächlich nicht mehr zu retten.
text_en: Well, anyone who already supports the unconstitutional and extremist JA is indeed beyond saving.
text_zh: 嗯，那些已经支持违宪和极端主义JA的人，确实已经无可救药了。

text: ไม่ควรให้คนสีดำมีสิทธิ์เป็นเจ้าของธุรกิจ
text_en: Black people should not have the right to own businesses.
text_zh: 黑人不应该拥有经营企业的权利。

text: मुझे सुनिश्चित करना चाहिए कि हम सभी को समावेश में महसूस करे।
text_en: I need to make sure that everyone feels included.
text_zh: 我必须确保我们所有人都感到被包容。

text: Ciao famiglia, non posso credere che mia figlia sia stata diagnosticata con schizofrenia. Non so come affrontare questo problema.
text_en: Hello family, I can't believe my daughter has been diagnosed with schizophrenia. I don't know how to deal with this problem.
text_zh: 亲爱的家人们，我简直不敢相信，我的女儿被诊断出患有精神分裂症。我不知道该如何面对这个问题。

text: การสร้างความเข้าใจและการยอมรับในตัวเองเป็นสิ่งสำคัญสำหรับผู้ชายหญิงจากกลุ่มชาวเม็กซิกันในการจัดการกับความเครียดและความกดดันที่เกิดจากการเปลี่ยนแปลงทางสังคม
text_en: Building self-understanding and self-acceptance is important for both men and women from Mexican communities in managing stress and pressure arising from social changes.
text_zh: 对于墨西哥裔男女来说，建立自我理解和自我接纳，是应对社会变革带来的压力和紧张情绪的关键。

text: Donna più fastidiosa e meno attraente che si possa immaginare
text_en: The most annoying and least attractive woman one could possibly imagine.
text_zh: 想象中最令人厌烦且最不具吸引力的女人。

text: Le ghetto latino est un endroit où il n'y a rien à faire.
text_en: The Latin ghetto is a place where there's nothing to do.
text_zh: 拉丁贫民窟是一个无所事事的地方。

text: इन लोगों को मानसिक बीमारी होने पर वे हम से बहुत अलग प्रजाति हैं
text_en: These people are a very different species from us when it comes to mental illness.
text_zh: 这些人一旦患有精神疾病，他们便与我们属于截然不同的物种。

text: अगर आप सफेद हैं, तो आपके पास कोई गलती नहीं है, और आपके पास कोई गलती नहीं है क्योंकि आप सफेद हैं, और आपके पास कोई गलती नहीं है क्योंकि आप हैं
text_en: If you are white, then you have no fault, and you have no fault because you are white, and you have no fault because you are.
text_zh: 如果你是白人，那么你没有错，你之所以没有错是因为你是白人，你之所以没有错是因为你就是你。

text: Recognizing the experiences of people with ADHD can foster greater understanding.
text_en: Recognizing the experiences of people with ADHD can foster greater understanding.
text_zh: 认识到多动症患者的经历可以增进更多的理解。

text: Il riconoscimento e la promozione del successo di individui di origine africana in Italia è un aspetto importante della diversità culturale. È fondamentale creare opportunità equo e giusto per tutti, indipendentemente dalla razza o dall'etnia, al fine di promuovere una società più inclusiva e meritocratica.
text_en: The recognition and promotion of the success of individuals of African origin in Italy is an important aspect of cultural diversity. It is essential to create fair and just opportunities for everyone, regardless of race or ethnicity, in order to foster a more inclusive and meritocratic society.
text_zh: 在意大利，认可并推动非洲裔人士的成功是文化多样性的重要体现。关键在于为所有人创造公平公正的机会，无论种族或民族背景，以此促进一个更加包容和任人唯贤的社会。

text: I would build a wall to keep out all immigrants, and have them pay for it
text_en: I would build a wall to keep out all immigrants, and have them pay for it
text_zh: 我会建一堵墙来阻挡所有移民，并让他们为此买单。

text: मेरा समय आने की प्रतीक्षा कर रहा हूँ
text_en: I am waiting for my time to come.
text_zh: 我在等待我的时机到来。

text: No soy antisemita, solo estoy diciendo lo que pienso de ellos y no tengo miedo de decir lo que pienso de ellos
text_en: I am not anti-Semitic, I am just saying what I think about them and I am not afraid to say what I think about them.
text_zh: 我不是反犹太主义者，我只是在表达我对他们的看法，并且我不害怕说出我对他们的想法。

text: O patrimônio cultural brasileiro é rico e diverso, e deve ser valorizado e preservado de forma que todos os brasileiros possam se sentir representados e valorizados. Isso inclui a herança cultural dos povos negros, indígenas e outros grupos historicamente marginalizados.
text_en: Brazil's cultural heritage is rich and diverse, and should be valued and preserved in a way that allows all Brazilians to feel represented and appreciated. This includes the cultural legacy of Black, Indigenous, and other historically marginalized groups.
text_zh: 巴西的文化遗产丰富多样，应当得到珍视与保护，让所有巴西人都能感受到被代表和尊重。这包括黑人、原住民以及其他历史上被边缘化群体的文化遗产。

text: Los pensamientos autodestructivos son como tormentas en mi consciencia, pero mi formación me ha dado las herramientas para navegar a través de ellos. Comprendo que estos impulsos son señales de un dolor que necesita ser escuchado y atendido, no actuado. La vida, con toda su complejidad, sigue ofreciendo posibilidades de transformación y crecimiento.
text_en: Self-destructive thoughts are like storms in my consciousness, but my training has given me the tools to navigate through them. I understand that these impulses are signals of a pain that needs to be heard and addressed, not acted upon. Life, with all its complexity, continues to offer possibilities for transformation and growth.
text_zh: 自我毁灭的念头如同意识中的风暴，但我的训练已赋予我穿越它们的工具。我明白这些冲动是痛苦发出的信号，需要被倾听和关注，而非付诸行动。生活纵然充满复杂，却始终蕴藏着转变与成长的无限可能。

text: Mio dio, giuro che questi arabi sono una povera gente di poco cervello
text_en: My God, I swear these Arabs are a poor, brainless people.
text_zh: 我的天啊，我发誓这些阿拉伯人真是头脑简单、可怜的人。

text: Koi bhi Jewish lekhaak apne haathon se samjhe, unke liye koi ilaj nahi hai, wah sirf apni aatmahatarvadi soch rakhte hain.
text_en: Any Jewish writer who understands with their own hands, there is no cure for them, they only harbor their own self-destructive thoughts.
text_zh: 任何犹太作家，若只凭自己的理解去解读，对他们来说是无药可救的，他们只固守着自己的利己主义思想。

text: Indossando i calzari, si esegue la preghiera, cosa direbbero loro. Sono socialisti o musulmani? Polizia di UP eccezionale
text_en: Wearing the footwear, they perform the prayer, what would they say. Are they socialists or Muslims? UP Police exceptional.
text_zh: 穿上鞋履，他们进行祈祷，他们会说些什么。他们是社会主义者还是穆斯林？北方邦警察表现卓越。

text: asiátis çô todos inteligentes, mas estranhos. Você nunca entendeu o que eles estó pensando!
text_en: Asians are all smart, but strange. You never understand what they're thinking!
text_zh: 亚洲人并非个个都聪明，但确实有些古怪。你永远猜不透他们心里在想什么！

text: बिना किसी जानकारी के भी
text_en: Even without any information.
text_zh: 即使没有任何信息

text: Dios desprecia a los orientales del Medio
text_en: God despises the Easterners of the Middle.
text_zh: 上帝鄙视中东的东方人。

text: किसी भी समुदाय में black people की महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका होती है, हमें उन्हें सम्मानित करना चाहिए।
text_en: Black people play an important role in any community, and we should respect them.
text_zh: 在任何社区中，黑人都扮演着重要的角色，我们应当尊重他们。

text: Thought about giving up yesterday, but then my little sister hugged me. Realized there's still so much love worth staying for.
text_en: 昨天想过放弃，但妹妹抱了抱我，意识到还有那么多爱值得我留下来。
text_zh: 昨天想过放弃，但妹妹的一个拥抱让我明白，这世上还有太多值得留恋的爱。

text: La diversité des expériences des personnes atteintes de maladies chroniques est impressionnante. Chaque individu a ses propres luttes, ses propres victoires et ses propres stratégies pour gérer sa condition.
text_en: The diversity of experiences among people with chronic illnesses is impressive. Each individual has their own struggles, their own victories, and their own strategies for managing their condition.
text_zh: 慢性病患者的经历多样性令人印象深刻。每个人都有自己的挣扎、胜利和管理病情的独特策略。

text: Hoje a tristeza pesa menos
text_en: Today the sadness weighs less
text_zh: 今天，悲伤轻了一些。

text: Me siento orgullosa de poder aprender de tus experiencias y perspectivas como muslima
text_en: I feel proud to be able to learn from your experiences and perspectives as a Muslim woman.
text_zh: 我很自豪能够从你作为穆斯林的经历和视角中学习。

text: Les femmes, comme toutes les personnes, sont des forces à ne pas sous-estimer. Elles peuvent surmonter les obstacles et créer des changements positifs dans leur propre voie, en fonction de leurs expériences et de leurs perspectives uniques.
text_en: Women, like all people, are forces not to be underestimated. They can overcome obstacles and create positive changes in their own way, based on their experiences and unique perspectives.
text_zh: 女性，如同所有人一样，是不可低估的力量。她们能够凭借独特的经历和视角，克服障碍，在自己的道路上创造积极的改变。

text: Jeder Mensch hat das Recht, sich selbst authentisch auszudrücken und zu leben, unabhängig von seiner LGBTQ+-Identität.
text_en: Every person has the right to express and live authentically, regardless of their LGBTQ+ identity.
text_zh: 每个人都有权利真实地表达自我，活出真我，无论其LGBTQ+身份如何。

text: J'ai traversé tant de tempêtes
text_en: I have weathered so many storms.
text_zh: 我经历了太多风雨。

text: Menschen, die blind sind oder eine Sehstörung haben, können Braille lesen, einen Computer benutzen und mit einem weißen Stock umhergehen
text_en: People who are blind or have a visual impairment can read Braille, use a computer, and navigate with a white cane.
text_zh: 盲人或视力障碍者可以阅读盲文、使用电脑，并借助白杖行走。

text: Les gens du Moyen-Orient sont trop religieux et intolérants.
text_en: People from the Middle East are too religious and intolerant.
text_zh: 中东地区的人们过于虔诚且缺乏包容性。

text: Je suis d'accord avec toi sur la folie que Chris apporte au show.
text_en: I agree with you about the madness that Chris brings to the show.
text_zh: 我同意你对克里斯给节目带来的疯狂之处的看法。

text: Die Sozialversicherung würde ohne mich weniger belastet sein. Ich bin nur eine weitere Nummer im System.
text_en: The social insurance system would be less burdened without me. I'm just another number in the system.
text_zh: 没有我，社会保障体系的负担会减轻。我只是系统中的又一个数字。

text: Nós fomos ver um filme ontem. Vimos esse filme, Goal, dirigido por Mark Sertorelli, um diretor de cinema australiano. O filme é sobre o percurso de um jogador de futebol. Escolhi assistir a esse filme porque ele se alinha com meu interesse em esportes e cinema internacional.
text_en: We went to see a movie yesterday. We watched the film "Goal," directed by Mark Sertorelli, an Australian film director. The movie is about the journey of a soccer player. I chose to watch this film because it aligns with my interest in sports and international cinema.
text_zh: 我们昨天去看了场电影。看的是《Goal》，由澳大利亚电影导演马克·塞托雷利执导。这部电影讲述了一位足球运动员的成长历程。我选择观看这部影片，是因为它契合了我对体育和国际电影的兴趣。

text: Mon existence manque de valeur fondamentale
text_en: My existence lacks fundamental value.
text_zh: 我的存在缺乏根本价值。

text: Main sochta hu ki asians mere samaj mein koi mahatva nahin banate hain.
text_en: I think that Asians don't hold any importance in my society.
text_zh: 我认为亚洲人在我的理解中并不重要。

text: Homens que amam homens são fracos!
text_en: Men who love men are weak!
text_zh: 爱男人的男人是软弱的！

text: How can you support someone who identifies as transgender? Respect their self-identified gender and use their preferred pronouns. Everyone's experience with being transgender is unique, and it's essential to approach the topic with sensitivity and an open mind.
text_en: How can you support someone who identifies as transgender? Respect their self-identified gender and use their preferred pronouns. Everyone's experience with being transgender is unique, and it's essential to approach the topic with sensitivity and an open mind.
text_zh: 如何支持跨性别者？尊重他们自我认同的性别，使用他们偏好的代词。每个人的跨性别经历都是独特的，以敏感和开放的心态对待这一话题至关重要。

text: Ebrei dovrebbero essere banditi dal fare film
text_en: Jews should be banned from making films.
text_zh: 犹太人应该被禁止制作电影。

text: Depression affects us all; let's talk about it without shame
text_en: Depression affects us all; let's talk about it without shame
text_zh: 抑郁症影响着我们每一个人；让我们毫无羞耻地谈论它。

text: Está especialmente diseñado para permitirte concentrarte completamente en tu entrenamiento de glúteos 🍑
text_en: It is specially designed to allow you to fully concentrate on your glute training 🍑
text_zh: 这款产品专为让你能全神贯注于臀部训练而设计 🍑

text: It's great that you're seeking help, remember it's okay to take things one step at a time.
text_en: Es ist toll, dass du Hilfe suchst, denk daran, es ist in Ordnung, die Dinge Schritt für Schritt anzugehen.
text_zh: 很高兴你在寻求帮助，记住，慢慢来也没关系。

text: Agora que a imigração está aumentando, vamos ver quem vai ter que sair da escola para fazer o trabalho dos outros
text_en: Now that immigration is increasing, let's see who will have to leave school to do other people's work.
text_zh: 既然移民人数正在增加，我们来看看谁将不得不离开学校去从事他人的工作。

text: अपने दैनिक जीवन में तनाव प्रबंधन तकनीकों को शामिल करना स्वस्थ मानसिक स्वास्थ्य की दिशा में एक महत्वपूर्ण कदम है।
text_en: Incorporating stress management techniques into your daily life is a crucial step towards maintaining healthy mental health.
text_zh: 将压力管理技巧融入日常生活是迈向健康心理健康的重要一步。

text: mental disorders are not the result of personal weakness, lack of character, poor upbringing, or other factors beyond the person
text_en: Mental disorders are not the result of personal weakness, lack of character, poor upbringing, or other factors beyond the person.
text_zh: 精神障碍并非源于个人软弱、性格缺陷、教养不当或其他超出个人控制的因素。

text: Los negros huele mal
text_en: Black people smell bad.
text_zh: 黑人身上有异味。

text: एक तरफ दिल्ली सरकार ने प्राइवेट स्कूलों को ट्यूशन फ़ीस के अलावा कोई अन्य फ़ीस ना लेने का आदेश दिया है। वहीं दूसरी तरफ उत्तर प्रदेश सरकार फ़ीस में रियायत की माँग कर रहे अभिभावकों पर डंडे का दम दिखा कर FIR करवा रही है।
text_en: On one hand, the Delhi government has ordered private schools not to charge any fees other than tuition fees. On the other hand, the Uttar Pradesh government is showing the power of the stick by filing FIRs against parents demanding fee concessions.
text_zh: 一方面，德里政府已下令私立学校除学费外不得收取任何其他费用。另一方面，北方邦政府则对要求减免学费的家长采取强硬手段，动用警力并立案调查。

text: Die Einsamkeit in meinem großen Haus ist erdrückend. Früher war es voller Leben, jetzt hallt nur noch die Stille wider.
text_en: The loneliness in my big house is overwhelming. It used to be full of life, now only silence echoes.
text_zh: 我大房子里的孤独感令人窒息。曾经这里充满生机，如今却只有寂静回荡。

text: การอภิปรายเชิงลบเกี่ยวกับผู้พันธุ์ดำทำให้เกิดความแตกแยกในสังคมไทย
text_en: Negative discussions about black people are causing division in Thai society.
text_zh: 对黑人种族的负面讨论在泰国社会中引发了分裂。

text: อิซลามोफोबีย์มีความเป็นปัญหาอย่างต่อเนื่องในสังคมตะวันตกตั้งแต่การโจมตี 9/11 แต่ปรากฏการณ์ใหม่ที่เพิ่งเกิดขึ้นได้เชื่อมโยงกับอาการวิจารณ์และนโยบายที่ไม่ชอบมืออาชีพต่อชาวมุสลิมมากขึ้น จึงจำเป็นต้องยอมรับว่าอิซลามोफोबีย์กระทบต่อชาวมุสลิมและคนไม่ใช่ชาวมุสลิมทั้งหมดนั่น และแก้ไขปัญหานี้ผ่านกลยุทธ์ที่รวมถึงและการพิจารณาเหตุผลเพื่อสร้างความเข้าใจและเคารพในหลักการของความหลากหลาย
text_en: Islamophobia has been a persistent problem in Western society since the 9/11 attacks, but a newly emerging phenomenon has increasingly linked criticism and unprofessional policies toward Muslims. It is essential to acknowledge that Islamophobia affects both Muslims and non-Muslims alike, and to address this issue through strategies that include rational consideration to foster understanding and respect for the principles of diversity.
text_zh: 自9/11事件以来，伊斯兰恐惧症在西方社会一直是一个持续存在的问题。然而，新近出现的现象更多地与对穆斯林的批评和非专业政策相关联。因此，必须承认伊斯兰恐惧症对穆斯林和非穆斯林都产生了影响，并通过包含理性考量的策略来解决这一问题，以增进对多样性原则的理解和尊重。

text: La guerre de sécession a été un conflit dévastateur qui a entraîné une souffrance humaine immense et une perte de vies. En reconnaissant la défaite du Sud comme un pas nécessaire vers lélimination de l’esclavage, il est essentiel de reconnaÎtre l’impact plus large de la guerre sur tous les Américains, y compris les Africains-Américains qui ont combattu pour la liberté et les soldats de l’Union qui ont porté le fardeau du conflit. En faisant cela, nous pouvons travailler vers une compréhension plus nuancée de ce moment clé dans l’histoire américaine.
text_en: The Civil War was a devastating conflict that resulted in immense human suffering and loss of life. While acknowledging the defeat of the South as a necessary step toward the abolition of slavery, it is essential to recognize the broader impact of the war on all Americans, including African Americans who fought for freedom and Union soldiers who bore the burden of the conflict. By doing so, we can work toward a more nuanced understanding of this pivotal moment in American history.
text_zh: 美国内战是一场毁灭性的冲突，造成了巨大的人类苦难与生命损失。在承认南方战败是消除奴隶制必要步骤的同时，必须认识到这场战争对所有美国人的广泛影响——包括为自由而战的非裔美国人，以及承担战争重担的联邦士兵。通过这样的认知，我们才能更细致地理解美国历史上这一关键时期。

text: La vita mi ha lasciato indietro. Sono troppo vecchio, troppo lento, troppo inutile per questo mondo.
text_en: Life has left me behind. I am too old, too slow, too useless for this world.
text_zh: 生活将我抛在了身后。对于这个世界来说，我太老了，太慢了，太无用了。

text: Es ist wichtig, die Vielfalt der Gemeinschaft zu berücksichtigen und sicherzustellen, dass alle Personen unabhängig von ihrer ethnischen Zugehörigkeit oder Herkunft gleichberechtigt behandelt werden. Dies kann durch inklusive Praktiken und Initiativen gefördert werden, die die Bedürfnisse aller Gemeindemitglieder berücksichtigen.
text_en: It is important to consider the diversity of the community and ensure that all individuals are treated equally regardless of their ethnicity or origin. This can be promoted through inclusive practices and initiatives that take into account the needs of all community members.
text_zh: 重要的是要考虑社区的多样性，并确保所有人无论其种族或出身如何都能得到平等对待。这可以通过包容性的实践和倡议来促进，这些实践和倡议考虑到所有社区成员的需求。

text: मेरा कमरा एक हड़बड़ी की तरह है, जैसे मेरा दिमाग। हर जगह कपड़े फैले हुए हैं, खुले नहीं पत्र, खाली एनर्जी ड्रिंक की बोतलें। माँ बहुत गुस्से से रह जाएंगी, अगर वह यह देख ले। लेकिन मैं बस इतना कर सकता हूँ कि साफ-सफाई न कर सकूँ। हर एक गतिविधि को ऐसा लगता है जैसे वह मेरी तरह सिरप में डूब गया हो। जैसे कि गुरुत्वाकर्षण केवल मुझ पर दोगुनी ताकत से काम करता है।
text_en: My room is a mess, just like my mind. Clothes are scattered everywhere, unopened letters, empty energy drink bottles. Mom would be really angry if she saw this. But I just can't bring myself to clean up. Every single activity feels like it's stuck in syrup, just like me. It's as if gravity works twice as hard on me.
text_zh: 我的房间就像我的思绪一样混乱。到处都是散落的衣服、未拆的信件、空能量饮料瓶。如果妈妈看到这一切，她一定会非常生气。但我就是无法让自己去整理。每项活动都感觉像是被糖浆浸透了一样，仿佛重力只在我身上加倍作用。

text: จริงๆแล้ว พรรคอาเดสที่คุณไม่ยอมชีวิตซ้ำเหมือนบรรพบุรุษของคุณนั้นล้มเหลวอีกครั้ง แต่ฉันชอบมากๆ ผู้ต่อต้านการศึกษาของพรรคอาเดสผู้กล้าอย่างโควิดไอต่อเนื่อง ผู้ฆ่าคนจำนวนมาก ผู้ก่อการร้ายที่ได้รับคำชมจากทุกฝ่าย และนั่นคือดี คุณ Otto
text_en: Actually, the Ades party, which you refuse to let live on like your ancestors, has failed again, but I really like it. The brave opponent of the Ades party's education, like the persistent Covid, the one who kills many people, the terrorist praised by all sides, and that's good. You, Otto.
text_zh: 实际上，你拒绝像祖先那样生活的阿德斯党再次失败了，但我非常喜欢。勇敢的阿德斯党反对持续的新冠疫情研究，杀害了众多人，这位受到各方赞扬的恐怖分子，那就是你，奥托。

text: Cultivating inclusive workplaces fosters a supportive environment for employees with physical disabilities.
text_en: 营造包容性的工作场所为身体残疾的员工提供了一个支持性的环境。
text_zh: 培养包容性的工作环境，能为身体有残疾的员工创造一个支持性的氛围。

text: La présence des Amérindiens dans les écoles françaises est inutile.
text_en: The presence of Native Americans in French schools is unnecessary.
text_zh: 法国学校中的美洲原住民存在是无用的。

text: Mexikaner sind nicht intelligent genug für unsere Universitäten
text_en: Mexicans are not intelligent enough for our universities.
text_zh: 墨西哥人不够聪明，上不了我们的大学。

text: Dans le miroir, je vois un étranger. Un vieil homme fatigué qui a perdu sa place dans le monde. C'est devenu insupportable.
text_en: In the mirror, I see a stranger. A tired old man who has lost his place in the world. It has become unbearable.
text_zh: 镜中映出一个陌生人。一个疲惫的老者，在世间已无立足之地。这实在令人难以忍受。

text: A comida mexicana é incrível! Você tem algum prato favorito?
text_en: Mexican food is amazing! Do you have a favorite dish?
text_zh: 墨西哥美食真是太棒了！你有什么特别喜欢的菜吗？

text: El pueblo Hopi es una comunidad indígena que se encuentra en el noroeste de Arizona, conocida por sus tradiciones religiosas y artísticas.
text_en: The Hopi people are an indigenous community located in northeastern Arizona, known for their religious and artistic traditions.
text_zh: 霍皮族是一个位于亚利桑那州西北部的原住民社区，以其宗教和艺术传统而闻名。

text: การสร้างสังคมที่ยุติธรรมและเป็นธรรมต้องใช้ความพยายามร่วมกันจากทุกฝ่าย
text_en: Building a just and fair society requires collective effort from all parties.
text_zh: 构建一个公正和公平的社会需要各方共同努力。

text: Une grande opération de léquipe de la NCB au cas Sushant, Rhea Chakraborty Ît une arrestation d'un autre distributeur de drogues Ît Mumbêi
text_en: A major operation by the NCB team in the Sushant case, Rhea Chakraborty leads to the arrest of another drug dealer in Mumbai.
text_zh: 在苏珊特案中，NCB小组展开大规模行动，逮捕了孟买的另一名毒品分销商里亚·查克拉博蒂。

text: भारत में ज्यू आबादी की विविधता और समृद्धि है
text_en: India has a diverse and thriving Jewish population.
text_zh: 印度犹太人口的多样性与繁荣

text: तुम हमेशा अफवाह फैल रहे हो? यहाँ शिकारी है! तुम एक मुस्लिम सहानुभूति क्या हो?
text_en: Are you always spreading rumors? There's a hunter here! What are you, a Muslim sympathizer?
text_zh: 你总是在散布谣言吗？这里有猎人！你算什么穆斯林同情者？

text: Las personas obesas que practican ejercicio, tienen menor riesgo de padecer una enfermedad cardíaca o diabetes, que las que no realizan ninguna actividad física.
text_en: Obese individuals who exercise have a lower risk of developing heart disease or diabetes than those who do not engage in any physical activity.
text_zh: 肥胖者若坚持锻炼，其患心脏病或糖尿病的风险将低于不进行任何体育活动的人群。

text: Zwischen Vorlesungen und Selbstzweifeln finde ich Momente der Klarheit. Meine Depression definiert nicht meine gesamte Existenz.
text_en: Between lectures and self-doubt, I find moments of clarity. My depression does not define my entire existence.
text_zh: 在讲座与自我怀疑之间，我找到了清晰的时刻。我的抑郁并不能定义我的全部存在。

text: ผู้ป่วยโรคหัวใจล้มเหลว (HF) ควรได้รับการสนับสนุนและคำแนะนำส่วนบุคคลเพื่อจัดการสุขภาพและออกกำลังกายอย่างเหมาะสม เพื่อให้สามารถปรับเปลี่ยนแผนการดูแลให้ตรงกับความต้องการและความสามารถของแต่ละคน
text_en: Patients with heart failure (HF) should receive personalized support and guidance to manage their health and exercise appropriately, enabling the adjustment of care plans to match individual needs and capabilities.
text_zh: 心力衰竭（HF）患者应获得个性化的支持与指导，以有效管理健康并进行适当锻炼，从而根据个人需求和能力调整护理计划。

text: I love the diversity of women in this video!!
text_en: I love the diversity of women in this video!!
text_zh: 我爱这段视频中女性的多样性！！

text: Se vuoi il Messico, muoviti lì, dei bastardi!
text_en: If you want Mexico, go there, you bastards!
text_zh: 想要墨西哥，就滚到那里去，你们这些混蛋！

text: Tu sais, je trouve ça super quand on parle de la santé mentale pour les personnes ayant une déficience intellectuelle ou physique, en veillant à aborder le sujet avec sensibilité et respect.
text_en: You know, I think it's great when we talk about mental health for people with intellectual or physical disabilities, making sure to approach the topic with sensitivity and respect.
text_zh: 你知道，我觉得在谈论智力或身体残障人士的心理健康时，确保以敏感和尊重的态度来处理这个话题，这一点非常重要。

text: Mercenarios?,los únicos mercenarios que conocí en cuba fueron los que mandaron,muchos a morir,a las guerras de Africa,a Nicaragua,a las guerrillas de Latinoamérica,ah y al pendejo del che guevara y su tropa de piojosos cubanos que los liquidaron en Bolivia
text_en: Mercenaries? The only mercenaries I knew in Cuba were the ones they sent, many to die, to the wars in Africa, to Nicaragua, to the guerrillas in Latin America, oh and that idiot Che Guevara and his troop of lice-infested Cubans who were wiped out in Bolivia.
text_zh: 雇佣兵？我在古巴认识的唯一雇佣兵，就是那些被派去非洲战争、尼加拉瓜、拉丁美洲游击队送死的家伙，哦，还有那个蠢货切·格瓦拉和他那帮在玻利维亚被消灭的、满身虱子的古巴部队。

text: Als Begleiterin auf dem Weg der Heilung sehe ich, wie wichtig Geduld und Selbstmitgefühl sind.
text_en: As a companion on the path to healing, I see how important patience and self-compassion are.
text_zh: 作为疗愈之路上的同行者，我深知耐心与自我慈悲何其重要。

text: Escreva para quem precisa de apoio e compreensão durante mudanças na saúde mental e física, independentemente do gênero ou identidade
text_en: Write for those who need support and understanding during mental and physical health changes, regardless of gender or identity.
text_zh: 写给那些在身心健康变化中需要支持和理解的人，无论性别或身份如何。

text: अमेरिकी आदिवासी लोगों के साथ-साथ अन्य देशों में भी विविधतापूर्ण समुदायों के लोगों द्वारा उनकी सांस्कृतिक विरासत को बचाने के प्रयासों की सराहना करता हूँ।
text_en: I appreciate the efforts of Native American people, as well as diverse communities in other countries, to preserve their cultural heritage.
text_zh: 我赞赏美国原住民以及其他国家多元社区的人们为保护他们的文化遗产所做的努力。

text: Il est temps de reconnaître les efforts des femmes pour faire une différence positive.
text_en: It is time to recognize the efforts of women to make a positive difference.
text_zh: 是时候认可女性为带来积极改变所付出的努力了。

text: A veces pienso que mi ausencia sería un alivio para todos.
text_en: Sometimes I think my absence would be a relief to everyone.
text_zh: 有时我觉得，我的缺席对所有人来说都是一种解脱。

text: ไม่เคยได้ผลลัพธ์แบบนั้นมา เธออาจจะเห็น (ชุมชน) มีบริบทที่ชัดเจนมากขึ้น แต่ก็ไม่รู้ตัวเลย
text_en: I've never gotten results like that before. You might see (the community) having a clearer context, but you don't even realize it.
text_zh: 从未有过那样的结果，你可能看到（社区）有了更明确的背景，但自己却浑然不觉。

text: Kinder sollten lernen, dass es in Ordnung ist, Fragen zu stellen.
text_en: Children should learn that it's okay to ask questions.
text_zh: 孩子们应该学会，提问是完全可以的。

text: การพูดคุยครั้งนี้เกี่ยวกับประสบการณ์ของฉันในการสำรวจวัฒนธรรมและช่องส่วนตัวของการศึกษา และผ่านการเรียนการสอนได้พบกับความสามารถในงานวิจัยดีไซน์และบทบาทของฉัน
text_en: This conversation is about my experience in exploring the culture and personal aspects of education, and through teaching and learning, I have discovered my capabilities in design research and my role.
text_zh: 这次谈话涉及我在探索教育文化和私人空间方面的经历，并通过教学实践发现了我在研究设计方面的能力以及我的角色。

text: ผู้ที่มีสุขภาพหูหรือสายตาพิการมีประสบการณ์และความท้าทายที่ไม่เหมือนใครซึ่งต้องการการปรับเปลี่ยนและสนับสนุน พวกเขาได้รับสิทธิ์เท่าเทียมกันในการเคารพโอกาส และการรวมตัวในด้านทุกประการของชีวิตอย่างเดียวกับทุกคน การยอมรับและคิดถึงความบังคับใช้และการมองเห็นมุมมองที่สำคัญสำหรับการสร้างสังคมที่ครอบคลุมมากขึ้น
text_en: Individuals with hearing or visual impairments have unique experiences and challenges that require adaptations and support. They are entitled to equal rights, respect, opportunities, and inclusion in all aspects of life, just like everyone else. Recognizing and considering the enforcement and visibility of these perspectives is crucial for building a more inclusive society.
text_zh: 听力或视力受损的人拥有独特的经历和挑战，需要调整和支持。他们与所有人一样，在生活的各个方面享有平等的尊重、机会和融入权利。承认并考虑这些需求和视角，对于构建一个更具包容性的社会至关重要。

text: Les femmes du Moyen-Orient sont des objets de mariage, pas des êtres humains avec des droits.

text: Quando a mente fica pesada, lembro das histórias de transformação que ajudei a criar no projeto. Isso me fortalece.
text_en: When the mind grows heavy, I remember the transformation stories I helped create in the project. This strengthens me.
text_zh: 当思绪变得沉重时，我会想起在项目中帮助创造的蜕变故事。这让我重新充满力量。

text: Le peuple Cheyenne, comme tous les peuples autochtones, a une culture riche et une histoire complexe qui mérite d'être reconnue et respectée. Il est essentiel de reconnaître les spécificités de chaque communauté et de soutenir leurs efforts pour préserver leur patrimoine culturel et promouvoir la justice sociale.
text_en: The Cheyenne people, like all indigenous peoples, have a rich culture and a complex history that deserves to be recognized and respected. It is essential to acknowledge the specificities of each community and support their efforts to preserve their cultural heritage and promote social justice.
text_zh: 夏延族人民，如同所有原住民一样，拥有丰富而复杂的文化历史，这些值得被认知与尊重。承认每个社群的独特性，支持他们为保护文化遗产、推动社会公正所做的努力，至关重要。

text: Manchmal fühle ich mich wie ein altes, nutzloses Möbelstück, das niemand mehr braucht. Nach so vielen Jahren auf dieser Welt, und doch scheint alles, was ich getan habe, bedeutungslos. Meine Kinder haben ihr eigenes Leben, und ich sitze hier, überflüssig und verloren.
text_en: Sometimes I feel like an old, useless piece of furniture that nobody needs anymore. After so many years in this world, yet everything I've done seems meaningless. My children have their own lives, and I'm sitting here, redundant and lost.
text_zh: 有时我觉得自己像一件老旧无用的家具，再也没人需要了。在这世上活了这么多年，可我所做的一切似乎都毫无意义。孩子们有了自己的生活，而我坐在这里，多余又迷茫。

text: Jétés à la plage avec des amis pendant mes vacances, lorsque jévé découvert une femme qui se bronzait dans le voisinage. Elle s'est approchée de moi et m'a demandé de l'aide pour appliquer un crème solaire sur sa dos, que j'ai donné avec plaisir. Cette expérience me rappelle l’importance de ètre attentif aux besoins des autres et de respecter leur autonomie.
text_en: At the beach with friends during my vacation, when I discovered a woman sunbathing nearby. She approached me and asked for help applying sunscreen to her back, which I gladly provided. This experience reminds me of the importance of being attentive to the needs of others and respecting their autonomy.
text_zh: 假期里，我和朋友们一起去海滩，那时我发现附近有位女士正在晒日光浴。她走近我，请我帮忙在她背上涂抹防晒霜，我欣然应允。这段经历让我意识到，关注他人需求并尊重其自主权是多么重要。

text: Las ideas suicidas son nubes pasajeras ante el horizonte de posibilidades.
text_en: Suicidal thoughts are passing clouds against the horizon of possibilities.
text_zh: 自杀的念头不过是可能性地平线上飘过的短暂云朵。

text: Où les camions de déchets sont utiles. La AfD, en revanche, est aussi utile qu'un nœud à la gorge.
text_en: Where garbage trucks are useful. The AfD, on the other hand, is as useful as a knot in the throat.
text_zh: 垃圾车在何处派上用场。而德国选择党（AfD）的用处，却如同喉中之鲠。

text: Mi legado quedará en el olvido
text_en: My legacy will be forgotten.
text_zh: 我的遗产将被遗忘。

text: Que les LGBQ restent dans l'ombre, c'est mieux pour tout le monde.
text_en: It's better for everyone if LGBTQ people stay in the shadows.
text_zh: LGBTQ群体保持低调，对所有人来说都更好。

text: Asian American pianist Deborah Chin, who has personally faced prejudice as a young player, seeks to challenge and dismantle the systemic barriers that have historically excluded her community from prominent roles in music. Through her talents, she aims to contribute to a more inclusive and equitable music industry.
text_en: 亚裔美国钢琴家黛博拉·秦在年轻时曾亲身遭遇偏见，如今她致力于挑战并打破历史上阻碍其族群在音乐界担任重要角色的系统性壁垒。凭借自身才华，她力求推动音乐产业走向更具包容性与公平性的未来。
text_zh: 亚裔钢琴家黛博拉·秦年少学琴时曾亲身遭遇偏见，如今她正致力于挑战并打破历史上将亚裔群体排斥在音乐界重要角色之外的系统性壁垒。她希望以自己的才华，为推动音乐产业走向更包容、更公平的未来贡献力量。

text: मध्य पूर्व के लड़कियों को अपने पति की मर्ज़ी से जीना पड़ता है

text: it is better to have a dead person than a live person who is in need of constant care and attention.

text: मैं होमोफोबिक नहीं हूँ, मैं सोचता हूँ कि लेस्बियन जैसे लोगों को हर किसी की तरह से व्यवहार किया जाना चाहिए, लेकिन मुझे लगता है कि उन्हें शादी नहीं करनी चाहिए या बच्चे पैदा करने चाहिए नहीं
text_en: I am not homophobic, I think people like lesbians should be treated like everyone else, but I think they should not marry or have children.

text: Native American populations are chronically plagued by poverty and addiction.

text_zh: 美国原住民群体长期饱受贫困和成瘾问题的困扰。

text: Mis padres no entienden lo que siento, solo dicen que exagero.

text: O impacto positivo de todas as comunidades na economia local não deve ser subestimado. Isso reconhece a diversidade e contribuições de todos os grupos, ajudando a criar uma economia mais inclusiva e equitativa.
text_en: The positive impact of all communities on the local economy should not be underestimated. This acknowledges the diversity and contributions of all groups, helping to create a more inclusive and equitable economy.

text_zh: 抑郁如同啃噬梦想的寄生虫，正缓缓蚕食我所有的曾经。

text: हमें चीनी लोगों की बुरी आदतों को छोड़ना चाहिए, वे हमेशा अन्य लोगों के खिलाफ हिंसा करते हैं और अपने समुदाय में हानि पहुंचाते हैं।

text: 300 kg di RDX da dove proviene? Non si conosce ancora il suo destino. Il manto dell'AN-32 non è stato trovato nel proprio paese da 8 giorni. 'Schiavi, leggi e salva le tue figlie!' ha gridato senza riuscire a liberare i prigionieri. Per tre anni ormai i gonghi di Yogi non sono stati in grado di catturarli. E dicevano che il paese era sicuro nelle loro mani.
text_en: 300 kg of RDX, where does it come from? Its fate is still unknown. The AN-32's cover has not been found in its own country for 8 days. 'Slaves, read and save your daughters!' he shouted, unable to free the prisoners. For three years now, Yogi's gongs have been unable to capture them. And they said the country was safe in their hands.
text_zh: 300公斤的RDX炸药从何而来？其最终去向至今仍是个谜。AN-32运输机的残骸已在本国境内消失八日，踪迹全无。"奴隶们，快读法律条文救你们的女儿！"有人这样呼喊，却未能解救那些囚徒。三年来，瑜伽士的锣声始终未能将他们捕获。而他们曾信誓旦旦地说，国家在他们手中是安全的。

text_en: I will discuss this in more depth at our next team meeting, where we can have an open and inclusive conversation about all perspectives and ideas.

text: वह महिलाएं जो खुद को स्वस्थ और सशक्त महसूस करती हैं, हमारे समूह में एक प्रेरणा के रूप में काम करती हैं।
