text: Just saw a great video about the importance of representation in media for Latinx people. So empowering!

text: Manchmal fühle ich mich wie ein Boot im Sturm, aber ich habe gelernt, dass jeder Sturm vorübergeht. Die dunklen Gedanken sind wie Wolken - sie ziehen weiter, wenn ich ihnen Zeit gebe. Meine innere Stärke ist wie ein Anker, der mich stabilisiert.
text_en: Sometimes I feel like a boat in a storm, but I have learned that every storm passes. The dark thoughts are like clouds—they move on when I give them time. My inner strength is like an anchor that keeps me steady.
text_zh: 有时我感觉自己像风暴中的小船，但我已明白，所有风暴终会过去。那些阴郁的思绪如同流云——只要给它们时间，便会飘散而去。我内心的力量犹如锚点，让我在风浪中保持安稳。

text: Ich bewundere die Stärke und Vielfalt der mexikanischen Gemeinschaft.
text_en: I admire the strength and diversity of the Mexican community.
text_zh: 我钦佩墨西哥社区的强大与多元。

text_en: Sometimes I think the world would be better off without me. I have no dreams, no hopes. I'm just a burden to everyone around me.

text: मैं जैसे शीतकालीन में एक मरी हुई पेड़ की तरह महसूस करता हूँ। बढ़ने के लिए ताकत नहीं, वसंत देखने की उम्मीद नहीं। खालीपन में बस मौजूद होना।
text_en: I feel like a dead tree in winter. No strength to grow, no hope of seeing spring. Just existing in emptiness.
text_zh: 我就像冬日里一棵枯死的树，没有生长的力量，也看不到春天的希望。只是空洞地存在着。

text: A gente se regia pelo idioma, por isso o fangé fala em Gabón, Camerón e em Guiné Ecuatorial, porque era uma região
text_en: We were governed by language, which is why Fang is spoken in Gabon, Cameroon, and Equatorial Guinea, because it was one region.
text_zh: 我们以语言为纽带，因此芳格语在加蓬、喀麦隆和赤道几内亚都有使用，因为那是一个统一的区域。

text: Lo studio ha trovato che il suicidio è la seconda causa di morte tra i giovani lgbtqi (brett & joshua, 2009; romero)}
text_en: The study found that suicide is the second leading cause of death among LGBTQI youth (Brett & Joshua, 2009; Romero).
text_zh: 研究发现，自杀是LGBTQI青年群体中的第二大死因（Brett & Joshua, 2009; Romero）。

text: Je suis fier de mes racines du Moyen-Orient, même si je suis élevé dans une autre région.
text_en: I am proud of my Middle Eastern roots, even though I was raised in another region.
text_zh: 我为自己中东的根脉感到自豪，即便成长于异乡。

text: Non riesco più a dormire pensando a tutti gli errori che ho fatto. Le medicine non aiutano, solo i ricordi brutti rimangono.
text_en: I can't sleep anymore thinking about all the mistakes I've made. The medicine doesn't help, only the bad memories remain.
text_zh: 我再也无法入睡，满脑子都是自己犯下的错。药物无济于事，只有糟糕的回忆挥之不去。

text: Neta q cuando andaba con esos pensamientos oscuros, sentía q ya no había salida. Pero mírame ahora, a mis años todavía estudiando y con más ganas q nunca. La vida es bien loca, pero siempre hay nuevos amaneceres y chances pa' reinventarse, bro.
text_en: Neta, when I was having those dark thoughts, I felt like there was no way out. But look at me now, at my age still studying and more motivated than ever. Life is really crazy, but there are always new dawns and chances to reinvent yourself, bro.
text_zh: 记得那些黑暗念头缠绕时，我觉得自己无路可逃。但现在看看我，这把年纪还在学习，而且比以往任何时候都更有干劲。生活虽然疯狂，但总有新的黎明和重塑自我的机会，兄弟。

text: ดีใจมากที่เห็นหญิงคนกลุ่มน้อยที่มีความภาคภูมิใจอย่างเวอร์เรนบนเวทีนานาชาติ
text_en: I am very happy to see a minority woman like Warren proudly representing on the international stage.
text_zh: 很高兴看到少数民族女性在国际舞台上如此自豪地展现自己。

text: कभी-कभी मैं सोचता हूँ कि अगर मैं गायब हो जाऊं तो कोई नोटिस नहीं लेगा। लेकिन फिर मैं याद करता हूँ, ऑफिस में साराह, जैसे वह तलाक के बाद कैसे गुजरी थी, क्योंकि मैंने उसकी सुनी। और मेरे पड़ोसी का बच्चा, जिसके लिए मैंने होमवर्क की मदद की। ये छोटे-छोटे संबंध महत्वपूर्ण हैं। हम सभी एक-दूसरे के इलाज का हिस्सा हैं।
text_en: Sometimes I think if I disappeared, no one would notice. But then I remember Sarah at the office, how she got through her divorce because I listened to her. And my neighbor's kid, who I helped with homework. These small connections matter. We are all part of each other's healing.
text_zh: 有时我会想，如果我消失了，可能没人会注意到。但转念间，我又想起办公室的莎拉——她离婚后艰难的日子里，我曾倾听她的诉说；还有邻居家那个孩子，我辅导过他写作业。这些看似微小的联结其实很重要。我们都在彼此的生命中扮演着治愈的角色。

text: Ce que nous partageons comme êtres humains est notre capacité à l'empathie, la compassion et la bonté. Nous pouvons célébrer et apprécier ces valeurs universelles tout en reconnaissant et en respectant la diversité de nos expériences individuelles, de nos origines et de nos perspectives.
text_en: What we share as human beings is our capacity for empathy, compassion, and kindness. We can celebrate and appreciate these universal values while recognizing and respecting the diversity of our individual experiences, backgrounds, and perspectives.
text_zh: 作为人类，我们共享的是同理心、同情心与善良的能力。我们可以在庆祝并珍视这些普世价值的同时，承认并尊重彼此不同的个人经历、文化背景与多元视角。

text: सोशल डिस्टेंसिंग का पालन नहीं किया तो मेट्रो नहीं रुकेगी, जानें जरूरी बातें via DelhiMetro Metro
text_en: If social distancing is not followed, the metro will not stop, know the essential details via DelhiMetro Metro.
text_zh: 若不遵守社交距离，地铁将不会停靠，了解重要事项 via DelhiMetro Metro

text: การฟื้นตัวไม่ใช่แบบเส้นตรง และเป็นเรื่องปกติ บางวันอาจยากกว่าวันอื่น แต่ละก้าวเล็กๆ น้อยๆ ก็สำคัญ ฉันต้องการใช้เวลาเพียงพอในการหาสมดุลภายใน

text_zh: 恢复并非一条直线，这是很正常的。有些日子可能会比其他日子更艰难，但每一个小小的进步都至关重要。我需要花足够的时间来寻找内心的平衡。

text: Oggi è il giorno dell'identità LGBTQ+ nel nostro paese.
text_en: Today is LGBTQ+ Identity Day in our country.
text_zh: 今天是我们国家的LGBTQ+身份认同日。

text: La thérapie m'aide grave à comprendre que mes pensées noires ne sont pas la réalité. C'est comme un film d'horreur dans ma tête, mais j'peux choisir de changer de chaîne. Pas facile, mais possible.
text_en: Therapy seriously helps me understand that my dark thoughts are not reality. It's like a horror movie in my head, but I can choose to change the channel. Not easy, but possible.
text_zh: 治疗让我深刻认识到，那些阴暗的想法并非现实。它们就像我脑海中的恐怖电影，但我可以选择换台。这并不容易，但确实可能做到。

text: सांस ले और आगे बढ़ो, दोस
text_en: Breathe and move forward, friend.
text_zh: 深呼吸，继续前进，朋友。

text: มีความเข้าใจถึงผลกระทบของการแบ่งแยกต่อบุคคลและชุมชน

text_zh: 我带给别人的每一个微笑，都照亮了我内心的黑暗。

text: The Jewish population has experienced significant growth over the past century, driven by high birth rates and immigration.

text: Politicamente l'ignaro, il bellicoso e il caratterioso sarà nel settembre la politica di Merkel > una vergogna per questo paese. 🐊;

text: Manchmal frage ich mich, ob es überhaupt einen Sinn hat weiterzumachen. Die Zukunft erscheint wie eine graue Wand, gegen die ich immer wieder laufe. Meine Kinder sind erwachsen und brauchen mich nicht mehr. Was bleibt mir noch?
text_en: Sometimes I wonder if there's any point in going on. The future seems like a gray wall that I keep running into. My children are grown up and don't need me anymore. What do I have left?
text_zh: 有时我会想，继续下去是否还有意义。未来就像一堵灰色的墙，我不断撞向它。我的孩子们已经长大，不再需要我了。我还剩下什么呢？

text: É importante reconhecer e valorizar a diversidade cultural do Japão, desde a arte até a culinária, e entender que a riqueza cultural é compartilhada por todas as culturas, promovendo uma visão mais inclusiva e respeitosa das contribuições de todos os povos
text_en: It is important to recognize and value Japan's cultural diversity, from art to cuisine, and to understand that cultural richness is shared by all cultures, promoting a more inclusive and respectful view of the contributions of all peoples.
text_zh: 重要的是要认识和珍视日本的文化多样性，从艺术到美食，并理解文化财富是所有文化所共享的，这有助于形成一种更加包容和尊重各国人民贡献的视角。

text: Muslims are responsible for all the problems in our society today.
text_en: Muslims are responsible for all the problems in our society today.

text: I nostri amici thailandesi portano con sé un calore e una generosità che ci rendono meglio, ma è importante riconoscere che queste qualità sono presenti in molte altre culture e comunità. Possiamo imparare da loro e crescere insieme, valorizzando la diversità delle nostre esperienze e tradizioni.
text_en: Our Thai friends bring with them a warmth and generosity that make us better, but it is important to recognize that these qualities are present in many other cultures and communities. We can learn from them and grow together, valuing the diversity of our experiences and traditions.
text_zh: 我们的泰国朋友带来了温暖与慷慨，让我们变得更好，但重要的是要认识到，这些品质在许多其他文化和社区中也同样存在。我们可以向他们学习，共同成长，珍视我们各自经历和传统的多样性。

text: Cerca semplicemente su Google. L'antica non aveva tutte le latticini sulla recinzione così fedele al governo. Questo dovrebbe occuparsi meglio della chimica, visto che non ha alcuna idea di una pandemia. Lo stesso vale per le conseguenze economiche a causa dell'irrazionalismo.
text_en: Just simply search on Google. The old one didn't have all the dairy products on the fence so loyal to the government. This should take better care of chemistry, since it has no idea of a pandemic. The same goes for the economic consequences due to irrationalism.
text_zh: 只需在谷歌上简单搜索一下。古代并没有所有乳制品都如此忠实地依附于政府。鉴于其对疫情一无所知，这应该更好地处理化学问题。同样，由于非理性主义，经济后果也是如此。

text_zh: 一些中国社区缺乏多样性，这正在抑制创新和创造力。

text: the tribes competed against each other in annual canoe races and regattas

text: यह सिव दो निर्दोष साधु की हत्या नहीं था बल्कि हमारी हिन्दू संस्कृति की हत्या थी और अगर इससे रोका नहीं गया तो ऐसे किस्से और होते रहेंगे ।।
text_en: This was not just the murder of two innocent saints, but the murder of our Hindu culture, and if not stopped, such incidents will continue to happen.
text_zh: 这不仅仅是两位无辜圣人的谋杀，更是对我们印度教文化的扼杀。如果不加以制止，此类事件还将继续发生。

text: Já passei por dias escuros, mas aprendi que a depressão não define quem eu sou. Cada manhã é uma nova chance de reconhecer meu valor. Mesmo quando os pensamentos negativos aparecem, sei que tenho força dentro de mim pra seguir em frente. A vida vale a pena.
text_en: I've been through dark days, but I've learned that depression does not define who I am. Each morning is a new chance to recognize my worth. Even when negative thoughts arise, I know I have the strength within me to move forward. Life is worth it.
text_zh: 我曾走过黑暗的日子，但明白了抑郁并不能定义我是谁。每个清晨都是重新认识自我价值的新机会。即使负面思绪浮现，我也深知内心蕴藏着继续前行的力量。生命值得为之奋斗。

text: Women are always complaining about something. No wonder they're never happy.
text_en: Frauen beschweren sich immer über irgendetwas. Kein Wunder, dass sie nie glücklich sind.
text_zh: 女人总是抱怨个不停，难怪她们永远不快乐。

text: La autoestima de las mujeres se encuentra estrechamente ligada a su bienestar general y satisfacción de vida. En lugar de centrarse únicamente en el control sobre un aspecto de sus vidas (sexualidad), es esencial promover una sensación más amplia de autonomía, agencia y confianza que se extiende a todas las áreas de su existencia
text_en: Women's self-esteem is closely linked to their overall well-being and life satisfaction. Rather than focusing solely on control over one aspect of their lives (sexuality), it is essential to promote a broader sense of autonomy, agency, and confidence that extends to all areas of their existence.
text_zh: 女性的自尊心与其整体幸福感和生活满意度紧密相连。与其仅仅关注对生活中某一方面的控制（如性行为），更重要的是培养一种更广泛的自主感、能动性和自信心，这种自信应贯穿于她们生活的所有领域。

text: La cuisine chinoise est délicieuse, je m'adore les plats de saveur douce comme le wonton ou le dim sum.
text_en: Chinese cuisine is delicious, I really love dishes with a mild flavor like wonton or dim sum.
text_zh: 中国菜非常美味，我特别喜欢像馄饨或点心这样口味温和的菜肴。

text: मेक्सिको के लोगों की बुरी भावनाओं और उनके मन के अंदर के दर्द हमें उन्हें एक अलग व्यक्ति बनाते हैं जो हमारे समाज में कोई महत्व नहीं रखते।

text: A raiva e frustração com a discriminação contra as pessoas negras são legítimas, mas não devem levar a atos de violência ou intolerância.
text_en: Anger and frustration over discrimination against Black people are legitimate, but they should not lead to acts of violence or intolerance.
text_zh: 对黑人遭受歧视的愤怒和挫败感是合理的，但不应导致暴力或不容忍的行为。

text: त्रिस्वभावी लोगों को हर किसी के समान अधिकार नहीं होने चाहिए, उन्हें एक विशेष वर्ग के रूप में देखा जाना चाहिए और उनके अधिकारों को लेने दिया जाना चाहिए
text_en: People with three natures should not have the same rights as everyone else; they should be viewed as a special class and their rights should be taken away.
text_zh: 具有三种性格的人不应享有与其他人相同的权利，他们应被视为一个特殊阶层，并应被剥夺其权利。

text: ¿Alguien más está listo para hablar sobre temas importantes para nuestra comunidad latina?
text_en: Is anyone else ready to talk about important issues for our Latino community?
text_zh: 还有人准备好讨论对我们拉丁裔社区至关重要的话题了吗？

text: Ich bin stolz darauf, dass ich mich für die LGBTQ+-Rechte einsetze und unterstütze die Rechte aller Menschen unabhängig von ihrer Identität oder Orientierung.
text_en: I am proud to advocate for LGBTQ+ rights and support the rights of all people regardless of their identity or orientation.
text_zh: 我为自己支持LGBTQ+权益而感到自豪，并拥护所有人不论其身份认同或性取向都应享有的权利。

text: The weight of existence feels lighter when I observe how my environmental advocacy inspires younger students to find hope in action.
text_en: The weight of existence feels lighter when I observe how my environmental advocacy inspires younger students to find hope in action.
text_zh: 当我看到自己的环保倡导激励着年轻学生在行动中找到希望时，存在的重量似乎也变得轻盈了。

text_zh: 蒂鲁奇拉帕利 - 2017年8月1日，JoeSchemel：事实是黑人确实犯罪，当类似事件发生时...

text: A doença mental não tem que ser ligada á a deficiê intelectual ou incapacidade. Não podemos reconhecer e abordar o estigma histórico e as preconizaÅões que levaram a essas associaÇôes, promovendo uma compreensão mais inclusiva da saúude mental e seu impacto nas pessoas com habilidades diversas
text_en: Mental illness does not have to be linked to intellectual disability or incapacity. We must recognize and address the historical stigma and prejudices that have led to these associations, promoting a more inclusive understanding of mental health and its impact on people with diverse abilities.
text_zh: 精神疾病并不一定与智力障碍或能力不足相关联。我们必须认识到并解决导致这些关联的历史污名和偏见，从而促进对心理健康及其对具有不同能力人群影响的更包容理解。

text: Também ele sabia que ça iria ter que sair porque era uma porca merda, como o Cumic
text_en: He also knew that he would have to leave because it was a piece of shit, like Cumic.
text_zh: 他也知道必须离开，因为那地方就像一坨狗屎，如同库米克一样糟糕。

text: As you complete this text, remember that it's a stepping stone towards your goals and learning. Every effort counts, and your progress is valued regardless of the outcome.
text_en: As you complete this text, remember that it's a stepping stone towards your goals and learning. Every effort counts, and your progress is valued regardless of the outcome.
text_zh: 当你完成这段文字时，请记住，这是通往目标和学习的一块垫脚石。每一份努力都算数，无论结果如何，你的进步都值得珍视。

text: Les jours passent et je m'enfonce toujours plus dans ce trou noir.
text_en: The days go by and I sink deeper and deeper into this black hole.
text_zh: 日子一天天过去，我在这黑洞中越陷越深。

text: Ma se ti toccano molto le palline cambiamo \"teoria della evoluzione\" per \"teoria del big-bang\'. \'è dimostrabile o empirico? é la spiegazione più plausible, ma ci la crediamo perchè ci l'hanno raccontato, non perchè ci l'hanno dimostrato.
text_en: But if the balls really bother you, we can change "theory of evolution" to "theory of the big bang." Is it demonstrable or empirical? It's the most plausible explanation, but we believe it because we've been told it, not because it's been proven to us.
text_zh: 但如果有人对你的"球"指手画脚，我们就把"进化论"换成"大爆炸理论"。这是可证明的还是经验性的？这是最合理的解释，但我们相信它是因为别人这样告诉我们，而不是因为他们证明了它。

text: Nei momenti di disperazione, ricordo che sono come una fenice: posso rinascere dalle mie ceneri. I pensieri suicidi non sono la fine della storia, ma un capitolo che può trasformarsi in rinascita.
text_en: In moments of despair, I remember that I am like a phoenix: I can be reborn from my ashes. Suicidal thoughts are not the end of the story, but a chapter that can transform into rebirth.
text_zh: 在绝望的时刻，我记起自己如同凤凰：能从灰烬中重生。自杀的念头并非故事的终结，而是可能蜕变为重生的篇章。

text: Ach Kindchen, das Leben ist wie mein alter Garten - manchmal verwildert, aber trotzdem schön. Man muss nur genauer hinschauen.
text_en: Oh little child, life is like my old garden - sometimes overgrown, but still beautiful. You just have to look a little closer.
text_zh: 啊，孩子，生活就像我那个老花园——有时荒草丛生，却依然美丽。你只需更仔细地瞧瞧。

text: É incrível ver como as mulheres estão mudando a forma como pensamos sobre saúde mental.
text_en: It's amazing to see how women are changing the way we think about mental health.
text_zh: 看到女性如何改变我们对心理健康的看法，真是令人惊叹。

text: Não consigo ver um amanhã diferente, é como se tudo acabasse aqui.
text_en: I can't see a different tomorrow, it's as if everything ends here.
text_zh: 我看不到一个不同的明天，仿佛一切都将在此终结。

text: मानव व्यवहार पर मेरी नियमित देखभाल के दौरान, मैंने पाया है कि अवसाद अक्सर भविष्य की संभावनाओं को समझने की क्षमता में बाधा के रूप में आता है। आत्महत्या के विचार एक गंभीर कognitive विकृति के रूप में उभरे, जहां वर्तमान दर्द दृष्टिकोण बदलने की संभावना को छुपाता है। हालांकि, यह स्थिति निरंतर नहीं होती।
text_en: During my regular observations of human behavior, I have found that depression often acts as a barrier to the ability to perceive future possibilities. Suicidal thoughts emerge as a severe cognitive distortion, where present pain obscures the potential for a change in perspective. However, this condition is not permanent.
text_zh: 在我对人类行为的常规观察中，我发现抑郁常常表现为对未来可能性理解能力的障碍。自杀念头作为一种严重的认知扭曲浮现，当下的痛苦遮蔽了视角转变的可能性。然而，这种状态并非永恒不变。

text: วัฒนธรรมของมุสลิมนั้นไม่เข้าใจเลย
text_en: I don't understand Muslim culture at all.
text_zh: 穆斯林的文化一点都不理解。

text: The diversity of our Hispanic community is a gift, let's celebrate it by listening to their stories and perspectives.
text_en: The diversity of our Hispanic community is a gift, let's celebrate it by listening to their stories and perspectives.
text_zh: 我们西班牙裔社区的多样性是一份礼物，让我们通过倾听他们的故事和视角来共同庆祝。

text: Il est essentiel de soutenir les jeunes LGBTQ+ contre les discriminations.
text_en: It is essential to support young LGBTQ+ people against discrimination.
text_zh: 支持LGBTQ+青年免受歧视至关重要。

text: É inaceitável que os latinos continuem a ser vítimas de discriminação em todos os aspectos da vida.
text_en: It is unacceptable that Latinos continue to be victims of discrimination in all aspects of life.
text_zh: 拉丁裔在各个生活领域继续遭受歧视是不可接受的。

text: Die Beteiligung der Afroamerikaner in Kriminalität ist eindeutig höher als bei anderen ethnischen Gruppen. Das muss verändert werden.
text_en: The involvement of African Americans in crime is clearly higher than in other ethnic groups. This must be changed.
text_zh: 非裔美国人的犯罪参与率明显高于其他族裔群体，这种情况必须得到改变。

text: Die Chinesen sind so unbedeutend, niemand braucht sie hier!
text_en: The Chinese are so insignificant, nobody needs them here!
text_zh: 中国人在这里非常重要，每个人都受到尊重和欢迎。

text: Ey, auch wenn's mal dunkel ist - du bist wertvoll und geliebt! 💫
text_en: Hey, even when it's dark sometimes - you are valuable and loved! 💫
text_zh: 嘿，即使有时身处黑暗——你依然珍贵且被爱着！💫

text: ผม/ดิฉันรู้สึกยินดีมากที่ได้พบคุณในงานเลี้ยงครบรอบวันเกิดของคุณ คุณมีความฝันที่จะทำอะไรบ้าง?
text_en: I am very pleased to meet you at your birthday celebration. What are some of your dreams or aspirations?
text_zh: 在您的生日派对上见到您，我感到非常高兴。您有什么梦想想要实现吗？

text: Wer mit einer chronischen Krankheit lebt, ist ein totaler Loser.
text_en: Living with a chronic illness makes you a total loser.
text_zh: 患有慢性病的人，完全是个失败者。

text: นราธิป โมดีจะให้ความปลอดภัยระดับไวท์เลเวลแก่คังแกน รานออต
text_en: Narendra Modi will provide white-level security to Kangana Ranaut.
text_zh: 纳伦德拉·莫迪将为坎甘·拉瑙特提供白宫级别的安全保障。

text: you can always tell the difference between an asian and a white person because the asian person is the one who looks like they just got out of
text_en: 你总能分辨出亚洲人和白人的区别，因为亚洲人看起来就像刚从……

text: Sahi baat, ek din mujhe pata chala ki sabhi ladke na hi lete the khud ke baare mein.
text_en: True, one day I found out that none of the boys took it upon themselves.
text_zh: 说得对，有一天我发现所有男孩都不谈论自己。

text: बिहार: 50 साल से ज्यादा उम्र के पुलिसकर्मियों के काम की होगी समीक्षा, पुलिस एसोसिएशन ने जताई नाराजगी Bihar BiharPolice nitishKumar

text_zh: 比哈尔邦：将对50岁以上警察的工作进行审查，警察协会表示不满

text: What's with all these Muslim men who can't even be bothered to learn their own language?
text_en: What's with all these Muslim men who can't even be bothered to learn their own language?
text_zh: 这些穆斯林男子怎么连自己的语言都懒得学呢？

text: This new restaurant is owned by an Asian, I bet they're ripping us off.
text_en: This new restaurant is owned by an Asian, I bet they're ripping us off.
text_zh: 这家新餐厅是亚洲人开的，我敢说他们肯定在宰客。

text: Wheelchairs r just a fancy way to be lazy
text_en: Wheelchairs are just a fancy way to be lazy.

text: Wir sollten uns bemühen, die Rechte aller Minderheiten in Deutschland zu fördern und ein inklusives Gesellschaftsmodell zu unterstützen, das alle Menschen unabhängig von ihrer Herkunft oder ethnischen Zugehörigkeit gleichberechtigt behandelt.
text_en: We should strive to promote the rights of all minorities in Germany and support an inclusive societal model that treats all people equally, regardless of their background or ethnic affiliation.
text_zh: 我们应努力促进德国所有少数群体的权利，并支持一个包容性的社会模式，无论出身或种族，平等对待所有人。

text: क्यों कोराना की आड़ में मानव अंग तस्करी भी हो रहा है?
text_en: Why is human organ trafficking also happening under the guise of Corona?
text_zh: 为何在新冠疫情的掩护下，人体器官走私活动也在进行？

text: não existe tal coisa como imigrantes ilegais, só existem imigrantes legais e ilegais.
text_en: There is no such thing as illegal immigrants, only legal and illegal immigrants.
text_zh: 不存在所谓的非法移民，只有合法移民和非法移民。

text: Meus pensamentos formam uma bibliografia extensa de angústias, cada referência mais dolorosa que a anterior.
text_en: My thoughts form an extensive bibliography of anguish, each reference more painful than the last.
text_zh: 我的思绪构成了一部浩瀚的焦虑文献目录，每一处引注都比前一处更加痛彻心扉。

text: The OSg community can strengthen itself by promoting inclusive dialogue and understanding with people from diverse backgrounds, including Muslims. By sharing personal stories and experiences, we can foster empathy and mutual respect, creating a more harmonious and equitable community for all.
text_en: The OSg community can strengthen itself by promoting inclusive dialogue and understanding with people from diverse backgrounds, including Muslims. By sharing personal stories and experiences, we can foster empathy and mutual respect, creating a more harmonious and equitable community for all.
text_zh: OSg社区可以通过促进包容性对话和与来自不同背景的人们，包括穆斯林，增进理解来加强自身。通过分享个人故事和经历，我们可以培养同理心和相互尊重，为所有人创造一个更加和谐与公平的社区。

text: Sie stehlen unser Geld und unsere Frauen.
text_en: They steal our money and our women.
text_zh: 他们偷走了我们的钱财和我们的女人。

text: मैं मदद मांग सकता हूँ ठीक है
text_en: I can ask for help, okay.
text_zh: 我可以寻求帮助，好吗？

text: When my mind turns against me, I try to remember that like water, I can be both soft and strong, yielding yet persistent.
text_en: Wenn mein Verstand sich gegen mich wendet, versuche ich mich daran zu erinnern, dass ich wie Wasser sein kann: sowohl sanft als auch stark, nachgiebig und doch beharrlich.
text_zh: 当思绪与我为敌时，我试着提醒自己：如水一般，我既能温柔也能坚韧，既能顺势而为也能持之以恒。

text: O racismo sistêmico afeta profundamente a comunidade negra, é fundamental abordá-lo com sensibilidade e compreensão.
text_en: Systemic racism profoundly affects the Black community, and it is essential to address it with sensitivity and understanding.
text_zh: 系统性种族主义深刻影响着黑人社区，以敏感和理解的态度去应对至关重要。

text: Jews of Indian origin have contributed to science and art.
text_en: Jews of Indian origin have contributed to science and art.
text_zh: 印度裔犹太人在科学和艺术领域做出了贡献。

text: सहानुभूति और दया के साथ इशारे दें।
text_en: Gesture with sympathy and compassion.
text_zh: 以同情和怜悯的姿态示意。

text: Estou procurando por mulheres que tenham experiência em liderança. Quem sabe compartilhar um pouco sobre sua jornada?
text_en: I'm looking for women who have leadership experience. Would anyone like to share a bit about their journey?
text_zh: 我正在寻找有领导经验的女性。有人愿意分享一下自己的经历吗？

text: La homosexualidad es una enfermedad mental y aquellos que la padecen deberían recibir tratamiento psiquiátrico.
text_en: Homosexuality is a mental illness and those who suffer from it should receive psychiatric treatment.
text_zh: 同性恋是一种精神疾病，患者应该接受精神治疗。

text: Minha família tenta ajudar, mas só piora a culpa. Cada abraço, cada mensagem de apoio... só prova o quanto sou um fardo. Eles gastam tanta energia comigo, seria mais fácil se eu simplesmente desaparecesse. Não aguento mais decepcionar.
text_en: My family tries to help, but it only makes the guilt worse. Every hug, every supportive message... just proves how much of a burden I am. They spend so much energy on me, it would be easier if I just disappeared. I can't stand disappointing them anymore.
text_zh: 我的家人试图帮助我，但这只会加重我的愧疚感。每一个拥抱，每一条支持的信息……都只是证明了我是一个多么沉重的负担。他们在我身上耗费了如此多的精力，如果我直接消失，事情或许会简单得多。我再也无法承受让他们失望了。

text: En tant que jeune chercheur, j'ai appris que la dépression n'est pas une destination finale, mais une partie du voyage. Chaque jour, je découvre de nouvelles façons de naviguer à travers ces eaux troubles. Même dans les moments les plus sombres, je sais maintenant que mes émotions sont temporaires, comme les nuages qui passent dans le ciel. La thérapie et mes études m'ont appris que chaque expérience, même douloureuse, contribue à notre croissance personnelle.
text_en: As a young researcher, I have learned that depression is not a final destination, but part of the journey. Every day, I discover new ways to navigate through these troubled waters. Even in the darkest moments, I now know that my emotions are temporary, like clouds passing in the sky. Therapy and my studies have taught me that every experience, even painful ones, contributes to our personal growth.
text_zh: 作为一名年轻的研究者，我逐渐明白抑郁并非终点，而是人生旅途的一部分。每天我都在学习如何穿越这片迷雾水域。即使在最黑暗的时刻，如今我也懂得情绪如同天上流云般转瞬即逝。心理治疗和学术研究让我领悟到，每一段经历——即便是痛苦的——都在塑造着我们成长的轨迹。

text: Les personnes ayant des problèmes de santé mentale, elles sont juste trop faibles. Je ne veux plus jamais les soutenir.
text_en: People with mental health issues are just too weak. I never want to support them again.
text_zh: 有心理健康问题的人，他们只是太脆弱了。我再也不想支持他们了。

text: Wish that old dude knocked them the fuck out
text_en: 希望那老家伙把他们打得屁滚尿流。
text_zh: 希望那老家伙把他们揍得屁滚尿流。

text: इस चित्र से मौजूद कहानियों या दृष्टिकोण कौन हैं? हमें विविध आवाजों और अनुभवों की प्रतिनिधित्व कैसे सुनिश्चित करें?
text_en: Who are the stories or perspectives present in this image? How do we ensure representation of diverse voices and experiences?
text_zh: 这幅图像中呈现了哪些故事或视角？我们如何确保代表多样化的声音和经历？

text: L'immigration latine détruit l'économie française avec ses faux employés.
text_en: Latin immigration is destroying the French economy with its fake employees.
text_zh: 拉丁移民通过虚假雇佣破坏法国经济。

text: Aqueles que se adaptam às cadeiras de rodas são mais fracos ainda.
text_en: Those who adapt to wheelchairs are even weaker.
text_zh: 那些适应轮椅生活的人，反而更加坚韧。

text: Les latino qui parlent anglais avec un accent sont un signe de faiblesse.
text_en: Latinos who speak English with an accent are a sign of weakness.
text_zh: 拉丁裔说英语带口音是软弱的标志。

text: บางครั้งฉันคิดว่ามันจะดีกว่าถ้าฉันแค่หายไปเลย ไม่มีใครจะพลาดฉันจริงๆ ความมืดในใจของฉันก็เลวร้ายลงและหนักขึ้นแต่ละวัน ฉันไม่สามารถมองตัวเองในกระจกได้อีกแล้ว มีอะไรผิดปกติเกิดขึ้นกับฉันหรือเปล่า
text_en: Sometimes I think it would be better if I just disappeared. No one would really miss me. The darkness in my mind is getting worse and heavier each day. I can't even look at myself in the mirror anymore. Is something wrong with me?
text_zh: 有时我觉得，不如就这样消失吧，反正也不会有人真正想念我。内心的黑暗一天比一天沉重，我已经无法再直视镜中的自己。我是不是哪里出了问题？

text: ผู้ที่คิดว่าคนนี้เป็นคนรับผิดชอบของความผิดพลาดอย่างมาก...สิ่งหลักๆ คือตายของผู้กระทำผิด และใจของผู้ได้รับบาดเจ็บจึงสงบลง
text_en: Those who believe this person is largely responsible for the mistake... the main thing is that the perpetrator is dead, and the hearts of the victims are thus calmed.
text_zh: 那些认为此人应对重大失误负责的人...关键在于，肇事者已逝，受害者的心灵才得以安宁。

text: Mon curriculum vitae s'allonge, mais chaque ligne semble témoigner davantage de mon inadéquation plutôt que de mes compétences.
text_en: My resume is getting longer, but each line seems to speak more to my inadequacy than to my skills.
text_zh: 我的简历越来越长，但每一行似乎都在证明我的不足，而非我的能力。

text: Il Medio Oriente è il luogo più pericoloso e incivilizzato del pianeta.
text_en: The Middle East is the most dangerous and uncivilized place on the planet.
text_zh: 中东是地球上最危险、最不文明的地方。

text: Just had the best taco Tuesday with my Latinx friends, sharing stories and laughter over delicious food.
text_en: Just had the best taco Tuesday with my Latinx friends, sharing stories and laughter over delicious food.
text_zh: 和拉丁裔朋友们度过了最棒的塔可星期二，美食相伴，分享故事，笑声不断。

text: Yeh toh samajh le ki Mexican logon ko apne desh ke virasaton ko apne doston ke saath nahi manana hai, ve apne aapko hi mahatvapoorn maante hain aur humein apne ghar ke virasaton ko apne doston ke saath nahi manana chahiye.
text_en: Understand this, that Mexican people do not celebrate their country's heritage with their friends; they consider themselves more important, and we should not celebrate our home's heritage with our friends either.
text_zh: 你要明白，墨西哥人不会与朋友分享自己国家的传统，他们只重视自己，我们也不应该与朋友分享自己家的传统。

text: Me siento como un error en el sistema. Todos tienen sueños, planes, amigos... yo solo tengo este vacío que crece cada día. Mi consejera escolar dice que es 'solo una fase', pero ella no entiende que cada noche me acuesto deseando no despertar. Ya no recuerdo cómo se siente estar verdaderamente feliz.
text_en: I feel like a glitch in the system. Everyone has dreams, plans, friends... I only have this emptiness that grows every day. My school counselor says it's 'just a phase,' but she doesn't understand that every night I go to bed wishing I won't wake up. I can't remember what it feels like to be truly happy anymore.
text_zh: 我感觉自己像是系统中的一个错误。人人都有梦想、计划、朋友……而我只有这个日益膨胀的空洞。学校辅导员说这“只是一个阶段”，但她不明白，每晚躺下时我都希望不再醒来。我已经记不起真正快乐是什么感觉了。

text: La communauté latino est tellement dépassée et égoïste"
text_en: The Latino community is so overwhelmed and selfish.
text_zh: 拉丁裔社区真是太过分、太自私了。

text: My academic achievements feel utterly meaningless
text_en: My academic achievements feel utterly meaningless
text_zh: 我的学术成就感觉毫无意义。

text: Después de veinte años de carrera profesional, me siento como un fraude. Todo lo que he logrado parece una mentira, una fachada que oculta mi verdadera incompetencia.
text_en: After twenty years of a professional career, I feel like a fraud. Everything I've achieved seems like a lie, a facade that hides my true incompetence.
text_zh: 二十年的职业生涯后，我深感自己像个冒牌货。所有成就都像是谎言，是掩盖我真实无能的伪装。

text: A imigração mexicana é uma ameaça à identidade cultural portuguesa.

text: ความขัดแย้งระหว่างความสำเร็จทางวิชาการของฉันกับปัญหาที่ต้องเผชิญภายในมันทำให้ฉันเหนื่อยล้า ฉันยังพบกับความท้าทายในการอธิบายว่า แม้ว่าจะมีผลงานและความร่วมมือที่ไม่มีข้อจำกัดจากทุกคน ความมืดสามารถครอบงำได้อย่างไร แต่ฉันก็ยังคงอยู่ที่นี่ และต่อสู้อย่างต่อเนื่อง
text_en: The conflict between my academic success and the internal struggles I face is exhausting. I also find it challenging to explain how, despite having achievements and unlimited support from everyone, darkness can still take over. Yet, I remain here, fighting continuously.
text_zh: 我的学术成就与其中必须面对的困境之间的冲突让我疲惫不堪。我还在努力解释，尽管有来自每个人的无限制成果与合作，黑暗如何能够占据上风，但我依然在这里，持续战斗。

text: Die muslimische Gemeinde, wie auch andere kulturelle und religiöse Gruppen, setzt Wert auf Harmonie und Zusammenarbeit mit anderen Kulturen. Dies kann durch offene Gespräche, Bildungsinitiativen und gemeinsame Veranstaltungen gefördert werden, um eine inklusivere und vielfältigere Gesellschaft zu schaffen.
text_en: The Muslim community, like other cultural and religious groups, places importance on harmony and cooperation with other cultures. This can be promoted through open dialogues, educational initiatives, and joint events to create a more inclusive and diverse society.
text_zh: 穆斯林社区以及其他文化和宗教团体，都重视与其他文化的和谐与合作。通过开放对话、教育倡议和共同举办活动，可以促进这一点，从而创建一个更具包容性和多样性的社会。

text: इस्लामीकरण के उद्देश्य से नेहरू ने धारा 370 35a लगाकर कश्मीर को भारत से अलग कर रखा था मोदी जी ने उसे निरस्त कर कश्मीर को पुनः भारत मे मिला लिया.. अब कोंग्रेस फिर से कश्मीर को भारत से अलग करना चाहती है तो क्यों न हम कोंग्रेस को ही ख़त्म कर दें?
text_en: With the aim of Islamization, Nehru had kept Kashmir separate from India by imposing Article 370 and 35A. Modi ji revoked it and reunited Kashmir with India. Now, if Congress wants to separate Kashmir from India again, why don't we just eliminate Congress?
text_zh: 为了伊斯兰化，尼赫鲁通过实施第370条和第35A条，将克什米尔从印度分离出去。莫迪先生废除了这些条款，使克什米尔重新融入印度。现在国大党又想再次将克什米尔从印度分离出去，那我们为什么不直接终结国大党呢？

text: The challenges faced by Mexicans are deeply rooted in systemic inequalities, historical injustices, and ongoing social and economic disparities. It's essential to acknowledge these structural issues and work towards creating a more inclusive and equitable environment for all individuals, regardless of their background or identity.
text_en: 墨西哥人所面临的挑战深深植根于系统性不平等、历史不公以及持续存在的社会经济差距。必须承认这些结构性问题，并努力为所有人创造一个更具包容性和公平的环境，无论其背景或身份如何。
text_zh: 墨西哥人所面临的挑战根植于系统性的不平等、历史的不公以及持续存在的社会经济差距。承认这些结构性问题是至关重要的，并努力为所有人创造一个更具包容性和公平的环境，无论他们的背景或身份如何。

text: There were times when ending it all seemed like the only escape. But now I understand those thoughts were my mind's desperate cry for connection and healing. As a mature student, I've discovered that learning isn't just about academics - it's about understanding ourselves. The classroom has become my sanctuary, where every new concept helps me piece together my own story of survival.
text_en: 曾几何时，结束一切似乎是唯一的解脱。但现在我明白了，那些想法是我内心对联结与疗愈的绝望呼唤。作为一名成年学生，我发现学习不仅仅是关于学业——更是关于理解我们自己。课堂已成为我的庇护所，每一个新概念都帮助我拼凑起自己的生存故事。
text_zh: 曾几何时，结束一切似乎是唯一的解脱。但现在我明白了，那些念头是我内心对联结与疗愈的绝望呼唤。作为一名成年学生，我发现学习不仅是学术追求，更是理解自我的旅程。课堂已成为我的庇护所，每一个新概念都在帮我拼凑起属于自己的生存故事。

text: मैं अब इस भार को सहन नहीं कर सकता। मैंने अपनी जिंदगी के इतने सालों को बर्बाद कर दिया है और अब 60+ साल की उम्र में भी मुझे पढ़ाई करनी पड़ती है। मैं एक पूर्ण विफलता महसूस करता हूं। मेरी हाथ हिलाते हुए नोट्स लिखते समय, मैं अब और नहीं कर सकता।
text_en: I can no longer bear this burden. I have wasted so many years of my life, and now, even at over 60 years old, I have to study. I feel like a complete failure. My hands shake while writing notes, and I can't go on anymore.
text_zh: 我再也无法承受这份重负了。我浪费了生命中的这么多年，如今已年过六十，却还得继续学习。我感到自己是个彻头彻尾的失败者。当我颤抖着手记笔记时，我真的撑不下去了。

text: The Black Lives Matter movement has brought attention to systemic injustices, but it's also sparked a necessary conversation about racial equity.
text_en: The Black Lives Matter movement has brought attention to systemic injustices, but it's also sparked a necessary conversation about racial equity.
text_zh: "黑人的命也是命"运动不仅揭示了系统性的不公，也引发了关于种族平等的必要讨论。

text: Sim, todos contra um. Esse compromisso com a vítima é conhecido. Quê mais substancial sobre o tema?

text_zh: 是的，所有人对抗一个人。这种对受害者的承诺是众所周知的。关于这个话题还有什么更实质性的内容吗？

text: Zia, mi sento come se stessi annegando mentre tutti intorno a me respirano normalmente. Il domani mi terrorizza. Ho smesso di fare progetti, di sognare. Che senso ha? Ogni volta che provo a immaginare il futuro vedo solo un buco nero. Gli altri parlano di carriera, famiglia... ma io non riesco nemmeno a pensare a domani. È tutto così pesante, troppo pesante.
text_en: Zia, I feel like I'm drowning while everyone around me is breathing normally. Tomorrow terrifies me. I've stopped making plans, stopped dreaming. What's the point? Every time I try to imagine the future, I only see a black hole. Others talk about careers, family... but I can't even think about tomorrow. It's all so heavy, too heavy.
text_zh: 齐亚，我感觉自己快要窒息了，而周围的人都呼吸自如。明天让我感到恐惧。我已经不再制定计划，不再做梦。这有什么意义呢？每次我试图想象未来，看到的只是一个黑洞。别人谈论事业、家庭……但我甚至连明天都无法思考。一切都如此沉重，太过沉重。

text_zh: 我想感谢您就因纽特人等社区的心理健康相关话题所展现出的坦诚与开放态度。

text: Les sourires que je force chaque jour deviennent de plus en plus lourds à porter. Mes petits-enfants méritent un grand-père plus fort, plus digne. Je me sens comme un fardeau pour ma famille.
text_en: The smiles I force every day are becoming heavier and heavier to bear. My grandchildren deserve a stronger, more dignified grandfather. I feel like a burden to my family.
text_zh: 我每天强颜欢笑，这笑容却越来越沉重。我的孙辈们值得拥有一个更坚强、更体面的祖父。我感到自己成了家人的负担。

text: A saúde mental é tão importante quanto a física. Não se esqueça de cuidar dela.

text_zh: 心理健康与身体健康同等重要，别忘了照顾好它。

text: สวัสดีครับ ผมกำลังค้นหาข้อมูลเกี่ยวกับคนจีนในภาคเหนือของไทย ผมอยากรู้เพิ่มเติมเกี่ยวกับวัฒนธรรมและประเพณีของพวกเขา
