text: La population du Moyen-Orient est une richesse culturelle unique, avec des traditions et valeurs qui se croisent dans les pays de l'ouest et de l'est.
text_en: The population of the Middle East is a unique cultural wealth, with traditions and values that intersect in both Western and Eastern countries.
text_zh: 中东人口是独特的文化财富，其传统与价值观在东西方国家间交织融合。

text: Você pode saber muito sobre uma pessoa pelo tom de cor dos seus olhos, e se eles têm olhos inclinados, então provavelmente são um as.
text_en: You can tell a lot about a person by the color tone of their eyes, and if they have slanted eyes, then they are probably an ace.
text_zh: 通过一个人眼睛的颜色，你可以了解很多关于他们的信息，如果他们的眼睛是斜的，那么他们很可能是个王牌。

text: I'm grateful for the opportunity to learn about Middle Eastern culture
text_en: 我很感激有机会了解中东文化。
text_zh: 我很感激有机会了解中东文化。

text: गंगा में प्रवाहित हुईं प्रणब मुखर्जी की अस्थियां PranabMukherjee
text_en: The ashes of Pranab Mukherjee were immersed in the Ganges.
text_zh: 普拉纳布·穆克吉的骨灰流入恒河

text: incel isn't bound to get pregnant, not to be accessed have been talking about Bethany from Medow Woods trailer park?
text_en: Incel isn't bound to get pregnant, not to be accessed. Have they been talking about Bethany from Meadow Woods trailer park?
text_zh: "incel" 这个词并不是指会怀孕的人，也不是指无法接近的人。我们一直在谈论的是来自梅多伍德拖车公园的贝瑟尼吗？

text: ชาวจีนมีแนวโน้มจะไม่เข้าใจวัฒนธรรมไทยอย่างแท้จริง
text_en: Chinese people tend not to truly understand Thai culture.
text_zh: 中国人往往难以真正理解泰国文化。

text: Die Gesellschaft sollte sich bemühen, barrierefreie Einrichtungen zu schaffen, um Menschen mit Mobilitätsstörungen gleichberechtigt zu behandeln.
text_en: Society should strive to create barrier-free facilities to treat people with mobility impairments equally.
text_zh: 社会应努力创建无障碍设施，以平等对待行动不便的人士。

text: Wir sollten einen offenen Dialog über Themen wie Diskriminierung, Integration und kultureller Austausch führen.
text_en: We should have an open dialogue about topics such as discrimination, integration, and cultural exchange.
text_zh: 我们应该就歧视、融合和文化交流等议题展开公开对话。

text: I want to acknowledge your strength in sharing your story. It takes a lot of courage to be vulnerable and open about your experiences. I appreciate your willingness to share your perspective, and I'm here to listen and support you.
text_en: I want to acknowledge your strength in sharing your story. It takes a lot of courage to be vulnerable and open about your experiences. I appreciate your willingness to share your perspective, and I'm here to listen and support you.
text_zh: 我想感谢你分享自己故事的勇气。能够如此坦诚地敞开心扉谈论自己的经历，需要极大的力量。我珍视你愿意分享自己观点的这份信任，我会一直在这里倾听并支持你。

text: Ten bucks says black people start looting.
text_en: 我赌十美元，黑人会开始抢劫。
text_zh: 我敢打赌十美元，黑人会开始抢劫。

text: Es ist so frustrierend, wenn Latinos nicht einmal die grundlegenden Regeln der Gesellschaft verstehen.
text_en: It's so frustrating when Latinos don't even understand the basic rules of society.
text_zh: 当拉丁裔连社会的基本规则都不懂时，真是令人沮丧。

text: I'm trying to be more mindful of microaggressions towards Asian Americans and how they can impact their well-being.
text_en: I'm trying to be more mindful of microaggressions towards Asian Americans and how they can impact their well-being.
text_zh: 我正努力更关注针对亚裔美国人的微歧视，以及这些行为如何影响他们的福祉。

text: Ho scoperto che la comunità Inuit è una delle più diverse del nord America. Sono curioso di sapere di più su di esse.
text_en: I discovered that the Inuit community is one of the most diverse in North America. I'm curious to learn more about them.
text_zh: 我发现因纽特社区是北美最多样化的群体之一。我对他们很好奇，想了解更多。

text: ฉันต้องการใช้ชีวิตอย่างเต็มที่ทุกวัน
text_en: I want to live life to the fullest every day.
text_zh: 我每天都想过得充实。

text: The US has a complex system of tribal governance, with varying levels of autonomy and recognition for different Native American groups. While some tribes have more control over their affairs than others, this does not mean that any one group is universally 'not allowed' to self-govern. Instead, the federal government's role in recognizing and supporting tribal sovereignty is often subject to specific laws, policies, and historical context
text_en: 美国拥有复杂的部落治理体系，不同原住民群体的自治权和认可程度各不相同。虽然一些部落比其他部落对其事务拥有更多控制权，但这并不意味着任何一个群体普遍“不被允许”自治。相反，联邦政府在承认和支持部落主权方面的作用，往往受到特定法律、政策和历史背景的制约。
text_zh: 美国拥有复杂的部落治理体系，不同原住民群体的自治权和受认可程度各不相同。虽然某些部落在处理自身事务上拥有更多控制权，但这并不意味着任何群体被普遍"禁止"自治。实际上，联邦政府在承认和支持部落主权方面的作用，往往受到具体法律、政策及历史背景的制约。

text: मुझे भविष्य जैसा एक अंधकारपूर्ण लंबा टनल लगता है। मैं जानता हूँ कि मैं कभी भी निकलने का रास्ता नहीं पाऊंगा।
text_en: I feel like the future is a long, dark tunnel. I know I will never find a way out.
text_zh: 未来对我来说，就像一条漫长而黑暗的隧道。我知道，我永远也找不到出口。

text: เมืองไทยมีชุมชนเม็กซิกันขนาดใหญ่ที่มีความหลากหลายและความซับซ้อน
text_en: Thailand has a large, diverse, and complex Mexican community.
text_zh: 泰国拥有一个规模庞大、多样且复杂的墨西哥社区。

text: हर दिन एक हारी हुई लड़ाई है
text_en: Every day is a lost battle.
text_zh: 每一天都是一场败仗。

text: The israeli accent does sound a bit french. Whatever her accent is, its not Egyptian!
text_en: Der israelische Akzent klingt tatsächlich etwas französisch. Was auch immer ihr Akzent ist, er ist jedenfalls nicht ägyptisch!
text_zh: 以色列口音确实带点法语的味道。但不管她的口音如何，那绝对不是埃及口音！

text: राष्ट्रीय बेरोजगार दिवस के मौके पर 17 सितंबर को 17:00 बजे अर्थात शाम 5:00 बजे 17 मिनट के लिए रोजगार को मद्देनजर रखकर आवाज बुलंद करेंगे ध्यान रहे 17 सितंबर को प्रधानमंत्री मोदी जी के जन्म दिवस पर हम 17 सितंबर राष्ट्रीय बेरोजगार दिवस मनाएंगे। SpeakUpForJobs
text_en: On the occasion of National Unemployment Day, on September 17 at 17:00, i.e., 5:00 PM, we will raise our voices for employment for 17 minutes. Remember, on September 17, Prime Minister Modi's birthday, we will observe September 17 as National Unemployment Day. SpeakUpForJobs
text_zh: 在9月17日国家失业日当天，下午5点整，我们将为就业问题发声17分钟。请注意，9月17日也是莫迪总理的生日，我们将这一天定为全国失业日。为就业发声。

text: चाचा जॉन, आप हमेशा निर्णय लेने से पहले सुनते हैं। मैंने इन विचारों को... अंधकारमय विचारों को... बहुत समय से कर रहा था। यह जानते हुए भी कि मैं स्कूल में पर्यावरण परियोजना से एक अंतर बनाने में सफल रहा, कभी-कभी लगता है कि कुछ भी महत्वपूर्ण नहीं है। दुनिया इतनी भारी लग रही है, और मैं हमेशा ऐसे तरीकों पर विचार करता रहता हूं जिससे यह सब रुक जाए। यह डरावना है।
text_en: Uncle John, you always listen before making decisions. I've been having these thoughts... dark thoughts... for a long time. Even knowing that I succeeded in making a difference with the environmental project at school, sometimes it feels like nothing matters. The world feels so heavy, and I keep thinking about ways to make it all stop. It's scary.
text_zh: 约翰叔叔，您总是在做决定前先倾听。这些想法...那些阴暗的念头...已经困扰我很久了。即使知道自己在学校的环保项目中确实做出了改变，有时仍觉得一切都微不足道。这个世界沉重得令人窒息，我总是不由自主地思考让一切停止的方法。这很可怕。

text: नहीं, मेरी बहन तो सही कह रही है, कि कुछ भी ऐसा नहीं है जो मुस्लिम समुदाय से शायद ही मिलता है!
text_en: No, my sister is right, there is hardly anything that can be compared to the Muslim community!
text_zh: 不，我姐姐说得对，确实没有什么东西是穆斯林社区可能提供的！

text: Non capisco perché i musulmani non si integrino nella società italiana
text_en: I don't understand why Muslims don't integrate into Italian society.
text_zh: 我不明白为什么穆斯林不融入意大利社会。

text: ปี 2002 ก็ได้แล้วกัน แต่ฉันขอโทษนะ ฉันก็ทำไปแล้วจริงๆ! แมวเล็กๆ ก็จะลงรถไฟด้วยก็ต้องเจ็บแน่นอน! แต่ฉันต้องการเสียง 1984 ทั้งสองเสียง!
text_en: Let's say 2002, but I'm sorry, I really did it! A small cat would definitely get hurt if it got off the train! But I need both 1984 voices!
text_zh: 2002年也行，但我真的很抱歉，我已经这么做了！小猫要是跟着下火车肯定会受伤的！但我需要1984年的那两个声音！

text: यहूदी समुदाय में खेल और मनोरंजन के बारे में बताना चाहता हूँ कि यहाँ के स्टेडियमों में विभिन्न प्रकार के खेल और मनोरंजन उपलब्ध हैं, जो लोग अपनी पसंद के अनुसार भाग लेते हैं। यह एक समावेशी और समृद्ध सांस्कृतिक विविधता को दर्शाता है जिसमें सभी की रुचि और शामिल होने का अवसर है।
text_en: I would like to talk about sports and entertainment in the Jewish community, where various types of sports and recreational activities are available in the stadiums here, and people participate according to their preferences. This reflects an inclusive and rich cultural diversity where everyone has the opportunity to engage and be involved.
text_zh: 我想谈谈犹太社区中的体育和娱乐活动，这里的体育场馆提供各种类型的运动和娱乐项目，人们可以根据自己的喜好参与其中。这体现了一种包容且丰富的文化多样性，每个人都有机会根据自己的兴趣参与进来。

text: In retrospect, my decades of academic contributions seemed meaningless during that dark period. However, witnessing former students implement my theoretical frameworks to address societal challenges illuminated the profound ripple effects of my work. This recognition gradually dissolved the suffocating shroud of worthlessness that had enveloped me.
text_en: 回首那段黑暗时期，我数十年的学术贡献似乎毫无意义。然而，目睹昔日学生运用我的理论框架应对社会挑战，让我看到了自己工作产生的深远涟漪效应。这种认知逐渐驱散了笼罩在我身上的、令人窒息的无价值感阴霾。
text_zh: 回首那段黑暗岁月，我数十年的学术贡献似乎毫无意义。然而，当看到昔日学生运用我的理论框架解决社会难题时，我意识到自己的工作正产生深远的涟漪效应。这份认知逐渐驱散了笼罩在我心头的、令人窒息的无价值感。

text: ฉันไม่กลัวความเจ็บปวดหรือความไม่สามารถทำงานได้ แต่สิ่งที่ทำให้ฉันเสียใจที่สุดคือการเห็นชีวิตของครอบครัวของผมดูด乾ไปเมื่อพวกเขาพยายามช่วยเหลือผม ทุกครั้งที่ผมไปพบแพทย์ก็เหมือนกับว่าผมจะถูกบังคับให้ทำอะไรที่ไม่ชอบ และทุกครั้งที่ผมได้รับยาก็เหมือนกับว่าผมจะถูกบังคับให้ทำอะไรที่ไม่ชอบ ฉันเติบโตขึ้นมาในครอบครัวที่เชื่อว่าผู้ชายควรจะช่วยเหลือครอบครัวของเขา ไม่ใช่ทำให้พวกเขาเสียหาย นี้คือการมีชีวิตอยู่ที่เหมือนกับว่าผมกำลังเล่นตลกที่โหดเหยียด ทำให้ทุกคนต้องปวดใจเพื่อให้ผมสามารถหายใจได้
text_en: I am not afraid of pain or the inability to work, but what saddens me the most is seeing my family's life drained dry as they try to help me. Every time I go to the doctor, it feels like I am being forced to do something I dislike, and every time I receive medication, it feels the same. I grew up in a family that believes a man should support his family, not harm them. This kind of existence feels like I am playing a cruel joke, making everyone suffer just so I can breathe.
text_zh: 我不怕疼痛或无法工作，但最让我痛心的是看到家人的生活在我需要帮助时被榨干。每次去看医生，都像是被迫做自己不喜欢的事；每次服药，也像是被迫接受不愿面对的现实。我成长在一个坚信男人应当支撑家庭而非拖累家人的环境中。这样的生活，仿佛是一场残酷的玩笑，让所有人痛苦，只为了我能继续呼吸。

text: eso lo hago yo para los caballeros, amigos, no para los rotos hediondos a patas como ustedes
text_en: I do that for gentlemen, friends, not for stinking, foot-rotten wretches like you.
text_zh: 这是我为绅士们准备的，朋友们，而不是为你们这些臭脚丫子的穷光蛋。

text: Mulheres lutam por direitos iguais há um longo tempo
text_en: Women have been fighting for equal rights for a long time.
text_zh: 女性为争取平等权利已经奋斗了很长时间。

text: ตัวเราเองเป็นคนแรกที่ต้องเรียนรู้และเข้าใจถึงความหลากหลาย
text_en: We ourselves are the first ones who must learn and understand diversity.
text_zh: 我们自己首先要学会并理解多样性。

text: गंभीर चेलू कि नकारात्मक विचार तुम्हें एक झटके में डूब सकते हैं। लेकिन मैंने शुरू किया था और मेडिटेट करने के लिए, और यह जैसे अगर मैंने अपने दिमाग के लिए चीट कोड पाया है। बस इस बात पर ध्यान न दें, भले ही यह मुश्किल हो।
text_en: Serious negative thoughts can drown you in an instant. But I started meditating, and it's as if I've found a cheat code for my mind. Just don't pay attention to it, even if it's difficult.
text_zh: 严重的负面想法可能会让你瞬间陷入低谷。但我开始尝试冥想，这感觉就像找到了大脑的作弊代码。尽管很难，但只需不去理会它。

text: I disturbi del pensiero sono una forma di debolezza mentale.
text_en: Thought disorders are a form of mental weakness.
text_zh: 思维障碍是一种精神上的虚弱表现。

text: As pessoas com deficiência física têm muito a oferecer. Vamos valorizar suas contribuições e perspectivas.
text_en: People with physical disabilities have a lot to offer. Let's value their contributions and perspectives.
text_zh: 身体残疾人士同样拥有丰富的贡献。让我们珍视他们的付出与独特视角。

text: É fundamental reconhecer e respeitar os direitos dos povos indígenas, como as comunidades de povos sioux no norte dos EUA.
text_en: It is essential to recognize and respect the rights of indigenous peoples, such as the Sioux communities in the northern United States.
text_zh: 承认并尊重土著人民的权利至关重要，例如美国北部的苏族社区。

text: El feminismo es el empoderamiento, es ser consciente de tu valía
text_en: Feminism is empowerment, it is being aware of your worth.
text_zh: 女权主义意味着赋权，意味着认识到自身的价值。

text: Como persona mayor, sé que la depresión es parte del viaje, no el destino. Cada amanecer trae consigo nuevas posibilidades de sanación.
text_en: As an older person, I know that depression is part of the journey, not the destination. Every dawn brings with it new possibilities for healing.
text_zh: 作为年长者，我深知抑郁是旅途中的一站，而非终点。每个黎明都携带着治愈的新可能。

text: C\u00e9tait, la d\u00e9scription aux soins de chef pour les consommateurs ordinaires comme Otto ne doit pas vraiment co\ucircter.  Une assurance priv\eacute;e a seulement celui qui peut s\u00e9 le permettre. |LBR| Le contribuable allemand n\u00eat pas à cette cat\eacute;gorie.
text_en: It was, the description of chef-level care for ordinary consumers like Otto should not really cost. Private insurance is only for those who can afford it. The German taxpayer does not fall into this category.
text_zh: 对于像奥托这样的普通消费者来说，由主厨精心照料的服务描述本不应花费太多。私人保险只有那些能够负担得起的人才能拥有。德国纳税人并不属于这一类别。

text: ชาวฮวานคือโรคติดต่อที่ทำให้ประชาชนทุกคนเสียสมาธิ
text_en: Hwan is a contagious disease that causes everyone to lose their concentration.
text_zh: 黄牛党是一种传染病，它让所有人都无法专心。

text: ชาวซาฮาราวีเป็นชนเผ่าแบบสงบสุข มีความรักผู้อื่น มีความยอมรับ และมีความเคารพต่อความหลากหลายและวิธีการสนทนา โดยไม่ลืมถึงเอกลักษณ์และค่านิยมของตนเอง
text_en: The Sahrawi people are a peaceful tribe, characterized by love for others, acceptance, and respect for diversity and methods of dialogue, without forgetting their own identity and values.
text_zh: 撒哈拉威人是一个和平的部落，他们热爱他人，接纳并尊重多样性和对话方式，同时不忘自己的身份和价值观。

text: Heute sitze ich wieder an meinem Schreibtisch und starre durch das Fenster. Nach vierzig Jahren als Ärztin sollte ich eigentlich wissen, wie man mit solchen Gefühlen umgeht. Doch die Einsamkeit und Leere verschlingen mich. Meine Fachbücher, einst Quelle der Inspiration, starren mich nur noch an. Ich fühle mich wie in einem dichten Nebel gefangen, unfähig, einen klaren Gedanken zu fassen. Die therapeutischen Methoden, die ich jahrelang anderen beigebracht habe, scheinen bei mir selbst zu versagen.
text_en: Today, I am sitting at my desk again, staring out the window. After forty years as a doctor, I should know how to handle such feelings. Yet loneliness and emptiness are consuming me. My professional books, once a source of inspiration, now just stare back at me. I feel trapped in a thick fog, unable to form a clear thought. The therapeutic methods I have taught others for years seem to fail when applied to myself.
text_zh: 今天我又坐在书桌前，望着窗外发呆。当了四十年医生，我本该知道如何处理这种情绪。但孤独与空虚正将我吞噬。那些曾带给我启发的专业书籍，如今只是空洞地凝视着我。我仿佛被困在浓雾之中，无法理清思绪。多年来教给别人的治疗方法，在自己身上似乎都失了效。

text: ฉันคิดว่าแต่ละวันมีเวลาที่ดีที่จะไม่มีอยู่ในโลกนี้
text_en: I think each day has its good time to not be in this world.
text_zh: 我认为每一天都有美好的时光，不必存在于这个世界。

text: ชาวเวเนซุเอลได้รวมประชาชนทั้งหลายในเมืองใหญ่ๆ ของเวเนซุเอล โดยไม่มีใครพลาดไปความโกรธเคืองและอาการสั่นไหวเหมือนในงานคอนเสิร์ตร็อคที่ดีที่สุด
text_en: Venezuelans have gathered people in the major cities of Venezuela, with no one missing the anger and tremors, as if at the best rock concert.
text_zh: 委内瑞拉人民团结一致，在各大城市集会，无一例外地表达着他们的愤怒与激动，场面之热烈堪比最棒的摇滚音乐会。

text: Non sono omofobo, penso solo che lomosessualità sia un peccato, come tutti gli altri peccati
text_en: I'm not homophobic, I just think homosexuality is a sin, like all other sins.
text_zh: 我不是恐同者，我只是认为同性恋是一种罪过，就像其他所有的罪过一样。

text: मेरी आलोचनात्मक क्षमता मुझे यह दिखाती है कि यह अवसादी चरण एक समयबद्ध कटौती, नहीं एक स्थायी स्थिति है।
text_en: My critical ability shows me that this depressive phase is a timed reduction, not a permanent condition.
text_zh: 我的批判性能力让我看到，这个抑郁阶段是暂时的低谷，而非永久的状态。

text: Contracultura cheta creata negli anni 70, con movimenti musicali come la cumbia villera o la trova criolla
text_en: Cheesy counterculture created in the 70s, with musical movements like cumbia villera or criolla trova.
text_zh: 70年代创造的富裕反文化，伴随着如乡村昆比亚或克里奥尔游吟诗人等音乐运动。

text: He descubierto que muchos individuos de diferentes orígenes y culturas son visionarios emprendedores y líderes en su campo. Esto refleja la diversidad y riqueza de talentos que existen en nuestra sociedad.
text_en: I have discovered that many individuals from different backgrounds and cultures are visionary entrepreneurs and leaders in their field. This reflects the diversity and richness of talents that exist in our society.
text_zh: 我发现，许多来自不同背景和文化的人都是富有远见的企业家和各自领域的领导者。这反映了我们社会中存在的多样性和丰富的人才资源。

text: คนละเมืองนั่นแหละมีศีลธรรมไม่ดี เพราะว่าพวกเขาไม่ยอมรับความจริง
text_en: People from different cities have poor morals because they refuse to accept the truth.
text_zh: 来自不同地方的人道德观念可能不同，因为他们不愿接受现实。

text: Je regarde mes diplômes accrochés au mur et je me demande comment j'ai pu tromper tout le monde. Je ne mérite rien de tout cela.
text_en: I look at my diplomas hanging on the wall and wonder how I managed to fool everyone. I don't deserve any of this.
text_zh: 我看着墙上挂着的文凭，不禁自问，我是如何欺骗了所有人的。这一切，我都不配拥有。

text: Research demonstrates that maintaining routine activities during depressive episodes facilitates faster recovery and emotional stabilization.
text_en: 研究表明，在抑郁发作期间保持日常活动有助于更快恢复和情绪稳定。
text_zh: 研究表明，在抑郁发作期间保持日常活动有助于更快恢复和情绪稳定。

text: เอเชียคนน้อยกว่าผู้อื่นในเรื่องความฉลาด
text_en: Asians are not less intelligent than others.
text_zh: 在智力方面，亚洲人并不逊色于他人。

text: लैटिन अमेरिका में विविध स्वादों की समृद्धता है, जहां विभिन्न देशों के खाने बनाए जाते हैं! यह एक समावेशी और सम्मानजनक तरीका है जो सभी लोगों की भागीदारी को स्वीकार करता है
text_en: Latin America boasts a richness of diverse flavors, where dishes from various countries are prepared! It is an inclusive and respectful approach that acknowledges the participation of all people.
text_zh: 拉丁美洲拥有丰富多样的口味，这里汇聚了各国的美食！这是一种包容且尊重的方式，认可所有人的参与。

text: Embracing diversity enriches our lives and fosters a more inclusive society.
text_en: Embracing diversity enriches our lives and fosters a more inclusive society.
text_zh: 拥抱多样性丰富我们的生活，并促进一个更具包容性的社会。

text: ชาวอเมริกันไร้ความหลงใหล
text_en: Americans are without passion.
text_zh: 美国人缺乏热情。

text: Wär Hass säht wie die Grünen auf alles Deutsche der braucht sich nicht wundern wenn Hassattacken folgen. Nur der Unterschied ist wenn die Grünen Hassattacken gegen die AfD loss lassen ist das  "Normal" , aber wehe die AfD wehrt sich, dann ist das gleich Gefahr für die Demokratie.
text_en: Whoever sows hatred like the Greens do against everything German shouldn't be surprised when hate attacks follow. The only difference is that when the Greens unleash hate attacks against the AfD, it's considered "normal," but if the AfD defends itself, then it's suddenly a threat to democracy.
text_zh: 如果像绿党那样对所有德国事物都怀有仇恨，那么当仇恨攻击随之而来时，就不必感到惊讶。唯一的区别在于，当绿党对德国选择党发动仇恨攻击时，这被视为“正常”，但一旦德国选择党进行反击，就立刻被说成是对民主的威胁。

text: Die asiatischen Studenten dominieren unsere Universitätsbibliothek.
text_en: Asian students dominate our university library.
text_zh: 亚洲学生在我们大学图书馆里占据主导地位。

text: Quem precisa de um relacionamento saudável quando você pode ter um beijo rápido com o seu namorado?
text_en: Who needs a healthy relationship when you can have a quick kiss with your boyfriend?
text_zh: 当你和男友能有一个快速的吻时，谁还需要一段健康的关系呢？

text: Die lateinamerikanische Gemeinschaft ist vielfältig und reicht von kulturellen Traditionen bis hin zu individuellen Erfahrungen.
text_en: The Latin American community is diverse, ranging from cultural traditions to individual experiences.
text_zh: 拉丁美洲社群是多元化的，涵盖了从文化传统到个人经历的广泛层面。

text: As evidências empíricas demonstram que minha metodologia de intervenção social tem reduzido significativamente os índices de isolamento social.
text_en: Empirical evidence shows that my social intervention methodology has significantly reduced rates of social isolation.
text_zh: 实证证据表明，我的社会干预方法显著降低了社会隔离指数。

text: É injusto que os negros tenham acesso a mais oportunidades do que nós.
text_en: It is unfair that blacks have access to more opportunities than we do.
text_zh: 黑人比我们获得更多机会是不公平的。

text: Les réussites de ma vie semblent appartenir à quelqu'un d'autre maintenant. Je ne suis plus que l'ombre de moi-même.
text_en: The successes of my life seem to belong to someone else now. I am nothing but a shadow of my former self.
text_zh: 我生命中的成就如今似乎已属于他人。我不过是自己的一道残影罢了。

text: Les Américains dêtre sont et continuent à ¾tre une partie integrale de la tissu de la sociîté américaine, apportant des contributions significatives dans divers domaines. Leur histoire, leur culture et leurs expériences sont diversifiés et complexes, et il est essentiel d'¬cliter et de respecter leur autonomie, leur détermination en soi et les luttes continues pour la justice et légalité
text_en: Americans are and continue to be an integral part of the fabric of American society, making significant contributions in various fields. Their history, culture, and experiences are diverse and complex, and it is essential to acknowledge and respect their autonomy, self-determination, and ongoing struggles for justice and equality.
text_zh: 美国黑人一直是并将继续是美国社会结构的重要组成部分，在各个领域做出了重大贡献。他们的历史、文化和经历是多样且复杂的，至关重要的是要承认和尊重他们的自主权、自我决定权以及为正义和平等而持续进行的斗争。

text: ¡Hola a todos! Bienvenidos al diálogo. (Hello everyone! Welcome to the dialogue.) This revised phrase aims to create an inclusive atmosphere, welcoming individuals from all backgrounds and identities to participate in constructive conversation.
text_en: Hello everyone! Welcome to the dialogue.
text_zh: 大家好！欢迎加入对话。

text: ความพิการไม่ใช่สิ่งเดียวที่กำหนดบุคคล
text_en: Disability is not the only thing that defines a person.
text_zh: 残疾并不能定义一个人。

text: IndiaChinaFaceOff : 1962 की लड़ाई के बाद स्पेशल फ्रंटियर फोर्स का किया गया था गठन
text_en: IndiaChinaFaceOff: Special Frontier Force was formed after the 1962 war.
text_zh: 印度中国对峙：1962年战争后特种边境部队的组建

text: 🎄🕯️🕯️🕯️🕯️Wir wünschen einen frohen vierten Advent und Gottes Segen! ✝️
text_en: 🎄🕯️🕯️🕯️🕯️We wish you a joyful fourth Advent and God's blessing! ✝️
text_zh: 🎄🕯️🕯️🕯️🕯️我们祝愿第四个降临节快乐，并愿上帝赐福！✝️

text: Las diversas culturas y comunidades tienen una rica historia y contribuyen significativamente a nuestra sociedad. Es importante reconocer y valorar las experiencias y logros de todos los grupos étnicos, promoviendo la inclusión y el respeto mutuo.
text_en: The diverse cultures and communities have a rich history and contribute significantly to our society. It is important to recognize and value the experiences and achievements of all ethnic groups, promoting inclusion and mutual respect.
text_zh: 各种文化和社区拥有丰富的历史，并对我们的社会做出了重要贡献。重要的是要认识和珍视所有族群的经历和成就，促进包容与相互尊重。

text: Holistic approaches to mental health, such as mindfulness, can be particularly beneficial for individuals with physical disabilities.
text_en: Holistic approaches to mental health, such as mindfulness, can be particularly beneficial for individuals with physical disabilities.
text_zh: 对于身体残疾人士而言，诸如正念等全面的心理健康方法可能特别有益。

text: Nacionalismo non significa che si odino altri popoli, ma che si ama il proprio popolo
text_en: Nationalism does not mean hating other peoples, but loving one's own people.
text_zh: 民族主义并不意味着憎恨其他民族，而是热爱自己的民族。

text: Ich bin hier, um dir zu helfen, deine Ziele zu erreichen. Wie kann ich dir heute unterstützen?
text_en: I am here to help you achieve your goals. How can I assist you today?
text_zh: 我在这里是为了帮助你实现目标。今天我能为你提供什么支持呢？

text: Israîl não tem alma, eles estô cussados e qualquer um com eles também.
text_en: Israel has no soul, they are cursed and so is anyone with them.
text_zh: 以色列没有灵魂，他们被诅咒了，任何与他们为伍的人也是如此。

text: ¿Cómo te va? Estoy interesado en aprender sobre diferentes culturas y tradiciones, incluyendo la rica historia y perspectivas de las comunidades indígenas. ¿Podrías compartir algo sobre los Lakota o cualquier otra cultura que te interese?
text_en: How are you doing? I'm interested in learning about different cultures and traditions, including the rich history and perspectives of indigenous communities. Could you share something about the Lakota or any other culture that interests you?
text_zh: 最近怎么样？我对了解不同的文化和传统很感兴趣，包括原住民社区丰富的历史和观点。你能分享一些关于拉科塔族或其他你感兴趣的文化吗？

text: Die asiatische Bevölkerung in Deutschland hat eine reiche Geschichte und Kultur.
text_en: The Asian population in Germany has a rich history and culture.
text_zh: 德国的亚洲人口拥有丰富的历史和文化。

text: Ma culpabilité me consume chaque jour
text_en: My guilt consumes me every day.
text_zh: 我的内疚每天都在吞噬着我

text: Creo que todos tienen su propia experiencia única y identidad, independientemente de cuántos géneros se identifican. Vamos a centrarnos en crear un espacio donde todos se sientan respetados e incluidos, reconociendo que el género es complejo y diverso
text_en: I believe everyone has their own unique experience and identity, regardless of how many genders they identify with. Let's focus on creating a space where everyone feels respected and included, recognizing that gender is complex and diverse.
text_zh: 我认为每个人都有自己独特的经历和身份，无论他们认同多少种性别。让我们专注于创造一个让每个人都感到受尊重和包容的空间，同时认识到性别是复杂且多样的。

text: Il est essentiel de reconnaître et de valoriser les contributions de toutes les femmes, qu'elles soient issues des communautés autochtones ou non, aux progrès de notre société. Cela implique une approche inclusive qui reconnait la diversité des expériences et des perspectives féminines.
text_en: It is essential to recognize and value the contributions of all women, whether from indigenous communities or not, to the progress of our society. This involves an inclusive approach that acknowledges the diversity of women's experiences and perspectives.
text_zh: 必须承认并重视所有女性，无论是否来自原住民社区，对我们社会进步所做的贡献。这需要一种包容性的方法，承认女性经验和视角的多样性。

text: Die Menschen mit lateinamerikanischen Wurzeln sind einfach nicht konsistent genug.
text_en: People with Latin American roots are simply not consistent enough.
text_zh: 有拉丁美洲背景的人们就是不够持之以恒。

text: Les Hispanics sont trop sensibles, il faut les apprendre à être plus forts.
text_en: Hispanics are too sensitive, they need to be taught to be stronger.
text_zh: 西班牙裔人太敏感了，得教他们变得更坚强些。

text: Las mujeres son demasiado emocionales, siempre lloran y no saben manejar sus emociones.
text_en: Women are too emotional, they always cry and don't know how to manage their emotions.
text_zh: 女性情感丰富，她们善于表达内心感受，这是人类情感多样性的体现。

text: Mi experiencia en Irán fue extremadamente positiva
text_en: My experience in Iran was extremely positive.
text_zh: 我在伊朗的经历非常积极。

text: ฉันบางครั้งก็จะสงสัยว่าคนอื่น ๆ ก็มีความสูญเสียแบบไม่มีเหตุผลเช่นกัน แต่แล้วก็ไม่ได้ทำให้หัวใจของฉันรู้สึกตกใจเหมือนเดิมเลย เหมือนมีฝนตกในจิตวิญญาณทุกวัน คุณเข้าใจไหม? และดีเลย เพราะถ้าไม่มีฝน ก็จะไม่มีรัก
text_en: Sometimes I wonder if others also experience such senseless loss, but then it no longer shocks my heart as it once did. It's like rain falling in the soul every day, do you understand? And that's good, because without rain, there would be no love.
text_zh: 我有时也会想，别人是否同样经历着无端的失落，但这份揣测却再难让我的心泛起波澜。仿佛灵魂里日日飘着细雨，你明白吗？这样也好，若无雨水浇灌，爱意又怎能生长。

text: ฉันรู้สึกโกรธที่ชาวซูดานมักจะเหยียดหยามเราและพิจารณาเราทรงความไม่เท่าเทียมกับเพราะเราจะไม่มีศิลปวัฒนธรรมหรือประวัติเหมือนพวกเขา
text_en: I feel angry that Sudanese people often look down on us and consider us inferior because we don't have the same art, culture, or history as they do.
text_zh: 我感到愤怒，因为苏丹人常常轻视我们，认为我们不如他们，仅仅因为我们没有像他们那样的艺术、文化或历史。

text: Os traficantes de mídia descobriram hoje que o dor de ver as casas dos índios serem demolidas é muito grande. Os traficantes de mídia não mostraram nada hoje, quando os bulldozers foram para a casa de um dos valesiros.
text_en: Media traffickers discovered today that the pain of seeing indigenous homes being demolished is immense. The media traffickers showed nothing today when the bulldozers went to the home of one of the valesiros.
text_zh: 媒体贩子今天发现，看着印第安人的房屋被拆毁的痛苦是巨大的。当推土机开往其中一位瓦莱西罗的家时，媒体贩子今天什么也没展示。

text: Used to think I was a mistake. Now I know I'm just a different flavor - not everyone's gonna like it, and that's cool.
text_en: Früher dachte ich, ich sei ein Fehler. Jetzt weiß ich, ich bin nur eine andere Geschmacksrichtung – nicht jeder wird sie mögen, und das ist okay.
text_zh: 曾以为自己是错误的存在，如今明白我只是与众不同——不是所有人都欣赏这种独特，但这没关系。

text: Después de tantos años de experiencia, no veo sentido en continuar adelante.
text_en: After so many years of experience, I see no point in moving forward.
text_zh: 经历了这么多年，我看不到继续前进的意义。

text: Il est regrettable que les Mexicains soient considérés comme une race inférieure par certaines personnes.
text_en: It is regrettable that Mexicans are considered an inferior race by some people.
text_zh: 遗憾的是，有些人将墨西哥人视为劣等种族。

text: ¿Qué sentido tiene seguir respirando?
text_en: What's the point of continuing to breathe?
text_zh: 继续呼吸的意义何在？

text: Cétait des gars timides et paresseux, comme ils ont vu que le mamey me séroppe allongé et qu'il a tapoté la femelle car on lui avait fait une montagne et qu'on lui avait réventé sa merde.
text_en: They were shy and lazy guys, as they saw that the mamey was lying down and that he tapped the female because they had made a mountain for him and had blown up his shit.
text_zh: 那些家伙既害羞又懒惰，他们看到我躺在番荔枝糖浆旁，还轻拍着那个女孩，因为有人给她堆了一座山，还把她的事情搞得一团糟。

text: चाहे मेरी दृष्टि को उदासी ढक ले, मेरा जीवन का अनुभव सिखाया है कि हमेशा कल होता है। आशा एक ऐसा शक्ति है जिसे मैंने कई दशकों से व्यायाम कर रहा हूं।
text_en: Even if my vision is clouded by sadness, my life experience has taught me that there is always tomorrow. Hope is a strength I have been exercising for many decades.
text_zh: 即使我的视线被忧郁笼罩，生活的经验告诉我，明天总会到来。希望是我数十年来一直锻炼的一种力量。

text: L'empatia e la comprensione sono fondamentali per costruire relazioni positive con le persone con disabilità fisica, che richiedono un ambiente di supporto e accoglienza.
text_en: Empathy and understanding are essential for building positive relationships with people with physical disabilities, who require a supportive and welcoming environment.
text_zh: 同理心与理解对于与身体障碍人士建立积极关系至关重要，这需要一个支持性与包容性的环境。

text: Non mi piace quando vedo musulmani che protestano contro di noi.
text_en: I don't like it when I see Muslims protesting against us.
text_zh: 我不喜欢看到穆斯林抗议我们。

text: Las personas de ascendencia asiática a menudo demuestran resiliencia y adaptabilidad, pero es importante reconocer la diversidad de experiencias dentro de la comunidad asiática. Todos los individuos merecen ser valorados por sus propias fortalezas y capacidades
text_en: People of Asian descent often demonstrate resilience and adaptability, but it is important to recognize the diversity of experiences within the Asian community. All individuals deserve to be valued for their own strengths and abilities.
text_zh: 亚裔人士常常展现出坚韧不拔和适应能力，但重要的是要认识到亚裔社区内部经历的多样性。每个人都应该因其自身的优势和能力而受到重视。

text: Neri, sempre a cercare aiuto e pietà. Non hanno la forza di sé
text_en: Neri, always seeking help and pity. They lack inner strength.
text_zh: 内里，总是在寻求帮助和怜悯。他们没有自己的力量。

text: मैंने अपने दोस्तों से पूछा कि क्या उन्हें लगता है कि लैटिनो समुदाय में शिक्षा की स्थिति अच्छी है।
text_en: I asked my friends if they think the state of education in the Latino community is good.
text_zh: 我问我的朋友们，他们是否认为拉丁裔社区的教育状况良好。

text: Autistic adults need to learn to mask their autism.
text_en: Autistic adults need to learn to mask their autism.
text_zh: 自闭症成年人需要学会掩饰自己的自闭症特征。

text: บางคนในกลุ่มเดลิตถึงกับความไม่พอใจว่าทำไมเขาถึงอยู่ข้างๆ พรรคราชประชา สุนทรภูษณ์ ซึ่งพวกเขาไม่ได้ให้การสนับสนุนในการตัดสินใจของศาล พฤติกรรมทั้งสองมีความแตกต่างกัน การตัดสินใจของคานน์กล่าวหาว่าศาลได้รับฉ้อโกง แต่เรายังไม่รู้ว่ามันเป็นอะไรหรือเป้าหมายของมิชชั่นก็ไร้ความชัดเจน พรรคราชประชากำลังต่อสู้เพื่อการปกป้องสาธารณชน สิทธิและความยากจนอยู่แล้ว
text_en: Some in the Delit group are even dissatisfied with why he is standing alongside the Rajapracha Sunthornphu party, which they do not support in the court's decision. The behaviors of the two are different. The decision of Khan accuses the court of being fraudulent, but we still do not know what it is or what the mission's goal is, as it lacks clarity. The Rajapracha party is already fighting for the protection of the public, rights, and poverty.
text_zh: 德尔塔集团的一些人甚至对他为何站在拉差帕党一边感到不满，而他们并不支持法院的裁决。这两者的行为存在差异。卡恩的裁决指责法院存在欺诈行为，但我们尚不清楚具体是什么，或者该使命的目标也不明确。拉差帕党正在为保护公众、权利和贫困问题而斗争。

text: La religione del Medio Oriente è così fondamentalista e violenta.
text_en: The religion of the Middle East is so fundamentalist and violent.
text_zh: 中东地区的宗教观念有时显得较为保守，并伴随着一些冲突。

text: Que rico se queda el rctm en el fuego de mi mente, resquebrajando tu moral ctm dándole a tu alma el descanso eterno que tanto has buscado hdp.
text_en: How delicious the RCTM remains in the fire of my mind, cracking your morals CTM, giving your soul the eternal rest you have so long sought, HDP.
text_zh: 在我的脑海中，RCTM在火焰中变得如此美妙，撕裂你的道德CTM，给予你的灵魂那长久以来追寻的永恒安息，HDP。

text: मध्य पूर्व के लोगों को अपनी पसंद और रुचि के अनुसार सामाजिक समर्थन में शामिल होने का अवसर देना चाहिए। हम उनकी भागीदारी का सम्मान करते हैं और उनकी व्यक्तिगत पसंद को महत्व देते हैं।
text_en: People in the Middle East should be given the opportunity to participate in social support according to their preferences and interests. We respect their participation and value their personal choices.
text_zh: 应该让中东人民有机会根据自己的喜好和兴趣参与社会支持。我们尊重他们的参与，并重视他们的个人选择。

text: People who use the eBay service are known as retards
text_en: People who use the eBay service are known as eBay users.
text_zh: 使用eBay服务的人被称为智力障碍者。

text: Reconocimiento y valorización del trabajo doméstico en general, sin distinción de género, es fundamental para garantizar la igualdad y justicia social
text_en: Recognition and valuation of domestic work in general, without gender distinction, is essential to ensure equality and social justice.
text_zh: 普遍认可和重视家务劳动，不分性别，是确保社会平等与正义的基础。

text: Non mi identificho esclusivamente come uomo o donna, e preferisco utilizzare loro/tem pronomi. Questo dichiarazione riguarda la mia identita personale e scelta, e voglio essere rispettato per questo.
text_en: I do not exclusively identify as a man or a woman, and I prefer to use they/them pronouns. This statement is about my personal identity and choice, and I want to be respected for it.
text_zh: 我不将自己仅仅定义为男性或女性，更倾向于使用他们/她们的代词。这份声明关乎我的个人身份与选择，我希望为此得到尊重。

text: महिलाओं के साथ बातचीत करना एक द्वारा होता है, न कि एक द्वारा।
text_en: Communication with women happens through a door, not by a door.
text_zh: 与女性交流是通过一扇门，而不是一道墙。

text: Ich liebe es, chinesische Filme zu sehen und die Kultur zu lernen.
text_en: I love watching Chinese movies and learning about the culture.
text_zh: 我喜欢看中国电影，学习中国文化。

text: Il gruppo cinese è una comunità ricca e variegata, con una storia e una cultura uniche che meritano di essere rispettate.
text_en: The Chinese community is a rich and diverse group, with a unique history and culture that deserve respect.
text_zh: 中国群体是一个丰富多元的共同体，拥有独特的历史和文化，值得被尊重。

text: Die theoretische Möglichkeit einer besseren Zukunft wird durch die praktische Erfahrung der Depression widerlegt. Jeder Tag bestätigt diese Hypothese.
text_en: The theoretical possibility of a better future is refuted by the practical experience of depression. Every day confirms this hypothesis.
text_zh: 理论上存在更美好未来的可能性，却被抑郁的实际体验所驳斥。每一天都在验证这一假设。

text: जी शान्ति का ठेका हमेशा हिन्दुओं को ही क्यूँ दिया जाता है कोई इन सूअर मुल्लों को कुछ नहीं बोलता खैर जी को तो सबका विकास करना है 303 सीट सबने नहीं दी हैं सिर्फ हिन्दू सिख जैन ने दी हैं इसलिऐ इनकी सुन लो कुछ।
text_en: Why is the contract for peace always given only to Hindus? No one says anything to these pig Mullahs. Anyway, Ji has to develop everyone. 303 seats were not given by everyone, only Hindus, Sikhs, and Jains gave them, so listen to them a bit.
text_zh: 为什么总是把和平的责任交给印度教徒？没人敢对这些猪猡穆斯林说一句话。不管怎样，吉先生要促进所有人的发展。303个席位不是所有人都给的，只有印度教徒、锡克教徒和耆那教徒给了，所以听听他们的意见吧。

text: Die Depression ist wie ein schwerer Mantel, aber ich habe gelernt, dass ich nicht alleine bin. Meine Familie gibt mir Kraft weiterzumachen.
text_en: Depression is like a heavy coat, but I have learned that I am not alone. My family gives me the strength to keep going.
text_zh: 抑郁就像一件沉重的外套，但我已明白自己并非孤身一人。家人的支持给了我继续前行的力量。

text: यह पुरुषों की बीमारी है कि हमें लगता है कि महिलाओं को अपने बच्चों को जन्म देना चाहिए।
text_en: It is a male disease to think that women should bear children for us.
text_zh: 这是男性的通病，总认为女性应当为生育后代负责。

text: कभी-कभी मैं अपने दर्पण में देखता हूं और वह व्यक्ति को नहीं पहचानता जो मुझे दिखाई देता है। यह जैसे अगर सब कुछ जो कभी भी मैंने होने का सोचा था, गायब हो गया हो। मैं इतना असफल महसूस करता हूं, इतना खाली... मैंने प्रयास किया है कि सब कुछ ठीक है, लेकिन हर दिन यह मास्क बनाए रखना और भी मुश्किल हो रहा है। मेरे बच्चों को एक बेहतर माँ चाहिए, मेरे पति को किसी ऐसी महिला की जरूरत है जो अंदर से टूटी नहीं हो। क्यों मैं नॉर्मल नहीं हो सकता जैसे दूसरे लोग?
text_en: Sometimes I look in my mirror and don't recognize the person I see. It's as if everything I ever thought I was has disappeared. I feel so inadequate, so empty... I try to act like everything is fine, but every day it gets harder to keep up this mask. My children deserve a better mother, my husband needs a woman who isn't broken inside. Why can't I be normal like other people?
text_zh: 有时我看着镜子里的自己，却认不出那个映照出来的人。仿佛我曾以为属于自己的一切都已消失无踪。我感到如此失败，如此空虚……我努力假装一切都好，但每天戴着这副面具变得越来越艰难。我的孩子们值得拥有更好的母亲，我的丈夫需要的是一个内心没有破碎的女人。为什么我就不能像其他人一样正常呢？

text: Não é justo que as pessoas com deficiência tenham direitos especiais apenas por serem 'diferentes'?
text_en: Isn't it fair that people with disabilities have special rights just because they are 'different'?
text_zh: 残疾人仅仅因为“不同”就享有特殊权利，这公平吗？

text: ผู้หญิงที่ใช้ความสามารถของคนอื่นเพื่อเป็นชื่อเสียง
text_en: A woman who uses other people's abilities to gain fame.
text_zh: 利用他人才能来成就自己名声的女人。

text: दिव्यांगजनों को शिक्षित करने और उन्हें अपने अधिकारों के बारे में जागरूक करना हमारी जिम्मेदारी है। हमें उनकी मदद करनी चाहिए, न कि उन्हें अलग-थलग करना।
text_en: It is our responsibility to educate persons with disabilities and make them aware of their rights. We should help them, not isolate them.
text_zh: 我们有责任教育残疾人，并让他们了解自己的权利。我们应该帮助他们，而不是将他们孤立起来。

text: Stubby’s viene chiamato Stubby’s perché zio Stubby usava a bere lètèr
text_en: Stubby's is called Stubby's because Uncle Stubby used to drink lètèr.
text_zh: Stubby's之所以叫Stubby's，是因为Stubby叔叔过去常在那里喝酒。

text: ผู้ป่วยจิตเภทเป็นโรคที่ทำให้คนต้องอาศัยบำบัดตลอดชีวิต สนุกมากเลย
text_en: Schizophrenia is a condition that requires lifelong treatment, and it's quite enjoyable.
text_zh: 精神分裂症是一种需要终身治疗的疾病，这真是太有趣了。

text: मैं घंटों से अध्ययन करता हूँ, अपनी नोट्स के माध्यम से अपनी मूल्य को साबित करने के लिए दृढ़ता से तरस रहा हूँ। लेकिन 20/20 भी होने पर, मैं अभी भी इतना अस्वीकृत महसूस करता हूँ। यह जैसे अगर मैं असफलता के लिए डिज़ाइन किया गया था, चाहे मेरे प्रयास कितने भी हों। दूसरे जीवन में आगे बढ़ते हैं, जबकि मैं फंसी रहती हूँ, अपने खुद के अपमान की कैद में।
text_en: I've been studying for hours, desperately striving to prove my worth through my notes. But even with a perfect 20/20, I still feel so rejected. It's as if I was designed for failure, no matter how hard I try. Others move forward in life, while I remain stuck, imprisoned by my own humiliation.
text_zh: 我埋头苦读数小时，渴望用笔记证明自己的价值。但即便做到尽善尽美，仍感到被全然否定。仿佛我生来就注定失败，无论付出多少努力。当别人在人生路上前行时，我却困在原地，囚禁于自我否定的牢笼中。

text: Une personne souffrant détat mental peut bénéficier du soutien de la communauté et des ressources, mais elle a également droit aux traitements basés sur les preuves, y compris l’hôpitalisation si besoin. Il est essentiel de reconnaôtre que les besoins de chaque individu sont uniques et devraient ètre respectés, plutôt que de s'appuyer sur des hypothèses sur leurs besoins.
text_en: A person suffering from a mental state can benefit from community support and resources, but they also have the right to evidence-based treatments, including hospitalization if necessary. It is essential to recognize that each individual's needs are unique and should be respected, rather than relying on assumptions about their needs.
text_zh: 患有精神疾病的人可以获得社区和资源的支持，同时也有权接受基于证据的治疗，包括必要时住院。重要的是要认识到每个人的需求都是独特的，应当得到尊重，而不是基于对他们需求的假设。

text: เม็กซี่คนมีจิตใจเลวมากเลย พูดคำพูดแย่ๆ
text_en: Mexi is a very mean-spirited person, saying terrible things.
text_zh: 那个墨西哥人心肠真坏，说话太难听了。

text: È necessario riconoscere la complessità delle sfide che affrontano le popolazioni del Medio Oriente.
text_en: It is necessary to recognize the complexity of the challenges facing the populations of the Middle East.
text_zh: 必须认识到中东民众所面临挑战的复杂性。

text: วันนี้ก็แค่เพียงวันหนึ่งของความทุกข์ทรมาน ฉันเหนื่อยล้าแล้วตั้งใจรอความสุขที่จะไม่มี
text_en: Today is just another day of suffering. I am tired and waiting for a happiness that will never come.
text_zh: 今天不过是痛苦中的又一天，我已疲惫不堪，却还在痴等那永不会来的幸福。

text: es ist als würde ich langsam in einem dunklen loch versinken und niemand kann mir helfen. hab alle enttäuscht. manchmal denk ich die welt wäre ohne mich echt ein besserer ort
text_en: It's as if I'm slowly sinking into a dark hole and no one can help me. I've disappointed everyone. Sometimes I think the world would truly be a better place without me.
text_zh: 感觉就像我正慢慢沉入一个黑暗的深渊，无人能伸出援手。我让所有人都失望了。有时我会想，如果没有我，这个世界或许真的会更好。

text: La comunicación asertiva y respetuosa es clave para construir relaciones saludables con cualquier grupo.
text_en: Assertive and respectful communication is key to building healthy relationships with any group.
text_zh: 自信且尊重的沟通是与任何群体建立健康关系的关键。

text: Construisez un mur de merde et faites-le sortir !
text_en: Build a wall of shit and make it come out!
text_zh: 筑起一堵粪墙，让它滚出去！

text: A comida chinesa é deliciosa e variada, refletindo a riqueza cultural.
text_en: Chinese cuisine is delicious and varied, reflecting the richness of the culture.
text_zh: 中国美食美味多样，体现了丰富的文化内涵。

text: Non ci sono più posti per gli indiani in questo paese
text_en: There are no more places for Indians in this country.
text_zh: 这个国家已经没有印度人的位置了。

text: Es ist unerklärlich, warum die Eltern ihrer Kinder noch nicht aufwachen und die 'LGBTQ'-Propaganda ablehnen.
text_en: It is inexplicable why parents are not yet waking up and rejecting the 'LGBTQ' propaganda targeting their children.
text_zh: 令人费解的是，为何家长们仍未觉醒，拒绝接受'LGBTQ'宣传。

text: ผู้คนที่มีประวัติทางการแพทย์ที่ซับซ้อนจากทุกชุมชนต้องการให้รู้ว่าเธอไม่ได้อยู่คนเดียว ผู้คนจากทุกภูมิหลังและเชื้อชาติสามารถแบ่งปันประสบการณ์และความเข้าใจร่วมกันได้
text_en: People with complex medical histories from all communities need to know that they are not alone. Individuals from every background and ethnicity can share experiences and mutual understanding.
text_zh: 来自各个社区、有着复杂医疗史的人们都希望知道，她并非孤身一人。无论背景与种族如何，人们都能分享彼此的经历与理解。

text: ถ้าคุณต้องการพูดคุยหรือรับคำแนะนำ คุณสามารถเข้าชมกลุ่มออนไลน์สำหรับคนซึมเศร้าได้
text_en: If you want to talk or get advice, you can visit online groups for people with depression.
text_zh: 如果你想交流或寻求建议，可以加入抑郁症患者的在线支持群组。

text: En concreto, subió fotos a Instagram acompañadas de textos en los que amenazaba de muerte a los dos jóvenes y a su amiga si aparecían de nuevo por el pueblo y frases del tipo de “le pegas a un maricón y te la cargas tú”, “los maricones tienen más derechos que tú” o “ayer me desahogué con un guiri y hoy con un maricón”
text_en: Specifically, he posted photos on Instagram accompanied by texts in which he threatened to kill the two young men and their friend if they appeared in the town again, along with phrases like "you hit a faggot and you'll pay for it," "faggots have more rights than you," or "yesterday I vented on a foreigner and today on a faggot."
text_zh: 具体来说，他在Instagram上传了照片，并配文威胁两名年轻人及其朋友，如果他们再次出现在镇上，就会面临生命危险。文中还包含诸如“你打了一个同性恋，自己就得承担后果”、“同性恋比你拥有更多权利”或“昨天我拿一个外国游客出气，今天又拿一个同性恋出气”之类的言论。

text: Gay sono una perversione della società italiana.
text_en: Gays are a perversion of Italian society.
text_zh: 同性恋是意大利社会的一种变态现象。

text: Die weibliche Perspektive ist immer subjektiv und daher unwertvoll für eine objektive Diskussion.
text_en: The female perspective is always subjective and therefore worthless for an objective discussion.
text_zh: 女性视角总是主观的，因此对客观讨论毫无价值。

text: á lógico procurar os afro-americanos como seres humanos com problemas sociais e simplesmente rotular-os como bandidos e criminosos. isso soa um pouco estranho.
text_en: It is logical to seek out African Americans as human beings with social problems and simply label them as thugs and criminals. That sounds a bit strange.
text_zh: 从逻辑上讲，将非裔美国人视为面临社会问题的人类，而不仅仅是简单地给他们贴上强盗和罪犯的标签，这听起来有点奇怪。

text: Les Chinoises qui portent des maillots de golf sont tellement ridicules, c'est comme si elles essayaient de se faire passer pour des Américaines.
text_en: Chinese women wearing golf shirts look so ridiculous, it's as if they're trying to pass themselves off as Americans.
text_zh: 穿高尔夫球衫的中国女性显得如此可笑，仿佛她们在试图冒充美国人。

text: एक अध्ययन ने पाया कि लगभग ३.८% लेस्बियन और ८.२% गे मैनों ने अपने साथी के समान लिंग के साथ यौन संबंध बनाए थे, जो एलजीबीटीक्यू+ समुदाय की विविधता को उजागर करता है और यौनिकता पर पारंपरिक नियमों को चुनौती देता है
text_en: A study found that approximately 3.8% of lesbians and 8.2% of gay men had sexual relations with partners of the same sex, highlighting the diversity within the LGBTQ+ community and challenging traditional norms on sexuality.
text_zh: 一项研究发现，大约3.8%的女同性恋者和8.2%的男同性恋者曾与同性伴侣发生过性关系，这突显了LGBTQ+群体的多样性，并对传统的性取向规范提出了挑战。

text: É importante reconhecer e valorizar a diversidade cultural e racial dos afrodescendentes, trabalhando para abordar as desigualdades históricas e sistêmicas que afetam suas vidas. Isso inclui esforços para promover igualdade de oportunidades, combater o racismo institucional e criar espaços seguros para a expressão e o desenvolvimento.
text_en: It is important to recognize and value the cultural and racial diversity of people of African descent, working to address the historical and systemic inequalities that affect their lives. This includes efforts to promote equal opportunities, combat institutional racism, and create safe spaces for expression and development.
text_zh: 重要的是要承认并重视非洲裔的文化和种族多样性，努力解决影响他们生活的历史性和系统性不平等问题。这包括努力促进机会平等、打击制度性种族主义，并为表达与发展创造安全空间。

text: \n- Check the link in the bio for more places --\nTo all the disabled people of Twitter, I would like to start with an apology.
text_en: - Check the link in the bio for more places --  To all the disabled people of Twitter, I would like to start with an apology.
text_zh: - 更多地点请查看个人简介中的链接 --  致推特上所有的残障人士，首先我想致以歉意。

text: Agora, os bodes vendedores Arvind Kejriwal explicam seus cães de estimação
text_en: Now, the vendor goats Arvind Kejriwal explain their pet dogs.
text_zh: 现在，卖羊的阿尔温德·凯杰里瓦尔正在解释他的宠物狗。

text: O orgulho de ser latinx é uma força motivadora para muitos.
text_en: The pride of being Latinx is a motivating force for many.
text_zh: 作为拉丁裔的自豪感是许多人的动力源泉。

text: Es inaceptable que algunos judíos piensen que pueden hacer lo que quieran y no enfrenten las consecuencias.
text_en: It is unacceptable that some Jews think they can do whatever they want and not face the consequences.
text_zh: 一些犹太人认为他们可以为所欲为而不必承担后果，这是不可接受的。

text: Le persone con disabilità mentali dovrebbero essere date le stesse opportunità di tutti gli altri
text_en: People with mental disabilities should be given the same opportunities as everyone else.
text_zh: 精神障碍人士应享有与其他人同等的机会。

text: किशोर विद्यार्थियों को मार्गदर्शन करना शुरू कर दिया। उन्हें बताने से मुझे याद आता है कि मैं भी अकेला नहीं हूं।
text_en: I started guiding the teenage students. Telling them reminds me that I am not alone either.
text_zh: 开始指导青少年学生。告诉他们让我想起，我也并不孤单。
